1,1,"Bismil|lahir|Raḥmaanir|Ra-ḥeem"
1,2,"Al-Ḥamdu|Lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen;"
1,3,"ʹAr-Raḥmaanir|Raḥeem;"
1,4,"Maaliki|Yawmid|Deen!"
1,5,"ʹIyyaaka|naʻbudu|wa-ʹiyyaaka|nastaʻeen."
1,6,"ʹIhdinaṣ|Ṣiraaṭal|Mustaq̣eem."
1,7,"Ṣiraaṭal|laẓeena|ʹanʻamta|ʻalayhim|G̣ayril|mag̣ḍoobi|ʻalayhim|wa-laḍ|ḍaaalleen."
2,1,"ʹAlif-laaam-meeem."
2,2,"Ẓaalikal|Kitaabu|laa -|rayba|feeh.|Hudal|lil-Muttaq̣een;"
2,3,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuʹminoona|bil-G̣aybi|wa-yuq̣eemoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|yuñfiq̣oon;"
2,4,"Wallaẓeena|yuʹminoona|bimaaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|miñ|q̣ablik,|wa-bilʹAakhirati|hum|yooq̣inoon."
2,5,"ʹUlaaaʹika|ʻalaa|Hudam|mir|Rabbihim,|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
2,6,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|Kafaroo|sawaaaʹun|ʻalayhim|ʹaʹañẓartahum|ʹam|lam|tuñẓirhum|laa|yuʹminoon."
2,7,"Khatamal|laahu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|wa-ʻalaa|samʻihim,|wa-ʻalaaa|ʹabṣaarihim|g̣ishaawah;|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
2,8,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yaq̣oolu|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|wa-bil-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-maa|hum̃|bimuʹmineen."
2,9,"Yukhaadiʻoonal|laaha|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo:|wa-maa|Yakhdaʻoona|ʹillaaa|ʹañfusahum|wa-maa|yashʻuroon."
2,10,"Fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍuñ|fazaadahumul|laahu|Maraḍaa.|Wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleemum̃|bimaa|Kaanoo|Yakẓiboon."
2,11,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|laa-|tufsidoo|fil|ʹarḍi|q̣aalooo|ʹinnamaa|naḥnu|muṣliḥoon."
2,12,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahum|humul|mufsidoona|wa-laakil|laa|yashʻuroon."
2,13,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|ʹaaminoo|kamaaa|ʹaamanan|naasu|q̣aalooo|ʹanuʹminu|kamaaa|ʹaamanas|sufahaaaʹ?|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahum|humus|sufahaaaʹu|wa-laakil|laa|yaʻlamoon."
2,14,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|laq̣ul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa,|wa-ʹiẓaa|Khalaw|ʹilaa|Shayaaṭeenihim|q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|maʻakum|ʹinnamaa|naḥnu|mustahziʹoon."
2,15,"ʹAllaahu|yastahziʹu|bihim|wa-yamudduhum|fee|ṭug̣yaanihim|yaʻmahoon."
2,16,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeenash|tarawuḍ|ḍalaalata|bilhudaa:|famaa|Rabiḥat|tijaaratuhum|wa-maa|Kaanoo|Muhtadeen."
2,17,"Mas̤aluhum|Kamas̤alil|laẓis|tawq̣ada|Naaraa;|falammaaa|ʹaḍaaaʹat|maa-|ḥawlahoo|ẓahabal|laahu|binoorihim|wa-tarakahum|fee|z̤̣ulumaatil|laa|Yubṣiroon."
2,18,"Ṣummum|bukmun|ʻumyuñ|fahum|laa-|yarjiʻoon."
2,19,"ʹAw|kaṣayyibim|minas|samaaaʹi|feehi|z̤̣ulumaatuñw|wa-raʻduñw|wa-barq̣:|yajʻaloona|ʹaṣaabiʻahum|feee|ʹaaẓaanihim|minaṣ|ṣawaaʻiq̣i|ḥaẓaral|mawt.|Wallaaḥu|Muḥeeṭum|bilkaafireen."
2,20,"Yakaadul|barq̣u|yakhṭafu|ʹabṣaarahum:|kullamaaa|ʹaḍaaaʹa|lahum|mashaw|feehi|wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹaz̤̣lama|ʻalayhim|q̣aamoo.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|laẓahaba|bisamʻihim|wa-ʹabṣaarihim;|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
2,21,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasuʻ|budoo.|Rabbakumul|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|wallazeena|miñ|q̣ablikum|laʻallakum|tattaq̣oon."
2,22,"Allaẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹarḍa|firaashañw|was-samaaaʹa|binaaaʹaa:|wa-ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaañ|faʹakhraja|bihee|minas̤|s̤amaraati|rizq̣al|lakum:|falaa|tajʻaloo|lillaahi|ʹañdaadañw|wa-ʹañtum|taʻlamoon."
2,23,"Wa-iñ|kuñtum|fee|raybim|mimmaa|nazzalnaa|ʻalaa|ʻAbdinaa|faʹtoo|bi-Sooratim|mim|mis̤lih;|wadʻoo|shuhadaaaʹakum|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
2,24,"faʹil|lam|tafʻaloo|wa-lañ|tafʻaloo|fattaq̣un|Naaral|latee|wa-q̣ooduhan|naasu|walḥijaaratu|ʹuʻiddat|lil-Kaafireen."
2,25,"Wa-bashshiril|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|ʹanna|lahum|jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaar.|Kullamaa|ruziq̣oo|minhaa|miñ|s̤amaratir|rizq̣añ|q̣aaloo|haaẓal|laẓee|ruziq̣naa|miñ|q̣abl.|wa-ʹutoo|bihee|mutashaabihaa.|Wa-lahum|feehaaa|ʹazwaajum|muṭahharah;|wahum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
2,26,"ʹInnal|laaha|laa|yastaḥyeee|ʹañy|yaḍriba|mas̤alam|maa|baʻooḍatañ|famaa|fawq̣ahaa.|Faʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|fayaʻlamoona|ʹannahul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbihim:|wa-ʹammal|laẓeena|kafaroo|fayaq̣ooloona|maaẓaaa|ʹaraadal|laahu|bihaaẓaa|mas̤alaa?|Yuḍillu|bihee|kas̤eerañw|wa-yahdee|bihee|kas̤eeraa:|wa-maa|yuḍillu|biheee|ʹillal|Faasiq̣een;"
2,27,"ʹAllaẓeena|yañq̣uḍoona|ʻAhdal|laahi|mim|baʻdi|mees̤aaq̣ihee,|wa-yaq̣ṭaʻoona|maaa|ʹamaral|laahu|biheee|ʹañy|yooṣala|wa-yufsidoona|fil|ʹarḍ:|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
2,28,"Kayfa|takfuroona|billaahi|wa-kuñtum|ʹamwaatañ|faʹaḥyaakum;|s̤umma|yumeetukum|s̤umma|yuḥyeekum|s̤umma|ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
2,29,"Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣a|lakum|maa|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻaa;|s̤ummas|tawaaa|ʹilas|Samaaaʹi|fasaw-waahunna|sabʻa|samaawaat;|wa-Huwa|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻaleem."
2,30,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Rabbuka|lil-Malaaaʹikati|ʹInnee|jaaʻiluñ|fil|ʹarḍi|Khaleefah˹.|Q̣aalooo|ʹatajʻalu|feehaa|mañy|yufsidu|feehaa|wa-yasfikud|dimaaaʹ?|wa-naḥnu|nusabbiḥu|bi-Ḥamdika|wa-nuq̣addisu|lak.|Q̣aala|˹ʹInneee|ʹaʻlamu|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon.˺"
2,31,"Wa-ʻallama|ʹAadamal|ʹasmaaaʹa|kullahaa|s̤umma|ʻaraḍahum|ʻalal|malaaaʹikati|faq̣aala|ʹambiʹoonee|biʹasmaaaʹi|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
2,32,"Q̣aaloo|˹Subḥaanaka|laa|ʻilma|lanaaa|ʹillaa|maa-|ʻallamtanaa:|ʹInnaka|ʹañtal|ʻAleemul|Ḥakeem.˺"
2,33,"Q̣aala|˹YaaaʹAadamu|ʹambiʹhum̃|biʹasmaaaʹihim.˺|Falammaaa|ʹambaʹahum̃|biʹasmaaaʹihim|q̣aala|ʹalam|ʹaq̣ul|lakum|ʹInneee|ʹaʻlamu|g̣aybas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-ʹaʻlamu|maa|tubdoona|wa-maa|kuñtum|taktumoon."
2,34,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ulnaa|lilmalaaaʹikatis|judoo|liʹAadama|fasajadooo|ʹillaaa|ʹIblees:|ʹabaa|wastakbara|wa-kaana|minal|Kaafireen."
2,35,"Wa-q̣ulnaa|yaaaʹAadamus|kun|ʹañta|wa-zawjukal|jannata|wa-kulaa|Minhaa|rag̣adan|ḥays̤u|shiʹtumaa;|wa-laa|taq̣rabaa|haaẓihish|shajarata|fatakoonaa|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
2,36,"Faʹazallahumash|Shaytaanu|ʻanhaa|faʹakhrajahumaa|mimmaa|kaanaa|feeh.|Wa-q̣ulnah|biṭoo|baʻḍukum|libaʻḍin|ʻaduww.|Wa-lakum|fil|ʹarḍi|mustaq̣arruñw|wa-mataaʻun|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
2,37,"Fatalaq̣q̣aaa|ʹAadamu|mir|Rabbihee|Kalimaatiñ|fataaba|ʻalayh:|ʹinnahoo|Huwat|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
2,38,"Q̣ulnah|biṭoo|minhaa|jameeʻaa;|faʹimmaa|yaʹtiyannakum|minnee|Hudañ|famañ|tabiʻa|Hudaaya|falaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
2,39,"Wallaẓeena|Kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naar;|hum|feehaa|Khaalidoon."
2,40,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelaẓ|kuroo|niʻmatiyal|lateee|ʹanʻamtu|ʻalaykum|wa-ʹawfoo|biʻAhdeee|ʹoofi|biʻAhdikum|wa-ʹiyyaaya|Farhaboon."
2,41,"Wa-ʹaaminoo|Bimaaa|ʹañzaltu|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|maʻakum|wa-laa|takoonooo|ʹawwala|Kaafirim̃|bih.|Wa-laa|tashtaroo|biʹAayaatee|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelaa;|wa-ʹiyyaaya|Fattaq̣oon."
2,42,"Wa-laa|Talbisul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|bilbaaṭili|wa-taktumul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-ʹañtum|taʻlamoon."
2,43,"Wa-ʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaata|Warkaʻoo|maʻar|raakiʻeen."
2,44,"ʹAtaʹmuroonan|naasa|bilbirri|wa-tañsawna|ʹañfusakum|wa-ʹañtum|tatloonal|Kitaab?|ʹAfalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
2,45,"Wastaʻeenoo|biṣ-Ṣabri|waṣ-Ṣalaah:|wa-ʹinnahaa|lakabeeratun|ʹillaa|ʻalal|Khaashiʻeen,"
2,46,"ʹAllaẓeena|Yaz̤̣unnoona|ʹannahum|mulaaq̣oo|Rabbihim|wa-ʹannahum|ʹilayhi|raajiʻoon."
2,47,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelaẓ|kuroo|niʻmatiyal|lateee|ʹanʻamtu|ʻalaykum|wa-ʹannee|faḍḍaltukum|ʻalal|ʻaalameen."
2,48,"Wattaq̣oo|Yawmal|laa|tajzee|nafsun|ʻan|nafsiñ|shayʹañw|wa-laa|yuq̣balu|minhaa|shafaaʻatuñw|wa-laa|yuʹkhaẓu|minhaa|ʻadluñw|wa-laa|hum|yuñṣaroon."
2,49,"Wa-ʹiẓ|najjaynaakum|min|ʹAali|Firʻawna|yasoomoonakum|soooʹal|ʻaẓaabi|yuẓabbiḥoona|ʹabnaaaʹakum|wa-yastaḥyoona|nisaaaʹakum;|wa-fee|ẓaalikum̃|balaaaʹum|mir|Rabbikum|ʻaz̤̣eem."
2,50,"Wa-ʹiẓ|Faraq̣naa|bikumul|baḥra|faʹañjaynaakum|wa-ʹag̣raq̣naaa|ʹAala|Firʻawna|wa-ʹañtum|tañz̤̣uroon."
2,51,"Wa-ʹiz|waaʻadnaa|Moosaaa|ʹarbaʻeena|laylatañ|s̤ummat|takhaẓtumul|ʻijla|mim|baʻdihee|wa-añtum|z̤̣aalimoon."
2,52,"S̤umma|ʻafawnaa|ʻañkum|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
2,53,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|wal-Furq̣uaana|laʻallakum|Tahtadoon."
2,54,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|li-Q̣awmihee|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹinnakum|z̤̣alamtum|ʹanfusakum̃|bitti-khaa-ẓikumul|ʻijla|fatoobooo|ʹilaa|Baariʹikum|faq̣tulooo|ʹañfusakum;|ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|ʻiñda|Baariʹikum.|Fataaba|ʻalaykum:|ʹinnahoo|Huwat|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
2,55,"Wa-ʹIẓ|q̣ultum|yaa-Moosaa|lan|nuʹmina|laka|ḥattaa|naral|laaha|Jahratañ|faʹakhaẓat-kumuṣ|ṣaaʻiq̣atu|wa-ʹañtum|tañz̤̣uroon."
2,56,"S̤umma|baʻas̤naakum|mim|baʻdi|Mawtikum|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
2,57,"Wa-Z̤̣allalnaa|ʻalaykumul|g̣amaama|wa-ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaykumul|Manna|was-Salwaaa:|Kuloo|miñ|ṭayyibaati|maa|razaq̣naakum|wa-maa|z̤̣alamoonaa|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
2,58,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ulnad|khuloo|haaẓihil|q̣aryata|fakuloo|minhaa|ḥays̤u|shiʹtum|rag̣adañw|wadkhulul|baaba|Sujjadañw|wa-q̣ooloo|ḥittatun|nag̣fir|lakum|Khaṭaayaakum:|wa-sanazeedul|Muḥsineen."
2,59,"Fabaddalal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|q̣awlan|g̣ayral|laẓee|q̣eela|lahum|faʹañzalnaa|ʻalal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|rijzam|minas|samaaaʹi|bimaa|Kaanoo|yafsuq̣oon."
2,60,"Wa-ʹiẓis|tasq̣aa|Moosaa|liq̣awmihee|faq̣ulnaḍ|rib|biʻAṣaakal|ḥajar.|Fañfajarat|minhus̤|nataa|ʻashrata|ʻaynaa.|Q̣ad|ʻalima|Kullu|ʻunaasim|mashrabahum.|Kuloo|washraboo|mir|rizq̣il|laahi|walaa|taʻs̤aw|fil|ʹarḍi|mufsideen."
2,61,"Waʹiẓ|q̣ultum|yaa-Moosaa|lan|naṣbira|ʻalaa|ṭaʻaamiñw|waaḥidiñ|fadʻu|lanaa|Rabbaka|yukhrij|lanaa|mimmaa|tumbitul|ʹarḍu|mim|baq̣lihaa|Wa-q̣is̤s̤aaaʹihaa|Wa-foomihaa|wa-ʻadasihaa|wa-baṣalihaa.|Q̣aala|ʹatastabdiloonal|laẓee|huwa|ʹadnaa|billaẓee|huwa|Khayr?|ʹIhbiṭoo|miṣrañ|faʹinna|lakum|maa|saʹaltum.|Waḍuribat|ʻalayhimuẓ|ẓillatu|walmaskanah;|wa-baaaʹoo|big̣aḍabim|minal|laah.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|kaanoo|yakfuroona|biʹaayaatil|laahi|wa-yaq̣tuloonan|nabiyyeena|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣.|Ẓaalika|bimaa|ʻaṣaw|Wa-kaanoo|yaʻtadoon."
2,62,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|Wallaẓeena|haadoo|wan-Naṣaaraa|waṣ-Ṣaabiʹeena|man|ʹaamana|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|waʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|falahum|ʹajruhum|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|Walaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|walaa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
2,63,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓnaa|Mees̤aaq̣akum|Wa-rafaʻnaa|fawq̣akumuṭ|Ṭoor:|Khuẓoo|maaa|aataynaakum̃|biq̣uwwatiñw|waẓkuroo|maa|feehi|laʻallakum|tattaq̣oon."
2,64,"S̤umma|tawallaytum|mim̃|baʻdi|ẓaalik:|Falawlaa|faḍlul|lahi|ʻalaykum|wa-raḥmatuhoo|lakuñtum|minal|khaasireen."
2,65,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʻalimtumul|laẓeenaʻ|tadaw|miñkum|fis|Sabti|faq̣ulnaa|lahum|koonoo|q̣iradatan|khaasiʹeen!"
2,66,"Fajaʻalnaahaa|nakaalal|limaa|bayna|yadayhaa|wa-maa|khalfahaa|wa-mawʻiz̤̣atal|lil-Muttaq̣een."
2,67,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|liq̣awmiheee|ʹinnal|laaha|yaʹmurukum|ʹañ|taẓbaḥoo|Baq̣arah.|Q̣aalooo|ʹatattakhiẓunaa|huzuwaa?|Q̣aala|ʹaʻooẓu|billaahi|ʹan|ʹakoona|minal|jaahileen!"
2,68,"Q̣aalud|ʻu|lanaa|Rabbaka|yubayyil|lanaa|maa-|hee!|Q̣aala|ʹinnahoo|yaq̣oolu|ʹinnahaa|baq̣aratul|laa|faariḍuñw|walaa|bikr;|ʻawaanum|bayna|ẓaalik:|fafʻaloo|maa-|tuʹmaroon."
2,69,"Q̣aalud|ʻu|lanaa|Rabbaka|yubayyil|lanaa|maa-|lawnuhaa.|Q̣aala|ʹinnahoo|yaq̣oolu|ʹinnahaa|baq̣aratuñ|ṣafraaaʹu|faaq̣iʻul|lawnuhaa|tasurrun|naaz̤̣ireen."
2,70,"Q̣aalud|ʻu|lanaa|Rabbaka|yubayyil|lanaa|maa-|hiya|ʹinnal|baq̣ara|tashaabaha|ʻalaynaa:|wa-ʹinnaaa|ʹiñ|shaaaʹal|laahu|lamuhtadoon."
2,71,"Q̣aala|ʹinnahoo|yaq̣oolu|ʹinnahaa|baq̣aratul|laa|ẓalooluñ|tus̤eerul|ʹarḍa|wa-laa|tasq̣il|hars̤;|musallamatul|laa|shiyata|feehaa.|Q̣aalul|ʹaana|jiʹta|bilḥaq̣q̣.|Faẓabaḥoohaa|wa-maa|kaadoo|yafʻaloon."
2,72,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ataltum|nafsañ|faddaaraʹtum|feehaa:|wallaahu|mukhrijum|maa|kuñtum|taktumoon."
2,73,"Faq̣ulnaḍ|riboohu|bibaʻḍihaa.|Kaẓaalika|yuḥyil|laa-hul|mawtaa|wa-yureekum|ʹAayaatihee|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
2,74,"S̤umma|q̣asat|q̣uloobukum|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|fahiya|kalḥijaarati|ʹaw|ʹashaddu|q̣aswah.|Wa-ʹinna|minal|ḥijaarati|lamaa|yatafajjaru|minhul|ʹanhaar;|wa-ʹinna|minhaa|lamaa|yash-shaq̣q̣aq̣u|fayakhruju|minhul|maaaʹ.|Wa-ʹinna|minhaa|lamaa|yahbiṭu|min|khashyatil|laah.|Wa-mal|laahu|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon,"
2,75,"ʹAfataṭmaʻoona|ʹañy|yuʹminoo|lakum|wa-q̣ad|kaana|fareeq̣um|minhum|yasmaʻoona|Kalaamal|laahi|s̤umma|yuḥarri-foonahoo|mim|baʻdi|maa-|ʻaq̣aloohu|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon?"
2,76,"wa-ʹiẓaa|laq̣ul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa:|wa-ʹiẓaa|khalaa|baʻḍuhum|ʹilaa|baʻḍiñ|q̣aal  ooo|ʹatuḥaddis̤oonahum|bimaa|fataḥal|laahu|ʻalaykum|liyuḥaaajjookum̃|bihee|ʻiñda|Rabbikum?|ʹAfalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
2,77,"ʹAwalaa|yaʻlamoona|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|yusirroona|wa-maa|yuʻlinoon?"
2,78,"Wa-minhum|ʹUmmiyyoona|laa-|yaʻlamoonal|Kitaaba|ʹillaaa|ʹamaaniyya|wa-ʹin|hum|ʹillaa|yaz̤̣unnoon."
2,79,"Fawaylul|lillaẓeena|yaktuboonal|Kitaaba|biʹaydeehim|s̤umma|yaq̣ooloona|haaẓaa|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|liyashtaroo|bihee|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelaa!|Fawaylul|lahum|mimmaa|katabat|ʹaydeehim|wa-waylul|lahum|mimmaa|yaksiboon!"
2,80,"Wa-q̣aaloo|lañ|tamassanan|Naaru|ʹillaaa|ʹayyaamam|maʻdoodah.|Q̣ul|ʹattakhaẓtum|ʻiñdal|laahi|ʻahdañ|falañy|yukhlifal|laahu|ʻahdahooo|ʹam|taq̣ooloona|ʻalal|laahi|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon?"
2,81,"Balaa|mañ|kasaba|sayyiʹatañw|waʹaḥaṭat|bihee|khaṭeeeʹatuhoo|faʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naar:|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
2,82,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannah:|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
2,83,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓnaa|Mees̤aaq̣a|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|laa-|taʻbudoona|ʹillal|laaha|wa-bilwaalidayni|ʹiḥsaanañw|waẓil|q̣urbaa|walyataamaa|walmasaakeeni|wa-q̣ooloo|linnasi|ḥusnañw|waʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaah.|Ṣumma|tawallaytum|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|miñkum|wa-ʹañtum|muʻriḍoon."
2,84,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓnaa|Mees̤aa-q̣akum|laa-|tasfikoona|dimaaaʹakum|wa-laa|tukhrijoona|ʹañfusakum|miñ|diyaarikum|s̤umma|ʹaq̣rartum|wa-ʹañtum|tashhadoon."
2,85,"S̤umma|ʹañtum|haaaʹulaaaʹi|taq̣tuloona|ʹañfusakum|wa-tukhrijoona|fareeq̣am|miñkum|miñ|diyaarihim;|taz̤̣aaharoona|ʻalayhim̃|bil-ʹis̤mi|walʻudwaan;|wa-ʹiñy|yaʹtookum|ʹusaaraa|tufaadoohum|wa-huwa|muḥarramun|ʻalaykum|ʹikhraajuhum.|ʹAfatuʹminoona|bibaʻḍil|Kitaabi|wa-takfuroona|bibaʻḍ?|Famaa|jazaaaʹu|mañy|yafʻalu|ẓaalika|miñkum|ʹillaa|khizyuñ|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa?|Wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|yuraddoona|ʹilaaa|ʹashaddil|ʻaẓaab.|Wa-mal|laahu|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon."
2,86,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeenash|tarawul|ḥayaatad|Dunyaa|bil-ʹAakhirati|falaa|yukhaffafu|ʻanhumul|ʻaẓaabu|wa-laa|hum|yuñṣaroon."
2,87,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|wa-q̣affaynaa|mim|baʻdihee|bir-rusuli|wa-ʹaataynaa|ʻeesab|na|Maryamal|Bayyinaati|wa-ʹayyadnaahu|bi-rooḥil|q̣udus.|ʹAfakullamaa|jaaaʹakum|Rasoolum̃|bimaa|laa-|tahwaaa|ʹañfusukumus|takbartum?|Fafareeq̣añ|kaẓẓabtum|wa-fareeq̣añ|taq̣tuloon?"
2,88,"Wa-q̣aloo|q̣uloobunaa|g̣ulf;|bal|laʻanahumul|laahu|bikufrihim|faq̣aleelam|maa|yuʹminoon."
2,89,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹahum|Kitaabum|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|muṣaddiq̣ul|limaa|maʻahum|wa-kaanoo|miñ|q̣ablu|yastaftiḥoona|ʻalal|laẓeena|kafaroo,|falammaa|jaaaʹahum|maa|ʻarafoo|kafaroo|bihee|falaʻnatul|laahi|ʻalal|Kaafireen."
2,90,"Biʹsamash|taraw|biheee|ʹañfusahum|ʹañy|yakfuroo|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|bag̣yan|ʹañy|yunazzilal|laahu|miñ|faz̤̣lihee|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadih.|Fabaaaʹoo|big̣aḍabin|ʻalaa|g̣aḍab.|Wa-lil-Kaafireena|ʻaẓaabum|muheen."
2,91,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|ʹaaminoo|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|q̣aaloo|nuʹminu|bimaaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalaynaa|wa-yakfuroona|bimaa|waraaaʹahoo|wa-huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|maʻahum.|Q̣ul|falima|taq̣tuloona|ʹambiyaaaʹal|laahi|miñ|q̣ablu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|muʹmineen?"
2,92,"Wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹakum|Moosaa|bil-Bayyinaati|s̤ummat|takhaẓtumul|ʻijla|mim|baʻdihee|wa-ʹañtum|z̤̣aalimoon."
2,93,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓnaa|Mees̤aaq̣akum|wa-rafaʻnaa|fawq̣akumuṭ|Ṭoor:|khuẓoo|maaa|ʹaataynaakum̃|biq̣uwwatiñw|wasmaʻoo.|Q̣aaloo|samiʻnaa|wa-ʻaṣaynaa:|wa-ʹushriboo|fee|q̣uloobihimul|ʻijla|bikufrihim.|Q̣ul|biʹsamaa|yaʹmurukum̃|biheee|ʹeemaanukum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|muʹmineen."
2,94,"Q̣ul|ʹiñ|kaanat|lakumud|Daarul|ʹAakhiratu|ʻiñdal|laahi|khaaliṣatam|min|doonin|naasi|fatamannawul|mawta|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
2,95,"Wa-lañy|yatamannawhu|ʹabadam|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeehim.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum̃|biz̤̣z̤̣aalimeen."
2,96,"Wa-latajidannahum|ʹaḥraṣan|naasi|ʻalaa|ḥayaah.|Wa-minal|laẓeena|ʹashrakoo|yawaddu|ʹaḥaduhum|law|yuʻammaru|ʹalfa|sanah:|wa-maa|huwa|bi-muzaḥziḥihee|minal|ʻaẓaabi|ʹañy|yuʻammar.|Wallaahu|Baseerum|bimaa|yaʻmaloon."
2,97,"Q̣ul|mañ|kaana|ʻaduwwal|li-Jibreela|faʹinnahoo|nazzalahoo|ʻalaa|q̣albika|biʹiẓnil|laahi|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayhi|wa-hudañw|wa- bushraa|lil-Muʹmineen,"
2,98,"Mañ|kaana|ʻaduwwal|lillaahi|wa-malaaaʹikatihee|wa-rusulihi|wa-Jibreela|wa-Meekaala|faʹinnal|laaha|ʻaduwwul|lilkaafireen."
2,99,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilayka|ʹAayaatim|bayyinaat;|wa-maa|yakfuru|bihaaa|ʹillal|faasiq̣oon."
2,100,"ʹAwa-kullamaa|ʻaahadoo|ʻahdan|nabaẓahoo|fareeq̣um|minhum?|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
2,101,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹahum|Rasoolum|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|muṣaddiq̣ul|limaa|maʻahum|nabaẓa|fareeq̣um|minal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|Kitaabal|laahi|waraaaʹa|z̤̣uhoorihim|kaʹannahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon!"
2,102,"Wattabaʻoo|maa-|tatlush|shayaaṭeenu|ʻalaa|mulki|Sulaymaan.|Wa-maa|kafara|Sulaymaanu|wa-laakinnash|shayaaṭeena|kafaroo|yuʻal-limoonan|naasas|siḥr,|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalal|malakayni|bi-Baabila|Haaroota|wa-Maaroot.|Wa-maa|yuʻallimaani|min|ʹaḥadin|ḥattaa|yaq̣oolaaa|ʹinnamaa|naḥnu|fitnatuñ|falaa|takfur.|Fayataʻal-lamoona|minhumaa -|maa|yufarriq̣oona|Bihee|baynal|marʹi|wa-zawjih.|Wa-maa|hum̃|biḍaaarreena|bihee|min|ʹaḥadin|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnil|laah.|Wa-yataʻallamoona|maa-|yaẓurruhum|wa-laa|yañfaʻuhum.|Wa-laq̣ad|ʻalimoo|lamanish|taraahu|maa-|lahoo|fil|ʹAakhirati|min|khalaaq̣.|Wa-labiʹsa|maa-|sharaw|biheee|ʹañfusahum,|law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoon."
2,103,"Wa-law|ʹannahum|ʹaamanoo|wattaq̣aw|lamas̤oobatum|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|khayr:|law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoon."
2,104,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|lazeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|taq̣ooloo|raaʻinaa|wa-q̣ooluñ|z̤̣urnaa|wasmaʻoo.|Wa-lil-Kaafireena|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
2,105,"Maa-|yawaddul|laẓeena|kafaroo|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|wa-lal|Mushrikeena|ʹañy|yunazzala|ʻalaykum|min|khayrim|mir|Rabbikum.|Wallaahu|yakhtaṣṣu|biraḥmatihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|Wallaahu|Ẓul|Faḍlil|ʹaz̤̣eem."
2,106,"Maa-|nañsakh|min|ʹaayatin|ʹaw|nuñsihaa|naʹti|bikhayrim|minhaaa|ʹaw|mis̤lihaa:|ʹalam|taʻlam|ʹannal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer?"
2,107,"ʹAlam|taʻlam|ʹannal|laaha|lahoo|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Wa-maa|lakum|miñ|doonil|laahi|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|naṣeer."
2,108,"ʹAm|tureedoona|ʹañ|tasʹaloo|Rasoolakum|kamaa|suʹila|Moosaa|miñ|q̣abl?|Wa-mañy|yatabaddalil|kufra|bil-ʹeemaani|faq̣ad|ḍalla|sawaaaʹas|sabeel."
2,109,"Wadda|kas̤eerum|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|law|yaruddoonakum|mim|baʻdi|ʹeemaanikum|kuffaaran,|ḥasadam|min|ʻiñdi|añfusihim|mim|baʻdi|maa-|tabayyana|lahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣.|Faʻfoo|waṣfaḥoo|ḥattaa|yaʹ-tiyal|laahu|biʹamrih:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
2,110,"Wa-ʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaah:|wa-maa|tuq̣addimoo|liʹañfusikum|min|khayriñ|tajidoohu|ʻiñdal|lah:|ʹinnal|laaha|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
2,111,"Wa-q̣aaloo|lañy|yadkhulal|Jannata|ʹillaa|mañ|kaana|Hoodan|ʹaw|Naṣaaraa.|Tilka|ʹamaaniyyuhum.|Q̣ul|haatoo|burhaanakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
2,112,"Balaa,|man|ʹaslama|wajhahoo|lillaahi|wa-huwa|muḥsinuñ|falahooo|ʹajruhoo|ʻiñda|Rabbih;|wa-laa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
2,113,"Wa-q̣aalatil|Yahoodu|laysatin|Naṣaaraa|ʻalaa|shayʹ;|wa-q̣aalatin|Naṣaaraa|laysatil|Yahoodu|ʻalaa|shayʹiñw|wa- hum|yatloonal|Kitaab.|Kaẓaalika|q̣aalal|laẓeena|laa-|yaʻlamoona|mis̤la|q̣awlihim.|Fallaahu|Yaḥkumu|baynahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|feemaa|kaanoo|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
2,114,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmam|manaʻa|masaajidal|lahi|ʹañy|yuẓkara|feehas|muhoo|wa-saʻaa|fee|kharaabihaa?|ʹUlaaaʹika|maa-|kaana|lahum|ʹany|yadkhuloohaaa|ʹillaa|khaaaʹifeen.|Lahum|fid|dunyaa|khizyuñw|wa-lahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
2,115,"Wa-lillaahil|Mashriq̣u|wal-Mag̣rib:|Faʹaynamaa|tuwalloo|fas̤amma|Wajhul|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
2,116,"Wa-q̣aalut|takhaẓal|laahu|waladañ|Subḥaanah!|Bal|lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|kullul|lahoo|q̣aanitoon."
2,117,"Badeeʻus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣aḍaaa|ʹamrañ|faʹinnamaa|yaq̣oolu|lahoo|˹Kuñ˺|fayakoon."
2,118,"Waq̣aalal|laẓeena|laa-|yaʻlamoona|law-laa|yukallimunal|laahu|ʹaw|taʹteenaaa|ʹAayah?|Kaẓaalika|q̣aalal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|mis̤la|q̣awlihim.|Tashaabahat|q̣uloobuhum.|Q̣ad|bayyannal|ʹaayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yooq̣inoon."
2,119,"ʹInnaaa|ʹarsalnaaka|bilḥaq̣q̣i|basheerañw|wanaẓeera|wa-laa|tusʹalu|ʻan|ʹAṣḥaabil|Jaḥeem."
2,120,"Wa-lañ|tarḍaa|ʻañkal|Yahoodu|wa-lan|Naṣaaraa|ḥattaa|tattabiʻa|millatahum.|Q̣ul|ʹinna|Hudal|laahi|huwal|Hudaa.|Wa-laʹinit|tabaʻta|ʹahwaaaʹahum|baʻdal|laẓee|jaaaʹaka|minal|ʻilmi|maa-|laka|minal|laahi|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|naṣeer."
2,121,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|yatloonahoo|ḥaq̣q̣a|tilaawatih:|ʹUlaaaʹika|yuʹminoona|bih.|Wa-mañy|yakfur|bihee|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
2,122,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelaẓ|kuroo|niʻmatiyal|lateee|ʹanʻamtu|ʻalaykum|wa-ʹannee|faḍḍaltukum|ʻalal|ʻaalameen."
2,123,"Wattaq̣oo|Yawmal|laa|tajzee|nafsun|ʻan|nafsiñ|shayʹañw|walaa|yuq̣balu|minhaa|ʻadluñw|Walaa|tañfaʻuhaa|shafaaʻatunw|walaa|hum|yuñṣaroon."
2,124,"Wa-ʹiẓib|talaaa|ʹIbraaheema|Rabbuhoo|bi-Kalimaatiñ|faʹatammahunna:|q̣aala|ʹInnee|jaaʻiluka|linnaasi|ʹImaamaa.|Q̣aala|wa-miñ|ẓurriyyatee!|Q̣aala|laa-|yanaalu|ʻahdiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
2,125,"Wa-ʹiẓ|jaʻalnal|Bayta|mas̤aabatal|linnaasi|wa-ʹamnaa;|wattakhiẓoo|mim|Maq̣aami|ʹIbraaheema|muṣallaa:|wa-ʻahidnaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|ʹañ|ṭahhiraa|Baytiya|liṭṭaaaʹifeena|walʻaakifeena|warrukkaʻis|sujood."
2,126,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|Rabbij|ʻal|haaẓaa|Baladan|ʹAaminañw|warzuq̣|ʹahlahoo|minas̤|s̤amaraati|man|ʹaamana|minhum̃|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Q̣aala|wa-mañ|kafara|faʹumattiʻuhoo|q̣aleelañ|s̤umma|ʹaḍṭarruhoo|ʹilaa|ʻaẓaabin|Naar,|wa-biʹsal|maṣeer!"
2,127,"Wa-ʹiẓ|yarfaʻu|ʹIbraaheemul|q̣awaaʻida|minal|Bayti|wa-ʹIsmaaʻeel:|Rabbanaa|taq̣abbal|minnaa:|ʹinnaka|ʹAñtas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
2,128,"Rabbanaa|wajʻalnaa|Muslimayni|laka|wa-miñ|ẓurriyyatinaaa|ʹUmmatam|Muslimatal|lak;|wa-ʹarinaa|manaasikanaa|wa-tub|ʻalaynaa;|ʹinnaka|ʹAntat|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
2,129,"Rabbanaa|wabʻas̤|feehim|Rasoolam|minhum|yatloo|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatika|wa-yuʻallimuhumul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|wa-yuzakkeehim:|ʹinnaka|ʹAñtal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
2,130,"Wa-mañy|yarg̣abu|ʻam|Millati|ʹIbraaheema|ʹillaa|mañ|safiha|nafsah?|Wa-laq̣adiṣ|ṭafaynaahu|fid|dunyaa:|wa-ʹinnahoo|fil|ʹAakhirati|laminaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
2,131,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|lahoo|Rabbuhooo|ʹaslim|q̣aala|ʹaslamtu|li-Rabbil|ʻaalameen."
2,132,"Wa-waṣṣaa|bihaaa|ʹIbraaheemu|baneehi|wa-Yaʻq̣oob:|yaa-baniyya|ʹinnal|laahaṣ|ṭafaa|lakumud|Deena|falaa|tamootunna|ʹillaa|wa-ʹañtum|Muslimoon."
2,133,"ʹAm|kuñtum|shuhadaaaʹa|ʹiẓ|ḥaḍara|Yaʻq̣oobal|mawtu|ʹiẓ|q̣aala|libaneehi|maa-|taʻbudoona|mim|baʻdee?|Q̣aaloo|naʻbudu|ʹIlaahaka|wa-ʹIlaaha|ʹaabaaaʹika|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣a|ʹIlaahañw|Waaḥidaa:|wa-naḥnu|lahoo|Muslimoon."
2,134,"Tilka|ʹummatuñ|q̣ad|khalat.|Lahaa|maa-|kasabat|wa-lakum|maa|kasabtum.|Wa-laa|tusʹaloona|ʻammaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
2,135,"Wa-q̣aaloo|koonoo|Hoodan|ʹaw|Naṣaaraa|tahtadoo.|Q̣ul|bal|Millata|ʹIbraaheema|Ḥaneefaa,|wa-maa|kaana|minal|mushrikeen."
2,136,"Q̣oolooo|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaynaa|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaaa|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|wal-ʹasbaaṭi|wa-maaa|ʹootiya|Moosaa|wa-ʻEesaa|wa-maaa|ʹootiyan|nabiyyoona|mir|Rabbihim.|Laa-|nufarriq̣u|bayna|ʹaḥadim|minhum,|wa-naḥnu|lahoo|Muslimoon."
2,137,"Faʹin|ʹaamanoo|bimis̤li|maaa|ʹaamañtum̃|bihee|faq̣adih|tadaw.|Wa-ʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinnamaa|hum|fee|shiq̣aaq̣:|fasayakfeekahumul|laah,|wa-Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
2,138,"Ṣibg̣atal|laah:|wa-man|ʹaḥsanu|minal|laahi|ṣibg̣ah?|Wa-naḥnu|lahoo|ʻaabidoon."
2,139,"Q̣ul|ʹatuḥaaajjoonanaa|fil|laahi|wa-Huwa|Rabbunaa|wa-Rabbukum;|wa-lanaa|ʹaʻmaalunaa|wa-lakum|ʹaʻmaalukum;|wa-naḥnu|lahoo|mukhliṣoon."
2,140,"ʹAm|taq̣ooloona|ʹinna|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|wal-ʹAsbaaṭa|kaanoo|Hoodan|ʹaw|Naṣaaraa?|Q̣ul|ʹaʹañtum|ʹaʻlamu|ʹamil|laah?|Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmañ|Katama|shahaadatan|ʻiñdahoo|minal|laah?|Wa-mal|laahu|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon."
2,141,"Tilka|ʹUmmatuñ|q̣ad|khalat.|Lahaa|maa-|kasabat|wa-lakum|maa|kasabtum.|Wa-laa|tusʹaloona|ʻammaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
2,142,"Sayaq̣oolus|sufahaaaʹu|minan|naasi|maa-|wallaahum|ʻañ|Q̣iblatihimul|latee|kaanoo|ʻalayhaa?|Q̣ul|lillaahil|Mashriq̣u|walmag̣hrib:|yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
2,143,"Wa-kaẓaalika|jaʻalnaakum|ʹUmmatañw|Waṣatal|litakoonoo|Shuhadaaʹa|ʻalan|naasi|wa-yakoonar|Rasoolu|ʻalaykum|Shaheedaa.|Wa-maa|jaʻalnal|Q̣iblatal|latee|kuñta|ʻalayhaaa|ʹillaa|linaʻlama|mañy|yattabiʻur|Rasoola|mimmañy|yañq̣alibu|ʻalaa|ʻaq̣ibayh.|Wa-ʹiñ|kaanat|lakabeeratan|ʹillaa|ʻalal|laẓeena|hadal|laah.|Wa-maa|Kaanal|laahu|liyuḍeeʻa|ʹeemaanakum.|ʹInnal|laaha|binnaasi|la-Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
2,144,"Q̣ad|naraa|taq̣alluba|wajhika|fis|samaaaʹie:|falanuwalliyannaka|Q̣iblatañ|tarḍaahaa.|Fawalli|wajhaka|shaṭral|Masjidil|Ḥaraam.|Waḥays̤u|maa-|kuñtum|fawalloo|wujoohakum|shaṭrah.|Wa-ʹinnal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|layaʻlamoona|ʹannahul|ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbihim.|Wa-mal|laahu|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|yaʻmaloon."
2,145,"Wa-laʹin|ʹataytal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|bikulli|ʹAayatim|maa|tabiʻoo|Q̣iblatak;|wa-maaaʹ|añta|bitaabiʻin|Q̣iblatahum;|wa-maa|baʻḍuhum̃|bitaabiʻiñ|Q̣iblata|baʻḍ.|Wa-laʹinit|tabaʻta|ʹahwaaaʹahum|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹaka|minal|ʻilmi|ʹinnaka|ʹiḍal|laminaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
2,146,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|kitaaba|yaʻrifoonahoo|kamaa|yaʹrifoona|ʹabnaaʹahum:|wa-ʹinna|fareeq̣am|minhum|layaktumoonal|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon."
2,147,"ʹAl-Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbika|falaa|takoonanna|minal|mumtareen."
2,148,"Wa-likulliñw|wijhatun|huwa|muwalleehaa|fastabiq̣ul|khayraat.|ʹAyna|maa-|takoonoo|yaʹti|bikumul|laahu|Jameeʻaa.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
2,149,"Wa-min|ḥays̤u|kharajta|fawalli|wajhaka|shaṭral|Masjidil|Ḥaraam;|wa-ʹinnahoo|lalḥaq̣q̣u|mir|rabbik.|Wa-mal|laahu|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon."
2,150,"Wa-min|ḥays̤u|kharajta|fawalli|wajhaka|shaṭral|Masjidil|haraam;|waḥays̤u|maa-|kuntum|fawalloo|Wujoohakum|shaṭrahoo|liʹallaa|yakoona|linnaasi|ʻalaykum|hujjatun|ʹillal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|minhum;|falaaa|takhshawhum|wakhshawnee;|wa-liʹutimma|niʻmatee|ʻalaykum|Wa-laʻallakum|tahtadoon."
2,151,"Kamaaa|ʹarsalnaa|feekum|Rasoolam|miñkum|yatloo|ʻalaykum|ʹAayaatinaa|wa-yuzakkikum|wa-yuʻalli-mukumul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|wa-yuʻAllimukum|maa|lam|takoonoo|taʻlamoon."
2,152,"Faẓkurooneee|ʹaẓkurkum|washkuroo|lee|wa-laa|takfuroon."
2,153,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanus|taʻeenoo|biṣ-Ṣabri|was-Ṣalaah;|ʹInnal|laaha|maʻaṣ|ṣaabreeen."
2,154,"Wa-laa|taq̣ooloo|limañy|yuq̣talu|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|ʹamwaat.|Bal|ʹaḥyaaaʹuñw|Wa laakil|laa|tashʻuroon"
2,155,"Wa-lanablu-wannakum̃|bishayʹim|minal|khawfi|waljooʻi|wa-naq̣ṣim|minal|ʹamwaali|wal-ʹañfusi|was̤-s̤amaraat:|wa-bashshiris̤|S̤aabireen,"
2,156,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaṣaabathum|muṣeebatuñ|q̣alooo|ʹinnaa|lillaahi|wa-ʹinnaaa|ʹilayhi|raajiʻoon."
2,157,"ʹUlaaaʻika|ʻalayhim|ṣalawaatum|mir|Rabbihim|wa-raḥmah:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Muhtadoon."
2,158,"ʹInnaṣ|S̤afaa|wal-Marwata|miñ|Shaʻaaʹiril|laah.|Faman|ḥajjal|Bayta|ʹawiʻ|tamara|falaa|Junaaḥa|ʻalayhi|ʻany|yaṭṭawwafa|bihimaa.|Wa-mañ|taṭawwaʻa|khayrañ|faʹinnal|laha|Shaakirun|ʻAleem."
2,159,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yaktumoona|maaa|ʹañzalnaa|minal|bayyinaati|walhudaa|mim|baʻdi|maa-|bayyannaahu|linnaasi|fil|Kitaabi|ʹulaaaʹika|yalʻanuhumul|laahu|wa-yalʻanuhumul|laa-ʻinoon,"
2,160,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|taaboo|wa-ʹaṣlaḥoo|wa-bayyanoo|faʹulaaaʹika|ʹatoobu|ʻalayhim;|wa-ʹAnat|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
2,161,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-maatoo|wa-hum|kuffaarun|ʹulaaaʹika|ʻalayhim|laʻnatul|laahi|walmalaaaʹikati|wannaasi|ʹajmaʻeen,"
2,162,"Khaalideena|feehaa:|laa-|yukhaffafu|ʻanhumul|ʻaẓaabu|wa-laa|hum|yuñz̤̣aroon."
2,163,"Wa-ʹIlaahukum|Ilaahuñw|Waaḥid:|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwar|Raḥmaanur|Raḥeem."
2,164,"ʹInna|fee|khalq̣is|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|Wakhtilaafil|layli|wannahaari|walfulkil|latee|tajree|fil|baḥri|bimaa|yañfaʻun|naasa|wa-maaa|ʻañzalal|aahu|minas|samaaaʹi|mim|maaaʹiñ|faʹaḥyaa|bihil|ʹarẓa|baʻda|mawtihaa|wa-bas̤s̤a|feehaa|miñ|kulli|daabbah:|wa-taṣreefir|riyaaḥi|was-saḥaabil|musakhkhari|baynas|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍi|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
2,165,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yattakhiẓu|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹañdaadañy|yuḥibboonahum|kaḥubbil|laah.|Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹashaddu|ḥubbal|lillaah.|Wa-law|yaral|laẓeena|z̤̣alamooo|ʹiẓ|yarawnal|ʻaẓaaba|ʹannal|Q̣uwwata|lillaahi|jameeʻañw|waʹannal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻaẓaab."
2,166,"ʹIẓ|tabarraʹal|laẓeenat|tubiʻoo|minal|laẓeenat|tabaʻoo|wa-raʹawul|ʻaẓaaba|wa-taq̣aṭṭaʻat|bihimul|ʹasbaab."
2,167,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeenat|tabaʻoo|law|ʹanna|lanaa|karratañ|fanatabarraʹa|minhum|kamaa|tabarraʹoo|minnaa.|Kaẓaalika|yureehimul|laahu|ʹaʻmaalahum|ḥasaraatin|ʻalayhim.|Wa-maa|hum̃|bikhaarijeena|minan|Naar."
2,168,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|kuloo|mimmaa|fil|ʹarḍi|Ḥalaalañ|ṭayyibaa;|wa-laa|tattabiʻoo|Khuṭuwaatish|Shayṭaan.|ʹInnahoo|lakum|ʻaduwwum|mubeen."
2,169,"ʹInnamaa|yaʹmurukum̃|bis-soooʹi|walfaḥshaaaʹi|wa-ʹañ|taq̣ooloo|ʻalal|laahi|maa-|laa-|taʻlamoon."
2,170,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahumut|tabiʻoo|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|q̣aaloo|bal|nattabiʻu|maaa|ʹalfaynaa|ʻalayhi|ʹaabaaaʹanaa.|ʹAwa-law|kaana|ʹaabaaaʹuhum|laa-|yaʻq̣iloona|shayʹañw|walaa|yahtadoon?"
2,171,"Wa-mas̤alul|laẓeena|kafaroo|kamas̤alil|laẓee|yanʻiq̣u|bimaa|laa-|yasmaʻu|ʹillaa|duʻaaaʹañw|wanidaaaʹaa.|S̤ummum̃|bukmun|ʻumyuñ|fahum|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon."
2,172,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|kuloo|miñ|ṭayyibaati|maa-|razaq̣naakum|washkuroo|lillahi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ʹiyyaahu|taʻbudoon."
2,173,"ʹInnamaa|ḥarrama|ʻalaykumul|maytata|waddama|wa-laḥmal|khiñzeeri|wa-maaa|ʹuhilla|bihee|lig̣ayril|laah.|Famaniḍ|ṭurra|g̣ayra|baag̣iñw|walaa|ʻaadiñ|falaaa|ʹis̤ma|ʻalayh.|ʹInnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
2,174,"ʹInnal|laẓeeena|yaktumoona|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|minal|Kitaabi|wa-yashtaroona|bihee|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelan|ʹulaaaʹika|maa-|yaʹkuloona|fee|buṭoonihim|illan|Naara|wa-laa|yukallimuhumul|laahu|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|wa-laa|yuzakkeehim|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
2,175,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|lazeenash|tarawuḍ|ḍalaalata|bilhudaa|walʻaẓaaba|bilmag̣firah.|Famaaa|ʹaṣbarahum|ʻalan|Naar!"
2,176,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|nazzalal|Kitaba|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-ʹinnal|laẓeenakh|talafoo|fil|Kitaabi|lafee|shiq̣aaq̣im|baʻeed."
2,177,"Laysal|birra|ʹañ|tuwalloo|wujoohakum|q̣ibalal|Mashriq̣i|wal-Mag̣ribi|wa-laakinnal|birra|man|ʹaamana|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wal-malaaaʹikati|wal-Kitaabi|wan-nabiyyeen:|wa-ʹaatal|maala|ʻalaa|ḥubbihee|ẓawil|q̣urbaa|walyataamaa|walmasaakeena|wabnas|sabeeli|wassaaaʹileena|wa-fir|riq̣aab:|wa-ʹaq̣aamaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaataz|Zakaah;|walmoofoona|biʻahdihim|iẓaa|ʻaahadoo;|waṣ-Ṣaabireena|fil|baʹsaaaʹi|waḍḍarraaaʹi|waḥeenal|baʹas.|ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ṣadaq̣oo:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Muttaq̣oon."
2,178,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|kutiba|ʻalaykumul|Q̣iṣaaṣu|fil|q̣atlaa:|ʹalḥurru|bilḥurri|walʻabdu|bilʻabdi|wal-ʹuñs̤aa|bil-ʹuñs̤aa.|Faman|ʻufiya|lahoo|min|ʹakheehi|shayʹuñ|fattibaaʻum|bilmaʻroofi|wa-ʹadaaaʹun|ʹilayhi|biʹiḥsaan.|Ẓaalika|takhfeefum|mir|Rabbikum|wa-raḥmah.|Famaniʻ|tadaa|baʻda|ẓaalika|falahoo|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
2,179,"Wa-lakum|fil|Q̣iṣaaṣi|Ḥayaatuñy|yaaaʹulil|ʹalbaabi|laʻallakum|tattaq̣oon."
2,180,"Kutiba|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓaa|ḥaḍara|ʹaḥadakumul|mawtu|ʹiñ|taraka|khayranil|waṣiyyatu|lilwaalidayni|wal-ʹaq̣rabeena|bil-maʻroof;|ḥaq̣q̣an|ʻalal|Muttaq̣een."
2,181,"Famam|baddalahoo|baʻdamaa|samiʻahoo|faʹinnamaaa|ʹis̤muhoo|ʻalal|laẓeena|yubaddiloonah.|ʹInnal|laaha|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
2,182,"Faman|khaafa|mim|mooṣiñ|janafan|ʹaw|ʹis̤mañ|faʹaṣlaḥa|baynahum|falaaa|ʹis̤ma|ʻalayh:|ʹInnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
2,183,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|kutiba|ʻalaykumuṣ|Ṣiyaamu|kamaa|kutiba|ʻalal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablikum|laʻallakum|tattaq̣oon."
2,184,"ʹAyyaamam|maʻdoodaat;|famañ|kaana|miñkum|mareeḍan|ʹaw|ʻalaa|safariñ|faʻiddatum|min|ʹayyaamin|ʹukhar.|Wa-ʻalal|laẓeena|yuṭeeq̣oonahoo|fidyatuñ|ṭaʻaamu|miskeen.|Famañ|taṭawwaʻa|khayrañ|fahuwa|khayrul|lah.|Wa-ʹañ|taṣoomoo|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|Kuñtum|taʻlamoon."
2,185,"Shahru|Ramaḍaanal|laẓeee|ʹuñzila|feehil|Q̣urʹaanu|hudal|linnaasi|wa-bayyinaatim|minal|hudaa|wal-furq̣aan.|Famañ|shahida|miñkumush|Shahra|fal-yaṣumh.|Wa-mañ|kaana|mareeḍan|ʹaw|ʻalaa|safariñ|faʻiddatum|min|ʹayyaamin|ʹukhar.|Yureedul|laahu|bikumul|yusra|wa-laa|yureedu|bikumul|ʻusr.|Wa-litukmilul|ʻiddata|wa-litukabbirul|laaha|ʻalaa|maa-|hadaakum|wa-laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
2,186,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|saʹalaka|ʻibaadee|ʻannee|faʹinnee|Q̣areeb:|ʹujeebu|daʻwatad|daaʻi|ʹiẓaa|daʻaani|falyastajeeboo|lee|wal-yuʹminoo|bee|laʻallahum|yarshudoon."
2,187,"ʹUḥilla|lakum|laylataṣ|Ṣiyaamir|rafas̤u|ʹilaa|nisaaaʹikum.|Hunna|libaasul|lakum|wa-ʹañtum|libaasul|lahunn.|ʻAlimal|laahu|ʹannaakum|kuñtum|takhtaanoona|ʹañfusakum|fataaba|ʻalaykum|wa-ʻafaa|ʻañkum;|falʹaana|baashiroohunna|wabtag̣oo|maa-|katabal|laahu|lakum,|wa-kuloo|washraboo|ḥattaa|yatabayyana|lakumul|khayṭul|ʹabyaḍu|minal|khayṭil|ʹaswadi|minal|Fajr.|S̤umma|ʹatimmuṣ|ṣiyaama|ʹilal|layl;|wa-laa|tubaashiroohunna|wa-ʹañtum|ʻaakifoona|fil|masaajid.|Tilka|ḥudoodul|laahi|falaa|taq̣raboohaa.|Kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|ʹAayaatihee|linnaasi|laʻallaahum|yattaq̣oon."
2,188,"Wa-laa|taʹkulooo|ʹamwaalakum̃|baynakum̃|bilbaaṭili|wa-tudloo|bihaaa|ʹilal|ḥukkaami|litaʹkuloo|fareeq̣am|min|ʹamwaalin|naasi|bil-ʹis̤mi|wa-ʹañtum|taʻlamoon."
2,189,"Yasʹaloonaka|ʻanil|ʹAhillah.|Q̣ul|hiya|mawaaq̣eetu|linnaasi|wal-Ḥajj.|Wa-laysal|birru|biʹañ|taʹtul|buyoota|miñ|z̤̣uhoorihaa|wa-laakinnal|birra|manit|taq̣aa.|Waʹtul|buyoota|min|ʹabwaabihaa|wattaq̣ul|laaha|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
2,190,"Wa-q̣aatiloo|fee|sabeelil|laahil|laẓeena|yuq̣aatiloonakum|wa-laa|taʻtadoo;|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbul|muʻtadeen."
2,191,"Waq̣-tuloohum|ḥays̤u|s̤aq̣iftumoohum|wa-ʹakhrijoohum|min|ḥays̤u|ʹakhrajookum|walfitnatu|ʹashaddu|minal|q̣atl.|Wa-laa|tuq̣aatiloohum|ʻiñdal|Masjidil|Ḥaraami|ḥattaa|yuq̣aatilookum|feeh;|faʹiñ|q̣aatalookum|faq̣-tuloohum.|Kaẓaalika|jazaaaʹul|kaafireen."
2,192,"Faʹiniñ|tahaw|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
2,193,"Wa-q̣aatiloohum|ḥattaa|laa-|takoona|fitnatuñw|wayakoonad|Deenu|lillaah;|faʹiniñ|tahaw|falaa|ʻudwaana|ʹillaa|ʻalaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
2,194,"ʹAsh-Shahrul|Ḥaraamu|bish-Shahril|Ḥaraami|wal-ḥurumaatu|q̣iṣaaṣ.|Famaniʻ|tadaa|ʻalaykum|faʻtadoo|ʻalayhi|bimis̤li|maʻ|tadaa|ʻalaykum.|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|maʻal|Muttaq̣een."
2,195,"Wa-ʻañfiq̣oo|fee|sabeelil|laahi|wa-laa|tulq̣oo|biʹaydeekum|ʹilat|tahlukah.|Wa-ʹaḥsinooo|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muḥsineen."
2,196,"Wa-ʹatimmul|Ḥajja|wal-ʻumrata|lillaah.|Faʹin|ʹuḥṣirtum|famas|taysara|minal|hadyi,|wa-laa|taḥliq̣oo|ruʹoosakum|ḥattan|yablug̣al|hadyu|maḥillah.|Famañ|kaana|miñkum|mareeḍan|ʹaw|biheee|ʹaẓam|mir|raʹsihee|fafidyatum|miñ|ṣiyaamin|ʹaw|ṣadaq̣atin|ʹaw|nusuk.|Faʹiẓaaa|ʹamiñtum,|famañ|tamattaʻa|bil-Umrati|ʹilal|Ḥajji|famas|taysara|minal|hadyi.|Famal|lam|yajid|faṣiyaamu|s̤alaas̤ati|ʹayyaamiñ|fil|Ḥajji|wa-sabʻatin|ʹiẓaa|rajaʻtum.|Tilka|ʹasharatuñ|kaamilah.|Ẓaalika|limal|lam|yakun|ʹahluhoo|ḥaaḍiril|Masjidil|Ḥaraam.|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
2,197,"ʹAl-Ḥajju|ʹashhurum|maʻ-loomaat.|Famañ|faraḍa|feehinnal|Ḥajja|falaa|rafas̤a|wa-laa|fusooq̣a|wa-laa|jidaala|fil|Ḥajj.|Wa-maa|tafʻaloo|min|khayriñy|yaʻlamhul|laah.|Wa-tazawwadoo|faʹinna|khayraz|zaadit|taq̣waa.|Wattaq̣ooni|yaaaʹulil|ʹalbaab."
2,198,"Laysa|ʻalaykum|junaaḥun|ʹañ|tabtag̣oo|faḍ-lam|mir|Rabbikum.|Faʹiẓaaa|ʹafaḍtum|min|ʻArafaatiñ|faẓkurul|laaha|ʻiñdal|Mashʻaril|Ḥaraam.|Waẓ-kuroohu|kamaa|hadaakum.|wa-ʹiñ|kuñtum|miñ|q̣ablihee|laminaḍ|ḍaaalleeen."
2,199,"S̤umma|ʹafeeḍoo|min|ḥays̤u|ʹafaaḍan|naasu|wastag̣firul|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
2,200,"Faʹiẓaa|q̣adaytum|manaasikakum|faẓkurul|laaha|kazikrikum,|ʹaabaaaʹakum|ʹaw|ʹashadda|ẓikraa.|Faminan|naasi|mañy|yaq̣oolu|Rabbanaaa|ʹaatinaa|fid|dunyaa|wa-maa|lahoo|fil|ʹAakhirati|min|khalaaq̣."
2,201,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yaq̣oolu|Rabanaaa|ʹaatinaa|fid|dunyaa|ḥasanatañw|wa-fil|ʹAakhirati|ḥasanatañw|wa-q̣inaa|ʻaẓaaban|Naar."
2,202,"ʹUlaaaʹika|lahum|naṣeebum|mimmaa|kasaboo:|wal-laahu|Sareeʻul|ḥisaab."
2,203,"Waẓkurul|laaha|feee|ʹayyaamim|maʻdoodaat.|Famañ|taʻajjala|fee|yawmayni|falaaa|ʹis̤ma|ʻalayh.|Wa-mañ|taʹakhkhara|falaaa|ʹis̤ma|ʻalayhi|limanit|taq̣aa.|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|waʻlamooo|ʹannakum|ʹilayhi|tuḥsharoon."
2,204,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yuʻjibuka|q̣awluhoo|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-yushhidul|laaha|ʻalaa|maa-|fee|q̣albihee|wa-huwa|ʹaladdul|khis̤aam."
2,205,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tawallaa|saʻaa|fil|ʹarḍi|liyufsida|fihaa|wa-yuhlikal|ḥars̤a|wannasl.|Wal-laahu|laa-|yuḥibbul|fasaad."
2,206,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahut|taq̣il|laaha|ʹakhaẓathul|ʻizzatu|bil-ʹis̤mi|faḥasbuhoo|Jahannam;|wa-labiʹsal|mihaad!"
2,207,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yashree|nafsahub|tig̣aaaʹa|Marḍaatil|laah:|wallaahu|Raʹoofum|bilʻibaad."
2,208,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanud|khuloo|fis|Silmi|kaaaffah;|wa-laa|tattabiʻoo|khuṭuwaatish|Shaytaan.|ʹInnahoo|lakum|ʻaduwwum|mubeen."
2,209,"Faʹiñ|zalaltum|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹatkumul|Bayyinaatu|faʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
2,210,"Hal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yaʹtiyahumul|laahu|fee|z̤̣ulalim|minal|g̣amaami|walmalaaaʹikatu|wa-q̣uḍiyal|ʹamr?|Wa-ʹilal|laahi|turjaʻul|ʹumoor."
2,211,"Sal|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|kam|ʹaataynaahum|min|ʹAayatim|bayyinah.|Wa-mañy|yubaddil|niʻmatal|laa-hi|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹathu|faʹinnal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
2,212,"Zuyyina|lillaẓeena|kafarul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|wa-yas-kharoona|minal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo.|Wallaẓeenat|taq̣aw|fawq̣ahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|Wallaahu|yarzuq̣u|mañy|yashaaaʹu|big̣ayri|ḥisaab."
2,213,"Kaanan|naasu|ʹummatañw|waaḥidah;|fabaʻas̤al|laahun|nabiyyeena|Mubashshireena|wa-Muñẓireen:|wa-ʹañzala|maʻahumul|Kitaaba|bilḥaq̣q̣i|liyaḥkuma|baynan|naasi|feemakh|talafooo|feeh.|Wa-makh|talafa|feehi|ʹillal|laẓeena|ʹootoohu|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹathumul|bayyinaatu|bag̣yam|baynahum.|Fahadal|lahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|limakh|talafoo|feehi|minal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|biʹiẓnih.|Wallaahu|yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
2,214,"ʹAm|ḥasibtum|ʹañ|tadkhulul|Jannata|wa-lammaa|yaʹ-tikum|mas̤alul|laẓeena|khalaw|miñ|q̣ablikum?|Massathumul|baʹsaaaʹu|waḍḍarraaaʹu|wa-zulziloo|ḥattaa|yaq̣oolar|Rasoolu|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|mataa|naṣrul|laah?|ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|naṣral|laahi|q̣areeb!"
2,215,"Yasʹaloonaka|maa-ẓaa|yuñfiq̣oon.|Q̣ul|maaa|ʹañfaq̣tum|min|khayriñ|falilwaalidayni|wal-ʹaq̣rabeena|walyataamaa|wal-masaakeeni|wabnis|sabeel.|Wa-maa|tafʻaloo|min|khayriñ|faʹinnal|laaha|bihee|ʻAleem."
2,216,"Kutiba|ʻalaykumul|q̣itaalu|wa-huwa|kurhul|lakum.|Wa-ʻasaaa|ʹañ|takrahoo|shayʹañw|wahuwa|khayrul|lakum.|Wa-ʻasaaa|ʹañ|tuḥibboo|shayʹañw|wahuwa|sharrul|lakum.|Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|wa-ʹañtum|laa-|taʻlamoon."
2,217,"Yasʹaloonaka|ʻanish|shahril|Ḥaraami|q̣itaaliñ|feeh.|Q̣ul|q̣itaaluñ|feehi|kabeer.|Wa-ṣaddun|ʻañ|sabeelil|laahi|wa-kufrum|bihee|wal-Masjidil|Ḥaraami|wa-ʹikhraaju|ʹahlihee|minhu|ʹakbaru|ʻiñdal|laah.|Wal-fitnatu|ʹakbaru|minal|q̣atl.|Wa-laa|yazaaloona|yuq̣aatiloonakum|ḥattaa|yaruddookum|ʻañ|Deenikum|ʹinis|taṭaaʻoo.|Wa-mañy|yartadid|miñkum|ʻañ|Deenihee|fayamut|wa-huwa|kaafiruñ|faʹulaaaʹika|ḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah.|Wa-ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
2,218,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wallaẓeena|haajaroo|wa-jaahadoo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|ʹulaaaʹika|yarjoona|Raḥmatal|laah:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
2,219,"Yasʹaloonaka|ʻanil|khamri|walmaysir.|Q̣ul|feehimaaa|ʹis̤muñ|kabeeruñw|wamanaafiʻu|linnaas:|Wa-ʹis̤muhumaaa|ʹakbaru|min|nafʻihimaa.|Wa-Yasʹaloonaka|maaẓaa|yuñfiq̣oon.|Q̣ulil|ʻafw.|Kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakumul|ʹaayaati|laʻallakum|tatafakkaroon"
2,220,"Fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah.|Wa-yasʹaloonaka|ʻanil|yataamaa.|Q̣ul|ʹiṣlaaḥul|lahum|khayr.|Wa-ʹiñ|tukhaaliṭoohum|faʹikhwaanukum.|Wallaahu|yaʻlamul|mufsida|minal|muṣliḥ.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|laʹaʻnatakum:|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
2,221,"Wa-laa|tañkiḥul|mushrikaati|ḥattaa|yuʹminn:|wa-laʹamatum|muʹminatun|khayrum|mim|mushrikatiñw|walaw|ʹaʻjabatkum.|Wa-laa|tuñkiḥul|mushrikeena|ḥattaa|yuʹminoo:|wa-laʻabdum|muʹminun|khayrum|mim|mushrikiñw|wa law|ʹaʻjabakum.|ʹUlaaaʹika|yadʻoona|ʹilan|Naar.|Wallaahu|yadʻoo|ʹilal|Jannati|wal-mag̣firati|biʹiẓnih,|wa-yubayyinu|ʹaayaatihee|linnaasi|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
2,222,"Wa-yasʹaloonaka|ʻanil|maḥeeḍ.|Q̣ul|huwa|ʹaẓañ|faʻtazilun|nisaaaʹa|fil|maḥeeḍi|wa-laa|taq̣raboohunna|ḥattaa|yaṭhurn.|Faʹiẓaa|taṭahharna|faʹtoohunna|min|ḥays̤u|ʹamarakumul|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|yuḥibbut|Tawwaabeena|wa-yuḥibbul|Mutaṭahhireen."
2,223,"Nisaaaʹukum|ḥars̤ul|lakum:|faʹtoo|ḥars̤akum|ʹannaa|shiʹtum;|wa-q̣addimoo|liʹañfusikum;|wattaq̣ul|laaha|waʻlamooo|ʹannakum|mulaaq̣ooh:|Wa-bash-shiril|Muʹmineen."
2,224,"Wa-laa|tajʻalul|laaha|ʻurḍatal|liʹaymaanikum|ʹañ|tabarroo|wa-tattaq̣oo|wa-tuṣliḥoo|baynan|naas;|Wallaahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
2,225,"Laa-|yuʹaakhiẓukumul|laahu|billag̣wi|fee|ʹaymaanikum|wa-laakiñy|yuʹaakhiẓukum̃|bimaa|kasabat|q̣uloobukum;|wallaahu|G̣afoorun|Ḥaleem."
2,226,"Lillaẓeena|yuʹloona|min|nisaaaʹihim|tarabbuṣu|ʹarbaʻati|ʹashhur!|faʹiñ|faaaʹoo|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
2,227,"Wa-ʹin|ʻazamuṭ|ṭalaaq̣a|faʹinnal|laaha|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
2,228,"Walmuṭallaq̣aatu|yatarabbaṣna|biʹañfusihinna|s̤alaas̤ata|q̣uroooʹ.|Wa-laa|yaḥillu|lahunna|ʹañy|yaktumna|maa-|khalaq̣al|laahu|feee|ʹarḥaamihinna|ʹiñ|kunna|yuʹminna|bil-laahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Wa-buʻoola-tuhunna|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|biraddihinna|fee|ẓaalika|ʹin|ʹaraadooo|ʹiṣlaaḥaa.|Wa-lahunna|mis̤lul|laẓee|ʻalayhinna|bilmaʻroof:|wa-lir-rijaali|ʻalayhinna|darajah.|Wallaahu|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
2,229,"ʹAṭṭalaaq̣u|marrataan:|faʹimsaakum|bimaʻroofin|ʹaw|tasreeḥum|biʹiḥsaan.|Wa-laa|yaḥillu|lakum|ʹañ|taʹkhuẓoo|mimmaaa|ʹaataytumoohunna|shayʹan|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yakhaafaaa|ʹallaa|yuq̣eemaa|Ḥudoodal|laah.|Faʹin|khiftum|ʹallaa|yuq̣eemaa|Ḥudoodal|laahi|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalayhimaa|feemaf|tadat|bih.|Tilka|Ḥudoodul|laahi|falaa|taʻtadoohaa.|Wa-mañy|yataʻadda|Ḥudoodal|laahi|faʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
2,230,"Faʹiñ|ṭallaq̣ahaa|falaa|taḥillu|lahu|mim|baʻdu|ḥattaa|ṭañkiḥa|zawjan|g̣ayrah:|faʹiñ|ṭallaq̣ahaa|falaa|junaaha|ʻalayhimaaa|ʹañy|yataraajaʻaaa|ʹiñ|z̤̣annaaa|ʹañy|yuq̣eemaa|Ḥudoodal|laah.|Wa-tilka|Ḥudoodul|laahi|yubayyinuhaa|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
2,231,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ṭallaq̣tumun|nisaaaʹa|fabalag̣na|ʹajalahunna|faʹamsikoohunna|bimaʻroofin|ʹaw|sarriḥoohunna|bimaʻroof.|Wa-laa|tumsikoohunna|ḍiraaral|litaʻtadoo.|Wa-mañy|yafʻal|ẓaalika|faq̣ad|z̤̣alama|naf-sah.|Wa-laa|tat-takhiẓooo|ʹAayaatil|laahi|huzuwaa,|waẓkuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|wa-maaa|ʹañzala|ʻalaykum|minal|Kitaabi|wal-Ḥikmati|yaʻi-Z̤̣ukum̃|bih|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
2,232,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ṭallaq̣tumun|nisaaaʹa|fabalag̣na|ʹajalahunna|falaa|taʻḍuloohunna|ʹañy|yañkiḥna|ʹazwaajahunna|ʹiẓaa|taraaḍaw|baynahum̃|bilmaʻroof.|Ẓaalika|yooʻaz̤̣u|bihee|mañ|kaana|miñkum|yuʹminu|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Ẓaalikum|ʹazkaa|lakum|wa-ʹaṭ-har.|Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|waʹañtum|laa-|taʻlamoon."
2,233,"Walwaalidaatu|yurḍiʻna|ʹawlaadahunna|ḥawlayni|kaamilayni|liman|ʹaraada|ʹañy|yutimmar|raḍaaʻah.|Wa-ʻalal|mawloodi|lahoo|rizq̣uhunna|wa-kiswatuhunna|bilmaʻroof.|Laa-|tukallafu|nafsun|ʹillaa|wusʻahaa.|Laa-|tuḍaaarra|waalidatum|biwaladihaa|wa-laa|mawloodul|lahoo|biwaladihee|wa-ʻalal|waaris̤i|mis̤lu|ẓaalik.|Faʹin|ʹaraadaa|fiṣaalan|ʻañ|taraaḍim|minhumaa|wa-tashaawuriñ|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalayhimaa.|Wa-ʹin|ʹarattum|ʹañ|tastarḍiʻooo|ʹawlaadakum|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓaa|sallamtum|maaa|ʹaataytum̃|bilmaʻroof.|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
2,234,"Wallaẓeena|yutawaffawna|miñkumwa|yaẓaroona|ʹazwaajañy|yatarabbaṣna|biʹañfusihinna|ʹarbaʻata|ʹashhuriñw|Waʻashraa.|Faʹiẓaa|balag̣na|ʹajalahunna|falaa|juñaḥa|ʻalaykum|feemaa|faʻalna|feee|ʹañfusihinna|bilmaʻroof.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeer."
2,235,"Wa-laa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|fimaa|ʻarraḍtum̃|bihee|min|khiṭbatin|nisaaaʹi|ʹaw|ʹaknañtum|feee|ʹañfusikum.|ʻAlimal|laahu|ʹannakum|sataẓkuroonahunna|wa-laakil|laa|tuwaaʻidoohunna|sirran|ʹillaa|ʹan|taq̣uloo|q̣awlam|maʻroofaa.|Wa-laa|taʻzimoo|ʻuq̣datan|Nikaaḥi|ḥattaa|Yablug̣al|Kitaabu|ʹajalah.|Waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|feee|ʹañfusikum|faḥ-ẓarooh;|Waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|G̣afoorun|Ḥaleem."
2,236,"Laa-|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|ʹiñ|ṭallaq̣tumun|nisaaaʹa|maa-|lam|tamassoohunna|ʹaw|tafriḍoo|lahunna|fareeḍah.|Wa-mattiʻoohunna,|ʻalal|moosiʻi|q̣adaruhoo|wa-ʻalal|muq̣tiri|q̣adaruh.|Mataaʻam|bil-maʻroofi:|Ḥaq̣q̣an|ʻalal|Muḥsineen."
2,237,"Wa-ʹiñ|ṭallaq̣tumoohunna|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañ|tamassoohunna|wa-q̣ad|faraḍtum|lahunna|fareeḍatañ|faniṣfu|maa-|faraḍtum|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yaʻfoona|ʹaw|yaʻfuwal|laẓee|biyadihee|ʻuq̣datun|Nikaaḥ.|Wa-ʹañ|taʻfoo|ʹaq̣rabu|littaq̣waa.|Wa-laa|tañsawul|faḍla|baynakum.|ʹInnal|laaha|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
2,238,"Ḥaafiz̤̣oo|ʻalaṣ|Ṣalawaati|waṣ-Ṣalaatil|wusṭaa;|wa-q̣oomoo|lillaahi|q̣aaniteen."
2,239,"Faʹin|khiftum|farijaalan|ʹaw|rukbaanaa.|Faʹiẓaaa|ʹamiñtum|faẓkurul|laaha|kamaa|ʻallamakum|maa|lam|takoonoo|taʻlamoon."
2,240,"Wallaẓeena|yutawaffawna|miñkum|wa-yaẓaroona|ʹazwaajañw|waṣiyyatal|liʹazwaajihim|mataaʻan|ʹilal|ḥawli|g̣ayra|ʹikhraaj.|Faʹin|kharajna|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|Fee|maa-|faʻalna|feee|ʹañfusihinna|mim|maʻroof.|Wal-laahu|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
2,241,"Wa-lilmuṭallaq̣aati|mataaʻum|bil-maʻroof.|Ḥaq̣q̣an|ʻalal|Muttaq̣een."
2,242,"Kaẓalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakum|ʹAayaatihee|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
2,243,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|kharajoo|miñ|diyaarihim|wa-hum|ʹuloofun|ḥaẓaral|mawti|faq̣aala|lahumul|laahu|mootoo:|s̤umma|ʹaḥyaahum.|ʹInnal|laaha|la-Ẓoo|Faḍlin|ʻalan|naasi|wa-lakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yashkuroon."
2,244,"Waq̣aatiloo|fee|sabeelil|laahi|waʻlamoo|ʹannal|laaha|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
2,245,"Mañ|ẓal|laẓee|yuq̣riḍul|laaha|Q̣arḍan|Ḥasanañ|fayuḍaaʻifahoo|lahooo|ʹaḍʻaafañ|kas̤eerah?|Wallaahu|yaq̣biḍu|wa-yabṣuṭ.|Wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
2,246,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|malaʹi|mim|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|mim|baʻdi|Moosa?|ʹIẓ|q̣aaloo|linabiyyil|lahumub|ʻas̤|lanaa|Malikan|nuq̣aatil|fee|Sabeelil|laah.|Q̣aala|hal|ʻasaytum|ʹiñ|kutiba|ʻalaykumul|q̣itaalu|ʹallaa|tuq̣aatiloo?|Q̣aaloo|wa-maa|lanaaa|ʹallaa|nuq̣aatila|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-q̣ad|ʹukhrijnaa|miñ|diyaarinna|wa-ʹabnaaaʹinaa?|Falammaa|kutiba|ʻalayhimul|q̣itaalu|tawallaw|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|minhum.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum|biz̤̣z̤̣aalimeen."
2,247,"Wa-q̣aala|lahum|Nabiyyuhum|ʹinnal|laaha|q̣ad|baʻas̤a|lakum|Ṭaaloota|Malikaa.|Q̣aalooo|ʹannaa|yakoonu|lahul|mulku|ʻalaynaa|wa-naḥnu|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|bilmulki|minhu|wa-lam|yuʹta|saʻatam|minal|maal?|Q̣aala|ʹinnal|laahaṣ|ṭafaahu|ʻalaykum|wa-zaadahoo|basṭatañ|fil|ʻilmi|waljism.|Wallaahu|yuʹtee|mulkahoo|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
2,248,"Wa-q̣aala|lahum|Nabiyyuhum|ʹinna|ʹaayata|Mulkiheee|ʹañy|yaʹtiyakumut|Taabootu|feehi|sakeenatum|mir|Rabbikum|wa-baq̣iyyatum|mimmaa|taraka|ʹAalu|Moosaa|wa-ʹAalu|Haaroona|taḥmiluhul|malaaaʹikah.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹaayatal|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
2,249,"Falammaa|faṣala|Ṭaalootu|biljunoodi|q̣aala|ʹinnal|laaha|mub-taleekum̃|binahr.|Famañ|shariba|minhu|falaysa|minnee:|Wa-mal|lam|yaṭʻamhu|faʹinnahoo|minneee|ʹillaa|manig̣h|tarafa|g̣urfatam|biyadih.|Fashariboo|minhu|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|minhum.|Falammaa|jaawazahoo|huwa|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|q̣aaloo|laa-|ṭaaq̣ata|lanal|Yawma|bi-Jaaloota|wa-junoodih.|Q̣aalal|laẓeena|ya-Z̤̣unnoona|ʹannahum|mulaaq̣ul|laahi|kam|miñ|fiʹatiñ|q̣aleelatin|g̣halabat|fiʹatañ|kas̤eeratam|biʹiẓnil|laah?|Wallaahu|maʻaṣ|Ṣaabireen."
2,250,"Wa-lammaa|barazoo|li-Jaaloota|wa-junoodihee|q̣aaloo|Rabbanaaa|ʹafrig̣h|ʻalaynaa|ṣabrañw|was̤abbit|ʹaq̣daamanaa|wañs̤urnaa|ʻalal|Q̣awmil|kaafireen."
2,251,"Fahazamoohum̃|biʹiẓnil|laahi|wa-q̣atala|Daawoodu|Jaaloota|wa-ʹaataahul|laahul|Mulka|wal-Ḥikmata|wa-ʻallamahoo|mimmaa|yashaaaʹ.|Wa-law-laa|dafʻul|laahin|naasa|baʻḍahum̃|bibaʻḍil|lafasadatil|ʹarḍu|wa-laakinnal|laaha|Ẓoo|Faḍlin|ʻalal|ʻaalameen."
2,252,"Tilka|ʹAayaatul|laahi|natloohaa|ʻalayka|bilḥaq̣q̣;|wa-ʹinnaka|laminal|Mursaleen."
2,253,"Tilkar|rusulu|faḍḍalnaa|baʻḍahum|ʻalaa|baʻḍ.|Minhum|mañ|kallamal|laahu|wa-rafaʻa|baʻḍahum|darajaat.|Wa-ʹaataynaa|ʻEesab|na|Maryamal|Bayyinaati|wa-ʹayyadnaahu|birooḥil|q̣udus.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maq̣|tatalal|laẓeena|mim|baʻdihim|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹathumul|Bayyinaatu|wa-laakinikh|talafoo|faminhum|man|ʹaamana|wa-minhum|mañ|kafar.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maq̣|tataloo;|wa-laakinnal|laaha|yafʻalu|maa-|yureed."
2,254,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹañfiq̣oo|mimmaa|razaq̣naakum|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|Yawmul|laa|bayʻuñ|feehi|walaa|khullatuñw|walaa|shafaaʻah .|Wal-kaafiroona|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
2,255,"ʹAllaahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|HooʹAl|Ḥayyul|Q̣ayyoom.|Laa-|taʹkhuẓuhoo|sinatuñw|walaa|nawm.|Lahoo|Maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Mañ|ẓal|laẓee|yashfaʻu|ʻiñdahooo|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnih?|Yaʻlamu|Maa-|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-maa|khalfahum.|Wa-laa|yuḥeeṭoona|bishayʹim|min|ʻilmiheee|ʹillaa|bimaa|shaaaʹ.|Wasiʻa|Kursiyyuhus|Samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ;|wa-laa|yaʹooduhoo|ḥifz̤̣uhumaa|wa-Huwal|ʻAliyyul|ʻAz̤̣eem."
2,256,"Laaa|ʹikraaha|fid|deen.|Q̣at|tabayyanar|Rushdu|minal|G̣ayy.|Famañy|yakfur|biṭ-Ṭaag̣ooti|wa-yuʹmim|billaahi|faq̣adis|tamsaka|bilʻurwatil|wus̤q̣aa,|lañ|fiṣaama|lahaa.|Wallaahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
2,257,"ʹAllaahu|Waliyyul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|yukhrijuhum|minaz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|noor.|Wallaẓeena|kafarooo|ʹawliyaaaʹuhumuṭ|Ṭaag̣ootu|yukhrijoonahum|minan|Noori|ʹilaz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaat.|ʹUlaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
2,258,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓee|ḥaaajja|ʹIbraaheema|fee|Rabbiheee|ʹan|ʹaataahul|laahul|mulk?|ʹIẓ|q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|Rabbiyal|laẓee|yuḥyee|wa-yumeetu|q̣aala|ʹana|ʹuḥyee|wa-ʹumeet.|Q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|faʹinnal|laha|yaʹtee|bish-Shamsi|minal|Mashriq̣i|faʹti|bihaa|minal|Mag̣ribi|Fabuhital|laẓee|kafar.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
2,259,"ʹAw|kallaẓee|marra|ʻalaa|q̣aryatiñw|wa hiya|khaawiyatun|ʻalaa|ʻurooshihaa.|Q̣aala|ʹannaa|yuḥyee|haaẓihil|laahu|baʻda|mawtihaa?|Faʹamaatahul|laahu|miʹata|ʻaamiñ|s̤umma|baʻas̤ah.|Q̣aala|kam|labis̤t?|Q̣aala|Labis̤tu|yawman|ʹaw|baʻḍa|yawm.|Q̣aala|bal|labis̤ta|miʹata|ʻaamiñ|fañz̤̣ur|ʹilaa|ṭaʻaamika|wa-sharaabika|lam|yatasannah.|Wañz̤̣ur|ʹilaa|ḥimaarik!|wa-linajʻalaka|ʹaayatal|linnaasi|wañz̤̣ur|ʹilal|ʻiz̤̣aami|kayfa|nuñshizuhaa|s̤umma|naksoohaa|laḥmaa.|Falammaa|tabyyana|lahoo|q̣aala|ʹaʻlamu|ʹannal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
2,260,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|Rabbi|ʹarinee|kayfa|tuḥyil|mawtaa.|Q̣aala|ʹa-wa-lam|tuʹmin?|Q̣aala|balaa|wa-laakil|liyaṭmaʹinna|q̣albee.|Q̣aala|fakhuẓ|ʹarbaʻatam|minaṭ|ṭayri|fas̤urhunna|ʹilayka|s̤ummaj|ʻal|ʻalaaa|kulli|jabalim|minhunna|juzʹañ|s̤ummad|ʻuhunna|yaʹteenaka|saʻyaa.|Waʻlam|ʹannal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
2,261,"Mas̤alul|laẓeena|yunñfiq̣oona|ʹamwaalahum|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|kamas̤ali|ḥabbatin|ʹambatat|sabʻa|sanaabila|fee|kulli|sumbulatim|miʹatu|ḥabbah.|Wallaahu|yuḍaaʻifu|limany|yashaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
2,262,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuñfiq̣oona|ʹamwaalahum|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|s̤umma|laa-|yutbiʻoona|maaa|ʹañfaq̣oo|mannañw|walaaa|ʹaẓal|lahum|ʹajruhum|ʻiñda|Rabbihim;|wa-laa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
2,263,"Q̣awlum|maʻroofuñw|wamag̣firatun|khayrum|miñ|ṣadaq̣atiñ|yatbaʻuhaaa|ʹaẓaa.|Wallaahu|G̣aniyyun|Ḥaleem."
2,264,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|aamanoo|laa-|tubṭiloo|ṣadaq̣aatikum̃|bilmanni|wal-ʹaẓaa|kallaẓee|yuñfiq̣u|maa-lahoo|riʹaaaʹan|naasi|wa-laa|yuʹminu|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Famas̤aluhoo|kamas̤ali|ṣafwaanin|ʻalayhi|turaabuñ|faʹaṣaabahoo|waabiluñ|fatarakahoo|ṣaldaa.|Laa-|yaq̣diroona|ʻalaa|shayʹim|mimmaa|kasaboo.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|kaafireen."
2,265,"Wa-mas̤alul|laẓeena|yuñfiq̣oonaʹ|amwaalahu|mubtig̣aaaʹa|marḍaatil|laahi|wa-tas̤beetam|min|ʹañfusihim|kamas̤ali|jannatim|birabwatin|ʹaṣaabahaa|waabiluñ|faʹaatat|ʹukulahaa|ḍiʻfayn.|Faʹil|lam|yuṣibhaa|waabiluñ|faṭall .|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
2,266,"ʹAyawaddu|ʹaḥadukum|ʹañ|takoona|lahoo|jannatum|min|nakheeliñw|waʹaʻnaabiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|lahoo|feehaa|miñ|kullis̤|s̤amaraati|wa-ʹaṣaa-bahul|kibaru|wa-lahoo|ẓurriyyatuñ|ḍuʻafaaaʹu|faʹaṣaabahaaa|ʹiʻṣaaruñ|feehi|naaruñ|faḥtaraq̣at?|Kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakumul|ʹaayaati|laʻallakum|tatafakkaroon."
2,267,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹañfiq̣oo|miñ|ṭayyibaati|maa-|kasabtum|wa-mimmaaa|ʹakhrajnaa|lakum|minal|ʹarḍ.|Wa-laa|tayammamul|khabees̤a|minhu|tuñfiq̣oona|wa-lastum̃|biʹaakhiẓeehi|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|tug̣miḍoo|feeh.|Waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|G̣aniyyun|Ḥameed."
2,268,"ʹAsh-Shayṭaanu|yaʻidukumul|faq̣ra|wa-yaʹmurukum̃|bil-faḥshaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|yaʻidukum|mag̣firatam|minhu|wa-faḍlaa.|Wallaahu|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
2,269,"Yuʻtil|Ḥikmata|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|Wa-mañy|yuʹtal|Ḥikmata|faq̣ad|ʹootiya|khayrañ|kas̤eeraa.|Wa-maa|yaẓẓakkaru|ʹillaaa|ʹulul|ʹalbaab."
2,270,"Wa-maaa|ʹañfaq̣tum|min|nafaq̣atin|ʹaw|naẓartum|min|naẓriñ|faʹinnal|laaha|yaʻlamuh.|Wa-maa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|min|ʹañṣaar."
2,271,"ʹIñ|tubduṣ|Ṣadaq̣aati|faniʻimmaa|hee;|Wa-ʹiñ|tukhfoohaa|wa-tuʹtoohal|fuq̣araaaʹa|fahuwa|khayrul|lakum:|wa-yukaffiru|ʻankum|miñ|sayyiʹaatikum.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeer."
2,272,"Laysa|ʻalayka|hudaahum|wa-laakinnal|laaha|yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wa-maa|tuñfiq̣oo|min|khayriñ|faliʹañfusikum:|wa-maa|tuñfiq̣oona|ʹillab|tig̣aaaʹa|Wajhil|laah.|Wa-maa|tuñfiq̣oo|min|khayriñy|yuwaffa|ʹilaykum|waʹañtum|laa-|tuz̤̣lamoon."
2,273,"Lil-fuq̣araaaʹil|laẓeena|ʹuḥṣiroo|fee|Sabeeli|laahi|laa-|yastaṭeeʻoona|ḍarbañ|fil|ʹarḍiyaḥ|sabuhumul|jaahilu|ʹag̣niyaaaʹa|minat|taʻaffuf.|Taʻrifuhum̃|biseemaahum|laa-|yasʹaloonan|naasa|ʹilḥaafaa.|Wa-maa|tuñfiq̣oo|min|khayriñ|faʹinnal|laaha|bihee|ʻAleem."
2,274,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuñfiq̣oona|ʹamwaalahum̃|billayli|wan-nahaari|sirrañw|waʻalaaniyatañ|falahum|ʹajruhum|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|wa-laa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
2,275,"ʹAllaẓeena|yaʹkuloonar|Ribaa|laa-|yaq̣oomoona|ʹillaa|kamaa|yaq̣oomul|laẓee|yatakhabbaṭuhush|Shayṭanu|minal|mass.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣alooo|ʹinnamal|Bayʻu|mis̤lur|Riba.|Wa-ʹaḥallal|laahul|Bayʻa|waḥarramar|Riba.|Famañ|jaaaʹahoo|mawʻiz̤̣atum|mir|Rabbihee|fañtahaa|falahoo|maa-|salaf:|wa-ʹamruhooo|ʹilal|laah.|Wa-man|ʻaada|faʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naar:|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
2,276,"Yamḥaq̣ul|laahur|Ribaa|wa-yurbiṣ|ṣadaq̣aat.|Wallaahu|laa-|yuḥibbu|kulla|kaffaarin|ʹas̤eem."
2,277,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaata-wuz|Zakaata|lahum|ʹajruhum|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|wa-laa|kawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
2,278,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|waẓaroo|maa-|baq̣iya|minar|Ribaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
2,279,"Faʹil|lam|tafʻaloo|faʹ-ẓanoo|biḥarbim|minal|laahi|wa-Rasoolih:|wa-ʹiñ|tubtum|falakum|ruʹoosu|ʹamwaaalikum:|laa-|taz̤̣limoona|wa-laa|tuz̤̣lamoon."
2,280,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|ẓoo|ʻusratiñ|fanaz̤̣iratun|ʻilaa|maysarah.|Wa-ʹañ|taṣaddaq̣oo|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon."
2,281,"Wattaq̣oo|Yawmañ|turjaʻoona|feehi|ʹilal|laah.|S̤umma|tuwaffaa|kullu|nafsim|maa|kasabat|wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
2,282,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooʹ|iẓaa|tadaayañtum̃|bidaynin|ʹilaa|ʹajalim|musammañ|faktubooh.|Walyaktub|baynakum|kaatibum|bilʻadl.|Wa-laa|yaʹba|kaatibun|ʹañy|yaktuba|kamaa|ʻallamahul|laahu|falyaktub.|Walyumlilil|laẓee|ʻalayhil|ḥaq̣q̣u|walyattaq̣il|laaha|Rabbahoo|wa-laa|yabkhas|minhu|shayʹaa.|Faʹiñ|kaanal|lazee|ʻalayhil|ḥaq̣q̣u|safeehan,|ʹaw|ḍaʻeefan|ʹaw|laa-|yastaṭeeʻu|ʹañy|yumilla|huwa|falyumlil|waliyyuhoo|bilʻadl.|Wastashhidu|shaheedayni|mir|rijaalikum:|faʹil|lam|yakoonaa|rajulayni|farajulunw|wamraʹataani|mimmañ|tarḍawna|minash|shuhadaaaʹi|ʹañ|taḍilla|ʹiḥdaahumaa|fatuẓakkira|ʹiḥdaahumal|ʹukhraa.|Wa-laa|yaʹbash|shuhadaaaʹu|ʹiẓaa|maa-|duʻoo.|Wa-laa|tasʹamooo|ʹañ|taktuboohu|ṣag̣eeran|ʹaw|kabeeran|ʹilaa|ʹajalih.|Ẓaalikum|ʹaq̣saṭu|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-ʹaq̣wamu|lishshahaadati|wa-ʹadnaaa|allaa|tartaabooo|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|takoona|tijaaratan|ḥaaḍiratañ|tudeeroonahaa|baynakum|falaysa|ʻalaykum|junaaḥun|ʹallaa|taktuboohaa.|Wa-ʹash-hidooo|ʹiẓaa|tabaayaʻtum.|Wa-laa|yu-Z̤̣aaarra|kaatibuñw|walaa|shaheed.|Wa-ʹiñ|tafʻaloo|faʹinnahoo|fusooq̣um|bikum.|Wattaq̣ul|laah:|wa-yuʻallimu-kumul|laah.|Wallaahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
2,283,"Wa-ʹiñ|kuñtum|ʻalaa|safariñw|walam|tajidoo|katibañ|farihaanum|maq̣booḍah.|Faʹin|ʹamina|baʻḍukum|baʻḍañ|falyuʹaddil|laẓiʹ|tumina|ʹamaanatahoo|wal-yattaq̣il|laaha|Rabbah.|Wa-laa|taktumush|shahaadah:|wa-mañy|yaktumhaa|faʹinnahooo|ʹaas̤imuñ|q̣albuh.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|ʻAleem."
2,284,"Lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Wa-ʹiñ|tubdoo|ma|feee|ʹañfusikum|ʹaw|tukhfoohu|yuḥaasibkum̃|bihil|laah.|Fayag̣firu|limañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-yuʻazzibu|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
2,285,"ʹAamanar|Rasoolu|bimaaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayhi|mir|Rabbihee|wal-Muʹminoon.|Kullun|ʹaamana|billaahi|wa-malaaaʹikatihee|wa-kutubihee|warusulih.|Laa-|nufarriq̣u|bayna|ʹaḥadim|mir|rusulih.|Wa-q̣aaloo|samiʻnaa|wa-ʹaṭaʻnaa:|G̣ufraanaka|Rabbanaa|wa-ʹilaykal|maṣeer."
2,286,"Laa-|yukalliful|laahu|nafsan|ʹillaa|wusʻahaa.|Lahaa|maa-|kasabat|wa-ʻalayhaa|mak|tasabat.|Rabbanaa|laa-|tuʹaakhiẓnaaa|ʹin|naseenaaa|ʹaw|ʹakhṭaʹnaa.|Rabbanaa|wa-laa|taḥmil|ʻalaynaaa|ʹiṣrañ|kamaaa|ḥamaltahoo|ʻalal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablinaa.|Rabbanaa|wa-laa|tuḥammilnaa|maa|laa-|ṭaaq̣ata|lanaa|bih.|Waʻfu|ʻannaa,|wag̣hfir|lanaa,|warḥamnaa.|ʹAñta|Mawlaanaa|fañṣurnaa|ʻalal|q̣awmil|Kaafireen."
3,1,"ʹA-lif-Laaam-Meeem."
3,2,"ʹAllaahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹilla|Huwal|Ḥayyul|Q̣ayyoom."
3,3,"Nazzala|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayhi|wa-ʹañzalat|Tawraata|wal-ʹIñjeel."
3,4,"Miñ|q̣ablu|Hudal|linnaasi|wa-ʹañzalal|Furq̣aan.|ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|biʹaayaatil|laahi|lahum|ʻaẓaabuñ|shadeed:|wallaahu|ʻAzeezuñ|Ẓuñ|tiq̣aam."
3,5,"ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yakhfaa|ʻalayhi|shayʹuñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|fis|samaaa;"
3,6,"Huwal|laẓeee|yuṣawwirukum|fil|ʹarḥaami|kayfa|yashaaaʹ.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
3,7,"Huwal|laẓeeeʹ|añzala|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|minhu|ʹaayaatum|Muḥ-kamaatun|hunna|ʹUmmul|Kitaabi|wa-ʹukharu|Mutashaabihaat.|Faʹammal|laẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|zayg̣uñ|fayattabiʻoona|maa-|tashaabaha|minhub|tig̣aaa|ʹalfitnati|wabtig̣aaaʹa|taʹweelih.|Wa-maa|yaʻlamu|taʹweelahooo|ʹillal|lah.|War-Raasi-khoona|fil|ʻilmi|yaq̣ooloona|ʹaamannaa|bihee|kullum|min|ʻiñdi|Rabbinaa:|wa-maa|yaẓẓakkaru|ʹillaaa|ʹulul|ʹalbaab."
3,8,"Rabbanaa|laa-|tuzig̣|q̣uloobabana|baʻda|ʹiẓ|hadaytanaa|wa-hab|lanaa|milla|duñka|raḥmah:|ʹinnaka|ʹAñtal|Wahhaab."
3,9,"Rabbanaaa|ʹinnaka|jaamiʻun|naasi|li-Yawmil|laa|rayba|feeh:|ʹinnal|Laaha|laa-|yukhliful|meeʻaad."
3,10,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lañ|tug̣niya|ʻanhum|ʹamwaaluhum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaaduhum|minal|laahi|shayʹaa:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|hum|waq̣oodun|Naar."
3,11,"Kadaʹabi|ʹaali|Firʻawna|wallaẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim.|Kaẓẓaboo|biʹaayaatinaa,|faʹakhaẓahumul|lahu|biẓunoobihim:|wallaahu|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
3,12,"Q̣ul|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|satug̣laboona|wa-tuḥsharoona|ʹilaa|Jahannam:|wa-biʹsal|mihaad!"
3,13,"Q̣ad|kaana|lakum|ʹAyatuñ|fee|fiʹataynil|taq̣ataa:|fiʹatuñ|tuq̣aatilu|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-ʹukhraa|kaafiratuñy|yarawnahum|mis̤layhim|raʹyal|ʻayn.|Wallaahu|yuʹayyidu|binaṣrihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʻibratal|liʹulil|ʹabṣaar."
3,14,"Zuyyina|linnaasi|ḥubbush|shahawaati|minan|nisaaʹi|wal-baneena|wal-q̣anaa-ṭeeril|muq̣añṭarati|minaẓ|ẓahabi|wal-fiḍḍati|wal-khaylil|musawwamati|wal-ʹanʻaami|walḥars̤.|Ẓaalika|mataaʻul|ḥayaatid|dunyaa;|wallaahu|ʻiñdahoo|ḥusnul|maʹaab."
3,15,"Q̣ul|ʹaʹunabbiʹukum̃|bikhayrim|miñ|ẓaalikum?|Lil-laẓeenat|taq̣aw|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|Jannaatuñ|tajree|miñ|tah-tihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa|wa-ʹazwaajum|muṭahharatuñw|wariḍwaanum|minal|laah.|Wallaahu|Baṣeerum|bilʻibaad,"
3,16,"ʹAllaẓeena|yaq̣ooloona|Rabbanaaa|ʹinnanaaa|ʹaamannaa|fag̣hfir|lanaa|ẓunoobanaa|waq̣inaa|ʻaẓaaban|Naar;"
3,17,"ʹAṣ-Ṣaabireena|waṣ-Ṣaadiq̣eena|wal-Q̣aaniteena|wal-Muñfiq̣eena|wal-Mustag̣fireena|bil-ʹas-ḥaar."
3,18,"Shahidal|laahu|ʹanna-Hoo|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwa|wal-malaaaʹikatu|wa-ʹulul|ʻilmi|q̣aaaʹimam|bilq̣isṭ.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
3,19,"ʹInnad|Deena|ʻiñdal|laahil|ʹIslaam.|Wa-makh|talafal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|ʹillaa|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹahumul|ʻilmu|bag̣hyam|baynahum.|Wa-mañy|yakfur|biʹAayaatil|lahi|faʹinnal|laaha|Sareeʻul|ḥisaab."
3,20,"Faʹin|ḥaajjooka|faq̣ul|ʹaslamtu|wajhiya|lillaahi|wa-manit|tabaʻan.|Wa-q̣ul|lillaẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|wal-ʹummiyyeena|ʹaʹaslamtum?|Faʹin|ʹaslamoo|faq̣adih|tadaw.|Wa-ʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinnamaa|ʻalaykal|balaag̣:|wallaahu|Baṣeerum|bil-ʻibaad."
3,21,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yakfuroona|biʹAayaaatil|laahi|wa-yaq̣tuloonan|nabiyyeena|big̣ayri|ḥaq̣q̣iñw|wayaq̣tuloonal|laẓeena|yaʹmuroona|bilq̣isṭi|minan|naasi|fabashshirhum̃|biʻaẓaabin|ʹaleem."
3,22,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹaakhirati|wa-maa|lahum|min|naṣireen."
3,23,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|ʹootoo|naṣeeban|minal|Kitaabi|yudʻawna|ʹilaa|Kitaabil|laahi|liyaḥkuma|bay-nahum|s̤umma|yatawallaa|fareeq̣um|minhum|wahum|muʻriḍoon."
3,24,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣aaloo|lañ|tamassanan|Naaru|ʹillaaa|ʹayyaaman|maʻdoodaat:|wa-g̣arrahum|fee|deenihim|maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
3,25,"Fakayfa|ʹiẓaa|jamaʻnaahum|liyawmil|laa|rayba|feeh,|wa-wuffiyat|kullu|nafsim|maa|kasabat|wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon?"
3,26,"Q̣ulil|laahumma|Maalikal|Mulki|tuʹtil|Mulka|mañ|tashaaʹu|wa-tañẓiʻul|Mulka|mimmañ|tashaaaʹ.|Wa-tuʻizzu|mañ|tashaaaʹu|wa-tuẓillu|mañ|tashaaaʹ:|biyadikal|Khayr.|ʹInnaka|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
3,27,"Toolijul|layla|fin|nahaari|wa-toolijun|nahaara|fil|layl:|wa-tukhrijul|ḥayya|minal|mayyiti|wa-tukhrijul|mayyita|minal|ḥayyi|wa-tarzuq̣u|mañ|tashaaʹu|big̣ayri|ḥisaab."
3,28,"Laa-|yattakhiẓil|Muʹminoonal|kaafireena|ʹawliyaaaʹa|miñ|doonil|Muʹmineen.|Wa-mañy|yafʻal|ẓaalika|falaysa|minal|laahi|fee|shayʹin|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|tat-taq̣oo|minhum|tuq̣aah.|Wa-yuḥaẓẓi-rukumul|laahu|Nafsah;|wa-ʹilal|laahil|maṣeer."
3,29,"Q̣ul|ʹiñ|tukhfoo|maa-|fee|ṣudoorikum|ʹaw|tubdoohu|yaʻlamhul|laah.|Wayaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
3,30,"Yawma|tajidu|kullu|nafsim|maa|ʻamilat|min|khayrim|muḥ-ḍarañw|wamaa|ʻamilat|miñ|soooʹ.|Tawaddu|law|ʹanna|baynahaa|wa-baynahooo|ʹamadam|baʻeedaa.|Wa-yuhaẓẓi-rukumul|lahu|Nafsah.|Wallaahu|Raʹoofum|bilʻibaad."
3,31,"Q̣ul|ʹiñ|kuñtum|tuḥibboonal|laaha|fattabiʻoonee|yuḥbibkumul|laahu|wa-yag̣fir|lakum|ẓunoobakum:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
3,32,"Q̣ul|ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|war-Rasool:|faʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbul|Kaafireen."
3,33,"ʹInnal|laahaṣ|ṭafaaa|ʹAadama|wa-Nooḥañw|waʹAala|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹAala|ʻImraana|ʻalal|ʻaalameen,"
3,34,"Ẓurreeyyatam|baʻḍuhaa|mim|baʻḍ:|wallaahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
3,35,"ʹIẓ|q̣aalat|imraʹatu|ʻImraana|Rabbi|ʹinnee|naẓartu|laka|maa-|fee|baṭnee|muḥarrarañ|fataq̣abbal|minnee:|ʹinnaka|ʹAñtas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
3,36,"Falammaa|waḍaʻathaa|q̣aalat|Rabbi|ʹinnee|waḍaʻtuhaaa|ʹuñs̤aa!|Wallaahu|ʹAʻlamu|bimaa|waḍaʻat|wa-laysaẓ|ẓakaru|kalʹuñs̤aa.|Waʹinnee|sammaytuhaa|Maryama|waʹinneee|ʹuʻeeẓuhaa|bika|waẓurriyatahaa|minash|Shayṭaanir|Rajeem."
3,37,"Fataq̣abbalahaa|Rabbuhaa|biq̣aboolin|ḥasaniñw|waʹambatahaa|nabaatan|ḥasanañw|wakaffalahaa|Zakariyyaa.|Kullamaa|dakhala|ʻalayhaa|Zakariyyal|Miḥraaba|wajada|ʻiñdahaa|rizq̣aa.|Q̣aala|yaa-Maryamuʹ|annaa|laki|haaẓaa?|Q̣aalat|huwa|min|ʻiñdil|laah:|ʹinnal|laha|yarzuq̣u|mañy|yashaaaʹu|big̣ayri|ḥisaab."
3,38,"Hunaalika|daʻaa|Zakariyyaa|Rabbah:|q̣aala|Rabbi|hab|lee|mil|laduñka|ẓurriyyatañ|ṭayyibah:|ʹinnaka|Sameeʻud|duʻaaaʹ."
3,39,"Fannaadathul|malaaʹikatu|wa-huwa|q̣aaʹimuñy|yuṣallee|fil|Miḥraabi|ʹannal|laaha|yubashshiruka|bi-Yaḥyaa|muṣaddiq̣am|bi-Kalimatim|minal|laahi|wa-sayyidañw|waḥaṣurañw|wa-Nabiyyam|minaṣ|ṣaaliḥeen."
3,40,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹannaa|yakoonu|lee|g̣ulaamuñw|waq̣ad|balag̣aniyal|kibaru|wam-raʹatee|ʻaaq̣ir?|Q̣aala|kaẓaalikal|laahu|yafʻalu|maa-|yashaaʹ."
3,41,"Q̣aala|Rabbij|ʻal|Leee|ʹAayah!|Q̣aala|ʹAayatuka|ʹallaa|tukalliman|naasa|s̤alaas̤ata|ʹayyaamin|ʹillaa|ramzaa.|Waẓkur|Rabbaka|kas̤eerañw|wasabbiḥ|bilʻashiyyi|wal-ʹib-kaar."
3,42,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aa-latil|malaaaʹikatu|yaa-Maryamu|ʹinnal|laahaṣ|ṭafaaki|waṭahharaki|waṣṭafaaki|ʻalaa|nisaaʹil|ʻaalameen."
3,43,"Yaa-Maryamu|uq̣nutee|li-Rabbiki|wasjudee|warkaʻee|maʻar|raakiʻeen."
3,44,"Ẓaalika|min|ʹambaaaʹil|g̣aybi|noo-ḥeehi|ʹilayk.|Wa-maa|kuñta|ladayhim|ʹiẓ|yulq̣oona|ʹaq̣laamahum|ʹayyuhum|yak-fulu|Maryam:|wa-maa|kuñta|ladayhim|ʹiẓ|yakhtaṣimoon."
3,45,"ʹIẓ|q̣aa-latil|malaaaʹikatu|yaa-Maryamu|ʹinnal|laaha|yubashshiruki|bi-Kalimatim|minhus|muhul|Maseeḥu|ʻEesab|nu|Maryama|wajeehañ|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirati|wa-minal|Muq̣arrabeen."
3,46,"Wa-yukallimun|naasa|fil|mahdi|wa-kahlañw|waminaṣ|ṣaaliheen."
3,47,"Q̣aalat|Rabbi|ʹannaa|yakoonu|lee|waladuñw|wa-lam|yamsasnee|bashar.|Q̣aala|kaẓaalikil|laahu|yakhlaq̣u|maa-|yashaaaʹ:|ʹiẓaa|q̣aẓaaa|ʹamrañ|faʹinnamaa|yaq̣oolu|lahoo|ʻKUÑʹ|fayakoon!"
3,48,"Wa-yuʻallimuhul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|wat-Tawraata|wal-ʹIñjeel,"
3,49,"Wa-Rasoolanʹ|ilaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel:|ʹannee|q̣ad|jiʹtukum̃|biʹaayatim|mir|Rabbikum|ʹanneee|ʹakhulq̣u|lakum|minaṭ|ṭeeni|kahayʹatiṭ|ṭayri|faʹanñfukhu|feehi|fayakoonu|ṭayram|biʹiẓnil|laaḥ.|Waʹubriʹul|ʹakmaha|wal-ʹabraṣa|waʹuḥyil|mawtaa|biʹiẓnil|laah.|Waʹunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|taʹkuloona|wamaa|taddakhi|fee|bayootikum.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹaayatal|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen;"
3,50,"Wa-Muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayya|minat|Tawraati|wa-liʹuḥilla|lakum̃|baʻḍal|laẓee|ḥurrima|ʻalaykum|wa-jiʹtukum̃|biʹAayatim|mir|Rabbikum,|fattaq̣ul|laaha|waʹaṭeeʻoon."
3,51,"ʹInnal|laaha|Rabbee|wa-Rabbukum|faʻbudooh.|Haaẓaa|Ṣiraṭum|mustaq̣eem."
3,52,"Fa-lammaaa|ʹaḥassa|ʻEesaa|min-humul|Kufra|q̣aala|man|ʹAñṣaareee|ʹilal|laah?|Q̣aalal|Ḥawaariyyoona|naḥnu|ʹAñṣaarul|laah:|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|washhad|biʹannaa|Muslimoon."
3,53,"Rabbanaaa|ʹaamannaa|bimaaa|ʹañzalta|wattabaʻnar|Rasoola|faktubnaa|maʻash|Shaahideen."
3,54,"Wa-makroo|wa-makral|laah:|wallaahu|Khayrul|maakireen."
3,55,"ʹIẓ|q̣aalal|laahu|yaa-ʻEesaaa|ʹinnee|mutawaffika|wa-raafiʻuka|ʹilayya|wa-muṭah-hiruka|minal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-jaaʻilul|laẓeenat|taabaʻooka|fawq̣al|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹila|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamah.|S̤umma|ʹilayya|marjiʻukum|faʹaḥkumu|baynakum|feemaa|kuñtum|feehi|takhtalifoon."
3,56,"Faʹammal|aẓeena|kafaroo|faʹuʻaẓẓibuhum|ʻaẓaabañ|shadeedañ|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAa|wa-maa|lahum|min|naaṣireen."
3,57,"Waʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|waʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|fayu|ʹujoorahum:|wallaahu|laa-|yuḥibbuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
3,58,"Ẓaalika|natloohu|ʻalayka|minal|ʹAayaati|waẓ-Ẓikril|Ḥakeem."
3,59,"ʹInna|mas̤ala|ʻEesaa|ʻiñdal|laahi|kamas̤ali|ʹAadam;|khalaq̣ahoo|miñ|turaabiñ|s̤umma|q̣aala|lahoo|ʻKUÑʹ|fayakoon."
3,60,"ʹAl-Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbika|falaa|takun|minal|mumtareen."
3,61,"Faman|ḥaajjaka|feehi|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹaka|minal|ʻilmi|faq̣ul|taʻaalaw|nadʻu|ʹabnaaaʹanaa|Waabnaaaʹakum|Wanisaaaʹanaa|wa-nisaaaʹakum|waʹañfusanaa|waʹañfusakum|s̤umma|nabtahil|fanajʻal|laʻnatal|laahi|ʻalal|kaaẓibeen."
3,62,"ʹInna|haaẓaa|lahuwal|q̣aṣaṣul|ḥaq̣q̣:|wa-maa|min|ʹilaahin|ʹillal|laah:|waʹinnal|laaha|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakim."
3,63,"Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|bil-mufsideen."
3,64,"Q̣ul|yaaa-ʹahlal|Kitaabi|taʻaalaw|ʹilaa|Kalimatiñ|sawaaaʹim|baynanaa|wa-baynakum|ʹallaa|naʻbuda|ʹilal|laaha|wa-laa|nushrika|bihee|shayʹañw|walaa|yat-takhiẓa|baʻḍunaa|baʻḍan|ʹarbaabam|miñ|doonil|laah.|Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faq̣oolush|hadoo|biʹannaa|Muslimoon."
3,65,"YaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|lima|tuḥaajjoona|feee|ʹIbraaheema|wa-maaa|ʹunẓilatit|Tawraatu|wal-ʹIñjeelu|ʹillaa|mim|baʻdih?|Afalaa|taʻq̣iloon."
3,66,"Haaaʹañtum|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ḥaa-jajtum|feemaa|lakum̃|bihee|ʻilmuñ|falima|tuḥaajjoona|feemaa|laysa|lakum̃|bihee|ʻilm?|Wal-laahu|yaʻlamu|waʹañtum|laa-|taʻlamoon!"
3,67,"Maa-|kaana|ʹIbraaheemu|Yahududiyaañw|walaa|Naṣraaniyyañw|Wa laakiñ|kaana|Ḥaneefam|Muslimaa:|wa-maa|kaana|minal|Mushrikeen."
3,68,"ʹInna|ʹawlan|naasi|biʹIb|lallaẓeenat|tabaʻoohu|wa-haaẓan|Nabiyyu|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo:|wallaahu|Waliyyul|Muʹmineen."
3,69,"Waddaṭ|ṭaaaʹifatum|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|law|yuḍilloonakum.|Wa-maa|yuḍilloona|ʹillaaa|ʹañfusahum|wa-maa|yashʻuroon."
3,70,"YaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|lima|takfuroona|biʹAayaatil|laahi|waʹantum|tashhadoon."
3,71,"YaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|lima|talbisoonal|ḥaq̣q̣a|bilbaaṭili|wa-taktumoonal|ḥaq̣q̣a|waʹañtum|taʻlamoon?"
3,72,"Wa-q̣aalaṭ|ṭaaaʹifatum|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|ʹaaminoo|billaẓeee|ʹaamanoo|ʻalal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|waj-han|nahaari|wak-furooo|ʹaakhirahoo|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon;"
3,73,"Wa-laa|tuʹminooo|ʹillaa|limañ|tabiʻa|Deenakum.|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|hudaa|hudal|laahi|ʹañy|yuʹtaaa|ʹaḥadum|mis̤la|maaa|ʹooteetum|ʹaw|yuḥaaaj|ʻiñda|Rabbikum.|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|faḍla|biyadil|lah:|yuʹteehi|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wal-laahu|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
3,74,"Yakhtaṣṣu|biraḥmatihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wal-laahu|Ẓul|faḍlil|ʻAz̤̣eem."
3,75,"Wa-min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|man|ʹiñ|taʹmanhu|biq̣iñṭaariñy|yuʹaddiheee|ʹilayk.|Wa-minhum|man|ʹiñ|taʹmanhu|bideenaril|laa|yuʹaddiheee|ʹilayka|illaa|maa-|dumta|ʻalayhi|q̣aaaʹimaa.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣aaloo|laysa|ʻalaynaa|fil|ʹummiyyeena|sabeel.|Wa-yaq̣ooloona|ʻalal|laahil|Kaẓiba|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon."
3,76,"Balaa|man|ʹawfaa|biʻahdihee|wattaq̣aa|faʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muttaq̣een."
3,77,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yashtaroona|biʻahdil|laahi|waʹaymaanihim|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelan|ʹulaaaʹika|laa-|khalaaq̣a|lahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|wa-laa|yukalimuhumul|laahu|wa-laa|yañz̤̣ura|ʹilayhim|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|wa-laa|yuzakkeehim:|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
3,78,"Waʹinna|minhum|lafareeq̣añy|yalwoona|ʹalsinatahum̃|bil-Kitaabi|litaḥsaboohu|minal|Kitaabi|wa-maa|huwa|minal|Kitaab.|Wa-yaq̣ooloona|huwa|miñ|ʻiñdil|laahi|wa-maa|huwa|min|ʻiñdil|laah:|wa-yaq̣ooloona|ʻalal|laaheel|kaẓiba|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon."
3,79,"Maa-|kaana|libasharin|ʹañy|yuʹtiyahul|laahul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥukma|wan-Nubuwwata|s̤umma|yaq̣oola|linnaasi|koonoo|ʻibaadal|lee|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-laakiñ|koonoo|Rabbaaniyyeena|bimaa|kuñtum|tuʻallimoonal|Kitaaba|wa-bimaa|kuñtum|tadrusoon."
3,80,"Wa-laa|yaʹmurakum|ʻañ|tat-takhiẓul|malaaaʹikata|wan-nabiyyeena|ʹarbaabaa.|ʹAyaʹmurukum̃|bilkufri|baʻda|ʹiẓ|ʹañtum|Muslimoon?"
3,81,"Waʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓal|laahu|Mees̤aaq̣an|Nabiyyeena|lamaaa|ʹaataytukum|miñ|Kitaabiñw|wa-Ḥikmatiñ|s̤umma|jaaaʹakum|Rasoolum|Muṣaddiq̣ul|limaa|maʻakum|latuʹminunna|bihee|wala-tañ-ṣuroonah.|Q̣aala|ʹaʹaq̣rartum|waʹakhaẓtum|ʹalaa|ẓaalikum|ʹIṣree?|Q̣aalooo|ʹaq̣rarnaa.|Q̣aala|fashhadoo|waʹana|maʻkum|minash|Shaahideen."
3,82,"Famañ|tawallaa|baʻda|ẓaalika|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|faasiq̣oon."
3,83,"ʹAfag̣ayra|Deenil|laahi|yab-g̣oona|wa-lahooo|ʹaslama|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|ṭawʻañw|wa karhañw|waʹilayhi|yurjaʻoon?"
3,84,"Q̣ul|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|wa-maa|ʹuñzila|ʻalaynaa|wa-maaa|ʹuñẓila|ʻalaaa|ʹIbraaheema|waʹIsmaaʻeela|waʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|wal-ʹAsbaaṭi|wa-maaa|ʹootiya|Moosaaa|waʻEesaa|wan-nabiyyoona|mir|Rabbihim.|Laa-|nufarriq̣u|bayna|ʹaḥadim|minhum,|wa-naḥnu|lahoo|Muslimoon."
3,85,"Wa-mañy|yabtag̣i|g̣ayral|ʹIslaami|Deenañ|falañy|yuq̣bala|minh;|wa-huwa|fil|ʹAakhirati|minal|khaasireen."
3,86,"Kayfa|yahdil|laahu|q̣awmañ|kafaroo|baʻda|ʹeemaanihim|wa-shahidooo|ʹannar|Rasoola|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|wajaaaʹahumul|Bayyinaat?|Wal-laahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
3,87,"ʹUlaaʹika|jazaaaʹuhum|ʹanna|ʻalayhim|laʻnatal|laahi|walmalaaaʹikati|wannaasi|ʹajmaʻeen;"
3,88,"Khaalideena|feehaa;|laa-|yukhaffafu|ʻanhumul|ʻaẓaabu|wa-laa|hum|yuñz̤̣aroon;"
3,89,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|taaboo|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|wa-ʹaṣlaḥoo;|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
3,90,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|baʻda|ʹeemaanihim|s̤ummaz|daadoo|kufral|lañ|tuq̣bala|tawbatuhum;|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humuḍ|ḍaaalloon."
3,91,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-maatoo|wa-hum|kuffaaruñ|falañy|yuq̣bala|min|ʹaḥadihim|milʹul|ʹarḍi|ẓahabañw|walawif|tadaa|bih.|ʹUlaaaʹika|lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleemuñw|Wamaa|lahum|min|naaṣireen."
3,92,"Lañ|tanaalul|birra|ḥattaa|tuñfiq̣oo|mimmaa|tuḥibboon.|Wa-maa|tuñfiq̣oo|miñ|shayʹiñ|faʹinnal|laaha|bihee|ʻAleem."
3,93,"Kulluṭ|ṭaʻaami|kaana|ḥillal|li-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʹillaa|maa-|ḥarrama|ʹIsraaaʹeelu|ʻalaa|nafsihee|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañ|tunazzalat|Tawraah.|Q̣ul|faʹtoo|bit-Tawraati|fatloohaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
3,94,"Famanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓiba|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|faʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
3,95,"Q̣ul|ṣadaq̣al|laah:|fattabiʻoo|Millata|ʹIbraaheema|ḥaneefaa;|wa-maa|kaana|minal|mushrikeen."
3,96,"ʹInna|ʹAwwala|Baytiñw|wuḍiʻa|linnaasi|lallaḍee|bi-Bakkata|mubaarakañw|wahudal|lil-ʻaalameen:"
3,97,"Feehi|ʹAayaatum|Bayyinaatum|Maq̣aamu|ʹIbraaheema;|wa-mañ|dakhalahoo|kaana|ʹaaminaa.|Wa-lillaahi|ʻalan|naasi|Ḥijjul|Bayti|manis|taṭaaʻa|ʹilayhi|sabeelaa.|Wa-mañ|kafara|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣aniyyun|ʻanil|ʻaalameen."
3,98,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|lima|takfuroona|biʹAayaatil|laahi|wallaahu|Shaheedun|ʻalaa|maa-|taʻmaloon?"
3,99,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|lima|taṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|man|ʹaamana|tab-g̣oo-nahaa|ʻiwajañw|waʹañtum|shuhadaaaʹ?|Wa-mal|laahu|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon."
3,100,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiñ|tuṭeeʻoo|fareeq̣am|minal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|yaruddookum̃|baʻda|ʹeemaanikum|kaafireen."
3,101,"Wa-kayfa|takfuroona|wa-ʹañtum|tutlaa|ʻalaykum|ʹAayaatul|laahi|wa-feekum|Rasooluh?|Wa-mañy|yaʻtaṣim̃|bil-laahi|faq̣ad|hudiya|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
3,102,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|ḥaq̣q̣a|tuq̣aatihee|wa-laa|tamootunna|ʹillaa|wa-ʹañtum|Muslimoon."
3,103,"Waʻtaṣimoo|bi-Ḥablil|laahi|jameeʻañw|walaa|tafarraq̣oo.|Waẓkuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓ|kuñtum|ʹaʻdaaaʹañ|faʹallafa|bayna|q̣uloobikum|faʹaṣbaḥtum̃|biniʻmatiheee|ʹikhwaanaa;|wa-kuñtum|ʻalaa|shafaa|ḥufratim|minan|naari|faʹañq̣aẓakum|minhaa.|Kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakum|ʹAayaatihee|laʻallakum|tahtadoon."
3,104,"Waltakum|miñkum|ʹUmmatuñy|yadʻoona|ʹilal|khayri|wa-yaʹmuroona|bil-maʻroofi|wa-yan-hawna|ʻanil|muñkar:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|mufliḥoon."
3,105,"Wa-laa|takoonoo|kallaẓeena|tafarraq̣oo|wakhtalafoo|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹahumul|Bayyinaat:|wa-ʹulaaʹika|lahum|ʻa-Z̤̣aabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
3,106,"Yawma|tabyaḍḍu|wujoohuñw|wataswaddu|wujooh:|faʹammal|laẓeenas|waddat|wujoohum:|ʹakafartum̃|baʻda|ʹeemaanikum|faẓooq̣ul|ʻaẓaaba|bimaa|kuñtum|takfuroon?"
3,107,"Wa-ʹammal|laẓeenab|biyaḍḍat|wujoohuhum|fafee|raḥmatil|laah:|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
3,108,"Tilka|ʹAayaatul|laahi|natloohaa|ʻalayka|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-mal|laahu|yureedu|z̤̣ulmal|lilʻaalameen."
3,109,"Walillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-ʹilal|laahi|turjaʻul|ʹumoor."
3,110,"Kuñtum|khayra|ʹummatin|ʹukhrijat|linnaasi|taʹmuroona|bilmaʻroofi|wa-tanhawna|ʻanil|muñkari|wa-tuʹminoona|billaah.|Wa-law|ʹaamana|ʹAhlul|Kitaabi|lakaana|khayral|lahum:|minhumul|muʹminoona|wa-ʹaks̤aru-humul|faasiq̣oon."
3,111,"Lañy|yaḍurrookum|ʹillaaa|ʹaẓaaa;|wa-ʹiñy|yuq̣aatilookum|yuwal-lookumul|ʹadbaar.|S̤umma|laa-|yuñṣaroon."
3,112,"Ḍuribat|ʻalayhimuẓ|ẓillatu|ʹayna|maa-|s̤uq̣ifooo|ʹillaa|bi-Ḥablim|minal|laahi|wa-Ḥablim|minan|naasi|wa-baaaʹoo|big̣aḍabim|minal|laahi|wa-ḍuribat|ʻalayhimul|maskanah.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|kaanoo|yakfuroona|biʹAayaatil|laahi|wa-yaq̣tuloonal|ʹambiyaaaʹa|big̣ayri|ḥaq̣q̣;|ẓaalika|bimaa|ʻaṣaw|Wakaanoo|yaʻtadoon."
3,113,"Laysoo|sawaaaʹaa.|Min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|ʹummatuñ|q̣aaaʹimatuñy|yatloona|ʹAayaatil|laahi|ʹaanaaaʹal|layli|wa-hum|yasjudoon."
3,114,"Yuʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-yaʹmuroona|bilmaʻroofi|wa-yanhawna|ʻanil|muñkari|wa-yusaariʻoona|fil|khayrat:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|minañ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
3,115,"Wa-maa|yafʻaloo|miñ|khayriñ|falañy|yukfarooh:|wal-laahu|ʻAleemum|bil-Muttaq̣een."
3,116,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lañ|tug̣niya|ʻanhum|ʹamwaaluhum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaaduhum|minal|laahi|shayʹaa:|waʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
3,117,"Mas̤alu|maa-|yuñfiq̣oona|fee|haaẓihil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|kamas̤ali|reeḥiñ|feeha|ṣirrun|ʹaṣaabat|ḥarsa|q̣awmiñ|z̤̣alamooo|ʹañfusahum|faʹahlakath.|Wa-maa|z̤̣alamahumul|laahu|wa-laakin|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
3,118,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tat-takhiẓoo|biṭaanatam|miñ|doonikum|laa-|yaʹloonakum|khabaalaa.|Waddu|maa-|ʻanittum.|Q̣ad|badatil|bag̣ḍaaaʹu|min|ʹafwaahihim|wa-maa|tukhfee|ṣudooruhum|ʹakbar.|Q̣ad|bayyanna|lakumul|ʹAayaati|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻq̣iloon."
3,119,"Haaaʹañtum|ʹulaaaʹi|tuḥibboonahum|wa-laa|yuḥibboonakum|wa-tuʹminoona|bil-Kitaabi|kullih.|Waʹiẓaa|laq̣ookum|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa:|waʹiẓa|khalaw|ʻaḍḍoo|ʻalaykumul|ʹanaamila|minal|g̣ayz̤̣.|Q̣ul|mootoo|big̣ayz̤̣ikum:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
3,120,"ʹIñ|tamsaskum|ḥasanatuñ|tasuʹhum|waʹiñ|tuṣibkum|sayyiʹatuñy|yafraḥoo|bihaa.|Waʹiñ|taṣbiroo|watattaq̣oo|laa-|yaḍurrukum|kayduhum|shayʹaa:|ʹinnal|laah|bimaa|yaʻmaloona|Muḥeeṭ."
3,121,"Waʹiẓ|g̣adawta|min|ʹahlika|tubawwiʹul|Muʹmineena|maq̣aaʻida|lilq̣itaal:|wal-laahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem:"
3,122,"ʹIẓ|hammaṭ|ṭaaaʹifataani|miñkum|ʹañ|taf-shalaa|wal-laahu|Waliyyuhuma,|waʻalal|laahi|fal-yatawak-kalil|Muʹminoon."
3,123,"Wa-laq̣ad|naṣarakumul|laahu|bi-Badriñw|waʹañtum|ʹaẓillah:|fattaq̣ul|laaha|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
3,124,"ʹIẓ|taq̣oolu|lil-Muʹmineena|ʹalañy|yakfiyakum|ʹañy|yumiddaku|Rabbukum̃|bis̤alaas̤ati|ʹaalaafim|minal|malaaaʹikati|muñzaleen?"
3,125,"Balaaa|ʹiñ|taṣbiroo|wa-tattaq̣oo|wa-yaʹtookum|miñ|fawrihim|haaẓaa|yumdidkum|Rabbukum̃|bikhamsati|ʹaalaafim|minal|malaaaʹikati|musawwimeen."
3,126,"Wa-maa|jaʻalahul|laahu|ʹillaa|bushraa|lakum|wa-litaṭmaʹinna|q̣uloobukum̃|bih:|wa-man|naṣru|ʹillaa|min|ʻiñdi|laahil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥakeem:"
3,127,"Liyaq̣ṭaʻa|ṭarafam|minal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹaw|yakbitahum|fayañq̣aliboo|khaaaʹibeen."
3,128,"Laysa|laka|minal|ʹamri|shayʹun|ʹaw|yatooba|ʻalayhim|ʹaw|yuʻaẓẓibahum|faʹinnahum|Z̤̣aalimoon."
3,129,"Walillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Yag̣firu|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yuʻaẓẓibu|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raheem."
3,130,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|taʹkulur|Ribaaa|ʹaḍʻaafam|muḍaaʻafah ;|wattaq̣ul|laaha|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
3,131,"Wattaq̣un|Naaral|lateee|ʹuʻiddat|lilkaafireen."
3,132,"Wa-ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|war-Rasoola|laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
3,133,"Wa-saariʻooo|ʹilaa|mag̣firatim|mir|Rabbikum|wa-Jannatin|ʻarḍuhas|samaawaatu|wal-ʹarḍu|ʹuʻiddat|lil-Muttaq̣een"
3,134,"ʹAllaẓeena|yunfiq̣oona|fis|sarraaaʹi|waḍ-ḍarraaaʹi|wal-kaa-Z̤̣imeenal|g̣ayz̤̣a|wal-ʻaafeena|ʻanin|naas:|wal-laahu|yuḥibbul|Muḥsineen;"
3,135,"Wal-laẓeena|ʹiẓaa|faʻaloo|faa-ḥishatan|ʹaw|z̤̣alamooo|ʹañfusahum|ẓakarul|laaha|fastag̣faroo|liẓunoobihim,|Wa-mañy|yag̣firuẓ|ẓunooba|ʹillal|laah?|wa-lam|yuṣirroo|ʻalaa|maa-|faʻaloo|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon."
3,136,"ʹUlaaaʹika|Jazaaʹuhum|mag̣firatum|mir|Rabbihim|wa-jannaatuñ|tajree|miñ|tah-tihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa:|wa-niʻma|ʹajrul|ʻaamileen!"
3,137,"Q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablikum|Sunanuñ|faseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mukaẓẓibeen."
3,138,"Haaẓaa|bayaanul|linnasi|wa-hudañw|wamawʻiz̤̣atul|lil-muttaq̣een."
3,139,"Wa-laa|tahinoo|wa-laa|tahẓanoo|wa-ʹañtumul|ʹaʻlawna|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen!"
3,140,"ʹIñy|yamsaskum|q̣arḥuñ|faq̣ad|massal|q̣awma|q̣arḥum|mis̤luh.|Wa-tilkal|ʹayyaamu|nudaawiluhaa|baynan|naas:|wa-liyaʻlamal|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-yattakhiẓa|miñkum|shuhadaaaʹ.|Wal-laahu|laa-|yu-ḥibbuz̤̣|Z̤̣aalimeen."
3,141,"Wa-liyumaḥ-ḥiṣal|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-yamḥaq̣al|kaafireen."
3,142,"ʹAm|ḥasibtum|ʹañ|tadkhulul|Jannata|wa-lamma|yaʻlamil|laahul|laẓeena|jaahadoo|miñkum|wa-yaʻlamaṣ|Ṣaabireen?"
3,143,"Wa-laq̣ad|kuñtum|tamannawnal|mawta|miñ|q̣abli|ʻañ|tal-q̣awh:|faq̣ad|raʹaytumoohu|wa-ʹañtum|tañz̤̣uroon."
3,144,"Wa-maa|Muḥammadun|ʹillaa|Rasool:|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablihir|rusul.|ʹAfaʹim|maata|ʹaw|q̣utilañ|q̣alabtum|ʻalaaa|ʹaʻq̣aabikum?|Wa-many|yañq̣alib|ʻalaa|ʻaq̣ibayhi|falañy|yaḍurral|laaha|shayʹaa;|wa-sayajzil|laahush|Shaakireen."
3,145,"Wa-maa|kaana|linafsin|ʹañ|tamoota|illaa|biʹiẓnil|laahi|kitaabam|muʹajjalaa.|Wa-mañy|yurid|s̤awaabad|dunyaa|nuʹtihee|minhaa;|wa-mañy|yurid|s̤awaabal|ʹAakhirati|nuʹtihee|minhaa|Wa-sanaj-zish|Shaakireen."
3,146,"Wakaʹayyim|min|nabyyiñ|q̣aatala|maʻahoo|Ribbiyyoona|kaseer?|Famaa|wahanoo|limaaa|ʹaṣaabahum|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-maa|ḍaʻufoo|wa-mas|takaanoo.|Wallaahu|yuḥibbuṣ|Ṣaabireen."
3,147,"Wa-maa|kaana|q̣awlahum|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aaloo|Rabbanag̣|fir|lanaa|ẓunoobanaa|wa-ʹisraafanaa|feee|ʹamrinaa|was̤abbit|ʹaq̣daamanaa|wañṣurnaa|ʻalal|q̣awmil|kaafireen."
3,148,"Faʹaataahumul|laahu|s̤awaabad|dunyaa|waḥusna|s̤awaabil|ʹAakhirah:|Wal-laahu|yuḥibbul|Muhsineen."
3,149,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|ʹiñ|tuṭeeʻul|laẓeena|kafaroo|yaruddookum|ʻalaaa|ʹaʻq̣aaabikum|fatañq̣aliboo|khaasireen."
3,150,"Balil|laahu|maw-laakum,|wa-Huwa|Khayrun|naaṣireen."
3,151,"Sanulq̣ee|fee|q̣uloobil|laẓeena|kafarur|ruʻba|bimaaa|ʹashrakoo|bil-laahi|maa-|lam|yunazzil|bihee|sulṭaanaa:|wa-maʹwaa-humun|Naar:|wa-biʹsa|mas̤waz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
3,152,"Wa-laq̣ad|ṣadaq̣akumul|laahu|waʻdahooo|ʹiẓ|taḥussoonahum̃|biʹiẓnih,|ḥattaaa|ʹizaa|fashiltum|wa-tanaazaʻtum|fil|ʹamri|wa-ʻaṣaytum|mim|baʻdi|maaa|ʹaraakum|maa|tuḥibboon.|Miñkum|mañy|yureedud|dunyaa|wa-miñkum|mañy|yureedul|ʹAakhirah.|S̤umma|ṣarafakum|ʻanhum|liyabtaliyakum.|Wa-laq̣ad|ʻafaa|ʻañkum:|wal-laahu|Ẓoo|faḍlin|ʻalal|Muʹmineen"
3,153,"ʹIẓ|tuṣʻidoona|wa-laa|talwoona|ʻalaaa|ʹaḥadiñw|war-Rasoolu|yadʻookum|feee|ʹukhraakum|faʹaṣaabakum|g̣ammam|big̣ammil|likaylaa|ṭaḥzanoo|ʻalaa|maa-|faatakum|wa-laa|maaa|ʹaṣaabakum.|Wal-laahu|Khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
3,154,"S̤umma|ʹañzala|ʻalaykum|min|baʻdil|g̣ammi|ʹamanatan|nuʻaasañy|yag̣shaa|ṭaaaʹifatam|miñkum|waṭaaaʹifatuñ|q̣ad|ʹahammathum|ʹañfusuhum|ya-Z̤̣unnoona|bil-laahi|g̣ayral|ḥaq̣q̣i|z̤̣annal|jaahiliyyah.|Yaq̣ooloona|hal|lanaa|minal|ʹamri|miñ|shayʹ.|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|ʹamra|kullahoo|lillaah.|Yukhfoona|feee|ʹañfusihim|Maa|laa-|yubdoona|lak.|Yaq̣ooloona|law|kaana|lanaa|minal|ʹamri|shayʹum|maa|q̣utilna|haahunaa.|Q̣ul|law|kuñtum|fee|buyootikum|labarazal|laẓeena|kutiba|ʻalayhimul|q̣atlu|ʹilaa|maḍaajiʻihim;|walliyabtaliyal|laahu|maa-|fee|ṣudoorikum|waliyumaḥḥiṣa|maa-|fee|q̣uloobikum.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
3,155,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|tawallaw|miñkum|Yawmal|taq̣al|jamʻaani|ʹinnamas|tazal-lahumush|Shayṭaanu|bibaʻḍi|maa-|kasaboo.|Wa-laq̣ad|ʻafal|laahu|ʻanhum:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorun|Haleem."
3,156,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|takoonoo|kallaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-q̣aalooo|liʹikhwaanihim|ʹiẓaa|ḍaraboo|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹaw|kaanoo|g̣uzzal|law|kaanoo|ʻiñdanaa|maa-|maatoo|wa-maa|q̣utiloo;|liyajʻalal|laahu|ẓaalika|ḥasratañ|fee|q̣uloobihim.|Wal-laahu|yuḥee|wa-yumeet,|wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
3,157,"Wa-laʹiñ|q̣utiltum|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|ʹaw|muttum|lamag̣firatum|minal|laahi|wa-raḥmatun|khayrum|mimmaa|yajmaʻoon."
3,158,"Wa-laʹim|muttum|ʹaw|q̣utiltum|laʹilal|laahi|tuḥsharoon."
3,159,"Fabimaa|Raḥmatim|minal|laahi|liñta|lahum.|Wa-law|kuñta|faz̤̣z̤̣an|g̣aleez̤̣al|q̣albi|lañ-faḍḍoo|min|ḥawlik:|faʻfu|ʻanhum|wastag̣fir|lahum|wa-shaawir-hum|fil|ʹamr.|Faʹiẓaa|ʻazamta|fatawakkal|ʻalal|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Mutawakkileen."
3,160,"ʹIñy|yañṣurkumul|laahu|falaa|g̣aaliba|lakum:|wa-ʹiñy|yakhẓulkum|famañ|ẓal|laẓee|yañ-ṣurukum|mim|baʻdih?|Wa-ʻalal|laahi|fal-yatawak-kalil|Muʹminoon."
3,161,"Wa-maa|kaana|linabiyyin|ʹañy|yag̣ull.|Wa-mañy|yag̣lul|yaʹti|bimaa|g̣alla|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah;|s̤umma|tuwaffaa|kullu|nafsim|maa|kasabat|wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
3,162,"ʹAfamanit|tabaʻa|Riḍwaanal|laahi|kamam|baaaʹa|bisakhaṭim|minal|laahi|wa-maʹwaahu|Jahannam,|wa-biʹsal|maṣeer?"
3,163,"Hum|darajaatun|ʻiñdal|laah:|wallaahu|Baṣeerum|bimaa|yaʻmaloon."
3,164,"Laq̣ad|mannal|laahu|ʻalal|Muʹmineena|ʹiẓ|baʻas̤a|feehim|Rasoolam|min|ʹañfusihim|yatloo|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatihee|wa-yuzak-keehim|wa-yuʻallimu-humul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|wa-ʹiñ|kaanoo|miñ|q̣ablu|lafee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
3,165,"ʹA-walammaaa|ʹaṣaabatkum|muṣeebatuñ|q̣ad|ʹaṣabtum|mis̤layhaa|q̣ultum|ʹannaa|haaẓaa?|Q̣ul|huwa|min|ʻiñdi|ʹañfusikum:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
3,166,"Wa-maaa|ʹaṣaabakum|yawmal|taq̣al|jamʻaani|fabiʹiẓnil|laahi|wa-liyaʻlamal|Muʹmineen;"
3,167,"Wa-liyaʻlamal|laẓeena|naafaq̣oo|wa-q̣eela|lahum|taʻaalaw|q̣aatiloo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|ʹawid|faʻoo.|Q̣aaloo|law|naʻlamu|q̣itaalal-lat|tabaʻnaakum.|Hum|lilkufri|yawmaʹiẓin|ʹaq̣rabu|minhum|lil-ʹeemaan,|Yaq̣ooloona|biʹafwaahihim|maa|laysa|fee|q̣uloobihim.|Wal-laahu|ʹAʻlamu|bimaa|yaktumoon."
3,168,"ʹAllaẓeena|q̣aaloo|liʹikhwaanihim|wa-q̣aʻadoo|law|ʹaṭaaʻoonaa|maa|q̣utiloo|Q̣ul|fadraʹoo|ʻan|ʹañfusikumul|mawta|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
3,169,"Wa-laa|taḥsabannal|laẓeena|q̣utiloo|fee|Sabilil|laahi|ʹamwaataa.|Bal|ʹaḥyaaaʹun|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|yurzaq̣oon;"
3,170,"Fariḥeena|bimaaa|ʹaataahumul|laahu|miñ|faḍlihee|wa-yas-tabshiroona|billaẓeena|lam|yalḥaq̣oo|bihim|min|khalfihim|ʹallaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
3,171,"Yastabshiroona|biniʻmatim|minal|laahi|wa-faḍliñw|wa-ʹannal|laaha|laa|yuḍeeʻu|ʹajral|Muʹmineen."
3,172,"ʹAl-laẓeenas|tajaaboo|lil-laahi|war-Rasooli|mim|baʻdi|maaa|ʹaṣaabahumul|q̣arḥu|lil-laẓeena|ʹaḥsanoo|minhum|wattaq̣aw|ʹajrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
3,173,"ʹAllaẓeena|q̣aala|lahumun|naasu|ʹinnan|naasa|q̣ad|jamaʻoo|lakum|fakhshawhum|fazaadahum|ʹeemaana:|wa-q̣aaloo|ḥasbunal|laahu|wa-Niʻmal|Wakeel."
3,174,"Fañ-q̣alaboo|biniʻmatim|minal|laahi|wa-faḍlil|lam|yam-sashum|soooʹuñw|wattabaʻoo|Riḍ-waanal|laah:|wal-laahu|Ẓu|faḍlin|ʻAz̤̣eem."
3,175,"ʹInnamaa|ẓaalikumush|Shayṭaanu|yukhawwifu|ʹawliyaaaʹah.|Falaa|takhaafoohum|wa-khaafooni|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
3,176,"Wa-laa|yaḥzuñkal|laẓeena|yusaariʻoona|fil|kufr:|ʹinnahum|lañy|yaḍurrul|laaha|shayʹaa.|Yureedul|laahu|ʹallaa|yajʻala|lahum|ḥaz̤̣z̤̣añ|fil|ʹAakhirati|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabum|ʻaz̤̣eem."
3,177,"ʹInnal|laẓeenash|tarawul|kufra|bil-ʹeemaani|lañy|yaḍurrul|laaha|shayʹaa;|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
3,178,"Wa-laa|yaḥ-sabannal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹannamaa|numlee|lahum|khayrulli|ʹañfusihim:|ʹinnamaa|numlee|lahum|liyazdaadooo|ʹis̤maa:|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabum|muheen."
3,179,"Maa-|kaanal|lahu|liyaẓaral|Muʹmineena|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹañtum|ʻalayhi|ḥattaa|yameeẓal|khabees̤a|minaṭ|ṭayyib.|Wa-maa|kaanal|laahu|liyuṭliʻakum|ʻalal|g̣aybi|wa-laakinnal|laaha|yajtabee|mir|rusulihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Faʹaaminoo|billaahi|wa-rusulih.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuʹminoo|wa-tattaq̣oo|falakum|ʹajrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
3,180,"Wa-laa|yaḥ-sabanaal|laẓeena|yab-khaloona|bimaaa|ʹaataahumul|laahu|miñ|faḍlihee|huwa|khayral|lahum:|bal|huwa|sharrul|lahum:|sayuṭawwaq̣oona|maa-|bakhiloo|bihee|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah|Wa-lillaahi|meeraas̤us|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wal-laahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeer."
3,181,"Laq̣ad|samiʻal|laahu|q̣awlal|laẓeena|q̣aaloo|ʹinnal|laaha|faq̣eeruñw|wanaḥnu|ʹag̣niyaaaʹ|Sanaktubu|maa-|q̣aaloo|wa-q̣at-lahumul|ʹAmbiyaaʹa|big̣ayri|ḥaq̣q̣iñw|wanaq̣oolu|ẓooq̣oo|ʻaẓaabal|ḥareeq̣!"
3,182,"Ẓaalika|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeekum|wa-ʹannal|laaha|laysa|bi-Z̤̣allaamil|lilʻabeed."
3,183,"ʹAllaẓeena|q̣aalooo|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻahida|ʹilaynaa|ʹallaa|nuʹmina|li-Rasoolin|ḥattaa|yaʹtiyanaa|biq̣urbaaniñ|taʹkuluhun|Naar.|Q̣ul|q̣ad|jaaaʹakum|rusulum|miñ|q̣ablee|bil-Bayyinaati|wa-billaẓee|q̣ultum|falima|q̣atal-tumoohum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
3,184,"Faʹiñ|kaẓ-ẓabooka|faq̣ad|kuẓ-ẓiba|rusulum|miñ|q̣ablika|jaaaʹoo|bil-Bayyinaati|waz-Zuburi|wal-Kitaabil|Muneer."
3,185,"Kullu|nafsiñ|ẓaaaʹiq̣atul|mawt.|Wa-ʹinnamaa|tuwaffawna|ʹujoorakum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|Famañ|zuḥziḥa|ʻanin|naari|wa-ʹudkhilal|Jannata|faq̣ad|faaz.|Wa-mal|ḥayaatud|dunyaaa|ʹillaa|mataaʻul|g̣uroor."
3,186,"Latublawunna|feee|ʹamwaalikum|wa-ʹañfusikum;|wa-latasmaʻunna|minal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablikum|wa-minal|laẓeena|ʹashrakooo|ʹaẓañ|kas̤eeraa.|Wa-ʹiñ|taṣbiroo|wa-tattaq̣oo|faʹinna|ẓaalika|min|ʻazmil|ʹumoor."
3,187,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓal|laahu|Mees̤aaq̣al|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|latubayyinunnahoo|lin-naasi|wa-laa|taktumoonah;|fanabaẓoohu|waraaaʹa|z̤̣uhoorihim|washtaraw|bihee|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelaa.|Fabiʹsa|maa-|yashtaroon."
3,188,"Laa-|taḥ-sabannal|laẓeena|yaf-raḥoona|bimaaa|ʹataw|Wa yuḥibboona|ʹañy|yuḥmadoo|bimaa|lam|yafʻaloo|falaa|taḥ-sa-bannahum̃|bimafaazatim|minal|ʻaẓaab.|Walahum|‘azaabun|Aleem"
3,189,"Wa-lillaahi|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi:|wal-laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
3,190,"ʹInna|fee|khalq̣is|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wakhtilaafil|layli|wan-nahaari|laʹAayaatil|liʹulil|ʹalbaab."
3,191,"ʹAl-laẓeena|yaẓ-kuroonal|laaha|q̣iyaamanw|waq̣uʻoodañw|waʻalaa|junoobihim|wa-yata-fakkaroona|fee|khalq̣is|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|Rabbanaa|maa-|khalaq̣ta|haaẓaa|baaṭilaa!|Subḥaanaka|faq̣inaa|ʻaẓaaban|Naar!"
3,192,"Rabbanaaa|ʹinnaka|mañ|tud-khilin|Naara|faq̣ad|ʹakhzaytah:|wa-maa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|min|ʹañṣaar!"
3,193,"Rabbanaaa|ʹinnanaa|samiʻnaa|Munaadiyañay|yaunaadee|lil-eemaani|ʹan|ʹaaminoo|bi-Rabbikum|faʹaamannaa.|Rabbanaa|fag̣fir|lanaa|ẓunoobanaa|wa-kaffir|ʻannaa|sayyiʹaatinaa|wa-tawaffanaa|maʻal|ʹAbraar."
3,194,"Rabbanaa|wa-ʹaatinaa|ma|wa-ʻattanaa|ʻalaa|rusulika|wa-laa|tukhzinaa|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah:|ʹinnaka|laa-|tukhliful|meeʻaad."
3,195,"Fas-tajaaba|lahum|Rabbuhum|ʹannee|laaa|ʹuḍeeʻu|ʻamala|ʻaamilim|miñkum|miñ|ẓakarin|ʹaw|ʹuñs̤aa.|Baʻḍukum|mim|baʻḍ.|Fal-laẓeena|haajaroo|wa-ʹukhrijoo|miñ|diyaarihim|wa-ʹooẓoo|fee|Sabeelee|wa-q̣aataloo|wa-q̣utiloo|laʹukaffiranna|ʻanhum|sayyiʹaatihim|wa-laʹudkhilanna-hum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥ-tihal|ʹanhaar|s̤awaabam|min|ʻiñdil|laah:|wal-laahu|ʻiñdahoo|ḥusnus̤|s̤awaab."
3,196,"Laa-|yag̣urrannaka|taq̣al-lubul|laẓeena|kafaroo|fil|bilaad."
3,197,"Mataaʻuñ|q̣aleel:|s̤umma|maʹwaahum|Jahannam:|wa-biʹsal|mihaad!"
3,198,"Laakinil|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|Rabbahum|lahum|Jannatuñ|tajree|miñ|taḥ-tihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa|nuzulam|min|ʻiñdil|laah:|wa-maa|ʻiñdal|laahi|khayrul|lil-ʹAbraar."
3,199,"Wa-ʹinna|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|lamañy|yuʹminu|billaahi|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaykum|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayhim|khaashiʻeena|lillaahi|laa-|yashtaroona|biʹAayaatil|laahi|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelaa.|ʹUlaaaʹika|lahum|ʹajruhum|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|ʹinnal|laaha|Sareeʻul|ḥisaab."
3,200,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanuṣ|biroo|waṣaabiroo|wa-raabiṭoo:|wattaq̣ul|laaha|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
4,1,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasut|taq̣oo|Rabbakumul|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|min|Nafsiñw|waaḥidatiñw|wakhalaq̣a|minhaa|zawjahaa|wa-bas̤s̤a|minhumaa|rijaalañ|kas̤eerañw|wanisaaaʹaa.|Wattaq̣ul|laahal|laẓee|tasaaaʹaloona|bihee|wal-ʹarḥaam:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻalaykum|Raq̣eebaa."
4,2,"Wa-ʹaatul|yataamaaa|ʹamwaalahum|wa-laa|tatabaddalul|khabees̤a|biṭṭayyib.|Wa-laa|taʹkulooo|ʹamwaalahum|ʹilaaa|ʹamwaalikum.|ʹInnahoo|kaana|ḥoobañ|kabeeraa."
4,3,"Wa-ʹin|khiftum|ʹallaa|tuq̣siṭoo|fil|yataamaa|fañkiḥoo|maa-|ṭaaba|lakum|minan|nisaaaʹi|mas̤naa|was̤ulaas̤a|wa-rubaaʻ.|Faʹin|khiftum|ʹallaa|taʻdiloo|fawaaḥidatan|ʹaw|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanukum.|Ẓaalika|ʹadnaaa|ʹallaa|taʻooloo."
4,4,"Wa-ʹaatun|nisaaaʹa|ṣaduq̣aatihinna|niḥlah;|faʹiñ|ṭibna|lakum|ʻañ|shayʹim|minhu|nafsañ|fakuloohu|haneeʹam|mareeeʹaa."
4,5,"Wa-laa|tuʹtus|sufahaaaʹa|ʹamwaalakumul|latee|jaʻalal|laahu|lakum|q̣iyaamañw|warzuq̣oohum|feehaa|waksoohum|wa-q̣ooloo|lahum|q̣awlam|maʻroofaa."
4,6,"Wabtalul|yataamaa|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|balag̣un|nikaaḥ;|faʹin|ʹaanastum|minhum|rushdañ|fad-faʻooo|ʹilayhim|ʹamwaalahum;|wa-laa|taʹkuloohaaa|ʹisraafañw|Wabidaaran|ʹañy|yakbaroo.|Wa-mañ|kaana|g̣aniyyañ|falyastaʻfif.|Wa-mañ|kaana|faq̣eerañ|fal-yaʹkul|bilmaʻroof.|Faʹiẓaa|dafaʻtum|ʹilayhim|ʹamwaalahum|faʹashhidoo|ʻalayhim:|wa-kafaa|billaahi|Ḥaseebaa."
4,7,"Lirrijaali|naṣeebum|mimmaa|tarakal|waalidaani|wal-ʹaq̣raboonaa,|wa-lin-nisaaaʹi|naṣeebum|mimmaa|tarakal|waalidaani|wal-ʹaq̣raboona|mimma|q̣alla|minhu|ʹaw|kas̤ur.|Naṣeebam|mafrooḍaa."
4,8,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ḥaḍaral|q̣ismata|ʹulul|q̣urbaa|walyataamaa|walmasaakeenu|farzuq̣oohum|minhu|wa-q̣ooloo|lahum|q̣awlam|maʻroofaa."
4,9,"Walyakhshal|laẓeena|law|tarakoo|min|khalfihim|ẓurriyyatañ|ḍiʻaafan|khaafoo|ʻalayhim:|falyattaq̣ul|laaha|walyaq̣ooloo|q̣awlañ|sadeedaa."
4,10,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yaʹkuloona|ʹamwaalal|yataamaa|z̤̣ulman|ʹinnamaa|yaʹkuloona|fee|buṭoonihim|Naaraa:-Wa|sayaṣlawna|saʻeeraa."
4,11,"Yooṣeekumul|laahu|feee|ʹawlaadikum:|liẓ-ẓakari|mis̤lu|ḥaz̤̣ẓil|ʹuñṣayayn:|faʹiñ|kunna|nisaaaʹañ|fawq̣as̤|natayni|falahunna|s̤ulus̤aa|maa-|tarak;|waʹiñ|kaanat|waaḥidatañ|falahan|niṣf.|Wa-liʹabawayhi|likulli|waaḥidim|minhumas|sudusu|mimmaa|taraka|ʹiñ|kaana|lahoo|walad;|faʹil|lam|yakul|lahoo|waladuñw|wawaris̤ahooo|ʹabawaahu|faliʹummihis̤|s̤ulus̤;|faʹiñ|kaana|lahooo|ʹikhwatuñ|faliʹummihis|sudusu|mim|baʻdi|waṣiyyatiñy|yooṣee|bihaaa|ʹaw|dayn.|Aabaaaʹukum,|waʹabnaaaʹukum|laa-|tadroona|ʹayyuhum|ʹaq̣rabu|lakum|nafʻaa.|Fareeḍatam|minal|laah;|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,12,"Wa-lakum|niṣfu|maa-|taraka|ʹazwaajukum|ʹil|lam|yakul|lahunna|walad;|faʹiñ|kaana|lahunna|waladuñ|falakumur|rubuʻu|mimmaa|tarakna|mim|baʻdi|Waṣiyyatiñy|yooṣeena|bihaaa|ʹaw|dayn.|Wa-lahunnar|rubuʻu|mimmaa|taraktum|ʹil|lam|yakul|lakum|walad;|faʹiñ|kaana|lakum|waladuñ|falahunnas̤|s̤umunu|mimmaa|taraktum|mim|baʻdi|Waṣiyyatiñ|tooṣoona|bihaaa|ʹaw|dayn.|Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|rajuluñy|yooras̤u|kalaalatan|ʹawim|raʹatuñw|walahooo|ʹakhun|ʹaw|ʹukhtuñ|falikulli|waaḥidim|minhumas|sudus;|faʹiñ|kaanooo|ʹaks̤ara|miñ|ẓaalika|fahum|shurakaaʹu|fis̤|s̤ulus̤i|mim|baʻdi|Waṣiyyatiñy|yooṣaa|bihaaa|ʹaw|daynin|g̣ayra|muḍaarr.|Waṣiyyatam|minal|laah;|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥaleem."
4,13,"Tilka|Ḥudoodul|laah:|wa-mañy|yuṭiʻil|laha|wa-Rasoolahoo|yudkhilhu|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa:|waẓaalikal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
4,14,"Wa-mañy|yaʻṣil|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wa-yataʻadda|ḥudoodahoo|yudkhilhu|Naaran|khaalidañ|feehaa:|wa-lahoo|ʻaẓaabum|muheen."
4,15,"Wallaatee|yaʹteenal|faaḥishata|min|nisaaaʹikum|fastashhidoo|ʻalayhinna|ʹarbaʻatam|miñkum:|faʹiñ|shahidoo|faʹamsikoohunna|fil|buyooti|ḥattaa|yatawaffaahunnal|mawtu|ʹaw|yajʻalal|laahu|lahunna|sabeelaa."
4,16,"Wallaẓaani|yaʹtiyaanihaa|miñkum|faʹaaẓoohumaa.|Faʹiñ|taabaa|wa-ʹaṣlaḥaa|faʹaʻriḍoo|ʻanhumaa;|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|Tawwaabar|Raḥeemaa."
4,17,"ʹInnamat|tawbatu|ʻalal|laahi|lillaẓeena|yaʻmaloonas|soooʹa|bijahaalatiñ|s̤umma|yatooboona|miñ|q̣areebiñ|faʹulaaaʹika|yatoobul|laahu|ʻalayhim:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,18,"Wa-laysatit|tawbatu|lillaẓeena|yaʻmaloonas|sayyiʹaati|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|ḥaḍara|ʹaḥadahumul|mawtu|q̣aala|ʹinnee|tubtul|ʹaana|wa-lal|laẓeena|yamootoona|wa-hum|kuffar:|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹaʻtadnaa|lahum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
4,19,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|yaḥillu|lakum|ʹañ|taris̤un|nisaaaʹa|karhaa.|Wa-laa|taʻḍuloohunna|litaẓhaboo|bibaʻḍi|maaa|ʹaataytumoohunna|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yaʹteena|bifaaḥishatim|mubayyinah;|wa-ʻaashiroohunna|bilmaʻroof.|Faʹiñ|karihtumoohunna|faʻasaaa|ʹañ|takrahoo|shyʹañw|wayajʻalal|laahu|feehi|khayrañ|kas̤eeraa."
4,20,"Wa-ʹin|ʹarattumustib|daala|ẓawjim|makaana|zawjiñw|waʹaataytum|ʹiḥdaahunna|q̣iñṭaarañ|falaa|taʹkhuẓoo|minhu|shayʹaa:|ʹataʹkhuẓoonahoo|buhtaanañw|waʹis̤mam|mubeenaa."
4,21,"Wa-kayfa|taʹkhuẓoonahoo|wa-q̣ad|ʹafḍaa|baʻḍukum|ʹilaa|baʻḍiñw|waʹakhaẓna|miñkum|mees̤aaq̣an|g̣aleez̤̣aa?"
4,22,"Wa-laa|tañkiḥoo|maa-|nakaḥa|ʹaabaaaʹukum|minan|nisaaaʹi|ʹillaa|maa-|q̣ad|salaf:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|faaḥishatañw|wamaq̣tanw|wasaaaʹa|sabeelaa."
4,23,"Ḥurrimat|ʻalaykum|ʹummahaatukum|wa-banaatukum|wa-ʹakhawaatukum|wa-ʻammaatukum|wa-khaalaatukum|wa-banaatul|ʹakhi|wa-banaatul|ʹukhti|wa-ʹummahaatu|kumul|laateee|ʹarḍaʻnakum|wa-ʹakhawaatukum|minarraḍaaʻati|wa-ʹummahaatu|nisaaaʹikum|wa-rabaaaʹibukumul|laatee|fee|ḥujoorikum|min|nisaaaʹikumul|laatee|dakhaltum̃|bihinn,|faʹil|lam|takoonoo|dakhaltum̃|bihinna|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|wa-ḥalaaaʹilu|ʹabnaaaʹikumul|laẓeena|min|ʹaṣlaabikum|wa-ʹañ|tajmaʻoo|baynal|ʹukhtayni|ʹillaa|maa-|q̣ad|salaf;|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa:"
4,24,"Walmuḥṣanaatu|minan|Nisaaaʹi|ʹillaa|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanukum.|Kitaabal|laahi|ʻalaykum.|Wa-ʹuḥilla|lakum|maa|waraaaʹa|ẓaalikum|ʹañ|tabtag̣oo|biʹamwaalikum|muḥṣineena|g̣ayra|musaafiḥeen.|Famas|tamtaʻtum̃|bihee|minhunna|faʹaatoohunna|ʹujoorahunna|fareeḍah.|Wa-laa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|fimaa|taraaḍaytum̃|bihee|mim|baʻdil|fareeḍati,|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,25,"Wa-mal|lam|yastaṭiʻ|miñkum|ṭawlan|ʹañy|yañkiḥal|Muḥṣanaatil|Muʹminaati|famim|maa|malakat|ʹaymaanukum|miñ|fatayaatikumul|Muʹminaat:|wallaahu|ʹaʻlamu|biʹeemaanikum|Baʻḍukum|mim|baʻḍ:|fañkiḥoohunna|biʹiẓni|ʹahlihinna|wa-ʹaatoohunna|ʹujoorahunna|bilmaʻroofi|muḥṣanaatin|g̣ayra|musaafiḥaatiñw|walaa|muttakhiẓaati|ʹakhdaan.|Faʹiẓaaa|ʹuḥṣinna|faʹin|ʹatayna|bifaaḥishatiñ|faʻalayhinna|niṣfu|maa-|ʻalal|muḥṣanaati|minal|ʻaẓaab.|Ẓaalika|liman|khashiyal|ʻanata|miñkum.|Wa-ʹañ|taṣbiroo|khayrul|lakum:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
4,26,"Yureedul|laahu|liyubayyina|lakum|wa-yahdiyakum|sunanal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablikum|wa-yatooba|ʻalaykum:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
4,27,"Wallaahu|yureedu|ʹañy|yatooba|ʻalaykum;|Wayureedul|laẓeena|yattabiʻoonash|shahawaati|ʹañ|tameeloo|maylan|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
4,28,"Yureedul|laahu|ʹañy|yukhaffifa|ʻañkum;|wa-khuliq̣al|ʹiñsaanu|ḍaʻeefaa."
4,29,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|taʹkulooo|ʹamwaalakum̃|baynakum̃|bilbaaṭili|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|takoona|tijaaratan|ʻañ|taraaḍim|miñkum:|walaa|taq̣tulooo|ʹanfusakum:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|bikum|Raḥeemaa!"
4,30,"Wa-mañy|yafʻal|ẓaalika|ʻudwaanañw|wa-Z̤̣ulmañ|fasawfa|nuṣleehi|Naaraa:|wa-kaana|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseeraa."
4,31,"ʹIñ|tajtaniboo|kabaaaʹira|maa-|tunhawna|ʻanhu|nukaffir|ʻañkum|sayyiʹaatikum|wa-nudkhilkum|Mudkhalañ|kareemaa."
4,32,"Wa-laa|tatamannaw|maa-|faḍḍalal|laahu|bihee|baʻḍakum|ʻalaa|baʻḍ.|Lirrijaali|naṣeebum|mimmak|tasaboo,|wa-lin-Nisaaaʹi|naṣeebum|mimmak|tasabn.|Wasʹalul|laaha|miñ|faḍlih.|ʹInnal|laaha|kaana|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleemaa."
4,33,"Wa-likulliñ|jaʻalnaa|mawaaliya|mimmaa|tarakal|waalidaani|wal-ʹaq̣raboon.|Wallaẓeena|ʻaq̣adat|ʹaymaanukum|faʹaatoohum|naṣeebahum.|ʹInnal|laaha|kaana|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Shaheedaa."
4,34,"ʹArrijaalu|q̣awwaamoona|ʻalan|Nisaaaʹi|bimaa|faḍ-ḍalal|laahu|baʻḍahum|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñw|wabimaaa|ʹañfaq̣oo|min|ʹamwaalihim,|Faṣ-Ṣaaliḥaatu|q̣aanitaatun|ḥaafi-Z̤̣atul|lil-g̣aybi|bimaa|ḥafi-Z̤̣al|laah.|Wallaatee|takhaafoona|nushoozahunna|faʻi-Z̤̣oohunna|wahjuroohunna|fil|maḍaajiʻi|waḍriboohunn.|Faʹin|ʹaṭaʻnakum|falaa|tabg̣oo|ʻalayhinna|sabeelaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAliyyañ|Kabeeraa."
4,35,"Wa-ʹin|khiftum|shiq̣aaq̣a|baynihimaa|fabʻas̤oo|ḥakamam|min|ʹahlihee|waḥakamam|min|ʹahlihaa.|ʹIñy|yureedaaa|ʹiṣlaaḥ|añyyuwaffiq̣il|laahu|baynahumaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAleeman|Khabeeraa."
4,36,"Waʻbudul|laaha|wa-laa|tushrikoo|bihee|shayʹañw|wabilwaalidayni|ʹiḥsaanañw|Wabiẓil|q̣urbaa|wal-yataamaa|wal-masaakeeni|wal-jaari|ẓil|q̣urbaa|wal-jaaril|junubi|waṣ-ṣaaḥibi|biljambi|wabnis|sabeeli|wa-maa|malakat|ʹaymaanukum:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbu|mañ|kaana|mukhtaalañ|fakhooraa;"
4,37,"ʹAllaẓeena|yabkhaloona|wa-yaʹmuroonan|naasa|bilbukhli|wa-yaktumoona|maaa|ʹaataahumul|laahu|miñ|faḍlih;|wa-ʹaʻtadnaa|lilkaafireena|ʻaẓaabam|muheenaa;"
4,38,"Wallaẓeena|yuñfiq̣oona|ʹamwaalahum|riʹaaaʹan|naasi|wa-laa|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wa-laa|bil-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Wa-mañy|yakunish|shayṭaanu|lahoo|q̣areenañ|fasaaaʹa|q̣areenaa."
4,39,"Wa-maaẓaa|ʻalayhim|law|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-ʹañfaq̣oo|mimmaa|razaq̣ahumul|laah?|Wa-|kaanallaahu|bihim|ʻAleemaa."
4,40,"ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yaz̤̣limu|mis̤q̣aala|z̤̣arrah:|wa-ʹiñ|taku|ḥaṣanatañy|yuḍaaʻifhaa|wa-yuʻti|mil|ladunhu|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
4,41,"Fakayfa|ʹiẓaa|jiʹnaa|miñ|kulli|ʹummatim|bishaheediñw|wa|jiʹnaabika|ʻalaa|haaaʹulaaaʹi|Shaheedaa?"
4,42,"Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yawad|dullaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-ʻaṣawur|Rasoola|law|tusawwaa|bihimul|ʹarḍ:|wa-laa|yaktumoonal|laaha|ḥadees̤aa!"
4,43,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|taq̣rabuṣ|ṣalaata|wa-ʹañtum|sukaaraa|ḥattaa|taʻlamoo|maa-|taq̣ooloona|wa-laa|junuban|ʹillaa|ʻaabiree|sabeelin|ḥatta|tag̣tasiloo.|Wa-ʹiñ|kuñtum|marḍaaa|ʹaw|ʻalaa|safarin|ʹaw|jaaaʹa|ʹaḥadum|miñkum|minal|g̣aaaʹiṭi|ʹaw|laamastumun|niṣaaaʹa|falam|tajidoo|maaaʹañ|fatayammamoo|ṣaʻeedañ|ṭayyibañ|famsaḥoo|biwujoohikum|wa-ʹaydeekum:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAfuwwan|G̣afooraa."
4,44,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|ʹootoo|naṣeebam|minal|Kitaabi|yashtaroonaḍ|ḍalaalata|wa-yureedoona|ʹañ|taḍillus|sabeel."
4,45,"Wallaahu|ʹaʻlamu|biʹaʻdaaaʹikum;|wa-kafaa|billaahi|Waliyyañw|Wakafaa|billaahi|Naṣeeraa."
4,46,"Minal|laẓeena|haadoo|yuḥarrifoonal|kalima|ʻam|mawaaḍiʻihee|wa-yaq̣ooloona|samiʻnaa|wa-ʻaṣaynaa|wasmaʻ|g̣ayra|musmaʻiñw|waraaʻinaa|lay-yam|biʹalsinatihim|waṭaʻnañ|fid|deen.|Wa-law|ʹannahum|q̣aaloo|samiʻnaa|wa-ʹaṭaʻnaa|wasmaʻ|wañz̤̣urnaa|lakaana|khayral|lahum|wa-ʹaq̣wama|wa-laakil|laʻanahumul|laahu|bikufrihim|falaa|yuʹminoona|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa."
4,47,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|ʹaaminoo|bimaa|nazzalnaa|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|maʻakum|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañ|naṭmisa|wujoohañ|fanaruddahaa|ʻalaaa|ʹadbaarihaaa|ʹaw|nalʻanahum|kamaa|laʻannaaa|ʹAṣḥaabas|Sabt.|Wa-kaana|ʹamrul|laahi|mafʻoolaa."
4,48,"ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yag̣firu|ʹañy|yushraka|bihee|wayag̣firu|maa-|doona|ẓaalika|limañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wa-mañy|yushrik|billaahi|faq̣adif|taraaa|ʹis̤man|ʻa-Z̤̣eemaa."
4,49,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|yuzakkoona|ʹañfusahum?|Balil|laahu|yuzakkee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-laa|yuz̤̣lamoona|fateela."
4,50,"ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|yaftaroona|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓib!|wa-kafaa|biheee|ʹiṣmam|mubeenaa!"
4,51,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|ʹootoo|naṣeebam|minal|Kitaabi|yuʹminoona|bil-Jibti|waṭ-Ṭaag̣ooti|wa-yaq̣ooloona|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹahdaa|minal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|sabeelaa?"
4,52,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|laʻanahumul|laah:|wa-mañy|yalʻanil|laahu|falañ|tajida|lahoo|naṣeeraa."
4,53,"ʹAm|lahum|naṣeebum|minal|mulki|faʹiẓal|laa|yuʹtoonan|naasa|naq̣eeraa?"
4,54,"ʹAm|yaḥsudoonan|naasa|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹaataahumul|laahu|miñ|faḍlih?|Faq̣ad|ʹaataynaaa|ʹAala|ʹIbraaheemal|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|wa-ʹaataynaahum|mulkan|ʻa-Z̤̣eemaa."
4,55,"Faminhum|man|ʹaamana|bihee|wa-minhum|mañ|ṣadda|ʻanh:|wa-kafaa|bi-Jahannama|saʻeeraa."
4,56,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|biʹAayaatinaa|sawfa|nuṣleehim|Naaraa.|kullamaa|naḍijat|julooduhum|baddalnaahum|juloodan|g̣ayrahaa|liyaẓooq̣ul|ʻaẓaab:|ʹinnal|laha|kaana|ʻAzeezan|Ḥakeemaa."
4,57,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|sanudkhiluhum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa:|lahum|feehaaa|ʹazwaajum|muṭahharah:|wa-nudkhiluhum|z̤̣illañ|z̤̣aleelaa."
4,58,"ʹInnal|laaha|yaʹmurukum|ʹañ|tuʹaddul|ʹamaanaati|ʹilaaa|ʹahlihaa|wa-ʹiẓaa|ḥakamtum̃|baynan|naasi|ʹañ|taḥkumoo|bil-ʻadl!|ʹInnal|laaha|niʻimmaa|yaʻiz̤̣ukum̃|bih!|ʹInnal|laaha|kaana|Sameeʻam|Baṣeeraa."
4,59,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻur|Rasoola|wa-ʹulil|ʹamri|miñkum.|Faʹiñ|tanaazaʻtum|fee|shayʹiñ|faruddoohu|ʹilal|laahi|war-Rasooli|ʹiñ|kuntum|tuʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Ẓaalika|khayruñw|waʹaḥsanu|taʹweelaa."
4,60,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|yazʻumoona|ʹannahum|aamanoo|bimaaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|miñ|q̣ablika|yureedoona|ʹañy|yataḥaakamooo|ʹilaṭ|Ṭaag̣ooti|wa-q̣ad|ʹumirooo|ʹañy|yakfuroo|bih.|Wayureedush|Shayṭaanu|ʹañy|yuḍillahum|ḍalaalam|baʻeedaa."
4,61,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|taʻaalaw|ʹilaa|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|wa-ʹilar|Rasooli|raʹaytal|Munaafiq̣eena|yaṣuddoona|ʻañka|ṣudoodaa."
4,62,"Fakayfa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaṣaabathum|muṣeebatum|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeehim|s̤umma|jaaaʹooka|yaḥlifoona|billaahi|ʹin|ʹaradnaaa|ʹillaaa|iḥsaanañw|watawfeeq̣aa!"
4,63,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|yaʻla|mullaahu|maa-|fee|q̣uloobihim|faʹaʻriḍ|ʻanhum|wa-ʻiẓhum|wa-q̣ul|lahum|feee|ʹañfusihim|q̣awlam|baleeg̣aa."
4,64,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|mir|Rasoolin|ʹillaa|liyuṭaaʻa|biʹIẓnil|laah.|Wa-law|ʹannahum|ʹiz̤̣|z̤̣alamooo|ʹañfusahum|jaaaʹooka|fastag̣farul|laaha|wastag̣fara|lahumur|Rasoolu|lawajadul|laaha|Tawwaabar|Raḥeemaa."
4,65,"Falaa|Wa-Rabbika|laa-|yuʹminoona|ḥattaa|yuḥakkimooka|fee-ma|shajara|baynahum|s̤umma|laa-|yajidoo|feee|ʹañfusihim|ḥarajam|mimmaa|q̣aḍayta|wa-yusal-limoo|tasleemaa."
4,66,"Wa-law|ʹannaa|katabnaa|ʻalayhim|ʹaniq̣|tulooo|ʹanfusakum|ʹawikh|rujoo|miñ|diyarikum|maa|faʻaloohu|ʹillaa|q̣aleelum|minhum:|wa-law|ʹannahum|faʻaloo|maa-|yooʻaz̤̣oona|bihee|lakaana|khayral|lahum|wa-ʹashadda|tas̤beetaa;"
4,67,"Wa-ʹiẓal|laʹaataynaahum|mil|ladunnaaa|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa;"
4,68,"Wa-la-hadynaahum|Ṣiraaṭam|Mustaq̣eema."
4,69,"Wa-mañy|yuṭiʻil|laaha|war-Rasoola|faʹulaaaʹika|maʻal|laẓeena|ʹanʻamal|laahu|ʻalayhim|minan|Nabiyeena|waṣ-Ṣiddeeq̣eena|wash-Shuhadaaaʹi|waṣ-Ṣaaliḥeen:|waḥasuna|ʹulaaʹika|Rafeeq̣aa."
4,70,"Ẓaalikal|Faḍlu|minal|laah:|wa-kafaa|billaahi|ʻAleemaa."
4,71,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|khuẓoo|ḥiẓrakum|fañfiroo|s̤ubaatin|ʹawiñ|firoo|jameeʻaa."
4,72,"Wa-ʹinna|miñkum|lamal|layubaṭṭiʹann:|faʹin|ʹaṣaabatkum|muṣeebatuñ|q̣aala|q̣ad|ʹanʻamal|laahu|ʻalayya|ʹiẓ|lam|ʹakum|maʻahum|shaheedaa."
4,73,"Wa-laʹin|ʹaṣaabakum|faḍlum|minal|laahi|layaq̣oolanna|kaʹal|lam|takum|baynakum|wabaynahoo|mawaddatuñy|yaa-laytanee|kuñtu|maʻahum|faʹafooza|fawzan|ʻa-Z̤̣eemaa!"
4,74,"Falyuq̣aatil|fee|Sabeelil|laahil|laẓeena|yashroonal|ḥayaatad|dunyaa|bil-ʹAakhirah.|Wa-mañy|yuq̣aatil|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|fayuq̣tal|ʹaw|yag̣lib|fasawfa|nuʹteehi|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
4,75,"Wa-maa|lakum|laa-|tuq̣aatiloona|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|walmustaḍʻafeena|minar|rijaali|wan-Nisaaaʹi|walwildaanil|laẓeena|yaq̣ooloona|Rabbanaaa|ʹakhrijnaa|min|haaẓihil|q̣aryatiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimi|ʹahluhaa;|wajʻal|lanaa|mil|laduñka|waliyyañw|wajʻal|lanaa|mil|laduñka|naṣeeraa!"
4,76,"Allaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|yuq̣aatiloona|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wallaẓeena|kafaroo|yuq̣aatiloona|fee|Sabeeliṭ|Ṭaag̣ooti|faq̣aatilooo|ʹawliyaaʹash|Shayṭaan:|ʹinna|kaydash|Shayṭaani|kaana|ḍaʻeefaa."
4,77,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|q̣eela|lahum|kuffooo|ʻaydiyakum|wa-ʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaah?|Falammaa|kutiba|ʻalayhimul|q̣italu|ʹiẓaa|fareeq̣um|minhum|yakhshawnan|naasa|kakhashyatil|laahi|ʹaw|ʹashadda|khashyah:|wa-q̣aaloo|Rabbana|lima|katabta|ʻalaynal|q̣itaal?|Law- laaa|ʹakhkhartanaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹajaliñ|q̣areeb?|Q̣ul|mataaʻud|dunyaa|q̣aleel:|wal-ʹAakhiratu|khayrul|limanit|taq̣aa:|wa-laa|tuz̤̣lamoona|fateelaa."
4,78,"ʹAynamaa|takoonoo|yudrikkumul|mawtu|walaw|kuñtum|fee|buroojim|mushayyadah.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuṣibhum|ḥasanatuñy|yaq̣ooloo|haaẓihee|min|ʻiñdil|laah;|wa-ʹiñ|tuṣibhum|sayyiʹatuñy|yaq̣ooloo|haaẓihee|min|ʻiñdik.|Q̣ul|kullum|min|ʻiñdil|laah.|Famaali|haaaʹulaaaʹil|q̣awmi|laa-|yakaadoona|yafq̣ahoona|ḥadees̤aa?"
4,79,"Maaa|ʹaṣaabaka|min|ḥasanatiñ|faminal|laah;|wa-maaa|ʹaṣaabaka|miñ|sayyiʹatiñ|famin|nafsik|Wa-ʹarsalnaaka|linnaasi|Rasoolaa.|Wa-kafaa|billaahi|Shaheedaa."
4,80,"Mañy|yuṭiʻir|Rasoola|faq̣ad|ʹaṭaaʻal|laah:|wa-mañ|tawallaa|famaaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʻalayhim|ḥafeez̤̣aa."
4,81,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|Ṭaaʻatun|faʹiẓaa|barazoo|min|ʻiñdika|bayyata|ṭaaaʹifatum|minhum|g̣ayral|laẓee|taq̣ool.|Wallaahu|yaktubu|maa-|yubayyitoon;|faʹaʻriḍ|ʻanhum|wa-tawakkal|ʻalal|lah:|wa-kafaa|billaahi|Wakeelaa."
4,82,"ʹAfalaa|yatadabbaroonal|Q̣urʹaan?|Wa-law|kaana|min|ʻiñdi|g̣ayril|laahi|lawajadoo|fee-hikh|tilaafañ|kas̤eeraa"
4,83,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹahum|ʹamrum|minal|ʹamni|ʹawil|khawfi|ʹaẓaaʻoo|bih.|Wa-law|raddoohu|ʹilar|rasooli|wa-ʹilaaa|ʹulil|ʹamri|minhum|laʻalimahul|laẓeena|yastambiṭoonahoo|minhum.|Wa-lawlaa|Faḍlul|laahi|ʻalaykum|wa-Raḥmatuhoo|lattabaʻtumush|Shayṭaana|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa."
4,84,"Faq̣aatil|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|laa-|tukallafu|ʹillaa|nafsaka|waḥarriḍil|Muʹmineen.|ʻAsal|laahu|ʹañy|yakuffa|baʹsal|laẓeena|kafaroo:|wallaahu|ʹashaddu|baʹsañw|waʹashaddu|tañkeelaa."
4,85,"Mañy|yashfaʻ|shafaaʻatan|ḥasanatañy|yakul|lahoo|naṣeebum|minhaa;|wa-mañy|yashfaʻ|shafaaʻatañ|sayyiʹatañy|yakul|lahoo|kiflum|minhaa:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹim|Muq̣eetaa."
4,86,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ḥuyyeetum̃|bitaḥiyatiñ|faḥayyoo|biʹaḥsana|minhaaa|ʹaw|ruddoohaa.|ʹInnal|laaha|kaana|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹin|Ḥas̤eebaa."
4,87,"ʹAllaahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|huwa|layajmaʻannakum|ʹilaa|yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|laa-|rayba|feeh.|Wa-man|ʹaṣdaq̣u|minal|laahi|ḥadees̤aa?"
4,88,"Famaa|lakum|fil|Munaafiq̣eena|fiʹatayni|wallaahu|ʹarkasahum̃|bimaa|kasaboo?|ʹAtureedoona|ʹañ|tahdoo|man|ʹaḍallal|laah?|Wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|falañ|tajida|lahoo|Sabeelaa."
4,89,"Waddoo|law|takfuroona|kamaa|kafaroo|fatakoonoona|sawaaaʹa;|falaa|tattakhiẓoo|minhum|ʹawliyaaaʹa|ḥattaa|yuhaajiroo|fee|sabeelil|laah;|faʹiñ|tawallaw|fakhuẓoohum|waq̣tuloohum|ḥays̤u|wajattumoohum;|wa-laa|tattakhiẓoo|minhum|waliyyañw|walaa|naṣeeraa:"
4,90,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|yaṣiloona|ʹilaa|q̣awmim|baynakum|wa-baynahum|mees̤aaq̣un|ʹaw|jaaaʹookum|ḥaṣirat|ṣudooruhum|ʹañy|yuq̣aatilookum|ʹaw|yuq̣aatiloo|q̣awmahum.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|lasallaṭahum|ʹalaykum|falaq̣aatalookum|Faʹiniʻ|tazalookum|falam|yuq̣aatilookum|wa-ʹalq̣aw|ʹilaykumus|salama|famaa|jaʻalal|laahu|lakum|ʻalayhim|sabeelaa."
4,91,"Satajidoona|ʹaakhareena|yureedoona|ʹañy|yaʹmanookum|wa-yaʹmanoo|q̣awmahum:|kulla|maa-|ruddooo|ʹilal|fitnati|ʹurkisoo|feehaa:|faʹil|lam|yaʻtazilookum|wa-yulq̣ooo|ʹilaykumus|salama|wa-yakuffooo|ʹaydiyahum|fakhuẓoohum|waq̣tuloohum|ḥays̤u|s̤aq̣iftumoohum:|wa-ʹulaaaʹikum|jaʻalnaa|lakum|ʻalayhim|sulṭaanam|mubeenaa."
4,92,"Wa-maa|kaana|limuʹminin|ʹañy|yaq̣tula|Muʹminan|ʹillaa|khaṭaʹaa.|Wa-mañ|q̣atala|Muʹminan|khaṭaʹañ|fataḥreeru|raq̣abatim|Muʹminatiñw|wadiyatum|musallamatun|ʹilaaa|ʹahliheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yaṣṣaddaq̣oo.|Faʹiñ|kaana|miñ|q̣awmin|ʻaduwwil|lakum|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|fataḥreeru|raq̣abatim|Muʹminah.|Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|miñ|q̣awmim|baynakum|wa-baynahum|mees̤aaq̣uñ|fadiyatum|musallamatun|ʹilaaa|ʹahlihee|wa-taḥreeru|raq̣abatim|Muʹminah.|Famal|lam|yajid|fa-Ṣiyaamu|Shahrayni|mutataabiʻayn:|tawbatam|minal|laah:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻaleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,93,"Wa-mañy|yaq̣tul|Muʹminam|mutaʻammidañ|fajazaaaʹuhoo|Jahannamu|khaalidañ|feehaa|wa-g̣aḍibal|laahu|ʻalayhi|wa-laʻanahoo|wa-ʹaʻadda|lahoo|ʻaẓaaban|ʻa-Z̤̣eemaa."
4,94,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|ḍarabtum|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|fatabayyanoo|wa-laa|taq̣ooloo|liman|ʹalq̣aaa|ʹilaykumus|salaama|lasta|Muʹminaa!|tabtag̣oona|ʻaraḍal|ḥayaatid|dunyaa:|faʻiñdal|laahi|mag̣aanimu|kas̤eerah.|Kaẓaalika|kuñtum|miñ|q̣ablu|famannal|laahu|ʻalaykum|fatabayyanoo.|ʹInnal|laaha|kaana|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeeraa."
4,95,"Laa-|yastawil|q̣aaʻidoona|minal|Muʹmineena|g̣ayru|ʹuliḍ|ḍarari|wal-Mujaahidoona|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim.|Faḍḍalal|laahul|Mujaahideena|biamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim|ʻalal|q̣aaʻideena|darajah|wa-kullañw|waʻdal|laahul|ḥusnaa:|wa-faḍḍalal|laahul|Mujaahideena|ʻalal|q̣aaʻideena|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa;―"
4,96,"Darajaatim|minhu|wa-mag̣firatañw|waraḥmah.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
4,97,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|tawaffaahumul|malaaaʹikatu|z̤̣aalimeee|ʹañfusihim|q̣aaloo|feema|kuñtum:|Q̣aaloo|kunnaa|mustaḍʻafeena|fil|ʹarḍ.|Q̣aalooo|ʹalam|takun|ʹarḍul|laahi|waasiʻatañ|fatuhaajiroo|feehaa?|Faʹulaaaika|maʹwaahum|Jahannam,|Wasaaaʹat|maṣeeraa:"
4,98,"ʹIllal|mustaḍʻafeena|minar|rijaali|wannisaaaʹi|walwildaani|laa-|yastaṭeeʻoona|ḥeelatañw|walaa|yahtadoona|sabeelaa."
4,99,"Faʹulaaaʹika|ʻasal|laahu|ʹañy|yaʻfuwa|ʻanhum:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAfuwwan|G̣afooraa."
4,100,"Wa-mañy|yuhaajir|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|yajid|fil|ʹarḍi|muraag̣amañ|kas̤eerañw|wasaʻah.|wa-mañy|yakhruj|mim|baytihee|muhaajiran|ʹilal|laahi|wa-Rasoolihee|s̤umma|yudrikhul|mawtu|faq̣ad|waq̣aʻa|ajruhoo|ʻalal|laah:|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
4,101,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ḍarabtum|fil|ʹarḍi|fallaysa|ʻalaykum|junaaḥun|ʹañ|taq̣ṣuroo|minaṣ|Ṣalaati|ʹin|khiftum|ʹañy|yaftinakumul|laẓeena|kafaroo:|ʹinnal|kaafireena|kaanoo|lakum|ʻaduwwam|mubeenaa."
4,102,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|kuñta|feehim|faʹaq̣amta|lahumuṣ|Ṣalaata|faltaq̣um|ṭaaaʹifatum|minhum|maʻaka|wal-yaʹkhuẓooo|ʹasliḥatahum:|faʹiẓaa|sajadoo|fal-yakoonoo|miñw|waraaaʹikum.|Wal-taʹti|ṭaaaʹifatun|ʹukhraa|lam|yuṣalloo|falyuṣalloo|maʻaka|wal-yaʹkhuẓoo|ḥiẓrahum|wa-ʹasliḥatahum.|Waddal|laẓeena|kafaroo|law|tag̣fuloona|ʻan|ʹasliḥatikum|wa-ʹamtiʻatikum|fayameeloona|ʻalaykum|maylatañw|waaḥidah.|Wa-laa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|ʹiñ|kaana|bikum|ʹaẓam|mim|maṭarin|ʹaw|kuñtum|marḍaaa|ʹañ|taḍaʻooo|ʹasliḥatakum:|wa-khuẓoo|ḥiẓrakum.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʹaʻadda|lilkaafireena|ʻaẓaabam|muheenaa."
4,103,"Faʹiẓaa|q̣aḍaytumuṣ|Ṣalaata|faẓkurul|laaha|q̣iyaamañw|waq̣uʻoodañw|waʻalaa|junoobikum.|Faʹiẓaṭ|maʹnañtum|faʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaah:|ʹinnaṣ|Ṣalaata|kanat|ʻalal|Muʹmineena|kitaabam|mawq̣ootaa."
4,104,"Wa-laa|tahinoo|fib|tig̣aaaʹil|q̣awm|ʹIñ|takoonoo|taʹlamoona|faʹinnahum|yaʹlamoona|kamaa|taʹlamoon;|wa-tarjoona|minal|laahi|maa|laa-|yar-joon.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,105,"ʹInnaaa|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykal|Kitaaba|bilḥaq̣q̣i|litaḥkuma|baynan|naasi|bimaaa|ʹaraakal|laah:|Wa-laa|takul|lilkhaaaʹineena|khaṣeemaa;"
4,106,"Wastag̣firil|laah;|innal|laaha|kaana|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
4,107,"Wa-laa|tujaadil|ʻanil|laẓeena|yakhtaanoona|ʹañfusahum:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibboo|mañ|kaana|khawwaanan|ʹas̤eemaa;"
4,108,"Yastakhfoona|minan|naasi|wa-laa|yastakhfoona|minal|laahi|wa-Huwa|maʻahum|ʹiẓ|yubayyitoona|maa|laa-|yarḍaa|minal|q̣awl:|wa-kaanal|laahu|bimaa|yaʻmaloona|Muḥeeṭaa."
4,109,"Haaaʹañtum|haaaʹulaaaʹi|jaadaltum|ʻanhum|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa.|Famañy|yujaadilul|laaha|ʻanhum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʹam|mañy|yakoonu|ʻalayhim|wakeelaa?"
4,110,"Wa-mañy|yaʻmal|soooʹan|ʹaw|yaz̤̣lim|nafsahoo|s̤umma|yastag̣firil|laaha|yajidil|laaha|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
4,111,"Wa-mañy|yaksib|is̤mañ|faʹinnamaa|yaksibuhoo|ʻalaa|nafsih:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,112,"Wa-mañy|yaksib|khaṭeeeʹatan|ʹaw|ʹis̤mañ|s̤ummaa|yarmi|bihee|bareeeʹañ|faq̣adiḥ|tamala|buhtaanañw|waʹis̤mam|mubeenaa."
4,113,"Wa-lawlaa|faḍlul|laahi|ʻalayka|wa-Raḥmatuhoo|lahammaṭ|ṭaaaʹifatum|minhum|ʹañy|yuḍillook.|Wa-maa|yuḍilloona|ʹillaaa|ʹañfusahum;|wa-maa|yaḍurroonaka|miñ|shayʹ.|Wa-ʹañzalal|laahu|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|waʻallamaka|maa-|lam|takuñ|taʻlam:|wa-kaana|faḍlul|laahi|ʻalayka|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
4,114,"Laa-|khayra|fee|kas̤eerim|min|najwaahum|ʹillaa|man|ʹamara|biṣadaq̣atin|ʹaw|maʻroofin|ʹaw|ʹiṣlaahim|baynan|naas.|Wa-mañy|yafʻal|ẓaalikab|tig̣aaaʹa|marḍaatil|laahi|fasawfa|nuʹteehi|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
4,115,"Wa-mañy|yushaaq̣iq̣ir|Rasoola|mim|baʹdi|maa-|tabayyana|lahul|hudaa|wa-yattabiʻ|g̣ayra|sabeelil|Muʹmineena|nuwallihee|maa-|tawallaa|wa-nuṣlihee|Jahannam:|wa-saaaʹat|maṣeeraa!"
4,116,"ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yag̣firu|ʹañy|yushraka|bihee|wayag̣firu|maa-|doona|ẓaalika|limañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wa-mañy|yushrik|billaahi|faq̣ad|ḍalla|ḍalaalam|baʻeedaa."
4,117,"ʹIñy|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|ʹillaaa|ʹinaas̤aa:|wa-ʹiñy|yadʻoona|ʹillaa|Shayṭaanam|mareedaa."
4,118,"Laʻanahul|laah.|Wa-q̣aala|laʹattakhiẓanna|min|ʻibaadika|naṣeebam|mafrooḍaa;"
4,119,"Wa-laʹuḍillannahum|wa-laʹumanni-yannahum|wa-la-aamurannahum|falayubattikunna|ʹaaẓaanal|ʹanʻaami|wa-laʹaamurannahum|falayug̣ayeerunna|khalq̣al|laah.|Wa-mañy|yattakhiẓish|Shayṭaana|waliyyam|miñ|doonil|laahi|faq̣ad|khasira|khusraanam|mubeenaa."
4,120,"Yaʻiduhum|wa-yuman-neehim;|wa-maa|yaʻiduhumush|Shayṭaanu|ʹillaa|g̣urooraa."
4,121,"ʹUlaaaʹika|maʹwaahum|jahannamu|wa-laa|yajidoona|ʻanhaa|maḥeeṣaa."
4,122,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaalihaati|sanudkhiluhum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|fihaaa|ʹabadaa.|Waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣aa:|wa-man|ʹaṣdaq̣u|minal|laahi|q̣eelaa?"
4,123,"Laysa|biʹamaaniyyikum|wa-laaa|ʹamaaniyyi|ʹAhlil|Kitaab.|Mañy|yaʻmal|soooʹañy|yujza|bihee|wa-laa|yajid|lahoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|waliyyañw|walaa|naṣeeraa."
4,124,"Wa-mañy|yaʻmal|minaṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|miñ|ẓakarin|ʹaw|ʹuñs̤aa|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|faʹulaaaʹika|yadkhuloonal|jannata|wa-laa|yuz̤̣lamoona|naq̣eeraa."
4,125,"wa-man|ʹaḥsanu|deenam|mimman|ʹaslama|wajhahoo|lillaahi|wa-huwa|Muḥsinuñw|wattabaʻa|Millata|ʹIbraaheema|Ḥaneefaa?|Wattakhaẓal|laahu|ʹIbraaheema|khaleelaa."
4,126,"Walillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-kaanal|laahu|bikulli|shayʹim|Muḥeeṭaa."
4,127,"Wa-yastaftoonaka|fin|nisaaaʹ.|Q̣ulil|laahu|yufteekum|feehinna|wa-maa|yutlaa|ʻalaykum|fil|Kitaabi|fee|yataaman|Nisaaaʹil|laatee|laa-|tuʹtoonahunna|maa-|kutiba|lahunna|wa-targ̣aboona|ʹañ|tañkiḥoohunna|wal-mustaḍʻa-feena|minal|wildaani|wa-ʹañ|taq̣oomoo|lilyataamaa|bilq̣isṭ.|Wa-maa|tafʻaloo|min|khayriñ|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|bihee|ʻAleemaa."
4,128,"Wa-ʹinim|raʹatun|khaafat|mim|baʻlihaa|nushoozan|ʹaw|ʹiʻraaḍañ|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalayhimaaa|ʹañy|yuṣliḥaa|baynahumaa|ṣulḥaa|waṣ-Ṣulhu|khayr;|wa-ʹuḥḍiratil|ʹañfusush|shuḥḥ.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuḥsinoo|wa-tattaq̣oo|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeeraa."
4,129,"Wa-lañ|tastaṭeeʻooo|ʹañ|taʻdiloo|baynan|Nisaaaʹi|wa-law|ḥaraṣtum|falaa|tameeloo|kullal|mayli|fataẓaroohaa|kalmuʻal-laq̣ah.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuṣliḥoo|wa-tattaq̣oo|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
4,130,"Wa-ʹiñy|yatafarraq̣aa|yug̣nil|laahu|kullam|miñ|saʻatih:|wa-kaanal|laahu|Waasiʻan|Ḥakeemaa."
4,131,"Walillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Wa-laq̣ad|waṣṣaynal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablikum|wa-ʹiyyaakum|ʹanit|taq̣ul|laah.|Wa-ʹin|takfuroo|faʹinna|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ;|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣aniyyan|Ḥameedaa."
4,132,"Walillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wakafaa|billaahi|Wakeelaa."
4,133,"ʹIñy|yashaʹ|yuẓhibkum|ʹay-yuhan|naasu|wa-yaʹti|biʹaakhareen;|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻalaa|ẓaalika|Q̣adeeraa."
4,134,"Mañ|kaana|yureedu|s̤awaabad|dunyaa|faʻiñdal|laahi|s̤awaabud|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah:|wa-kaanal|laahu|Sameeʻam|Baṣeeraa."
4,135,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|koonoo|q̣awwaameena|bilq̣isṭi|shuhadaaaʹa|lillaahi|wa-law|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusikum|ʹawil|waalidayni|wal-ʹaq̣rabeen,|ʹiñy|yakun|g̣aniyyan|ʹaw|faq̣eeran|fallaahu|awlaa|bihimaa.|Falaa|tattabiʻul|hawaaa|ʹañ|taʻdiloo.|wa-ʹiñ|talwooo|ʹaw|tuʻriḍoo|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeeraa."
4,136,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹaaminoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wal-Kitaabil|laẓee|nazzala|ʻalaa|Rasoolihee|wal-Kitaabil|laẓeee|ʹañzala|miñ|q̣abl.|Wa-mañy|yakfur|billaahi|wa-malaaaʹikatihee|wa-Kutubihee|wa-Rusulihee|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|faq̣ad|ḍalla|ḍalaalam|baʹeedaa."
4,137,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|s̤umma|kafaroo|s̤umma|ʹaamanoo|s̤umma|kafaroo|s̤ummaz|daadoo|kufral|lam|yakunil|laahu|liyag̣fira|lahum|wa-laa|liyahdiyahum|Sabeelaa."
4,138,"Bashshiril|Munaafiq̣eena|biʹanna|lahum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa;―"
4,139,"ʹAllaẓeena|yattakhiẓoonal|kaafireena|ʹawliyaaaʹa|miñ|doonil|Muʹmineen:|ʹa-yabtag̣oona|ʻiñdahumul|ʻizzata|faʹinnal|ʻizzata|lillaahi|jameeʻaa?"
4,140,"Wa-q̣ad|nazzala|ʻalaykum|fil|Kitaabi|ʹan|ʹiẓaa|samiʻtum|ʹAayaatil|laahi|yukfaru|bihaa|wa-yustahzaʹu|bihaa|falaa|taq̣ʻudoo|maʻahum|ḥattaa|yakhooḍoo|fee|ḥadees̤in|g̣ayrih.|Innakum|ʹiẓam|mis̤luhum.|ʹInnal|laha|jaamiʻul|Munaafiq̣eena|wal-kaafireena|fee|jahannama|jameeʻaa;―"
4,141,"ʹAllaẓeena|yatarabbaṣoona|bikum:|faʹiñ|kaana|lakum|fatḥum|minal|laahi|q̣aalooo|ʹalam|nakum|maʻakum?|Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|lilkaafireena|naṣeebuñ|q̣aalooo|ʹalam|nastaḥwiẓ|ʻalaykum|wa-namnaʻkum|minal|Muʹmineen?|Fallaahu|yaḥkumu|baynakum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|Wa-lañy|yajʻalal|laahu|lilkaafireena|ʻalal|Muʹmineena|sabeelaa."
4,142,"ʹInnal|Munaafiq̣eena|yukhaadiʻoonal|laaha|wa-Huwa|khaadiʻuhum.|Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣aamooo|ʹilaṣ|Ṣalaati|q̣aamoo|kusaalaa|yuraaaʹoonan|naasa|wa-laa|yaẓkuroonal|laaha|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa;"
4,143,"Muẓabẓabeena|bayna|ẓaalika,|Laaa|ʹilaa|haaaʹulaaaʹi|wa-laaa|ʹilaa|haaaʹulaaaʹ.|Wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|falañ|tajida|lahoo|Sabeelaa."
4,144,"Yaaaʹayoohal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tattakhiẓul|kaafireena|ʹawliyaaaʹa|miñ|doonil|Muʹmineen.|Atureedoona|ʹañ|tajʻaloo|lillaahi|ʻalaykum|sulṭaanam|mubeenaa?"
4,145,"ʹInnal|Munaafiq̣eena|fid|darkil|ʹasfali|minan|naar:|wa-lan|tajida|lahum|naṣeeraa;"
4,146,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|taaboo|wa-ʹaṣlaḥoo|waʻtaṣamoo|billaahi|wa-ʹakhlaṣoo|deenahum|lillaahi|faʹulaaaʹika|maʻal|Muʹmineen.|Wa-sawfa|yuʹtil|laahul|Muʹmineena|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
4,147,"Maa-|yafʻalul|laahu|biʻaẓaabikum|ʹiñ|shakartum|wa-ʹaamañtum?|Wa-kaanal|laahu|Shaakiran|ʻAleema."
4,148,"Laa-|yuḥibbul|laahul|jahra|bis-sooʹi|minal|q̣awli|ʹillaa|mañ|z̤̣ulim;|wa-kanal|laahu|Sameeʻan|ʻAleemaa."
4,149,"ʹIñ|tubdoo|khayran|ʹaw|tukhfoohu|ʹaw|taʻfoo|ʻañ|soooʹiñ|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAfuwwañ|Q̣adeeraa."
4,150,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yakfuroona|billaahi|wa-rusulihee|wa-yureedoona|ʹañy|yufarriq̣oo|baynal|laahi|wa-Rusulihee|wa-yaq̣ooloona|nuʹminu|bibaʻḍiñw|wanakfuru|bibaʻḍiñw|wayureedoona|ʹañy|yattakhizoo|bayna|ẓaalika|sabeelaa,"
4,151,"ʹUlaaaʹika|humul|kaafiroona|ḥaq̣q̣aa;|wa-ʹaʻtadnaa|lilkaafireena|ʻaẓaabam|muheenaa."
4,152,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|wa-Rusulihee|wa-lam|yufarriq̣oo|bayna|ʹaḥadim|minhum|ʹulaaʹika|sawfa|yuʹteehim|ʹujoorahum:|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
4,153,"Yasʹaluka|ʹAhlul|Kitaabi|añ|tunazzila|ʻalayhim|Kitaabam|minas|samaaaʹi|faq̣ad|saʹaloo|Moosaaa|ʹakbara|miñ|ẓaalika|faq̣aalooo|ʹarinal|laaha|jahratañ|faʹakhaẓathumuṣ|ṣaaʻiq̣atu|biz̤̣ulmihim.|S̤ummat|takhaẓul|ʻijla|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹathumul|Bayyinaatu|faʻafawnaa|ʻañ|ẓaalik:|wa-ʹaataynaa|Moosaa|sulṭaanam|mubeena."
4,154,"Wa-Rafaʻnaa|fawq̣ahumuṭ|Ṭoora|bi-Mis̤aaq̣ihim|wa-q̣ulnaa|lahumud|khulul|abaaba|sujjadañw|waq̣ulnaa|lahum|laa-|taʻdoo|fis|Sabti|wa-ʹakhaẓnaa|minhum|Mees̤aaq̣an|g̣aleez̤̣aa."
4,155,"Fabimaa|naq̣ḍihim|Mees̤aaq̣ahum|wa-kufrihim̃|biʹAayaatil|laahi|wa-q̣atlihimul|ʹambiyaaaʹa|big̣ayri|ḥaq̣q̣iñw|wa-q̣awlihim|q̣uloobunaa|g̣ulf;|bal|ṭabaʻal|laahu|ʻalayhaa|bikufrihim|falaa|yuʹminoona|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa;"
4,156,"Wa-bikufrihim|wa-q̣awlihim|ʻalaa|Maryama|buh-taanan|ʻaz̤̣eemaa;"
4,157,"Wa-q̣awlihim|ʹinnaa|q̣atal-nal|Maseeḥa|ʻEesab|na|Maryama|Rasoolal|laah;―|wa-maa|q̣ataloohu|wa-maa|ṣalaboohu|wa-laakiñ|shubbiha|lahum;|wa-ʹinnal|laẓeenakh|talafoo|feehi|lafee|shakkim|minh:|maa-|lahum̃|bihee|min|ʻilmin|ʹillat|tibaaʻaz̤̣|z̤̣ann;|wa-maa|q̣ataloohu|yaq̣eenaa;―"
4,158,"Bar|rafaʻahul|laahu|ʹilayh:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʹAzeezan|Ḥakeemaa;―"
4,159,"Wa-ʹim|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|ʹillaa|layuʹminanna|bihee|q̣abla|mawtih;|wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|yakoonu|ʻalayhim|shaheedaa;―"
4,160,"Fabiz̤̣ulmim|minal|laẓeena|haadoo|ḥarramnaa|ʻalayhim|ṭayyibaatin|ʹuḥillat|lahum|wa-biṣaddihim|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|kas̤eeraa;―"
4,161,"Wa-ʹakhẓihimur|Ribaa|wa-q̣ad|nuhoo|ʻanhu|wa-ʹaklihim|ʹamwaalan|naasi|bilbaaṭil;―|waʹaʻtadnaa|lilkaafireena|minhum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
4,162,"Laakinir|Raasikhoona|fil|ʻilmi|minhum|wal-Muʹminoona|yuʹminoona|bimaaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|miñ|q̣ablika|walmuq̣eemeenaṣ|Ṣalaata|Walmuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wal-Muʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir:|ʹulaaaʹika|sanuʹteehim|ʹajran|ʻa-Z̤̣eemaa."
4,163,"ʹInnaaa|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|kamaaa|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Nooḥiñw|wan-nabiyyeena|mim|baʻdih;|wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|wal-ʹasbaaṭi|wa-ʻEesaa|wa-ʹayyooba|wa-Yoonusa|wa-Haaroona|wa-Sulaymaan:|wa-ʹaataynaa|Daawooda|Zabooraa."
4,164,"Wa-rusulañ|q̣ad|q̣aṣaṣnaahum|ʻalayka|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-rusulal|lam|naq̣ṣuṣhum|ʻalayk;|wa-kallamal|laahu|Moosaa|takleemaa;"
4,165,"Rusulam|mubashshireena|wa-muñẓireena|liʹallaa|yakoona|linnaasi|ʻalal|laahi|ḥujjatum|baʻdar|rusul;|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAzeezan|Ḥakeemaa."
4,166,"Laakinil|laahu|yashhadu|bimaaa|ʹañzala|ʹilayka|ʹañzalahoo|biʻilmihee|wal-malaaaikatu|yashhadoon:|wa-kafaa|billaahi|Shaheedaa."
4,167,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-saddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|q̣ad|ḍalloo|ḍalaalam|baʻeedaa."
4,168,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|waz̤̣alamoo|lam|yakunil|laahu|liyag̣fira|lahum|wa-laa|liyahdiyahum|ṭareeq̣aa―"
4,169,"ʹIllaa|ṭareeq̣a|jahannama|khaalideena|fihaaa|ʹabadaa.|Wa-kaana|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseeraa."
4,170,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|q̣ad|jaaaʹakumur|Rasoolu|bilḥaq̣q̣i|mir|rabbikum|faʹaaminoo|khayral|lakum.|Wa-ʹiñ|takfuroo|faʹinna|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
4,171,"Yaaaʹahlal|Kitaabi|laa-|tag̣loo|fee|deenikum|wa-laa|taq̣ooloo|ʻalal|laahi|ʹillal|ḥaq̣q̣.|ʹInnamal|Maseeḥu|ʻEesab|nu|Maryama|Rasoolul|laahi|wa-Kalimatuhooo|ʹalq̣aahaaa|ʹilaa|Maryama|wa-rooḥum|minh.|Faʹaaminoo|billaahi|wa-Rusulih.|Wa-laa|taq̣ooloo|S̤alaas̤ah:|ʹiñtahoo|khayral|lakum:|ʹinnamal|laahu|ʹIlaahuñw|waaḥid:|Subḥaanahooo|ʹañy|yakoona|lahoo|walad.|Lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Wa-kafa|billaahi|Wakeela."
4,172,"Lañy|yastañkifal|Maseeḥu|ʹañy|yakoona|ʻAbdal|lillaahi|wa-lal|malaaaʹikatul|muq̣arraboon.|Wa-mañy|yastañkif|ʻan|ʻibaadatihee|wa-yastakbir|fasayaḥshuruhum|ʹilayhi|jameeʻaa."
4,173,"Faʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|fayuwaffeehim|ʹujoorahum|wa-yazeeduhum|miñ|faḍlih;|wa-ʹammal|laẓeenas|tañkafoo|wastakbaroo|fayuʻaẓẓibuhum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa.|Wa-laa|yajidoona|lahum|miñ|doonil|laahi|waliyyañw|walaa|naṣeeraa."
4,174,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhan|naasu|q̣ad|jaaaʹakum|Burhaanum|mir|Rabbikum|wa-ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykum|Nooram|mubeena."
4,175,"Faʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|waʻtaṣamoo|bihee|fasayudkhiluhum|fee|Raḥmatim|minhu|wa-Faḍliñw|wayahdeehim|ʹilayhi|Ṣiraaṭam|Mustaq̣eemaa."
4,176,"Yastaftoonaka|qulil|laahu|yufteekum|fil|Kalaalah.|ʹInim|ruʹun|halaka|laysa|lahoo|waladuñw|walahooo|ʹukhtuñ|falahaa|niṣfu|maa-|tarak:|wa-huwa|yaris̤uhaaa|ʹil|lam|yakul|lahaa|walad.|Faʹiñ|kaanatas̤|natayni|falahumas̤|s̤ulus̤aani|mimmaa|tarak:|wa-ʹiñ|kaanooo|ʹikhwatar|rijaalañw|wa-Nisaaaʹañ|faliẓẓakari|mis̤lu|ḥaz̤̣z̤̣il|ʹuñs̤ayayn.|Yubayyinul|laahu|lakum|ʹañ|taḍilloo.|Wallaahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
5,1,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹawfoo|bilʻuq̣ood.|ʹUḥillat|lakum̃|baheematul|ʹanʻaami|ʹillaa|maa-|yutlaa|ʻalaykum|g̣ayra|muḥilliṣ|ṣaydi|wa-ʹañtum|ḥurum:|ʹinnal|laaha|yaḥkumu|maa-|yureed."
5,2,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tuḥilloo|Shaʻaaaʹiral|laahi|wa-lash|Shahral|Ḥaraama|wa-lal|hadya|wa-lal|q̣alaaʹida|wa-laaa|ʹaaammeenal|Baytal|Ḥaraama|yabtag̣oona|faḍlam|mir|Rabbihim|wa-riḍwaanaa.|Wa-ʹiẓaa|ḥalaltum|faṣṭaadoo.|Wa-laa|yajrimannakum|shanaʹaanu|q̣awmin|ʹañ|ṣaddookum|ʻanil|Masjidil|Ḥaraami|ʹañ|taʻtadoo.|Wa-taʻaawanoo|ʻalal|birri|wattaq̣waa,|wa-laa|taʻaawanoo|ʻalal|ʹis̤mi|walʻudwaan:|wattaq̣ul|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
5,3,"Ḥurrimat|ʻalaykumul|may-tatu|waddamu|wa-laḥmul|khiñzeeri|wa-maaa|ʹuhilla|lig̣ayril|laahi|bihee|walmunkhaniq̣atu|wal-mawq̣ooẓatu|wal-mutarad-diyatu|wan-naṭeeḥatu|wa-maaa|ʹakalas|sabuʻu|ʹillaa|maa-|ẓakkaytum;|wa-maa|ẓubiḥa|ʻalan|nuṣubi|wa-ʹañ|tastaq̣simoo|bil-ʹazlaam:|ẓaalikum|fisq̣.|ʹAlyawma|yaʹisal|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|deenikum|falaa|takhshawhum|wakhshawn.|ʹAlyawma|ʹakmaltu|lakum|Deenakum|wa-ʹatmamtu|ʹalaykum|niʻmatee|wa-raḍeetu|lakumul|ʹISLAAMA|Deenaa.|Famaniḍ|ṭurra|fee|makhmaṣatin|g̣ayra|mutajaanifil|liʹis̤miñ|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
5,4,"Yas-ʹaloonaka|maaẓaaa|ʹuḥilla|lahum.|Q̣ul|ʹuḥilla|lakumuṭ|ṭayyibaatu|wa-maa|ʻallamtum|minal|jawaariḥi|mukal-libeena|tuʻallimoonahunna|mimmaa|ʻallamakumul|laah:|fakuloo|mimmaaa|ʹamsakna|ʻalaykum|waẓkurus|mal|laahi|ʻalayh:|wattaq̣ul|laah;|ʹinnal|laaha|Sareeʻul|Ḥisaab."
5,5,"ʹAlyawma|ʹuḥhilla|lakumuṭ|ṭayyibaat.|Wa-ṭaʻaamul|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|ḥillul|lakum,|wa-ṭaʻaamukum|ḥillul|lahum.|Wal-muḥṣanaatu|minal|muʹminaati|wal-muḥṣanaatu|minal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablikum|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaataytumoohunna|ʹujoorahunna|muḥṣineena|g̣ayra|musaafiḥeena|wa-laa|muttakhiẓeee|ʹakhdaan.|Wa-mañy|yakfur|bil-ʹeemaani|faq̣ad|ḥabiṭa|ʻamaluhoo|wa-huwa|fil|ʹAakhirati|minal|khaasireen."
5,6,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|q̣umtum|ʹilaṣ|Ṣalaati|fag̣siloo|wujoohakum|wa-ʹaydiyakum|ʹilal|maraafiq̣i|wam-saḥoo|biruʹoosikum|wa-ʹarjulakum|ʹilal|kaʻbayn.|Wa-ʹiñ|kuñtum|junubañ|faṭṭahharoo.|Wa-ʹiñ|kuñtum|marḍaaa|ʹaw|ʻalaa|safarin|ʹaw|jaaaʹa|ʹaḥadum|miñkum|minal|g̣aaaʹiṭi|ʹaw|laamastumun|Nisaaaʹa|falam|tajidoo|maaaʹañ|fatayammamoo|ṣaʻeedañ|tayyibañ|famsaḥoo|biwujoohikum|waʹaydeekum|minh.|Maa-|yureedul|laahu|liyajʻala|ʻalaykum|min|ḥarajiñw|walaakiñy|yureedu|liyuṭahhirakum|wa-liyutimma|niʻmatahoo|ʻa|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
5,7,"Waẓkuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|wa-Mees̤aaq̣ahul|laẓee|waas̤aq̣akum̃|biheee|ʹiẓ|q̣ultum|samiʻnaa|wa-ʹaṭaʻ|wattaq̣ul|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|biẓaaṭiṣ|ṣudoor."
5,8,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|koonoo|q̣awwaameena|lillaahi|shuhadaaaʹa|bilq̣isṭi|wa-laa|yajrimannakum|shanaʹaanu|q̣awmin|ʻalaaa|ʹallaa|taʻdiloo.|ʹIʻdiloo:|huwa|ʹaq̣rabu|littaq̣waa:|wattaq̣ul|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
5,9,"Wa-ʻadal|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|lahum|mag̣firatuñw|waʹajrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
5,10,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jaḥeem."
5,11,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanuẓ|kuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓ|hamma|q̣awmun|ʹañy|yabsuṭooo|ʹilaykum|ʹaydiyahum|fakaffa|ʹaydiyahum|ʻañkum:|wattaq̣ul|laah.|Wa-ʻalal|laahi|fal-yatawakkalil|Muʹminoon."
5,12,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹakhaẓal|laahu|Mees̤aaq̣a|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|wa-baʻas̤naa|minhumus̤|na|ʻashara|Naq̣eebaa.|Wa-q̣aalal|laahu|ʹinnee|maʻakum:|laʹin|ʹaq̣amtumuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaataytumuz|Zakaata|wa-ʹaamañtum̃|birusulee|wa-ʻazzartumoohum|wa-ʹaq̣raḍtumul|laaha|Q̣arḍan|Ḥasanal|laʹukaffiranna|ʻañkum|sayyiʹaatikum|wa-laʹudkhilan-nakum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥ-tihal|ʹanhaar;|famañ|kafara|baʻda|ẓaalika|miñkum|faq̣ad|ḍalla|sawaaa|ʹassabeel."
5,13,"Fabimaa|naq̣-ḍihim|Mees̤aaq̣ahum|laʻannaahum|wa-jaʻalnaa|q̣uloobahum|q̣aasiyah.|Yuḥarrifoonal|kalima|ʻamma|waaḍiʻihee|wa-nasoo|ḥaz̤̣z̤̣am|mimmaa|ẓukkiroo|bih.|Wa-laa|tazaalu|taṭṭaliʻu|ʻalaa|khaaaʹinatim|minhum|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|minhum|faʻfu|ʻanhum|waṣfaḥ;|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muḥsineen."
5,14,"Wa-minal|laẓeena|q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|Naṣaaraaa|ʹakhaẓnaa|Mee-s̤aaq̣ahum|fanasoo|ḥaz̤̣z̤̣am|mimmaa|ẓukkiroo|bih:|faʹag̣raynaa|baynahumul|ʻadaawata|wal-bag̣ḍaaaʹa|ilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamah.|Wa-sawfa|yunabbiʹuhumul|laahu|bimaa|kaanoo|yaṣnaʻoon."
5,15,"YaaaʹAhlal|kitaabi|q̣ad|jaaaʹakum|Rasoolunaa|yubayyinu|lakum|kas̤eeram|mimmaa|kuñtum|tukhfoona|minal|Kitaabi|wa-yaʻfoo|ʻañ|kas̤eer.|Q̣ad|jaaaʹakum|minal|laahi|Nooruñw|Wa-Kitaabum|Mubeen,"
5,16,"Yahdee|bihil|laahu|manit|tabaʻa|Riḍwaanahoo|subulas|salaami|Wa-yukhrijuhum|minaz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|noori|biʹiẓnihee|wa-yahdeehim|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
5,17,"Laq̣ad|kafaral|laẓeena|q̣aalooo|ʹinnal|laaha|Huwal|Maseeḥub|nu|Maryam.|Q̣ul|famañy|yamliku|minal|laahi|sahyʹan|ʹin|ʹaraada|ʹañy|yuhlikal|Maseeḥab|na|Maryama|wa-ʹummahoo|wa-mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻaa?|Wa-lillaahi|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa.|Yakhluq̣u|maa-|yashaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
5,18,"Wa-q̣aalatil|Yahoodu|wan-Naṣaaraa|naḥnu|ʹabnaaaʹul|laahi|wa-ʹaḥibbaaaʹuh.|Q̣ul|falima|yuʻaẓẓibukum̃|biẓunoobikum?|Bal|ʹañtum̃|basharum|mimman|khalaq̣:|yag̣firu|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yuʻaẓẓibu|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wa-lillaahi|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa|wa-ʹilayhil|maṣeer."
5,19,"YaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|q̣ad|jaaaʹakum|Rasoolunaa|yubayyinu|lakum|ʻalaa|fatratim|minar|rusuli|ʹañ|taq̣ooloo|maa-|jaaaʹanaa|mim|basheeriñw|walaa|naẓeer:|faq̣ad|jaaaʹakum̃|Basheeruñw|Wa-Naẓeer.|Wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
5,20,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|liq̣awmihee|yaa-q̣awmiẓ|kuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓ|jaʻala|feekum|ʹambiyaaaʹa|wajaʻalakum|mulookañw|wa-ʹaataakum|maa|lam|yuʹti|ʹaḥadam|minal|ʻaalameen."
5,21,"Yaa-q̣awmid|khulul|ʹArḍal|Muq̣addasatal|latee|katabal|laahu|lakum|wa-laa|tartaddoo|ʻalaaa|ʹadbaarikum|fatañq̣aliboo|khaasireen."
5,22,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹinna|feehaa|q̣awmañ|jabbaareena|wa-ʹinnaa|lan|nad-khulahaa|ḥattaa|yakhrujoo|minhaa:|faʹiñy|yakhrujoo|minhaa|faʹinnaa|daa-khiloon."
5,23,"Q̣aala|rajulaani|minal|laẓeena|yakhaafoona|ʹanʻamal|laahu|ʻalayhimad|khuloo|ʻalayhimul|Baab:|faʹiẓaa|dakhal-tumoohu|faʹinnakum|g̣aaliboon.|Wa-ʻalal|laahi|fatawakkalooo|ʻiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
5,24,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹinnaa|lan|nad-khulahaaa|ʹa-badam|maa|daamoo|feehaa|faẓhab|ʹañta|wa-Rabbuka|faq̣aatilaaa|ʹinnaa|haa-hunaa|q̣aaʻidoon."
5,25,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnee|laaa|ʹamliku|ʹillaa|nafsee|wa-ʹakhee|fafruq̣|baynanaa|wa-baynal|q̣awmil|faasiq̣een."
5,26,"Q̣aala|faʹinnahaa|muḥarramatun|ʻalayhim|ʹarbaʻeena|sanah:|yateehoona|fil|ʹarḍ.|Falaa|taʹsa|ʻalal|Q̣awmil|faasiq̣een."
5,27,"Watlu|ʻalayhim|naba|ʹabna|ʹAadama|bilḥaq̣q̣.|ʹIẓ|q̣arrabaa|q̣urbaanañ|fatuq̣ubbila|min|ʹaḥadihimaa|wa-lam|yutaq̣abbal|minal|ʹaakhar.|Q̣aala|laʹaq̣tulannak.|Q̣aala|ʹinnamaa|yataq̣abbalul|laahu|minal|Muttaq̣een."
5,28,"Laʹim|basata|ʹilayya|yadaka|litaq̣tulanee|maaa|ʹana|bibaasiṭiñy|yadiya|ʹilayka|liʹaq̣tulak:|ʹinneee|ʹakhaaful|laaha|Rabbal|ʻAalameen."
5,29,"ʹInneee|ʹureedu|ʹañ|taboooʹa|biʹis̤mee|wa-ʹis̤mika|fatakoona|min|ʹAṣḥaabin|Naar.|Waẓaalika|jazaaaʹuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
5,30,"Faṭawwaʻat|lahoo|nafsuhoo|q̣atla|ʹakheehi|faq̣atalahoo|faʹaṣbaḥa|minal|khaasireen."
5,31,"Fabaʻas̤al|laahu|g̣uraabañy|yab-ḥas̤u|fil|ʹarḍi|liyuriyahoo|kayfa|yuwaaree|sawʹata|ʹakheeh.|Q̣aala|yaa-waylataaa|ʹaʻajaztu|ʹan|ʹakoona|mis̤la|haaẓal|g̣uraabi|faʹuwaariya|saw-ʹata|ʹakhee!|Faʹaṣbaḥa|minan|naadimeen."
5,32,"Min|ʹajli|ẓaalika|katabnaa|ʻalaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʹannahoo|mañ|q̣atala|nafsam|big̣ayri|nafsin|ʹaw|fasaadiñ|fil|ʹarḍi|fakaʹannamaa|q̣atalan|naasa|jameeʻaa:|wa-man|ʹaḥyaahaa|fakaʹannamaaa|ʹaḥyan|naasa|jameeʻaa.|Wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹathum|rusulunaa|bil-Bayyinaati|s̤umma|inna|kas̤eeram|minhum̃|baʹda|ẓaalika|fil|ʹarḍi|lamusrifoon."
5,33,"ʹInnamaa|jazaaaʹul|laẓeena|yuḥaariboonal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wa-yasʻawna|fil|ʹarḍi|fasaadan|ʹañy|yuq̣attalooo|ʹaw|yuṣallabooo|ʹaw|tuq̣aṭṭaʻa|ʹaydeehim|wa-ʹarjuluhum|min|khilaafin|ʹaw|yuñfaw|minal|ʹarḍ.|Ẓaalika|lahum|khizyuñ|fid|dunyaa|wa-lahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem;"
5,34,"ʹlllal|laẓeena|taaboo|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañ|taq̣diroo|ʻalayhim:|faʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
5,35,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|wabtag̣ooo|ʹilayhil|Waseelata|wa-jaahidoo|fee|Sabeelihee|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
5,36,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|law|ʹanna|lahum|maa|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻañw|wamis̤lahoo|maʻahoo|liyaftadoo|bihee|min|ʻaẓaabi|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|maa-|tuq̣ubbila|minhum.|Wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
5,37,"Yureedoona|ʹañy|yakhrujoo|minan|Naari|wa-maa|hum̃|bikhaarijeena|minhaa:|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabum|muq̣eem."
5,38,"Wassaariq̣u|wassaariq̣atu|faq̣ṭaʻooo|ʹaydiyahumaa|jazaaaʹam|bimaa|kasabaa|nakaalam|minal|laah:|wallaahu|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
5,39,"Famañ|taaba|mim|baʻdi|z̤̣ulmihee|wa-ʹaṣlaḥa|faʹinnal|laaha|yatoobu|ʻalayh;|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
5,40,"ʹAlam|taʻlam|ʹannal|laaha|lahoo|mulkus|samaawati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Yuʻaẓẓibu|mañy|yashaaaʹ|wayag̣firu|limañy|yashaaaʹ:|wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
5,41,"Yaaaʹayyuhar|Rasoolu|laa-|yaḥzuñkal|laẓeena|yusaariʻoona|fil|kufri|minal|laẓeena|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|biʹafwaahihim|wa-lam|tuʹmiñ|q̣uloobuhum.|Wa-minal|laẓeena|haadoo|sammaaʻoona|lil-kaẓibi|sammaaʻoona|liq̣awmin|ʹaakhareena|lam|yaʹtook.|Yuḥarrifoonal|kalima|mim|baʻdi|mawaaḍiʻih.|Yaq̣ooloona|ʹin|ʹooteetum|haaẓaa|fakhuẓoohu|wa-ʹil|lam|tuʹtawhu|faḥ-ẓaroo!|Wa-mañy|yuridil|laahu|fitnatahoo|falañ|tamlika|lahoo|minal|laahi|shayʹaa.|ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|lam|yuridil|laahu|ʹañy|yuṭahhira|q̣uloobahum.|Lahum|fid|dunyaa|khizyuñw|walahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem;"
5,42,"Sammaaʻoona|lilkaẓibi|ʹakkaaloona|lis-suḥt.|Faʹiñ|jaaaʹooka|faḥkum̃|baynahum|ʹaw|ʹaʻriḍ|ʻanhum.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuʻriḍ|ʻanhum|falañy|yaḍurrooka|shayaa.|Wa-ʹin|ḥakamta|faḥkum̃|baynahum̃|bilq̣isṭ.|ʹInnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muq̣siṭeen."
5,43,"Wa-kayfa|yuḥakkimoonaka|wa-ʻiñda-humut|Tawraatu|feehaa|ḥukmul|laahi|s̤umma|yatawallawna|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalik?|Wa-maaa|ʹulaaaʹika|bil-Muʹmineen."
5,44,"ʹInnaaa|ʹañzalnat|Tawraata|feehaa|Hudañw|Wa-Noor.|Yaḥkumu|bihan|nabiyyoonal|laẓeena|ʹaslamoo|lillaẓeena|haadoo|war-Rabbaaniyyoona|wal-ʹaḥbaaru|bimas|tuḥfiz̤̣oo|miñ|Kitaabil|laahi|wa-kaanoo|ʻalayhi|shuhadaaaʹ.|Falaa|takhshawun|naasa|wakhshawni|wa-laa|tashtaroo|biʹAayaatee|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelaa.|Wa-mal|lam|yaḥkum̃|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|kaafiroon."
5,45,"wa-katabnaa|ʻalayhim|feehaaa|ʹannan|nafsa|binnafsi|walʻayna|bilʻayni|wal-ʹañfa|bilʹañfi|wal-ʹuẓuna|bil-ʹuẓuni|wassinna|bissinni|waljurooḥa|Q̣iṣaaṣ.|Famañ|taṣaddaq̣a|bihee|fahuwa|kaffaaratul|lah.|Wa-mal|lam|yaḥkum̃|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|faʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
5,46,"Wa-q̣affaynaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihim̃|biʻeesab|ni|Maryama|Muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayhi|minat|Tawraah:|wa-ʹaataynaahul|ʹIñjeela|feehi|Hudañw|Wa-Nooruñw|wamuṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayhi|minat|Tawraati|wa-Hudañw|wa-Mawʻiz̤̣atal|lil-Muttaq̣een."
5,47,"Walyaḥkum|ʹAhlul|ʹIñjeeli|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|feeh.|Wa-mal|lam|yaḥkum̃|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|faʹulaaaika|humul|faasiq̣oon."
5,48,"Wa-ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykal|Kitaaba|bilḥaq̣q̣i|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayhi|minal|Kitabi|wa-muhayminan|ʻalayhi|faḥkum̃|baynahum̃|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|wa-laa|tattabiʻ|ʹahwaaaʹahum|ʻammaa|jaaaʹaka|minal|Ḥaq̣q̣.|Likulliñ|jaʻalnaa|miñkum|Shirʻatañw|Wa-Minhaajaa.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|lajaʻalakum|ʹUmmatañw|Waaḥidatañw|Walaakil|liyabluwakum|fee|maaa|ʹaataakum|fastabiq̣ul|khayraat.|ʹIlal|laahi|marjiʻukum|jameeʻañ|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|feehi|takhtalifoon;"
5,49,"Wa-ʹaniḥ|kum̃|baynahum̃|bimaaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|wa-laa|tattabiʻ|ʹahwaaaʹahum|waḥẓarhum|ʹañy|yaftinooka|ʻam|baʻḍi|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|ʹilayk.|Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faʻlam|ʹannamaa|yureedul|laahu|ʹañy|yuṣeebahum̃|bibaʻḍi|ẓunoobihim.|Wa-ʹinna|kas̤eeram|minan|naasi|lafaasiq̣oon."
5,50,"ʹAfaḥukmal|Jaahiliyyati|yabg̣oon?|Wa-man|ʹaḥsanu|minal|laahi|ḥukmal|liq̣awmiñy|yooq̣inoon."
5,51,"yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tattakhiẓul|Yahooda|wan-Naṣaaraaa|ʹawliyaaaʹ.|Baʻḍuhum|ʹawliyaaaʹu|baʻḍ.|Wa-mañy|yatawallahum|miñkum|faʹinnahoo|minhum.|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
5,52,"Fataral|laẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍuñy|yusaariʻoona|feehim|yaq̣ooloona|nakhshaaa|ʹañ|tuṣeebanaa|daaaʹirah.|Faʻasal|laahu|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|bilfatḥi|ʹaw|ʹamrim|min|ʻiñdihee|fayuṣbiḥoo|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹasarroo|feee|ʹañfusihim|naadimeen."
5,53,"Wa-yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹahaaaʹulaaaʹil|laẓeena|ʹaq̣samoo|billaahi|jahda|ʹaymaanihim|ʹinnahum|lamaʻakum?|Ḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum|faʹaṣbaḥoo|khaasireen."
5,54,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|mañy|yartadda|miñkum|ʻañ|Deenihee|fasawfa|yaʹtil|laahu|biq̣awmiñy|yuḥibbuhum|wa-yuḥibboonahooo|ʹaẓillatin|ʻalal|Muʹmineena|ʹaʻizzatin|ʻalal|Kaafireena,|yujaahidoona|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-laa|yakhaafoona|lawmata|laaaʹim.|Ẓaalika|Faḍlul|laahi|yuʹteehi|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
5,55,"ʹInnamaa|Waliyyukumul|laahu|wa-Rasooluhoo|wal-laẓeena|ʹaamanul|laẓeena|yuq̣eemoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-yuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wa-hum|raakiʻoon."
5,56,"Wa-mañy|yatawallal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|faʹinna|Ḥizbal|laahi|humul|g̣aaliboon."
5,57,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tattakhiẓul|laẓeenat|takhaẓoo|Deenakum|huzuwañw|walaʻibam|minal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablikum|walkuffaara|ʹawliyaaaʹ.|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
5,58,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|naadaytum|ʹilaṣ|Ṣalaatit|takhaẓoohaa|huzuwañw|walaʻibaa;|ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣awmul|laa|yaʻq̣iloon."
5,59,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|hal|tañq̣imoona|minnaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹan|ʹaamannaa|billahi|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaynaa|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-ʹanna|ʹaks̤arakum|faasiq̣oon?"
5,60,"Q̣ul|hal|ʹunabbiʹukum̃|bisharrim|miñ|ẓaalika|mas̤oobatan|ʻiñdal|laah?|Mal|laʻanahul|laahu|wa-g̣aḍiba|ʻalayhi|wa-jaʻala|min-humul|q̣iradata|wal-khanaazeera|wa-ʻabadaṭ|Ṭaag̣oot;|ʹulaaaʹika|sharrum|makaañaw|waʹaḍallu|ʻañ|sawaaaʹis|sabeel!"
5,61,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹookum|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|wa-q̣ad|dakhaloo|bilkufri|wa-hum|q̣ad|kharajoo|bih.|Wallaahu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|kaanoo|yaktumoon."
5,62,"Wa-taraa|kas̤eeram|minhum|yusaariʻoona|fil|ʹis̤mi|walʻudwaani|waʹaklihimus|suḥt;|labiʹsa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon!"
5,63,"Law-laa|yanhaahumur|Rabbaaniyyoona|wal-ʹaḥbaaru|ʻañ|q̣awlihimul|ʹis̤ma|wa-ʹaklihimus|suḥt?|Labiʹsa|maa-|kaanoo|yaṣnaʻoon."
5,64,"Wa-q̣aalatil|Yahoodu|yadul|laahi|mag̣loolah.|G̣ullat|ʹaydeehim|wa-luʻinoo|bimaa|q̣aalu.|Bal|Yadaahu|mabsooṭataani|yuñfiq̣u|kayfa|yashaaaʹ.|Wa-la-yazeedanna|kas̤eeram|minhum|maaa|uñzila|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbika|ṭug̣yaanañw|wakufraa.|Wa-ʹalq̣aynaa|baynahumul|ʻadaawata|wal-bag̣ḍaaaʹa|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamah.|Kullamaaa|ʹawq̣adoo|naaral|lilḥarbi|ʹaṭfaʹahal|laahu|wa-yasʻawna|fil|ʹarḍi|fasaadaa.|Wal-laahu|laa-|yuḥibbul|mufsideen."
5,65,"Wa-law|ʹanna|ʹAhlal|Kitaabi|ʹaamanoo|wattaq̣aw|lakaffarnaa|ʻanhum|sayyiʹaatihim|walaʹadkhalnaahum|Jannaatin|Naʻeem."
5,66,"Wa-law|ʹannahum|ʹaq̣aamut|Tawraata|wal-ʹIñjeela|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayhim|mir|Rabbihim|laʹakaloo|miñ|fawq̣ihim|wa-miñ|taḥti|ʹarjulihim.|Minhum|ʹummatum|muq̣taṣidah:|wa-kas̤eerum|minhum|saaʹa|maa-|yaʻmaloon."
5,67,"Yaaaʹayyuhar|Rasoolu|ballig̣|maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbik.|Wa-ʹil|lam|tafʻal|famaa|ballag̣ta|Risaalatah.|Wallaahu|yaʻṣimuka|minan|naas.|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|Kaafireen."
5,68,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|lastum|ʻalaa|shayʹin|ḥattaa|tuq̣eemut|Tawraata|wal-ʹIñjeela|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaykum|mir|Rabbikum.|Wa-layazeedanna|kas̤eeram|minhum|maaa|uñzila|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbika|ṭug̣yaanañw|wakufraa.|Falaa|taʹsa|ʻalal|Q̣awmil|Kaafireen."
5,69,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wallaẓeena|haadoo|waṣ-Ṣaabiʹoona|wan-Naṣaaraa|man|ʹaamana|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|falaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
5,70,"Laq̣ad|ʹakhaẓnaa|Mees̤aaq̣a|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|wa-ʹarsalnaaa|ʹilayhim|rusulaa.|Kullamaa|jaaʹahum|Rasoolum|bimaa|laa-|tahwaaa|ʹañfusuhum|fareeq̣añ|kaẓẓaboo|wa-fareeq̣añy|yaq̣tuloon."
5,71,"Waḥasibooo|ʹallaa|takoona|fitnatuñ|faʻamoo|waṣammoo|s̤umma|taabal|laahu|ʻalayhim|s̤umma|ʻamoo|waṣammoo|kas̤eerum|minhum.|Wallaahu|Baṣeerum|bimaa|yaʻmaloon."
5,72,"Laq̣ad|kafaral|laẓeena|q̣aalooo|ʹinnal|laaha|Huwal|Maseeḥub|nu|Maryam.|Wa-q̣aalal|Maseeḥu|yaa-baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelaʻ|U’budul|laaha|Rabbee|wa-Rabbakum.|ʹInnahoo|mañy|yushrik|billaahi|faq̣ad|ḥarramal|laahu|ʻalayhil|Jannata|wa-maʹwaahun|Naar.|Wa-maa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|min|ʻañṣaar."
5,73,"Laq̣ad|kafaral|laẓeena|q̣aalooo|ʹinnal|laaha|S̤aaliṣu|S̤alaas̤ah.|Wa-maa|min|ʹilaahin|ʹillaaa|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥid.|Wa-ʹil|lam|yañtahoo|ʻammaa|yaq̣ooloona|layamassannal|laẓeena|kafaroo|minhum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
5,74,"ʹAfalaa|yatooboona|ʹilal|laahi|wa-yastag̣firoonah?|Wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
5,75,"Mal|maseeḥub|nu|maryama|illaa|rasool;|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablihir|rusul.|Wa-ʹummuhoo|S̤iddeeq̣ah.|Kaanaa|yaʹ-kulaaniṭ|ṭaʻaam.|ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|nubayyinu|lahumul|ʹaayaati|s̤ummañ|z̤̣ur|annaa|yuʹfakoon!"
5,76,"Q̣ul|ʹataʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa-|laa-|yamliku|lakum|ḍarrañw|walaa|nafʻaa?|Wallaahu|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
5,77,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹAhlal|Kitaabi|laa-|tag̣loo|fee|Deenikum|g̣ayral|ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laa|tattabiʻooo|ʹahwaaaʹa|q̣awmiñ|q̣ad|ḍalloo|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-ʹaḍalloo|kaseerañw|waḍalloo|ʻañ|sawaaaʹis|sabeel."
5,78,"Luʻinal|laẓeena|kafaroo|mim|baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʻalaa|lisaani|Daawooda|wa-ʻEesab|ni|Maryam:|ẓaalika|bimaa|ʻaṣaw|Wakaanoo|yaʻtadoon."
5,79,"Kaanoo|laa-|yatanaahawna|ʻam|muñkariñ|faʻalooh:|Labiʹsa|maa-|kaanoo|yafʻaloon!"
5,80,"Taraa|kas̤eeram|minhum|yatawallawnal|laẓeena|kafaroo.|Labiʹsa|maa-|q̣addamat|lahum|ʹañfusuhum|ʹañ|sakhiṭal|laahu|ʻalayhim|wa-fil|ʻaẓaabi|hum|khaalidoon."
5,81,"Wa-law|kaanoo|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wan-nabiyyi|wa-maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayhi|mat|takhaẓoohum|ʹawliyaaaʹa|wa-laakinna|kas̤eeram|minhum|faasiq̣oon."
5,82,"Latajidanna|ʹashaddan|naasi|ʻadaawatal|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanul|Yahooda|wallaẓeena|ʹashrakoo:|wa-latajidanna|ʹaq̣rabahum|mawaddatal|lil-laẓeena|ʹaamanul|laẓeena|q̣aalooo|innaa|Naṣaaraa:|ẓaalika|biʹanna|minhum|Q̣isseeseena|Wa-Ruhbaanañw|Waʹannahum|laa-|yastakbiroon."
5,83,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|samiʻoo|maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilar|Rasooli|taraaa|ʹaʻyunahum|tafeeḍu|minad|damʻi|mimmaa|ʻarafoo|minal|ḥaq̣q̣.|Yaq̣ooloona|Rabbanaaa|ʹaamannaa|faktubnaa|maʻash|shaahideen."
5,84,"Wa-maa|lanaa|laa-|nuʹminu|billaahi|wa-maa|jaaaʹanaa|minal|ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-naṭmaʻu|ʹañy|yudkhilanaa|Rabbunaa|maʻal|q̣awmiṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
5,85,"Faʹas̤aabahumul|laahu|bimaa|q̣aaloo|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa.|Waẓaalika|jazaaaʹul|Muḥsineen."
5,86,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹayaatinaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jaḥeem."
5,87,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tuḥarrimoo|ṭayyibaati|maaa|ʹaḥallal|laahu|lakum|wa-laa|taʻtadoo:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbul|muʻtadeen."
5,88,"Wa-kuloo|mimmaa|razaq̣akumul|laahu|ḥalaalañ|ṭayyibaa;|wattaq̣ul|laahal|laẓeee|ʹañtum̃|bihee|Muʹminoon."
5,89,"Laa-|yuʹaakhiẓukumul|laahu|billag̣wi|feee|ʹaymaanikum|wa-laakiñy|yuʹaakhiẓukum̃|bimaa|ʻaq̣q̣attumul|ʹaymaan:|fakaffaaratuhooo|ʹiṭʻaamu|ʻasharati|masaakeena|min|ʹawsaṭi|maa-|tuṭʻimoona|ʹahleekumʹ|aw|kiswatuhumʹ|aw|taḥreeru|raq̣abah.|Famal|lam|yajid|fa-Ṣiyaamu|s̤alaas̤ati|ʹay-yaam.|Ẓaalika|kaffaaratu|ʹaymaanikum|ʹiẓaa|ḥalaftum|Waḥfaz̤̣ooo|ʹaymaanakum.|Kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakum|ʹAayaatihee|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
5,90,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʻaamanoooʹ|innamal|khamru|walmaysiru|wal-ʹañṣaabu|wal-ʹazlaamu|rijsum|min|ʻamalish|shayṭaani|fajtaniboohu|laʻal-lakum|tufliḥoon."
5,91,"ʹInnamaa|yureedush|Shayṭaanu|ʹañy|yooq̣iʻa|baynakumul|ʻadaawata|wal-bag̣ḍaaaʹa|fil|khamri|wal-maysiri|wa-yaṣuddakum|ʻañ|ẓikril|laahi|wa-ʻaniṣ|Ṣalaah:|fahal|ʹañtum|muñtahoon."
5,92,"Wa-ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻur|Rasoola|waḥẓaroo:|faʹiñ|tawal-laytum|faʻlamooo|ʹannamaa|ʻalaa|Rasoolinal|balaag̣ul|mubeen."
5,93,"Laysa|ʻalal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamilus|ṣaaliḥaati|junaaḥuñ|feemaa|ṭaʻimooo|ʹiẓaa|mat|taq̣aw|waʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|s̤ummat|taq̣aw|waʹaamanoo|s̤ummat|taq̣aw|waʹaḥsanoo.|Wallaahu|yuḥibbul|muḥsineen."
5,94,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|layabluwannakumul|laahu|bishayʹim|minaṣ|ṣaydi|tanaaluhooo|ʹaydeekum|wa-rimaaḥukum|liyaʻlamal|laahu|mañy|yakhaafuhoo|bilg̣ayb:|famaniʻ|tadaa|baʻda|ẓaalika|falahoo|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
5,95,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|taq̣tuluṣ|ṣayda|wa-ʹañtum|ḥurum.|Wa-mañ|q̣atalahoo|miñkum|mutaʻammidañ|fajazaaaʹum|mis̤lu|maa-|q̣atala|minan|naʻami|yaḥkumu|bihee|ẓawaa|ʻadlim|miñkum|hadyam|baalig̣al|kaʻbati|ʹaw|kaffaaratuñ|ṭaʻaamu|masaakeena|ʹaw|ʻadlu|ẓaalika|ṣiyaamal|liyaẓooq̣a|wabaala|ʹamrih.|ʻAfal|laahu|ʻammaa|salaf:|wa-man|ʻaada|fayañtaq̣imul|laahu|minh.|Wallaahu|ʻAzeezuñ|Ẓun|tiq̣aam."
5,96,"ʹUḥilla|lakum|ṣaydul|baḥri|waṭaʻaamuhoo|mataaʻal|lakum|wa-lis-sayyaarah;|waḥurrima|ʻalaykum|ṣaydul|barri|maa-|dumtum|ḥurumaa.|Wattaq̣ul|lahal|laẓeee|ʹilayhi|tuḥ-sharoon."
5,97,"Jaʻalal|laahul|Kaʻbatal|Baytal|Ḥaraama|q̣iyaamal|linnaasi|wash-Shahral|Ḥaraama|wal-hadya|wal-q̣alaaaʹid.|Ẓaalika|litaʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹannal|laaha|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
5,98,"ʹIʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aabi|wa-ʹannal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
5,99,"Maa-|ʻalar|rasooli|ʹillal|balaag̣.|Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|tubdoona|wa-maa|taktumoon."
5,100,"Q̣ul|laa|yastawil|khabees̤u|waṭṭayyibu|wa-law|ʹaʻjabaka|kas̤ratul|khabees̤;|fattaq̣ul|laaha|yaaaʹulil|ʹalbaabi|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
5,101,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tasʹaloo|ʻan|ʹashyaaaʹa|iñ|tubda|lakum|tasuʹkum.|Wa-ʹiñ|tasʹaloo|ʻanhaa|ḥeena|yunazzalul|Q̣urʹaanu|tubda|lakum.|ʻAfal|laahu|ʻanhaa;|wallaahu|G̣afoorun|Ḥaleem."
5,102,"Q̣ad|saʹalahaa|q̣awmum|miñ|q̣ablikum|s̤umma|ʹaṣbaḥoo|bihaa|kaafireen."
5,103,"Maa-|jaʻalal|laahu|mim|baḥeeratiñw|walaa|saaaʹibatiñw|walaa|waṣeelatiñw|walaa|ḥaamiñw|walaakinnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|yaftaroona|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓib;|waʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon."
5,104,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|taʻaalaw|ʹilaa|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|wa-ʹilar|Rasooli|q̣aaloo|ḥasbunaa|maa-|wajadnaa|ʻalayhi|ʹaabaaaʹanaa.|ʹA-walaw|kaana|ʹaabaaaʹuhum|laa-|yaʻlamoona|shayʹañw|walaa|vahtadoon?"
5,105,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|ʻalaykum|ʹañfusakum:|laa-|yaḍurrukum|mañ|ḍalla|ʹiẓah|tadaytum.|ʹIlal|laahi|marjiʻukum|jameeʻañ|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
5,106,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|shahaadatu|baynikum|ʹiẓaa|ḥaḍara|ʹaḥadakumul|mawtu|ḥeenal|waṣiyyatis̤|naani|ẓawaa|ʻadlim|miñkum|ʹaw|ʹaakharaani|min|g̣ayrikum|ʹin|ʹañtum|ḍarabtum|fil|ʹarḍi|faʹaṣaabatkum|muṣeebatul|mawt.|Taḥbisoonahumaa|mim|baʻdiṣ|Ṣalaati|fayuq̣simaani|billaahi|ʹinir|tabtum|laa-|nashtaree|bihee|s̤amanañw|wa law|kaana|ẓaa|q̣urbaa|wa-laa|naktumu|shahaadatal|laahi|ʹinnaaa|ʹiẓal|laminal|ʹaas̤imeen."
5,107,"Faʹin|ʻus̤ira|ʻalaaa|ʹannahumas|taḥaq̣q̣aaa|ʹis̤mañ|faʹaakharaani|yaq̣oomaani|maq̣aamahumaa|minal|laẓeenas|taḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhimul|ʹawlayaani|fayuq̣simaani|billaahi|lashahaadatunaaa|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|miñ|shahaadatihimaa|wa-maʻ|tadaynaaa|ʹinnaaa|ʹiẓal|laminaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
5,108,"Ẓaalika|ʹadnaaa|ʹañy|yaʹtoo|bishshahaadati|ʻalaa|wajhihaaa|ʹaw|yakhaafooo|ʹañ|turadda|ʹaymaanum|baʻda|ʹaymaanihim.|Wattaq̣ul|laaha|wasmaʻoo:|wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|faasiq̣een."
5,109,"Yawma|yajmaʻul|laahur|rusula|fayaq̣oolu|maa-ẓaaa|ʹujibtum?|Q̣aaloo|laa-|ʻilma|lanaa:|innaka|ʹAñta|ʻAllaamul|g̣uyoob."
5,110,"ʹIẓ|q̣aalal|laahu|yaa-ʻEesab|na|Maryamaẓ|kur|niʻmatee|ʻalayka|wa-ʻalaa|waalidatik.|ʹIẓ|ʹayyattuka|birooḥil|q̣udus.|Tukallimun|naasa|fil|mahdi|wa-kahlaa.|Wa-ʹiẓ|ʻallamtukal|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmata|wat-Tawraata|wal-ʹIñjeel.|Wa-ʹiẓ|takhluq̣u|minaṭ|ṭeeni|kahayʹatiṭ|ṭayri|biʹiẓnee|fatañfukhu|feehaa|fatakoonu|ṭayram|biʹiẓnee|wa-tubriʹul|ʹakmaha|wal-ʹabraṣa|biʹiẓnee.|Wa-ʹiẓ|tukhrijul|mawtaa|biʹiẓnee.|Wa-ʹiz|kafaftu|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʻañka|ʹiẓ|jiʹtahum̃|bil-bayyinaati|faq̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|minhum|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|siḥrum|mubeen."
5,111,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹawḥaytu|ʹilal|Ḥawaariyyeena|ʹan|ʹaaminoo|bee|wa-bi-Rasoolee:|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|washhad|biʹannanaa|Muslimoon."
5,112,"ʹIẓ|q̣aalal|Ḥawaariyyoona|yaa-ʻEesab|na|Maryama|hal|yastaṭeeʻu|Rabbuka|ʹañy|yunazzila|ʻalaynaa|maaaʹidatam|minas|samaaaʹ?|Q̣aalat|taq̣ul|laaha|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
5,113,"Q̣aaloo|nureedu|ʹan|naʹkula|minhaa|wa-taṭmaʹinna|q̣uloobunaa|wa-naʻlama|ʹañ|q̣ad|ṣadaq̣tanaa|wa-nakoona|ʻalayhaa|minash|shaahideen."
5,114,"Q̣aala|ʻEesab|nu|Maryamal|laahumma|Rabbanaa|ʹañzil|ʻalaynaa|MaaaʹIdatam|minas|Samaaʹi|takoonu|lanaa|ʻeedal|liʹawwalinaa|wa-ʹaakhirinaa|wa-ʹAayatam|miñka|warzuq̣naa|wa-ʹAñta|Khayrur|raaziq̣een."
5,115,"Q̣aalal|laahu|ʹinnee|munazziluha|ʻalaykum.|Famañy|yakfur|baʻdu|miñkum|faʹinneee|ʹuʻaẓẓibuhoo|ʻaẓaabal|laaa|ʹuʻaẓẓibuhooo|ʹaḥadam|minal|ʻaalameen."
5,116,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aalal|laahu|yaa-ʻEesab|na|Maryama|ʹaʹañta|q̣ulta|linnaasit|takhiẓoonee|wa-ʹummiya|ʹilaahayni|miñ|doonil|laah?|Q̣aala|Subḥaanaka|maa|yakoonu|leee|ʹan|ʹaq̣oola|maa-|laysa|lee|biḥaq̣q̣.|ʹIñ|kuñtu|q̣ultuhoo|faq̣ad|ʻalimtah.|Taʻlamu|maa-|fee|nafsee|wa-laaa|ʹaʻlamu|maa-|fee|nafsik.|ʹInnaka|ʹAñta|ʻAllaamul|g̣uyoob."
5,117,"Maa-|q̣ultu|lahum|ʹillaa|maaa|ʹamartanee|biheee|ʹaniʻ|budul|laaha|rabbee|wa-Rabbakum;|wa-kuntu|ʻalayhim|shaheedam|maa|dumtu|feehim.|Falammaa|tawaffaytanee|kuñta|ʹAntar|Raq̣eeba|ʻalayhim:|wa-ʹAñta|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Shaheed."
5,118,"ʹIñ|tuʻaẓẓibhum|faʹinnahum|ʻibaaduk;|wa-ʹiñ|tag̣fir|lahum|faʹinnaka|ʹAñtal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
5,119,"Q̣aalal|laahu|haaẓaa|yawmu|yañfaʻuṣ|Ṣaadiq̣eena|Ṣidq̣uhum;|lahum|jannaatuñ|tajree|miñ|taḥ-tihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa:|Raḍiyal|laahu|ʻanhum|wa-raḍoo|ʻanh:|Ẓaalikal|Fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
5,120,"Lillaahi|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|feehinn:|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
6,1,"ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓee|khalaq̣as|Samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-jaʻalaz̤̣|z̤̣u-lu-maa-ti|wan-Noor.|S̤ummal|laẓeena|kafaroo|bi-Rabbihim|yaʻdiloon."
6,2,"Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|miñ|ṭeeniñ|s̤umma|q̣aḍaaa|ʹajalaa.|Wa-ʹajalum|Musamman|ʻiñdahoo|s̤umma|ʹañtum|tamtaroon!"
6,3,"Wa-Huwal|laahu|fis|samaawaati|wa-fil|ʹarḍ?|Yaʻlamu|sirrakum|wa-jahrakum|wayaʻlamu|maa-|taksiboon."
6,4,"Wa-maa|taʹteehim|min|ʹAayaati|Min|ʹAayatim|Rabbihim|ʹillaa|kaanoo|ʻanhaa|muʻriḍeen."
6,5,"Faq̣ad|kaẓẓaboo|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|lammaa|jaaaʹahum:|fasawfa|yaʹteehim|ʹambaaaʹu|maa-|kaanoo|bihee|yas-tahziʹoon."
6,6,"ʹAlam|yaraw|kam|ʹahlaknaa|miñ|q̣ablihim|miñ|q̣arnim|makkannaahum|fil|ʹarḍi|maa-|lam|numakkil|lakum|wa-ʹarsalnas|samaaaʹa|ʻalayhim|midraaraa,|wa-jaʻalnal|ʹanhaara|tajree|miñ|taḥ-tihim|faʹahlaknaahum|biẓunoobihim|wa-ʹañshaʹnaa|mim|baʻdihim|q̣arnan|ʹaakhareen."
6,7,"Wa-law|nazzalnaa|ʻalayka|Kitaabañ|fee|q̣irṭaasiñ|falamasoohu|biʹaydeehim|laq̣aalal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|siḥrum|mubeen."
6,8,"Wa-q̣aaloo|Laaa-law|ʹuñzila|ʻalayhi|malak?|Wa-law|ʹañzalnaa|malakal|laq̣uḍiyal|ʹamru|s̤umma|laa-|yuñz̤̣aroon."
6,9,"Wa-law|jaʻalnaahu|malakal|lajaʻalnaahu|rajulañw|wa-la-labasnaa|ʻalayhim|maa|yalbisoon."
6,10,"Wa-laq̣adis|tuhziʹa|birusulim|miñ|q̣ablika|faḥaaq̣a|billaẓeena|sakhiroo|minhum|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon."
6,11,"Q̣ul|seeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|s̤ummañ|z̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mukaẓẓibeen."
6,12,"Q̣ul|limam|maa|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Q̣ul|lillaah.|Kataba|ʻalaa|Nafsihir|Raḥmah.|Layajmaʻannakum|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|laa-|rayba|feeh.|ʹAllaẓeena|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|fahum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
6,13,"Walahoo|maa-|sakana|fil|lay-li|wan-nahaar.|Wa-Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
6,14,"Q̣ul|ʹag̣ayral|laahi|ʹattakhiẓu|waliyyañ|Faaṭiris|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-Huwa|yuṭʻimu|wa-laa|yuṭʻam.|Q̣ul|ʹinneee|ʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹakoona|ʹawwala|man|ʹaslama|wa-laa|takoonanna|minal|mushrikeen."
6,15,"Q̣ul|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹin|ʻaṣaytu|Rabbee|ʻaẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻAz̤̣eem."
6,16,"Mañy|yuṣraf|ʻanhu|yawmaʹiẓin|faq̣ad|raḥimah;|waẓaalikal|fawzul|mubeen."
6,17,"Wa-ʹiñy|yam-saskal|laahu|biḍurriñ|falaa|kaashifa|lahooo|ʹillaa|Hoo:|wa-ʹiñy|yam-saska|bikhayriñ|fa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
6,18,"Wa-huwal|Q̣aahiru|fawq̣a|ʻibaadih;|wa-Huwal|Ḥakeemul|Khabeer."
6,19,"Q̣ul|ʹayyu|shayʹin|ʹakbaru|shahaadah?|Q̣ulil|laahu|shaheedum|baynee|wa-baynakum,|wa-ʹooḥiya|ʹilayya|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaanu|liʹuñẓirakum̃|bihee|wa-mam|balag̣.|ʹAʹinnakum|latashhadoona|ʹanna|maʻal|laahi|ʹaalihatan|ʹukhraa?|Q̣ul|laaa|ʹashhad!|Q̣ul|ʹinnamaa|Huwa|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥiduñw|wa-ʹinnanee|bareeeʹum|mimmaa|tushrikoon."
6,20,"Allaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|yaʻrifoonahoo|kamaa|yaʻrifoona|ʹabnaaaʹahum.|ʹAllaẓeena|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|fahum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
6,21,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mim-manif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|ʹaw|kaẓẓaba|biʹAayaatih?|ʹInnahoo|laa-|yufliḥuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
6,22,"Wa-yawma|naḥ-shuruhum|jameeʻañ|s̤umma|naq̣oolu|lil-laẓeena|ʹashrakooo|ʹayna|shurakaaaʹukumul|laẓeena|kuñtum|tazʻumoon."
6,23,"S̤umma|lam|takuñ|fitnatuhum|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aaloo|wallaahi|Rabbina|maa-|kunnaa|mushrikeen."
6,24,"ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaẓaboo|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim|wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
6,25,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yastamiʻu|ʹilayk;|wa-jaʻalnaa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|ʹakinnatan|ʹañy|yafq̣ahoohu|wa-feee|ʹaaẓaanihim|waq̣raa;|wa-ʹiñy|yaraw|kulla|ʹAayatil|laa|yuʹminoo|bihaa:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹooka|yujaadiloonaka|yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleen."
6,26,"Wa-hum|yan-hawna|ʻanhu|wa-yanʹawna|ʻanh:|wa-ʹiñy|yuh-likoona|ʹillaaa|ʹañfusahum|wa-maa|yashʻuroon."
6,27,"Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓ|wuq̣ifoo|ʻalan|Naari|faq̣aaloo|yaa-laytanaa|nuraddu|wa-laa|nukaẓẓiba|biʹAayaati|Rabbinaa|wa-nakoona|minal|Muʹmineen!"
6,28,"Bal|badaa|lahum|maa|kaanoo|yukhfoona|miñ|q̣abl.|Wa-law|ruddoo|laʻaadoo|limaa|nuhoo|ʻanhu|wa-ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon."
6,29,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹin|hiya|ʹillaa|ḥayaatunad|dunyaa|wa-maa|naḥnu|bimabʻoos̤een."
6,30,"Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓ|wuq̣ifoo|ʻalaa|Rabbihim!|q̣aala|ʹalaysa|haaẓaa|bilḥaq̣q̣?|Q̣aaloo|balaa|wa-Rabbinaa!|Q̣aala|faẓooq̣ul|ʻaẓaaba|bimaa|kuñtum|takfuroon."
6,31,"Q̣ad|khasiral|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|bi-liq̣aaaʹil|laah,―|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹathumus|Saaʻatu|bag̣tatañ|q̣aaloo|yaa-ḥasratanaa|ʻalaa|maa-|farraṭnaa|feehaa|wa-hum|yaḥ-miloona|ʹawzaarahum|ʻalaa|z̤̣uhoorihim.|ʹAlaa|saaaʹa|maa-|yaziroon!"
6,32,"Wa-mal|ḥayaatud|dunyaaa|ʹillaa|laʻibuñw|walahw?|Wa-lad-Daarul|ʹAakhiratu|khayrul|lillaẓeena|yattaq̣oon.|ʹAfalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
6,33,"Q̣ad|naʻlamu|innahoo|layaḥzunukal|laẓee|yaq̣ooloona|faʹinnahum|laa-|yukaẓẓiboonaka|wa-laakinnaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|biʹAayaatil|lahi|yaj-ḥadoon."
6,34,"Wa-laq̣ad|kuẓẓibat|Rusulum|miñ|q̣ablika|faṣabaroo|ʻalaa|maa-|kuẓẓiboo|wa-ʹooẓoo|ḥattaaa|ʹataahum|naṣrunaa.|Wa-laa|mubaddila|li-Kalimaatil|laah.|Wa-laq̣ad|jaaʹaka|min|nabaʹil|Mursaleen."
6,35,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|kabura|ʻalayka|ʹiʻraaḍuhum|faʹinis|taṭaʻta|ʹañ|tabtag̣iya|nafaq̣añ|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹaw|sullamañ|fis|samaaaʹi|fataʹtiyahum̃|biʹAayah.|Wa-law|shaaʹal|laahu|lajamaʻahum|ʻalal|hudaa|falaa|takoonanna|minal|jaahileen!"
6,36,"ʹInnamaa|yastajeebul|laẓeena|yasmaʻoon.|Wal-mawtaa|yabʻas̤uhumul|laahu|s̤umma|ʹilayhi|yurjaʻoon."
6,37,"Waq̣aaloo|laa-law|nuzzila|ʻalayhi|ʹaayatum|mir|rabbih?|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|laaha|Q̣aadirun|ʻalaaa|ʹañy|yunazzila|ʹAayatañw|Walaakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
6,38,"Wa-maa|miñ|daaabbatiñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|ṭaaaʹiriny|yaṭeeru|bijanaaḥayhi|ʹillaaa|ʹumamun|ʹams̤aalukum.|Maa-|farraṭnaa|fil|Kitaabi|miñ|shayʹiñ|s̤umma|ʹilaa|Rabbihim|yuḥ-sharoon."
6,39,"Wallaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|ṣummuñw|wabukmuñ|fiz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaat:|mañy|yashaʹil|laahu|yuḍ-lilh:|wa-mañy|yashaʹ|yajʻalhu|ʻalaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
6,40,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytakum|ʹin|ʹataakum|ʻaẓabul|laahi|ʹaw|ʹatatkumus|Saaʻatu|ʹa-g̣ayral|laahi|tadʻoon?|ʹIñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
6,41,"Bal|ʹiyyaahu|tadʻoona|fayakshifu|maa-|tadʻoona|ʹilayhi|ʹiñ|shaaʹa|watañsawna|maa-|tushrikoon!"
6,42,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaaa|ilaaa|ʹumamim|miñ|q̣ablika|faʹakhaẓnaahum̃|bil-baʹsaaaʹi|waḍ-ḍarraaaʹi|laʻallahum|yataḍarraʻoon."
6,43,"Falawlaaa|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹahum̃|baʹsunaa|taḍarraʻoo|walaakiñ|q̣asat|q̣uloobuhum|wa-zayyana|lahumush|Shayṭaanu|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
6,44,"Falammaa|nasoo|maa-|ẓukkiroo|bihee|fataḥnaa|ʻalayhim|ʹabwaaba|kulli|shayʹ;|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|fariḥoo|bimaaa|ʹootooo|ʹakhaẓnaahum̃|bag̣tatañ|faʹiẓaa|hum|mublisoon."
6,45,"Faq̣uṭiʻa|daa-birul|q̣awmil|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo.|Wal-Ḥamdu|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
6,46,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹin|ʹakhaẓal|laahu|samʻakum|wa-ʹabṣaarakum|wa-khatama|ʻalaa|q̣uloobikum|man|ʹilaahun|g̣ayrul|laahi|yaʹteekum̃|bih?|ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|nuṣarriful|ʹaayaati|s̤umma|hum|yaṣdifoon."
6,47,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytakum|ʹin|ʹataakum|ʻaẓaabul|laahi|bag̣tatan|ʻaw|jahratan|hal|yuhlaku|ʹillal|q̣awmuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon!"
6,48,"Wa-maa|nursilul|Mursaleena|ʹillaa|mubashshireena|wa-muñẓireen.|Faman|ʹaamana|wa-ʹaṣlaḥa|falaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
6,49,"Wallaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|yamassuhumul|ʻaẓaabu|bimaa|kaanoo|yaf-suq̣oon."
6,50,"Q̣ul|laaa|ʹaq̣oolu|lakum|ʻiñdee|khazaaaʹinul|laahi|wa-laaa|ʹaʻlamul|g̣ayba|wa-laaa|ʹaq̣oolu|lakum|ʹinnee|malak.|ʹIn|ʹattabiʻu|ʹillaa|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayy.|Q̣ul|hal|yastawil|ʹaʻmaa|wal-baṣeer?|ʹAfalaa|tatafakkaroon?"
6,51,"Wa-ʹañẓir|bihil|laẓeena|yakhaafoona|ʹañy|yuḥ-sharooo|ʹilaa|Rabbihim|laysa|lahum|miñ|doonihee|waliyyuñw|walaa|shafeeʻul|laʻallahum|yattaq̣oon."
6,52,"Wa-laa|taṭrudil|laẓeena|yadʻoona|Rabbahum̃|bil-g̣adaati|wal-ʻashiyyi|yureedoona|Waj-hah.|Maa-|ʻalayka|Min|ḥisaabihim|miñ|shayʹiñw|wamaa|min|ḥisaabika|ʻalayhim|miñ|shayʹiñ|fataṭrudahum|fatakoona|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
6,53,"Wa-kaẓaalika|fatannaa|baʻḍahum̃|bibaʻḍil|liyaq̣oolooo|ʹahaaaʹulaaaʹi|mannal|laahu|ʻalayhim|min|bay-ninaa?|ʹAlaysal|laahu|biʹaʻlama|bishshaakireen."
6,54,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹakal|laẓeena|yuʹminoona|biʹAayaatinaa|faq̣ul|Salaamun|ʻalaykum|kataba|Rabbukum|ʻalaa|Nafsihir|Raḥmata|ʹannahoo|man|ʻamila|miñkum|soooʹam|bijahaalatiñ|s̤umma|taaba|mim|baʻdihee|wa-ʹaṣlaḥa|faʹannahoo|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
6,55,"Wa-kaẓaalika|nufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|wa-litastabeena|sabeelul|mujrimeen."
6,56,"Q̣ul|ʹinnee|nuheetu|ʹan|ʹaʻbudal|laẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laah.|Q̣ul|Laaa|ʹattabiʻu|ʹahwaaaʹakum|q̣ad|ḍalaltu|ʹiẓañw|Wamaaa|ʹana|minal|Muhtadeen."
6,57,"ʹinnee|Q̣ul|ʻalaa|bayyinatim|mir|Rabbi|Wakaẓẓabtum̃|bih.|Maa-|ʻiñdee|maa-|tastaʻjiloona|bih.|ʹInil|Ḥukmu|ʹillaa|lillaah:|yaq̣uṣṣul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-Huwa|khayrul|faaṣileen."
6,58,"Q̣ul|law|ʹanna|ʻiñdee|maa-|tastaʻjiloona|bihee|laq̣uḍiyal|ʹamru|baynee|wa-baynakum.|Wallaahu|ʹaʻlamu|biz̤̣z̤̣aalimeen."
6,59,"Wa-ʻiñdahoo|mafaatiḥul|G̣aybi|laa-|yaʻlamuhaaa|ʹillaa|Hoo.|Wayaʻlamu|maa-|fil|barri|wal-baḥr.|Wa-maa|tasq̣uṭu|miñw|waraq̣atin|ʹillaa|yaʻlamuhaa|wa-laa|ḥabbatiñ|fee|z̤̣ulumaatil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|raṭbiñw|wa-laa|yaabisin|ʹillaa|fee|Kitaabim|Mubeen."
6,60,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|yatawaffaakum̃|billayli|wayaʻlamu|maa-|jaraḥtum̃|bin-nahaari|s̤umma|yabʻas̤ukum|feehi|liyuq̣ḍaaa|ʹajalum|musammaa.|S̤umma|ʹilayhi|marjiʻukum|s̤umma|yunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
6,61,"Wa-Huwal|Q̣aahiru|fawq̣a|ʻibaadihee|wa-yursilu|ʻalaykum|ḥafaz̤̣ah.|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹaḥadakumul|mawtu|tawaffathu|rusulunaa|wahum|laa-|yufarriṭoon."
6,62,"S̤umma|ruddooo|ʹilal|laahi|Mawlaahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣.|ʹAlaa|lahul|Ḥukmu|wa-Huwa|ʹAsraʻul|ḥaasibeen."
6,63,"Q̣ul|mañy|yunajjeekum|miñ|z̤̣ulumaatil|barri|walbaḥri|tadʻoonahoo|taḍarruʻañw|wakhufyah:|laʹin|ʹañjaanaa|min|haaẓihee|lanakoonanna|minash|shaakireen."
6,64,"Q̣ulil|laahu|yunajjeekum|minhaa|wa-miñ|kulli|karbiñ|s̤umma|ʹañtum|tushrikoon!"
6,65,"Q̣ul|Huwal|q̣aadiru|ʻalaaa|ʹañy|yabʻas̤a|ʻalaykum|ʻaẓaabam|miñ|fawq̣ikum|ʹaw|miñ|taḥti|ʹarjulikum|ʹaw|yalbisakum|shiyaʻañw|wayuẓeeq̣a|baʻḍakum̃|baʹsa|baʻḍ.|ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|nuṣarriful|ʹAayaati|laʻallahum|yafq̣ahoon."
6,66,"Wa-kaẓ-ẓaba|bihee|q̣awmuka|wa-huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣.|Q̣ul|lastu|ʻalaykum̃|bi-Wakeel;"
6,67,"Likulli|nabaʹim|mustaq̣arruñw|wasawfa|taʻlamoon."
6,68,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|raʹaytal|laẓeena|yakhooḍoona|feee|ʹAayaatinaa|faʹaʻriḍ|ʻanhum|ḥattaa|yakhooḍoo|fee|ḥadees̤in|g̣ayrih.|Wa-ʹimmaa|yuñsiyannakash|Shayṭaanu|falaa|taq̣ʻud|baʻdaẓ|ẓikraa|maʻal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
6,69,"Wa-maa|ʻalal|laẓeena|yattaq̣oona|min|ḥisaabihim|miñ|shayʹiñw|walaakiñ|Ẓikraa|laʻallahum|yattaq̣oon."
6,70,"Wa-ẓaril|laẓeenat|takhaẓoo|deenahum|laʻibañw|walahwañw|wag̣arrathumul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|waẓakkir|biheee|ʹañ|tubsala|nafsum|bimaa|kasabat:|laysa|lahaa|miñ|doonil|laahi|waliyyuñw|walaa|shafeeʻ.|Wa-ʹiñ|taʻdil|kulla|ʻadlil|laa|yuʹkhaẓ|minhaa.|ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ʹubsiloo|bimaa|kasaboo.|Lahum|sharaabum|min|ḥameemiñw|waʻaẓaabun|ʹaleemum|bimaa|kaanoo|yakfuroon."
6,71,"Q̣ul|ʹanadʻoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yañfaʻunaa|wa-laa|yaḍurrunaa|wa-nurraddu|ʻalaaa|ʹaʻq̣aabinaa|baʻda|ʹiẓ|hadaanal|laahu|kal-laẓis|tahwathush|shayaaṭeenu|fil|ʹarḍi|ḥayraan.|Lahooo|ʹaṣḥaabuñy|yadʻoonahooo|ʹilal|hudaʹ|tinaa.|Q̣ul|ʹinna|hudal|laahi|huwal|hudaa.|Wa-ʹumirnaa|linuslima|lirabbil|ʻAalameen:―"
6,72,"Wa-ʹan|ʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wattaq̣ooh;|wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹilayhi|tuḥ-sharoon."
6,73,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bilḥaq̣q̣:|wa-yawma|yaq̣oolu|kuñ|Fayakoon.|Q̣awluhul|Ḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-lahul|mulku|Yawma|yuñfakhu|fiṣ|Ṣoor.|ʻAalimul|g̣aybi|washshahaadah.|Wa-Huwal|Ḥakeemul|Khabeer."
6,74,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|liʹabeehi|ʹAazara|ʹatattakhiẓu|ʹaṣnaaman|ʹaalihah?|ʹInneee|ʹaraaka|wa-q̣awmaka|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
6,75,"Wa-kaẓaalika|nureee|ʹIbraaheema|Malakootas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-liyakoona|minal|Mooq̣ineen."
6,76,"Falammaa|janna|ʻalayhil|laylu|raʹaa|kaw-kabaa.|Q̣aala|haaẓaa|Rabbee.|Falammaaa|ʹafala|q̣aala|laaa|ʹuḥibbul|ʹaafileen."
6,77,"Falammaa|raʹal|q̣amara|baazig̣añ|q̣aala|haaẓaa|Rabbee.|Falammaaa|ʹafala|q̣aala|laʹil|lam|yahdinee|Rabbee|laʹakoonanna|minal|q̣awmiḍ|ḍaaalleeen."
6,78,"Falammaa|ra|ʹash-shamsa|baazig̣atañ|q̣aala|haaẓaa|Rabbee|haaẓaaa|ʹakbar.|Falammaaa|ʹafalat|q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹinnee|bareeʹum|mimmaa|tushrikoon."
6,79,"ʹInnee|waj-jahtu|wajhiya|lillaẓee|faṭaras|samaawaati|wal-arḍa|ḥaneefañw|wamaaa|ʹana|minal|mushrikeen."
6,80,"Wa-haaaj-jahoo|q̣aw-muh.|Q̣aala|ʹa-tu-ḥaaaj-jooon-nee|fil|laahi|wa-q̣ad|hadaan?|Wa-laaa|ʹakhaafu|maa-|tushrikoona|biheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yashaaaʹa|Rabbee|shayʹaa.|Wasiʻa|Rabbee|kulla|shayʹin|ʻilmaa.|ʹAfalaa|tataẓakkaroon?"
6,81,"Wa-kayfa|ʹakhaafu|maaa|ʹashraktum|wa-laa|takhaafoona|ʹannakum|ʹashraktum̃|billaahi|maa-|lam|yunazzil|bihee|ʻalaykum|sulṭaanaa?|Faʹayyul|fareeq̣ayni|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|bil-amn?|ʹIñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon."
6,82,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-lam|yal-bisooo|ʹeemaanahum̃|biz̤̣ulmin|ʹulaaaʹika|lahumul|ʹamnu|wa-hum|Muhtadoon."
6,83,"Wa-tilka|ḥujjatunaaa|ʹaataynaahaaa|ʹibraaheema|ʻalaa|q̣awmih.|Narfaʻu|darajaatim|man|nashaaaʹ.|Inna|Rabbaka|Ḥakeemun|ʻAleem."
6,84,"Wa-wahabnaa|lahooo|ʹIs-ḥaaq̣a|wa-yaʻq̣oob:|kullan|hadaynaa:|wa-Nooḥan|hadaynaa|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-miñ|Ẓurriyyatihee|Daawooda|wa-Sulaymaana|wa-ʹAyyooba|wa-Yoosufa|wa-Moosaa|wa-Haaroon:|wa-kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen:"
6,85,"Wa-Zakariyyaa|wa-Yaḥyaa|wa-ʻEesaa|wa-ʹIlyaas.|Kullum|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
6,86,"Wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|wal-Yasaʻa|wa-Yoonusa|wa-Looṭaa:|wa-kullañ|faḍḍalnaa|ʻalal|ʻaalameen:"
6,87,"Wa-min|ʹaabaaaʹihim|waẓurriyyaatihim|wa-ʹikhwaa-nihim:|waj-tabay-naahum|wa-haday-naahum|ʹilaa|Ṣiraatim|Mustaq̣eem."
6,88,"Ẓaalika|Hudal|laahi|yahdee|bihee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadih.|Wa-law|ʹashrakoo|laḥabiṭa|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
6,89,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥukma|wan-Nubuwwah.|Faʹiñy|yakfur|bihaa|haaaʹulaaaʹi|faq̣ad|wak-kalnaa|bihaa|q̣awmal|laysoo|bihaa|bi-Kaafireen."
6,90,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|hadal|laahu|fabihudaahumuq̣|tadih.|Q̣ul|laaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|ʹajraa:|ʹIn|huwa|illaa|Ẓikraa|lil-ʻaalameen."
6,91,"Wa-maa|q̣adarul|laaha|ḥaq̣q̣a|q̣adriheee|ʹiẓ|q̣aaloo|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|ʻalaa|basharim|miñ|shayʹ.|Q̣ul|man|ʹañzalal|Kitaabal|laẓee|jaaʹa|bihee|Moosaa|Noorañw|Wa-Hudal|lin-naasi|tajʻaloonahoo|q̣araaṭeesa|tubdoonahaa|wa-tukhfoona|kas̤eeraa.|Wa-ʻullimtum|maa|lam|taʻlamooo|ʹañtum|wa-laaa|ʹaabaaaʹukum.|Q̣ulil|laahu|s̤umma|ẓarhum|fee|khawḍihim|yalʻaboon."
6,92,"Wa-haaẓaa|Kitaabun|ʹañzalnaahu|Mubaarakum|Muṣaddiq̣ul|laẓee|bayna|yadayhi|wa-lituñẓira|ʹUmmal|Q̣uraa|wa-man|ḥawlahaa.|Wallaaẓeena|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹaakhirati|yuʹminoona|bihee|wa-hum|ʻalaa|Ṣalaatihim|yuḥaafiz̤̣oon."
6,93,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|ʹaw|q̣aala|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayya|wa-lam|yooḥa|ʹilayhi|shayʹuñw|wamañ|q̣aala|saʹuñzilu|mis̤la|maaa|ʹañzalal|laah?|Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|fee|g̣amaraatil|mawti|walmalaaaʹikatu|baasiṭooo|ʹaydeehim:|ʹakhrijoo|ʹañfusakum.|ʹAl-yawma|tujzawna|ʻaẓaabal|hooni|bimaa|kuñtum|taq̣ooloona|ʻalal|laahi|g̣ayral|ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-kuñtum|ʻan|ʻAayaatihee|tastakbiroon."
6,94,"Wa-laq̣ad|jiʹtumoonaa|furaadaa|kamaa|khalaq̣naakum|ʹawwala|marratiñw|wataraktum|maa|khawwal-naakum|wa-raaaʹa|z̤̣uhoorikum:|wa-maa|naraa|maʻakum|shufaʻaaaʹakumul|laẓeena|zaʻamtum|ʹannahum|feekum|shurakaaaʹ.|Laq̣at|taq̣aṭṭaʻa|baynakum|wa-ḍalla|ʻañkum|maa|kuñtum|tazʻumoon!"
6,95,"ʹInnal|laaha|faaliq̣ul|ḥabbi|wannawaa.|Yukhrijul|ḥayya|minal|mayyiti|wa-Mukhrijul|mayyiti|minal|ḥayy.|Ẓaalikumul|laahu|faʹannaa|tuʹfakoon?"
6,96,"Faaliq̣ul|ʹiṣbaaḥ:|wa-jaʻalal|layla|sakanañw|washshamsa|walq̣amara|ḥusbaanaa,|ẓaalika|taq̣deerul|ʻAzeezil|ʻAleem."
6,97,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumun|nujooma|litahtadoo|bihaa|fee|z̤̣ulumaatil|barri|walbahr:|q̣ad|faṣṣalnal|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
6,98,"Wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañshaʹakum|min|nafsiñw|waaḥidatiñ|famustaq̣arruñw|wa-mustawdaʻ:|q̣ad|faṣṣalnal|ʹAayaati|liq̣aw|miñyyafq̣ahoon."
6,99,"Wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹaa:|faʹakhrajnaa|bihee|nabaata|kulli|shayʹiñ|faʹakhrajnaa|minhu|khaḍiran|nukhriju|minhu|ḥabbam|mutaraakibaa;|wa-minan|nakhli|miñ|ṭalʻihaa|q̣in-waanuñ|daaniyatuñw|wa-jannaatim|min|ʹaʻnaabiñw|wazzaytoona|warrummaana|mushtabihañw|wa-g̣ayra|mutashaabih.|ʹUñz̤̣urooo|ʹilaa|s̤amariheee|ʹiẓaaa|ʹas̤mara|wa-yanʻih.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalikum|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
6,100,"Wa-jaʻaloo|lillaahi|shurakaaaʹal|jinna|wa-khalaq̣a-hum|wa-kharaq̣oo|lahoo|baneena|wa-banaatim|big̣ayri|ʻilm.|Subḥaanahoo|wa-taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yaṣifoon."
6,101,"Badeeʻus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|Annaa|yakoonu|lahoo|waladuñw|wa-lam|takul|lahoo|ṣaaḥibah?|Wa-khalaq̣a|kulla|shayʹ,|wa-Huwa|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
6,102,"Ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukum!|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo.|khaaliq̣u|kulli|shayʹiñ|faʻbudooh;|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñw|Wakeel."
6,103,"Laa|tudrikuhul|ʹabṣaaru.|wa-Huwa|yudrikul|ʹabṣaar:|wa-Huwal|Laṭeeful|Khabeer."
6,104,"Q̣ad|jaaaʹakum̃|baṣaaaʹiru|mir|rabbikum:|faman|ʹabṣara|falinafsih:|wa-man|ʻamiya|faʻalayhaa:|wa-maaa|ʹana|ʻalaykum̃|biḥafeez̤̣."
6,105,"Wa-kaẓaalika|nuṣarriful|ʹAayaati|wa-liyaq̣ooloo|darasta|wa-li-nubayyi-nahoo.|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
6,106,"ʹIttabiʻ|maaa|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbik:|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo:|wa-ʹaʻriḍ|ʻanil|mushrikeen."
6,107,"Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maaa|ʹashrakoo:|wa-maa|jaʻalnaaka|ʻalayhim|ḥafeez̤̣aa,|wa-maaa|ʹañta|ʻalayhim̃|biwakeel."
6,108,"Wa-laa|tasubbul|laẓeena|yadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|fayasubbul|laaha|ʻadwam|big̣ayri|ʻilm.|Kaẓaalika|zayyannaa|likulli|ʹummatin|ʻamalahum.|S̤umma|ʹilaa|Rabbihim|marjiʻuhum|fayunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
6,109,"Wa-ʹaq̣samoo|billaahi|jahda|ʹaymaanihim|laʹiñ|jaaaʹathum|ʹAayatul|layuʹminunna|bihaa.|Q̣ul|ʹinnamal|ʹAayaatu|ʻindal|laahi|wa-maa|yushʻirukum|ʹannahaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹat|laa|yuʹminoon?"
6,110,"Wa-nuq̣allibu|ʹafʹidatahum|wa-ʹabṣaarahum|kamaa|lam|yuʹminoo|biheee|ʹawwala|marratiñ|wa-naẓaruhum|fee|ṭug̣yaanihim|yaʻmahoon."
6,111,"Wa-law|ʹannanaa|nazzal-naaa|ʹilayhimul|malaaaʹikata|wa-kallamahumul|mawtaa|waḥasharnaa|ʻalayhim|kulla|shayʹiñ|q̣ubulam|maa|kaanoo|liyuʹminooo|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yashaaaʹal|laahu|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|yajhaloon."
6,112,"Wa-kaẓaalika|jaʻalnaa|likulli|nabiyyin|ʻaduwwañ|shayaaṭeenal|ʹiñsi|waljinni|yooḥee|baʻḍuhum|ʹilaa|baʻḍiñ|zukhrufal|q̣awli|g̣urooraa.|Wa-law|shaaaʹa|Rabbuka|maa-|faʻaloohu|faẓarhum|wa-maa|yaftaroon."
6,113,"Walitaṣg̣aaa|ʹilayhi|ʹafʹidatul|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|wa-liyarḍawhu|waliyaq̣tarifoo|maa-|hum|muq̣tarifoon."
6,114,"ʹAfag̣ayral|laahi|ʹabtag̣ee|ḥakamañw|wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañzala|ʹilaykumul|Kitaaba|mufaṣṣalaa?|Wallaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|yaʻlamoona|ʹannahoo|munazzalum|mir|Rabbika|bilḥaq̣q̣i|falaa|takoonanna|minal|mumtareen."
6,115,"Wa-tammat|kalimatu|Rabbika|ṣidq̣añw|waʻadlaa:|laa-|mubaddila|li-Kalimaatih:|wa-Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
6,116,"Wa-ʹiñ|tuṭiʻ|ʹaks̤ara|mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|yuḍillooka|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah.|ʹIñy|yattabiʻoona|ʹillaz̤̣|z̤̣anna|wa-ʹin|hum|ʹillaa|yakhruṣoon."
6,117,"ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|mañy|yaḍillu|ʻañ|Sabeelih;|wa-Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bil-Muhtadeen."
6,118,"Fakuloo|mimmaa|ẓukiras|mul|laahi|ʻalayhi|ʹiñ|kuñtum̃|biʹAayaatihee|muʹmineen."
6,119,"Wa-maa|lakum|ʹallaa|taʹkuloo|mimmaa|ẓukiras|mul|laahi|ʻalayhi|wa-q̣ad|faṣṣala|lakum|maa|ḥarrama|ʻalaykum|ʹillaa|maḍ|ṭurirtum|ʹilayh?|Wa-ʹinna|kas̤eeral|layuḍilloona|biʹahwaaaʹihim̃|big̣ayri|ʻilm.|ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bilmuʻtadeen."
6,120,"Waẓaroo|z̤̣aahiral|ʹis̤mi|wa-baaṭinah:|ʹInnal|laẓeena|yaksiboonal|ʹis̤ma|sayujzawna|bimaa|kaanoo|yaq̣tarifoon."
6,121,"Wa-laa|taʹkuloo|mimmaa|lam|yuẓkaris|mul|laahi|ʻalayhi|wa-ʹinnahoo|lafisq̣.|Wa-ʹinnash|shayaaṭeena|layooḥoona|ʹilaaa|ʹawliyaaaʹihim|liyujaadilookum.|Wa-ʹin|ʹaṭaʻtumoohum|ʹinnakum|lamushrikoon."
6,122,"ʹA-wamañ|kaana|maytañ|faʹaḥyaynaahu|wa-jaʻalnaa|lahoo|Noorañy|yamshee|bihee|fin|naasi|kamam|mas̤aluhoo|fiz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|laysa|bikhaarijim|minhaa?|Kaẓaalika|zuyyina|lilkaafireena|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
6,123,"Wa-kaẓaalika|jaʻalnaa|fee|kulli|q̣aryatin|ʹakaabira|mujrimeehaa|liyamkuroo|feehaa;|wa-maa|yamkuroona|ʹillaa|biʹañfusihim|wa-maa|yashʻuroon."
6,124,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹathum|ʹAayatuñ|q̣aaloo|lan|nuʹmina|ḥattaa|nuʹtaa|mis̤la|maaa|ʹootiya|rusulul|laah.|ʹAllaahu|ʹaʻlamu|ḥays̤u|yajʻalu|Risaalatah.|Sayuṣeebul|laẓeena|ʹajramoo|ṣag̣aarun|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-ʻaẓaabuñ|shadeedum|bimaa|kaanoo|yamkuroon."
6,125,"Famañy|yuridil|laahu|ʹañy|yahdiyahoo|yashraḥ|ṣadrahoo|lil-ʹIslaam;|wa-mañy|yurid|ʹañy|yuḍillahoo|yajʻal|ṣadrahoo|ḍayyiq̣an|harajañ|kaʹannamaa|yaṣṣaʻʻadu|fis|samaaaʹ.|Kaẓaalika|yajʻalul|laahur|rijsa|ʻalal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoon."
6,126,"Wa-haaẓaa|Ṣiraaṭu|Rabbika|Mustaq̣eemaa:|q̣ad|faṣṣalnal|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yaẓẓakkaroon."
6,127,"lahum|Daarus|Salaami|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|wa-Huwa|Waliyyuhum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
6,128,"Wa-yawma|yaḥ-shuruhum|jameeʻaa:|yaa-maʻsharal|jinni|q̣adis|taks̤artum|minal|ʹiñs.|Wa-q̣aala|ʹawliyaaaʹuhum|minal|ʹiñsi|Rabbanas|tamtaʻa|baʻḍunaa|bibaʻḍiñw|wabalag̣naaa|ʹajalanal|laẓeee|ʹajjalta|lanaa:|q̣aalan|Naaru|mas̤waakum|khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹillaa|maa-|shaaa|ʹallaah.|ʹInna|Rabbaka|Ḥakeemun|ʻAleem."
6,129,"Wa-kaẓaalika|nuwallee|baʻḍaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|baʻḍam|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
6,130,"Yaa-maʻsharal|jinni|wal-ʹiñsi|ʹalam|yaʹtikum|rusulum|miñkum|yaq̣uṣṣoona|ʻalaykum|ʹAayaatee|wa-yuñẓiroonakum|liq̣aaaʹa|yawmikum|haaẓaa?|Q̣aaloo|shahidnaa|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusinaa|wa-g̣arrat-humul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|wa-shahidoo|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim|ʹannahum|kaanoo|Kaafireen."
6,131,"Ẓaalika|ʹal|lam|yakur|Rabbuka|muhlikal|q̣uraa|biz̤̣ulmiñw|waʹahluhaa|g̣aafiloon."
6,132,"Wa-likulliñ|darajaatum|mimmaa|ʻamiloo:|wa-maa|Rabbuka|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|yaʻmaloon."
6,133,"Wa-Rabbukal|G̣aniyyu|Ẓur|Raḥmah:|ʹiñy|yashaʹ|yuẓ-hibkum|wa-yastakhlif|mim|baʻdikum|maa|yashaaʹu|kamaaa|ʹañshaʹakum|miñ|ẓurriyyati|q̣awmin|ʹaakhareen."
6,134,"ʹInna|maa-|tooʻadoona|laʹaatiñw|wamaaa|ʹañtum̃|bimuʻjizeen."
6,135,"Q̣ul|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|maloo|ʻalaa|makaanatikum|ʹinnee|ʻaamil:|fasawfa|taʻlamoona|mañ|takoonu|lahoo|ʻAaq̣ibatud|daar:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yufliḥuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
6,136,"Wa-jaʻaloo|lillaahi|mimmaa|ẓaraʹa|minal|ḥars̤i|walanʻaami|naṣeebañ|faq̣aaloo|haaẓaa|lillaahi|bizaʻmihim|wa-haaẓaa|lishurakaaaʹinaa!|Famaa|kaana|lishurakaaaʹihim|falaa|yaṣilu|ʹilal|laah;|wamaa|kaana|lillaahi|fahuwa|yaṣilu|ʹilaa|shurakaaʹihim!|Saaaʹa|maa-|yaḥkumoon!"
6,137,"Wa-kaẓaalika|zayyana|likas̤eerim|minal|mushrikeena|q̣atla|ʹawlaadihim|shurakaaaʹuhum|liyurdoohum|wa-liyalbisoo|ʻalayhim|deenahum.|Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maa-|faʻaloohu|faẓarhum|wa-maa|yaftaroon."
6,138,"Wa-q̣aaloo|haaẓiheee|ʹanʻaamuñw|waḥarsun|ḥijr.|Laa|yaṭʻamuhaaa|ʹillaa|man|nashaaaʹu|bizaʻmihim|wa-ʹanʻaamun|ḥurrimat|z̤̣uhooruhaa|wa-ʹanʻaamul|laa|yaẓkuroonas|mal|laahi|ʻalayhaf|tiraaaʹan|ʻalayh:|Sayajzeehim̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
6,139,"Waq̣aaloo|maa-|fee|buṭooni|haaẓihil|ʹanʻaami|khaaliṣatul|liẓukoorinaa|wa-muḥarramun|ʻalaaa|ʹazwaajinaa;|wa-ʹiñy|yakum|maytatañ|fahum|feehi|shurakaaaʹ.|Sayajzeehim|waṣfahum:|ʹinnahoo|Ḥakeemun|ʻAleem."
6,140,"Q̣ad|khasiral|laẓeena|q̣atalooo|ʹawlaadahum|safaham|big̣ayri|ʻilmiñw|waḥarramoo|maa-|razaq̣ahumul|laahuf|tiraaʹan|ʻalal|laah.|Q̣ad|ḍalloo|wa-maa|kaanoo|muhtadeen."
6,141,"Wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañshaʹa|jannaatim|maʻrooshaatiñw|wag̣ayra|maʻrooshaatiñw|wan-nakhla|wazzarʻa|mukhtalifan|ʹukuluhoo|wazzaytoona|warrummaana|mutashaabihañw|wag̣ayra|mutashaabih:|kuloo|miñ|s̤amariheee|ʹiẓaaa|ʹas̤mara|wa-ʹaatoo|ḥaq̣q̣ahoo|yawma|ḥasaadih.|Wa-laa|tusrifoo:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yuḥibbul|musrifeen."
6,142,"Waminal|ʹanʻaami|ḥamoolatañw|wafarshaa.|kuloo|mimmaa|razaq̣akumul|laahu|wa-laa|tattabiʻoo|khuṭuwaatish|Shayṭaan:|ʹinnahoo|lakum|ʻaduwwum|mubeen."
6,143,"S̤amaaniyata|ʹazwaaj:|minaḍ|ḍaʹnis̤|nayni|wa-minal|maʻzis̤|nayn.|Q̣ul|ʹaaaẓẓakarayni|ḥarrama|ʹamil|ʹuñs̤ayayni|ʹammash|tamalat|ʻalayhi|ʹarḥaamul|ʹuñs̤ayayn?|Nabbiʹoonee|biʻilmin|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Ṣaadiq̣een:"
6,144,"Wa-minal|ʹibilis̤|nayni|wa-minal|baq̣aris̤|nayn.|Q̣ul|ʹaaaẓẓakarayni|ḥarrama|ʹamil|ʹuñs̤ayayni|ʹammash|tamalat|ʻalayhi|ʹarḥaamul|ʹuñs̤ayayn?|Am|kuñtum|shuhadaaaʹa|iẓ|waṣṣaakumul|laahu|bihaaẓaa?|Faman|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓibal|liyuḍillan|naasa|big̣ayri|ʻilm?|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
6,145,"Q̣ul|laaa|ʹajidu|fee|maaa|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayya|muḥarraman|ʻalaa|ṭaaʻimiñy|yatʻamuhooo|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yakoona|maytatan|ʹaw|damam|masfooḥan|ʹaw|laḥma|khiñzeeriñ|faʹinnahoo|rijsun|ʹaw|fisq̣an|ʹuhilla|lig̣ayril|laahi|bih.|Famaniḍ|ṭurra|g̣ayra|baa-g̣iñw|walaa|ʻaadiñ|faʹinna|Rabbaka|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
6,146,"Wa-ʻalal|laẓeena|haadoo|ḥarramnaa|kulla|ẓee|Z̤̣ufur.|Wa-minal|baq̣ari|walg̣anami|ḥarramnaa|ʻalayhim|shuḥoomahumaaa|ʹillaa|maa-|ḥamalat|z̤̣uhooruhumaaa|ʹawil|ḥawaayaaa|ʹaw|makh|talaṭa|biʻaz̤̣m.|Ẓaalika|jazaynaahum̃|bibag̣yihim:|wa-ʹinnaa|la-Ṣaadiq̣oon."
6,147,"Faʹiñ|kaẓẓabooka|faq̣ur|Rabbukum|Ẓoo|Raḥmatiñw|waasiʻah;|wa-laa|yuraddu|baʹsuhoo|ʻanil|q̣awmil|mujrimeen."
6,148,"Sayaq̣oolul|laẓeena|ʹashrakoo|law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maaa|ʹashraknaa|wa-laaa|ʹaabaaaʹunaa|wa-laa|ḥarramnaa|miñ|shayʹ.|Kaẓaalika|kaẓẓabal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|ḥattaa|ẓaaq̣oo|baʹsanaa.|Q̣ul|hal|ʹiñdakum|min|ʻilmiñ|fatukhrijoohu|lanaa?|ʹIñ|tattabiʻoona|ʹillaz̤̣|z̤̣anna|wa-ʹin|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|takhruṣoon."
6,149,"Q̣ul|falillaahil|Ḥujjatul|baalig̣ah:|falaw|shaaaʹa|lahadaakum|ʹajmaʻeen."
6,150,"Q̣ul|halumma|shuhadaaaʹakumul|laẓeena|yashhadoona|ʹannal|laaha|ḥarrama|haaẓaa.|Faʹiñ|shahidoo|falaa|tashhad|maʻahum.|Wa-laa|tattabiʻ|ʹahwaaaʹal|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayatinaa|wallaẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|wa-hum̃|bi-Rabbihim|yaʻdiloon."
6,151,"Q̣ul|taʻaalaw|ʹatlu|maa-|ḥarrama|Rabbukum|ʻalaykum|ʹallaa|tushrikoo|bihee|shayʹañw|wabilwaalidayni|ʹiḥsaanaa;|wa-laa|taq̣tulooo|ʹawlaadakum|min|ʹimlaaq̣.|Naḥnu|narzuq̣ukum|wa-ʹiyyaahum;|wa-laa|taq̣rabul|fawaaḥisha|maa-|z̤̣ahara|minhaa|wa-maa|baṭan.|Wa-laa|taq̣tulun|nafsal|latee|ḥarramal|laahu|ʹillaa|bilhaq̣q̣:|ẓaalikum|waṣṣaakum̃|bihee|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
6,152,"Wa-laa|taq̣raboo|maalal|yateemi|ʹillaa|billatee|hiya|ʹaḥsanu|ḥattaa|yablug̣a|ʹashuddah.|Wa-ʹawful|kayla|wal-meezaana|bilq̣isṭ.|Laa-|nukallifu|nafsan|ʹillaa|wusʻahaa;―|wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣ultum|faʻdiloo|wa-law|kaana|ẓaa|q̣urbaa:|wa-biʻAhdil|laahi|ʹawfoo:|ẓaalikum|waṣṣaakum̃|bihee|laʻallakum|taẓakkaroon."
6,153,"Wa-ʹanna|haaẓaa|Ṣiraaṭee|Mustaq̣eemañ|fattabiʻooh:|wa-laa|tattabiʻus|subula|fatafarraq̣a|bikum|ʻañ|sabeelih:|ẓaalikum|waṣṣaakum̃|bihee|laʻallakum|tattaq̣oon."
6,154,"S̤umma|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|tamaaman|ʻalal|laẓeee|ʹaḥsana|wa-tafṣeelal|likulli|shayʹiñw|wahudañw|waraḥmatal|laʻallahum̃|biliq̣aaaʹi|Rabbihim|yuʹminoon."
6,155,"Wa-haaẓaa|Kitaabun|ʹañzalnaahu|mubaarakuñ|fattabiʻoohu|wattaq̣oo|laʻal-lakum|turḥamoon;"
6,156,"ʹAñ|taq̣oolooo|ʹinnamaaa|ʹuñzilal|Kitaabu|ʻalaa|Ṭaaaifatayni|miñ|q̣ablinaa.|Wa-ʹiñ|kunnaa|ʻañ|diraasatihim|lag̣aafileen;"
6,157,"ʹAw|taq̣ooloo|law|annaaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalaynal|Kitaabu|lakunnaaa|ʹahdaa|minhum.|Faq̣ad|jaaaʹakum̃|bayyinatum|mir|Rabbikum|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmaḥ.|Faman|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmañ|kaẓẓaba|biʹAayaatil|laahi|waṣadafa|ʻanhaa?|Sanajzil|laẓeena|yaṣdifoona|ʻan|ʹAayaatinaa|soooʹal|ʻaẓaabi|bimaa|kaanoo|yaṣdifoon."
6,158,"Hal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|taʹtiyahumul|malaaaʹikatu|ʹaw|yaʹtiya|Rabbuka|ʹaw|yaʹtiya|baʻḍu|ʹAayaati|Rabbik?|Yawma|yaʹtee|baʻḍu|ʹAayaati|Rabbika|laa|yañfaʻu|nafsan|ʹeemaanuhaa|lam|takun|ʹaamanat|miñ|q̣ablu|ʹaw|kasabat|feee|ʹeemaanihaa|khayraa.|Q̣uliñ|taz̤̣irooo|ʹinnaa|muñtaz̤̣iroon."
6,159,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|farraq̣oo|deenahum|wa-kaanoo|shiyaʻal|lasta|minhum|fee|shayʹ|Innamaaa|ʹamruhum|ʹilal|laahi|s̤umma|yunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yafʻaloon."
6,160,"Mañ|jaaaʹa|bilḥasanati|falahoo|ʻashru|ams̤aalihaa,|wa-mañ|jaaaʹa|bis-sayyiʹati|falaa|yujzaaa|ʹillaa|mis̤lahaa|wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
6,161,"Q̣ul|ʹinnanee|hadaanee|Rabbeee|ʹilaa|Ṣiraatim|Mustaq̣eem,|Deenañ|Q̣iyamam|Millata|ʹIbraaheema|ḥaneefaa,|wa-maa|kaana|minal|mushrikeen."
6,162,"Q̣ul|ʹinna|Ṣalaatee|wa-nusukee|wa-maḥyaaya|wa-mamaatee|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻaalameen:"
6,163,"Laa-|shareeka|lah:|wa-biẓaalika|ʹumirtu|wa-ʹana|ʹawwalul|Muslimeen."
6,164,"Q̣ul|ag̣ayral|laahi|ʹabg̣ee|Rabbañw|Wa-Huwa|Rabbu|kulli|shayʹ?|Wa-laa|taksibu|kullu|nafsin|ʹillaa|ʻalayhaa:|wa-laa|taziru|waaziratuñw|wizra|ʹukhraa.|S̤umma|ʹilaa|Rabbikum|marjiʻukum|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|feehi|takhtalifoon."
6,165,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|jaʻalakum|khalaaaʹifal|ʹarḍi|wa-rafaʻa|baʻḍakum|fawq̣a|baʻḍiñ|darajaatil|liyabluwakum|fee|maaa|ʹaataakum:|ʹInna|Rabbaka|Sareeʻul|ʻiq̣aabi|wa-ʹinnahoo|la-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
7,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Meeem-Ṣaaad."
7,2,"Kitaabun|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|falaa|yakuñ|fee|ṣadrika|ḥarajum|min-hu|lituñẓira|bihee|waẓikraa|lil-Muʹmineen."
7,3,"ʹIttabiʻoo|maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaykum|mir|rabbikum|wa-laa|tattabiʻoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹawliyaaaʹ.|Q̣aleelam|maa|taẓakkaroon."
7,4,"Wa-kam|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹahlaknaahaa|fajaaaʹahaa|baʹsunaa|bayaatan|ʹaw|hum|q̣aaaʹiloon?"
7,5,"Famaa|kaana|daʻwaahum|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹahum̃|baʹsunaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|z̤̣aalimeen."
7,6,"falanasʹalannal|laẓeena|ursila|ʹilayhim|wa-lanasʹalannal|mursaleen."
7,7,"Falanaq̣uṣṣanna|ʻalayhim̃|biʻilmiñw|wamaa|kunnaa|g̣aaaʹibeen."
7,8,"Walwaznu|Yawmaʹiẓinil|ḥaq̣q̣.|Famañ|s̤aq̣ulat|mawaazeenuhoo|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
7,9,"Wa-man|khaffat|mawaazeenuhoo|faʹulaaaikal|laẓeena|khasirooo|añfusahum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|yaz̤̣limoon."
7,10,"Wa-laq̣ad|makkannaakum|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-jaʻalnaa|lakum|feehaa|maʻaayish:|q̣aleelam|maa|tashkuroon!"
7,11,"Wa-laq̣ad|khalaq̣naakum|s̤umma|ṣawwarnaakum|s̤umma|q̣ulnaa|lil-malaaaʹikatis|judoo|liʹAadama|fasajadooo|ʹillaaa|ʹIblees;|lam|yakum|minas|saajideen."
7,12,"Q̣aala|maa-|manaʻaka|ʹallaa|tasjuda|ʹiẓ|ʹamartuk?|Q̣aala|ʹana|khayrum|minh.|Khalaq̣tanee|miñ|naariñw|wakhalaq̣tahoo|miñ|ṭeen."
7,13,"Q̣aala|fahbiṭ|minhaa|famaa|yakoonu|laka|ʹañ|tatakabbara|feehaa|fakhruj|ʹinnaka|minaṣ|ṣaag̣ireen."
7,14,"Q̣aala|ʹañz̤̣irneee|ʹilaa|yawmi|yubʻas̤oon."
7,15,"Q̣aala|ʹinnaka|minal|muñz̤̣areen."
7,16,"Q̣aala|fabimaaa|ʹag̣waytanee|laʹaq̣ʻudanna|lahum|Ṣiraaṭakal|Mustaq̣eem:"
7,17,"S̤umma|laʹaatiyannahum|mim|bayni|ʹaydeehim|wa-min|khalfihim|wa-ʻan|ʹaymaanihim|wa-ʻañ|shamaaaʹilihim:|wa-laa|tajidu|ʹaks̤arahum|shaakireen."
7,18,"Q̣aala|khruj|minhaa|maẓʹoomam|madḥooraa.|Lamañ|tabiʻaka|minhum|laʹamlaʹanna|Jahannama|miñkum|ʹajmaʻeen."
7,19,"Wa-yaaaʹAadamus|kun|ʹañta|wa-zawjukal|jannata|fakulaa|min|ḥays̤u|shiʹtumaa|wa-laa|taq̣rabaa|haaẓihish|shajarata|fatakoona|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
7,20,"Fawaswasa|lahumash|Shayṭaanu|liyubdiya|lahumaa|maa-|wooriya|ʻanhumaa|miñ|saw-ʹaatihimaa|waq̣aala|maa-|nahaakumaa|Rabbukumaa|ʻan|haaẓihish|shajarati|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|takoonaa|malakayni|ʹaw|takoonaa|minal|khaalideen."
7,21,"Wa-q̣aasamahumaaa|ʹinnee|lakumaa|laminan|naaṣiḥeen."
7,22,"Fadal-laahumaa|big̣uroor.|Falammaa|ẓaaq̣ash|shajarata|badat|lahumaa|saw-ʹaatuhumaa|waṭafiq̣aa|yakhṣifaani|ʻalayhimaa|miñw|waraq̣il|Jannah.|Wa-naadaa-humaa|Rabbuhumaaa|ʹalam|ʹanhakumaa|ʻañ|til-kumash|shajarati|wa-ʹaq̣ul|lakumaaa|ʹinnash|Shayṭaana|lakumaa|ʻaduwwum|mubeen?"
7,23,"Q̣aalaa|Rabbanaa|z̤̣alamnaaa|ʹañfusanaa:|wa-ʹil|lam|tag̣fir|lanaa|wa-tarḥamnaa|lanakoonanna|minal|Khaasireen."
7,24,"Q̣aalah|biṭoo|baʻḍukum|libaʻḍin|ʻaduww.|Wa-lakum|fil|ʹarḍi|mustaq̣arruñw|wamataaʻun|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
7,25,"Q̣aala|feehaa|taḥ-yawna|wa-feehaa|tamootoona|wa-minhaa|tukhrajoon."
7,26,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹaadama|q̣ad|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaykum|libaasañy|yuwaaree|saw-ʹaatikum|wa-reeshaa.|Wa-libaasut|taq̣waa|ẓaalika|khayr.|Ẓaalika|min|ʹAayaatil|laahi|laʻallahum|yaẓ-ẓakkaroon."
7,27,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹAadama|laa-|yaftinannakumush|Shayṭaanu|kamaaa|ʹakhraja|ʹa-bawaykum|minal|Jannati|yañziʻu|ʻanhumaa|libaasahumaa|liyuriyahumaa|saw-ʹaati-himaa.|ʹInnahoo|yaraakum|huwa|wa-q̣abeeluhoo|min|ḥays̤u|laa-|tarawnahum.|ʹInnaa|jaʻalnash|shayaaṭeena|ʹawliyaaaʹa|lillaẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoon."
7,28,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|faʻaloo|faaḥishatañ|q̣aaloo|wajadnaa|ʻalayhaaa|ʹaabaaaʹanaa|wallaahu|ʹa-maranaa|bihaa.|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yaʹmuru|bilfaḥshaaaʹ.|ʹA-taq̣ooloona|ʻalal|laahi|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon?"
7,29,"Q̣ul|ʹamara|Rabbee|bil-q̣isṭ.|Wa-ʹaq̣eemoo|wujoohakum|ʻiñda|kulli|masjidiñw|wadʻoohu|mukhliṣeena|lahud|deen.|Kamaa|badaʹakum|taʻoodoon."
7,30,"Fareeq̣an|hadaa|wa-fareeq̣an|ḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhimuḍ|ḍalaalah:|ʹinnahumut|takhaẓush|shayaaṭeena|ʹawliyaaaʹa|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-yaḥsaboona|ʹannahum|muhtadoon."
7,31,"Yaa-Baaneee|ʹAadama|khuẓoo|zeenatakum|ʻiñda|kulli|masjidiñw|wakuloo|washraboo|wa-laa|tusrifoo,|innahoo|laa-|yuḥibbul|musrifeen."
7,32,"Q̣ul|man|ḥarrama|zeenatal|laahil|lateee|ʹakhraja|liʻibaadihee|waṭ-ṭayyibaati|minar|rizq̣?|Q̣ul|hiya|lil-laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|khaaliṣatañy|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|Kaẓaalika|nufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
7,33,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaa|ḥarrama|Rabbiyal|fawaaḥisha|maa-|z̤̣ahara|minhaa|wa-maa|baṭana|wal-ʹis̤ma|wal-bag̣ya|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹañ|tushrikoo|billaahi|maa-|lam|yunazzil|bihee|sulṭaanañw|waʹañ|taq̣ooloo|ʻalal|laahi|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon."
7,34,"Wa-likulli|ʹummatin|ʹajal:|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹajaluhum|laa-|yastaʹkhiroona|saaʻatañw|walaa|yastaq̣dimoon."
7,35,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹAadama|ʹimmaa|yaʹtiyannakum|rusulum|miñkum|yaq̣uṣṣoona|ʻalaykum|ʹAayaatee|famanit|taq̣aa|wa-ʹaṣlaḥa|falaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
7,36,"Wallaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wastakbaroo|ʻan-haaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
7,37,"Faman|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|ʹaw|kaẓẓaba|biʹAayaatih?|ʹUlaaaʹika|yanaaluhum|naṣeebuhum|minal|Kitaab:|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹathum|rusulunaa|yatawaffawnahum|q̣aalooo|ʹayna|maa-|kuñtum|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laah?|Q̣aaloo|ḍalloo|ʻannaa|wa-shahidoo|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim|ʹannahum|kaanoo|kaafireen."
7,38,"Q̣aalad|khuloo|feee|ʹu-mamiñ|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ab-likum|minal|jinni|wal-ʹiñsi|fin|Naar.|Kullamaa|dakhalat|ʹummatul|laʻanat|ʹukhtahaa,|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓad|daa-rakoo|feehaa|jameeʻañ|Q̣aalat|ʹukh-raahum|liʹoolaahum|Rabbanaa|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹaḍal-loonaa|faʹaatihim|ʻaẓaabañ|ḍiʻfam|minan|Naar.|Q̣aala|likulliñ|ḍiʻfuñw|walaakil|laa|taʻlamoon."
7,39,"Wa-q̣aalat|ʹoolaahum|liʹukhraahum|famaa|kaana|lakum|ʻalaynaa|miñ|faḍliñ|faẓooq̣ul|ʻaẓaaba|bimaa|kuñtum|taksiboon."
7,40,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wastakbaroo|ʻanhaa|laa-|tufattaḥu|lahum|ʹabwaabus|samaaaʹi|wa-laa|yad-khuloonal|Jannata|ḥattaa|yalijal|jamalu|fee|sammil|khiyaaṭ:|wa-kaẓaalika|najzil|mujrimeen."
7,41,"Lahum|miñ|Jahannama|mihaaduñw|wamiñ|faw-q̣ihim|g̣awaash:|wakaẓaalika|najziz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
7,42,"Wal-laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|waʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|laa-|nukallifu|nafsan|ʹillaa|wusʻahaaa,|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannati|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
7,43,"Wanazaʻnaa|maa-|fee|ṣudoorihim|min|g̣illiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥ-tihimul|ʹanhaar;|wa-q̣aalul|Ḥamdu|lil-laahil|laẓee|hadaanaa|lihaaẓaa:|wa-maa|kunnaa|linahtadiya|law-laaa|ʹan|hadaanal|laah.|Laq̣ad|jaaaʹat|rusulu|Rabbinaa|bilḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-noodooo|ʹañ|til-kumul|Jannatu|ʹooris̤tumoohaa|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
7,44,"Wa-naadaaa|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannati|ʹAṣḥaaban|Naari|ʹañ|q̣ad|wajadnaa|maa-|waʻadanaa|Rabbunaa|ḥaq̣q̣añ|fahal|wajattum|maa|waʻada|Rabbukum|ḥaq̣q̣aa?|Q̣aaloo|naʻam.|Faʹaẓẓana|Muʹaẓẓinum|baynahum|ʹal|laʻnatul|laahi|ʻalaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen;―"
7,45,"ʹAllaẓeena|yaṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-yabg̣oonahaa|ʻiwajaa:|wa-hum̃|bil-ʹAakhirati|kaafiroon."
7,46,"Wa-baynahumaa|ḥijaab.|Wa-ʻalal|ʹAʻRAAFI|rijaaluñy|yaʻrifoona|kullam|biseemaahum.|Wa-naadaw|ʹAṣḥaabal|Jannati|ʹañ|Salaamun|ʻalaykum:|lam|yad-khuloohaa|wa-hum|yaṭmaʻoon."
7,47,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ṣurifat|ʹabṣaaruhum|tilq̣aaaʹa|ʹAṣḥaabin|Naari|q̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|laa-|tajʻalnaa|maʻal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
7,48,"Wa-naadaaa|ʹAṣḥaabul|ʹAʻRAAFI|rijaalañy|yaʻrifoonahum̃|biseemaahum|q̣aaloo|maaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻañkum|jamʻukum|wa-maa|kuñtum|tastakbiroon?"
7,49,"ʹA-haaaʹulaaaʹil|laẓeena|ʹaq̣samtum|laa-|yanaaluhumul|laahu|biraḥmah?|ʹUdkhulul|Jannata|laa-|khawfun|ʻalaykum|wa-laaa|ʹañtum|taḥ-zanoon."
7,50,"Wa-naadaaa|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|ʹAṣḥaabal|Jannati|ʹan|ʹafeeḍoo|ʻalaynaa|minal|maaaʹi|ʹaw|mimmaa|razaq̣akumul|laah.|Q̣aalooo|ʹinnal|laaha|ḥarramahumaa|ʻalal|kaafireen."
7,51,"ʹAllazeenat|takhaẓoo|deenahum|lahwañw|walaʻibañw|wag̣arrathumul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa.|Fal-yawma|nañsaahum|kamaa|nasoo|liq̣aaaʹa|yawmihim|haaẓaa|wa-maa|kaanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|yajḥadoon."
7,52,"Wa-laq̣ad|jiʹnaahum̃|bi-Kitaabiñ|faṣṣalnaahu|ʻalaa|ʻilmin|hudañw|waraḥmatal|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
7,53,"Hal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillaa|taʹweelah?|Yawma|yaʹtee|taʹweeluhoo|yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|nasoohu|miñ|q̣ablu|q̣ad|jaaaʹat|rusulu|Rabbinaa|bilḥaq̣q̣.|Fahal|lanaa|miñ|shufaʻaaaʹa|fayashfaʻoo|lanaaa|ʹaw|nuraddu|fanaʻmala|g̣ayral|laẓee|kunnaa|naʻmal?|Q̣ad|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
7,54,"ʹInna|Rabbakumul|laahul|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|fee|sittati|ʹayyaamiñ|s̤ummas|tawaa|ʻalal|ʻarsh.|Yug̣shil|laylan|nahaara|yaṭlubuhoo|ḥas̤ees̤añw|washshamsa|wal-q̣amara|wan-nujooma|musakh-Kharaatim|biʹamrih.|ʹAlaa|lahul|Khalq̣u|wal-ʹAmr.|Tabaarakal|laahu|Rabbul|ʻAalameen!"
7,55,"ʹUdʻoo|Rabbakum|taḍarruʻañw|wakhufyah:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yuḥibbul|muʻtadeen."
7,56,"Wa-laa|tufsidoo|fil|ʹarḍi|baʻda|ʹiṣlaaḥihaa|wadʻoohu|khawfañw|waṭamaʻaa:|ʹinna|Raḥmatal|laahi|q̣areebum|minal|Muḥsineen."
7,57,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|yursilur|riyaaḥa|bushram|bayna|yaday|raḥmatih:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaq̣allat|saḥaabañ|s̤iq̣aalañ|suq̣naahu|libaladim|mayyitiñ|faʹañzalnaa|bihil|maaaʹa|faʹakhrajnaa|bihee|miñ|kullis̤|s̤amaraat.|Kaẓaalika|nukhrijul|mawtaa|laʻallakum|taẓakkaroon."
7,58,"Walbaladuṭ|ṭayyibu|yakhruju|nabaatuhoo|biʹiẓni|Rabbih:|wallaẓee|khabus̤a|laa-|yakhruju|ʹillaa|nakidaa.|Kaẓaalika|nuṣarriful|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yashkuroon."
7,59,"Laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Nooḥan|ʹilaa|q̣awmihee|faq̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|ʹInneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|ʻaẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
7,60,"Q̣aalal|malaʹu|miñ|q̣aw-miheee|ʹinnaa|lanaraaka|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
7,61,"Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|laysa|bee|ḍalaalatuñw|walaakinnee|Rasoolum|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
7,62,"ʹUballig̣ukum|risaalaati|Rabbee|wa-ʹañṣaḥu|lakum|wa-ʹaʻlamu|minal|laahi|maa-|laa-|taʻlamoon."
7,63,"ʹAwaʻajibtum|ʹañ|jaaaʹakum|ẓikrum|mir|Rabbikum|ʻalaa|rajulim|miñkum|liyuñẓirakum|wa-litattaq̣oo|wa-laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
7,64,"Fakaẓẓaboohu|faʹañjaynaahu|wallaẓeena|maʻahoo|fil|Fulki|wa-ʹag̣raq̣nal|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa.|ʹInnahum|kaanoo|q̣awman|ʻameen."
7,65,"Wa-ʹilaa|ʻAadin|ʹakhaahum|Hoodaa.|Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|ʹAfalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
7,66,"Q̣aalal|malaʹul|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|q̣awmiheee|innaa|lanaraaka|fee|safaahatiñw|waʹinnaa|lanaz̤̣unnuka|minal|kaaẓibeen."
7,67,"Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|laysa|bee|safaahatuñw|walaakinnee|Rasoolum|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
7,68,"ʹUballig̣ukum|risaalaati|Rabbee|wa-ʹana|lakum|naaṣiḥun|ʹameen."
7,69,"ʹAwaʻajibtum|ʹañ|jaaaʹakum|ẓikrum|mir|Rabbikum|ʻalaa|rajulim|miñkum|liyuñẓirakum?|Waẓkurooo|ʹiẓ|jaʻalakum|khulafaaaʹa|mim|baʻdi|q̣awmi|Nooḥiñw|Wazaadakum|fil|khalq̣i|basṭah.|Faẓkurooo|ʹaalaaaʹal|laahi|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
7,70,"Q̣aalooo|ʹajiʹtanaa|linaʻbudal|laaha|Waḥdahoo|Wanaẓara|maa-|kaana|yaʻbudu|ʹaabaaaʹunaa?|Faʹtinaa|bimaa|taʻidunaaa|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een!"
7,71,"Q̣aala|q̣ad|waq̣aʻa|ʻalaykum|mir|Rabbikum|rijsuñw|wag̣aḍab.|ʹAtujaadiloonanee|feee|ʹasmaaaʹiñ|sammaytumoohaaa|ʹañtum|wa-ʹaabaaaʹukum|maa|nazzalal|laahu|bihaa|miñ|sulṭaan?|Fañtaz̤̣irooo|ʹinnee|maʻakum|minal|muñtaz̤̣ireen."
7,72,"Faʹañjaynaahu|wallaẓeena|maʻahoo|biraḥmatim|minnaa|wa-q̣aṭaʻnaa|daabiral|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-maa|kaanoo|Muʹmineen."
7,73,"Wa-ʹilaa|S̤amooda|ʹakhaahum|Ṣaaliḥaa.|Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|Q̣ad|jaaaʹatkum̃|Bayyinatum|Mir|Rabbikum|Haaẓihee|Naaq̣atul|laahi|lakum|ʹAayatañ|faẓaroohaa|taʹkulʻ|feee|ʹarḍil|laahi|wa-laa|tamassoohaa|bisoooʹiñ|fayaʹkhuẓakum|aẓaabun|ʹaleem."
7,74,"Waẓkurooo|ʹiẓ|jaʻalakum|khulafaaaʹa|mim|baʻdi|ʻAadiñw|Wabawwaʹakum|fil|ʹarḍi|tatta-Khiẓoona|miñ|suhoolihaa|q̣uṣoorañw|watanḥitoonal|jibaala|buyootaa.|Faẓkurooo|ʹaalaaaʹal|laahi|wa-laa|taʻs̤aw|fil|ʹarḍi|mufsideen."
7,75,"Q̣aalal|malaʹul|laẓeenas|takbaroo|miñ|q̣awmihee|lillaẓeenas|tuḍʻifoo|liman|ʹaamana|minhum|ʹataʻlamoona|ʹanna|Ṣaliḥam|mursalum|mir|Rabbih?|Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|bimaaa|ʹursila|bihee|Muʹminoon."
7,76,"Q̣aalal|laẓeenas|takbarooo|ʹinnaa|billaẓeee|ʹaamañtum̃|bihee|kaafiroon."
7,77,"Faʻaq̣arun|Naaq̣ata|wa-ʻataw|ʻan|ʹamri|Rabbihim|wa-q̣aaloo|yaa-Ṣaaliḥuʹ|tinaa|bimaa|taʻidunaaa|ʹiñ|kuñta|minal|mursaleen."
7,78,"Faʹakhaẓathumur|rajfatu|faʹaṣbaḥoo|fee|daarihim|jaas̤imeen."
7,79,"Fatawallaa|ʻanhum|wa-q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|laq̣ad|ʹablag̣tukum|risaalata|Rabbee|wa-naṣaḥtu|lakum|wa-laakil|laa|tuḥibboonan|naaṣiḥeen."
7,80,"Wa-Looṭan|ʹiẓ|q̣aala|liq̣awmiheee|ʹataʹtoonal|faaḥishata|maa-|sabaq̣akum̃|bihaa|min|ʹaḥadim|minal|ʻaalameen?"
7,81,"ʹInnakum|lataʹtoonar|rijaala|shahwatam|miñ|doonin|nisaaaʹ.|Bal|ʹañtum|q̣awmum|musrifoon."
7,82,"Wa-maa|kaana|jawaaba|q̣awmiheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aalooo|ʹakhrijoohum|miñ|q̣aryatikum:|ʹinnahum|ʹunaasuñy|yataṭahharoon!"
7,83,"Faʹañjaynaahu|wa-ʹahlahooo|ʹillam|raʹatahoo|kaanat|minal|g̣aabireen."
7,84,"Wa-ʹamṭarnaa|ʻalayhim|maṭaraa:|fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mujrimeen!"
7,85,"Wa-ʹilaa|Madyana|ʹakhaahum|Shuʻaybaa.|Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|Q̣ad|jaaaʹatkum̃|Bayyinatum|mir|Rabbikum|faʹawful|kayla|walmeezaana|wa-laa|tabkhasun|naasa|ʹashyaaaʹahum|wa-laa|tufsidoo|fil|ʹarḍi|baʻda|ʹiṣlaaḥihaa:|ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
7,86,"Wa-laa|taq̣ʻudoo|bikulli|siraatiñ|tooʻidoona|wa-taṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|man|ʹaamana|bihee|wa-tabg̣oonahaa|ʻiwajaa.|Waẓ-kurooo|ʹiẓ|kuñtum|q̣aleelañ|fakas̤s̤arakum.|Wañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mufsideen."
7,87,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|ṭaaaʹifatum|miñkum|ʹaamanoo|billazeee|ʹursiltu|bihee|waṭaaaʹifatul|lam|yuʹminoo|faṣbiroo|ḥattaa|yaḥkumal|laahu|baynanaa:|wa-Huwa|Khayrul|Ḥaakimeen."
7,88,"Q̣aalal|malaʹul|laẓeenas|takbaroo|miñ|q̣awmihee|lanukhrijannaka|yaa-Shuʻaybu|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻaka|miñ|q̣aryatinaaa|ʹaw|lataʻoodunna|fee|millatinaa.|Q̣aala|ʹa-wa law|kunnaa|kaariheen?"
7,89,"Q̣adif|taraynaa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|ʹin|ʻudnaa|fee|millatikum̃|baʻda|ʹiẓ|najjaanal|laahu|minhaa.|Wa-maa|yakoonu|lanaaa|ʹan|naʻooda|feehaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yashaaaʹal|laahu|Rabbunaa.|Wasiʻa|Rabbunaa|kulla|shayʹin|ʻilmaa.|ʻAlal|laahi|tawakkalnaa.|Rabbanaf|taḥ|baynanaa|wa-bayna|q̣awminaa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹAñta|Khayrul|Faatiḥeen."
7,90,"Wa-q̣aalal|malaʹul|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|q̣awmihee|laʹinit|tabaʻtum|Shuʻayban|ʹinnakum|ʹiẓal|lakhaasiroon!"
7,91,"Faʹakhaẓathumur|rajfatu|faʹaṣbaḥoo|fee|daarihim|jaas̤imeen."
7,92,"ʹAllaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|Shuʻaybañ|kaʹal|lam|yag̣naw|feehal|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|Shuʻaybañ|kaanoo|humul|khaasireen!"
7,93,"Fatawallaa|ʹanhum|wa-q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|laq̣ad|ʹablag̣tukum|risaalaati|Rabbee|wa-naṣaḥtu|lakum;|fakayfa|ʹaasaa|ʻalaa|q̣awmiñ|kaafireen."
7,94,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|fee|q̣aryatim|min|nabiyyin|ʹillaaa|ʹakhaẓnaaa|ʹahlahaa|bil-baʹsaaaʹi|waḍḍarraaaʹi|laʻallahum|yaḍḍarraʻoon."
7,95,"S̤umma|baddalnaa|makaanas|sayyiʹatil|ḥasanata|ḥattaa|ʻafaw|Waq̣aaloo|q̣ad|massa|ʹaabaaaʹanaḍ|ḍarraaaʹu|wassarraaaʹu|faʹakhaẓnaahum̃|bag̣tatañw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon."
7,96,"Wa-law|ʹanna|ʹahlal|q̣uraaa|ʹaamanoo|wattaq̣aw|lafataḥnaa|ʻalayhim|barakaatim|minas|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-laakiñ|kaẓẓaboo|faʹakhaẓnaahum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
7,97,"ʹA-faʹamina|ahlul|q̣uraaa|ʹañy|yaʹtiyahum|baʹsunaa|bayaatañw|wahum|naaaʹimoon?"
7,98,"ʹA-waʹamina|ʹahlul|q̣uraaa|ʹañy|yaʹtiyahum|baʹsunaa|ḍuḥañw|wahum|yalʻaboon?"
7,99,"ʹA-faʹaminoo|makral|laaḥ?|Falaa|yaʹmanu|makral|laahi|ʹillal|q̣awmul|khaasiroon!"
7,100,"ʹA-walam|yahdi|lillaẓeena|yaris̤oonal|ʹarḍa|mim|baʻdi|ʹahlihaaa|ʹal|law|nashaaaʹu|ʹaṣabnaahum̃|biẓunoobihim,|wa-naṭbaʻu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|fahum|laa-|yasmaʻoon?"
7,101,"Tilkal|q̣uraa|naq̣uṣṣu|ʻalayka|min|ʹambaaaʹihaa.|Wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹathum|rusuluhum̃|bil-Bayyinaat:|famaa|kaanoo|liyuʹminoo|bimaa|kaẓẓaboo|miñ|q̣abl.|Kaẓaalika|yaṭbaʻul|laahu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobil|kaafireen."
7,102,"Wa-maa|wajadnaa|liʹaks̤arihim|min|ʻahd.|Wa-ʹiñw|wajadnaaa|ʹaks̤arahum|lafaasiq̣een."
7,103,"S̤umma|baʻas̤naa|mim|baʻdihim|Moosaa|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹihee|faz̤̣alamoo|bihaa:|fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mufsideen."
7,104,"Wa-q̣aala|Moosaa|Yaa- -Firʻawnu|ʹinnee|Rasoolum|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
7,105,"Ḥaq̣eeq̣un|ʻalaaa|ʹal|laaa|ʹaq̣oola|ʻalal|laahi|ʹillal|ḥaq̣q̣.|Q̣ad|jiʹtukum̃|bi-Bayyinatim|mir|Rabbikum|faʹarsil|maʻiya|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel."
7,106,"Q̣aala|ʹiñ|kuñta|jiʹta|biʹAayatiñ|faʹti|bihaaa|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een."
7,107,"Faʹalq̣aa|ʻAṣaahu|faʹiẓaa|hiya|s̤uʻbaanum|mubeen!"
7,108,"Wa-nazaʻa|yadahoo|faʹiẓaa|hiya|bayḍaaaʹu|linnaaz̤̣ireen!"
7,109,"Q̣aalal|malaʹu|miñ|q̣awmi|Firʻawna|ʹinna|haaẓaa|lasaaḥirun|ʻaleem."
7,110,"Yureedu|ʹañy|yukhrijakum|min|ʹarḍikum:|famaaẓaa|taʹmuroon?"
7,111,"Q̣aalooo|ʹarjih|wa-ʹakhaahu|wa-arsil|fil|Madaaaʹini|ḥaashireena."
7,112,"Yaʹtooka|bikulli|saaḥirin|ʻaleem."
7,113,"Wa-jaaaʹas|saḥaratu|Firʻawna|q̣aalooo|ʹinna|lanaa|laʹajran|ʹiñ|kunnaa|naḥnul|g̣aalibeen."
7,114,"Q̣aala|naʻam|wa-ʹinnakum|laminal|muq̣arrabeen."
7,115,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹimmaaa|ʹañ|tulq̣iya|wa-ʹimmaaa|ʹan|nakoona|naḥnul|mulq̣een?"
7,116,"Q̣aala|ʹalq̣oo.|Falammaaa|ʹalq̣aw|saḥarooo|ʹaʻyunan|naasi|wastarhaboohum|wa-jaaaʹoo|bisiḥrin|ʻaz̤̣eem."
7,117,"Wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosaaa|ʹan|ʹalq̣i|ʻAṣaak:|faʹiẓaa|hiya|talq̣afu|maa-|yaʹfikoon!"
7,118,"Fawaq̣aʻal|ḥaq̣q̣u|wabaṭala|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
7,119,"Fag̣uliboo|hunaalika|wañq̣alaboo|ṣaag̣ireen."
7,120,"Wa-ʹulq̣iyas|saḥaratu|saajideen,"
7,121,"Q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|bi-Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
7,122,"Rabbi|Moosaa|wa-Haaroon."
7,123,"Q̣aala|Firʻawnu|ʹaamañtum̃|bihee|q̣abla|ʹan|ʹaaẓana|lakum?|ʹInna|haaẓaa|lamakrum|makartumoohu|fil|Madeenati|litukhrijoo|minhaaa|ʹahlahaa:|fasawfa|taʻlamoon."
7,124,"Laʹuq̣aṭṭiʻanna|ʹaydiyakum|wa-ʹarjulakum|min|khilaafiñ|s̤umma|laʹuṣallibannakum|ʹajmaʻeen."
7,125,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaaa|ʹilaa|Rabbinaa|muñq̣aliboon:"
7,126,"Wa-maa|tañq̣imu|minnaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹan|ʹaamannaa|biʹAayaati|Rabbinaa|lammaa|jaaaʹatnaa!|Rabbanaaa|ʹafrig̣|ʻalaynaa|ṣabrañw|watawaffanaa|Muslimeen!"
7,127,"Wa-q̣aalal|malaʹu|miñ|q̣awmi|Firʻawna|ʹataẓaru|Moosaa|wa-q̣awmahoo|liyufsidoo|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-yaẓaraka|wa-ʹaalihatak?|Q̣aala|sanuq̣attilu|ʹabnaaaʹahum|wa-nastaḥyee|nisaaaʹahum;|wa-ʹinnaa|fawq̣ahum|q̣aahiroon."
7,128,"Q̣aala|Moosaa|liq̣awmihis|taʻeenoo|billaahi|waṣbiroo.|ʹInnal|ʹarḍa|lillaahi|yooris̤uhaa|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadih;|wal-ʻaaq̣ibatu|lil-Muttaq̣een."
7,129,"Q̣aalooo|ʹooẓeenaa|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañ|taʹtiyanaa|wa-mim|baʻdi|maa-|jiʹtanaa.|Q̣aala|ʻasaa|Rabbukum|ʹañy|yuhlika|ʻaduwwakum|wa-yastakhlifakum|fil|ʹarḍi|fayañz̤̣ura|kayfa|taʻmaloon."
7,130,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹakhaẓnaaa|ʹaala|Firʻawna|bis-sineena|wa-naq̣ṣim|minas̤|s̤amaraati|laʻallahum|yaẓẓakkaroon."
7,131,"Faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹathumul|ḥasanatu|q̣aaloo|lanaa|ḥaazih:|wa-ʹiñ|tuṣibhum|sayyiʹatuñy|yaṭṭayyaroo|bi-Moosaa|wa-mam|maʻah.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnamaa|ṭaaaʹiruhum|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon!"
7,132,"Wa-q̣aaloo|mahmaa|taʹtinaa|bihee|min|ʹAayatil|litasḥaranaa|bihaa|famaa|naḥnu|laka|bi-Muʹmineen."
7,133,"Faʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhimuṭ|Ṭoofaana|wal-Jaraada|wal-Q̣ummala|waḍ-Ḍafaadiʻa|wad-Dama|ʹaayaatim|mufaṣṣalaat.|Fastakbaroo|wa-kaanoo|q̣awmam|mujrimeen."
7,134,"Wa-lammaa|waq̣aʻa|ʻalayhimur|rijzu|q̣aaloo|yaa-Moosad|ʻu|lanaa|Rabbaka|bimaa|ʻahida|ʻiñdaka|laʹiñ|kashafta|ʻannar|rijza|lanuʹminanna|laka|wa-lanursilanna|maʻaka|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel."
7,135,"Falammaa|kashafnaa|ʻanhumur|rijza|ʹilaaa|ʹajalin|hum̃|baalig̣oohu|ʹiẓaa|hum|yañkus̤oon!"
7,136,"Fañtaq̣amnaa|minhum|faʹag̣raq̣naahum|fil|yammi|biʹannahum|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-kaanoo|ʻanhaa|g̣aafileen."
7,137,"Wa-ʹawras̤nal|q̣awmal|laẓeena|kaanoo|yustaḍʻafoona|mashaariq̣al|ʹarḍi|wa-mag̣aari-bahal|latee|baaraknaa|feehaa.|Watammat|Kalimatu|Rabbikal|ḥusnaa|ʻalaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|bimaa|ṣabaroo;|wadammarnaa|maa-|kaana|yaṣnaʻu|Firʻawnu|wa-q̣awmuhoo|wa-maa|kaanoo|yaʻrishoon."
7,138,"Wa-jaawaznaa|bi-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelal|baḥra|faʹataw|ʻalaa|q̣awmiñy|yaʻkufoona|ʻalaaa|ʹaṣnaamil|lahum.|Q̣aaloo|yaa-Moosaj|ʻal|lanaaa|ʹilaahañ|kamaa|lahum|ʹaalihah.|Q̣aala|ʹinnakum|q̣awmuñ|tajhaloon."
7,139,"ʹInna|haaaʹulaaaʹi|mutabbarum|maa|hum|feehi|wa-baaṭilum|maa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
7,140,"Q̣aala|ʹa-g̣ayral|laahi|ʹabg̣eekum|ʹilaahañw|Wa-Huwa|faḍḍalakum|ʻalal|ʻaalameen?"
7,141,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹañjaynaakum|min|ʹAali|Firʻawna|yasoomoonakum|soooʹal|ʻaẓaabi,|yuq̣attiloona|ʹabnaaaʹakum|wa-yastaḥyoona|nisaaaʹakum:|wa-fee|ẓaalikum|balaaaʹum|mir|Rabbikum|ʻaz̤̣eem."
7,142,"Wa-waaʻadnaa|Moosaa|s̤alaas̤eena|laylatañw|waʹatmamnaahaa|biʻashriñ|fatamma|meeq̣aatu|Rabbiheee|ʹarbaʻeena|laylah.|Wa-q̣aala|Moosaa|liʹakheehi|Haaroonakh|lufnee|fee|q̣awmee|wa-ʹaṣliḥ|wa-laa|tattabiʻ|sabeelal|mufsideen."
7,143,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹa|Moosaa|limeeq̣aatinaa|wa-kallamahoo|Rabbuhoo|q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹarineee|ʹañz̤̣ur|ʹilayk.|Q̣aala|lañ|taraanee|wa-laakiniñ|z̤̣ur|ʹilal|jabali|faʹinis|taq̣arra|makaanahoo|fasawfa|taraanee.|Falammaa|tajallaa|Rabbuhoo|lil-Jabali|jaʻalahoo|dakkañw|wakharra|Moosaa|ṣaʻiq̣aa.|Falammaaa|ʹafaaq̣a|q̣aala|Subḥaanaka|tubtu|ʹilayka|wa-ʹana|ʹawwalul|Muʹmineen."
7,144,"Q̣aala|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹinniṣ|ṭafaytuka|ʻalan|naasi|bi-Risaalaatee|wa-bi-Kalaamee|fakhuẓ|maaa|ʹaataytuka|wa-kum|minash|shaakireen."
7,145,"Wa-katabnaa|lahoo|fil|ʹAlwaaḥi|miñ|kulli|shayʹim|mawʻiz̤̣a|watafṣeelal|likulli|shayʹ:|fakhuzhaa|biq̣uwwatiñw|waʹmur|q̣awmaka|yaʹkhuẓoo|biʹaḥsanihaa:|saʹureekum,|daaral|faasiq̣een."
7,146,"Saʹaṣrifu|ʻan|ʹAayaatiyal|laẓeena|yatakabbaroona|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣:|wa-ʹiñy|yaraw|kulla|ʹAayatil|laa|yuʹminoo|bihaa;|wa-ʹiñy|yaraw|sabeelar|rushdi|laa-|yattakhiẓoohu|Sabeelaa:|wa-ʹiñy|yaraw|sabeelal|g̣ayyi|yattakhiẓoohu|Sabeelaa.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-kaanoo|ʻanhaa|g̣aafileen."
7,147,"Wallaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-Liq̣aaaʹil|ʹAakhirati|ḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum.|Hal|yujzawna|ʹillaa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon?"
7,148,"Wattakhaẓa|q̣awmu|Moosaa|mim|baʻdihee|min|ḥuliyyihim|ʻijlañ|jasadal|lahoo|khuwaar.|ʹAlam|yaraw|ʹannahoo|laa-|yukallimuhum|wa-laa|yahdeehim|Sabeelaa?|ʹItta-Khaẓoohu|wa-kaanoo|z̤̣aalimeen."
7,149,"Wa-lammaa|suq̣iṭa|feee|ʹaydeehim|wa-ra|ʹawʹannahum|q̣ad|ḍalloo|q̣aaloo|laʹil|lam|yarḥamnaa|Rabbunaa|wa-yag̣fir|lanaa|lanakoonanna|minal|khaasireen."
7,150,"Wa-lammaa|rajaʻa|Moosaaa|ʹilaa|q̣awmihee|g̣aḍbaana|ʹasifañ|q̣aala|biʹsamaa|khalaftumoonee|mim|baʻdee.|ʹA-ʻajiltum|ʹamra|rabbikum?|Wa-ʹalq̣al|ʹAlwaaḥa|wa-ʹakhaẓa|biraʹsi|akheehi|yajurruhooo|ʹilayh.|Q̣aalab|na|umma|ʹinnal|q̣awmas|taḍʻafoonee|wa-kaadoo|yaq̣tuloonanee.|Falaa|tushmit|biyal|ʹaʻdaaaʹa|wa-laa|tajʻalnee|maʻal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
7,151,"Q̣aala|Rabbig̣|fir|lee|wa-liʹakhee|wa-ʹadkhilnaa|fee|Raḥmatika|wa-ʹAñta|ʹArḥamur|raaḥimeen!"
7,152,"ʹInnal|laẓeenat|takhaẓul|ʻijlasa|yanaaluhum|g̣aḍabum|mir|Rabbihim|waẓillatuñ|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa:|wa-kaẓaalika|najzil|muftareen."
7,153,"Wallaẓeena|ʻamilus|sayyiʹaati|s̤umma|taaboo|mim|baʻdihaa|wa-ʹaamanooo|ʹinna|Rabbaka|mim|baʻdihaa|la-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
7,154,"Wa-lammaa|sakata|ʻam|Moosal|g̣aḍabu|ʹakhaẓal|ʹAlwaaḥa|wa-fee|nuskhatihaa|Hudañw|Wa-Raḥmatul|lil-laẓeena|hum|li-Rabbihim|yarhaboon."
7,155,"Wakhtaara|Moosaa|q̣awmahoo|sabʻeena|rajulal|li-Meeq̣aatinaa:|falammaaa|ʹakhaẓathumur|rajfatu|q̣aala|Rabbi|law|shiʹta|ʹahlaktahum|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-ʹiyyaay.|ʹA-tuhlikunaa|bimaa|faʻalas|sufahaaaʹu|minnaa?|ʹIn|hiya|ʹillaa|fitnatuk.|Tuḍillu|bihaa|mañ|tashaaaʹu|wa-tahdee|mañ|tashaaaʹ.|ʹAñta|Waliyyunaa|fag̣fir|lanaa|warḥamnaa|wa-ʹAñta|Khayrul|g̣aafireen."
7,156,"Waktub|lanaa|fee|haaẓihid|dunyaa|ḥasanatañw|wafil|ʹAakhirati|ʹinnaa|hudnaaa|ʹilayk.|Q̣aala|ʻaẓaabeee|ʹuṣeebu|bihee|man|ʹashaaaʹ.|Wa-Raḥmatee|wasiʻat|kulla|shayʹ.|Fasaʹaktubuhaa|lil-laẓeena|yattaq̣oona|wa-yuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wal-laẓeena|hum̃|biʹAayaatinaa|yuʹminoon;―"
7,157,"ʹAllaẓeena|yattabiʻoonar|Rasoolan|Nabiyyal|ʹUmmiyyal|laẓee|yajidoonahoo|maktooban|ʻiñdahum|fit|Tawraati|wal-ʹIñjeel.|Yaʹmuruhum̃|bilmaʻroofi|wa-yanhaahum|ʻanil|muñkari|wa-yuḥillu|lahumuṭ|ṭayyibaati|wa-yuḥarrimu|ʻalayhimul|khabaaaʹis̤a|wa-yaḍaʻu|ʻanhum|ʹiṣrahum|wal-ʹag̣laalal|latee|kanat|ʻalayhim.|Fallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|bihee|wa-ʻazzaroohu|wa-naṣaroohu|wattabaʻun|Nooral|laẓeee|ʹuñzila|maʻahooo|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
7,158,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹinnee|Rasoolul|laahi|ʹilaykum|jameeʻanil|laẓee|lahoo|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Laaa|ʹillaa|ʹilaaha|Huwa|yuḥyee|wa-yumeet.|Faʹaaminoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihin|Nabiyyil|ʹUmmiyyil|laẓee|yuʹminu|billaahi|wa-Kalimaatihee|wattabiʻoohu|laʻallakum|tahtadoon."
7,159,"Wa-miñ|q̣awmi|Moosaaa|ʹummatuñy|yahdoona|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-bihee|yaʻdiloon."
7,160,"Wa-q̣aṭṭaʻnaahumus̤|natay|ʹasbaaṭan|ʻashrata|ʹumamaa.|Wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosaaa|ʹiẓis|tasq̣aahu|q̣awmuhooo|ʹaniḍ|rib|biʻaṣaakal|ḥajar.|Fambajasat|minhus̤|nataa|ʻashrata|ʻaynaa|q̣ad|ʻalima|kullu|ʹunaasim|mashrabahum.|Waz̤̣allalnaa|ʻalayhimul|g̣amaama|wa-ʹañzalnaa|ʻalayhimul|Manna|was-Salwaa:|kuloo|miñ|ṭayyibaati|maa-|razaq̣naakum.|Wa-maa|z̤̣alamoonaa|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
7,161,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣eela|lahumus|kunoo|haaẓihil|q̣aryata|wa-kuloo|minhaa|ḥays̤u|shiʹtum|wa-q̣ooloo|Ḥiṭṭatuñw|wadkhulul|baaba|sujjadan|nag̣fir|lakum|khaṭeeeʹaatikum:|sanazeedul|Muḥsineen."
7,162,"Fabaddalal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|minhum|q̣awlan|g̣ayral|laẓee|q̣eela|lahum|faʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhim|rijzam|minas|samaaaʹi|bimaa|kaanoo|yaz̤̣limoon."
7,163,"Wasʹalhum|ʻanil|q̣aryatil|latee|kaanat|ḥaaḍiratal|baḥr.|ʹIẓ|yaʻdoona|fis|Sabti|ʹiẓ|taʹteehim|ḥeetaanuhum|yawma|Sabtihim|shurraʻañw|wayawma|laa-|yasbitoona|laa-|taʹteehim.|Kaẓaalika|nabloohum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yafsuq̣oon."
7,164,"wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aalat|ʹummatum|minhum|lima|taʻiz̤̣oona|q̣aw-manil|laahu|muhlikuhum|ʹaw|muʻaẓẓibuhum|ʻazaabañ|shadeedaa?|Q̣aaloo|maʻẓiratan|ʹilaa|Rabbikum|wa-laʻallahum|yattaq̣oon."
7,165,"Falammaa|nasoo|maa-|ẓukkiroo|biheee|ʹañjaynal|laẓeena|yanhawna|ʻanis|soooʹi|wa-ʹakhaẓnal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|biʻaẓaabim|baʹeesim|bimaa|kaanoo|yafsuq̣oon."
7,166,"Falammaa|ʻataw|ʻam|maa|nuhoo|ʻanhu|q̣ulnaa|lahum|koonoo|q̣iradatan|khaasiʹeen."
7,167,"Wa-ʹiẓ|taʹaẓẓana|Rabbuka|layabʻas̤anna|ʻalayhim|ʹilaa|yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|mañy|yasoomuhum|soooʹal|ʻaẓaab.|ʹInna|rabbaka|la-Sareeʻul|ʻiq̣aabi|wa-ʹinnahoo|la-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
7,168,"Wa-q̣aṭṭaʻnaahum|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹumamaa.|Min-humuṣ|ṣaaliḥoona|wa-minhum|doona|ẓaalik.|Wa-balawnaahum̃|bil-ḥasanaati|was-sayyiʹaati|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
7,169,"Fakhalafa|mim|baʻdihim|khalfuñw|waris̤ul|Kitaaba|yaʹkhuẓoona|ʻaraḍa|haaẓal|ʹadnaa|wa-yaq̣ooloona|sayug̣faru|lanaa.|Wa-ʹiñy|yaʹtihim|ʻaraḍum|mis̤luhoo|yaʹkhuẓooh.|ʹAlam|Yuʹkhaẓ|ʻalayhim|Mees̤aaq̣ul|Kitaabi|ʹal|laa|yaq̣ooloo|ʻalal|laahi|ʹillal|ḥaq̣q̣a|wadarasoo|maa-|feeh?|Wad-Daarul|ʹAakhiratu|khayrul|lil-laẓeena|yattaq̣oon.|ʹAfalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
7,170,"Wallaẓeena|yumassikoona|bil-Kitaabi|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|ʹinnaa|laa-|nuḍeeʻu|ʹajral|Muṣliḥeen."
7,171,"Wa-ʹiẓ|nataq̣nal|Jabala|fawq̣ahum|kaʹannahoo|z̤̣ullatuñw|waz̤̣annooo|ʹannahoo|waaq̣iʻum|bihim:|khuẓoo|maaa|ʹaataynaakum̃|biq̣uwwatiñw|waẓkuroo|maa-|feehi|laʻallakum|tattaq̣oon."
7,172,"Wa-ʹiẓ|akhaẓa|Rabbuka|mim|Baneee|ʹaadama|miñ|z̤̣uhoorihim|ẓurriyyatahum|wa-ʹashhadahum|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim:|ʹAlastu|bi-Rabbikum?|Q̣aaloo|Balaa|shahidnaa!|ʹAñ|taq̣ooloo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|ʻan|haaẓaa|g̣aafileen:"
7,173,"ʹAw|taq̣oolooo|ʹinnamaaa|ʹashraka|ʹaabaaaʹunaa|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-kunnaa|ẓurriyyatam|mim|baʻdihim:|ʹa-fa-tuhlikunaa|bimaa|faʻalal|mubṭiloon."
7,174,"Wa-kaẓaalika|nufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|wa-laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
7,175,"Watlu|ʻalayhim|naba|ʹallaẓeee|ʹaataynaahu|ʹaayaatinaa|fañsalakha|minhaa|faʹatba|ʻahush-Shayṭaanu|fakaana|minal|g̣aaween."
7,176,"Wa-law|shiʹnaa|larafaʻnaahu|bihaa|walaakinnahooo|ʹakhlada|ʹilal|ʹarḍi|wattabaʻa|hawaah.|Famas̤aluhoo|kamas̤alil|kalb:|ʹiñ|taḥmil|ʻalayhi|yalhas̤|ʹaw|tatrukhu|yalhas̤.|Ẓaalika|mas̤alul|q̣awmil|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa.|Faq̣ṣuṣil|q̣aṣaṣa|laʻallahum|yatafakkaroon."
7,177,"Saaaʹa|mas̤alanil|q̣awmul|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-ʹañfusahum|kaanoo|yaz̤̣limoon."
7,178,"Mañy|yahdil|laahu|fahuwal|muhtadee:|wa-mañy|yuḍlil|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
7,179,"Wa-laq̣ad|ẓaraʹnaa|lijahannama|kas̤eeram|minal|jinni|wal-ʹiñs:|lahum|q̣uloobul|laa|yafq̣ahoona|bihaa,|wa-lahum|ʹaʻyunul|laa|yubṣiroona|bihaa,|wa-lahum|ʹaaẓaanul|laa|yasmaʻoona|bihaa.|ʹUlaaaʹika|kal-ʹanʻaami|bal|hum|ʹaḍall:|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|g̣aafiloon."
7,180,"Wa-lillaahil|ʹAsmaaaʹul|Ḥusnaa|fadʻoohu|bihaa.|Waẓarul|laẓeena|yulḥidoona|feee|ʹAsmaaaʹih:|sayujzawna|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
7,181,"Wa-mimman|khalaq̣naaa|ʹummatuñy|yahdoona|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-bihee|yaʻdiloon."
7,182,"Wallaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|sanastadrijuhum|min|ḥays̤u|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
7,183,"Wa-ʹumlee|lahum:|ʹinna|kaydee|mateen."
7,184,"ʹAwalam|yatafakkaroo,|Maa-|bi-Ṣaaḥibihim|miñ|jinnah;|ʹin|huwa|ʹillaa|naẓeerum|mubeen."
7,185,"ʹAwalam|yañz̤̣uroo|fee|Malakootis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|khalaq̣al|laahu|miñ|shayʹiñw|waʹan|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yakoona|q̣adiq̣|taraba|ʹajaluhum?|fabiʹayyi|Ḥadees̤im|baʻdahoo|yuʹminoon?"
7,186,"Mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|falaa|haadiya|lah:|wa-yaẓaruhum|fee|ṭug̣yaanihim|yaʻmahoon."
7,187,"Yasʹaloonaka|ʻanis|Saaʻati|ʹayyaana|mursaahaa?|Q̣ul|ʹinnamaa|ʻilmuhaa|ʻiñda|Rabbee.|Laa-|yujalleehaa|liwaq̣tihaaa|ʹillaa|Hoo.|S̤aq̣ulat|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Laa-|taʹteekum|ʹillaa|bag̣tah.|Yasʹaloonaka|kaʹannaka|ḥafiyyun|ʻanhaa.|Q̣ul|ʹinnamaa|ʻilmuhaa|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
7,188,"Q̣ul|laaa|ʹamliku|linafsee|nafʻañw|walaa|ḍarran|ʹillaa|maa-|shaaaʹal|laah.|Wa-law|kuñtu|ʹaʻlamul|g̣ayba|lastaks̤artu|minal|khayri|wa-maa|massaniyas|soooʹ.|ʹIn|ʹana|ʹillaa|naẓeeruñw|wabasheerul|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
7,189,"Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|min|nafsiñw|waaḥidatiñw|wajaʻala|minhaa|zawjahaa|liyaskuna|ʹilayhaa.|Falammaa|tag̣ashshaahaa|ḥamalat|ḥamlan|khafeefañ|famarrat|bih.|Falammaaa|ʹas̤q̣alad|daʻawal|laaha|Rabbahumaa|laʹin|ʹaataytanaa|ṣaaliḥal|lanakoonanna|minash|Shaakireen."
7,190,"Falammaaa|ʹaataahumaa|ṣaaliḥañ|jaʻalaa|lahoo|shurakaaaʹa|feemaaa|ʹaataahumaa.|Fataʻaalal|laahu|ʻammaa|yushrikoon."
7,191,"ʹA-yushrikoona|Maa|laa-|yakhluq̣u|shayʹañw|wahum|yukhlaq̣oon?"
7,192,"Wa-laa|yastaṭeeʻoona|lahum|naṣrañw|walaaa|ʹañfusahum|yañṣuroon."
7,193,"Wa-ʹiñ|tadʻoohum|ʹilal|hudaa|laa-|yattabiʻookum.|Sawaaaʹun|ʻalaykum|ʹa-daʻawtumoohum|ʹam|ʹañtum|ṣaamitoon."
7,194,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʻibaadun|ʹams̤aalukum|fadʻoohum|fal-yastajeeboo|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
7,195,"ʹAlahum|ʹarjuluñy|yamshoona|bihaaa|ʹam|lahum|ʹaydiñy|yabṭishoona|bihaaa|ʹam|lahum|ʹaʻyunuñy|yubṣiroona|bihaaa|ʹam|lahum|ʹaaẓaanuñy|yasmaʻoona|bihaa?|Q̣ulid|ʻoo|shurakaaaʹakum|s̤umma|keedooni|falaa|tuñz̤̣iroon."
7,196,"ʹInna|Waliyyal|laahul|laẓee|nazzalal|Kitaaba|wa-Huwa|yatawallaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
7,197,"Wallaẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|laa-|yastaṭeeʻoona|naṣrakum|wa-laaa|ʹañfusahum|yañṣuroon."
7,198,"Wa-ʹiñ|tadʻoohum|ʹilal|hudaa|laa-|yasmaʻoo.|Wa-taraahum|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹilayka|Wahum|laa-|yubṣiroon."
7,199,"Khuẓil|ʻafwa|waʹmur|bilʻurfi|wa-ʹaʻriḍ|ʻanil|jaahileen."
7,200,"Wa-ʹimmaa|yañzag̣annaka|minash|Shayṭaani|nazg̣uñ|fastaʻiẓ|billaah;|ʹinnahoo|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
7,201,"ʹInnal|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|ʹiẓaa|massahum|ṭaaaʹifum|minash|Shayṭaani|taẓakkaroo|faʹiẓaa|hum|mubṣiroon!"
7,202,"Wa-ʹikhwaanuhum|yamuddoonahum|fil|g̣ayyi|s̤umma|laa-|yuq̣ṣiroon."
7,203,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|lam|taʹtihim̃|biʹAayatiñ|q̣aaloo|law-laj|tabaytahaa?|Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹattabiʻu|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayya|mir|Rabbee.|Haaẓaa|Baṣaaaʹiru|mir|Rabbikum|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatul|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
7,204,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣uriʹal|Q̣urʹaanu|fastamiʻoo|lahoo|wa-añṣitoo|laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
7,205,"Waẓkur|Rabbaka|fee|nafsika|taḍarruʻañw|wakheefatañw|wadoonal|jahri|minal|q̣awli|bilg̣uduwwi|wal-ʹaaṣaali|wa-laa|takum|minal|g̣aafileen."
7,206,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʻiñda|Rabbika|laa-|yastakbiroona|ʻan|ʻibaadatihee|wa-yusabbiḥoonahoo|wa-lahoo|yasjudoon,"
8,1,"Yasʹaloonaka|ʻanil|ʹAÑ-FAAL.|Q̣ulil|ʹAñfaalu|lillaahi|war-Rasool:|Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṣliḥoo|ẓaata|baynikum:|wa-ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-Rasoolahooo|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
8,2,"ʹInnamal|Muʹminoonal|laẓeena|ʹizaa|ẓukiral|laahu|wajilat|q̣uloobuhum|wa-ʹiẓaa|tuliyat|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatuhoo|zaadathum|ʹeemaanañw|Waʻalaa|Rabbihim|yatawakkaloon;"
8,3,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuq̣eemoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|yuñfiq̣oon:"
8,4,"ʹUlaaaʹika|humul|Muʹminoona|ḥaq̣q̣aa;|lahum|darajaatun|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|wa-mag̣firatuñw|warizq̣uñ|kareem."
8,5,"Kamaaa|ʹakhrajaka|Rabbuka|mim|baytika|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹinna|fareeq̣am|minal|Muʹmineena|lakaarihoon,"
8,6,"Yujaadiloonaka|fil|Ḥaq̣q̣i|baʻdamaa-|tabayyana|kaʹannamaa|yusaaq̣oona|ʹilal|mawti|wa-hum|yañz̤̣uroon."
8,7,"Wa-ʹiẓ|yaʻidukumul|laahu|ʹiḥdaṭ|ṭaaaʹifatayni|ʹannahaa|lakum|wa-tawaddoona|ʹanna|g̣ayra|ẓaatish|shawkati|takoonu|lakum|wa-yureedul|laahu|ʹañy|yuḥiq̣q̣al|Ḥaq̣q̣a|bi-Kalimaatihee|wa-yaq̣ṭaʻa|daabiral|kaafireen;―"
8,8,"Liyuḥiq̣q̣al|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-yubṭilal|Baaṭila|wa-law|karihal|mujrimoon."
8,9,"ʹIẓ|tastag̣ees̤oona|Rabbakum|fastajaaba|lakum|ʹannee|mumiddukum̃|biʹalfim|minal|malaaaʹikati|murdifeen."
8,10,"Wa-maa|jaʻalahul|laahu|ʹillaa|bushraa|wa-litaṭmaʹinna|bihee|q̣uloobukum.|Wa-man|naṣru|ʹillaa|min|ʻiñdil|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
8,11,"ʹIẓ|yug̣ashsheekumun|nuʻaasa|ʹamanatam|minhu|wa-yunazzilu|ʻalaykum|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹal|liyuṭahhirakum̃|bihee|wa-yuẓhiba|ʻañkum|rijzash|Shayṭaani|wa-liyarbiṭa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobikum|wa-yus̤abbita|bihil|ʹaq̣daam."
8,12,"ʹIẓ|yooḥee|Rabbuka|ʹilal|malaaaʹikati|ʹannee|maʻakum|fas̤abbitul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo.|Saʹulq̣ee|fee|q̣uloobil|laẓeena|kafarur|ruʻba|faḍriboo|fawq̣al|ʹaʻnaaq̣i|waḍriboo|minhum|kulla|banaan."
8,13,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|shaaaq̣q̣ul|laaha|wa-Rasoolah:|wa-mañy|yushaaq̣iq̣il|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|faʹinnal|laaha|shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
8,14,"Ẓaalikum|faẓooq̣oohu|wa-ʹanna|lilkaafireena|ʻaẓaaban|Naar."
8,15,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|laq̣eetumul|laẓeena|kafaroo|zaḥfañ|falaa|tuwalloohumul|ʹadbaar."
8,16,"Wa-mañy|yuwallihim|yawmaʹiẓiñ|duburahooo|ʹillaa|mutaḥarrifal|liq̣itaalin|ʹaw|mutaḥayyizan|ʹilaa|fiʹatiñ|faq̣ad|baaaʹa|big̣aḍabim|minal|laahi|wa-maʹwaahu|Jahannam,―|wa-biʹsal|maṣeer!"
8,17,"Falam|taq̣tuloohum|wa-laakinnal|laaha|q̣atalahum.|Wa-maa|ramayta|ʹiẓ|ramayta|wa-laakinnal|laaha|ramaa:|wa-liyubliyal|Muʹmineena|minhu|balaaaʹan|ḥasanaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
8,18,"Ẓaalikum|wa-ʹannal|laaha|moohinu|kaydil|kaafireen."
8,19,"ʹIñ|tastaftiḥoo|faq̣ad|jaaaʹakumul|fatḥ.|Wa-ʹiñ|tañtahoo|fahuwa|khayrul|lakum.|Wa-ʹiñ|taʻoodoo|naʻud.|Wa-lañ|tug̣niya|ʻañkum|fiʹatukum|shayʹañw|walaw|kas̤urat|wa-ʹannal|laaha|maʻal|Muʹmineen!"
8,20,"Yaaaʹayyuhaal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wa-laa|tawallaw|ʻanhu|wa-ʹañtum|tasmaʻoon."
8,21,"Wa-laa|takoonoo|kallaẓeena|q̣aaloo|samiʻnaa|wahum|laa-|yasmaʻoon:"
8,22,"ʹInna|sharrad|dawaaabbi|ʻiñdal|laahiṣ|ṣummul|bukmul|laẓeena|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon."
8,23,"Wa-law|ʻalimal|laahu|feehim|khayral|laʹasmaʻahum:|wa-law|ʹasmaʻahum|latawallaw|wahum|muʻriḍoon."
8,24,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanus|tajeeboo|lillaahi|wa-lir-Rasooli|ʹiẓaa|daʻaakum|limaa|yuḥyeekum:|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|yaḥoolu|baynal|marʹi|wa-q̣albihee|wa-ʹannahooo|ʹilayhi|tuḥsharoon."
8,25,"Wattaq̣oo|fitnatal|laa|tuṣeebannal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|miñkum|khaaaṣṣah:|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
8,26,"Waẓkurooo|ʹiẓ|ʹañtum|q̣aleelum|mustaḍʻafoona|fil|ʹarḍi|takhaafoona|ʹañy|yatakhaṭṭafakumun|naasu|faʹaawaakum|wa-ʹayyadakum̃|binaṣrihee|wa-razaq̣akum|minaṭ|ṭayyibaati|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
8,27,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|takhoonul|laaha|war-Rasoola|wa-takhoonooo|ʹamaanaatikum|wa-ʹañtum|taʻlamoon."
8,28,"Waʻlamooo|ʹannamaaa|ʹamwaalukum|wa-ʹawlaadukum|fitnatuñw|waʹannal|laaha|ʻiñdahooo|ʹajrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
8,29,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiñ|tattaq̣ul|laaha|yajʻal|lakum|Furq̣aanañw|Wayukaffir|ʻañkum|sayyiʹaatikum|wa-yag̣fir|lakum.|Wallaahu|Ẓul|Faḍlil|ʻaz̤̣eem."
8,30,"Wa-ʹiẓ|yamkuru|bikal|laẓeena|kafaroo|liyus̤bitooka|ʹaw|yaq̣tulooka|ʹaw|yukhrijook.|Wa-yamkuroona|wa-yamkurul|laah:|wallaahu|Khayrul|maakireen."
8,31,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|q̣aaloo|q̣ad|samiʻnaa|law|nashaaaʹu|laq̣ulnaa|mis̤la|haaẓaaa|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleen."
8,32,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aalul|laahumma|ʹiñ|kaana|haaẓaa|huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣a|min|ʻiñdika|faʹamṭir|ʻalaynaa|ḥijaaratam|minas|samaaaʹi|ʹawiʹ|tinaa|biʻaẓaabin|ʹaleem."
8,33,"Wa-maa|kaanal|laahu|liyuʻaẓẓibahum|wa-ʹañta|feehim;|wa-maa|kaanal|laahu|muʻaẓẓibahum|wa-hum|yastag̣firoon."
8,34,"Wa-maa|lahum|ʹallaa|yuʻaẓẓibahumul|laahu|wa-hum|yaṣuddoona|ʻanil|Masjidil|Ḥaraami|wa-maa|kaanooo|ʹawliyaaaʹah?|ʹIn|ʹawliyaaaʹuhooo|ʹillal|Muttaq̣oona|walaakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
8,35,"Wa-maa|kaana|ṣalaatuhum|ʻiñdal|Bayti|ʹillaa|mukaaaʹañw|wataṣdiyah:|faẓooq̣ul|ʻaẓaaba|bimaa|kuñtum|takfuroon."
8,36,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|yuñfiq̣oona|ʹamwaalahum|liyaṣuddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah.|Fasayuñfiq̣oonahaa|s̤umma|takoonu|ʻalayhim|ḥasratañ|s̤umma|yug̣laboon.|Wal-laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹilaa|Jahannama|yuḥsharoon."
8,37,"Liyameezal|laahul|khabees̤a|minaṭ|ṭayyibi|wa-yajʻalal|khabees̤a|baʻḍahoo|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñ|fayarkumahoo|jameeʻañ|fayajʻalahoo|fee|jahannam.|ʹUlaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
8,38,"Q̣ul|lillaẓeena|kafarooo|ʹiñy|yañtahoo|yug̣far|lahum|maa|q̣ad|salaf;|wa-ʹiñy|yaʻoodoo|faq̣ad|maḍat|Sunnatul|ʹawwaleen."
8,39,"Wa-q̣aatiloohum|ḥattaa|laa-|takoona|fitnatuñw|wayakoonad|Deenu|kulluhoo|lillaah;|faʹiniñ|tahaw|faʹinnal|laaha|bimaa|yaʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
8,40,"Wa-ʹin|tawallaw|faʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|Mawlaakum―|Niʻmal|Mawlaa|wa-Niʻman|Naṣeer."
8,41,"Waʻlamooo|ʹannamaa|g̣animtum|miñ|shayʹiñ|faʹanna|lillaahi|khumusahoo|wa-lir-Rasooli|wa-liẓil|q̣urbaa|walyataamaa|walmasaakeeni|wabnis|sabeeli|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ʹaamañtum̃|billaahi|wa-maaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaa|ʻAbdinaa|Yawmal|Furq̣aani|Yawmal|taq̣al|jamʻaan.|Wal-laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
8,42,"ʹIẓ|ʹañtum̃|bilʻudwatid|dunyaa|wa-hum̃|bilʻudwatil|q̣uṣwaa|warrakbu|ʹasfala|miñkum.|Wa-law|tawaaʻattum|lakhtalaftum|fil|meeʻaadi|wa-laakil|liyaq̣ḍiyal|laahu|ʹamrañ|kaana|mafʻoolaa;|liyahlika|man|halaka|ʻam|Bayyinatiñw|Wayaḥyaa|man|ḥayya|ʻam|Bayyinah.|Wa-innal|laaha|la-Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
8,43,"ʹIẓ|yureekahumul|laahu|fee|manaamika|q̣aleelaa:|wa-law|ʹaraakahum|kas̤eeral|lafashiltum|wa-latanaazaʻtum|fil|ʹamri|wa-laakinnal|laaha|sallam:|ʹinnahoo|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
8,44,"Wa-ʹiẓ|yureekumoohum|ʹiẓil|taq̣aytum|feee|ʹaʻyunikum|q̣aleelañw|wayuq̣allilukum|feee|ʹaʻyunihim|liyaq̣ḍiyal|laahu|ʹamrañ|kaana|mafʻoolaa.|Wa-ʹilal|laahi|turjaʻul|ʹumoor."
8,45,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|laq̣eetum|fiʹatañ|fas̤butoo|waẓkurul|laaha|kas̤eeral|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon:"
8,46,"Wa-ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wa-laa|tanaazaʻoo|fatafshaloo|wa-taẓhaba|reeḥukum|waṣbiroo:|ʹinnal|laaha|maʻaṣ|Ṣaabireen."
8,47,"Wa-laa|takoonoo|kallaẓeena|kharajoo|miñ|diyaarihim̃|baṭarañw|wariʹaaaʹan|naasi|wa-yaṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah:|wallaahu|bimaa|yaʻmaloona|Muḥeeṭ."
8,48,"Wa-ʹiẓ|zayyana|lahumush|Shayṭaanu|ʹaʻmaalahum|Waq̣aala|laa-|g̣aaliba|lakumul|yawma|minan|naasi|wa-ʹinnee|jaarul|lakum.|Falammaa|taraaaʹatil|fiʹataani|nakaṣa|ʻalaa|ʻaq̣ibayhi|wa-q̣aala|ʹinnee|bareeeʹum|miñkum|ʹinneee|ʹaraa|Maa|laa-|tarawna|ʹinneee|ʹakhaaful|laah;|wallaahu|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
8,49,"ʹIẓ|yaq̣oolul|Munaafiq̣oona|wallaẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍun|g̣arra|haaaʹulaaaʹi|Deenuhum.|Wa-mañy|yatawakkal|ʻalal|laahi|faʹinnal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
8,50,"Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓ|yatawaffal|laẓeena|kafarul|malaaaʹikatu|yaḍriboona|wujoohahum|wa-ʹadbaarahum:|wa-ẓooq̣oo|ʻAẓaabal|ḥareeq̣!"
8,51,"Ẓaalika|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeekum|wa-ʹannal|laaha|laysa|biz̤̣allaamil|lil-ʻabeed:"
8,52,"Kadaʹbi|ʹAali|Firʻawna|wal-laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim:|kafaroo|biʹAayaatil|laahi|faʹakhaẓahumul|laahu|biẓunoobihim.|ʹInnal|laaha|Q̣awiyyuñ|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
8,53,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|lam|yakumu|g̣ayyiran|niʻmatan|ʹanʻamahaa|ʻalaa|q̣awmin|ḥattaa|yug̣ayyiroo|maa-|biʹañfusihim|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem:"
8,54,"Kadaʹbi|ʹAali|Firʻawna|wallaẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim:|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaati|Rabbihim|faʹahlaknaahum̃|biẓunoobihim|wa-ʹag̣raq̣naaa|ʹAala|Firʻawn:|wa-kulluñ|kaanoo|z̤̣aalimeen."
8,55,"ʹInna|sharrad|dawaaabbi|ʻiñdal|laahil|laẓeena|kafaroo|fahum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
8,56,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʻaahatta|min-hum|s̤umma|yañq̣uḍoona|ʻahdahum|fee|kulli|marratiñw|wahum|laa-|yattaq̣oon."
8,57,"Faʹimmaa|tas̤q̣afannahum|fil|ḥarbi|fasharrid|bihim|man|khalfahum|laʻallahum|yaẓẓakkaroon."
8,58,"Wa-ʹimmaa|takhaafanna|miñ|q̣awmin|khiyaanatañ|fambiẓ|ʹilayhim|ʻalaa|sawaaaʹ:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbul|khaaaʹineen."
8,59,"Wa-laa|yaḥsabannal|laẓeena|kafaroo|sabaq̣oo:|ʹinnahum|laa-|yuʻjizoon."
8,60,"Wa-ʹaʻiddoo|lahum|mas|taṭaʻtum|miñ|q̣uwwatiñw|wamir|ribaaṭil|khayli|turhiboona|bihee|ʻaduwwal|laahi|wa-ʻaduwwakum|wa-ʹaakhareena|miñ|doonihim,|laa-|taʻlamoonahu|mullaahu|yaʻlamuhum.|Wa-maa|tuñfiq̣oo|miñ|shayʹiñ|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|yuwaffa|ʹilaykum|waʹañtum|laa-|tuz̤̣lamoon."
8,61,"Wa-ʹiñ|janaḥoo|lissalmi|fajnaḥ|lahaa|wa-tawakkal|ʻalal|laah:|ʹinnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
8,62,"Wa-ʹiñy|yureedooo|ʹañy|yakhdaʻooka|faʹinna|ḥasbakal|laah.|Huwal|laẓeee|ʹayyadaka|binaṣrihee|wa-bil-Muʹmineen."
8,63,"Wa-ʹallafa|bayna|q̣uloobihim.|Law|ʹañfaq̣ta|maa-|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻam|maaa|ʹallafta|bayna|q̣uloobihim|wa-laakinnal|laaha|ʹallafa|baynahum;|ʹinnahoo|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
8,64,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|nabiyyu|ḥasbukal|lahu|wa-manit|tabaʻaka|minal|Muʹmineen."
8,65,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|ḥarriḍil|Muʹmineena|ʻalal|q̣itaal.|ʹIñy|yakum|miñkum|ʻishroona|ṣaabiroona|yag̣liboo|miʹatayn;|wa-ʹiñy|yakum|miñkum|miʹatuñy|yag̣libooo|ʹalfam|minal|laẓeena|kafaroo|biʹannahum|q̣awmul|laa|yafq̣ahoon."
8,66,"ʹAlʹaana|khaffafal|laahu|ʻañkum|wa-ʻalima|ʹanna|feekum|ḍaʻfaa.|Faʹiñy|yakum|miñkum|miʹatuñ|Ṣaabiratuñy|yag̣liboo|miʹatayn.|Wa-ʹiñy|yakum|miñkum|ʹalfuñy|yag̣libooo|ʹalfayni|biʹiẓnil|laah:|wallaahu|maʻaṣ|Ṣaabireen."
8,67,"Maa-|kaana|li-Nabiyyin|ʹañy|yakoona|lahooo|ʹasraa|ḥattaa|yus̤khina|fil|ʹarḍ.|Tureedoona|ʻaraḍad|dunyaa,|wallaahu|yureedul|ʹAakhirah:|wallaahu|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
8,68,"Law-laa|Kitaabum|minal|laahi|sabaq̣a|lamassakum|fee-maaa|ʹakhaẓtum|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
8,69,"Fakuloo|mimmaa|g̣animtum|ḥalaalañ|ṭayyibaa;|watta|q̣ullaah:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
8,70,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|q̣ul|limañ|feee|ʹaydeekum|minal|ʹasraaa|ʹiñy|yaʻlamil|laahu|fee|q̣uloobikum|khayrañy|yuʹtikum|khayram|mimmaaa|ʹukhiẓa|miñkum|wa-yag̣fir|lakum:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
8,71,"Wa-ʹiñy|yureedoo|khiyaanataka|faq̣ad|khaanul|laaha|miñ|q̣ablu|faʹamkana|minhum.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
8,72,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-haajaroo|wa-jaahadoo|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wallaẓeena|ʹaawaw|Wanaṣarooo|ʹulaaaʹika|baʻḍuhum|ʹawliyaaaʹu|baʻḍ.|Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-lam|yuhaajiroo|maa-|lakum|miñw|walaayatihim|miñ|shayʹin|ḥattaa|yuhaajiroo;|wa-ʹinis|tañṣarookum|fid|deeni|faʻalayku|munnaṣru|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|q̣awmim|baynakum|wa-baynahum|Mees̤aaq̣.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
8,73,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|baʻḍuhum|ʹawliyaaaʹu|baʻḍ:|ʹillaa|tafʻaloohu|takuñ|fitnatuñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-fasaaduñ|kabeer."
8,74,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-haajaroo|wa-jaahadoo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wallaẓeena|ʹaawaw|Wanaṣarooo|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Muʹminoona|ḥaq̣q̣aa:|lahum|mag̣firatuñw|warizq̣uñ|Kareem."
8,75,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|mim|baʻdu|wa-haajaroo|wa-jaahadoo|maʻakum|faʹulaaaʹika|miñkum.|Wa-ʹulul|ʹarḥaami|baʻḍuhum|ʹawlaa|bibaʻḍiñ|fee|Kitaabil|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
9,1,"BARAAAʹATUM|MINAL|LAAHI|wa-Rasooliheee|ʹilal|laẓeena|ʻaahattum|minal|Mushrikeen:―"
9,2,"Faseeḥoo|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹarbaʻata|ʹashhuriñw|waʻlamooo|ʹannakum|g̣ayru|muʻjizil|laahi|wa-ʹannal|laaha|mukhzil|kaafireen."
9,3,"Wa-ʹaẓaanum|minal|laahi|wa-Rasooliheee|ʹilan|naasi|yawmal|Ḥajjil|ʹAkbari|ʹannal|laaha|bareeeʹum|minal|mushrikeena|wa-Rasooluh.|Faʹiñ|tubtum|fahuwa|khayrul|lakum:|wa-ʹiñ|tawallaytum|faʻlamooo|ʹannakum|g̣ayru|muʻjizil|laah.|Wa-bashshiril|laẓeena|kafaroo|biʻaẓaabin|ʹaleem:"
9,4,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|ʻaahattum|minal|mushrikeena|s̤umma|lam|yañq̣uṣookum|shayʹañw|walam|yuz̤̣aahiroo|ʻalaykum|ʹaḥadañ|faʹatimmooo|ʹilayhim|ʻahdahum|ʹilaa|muddatihim:|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muttaq̣een."
9,5,"Faʹiẓañ|salakhal|ʹAshhurul|Ḥurumu|faq̣tulul|mushrikeena|ḥays̤u|wajattumoohum|wa-khuẓoohum|waḥṣuroohum|waq̣ʻudoo|lahum|kulla|marṣad.|Faʹiñ|taaboo|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatawuz|Zakaata|fakhalloo|sabeelahum:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
9,6,"Wa-ʹin|ʹaḥadum|minal|mushrikeenas|tajaaraka|faʹajirhu|ḥattaa|yasmaʻa|Kalaamal|laahi|s̤umma|ʹablig̣hu|maʹmanah.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣awmul|laa|yaʻlamoon."
9,7,"Kayfa|yakoonu|lilmushrikeena|ʻahdun|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-ʻiñda|Rasooliheee|ʹillal|laẓeena|ʻaahattum|ʻiñdal|Masjidil|Ḥaraam?|Famas|taq̣aamoo|lakum|fastaq̣eemoo|lahum:|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muttaq̣een."
9,8,"Kayfa|wa-ʹiñy|yaz̤̣haroo|ʻalaykum|laa-|yarq̣uboo|feekum|ʹillañw|Walaa|ẓimmah?|Yurḍoonakum̃|biʹafwaahihim|wa-taʹbaa|q̣uloobuhum;|wa-ʹaks̤aruhum|faasiq̣oon."
9,9,"ʹIshtaraw|biʹAayaatil|laahi|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelañ|faṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelih:|ʹinnahum|saaaʹa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
9,10,"Laa-|yarq̣uboona|fee|Muʹminin|ʹillañw|Walaa|ẓimmah.|Wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|muʻtadoon."
9,11,"Faʹiñ|taaboo|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatawuz|Zakaata|faʹikhwaanukum|fid|Deen:|wa-nufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
9,12,"Wa-ʹin|nakas̤ooo|ʹaymaanahum|mim|baʻdi|ʻahdihim|waṭaʻanoo|fee|Deenikum|faq̣aatilooo|ʹaʹimmatal|kufri|ʹinnahum|laaa|ʹaymaana|lahum|laʻallahum|yañtahoon."
9,13,"ʹAlaa|tuq̣aatiloona|q̣awman|nakas̤ooo|ʹaymaanahum|wa-hammoo|biʹikhraajir|Rasooli|wa-hum̃|badaʹookum|ʹawwala|marrah?|ʹAtakhshawnahum?|Fallaahu|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|ʹañ|takhshawhu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
9,14,"Q̣aatiloohum|yuʻaẓẓibhumul|laahu|biʹaydeekum|wa-yukhzihim|wa-yañṣurkum|ʻalayhim|wa-yashfi|ṣudoora|q̣awmim|Muʹmineen."
9,15,"Wa-yuẓhib|g̣ayz̤̣a|q̣uloobihim.|Wa-yatoobul|laahu|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹ;|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
9,16,"ʹAm|ḥasibtum|ʹañ|tutrakoo|wa-lammaa|yaʻlamil|laahul|laẓeena|jaahadoo|miñkum|wa-lam|yattakhiẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-laa|Rasoolihee|wa-lal|Muʹmineena|waleejah?|Wallaahu|khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
9,17,"Maa-|kaana|lil-Mushrikeena|ʹañy|yaʻmuroo|masaajidal|laahi|shaahideena|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim̃|bilkufr.|ʹUlaaaʹika|ḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum|wa-fin|Naari|hum|khaalidoon."
9,18,"ʹInnamaa|yaʻmuru|masaajidal|laahi|man|ʹaamana|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-ʹaq̣aamaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaataz|Zakaata|wa-lam|yakhsha|ʹillal|laah.|Faʻasaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹañy|yakoonoo|minal|Muhtadeen."
9,19,"ʹAjaʻaltum|siq̣aayatal|Ḥaaajji|wa-ʻimaaratal|Masjidil|Ḥaraami|kaman|ʹaamana|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-jaahada|fee|Sabeelil|laah?|Laa-|yastawoona|ʻiñdal|laah:|wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
9,20,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-haajaroo|wa-jaahadoo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim|ʹaʻz̤̣amu|darajatan|ʻiñdal|laah:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|faaaʹizoon."
9,21,"Yubashshiruhum|Rabbuhum̃|biraḥmatim|minhu|wa-riḍwaaniñw|wa-Jannaatil|lahum|feehaa|naʻeemum|muq̣eem;"
9,22,"Khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻiñdahooo|ʹajrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
9,23,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tattakhiẓooo|ʹaabaaaʹakum|wa-ʹikhwaanakum|ʹawliyaaaʹa|ʹinis|taḥabbul|kufra|ʻalal|ʹeemaan.|Wa-mañy|yatawal-lahum|miñkum|faʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
9,24,"Q̣ul|ʹiñ|kaana|ʹaabaaaʹukum|wa-ʹabnaaaʹukum|wa-ʹikhwaanukum|wa-ʹazwaajukum|wa-ʻasheeratukum|wa-ʹamwaaluniq̣|taraftumoohaa|wa-tijaaratuñ|takhshawna|kasaadahaa|wa-masaakinu|tarḍawnahaaa|ʹaḥabba|ʹilaykum|minal|laahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-Jihaadiñ|fee|Sabeelihee|fatarabbaṣoo|ḥattaa|yaʹtiyallaahu|bi|ʹAmrih.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|faasiq̣een."
9,25,"Laq̣ad|naṣarakumul|laahu|fee|mawaaṭina|kas̤eeratiñw|wayawma|Ḥunaynin|ʹiẓ|ʹaʻjabatkum|kas̤ratukum|falam|tug̣ni|ʻañkum|shayʹañw|waḍaaq̣at|ʻalaykumul|ʹarḍu|bimaa|raḥubat|s̤umma|wallaytum|mudbireen!"
9,26,"S̤umma|ʹañzalal|laahu|sakeenatahoo|ʻalaa|Rasoolihee|wa-ʻalal|Muʹmineena|wa-ʹañzala|junoodal|lam|tarawhaa:|wa-ʻaẓẓabal|laẓeena|kafaroo.|Wa-ẓaalika|jazaaaʹul|kaafireen."
9,27,"S̤umma|yatoobul|laahu|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
9,28,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹinnamal|Mushrikoona|najasuñ|falaa|yaq̣rabul|Masjidal|Ḥaraama|baʻda|ʻaamihim|haaẓaa.|Wa-ʹin|khiftum|ʻaylatañ|fasawfa|yug̣neekumul|laahu|miñ|faḍliheee|ʹiñ|shaaaʹ.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
9,29,"Q̣aatilul|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wa-laa|bil-yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wa-laa|yuḥarrimoona|maa-|ḥarramal|laahu|wa-Rasooluhoo|wa-laa|yadeenoona|Deenal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|minal|laẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|ḥattaa|yuʻṭul|Jizyata|ʻañy|yadiñw|wahum|ṣaag̣iroon."
9,30,"Wa-q̣aalatil|Yahoodu|ʻUzayrunib|nul|laahi|wa-q̣aalatin|Naṣaaral|Maseeḥub|nul|laah.|Ẓaalika|q̣awluhum̃|biʹafwaahihim.|Yuḍaahiʹoona|q̣awlal|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|q̣abl.|Q̣aatalahumul|laah;|ʹannaa|yuʹfakoon!"
9,31,"ʹIttakhaẓooo|ʹaḥbaarahum|wa-ruhbaanahum|ʹarbaabam|miñ|doonil|laahi|wal-Maseeḥab|na|Maryam.|Wa-maaa|ʹumirooo|ʹillaa|liyaʻbudooo|ʹIlaahañw|Waa-ḥidaa.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo.|Subḥaanahoo|ʻammaa|yushrikoon."
9,32,"Yureedoona|ʹañy|yuṭfiʹoo|Nooral|laahi|biʹafwaahihim|wa-yaʹbal|laahu|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yutimma|Noorahoo|wa-law|karihal|Kaafiroon."
9,33,"Huwal|laẓeee|ʹarsala|Rasoolahoo|bil-Hudaa|wa-Deenil|Ḥaq̣q̣i|liyuz̤̣hirahoo|ʻalad|deeni|kullihee|wa-law|karihal|Mushrikoon."
9,34,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹinna|kas̤eeram|minal|ʹaḥbaari|warruhbaani|layaʹkuloona|ʹamwaalan|naasi|bil-baaṭili|wa-yaṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah.|Wallaẓeena|yaknizoonaẓ|ẓahaba|wal-fiḍḍata|wa-laa|yuñfiq̣oonahaa|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|fabashshirhum̃|biʻaẓaabin|ʹaleem."
9,35,"Yawma|yuḥmaa|ʻalayhaa|fee|Naari|Jahannama|fatukwaa|bihaa|jibaahuhum|wa-junoobuhum|waz̤̣uhooruhum.|Haaẓaa|maa-|kanaztum|liʹañfusikum|faẓooq̣oo|maa-|kuñtum|taknizoon."
9,36,"ʹInna|ʻiddatash|shuhoori|ʻiñdal|laahis̤|naa|ʻashara|shahrañ|fee|Kitaabil|laahi|yawma|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|minhaaa|ʹarbaʻatun|ḥurum:|ẓaalikad|Deenul|Q̣ayyim.|Falaa|taz̤̣limoo|feehinna|ʹañfusakum;|wa-q̣aatilul|Mushrikeena|kaaaffatañ|kamaa|yuq̣aatiloonakum|kaaaffah.|Waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|maʻal|Muttaq̣een."
9,37,"ʹInnaman|naseeeʹu|ziyaadatuñ|fil|kufri|yuḍallu|bihil|laẓeena|kafaroo|yuḥillunahoo|ʻaamañw|Wayuḥarrimoonahoo|ʻaamal|liyuwaaṭiʹoo|ʻiddata|maa-|ḥarramal|laahu|fayuḥilloo|maa-|harramal|laah.|Zuyyina|lahum|soooʹu|ʹaʻmaalihim.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|Kaafireen."
9,38,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maa-|lakum|ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lakumuñ|firoo|fee|Sabeelil|laahis̤|s̤aaq̣altum|ʹilal|ʹarḍ?|ʹAraḍeetum̃|bilḥayaatid|dunyaa|minal|ʹAakhirah?|Famaa|mataaʻul|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʹillaa|q̣aleel."
9,39,"ʹIllaa|tañfiroo|yuʻaẓẓibkum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemañw|Wayastabdil|q̣awman|g̣ayrakum|wa-laa|taḍurroohu|shayʹaa.|Wal-laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
9,40,"ʹIllaa|tañṣuroohu|faq̣ad|naṣarahul|laahu|ʹiẓ|ʹakhrajahul|laẓeena|kafaroo|S̤aaniyas̤|nayni|ʹiẓ|humaa|fil|G̣aari|ʹiẓ|yaq̣oolu|li-Ṣaaḥibihee|˹Laa|taḥzan|ʹinnal|laaha|maʻanaa.|Faʹañzalal|laahu|sakeenatahoo|ʻalayhi|wa-ʹayyadahoo|bijunoodil|lam|tarawhaa|wa-jaʻala|kalimatal|laẓeena|kafarus|suflaa;|wa-Kalimatul|laahi|hiyal|ʻUlyaa:|wallaahu|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
9,41,"ʹIñfiroo|khifaafañw|was̤iq̣aalañw|wajaahidoo|biʹamwaalikum|wa-ʹañfusikum|fee|Sabeelil|laah.|Ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon."
9,42,"Law|kaana|ʻaraḍañ|q̣areebañw|wasafarañ|q̣aaṣidal|lattabaʻooka|wa-laakim|baʻudat|ʻalayhimush|shuq̣q̣ah.|Wa-sayaḥlifoona|billaahi|lawis|taṭaʻnaa|lakharajnaa|maʻakum.|Yuhlikoona|ʹañfusahum;|wal-laahu|yaʻlamu|ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon."
9,43,"ʻAfal|laahu|ʻañka|Lima|ʹaẓiñta|lahum|ḥattaa|yatabayyana|lakal|laẓeena|ṣadaq̣oo|wa-taʻlamal|kaaẓibeen."
9,44,"Laa-|yastaʹẓinukal|laẓeena|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|ʹañy|yujaahidoo|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum|bil-Muttaq̣een."
9,45,"ʹInnamaa|yastaʹẓinukal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|wartaabat|q̣uloobuhum|fahum|fee|raybihim|yataraddadoon."
9,46,"Wa-law|ʹaraadul|khurooja|laʹaʻaddoo|lahoo|ʻuddatañw|Walaakiñ|karihal|laahum|biʻaas̤ahum|fas̤abbaṭahum|wa-q̣eelaq̣|ʻudoo|maʻal|q̣aaʻideen."
9,47,"Law|kharajoo|feekum|maa|zaadookum|ʹillaa|khabaalañw|walaʹawḍaʻoo|khilaalakum|yabg̣oonakumul|fitnah;|wa-feekum|sammaaʻoona|lahum.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum|biz̤̣z̤̣aalimeen."
9,48,"Laq̣adib|tag̣awul|fitnata|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-q̣allaboo|lakal|ʹumoora|ḥattaa|jaaaʹal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|waz̤̣ahara|ʹAmrul|laahi|wa-hum|kaarihoon."
9,49,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yaq̣ooluʹ|ẓal|lee|wa-laa|taftinnee.|ʹAlaa|fil|fitnati|saq̣aṭoo?|Wa-ʹinna|Jahannama|lamuḥeeṭatum|bil-Kaafireen."
9,50,"ʹIñ|tuṣibka|ḥasanatuñ|tasuʹhum;|wa-ʹiñ|tuṣibka|muṣeebatuñy|yaq̣ooloo|q̣ad|ʹakhaẓnaaa|ʹamranaa|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-yatawallaw|wahum|fariḥoon."
9,51,"Q̣ul|lañy|yuṣeebanaaa|ʹillaa|maa-|katabal|laahu|lanaa|Huwa|Mawlaanaa:|wa-ʻalal|laahi|fal-yatawakkalil|Muʹminoon."
9,52,"Q̣ul|hal|tarabbaṣoona|binaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹiḥdal|ḥusnayayn?|Wa-naḥnu|natarabbaṣu|bikum|ʹañy|yu-ṣeebakumul|laahu|biʻaẓaabim|min|ʻiñdiheee|ʹaw|biʹaydeenaa.|Fatarabbaṣooo|ʹinnaa|maʻakum|mutarabbiṣoon."
9,53,"Q̣ul|ʹañfiq̣oo|ṭawʻan|ʹaw|karhal|lañy|yutaq̣abbala|miñ-kum:|ʹinnakum|kuñtum|q̣awmañ|faasiq̣een."
9,54,"Wa-maa|manaʻahum|ʹañ|tuq̣bala|minhum|nafaq̣aatuhum|ʹillaaa|ʹannahum|kafaroo|billaahi|wa-bi-Rasoolihee|wa-laa|yaʹtoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|ʹillaa|wa-hum|kusaalaa|wa-laa|yuñfiq̣oona|ʹillaa|wa-hum|kaarihoon."
9,55,"Falaa|tuʻjibka|ʹamwaaluhum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaaduhum.|ʹInnamaa|yureedul|laahu|liyuʻaẓẓibahum̃|bihaa|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-tazhaq̣a|ʹañfusuhum|wa-hum|kaafiroon."
9,56,"Wa-yaḥlifoona|billaahi|ʹinnahum|lamiñkum;|wa-maa|hum|miñkum|wa-laakinnahum|q̣awmuñy|yafraq̣oon."
9,57,"Law|yajidoona|maljaʹan|ʹaw|mag̣aaraatin|ʹaw|muddakhalal|lawallaw|ʹilayhi|wa-hum|yajmaḥoon."
9,58,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yalmizuka|fiṣ|ṣadaq̣aat:|faʹin|ʹuʻṭoo|minhaa|raḍoo|wa-ʹil|lam|yuʻṭaw|minhaaa|ʹiẓaa|hum|yaskhaṭoon!"
9,59,"Wa-law|ʹannahum|raḍoo|maaa|ʹaataahumul|laahu|wa-Rasooluhoo|wa-q̣aaloo|ḥasbunal|laahu|sayuʹteenal|laahu|miñ|faḍlihee|wa-Rasooluhooo|ʹinnaaa|ʹilal|laahi|raag̣iboon."
9,60,"ʹInnamaṣ|Ṣadaq̣aatu|lilfuq̣araaaʹi|walmasaakeeni|wal-ʻaamileena|ʻalayhaa|wal-muʹallafati|q̣uloobuhum|wa-fir|riq̣aabi|walg̣aarimeena|wa-fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wabnis|sabeel:|fareeḍatam|minal|laah,|wal-laahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
9,61,"Wa-minhumul|laẓeena|yuʹẓoonan|Nabiyya|wa-yaq̣ooloona|Huwa|ʹuẓun.|Q̣ul|ʹuẓunu|khayril|lakum|yuʹminu|billaahi|wa-yuʹminu|lil-muʹmineena|wa-Raḥmatul|lil-laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|miñkum.|Wallaẓeena|yuʹẓoona|Rasoolal|laahi|lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
9,62,"Yaḥlifoona|billaahi|lakum|liyurḍookum:|wallaahu|wa-Rasooluhooo|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|ʹañy|yurzoohu|ʹiñ|kaanoo|Muʹmineen."
9,63,"ʹAlam|yaʻlamooo|ʹannahoo|mañy|yuḥaadidil|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|faʹanna|lahoo|naara|Jahannama|khaalidañ|feehaa.|Ẓaalikal|khizyul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
9,64,"Yaḥẓarul|Munaafiq̣oona|ʹañ|tunazzala|ʻalayhim|sooratuñ|tunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|fee|q̣uloobihim.|Q̣ulis|tahziʹoo!|ʹInnal|laaha|mukhrijum|maa|taḥẓaroon."
9,65,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|layaq̣oolunna|ʹinnamaa|kunnaa|nakhooḍu|wa-nalʻab.|Q̣ul|ʹabillaahi|wa-ʹAayaatihee|wa-Rasoolihee|kuñtum|tastahziʹoon."
9,66,"Laa-|taʻtaẓiroo|q̣ad|kafartum|baʻda|ʹeemaanikum.|ʹIn|naʻfu|ʻañ|ṭaaaʹifatim|miñkum|nuʻaẓẓib|ṭaaaʹifatam|biʹannahum|kaanoo|mujrimeen."
9,67,"ʹAl-Munaafiq̣oona|wal-Munaafiq̣aatu|baʻḍuhum|mim|baʻḍ.|Yaʹmuroona|bilmuñkari|wa-yanhawna|ʻanil|maʻroofi|wa-yaq̣biḍoona|ʹaydiyahum.|Nasul|laaha|fanasiyahum.|ʹInnal|Munaafiq̣eena|humul|faasiq̣oon."
9,68,"Waʻadal|laahul|Munaafiq̣eena|wal-Munaafiq̣aati|wal-Kuffaara|naara|Jahannama|khaalideena|feehaa.|Hiya|ḥasbuhum:|wa-laʻanahumul|laah,|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabum|muq̣eem."
9,69,"Kallaẓeena|miñ|q̣ablikum|kaanooo|ʹashadda|miñkum|q̣uwwatañw|waʹaks̤ara|ʹamwaalañw|Waʹawlaadaa.|Fastamtaʻoo|bikhalaaq̣ihim|fastamtaʻtum̃|bikhalaaq̣ikum|kamas|tamtaʻal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablikum̃|bikhalaaq̣ihim|wa-khuḍtum|kallaẓee|khaaḍoo.|ʹUlaaaʹika|ḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah;|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
9,70,"ʹAlam|yaʹtihim|naba|ʹullaẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|q̣awmi|Nooḥiñw|WaʻAadiñw|wa-S̤amooda|wa-q̣awmi|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹAṣḥaabi|Madyana|wal-Muʹtafikaat.|ʹAtathum|rusuluhum̃|bilbayyinaat.|Famaa|kaanal|laahu|liyaz̤̣limahum|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
9,71,"Wal-Muʹminoona|Wal-Muʹminaatu|baʻḍuhum|ʹawliyaaaʹu|baʻḍ.|Yaʹmuroona|bilmaʻroofi|wa-yanhawna|ʻanil|muñkari|wa-yuq̣eemoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-yuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wa-yuṭeeʻoonal|laaha|wa-Rasoolah.|ʹUlaaaʹika|sayarḥamuhumul|laah;|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
9,72,"Waʻadal|laahul|Muʹ-mineena|wal-Muʹminaati|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa|wa-masaakina|ṭayyibatañ|fee|Jannaati|ʻAdn.|Wa-Riḍwaanum|minal|laahi|ʹakbar:|ẓaalika|huwal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
9,73,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|jaahidil|kuffaara|wal-Munaafiq̣eena|wag̣luz̤̣|ʻalayhim.|Wa-maʹwaahum|Jahannam:|wa-biʹsal|maṣeer."
9,74,"Yaḥlifoona|billaahi|maa-|q̣aaloo.|Wa-laq̣ad|q̣aaloo|kalimatal|kufri|wa-kafaroo|baʻda|ʹIslaamihim|wa-hammoo|bimaa|lam|yanaaloo:|wa-maa|naq̣amooo|ʹillaaa|ʹan|ʹag̣naahumul|laahu|wa-Rasooluhoo|miñ|faḍlih!|Faʹiñy|yatooboo|yaku|khayral|lahum;|wa-ʹiñy|yatawal-law|yuʻaẓẓibhumul|laahu|ʻaẓaaban|ʻaleemañ|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah;|wa-maa|lahum|fil|ʹarḍi|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|naṣeer."
9,75,"Wa-minhum|man|ʻaahadal|laaha|laʹin|ʹaataanaa|miñ|faḍlihee|lanaṣṣaddaq̣anna|wa-lanakoonanna|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
9,76,"Falammaaa|ʹaataahum|miñ|faḍlihee|bakhiloo|bihee|wa-tawallaw|wahum|muʻriḍoon."
9,77,"Faʹaʻq̣abahum|nifaaq̣añ|fee|q̣uloobihim|ʹilaa|yawmi|yalq̣awnahoo|bimaaa|ʹakhlaful|laaha|maa-|waʻadoohu|wa-bimaa|kaanoo|yakẓiboon."
9,78,"ʹAlam|yaʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|sirrahum|wa-najwaahum|wa-ʹannal|laaha|ʻAllaamul|g̣uyoob."
9,79,"ʹAllaẓeena|yalmizoonal|muṭṭawwiʻeena|minal|Muʹmineena|fiṣ|ṣadaq̣aati|wallaẓeena|laa-|yajidoona|ʹillaa|juhdahum|fayaskharoona|minhum,―|sakhiral|laahu|minhum:|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
9,80,"ʹIstag̣fir|lahum|ʹaw|laa-|tastag̣fir|lahum:|ʹiñ|tastag̣fir|lahum|sabʻeena|marratañ|falañy|yag̣firal|laahu|lahum.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|kafaroo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolih:|wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|faasiq̣een."
9,81,"Fariḥal|mukhallafoona|bimaq̣ʻadihim|khilaafa|Rasoolil|laahi|wa-karihooo|ʹañy|yujaahidoo|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|waq̣aaloo|laa-|tañfiroo|fil|ḥarr.|Q̣ul|Naaru|Jahannama|ʹashaddu|ḥarraa:|Law|kaanoo|yafq̣ahoon!"
9,82,"Falyaḍḥakoo|q̣aleelañw|walyabkoo|kas̤eeraa:|jazaaaʹam|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
9,83,"Faʹir|rajaʻakal|laahu|ʹilaa|ṭaaaʹifatim|minhum|fastaʹẓanooka|lilkhurooji|faq̣ul|lañ|takhrujoo|maʻiya|ʹabadañw|Walañ|tuq̣aatiloo|maʻiya|ʻaduwwaa.|ʹInnakum|raḍeetum̃|bilq̣uʻoodi|ʹawwala|marratiñ|faq̣ʻudoo|maʻal|khaalifeen."
9,84,"Wa-laa|tuṣalli|ʻalaaa|ʹaḥadim|minhum|maata|ʹabadañw|Walaa|taq̣um|ʻalaa|q̣abrih.|ʹInnahum|kafaroo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-maatoo|wa-hum|faasiq̣oon."
9,85,"Wa-laa|tuʻjibka|ʹamwaaluhum|wa-ʹawlaaduhum!|ʹInnamaa|yureedul|laahu|ʹañy|yuʻaẓẓibahum̃|bihaa|fid|dunyaa|wa-tazhaq̣a|ʹañfusuhum|wa-hum|kaafiroon."
9,86,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹuñzilat|Sooratun|ʹan|ʹaaminoo|billaahi|wa-jaahidoo|maʻa|Rasoolihis|taʹẓanaka|ʹuluṭ|ṭawli|minhum|wa-q̣aaloo|ẓarnaa|nakum|maʻal|q̣aaʻideen."
9,87,"Raḍoo|biʹañy|yakoonoo|maʻal|khawaalifi|waṭubiʻa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|fahum|laa-|yafq̣ahoon."
9,88,"Laakinir|Rasoolu|wal-laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|jaahadoo|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim.|Wa-ʹulaaaʹika|lahumul|khayraat:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
9,89,"ʹAʻaddal|laahu|Lahum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa:|ẓaalikal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
9,90,"Wa-jaaaʹal|muʻaẓẓiroona|minal|ʹAʻraabi|liyuʹẓana|lahum|wa-q̣aʻadal|laẓeena|kaẓabul|laaha|wa-Rasoolah.|Sayuṣeebul|laẓeena|kafaroo|minhum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
9,91,"Laysa|ʻalaḍ|ḍuʻafaaaʹi|wa-laa|ʻalal|marḍaa|wa-laa|ʻalal|laẓeena|laa-|yajidoona|maa-|yuñfiq̣oona|ḥarajun|ʹiẓaa|naṣaḥoo|lillaahi|wa-Rasoolih:|maa-|ʻalal|Muḥsineena|miñ|sabeel:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
9,92,"Wa-laa|ʻalal|laẓeena|ʹiẓaa|maaa|ʹatawka|litaḥmilahum|q̣ulta|laaa|ʹajidu|maaa|ʹaḥmilukum|ʻalayhi|tawallaw|waʹaʻyunuhum|tafeeḍu|minad|damʻi|ḥazanan|ʹallaa|yajidoo|maa-|yuñfiq̣oon."
9,93,"ʹInnamas|sabeelu|ʻalal|laẓeena|yastaʹẓinoonaka|wa-hum|ʹag̣niyaaaʹ.|Raḍoo|biʹañy|yakoonoo|maʻal|khawaalifi|waṭabaʻal|laahu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|fahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
9,94,"Yaʻtaẓiroona|ʹilaykum|ʹiẓaa|rajaʻtum|ʹilayhim.|Q̣ul|laa|taʻtaẓiroo|lan|nuʹmina|lakum|q̣ad|nabbaʹanal|laahu|min|ʹakhbaarikum:|wa-sayaral|laahu|ʻamalakum|wa-Rasooluhoo|s̤umma|turaddoona|ʹilaa|ʻAalimil|g̣aybi|washshahaadati|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
9,95,"Sayaḥlifoona|billaahi|lakum|ʹiẓañ|q̣alabtum|ʹilayhim|lituʻriḍoo|ʻanhum.|Faʹaʻriḍoo|ʻanhum:|ʹinnahum|rijsuñw|wamaʹwaahum|Jahannam,―|jazaaaʹam|bi|maakaanoo|yaksiboon."
9,96,"Yaḥlifoona|lakum|litarḍaw|ʻanhum.|Faʹiñ|tarḍaw|ʻanhum|faʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yarḍaa|ʻanil|q̣awmil|faasiq̣een."
9,97,"ʹAlʹaʻraabu|ʹashaddu|kufrañw|wanifaaq̣añw|waʹajdaru|ʹallaa|yaʻlamoo|ḥudooda|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|ʻalaa|Rasoolih:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
9,98,"Wa-minal|ʹAʻraabi|mañy|yatṭakhiẓu|maa-|yuñfiq̣u|mag̣ramañw|wayatarabbaṣu|bikumud|dawaaaʹir:|ʻalayhim|daaaʹiratus|sawʹ:|wallaahu|sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
9,99,"Wa-minal|ʹAʻraabi|mañy|yuʹminu|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|Wayattakhiẓu|maa-|yuñfiq̣u|q̣urubaatin|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-Ṣalawaatir|Rasool.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahaa|q̣urbatul|lahum:|Sayudkhiluhumul|laahu|fee|Raḥmatih:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
9,100,"Was-saabiq̣oonal|ʹAwwaloona|minal|Muhaajireena|wal-ʹAñṣaari|wallaẓeenat|tabaʻoohum̃|biʹiḥsaanir|raḍiyal|laahu|ʻanhum|wa-raḍoo|ʻanhu|wa-ʹaʻadda|lahum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|taḥtahal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa:|ẓaalikal|fawzul|ʻAz̤̣eem."
9,101,"Wa-mimman|ḥawlakum|minal|ʹAʻraabi|Munaafiq̣oon.|Wa-min|ʹahlil|Madeenati|maradoo|ʻalan|nifaaq̣:|laa-|taʻlamuhum:|naḥnu|naʻlamuhum:|sanuʻaẓẓibuhum|marratayni|s̤umma|yuraddoona|ʹilaa|ʻaẓaabin|ʻAz̤̣eem."
9,102,"Wa-ʹaakharoo|naʻtarafoo|biẓunoobihim|khalaṭoo|ʻamalañ|ṣaaliḥañw|waʹaakhara|sayyiʹaa.|ʻAsal|laahu|ʹañy|yatooba|ʻalayhim;|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
9,103,"Khuẓ|min|ʹamwaalihim|ṣadaq̣atañ|tuṭahhiruhum|wa-tuzakkeehim̃|bihaa|waṣalli|ʻalayhim.|ʹInna|ṣalaataka|sakanul|lahum:|wallaahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
9,104,"ʹAlam|yaʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|Huwa|yaq̣balut|TAWBATA|ʻan|ʻibaadihee|wa-yaʹkhuẓuṣ|ṣadaq̣aati|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Huwat|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
9,105,"Wa-q̣ul|iʻmaloo|fasayaral|laahu|ʻamalakum|wa-Rasooluhoo|wal-Muʹminoon:|wa-saturaddoona|ʹilaa|ʻAalimil|g̣aybi|washshahaadati|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
9,106,"Wa-ʹaakharoona|murjawna|liʹamril|laahi|ʹimmaa|yuʻaẓẓibuhum|wa-ʹimmaa|yatoobu|ʻalayhim:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
9,107,"Wallaẓeenat|takhaẓoo|masjidañ|ḍiraarañw|wakufrañw|watafreeq̣am|baynal|Muʹmineena|wa-ʹirṣaadal|liman|ḥaarabal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|miñ|q̣abl.|Wa-la-yaḥlifunna|ʹin|ʹaradnaaa|ʹillal|ḥusnaa;|wallaahu|yashhadu|ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon."
9,108,"Laa-|taq̣um|feehi|ʹabadaa.|Lamasjidun|ʹussisa|ʻalat|taq̣waa|min|ʹawwali|yawmin|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|ʹañ|taq̣ooma|feeh.|Feehi|rijaaluñy|yuḥibboona|ʹañy|yataṭahharoo,|wallaahu|yuḥibbul|Muṭṭahhireen."
9,109,"ʹAfaman|ʹassasa|bunyaanahoo|ʻalaa|taq̣waa|minal|laahi|wa-Riḍwaanin|khayrun|ʹam|man|assasa|bunyaanahoo|ʻalaa|shafaa|jurufin|haariñ|fanhaara|bihee|fee|naari|Jahannam.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
9,110,"Laa-|yazaalu|bunyaanuhumul|laẓee|banaw|reebatañ|fee|q̣uloobihim|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|taq̣aṭṭaʻa|q̣uloobuhum.|Wal-laahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
9,111,"ʹInnal|laahash|taraa|minal|Muʹmineena|ʹañfusahum|wa-ʹamwaalahum|biʹanna|lahumul|Jannah:|yuq̣aatiloona|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|fayaq̣tuloona|wa-yuq̣taloon:|waʻdan|ʻalayhi|Ḥaq̣q̣añ|fit|Tawraati|wal-ʹIñjeeli|wal-Q̣urʹaan:|wa-man|ʹawfaa|biʻAhdihee|minal|laahi|fastabshiroo|bibayʻikumul|laẓee|baayaʻtum̃|bih:|waẓaalika|huwal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
9,112,"ʹAt-Taaaʹiboonal|ʻaabidoonal|ḥaamidoonas|saaaʹiḥoonar|raakiʻoonas|saajidoonal|ʹaamiroona|bilmaʻroofi|wannaahoona|ʻanil|muñkari|walḥaafiz̤̣oona|liḥudoodil|laah.|Wa-bashshiril|Muʹmineen."
9,113,"Maa-|kaana|lin-Nabiyyi|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹañy|yastag̣firoo|lil-Mushrikeena|wa-law|kaanooo|ʹulee|q̣urbaa|mim|baʻdi|maa-|tabayyana|lahum|ʹannahum|ʹaṣḥaabul|Jaḥeem."
9,114,"Wa-maa|kaanas|tig̣faaru|ʹIbraaheema|liʹabeehi|ʹillaa|ʻam|mawʻidatiñw|waʻadahaaa|ʹiyyaah.|Falammaa|tabayyana|lahooo|ʹannahoo|ʻaduwwul|lillaahi|tabarraʹa|minh:|ʹinna|ʹIbraaheema|laʹawwaahun|ḥaleem."
9,115,"Wa-maa|kaanal|laahu|liyuḍilla|q̣awmam|baʻda|ʹiẓ|hadaahum|ḥattaa|yubayyina|lahum|maa|yattaq̣oon,―|ʹinnal|laaha|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
9,116,"ʹInnal|laaha|lahoo|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Yuḥyee|wa-yumeet.|Wa-maa|lakum|miñ|doonil|laahi|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|naṣeer."
9,117,"Laq̣at|taabal|laahu|ʻalan|Nabiyyi|wal-Muhaajireena|wal-ʹAñṣaaril|laẓeenat|tabaʻoohu|fee|saaʻatil|ʻusrati|mim|baʻdi|maa-|kaada|yazeeg̣u|q̣uloobu|fareeq̣im|minhum|s̤umma|taaba|ʻalayhim:|ʹinnahoo|bihim|Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
9,118,"Wa-ʻalas̤|s̤alaas̤atil|laẓeena|khullifoo:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|ḍaaq̣at|ʻalayhimul|ʹarḍu|bimaa|raḥubat|wa-ḍaaq̣at|ʻalayhim|ʹañfusuhum|waz̤̣annooo|ʹal|laa|maljaʹa|minal|laahi|ʹillaaa|ʹilayh.|S̤umma|taaba|ʻalayhim|liyatooboo:|ʹinnal|laaha|Huwat|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
9,119,"yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|wa-koonoo|maʻaṣ|Ṣaadiq̣een."
9,120,"Maa-|kaana|liʹahlil|Madeenati|wa-man|ḥawlahum|minal|ʹAʻraabi|ʹañy|yatakhallafoo|ʻar|Rasoolil|laahi|wa-laa|yarg̣aboo|biʹañfusihim|ʻan|nafsih:|ẓaalika|biʹannahum|laa-|yuṣeebuhum|z̤̣amaʹuñw|walaa|naṣabuñw|walaa|makhmaṣatuñ|fee|sabeelil|laahi|wa-laa|yaṭaʹoona|mawṭiʹañy|yag̣eez̤̣ul|kuffaara|wa-laa|yanaaloona|min|ʻaduwwin|naylan|ʹillaa|kutiba|lahum̃|bihee|ʻamaluñ|ṣaaliḥ:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḍeeʻu|ʹajral|Muḥsineen."
9,121,"Wa-laa|yuñfiq̣oona|nafaq̣atañ|ṣag̣eeratañw|walaa|kabeeratañw|walaa|yaq̣ṭaʻoona|waadiyan|ʹillaa|kutiba|lahum|liyajziyahumul|laahu|ʹaḥsana|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
9,122,"Wa-maa|kaanal|Muʹminoona|li-Yañfiroo|kaaaffah:|falawlaa|nafara|miñ|kulli|firq̣atim|minhum|ṭaaaʹifatul|liyatafaq̣q̣ahoo|fid|deeni|wa-liyuñẓiroo|q̣awmahum|ʹiẓaa|rajaʻooo|ʹilayhim|laʻallahum|yaḥẓaroon."
9,123,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|q̣aatilul|laẓeena|yaloonakum|minal|kuffaari|walyajidoo|feekum|g̣ilz̤̣ah:|waʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|maʻal|Muttaq̣een."
9,124,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|maaa|uñzilat|sooratuñ|faminhum|mañy|yaq̣oolu|ʹayyukum|zaadathu|haaẓiheee|ʹeemaanaa?|Faʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|fazaadathum|ʹeemaanañw|wahum|yastabshiroon."
9,125,"Wa-ʹammal|laẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍuñ|fazaadathum|rijsan|ʹilaa|rijsihim|wa-maatoo|wa-hum|kaafiroon."
9,126,"ʹAwalaa|yarawna|ʹannahum|yuftanoona|fee|kulli|ʻaamim|marratan|ʹaw|marratayni|s̤umma|laa-|yatooboona|wa-laa|hum|yaẓẓakkaroon."
9,127,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|maaa|ʹuñzilat|sooratun|naz̤̣ara|baʻḍuhum|ʹilaa|baʻḍ:|hal|yaraakum|min|ʹaḥadiñ|s̤ummañ|ṣarafoo:|ṣarafal|laahu|q̣uloobahum̃|biʹannahum|q̣awmul|laa|yafq̣ahoon."
9,128,"Laq̣ad|jaaaʹakum|Rasoolum|min|ʹañfusikum|ʻazeezun|ʻalayhi|maa-|ʻanittum|ḥareeṣun|ʻalaykum̃|bil-Muʹmineena|raʹoofur|raḥeem."
9,129,"Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faq̣ul|Ḥasbiyal|laahu|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo:|ʻalayhi|tawakkaltu|wa-Huwa|Rabbul|ʻArshil|ʻAz̤̣eem!"
10,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Raa.|Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Kitaabil|Ḥakeem."
10,2,"ʹAkaana|linnaasi|ʻajaban|ʹan|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|rajulim|minhum|ʹan|ʹañẓirin|naasa|wa-bashshiril|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹanna|lahum|q̣adama|Ṣidq̣in|ʻiñda|Rabbihim?|Q̣aalal|Kaafiroona|ʹinna|haaẓaa|lasaaḥirum|mubeen!"
10,3,"ʹInna|Rabbakumul|laahul|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|fee|sittati|ʹay-yaamiñ|s̤ummas|tawaa|ʻalal|ʻArshi|yudabbirul|ʹamr.|Maa-|miñ|shafeeʻin|ʹillaa|mim|baʻdi|ʹiẓnih.|Ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukum|faʻbudooh:|ʹafalaa|taẓakkaroon?"
10,4,"ʹIlayhi|marjiʻukum|jameeʻaa.|Waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣aa.|ʹInnahoo|yabdaʹul|Khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduhoo|liyajziyal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|bilq̣isṭ;|wallaẓeena|kafaroo|lahum|sharaabum|min|ḥameemiñw|waʻaẓaabun|ʹaleemum|bimaa|kaanoo|yakfuroon."
10,5,"Huwal|laẓee|jaʻalash|shamsa|ḍiyaaaʹañw|walq̣amara|noorañw|waq̣addarahoo|manaazila|litaʻlamoo|ʻadadas|sineena|walḥisaab.|Maa-|khalaq̣al|laahu|ẓaalika|ʹillaa|bilḥaq̣q̣.|Yufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
10,6,"ʹInna|fikh|tilaafil|layli|wannahaari|wa-maa|khalaq̣al|laahu|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yattaq̣oon."
10,7,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|laa-|yarjoona|liq̣aaaʹanaa|wa-raḍoo|bil-Ḥayaatid|dunyaa|waṭmaʹannoo|bihaa|wallaẓeena|hum|ʻan|ʹAayaatinaa|g̣aafiloon,―"
10,8,"ʹUlaaaʹika|maʹwaahumun|Naaru|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
10,9,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|yahdeehim|Rabbuhum̃|biʹeemaanihim:|tajree|miñ|taḥtihimul|ʹanhaaru|fee|Jannaatin|naʻeem."
10,10,"Daʻwaahum|feehaa|Subḥaanakal|laahumma|wa-taḥiyyatuhum|feehaa|Salaam!|Wa-ʹaakhiru|daʻwaahum|ʹanil|Ḥamdu|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻaalameen!"
10,11,"Wa-law|yuʻajjilul|laahu|linnaasish|sharra|stiʻjaalahum̃|bil-khayri|laq̣uḍiya|ʹilayhim|ʹajaluhum.|Fanaẓarul|laẓeena|laa-|yarjoona|liq̣aaaʹanaa|fee|ṭug̣yaanihim|yaʻmahoon."
10,12,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|massal|ʹiñsaanaḍ|ḍurru|daʻaanaa|lijambiheee|ʹaw|q̣aaʻidan|ʹaw|q̣aaaʹimaa.|Falammaa|kashafnaa|ʻanhu|ḍurrahoo|marra|kaʹal|lam|yadʻunaaa|ʹilaa|ḍurrim|massah!|Kaẓaalika|zuyyina|lilmusrifeena|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon!"
10,13,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹahlaknal|q̣uroona|miñ|q̣ablikum|lammaa|z̤̣alamoo|wa-jaaaʹathum|rusuluhum̃|bil-Bayyinaati|wa-maa|kaanoo|liyuʹminoo!|kaẓaalika|najzil|q̣awmal|mujrimeen!"
10,14,"S̤umma|jaʻalnaakum|khalaaaʹifa|fil|ʹarḍi|mim|baʻdihim|linañz̤̣ura|kayfa|taʻmaloon!"
10,15,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|Bayyinaatiñ|q̣aalal|laẓeena|laa-|yarjoona|liq̣aaa|ʹanaʹti|bi-Q̣urʹaanin|g̣ayri|haaẓaaa|ʹaw|baddilh.|Q̣ul|maa-|yakoonu|leee|ʹan|ʹubaddilahoo|miñ|tilq̣aaaʹi|nafsee:|ʹin|ʹattabiʻu|ʹillaa|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayy:|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹin|ʹaṣaytu|Rabbee|ʻAẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻAz̤̣eem."
10,16,"Q̣ul|law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maa-|talawtuhoo|ʻalaykum|wa-laaa|ʹadraakum̃|bih.|Faq̣ad|labis̤tu|feekum|ʻumuram|miñ|q̣ablih:|ʹafalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
10,17,"Faman|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|aw|kaẓẓaba|biʹAayaatih.|ʹInnahoo|laa-|yufliḥul|mujrimoon."
10,18,"Wa-yaʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yaḍurruhum|wa-laa|yañfaʻuhum|wa-yaq̣ooloona|haaaʹulaaaʹi|shufaʻaaaʹunaa|ʻiñdal|laah.|Q̣ul|ʹa-tunabbiʹoonal|laaha|bimaa|laa-|yaʻlamu|fis|samaawaati|wa-laa|fil|ʹarḍ?|Subḥaanahoo|wa-Taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
10,19,"Wa-maa|kaanan|naasu|ʹillaaa|ʹummatañw|waaḥidatañ|fakhtalafoo.|Wa-lawlaa|kalimatuñ|sabaq̣at|mir|Rabbika|laq̣uḍiya|baynahum|fee-maa|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
10,20,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|Law-laaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalayhi|ʹAayatum|mir|Rabbih?|Faq̣ul|ʹinnamal|G̣aybu|lillaahi|fañtaz̤̣iroo:|ʹinnee|maʻakum|minal|muñtaz̤̣ireen."
10,21,"Waʹiẓaaa|ʹaẓaq̣nan|naasa|raḥmatam|mim|baʻdi|ḍarraaaʹa|massathum|ʹiẓaa|lahum|makruñ|feee|ʹAayaatinaa!|Q̣ulil|laahu|ʹasraʻu|makraa!|ʹInna|rusulanaa|yaktuboona|maa-|tamkuroon!"
10,22,"Huwal|laẓee,|yusayyirukum|fil|barri|walbaḥr;|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|kuñtum|fil|fulk;|wa-jarayna|bihim̃|bireeḥiñ|ṭayyibatiñw|wafariḥoo|bihaa|jaaaʹathaa|reeḥun|ʻaaṣifuñw|Wajaaaʹahumul|mawju|miñ|kulli|makaaniñw|waz̤̣annooo|ʹannahum|ʹuḥeeṭa|bihim|daʻa|wullaaha|mukhliṣeena|lahud|Deen:|laʹin|ʹañjaytanaa|min|haaẓihee|lanakoonanna|minash|Shaakireen!"
10,23,"Falammaaa|ʹañjaahum|ʹiẓaa|hum|yabg̣oona|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣!|Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹinnamaa|bag̣yukum|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusikum|mataaʻal|Ḥayaatid|dunyaa:|s̤umma|ʹilaynaa|marjiʻukum|fanunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
10,24,"ʹInnamaa|Mas̤alul|Ḥayaatid|dunyaa|kamaaaʹin|ʹañzalnaahu|minas|samaaaʹi|fakhtalaṭa|bihee|nabaatul|ʹarḍi|mimmaa|yaʹkulun|naasu|wal-ʹanʻaam:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹakhaẓatil|ʹarḍu|zukhrufahaa|wazzayyanat|waz̤̣anna|ʹahluhaaa|ʹannahum|q̣aadiroona|ʻalayhaaa|ʹataahaaa|ʹamrunaa|laylan|ʹaw|nahaarañ|fajaʻalnaahaa|ḥaṣeedañ|kaʹal|lam|tag̣na|bil-ʹams!|Kaẓaalika|nufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
10,25,"Wallaahu|yadʻooo|ʹilaa|Daaris|Salaam:|wa-yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
10,26,"Lil-laẓeena|ʹaḥsanul|ḥusnaa|wa-ziyaadah!|Wa-laa|yarhaq̣u|wujoohahum|q̣ataruñw|walaa|ẓillah!|ʹUlaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannah;|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
10,27,"Wallaẓeena|kasabus|sayyiʹaati|jazaaaʹu|sayyiʹatim|bimis̤lihaa|wa-tarhaq̣uhum|ẓillah:|maa-|lahum|minal|laahi|min|ʻaaṣim:|Kaʹannamaaa|ʹug̣shiyat|wujoohuhum|q̣iṭaʻam|minal|layli|muz̤̣limaa:|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon!"
10,28,"Wa-yawma|naḥshuruhum|jameeʻañ|s̤umma|naq̣oolu|lil-laẓeena|ʹashrakoo|makaanakum|ʹañtum|wa-shurakaaʹukum.|Fazayyalnaa|baynahum|wa-q̣aala|shurakaaaʹuhum|maa|kuñtum|ʹiyyaanaa|taʻbudoon!"
10,29,"Fakafaa|billaahi|shaheedam|baynanaa|wa-baynakum|ʹiñ|kunnaa|ʻan|ʻibaadatikum|lag̣aafileen!"
10,30,"Hunaalika|tabloo|kullu|nafsim|maaa|ʹaslafat|wa-ruddooo|ʹilal|laahi|Mawlaahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kanoo|yaftaroon."
10,31,"Q̣ul|mañy|yarzuq̣ukum|minas|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍi|ʹammañy|yamlikus|samʻa|wal-ʹabṣaara|wa-mañy|yukhrijul|ḥayya|minal|mayyiti|wa-yukhrijul|mayyita|minal|ḥayyi|wa-mañy|yudabbirul|ʹamr?|Fasayaq̣ooloonal|laah.|faq̣ul|ʹafalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
10,32,"Faẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukumul|Ḥaq̣q̣:|famaaẓaa|baʻdal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|ʹillaḍ|ḍalaal?|Faʹannaa|tuṣrafoon?"
10,33,"Kaẓaalika|ḥaq̣q̣at|Kalimatu|Rabbika|ʻalal|laẓeena|fasaq̣ooo|ʹannahum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
10,34,"Q̣ul|hal|miñ|shurakaaaʹikum|mañy|yabdaʹul|khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduh?|Q̣ulil|laahu|yabdaʹul|khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduhoo|faʹannaa|tuʹfakoon?"
10,35,"Q̣ul|hal|miñ|shurakaaaʹikum|mañy|yahdeee|ʹilal|Ḥaq̣q̣?|Q̣ulil|laahu|yahdee|lil-Ḥaq̣q̣.|ʹAfamañy|yahdeee|ʹilal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|ʹañy|yuttabaʻa|ʹammal|laa|yahiddeee|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yuhdaa?|Famaa|lakum?|Kayfa|taḥkumoon?"
10,36,"Wa-maa|yattabiʻu|ʹaks̤aruhum|ʹillaa|z̤̣annaa:|ʹinnaz̤̣|z̤̣anna|laa-|yug̣nee|minal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|shayʹaa.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|bimaa|yafʻaloon."
10,37,"Wa-maa|kaana|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaanu|ʹañy|yuftaraa|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-laakiñ|taṣdeeq̣al|laẓee|bayna|yadayhi|wa-tafṣeelal|Kitaabi|laa-|rayba|feehi|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
10,38,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloonaf|taraah?|Q̣ul|faʹtoo|bisooratim|mis̤lihee|wadʻoo|manis|taṭaʻtum|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Ṣaadiq̣een!."
10,39,"Bal|kaẓẓaboo|bimaa|lam|yuḥeeṭoo|biʻilmihee|wa-lammaa|yaʹtihim|taʹweeluh:|Kaẓaalika|kaẓẓabal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
10,40,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yuʹminu|bihee|wa-minhum|mal|laa|yuʹminu|bih:|wa-Rabbuka|ʹaʻlamu|bilmufsideen."
10,41,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaẓẓabooka|faq̣ul|lee|ʻamalee|wa-lakum|ʻamalukum!|ʹAñtum̃|bareeeʹoona|mimmaaa|ʹaʻmalu|wa-ʹana|bareeeʹum|mimmaa|taʻmaloon!"
10,42,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yastamiʻoona|ʹilayk:|ʹa-faʹañta|tusmiʻuṣ|ṣumma|wa-law|kaanoo|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon?"
10,43,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yañz̤̣uru|ʹilayk:|ʹa-faʹanta|tahdil|ʻumya|wa-law|kaanoo|laa-|yubṣiroon?"
10,44,"ʹInnal|laaha|la|yaz̤̣limun|naasa|shayʹañw|walaakin|nannaasa|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
10,45,"Wa-yawma|yaḥshuruhum|kaʹal|lam|yalbas̤ooo|ʹillaa|saaʻatam|minan|nahaari|yataʻaarafoona|baynahum.|Q̣ad|khasiral|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biliq̣aaaʹil|laahi|wa-maa|kaanoo|muhtadeen."
10,46,"Wa-ʹimmaa|nuriyannaka|baʻḍal|laẓee|naʻiduhum|ʹaw|natawaffayannaka|faʹilaynaa|marjiʻuhum|s̤ummal|laahu|shaheedun|ʻalaa|maa-|yafʻaloon."
10,47,"Wa-likulli|ʹummatir|Rasool:|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|Rasooluhum|q̣uḍiya|baynahum̃|bilq̣isṭi|wa-hum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
10,48,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|waʻdu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
10,49,"Q̣ul|laaa|ʹamliku|linafsee|ḍarrañw|walaa|nafʻan|ʹillaa|maa-|shaaaʹal|laah.|Likulli|ʹUmmatin|ʹajal:|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹajaluhum|falaa|yastaʹkhiroona|saaʻatañw|walaa|yastaq̣dimoon."
10,50,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹin|ʹataakum|ʻaẓaabuhoo|bayaatan|ʹaw|nahaaram|maaẓaa|yastaʻjilu|minhul|mujrimoon."
10,51,"ʹAs̤umma|ʹiẓaa|maa-|waq̣aʻa|ʹaamañtum̃|bih?|ʹAaalʹaana|wa-q̣ad|kuñtum̃|bihee|tastaʻjiloon!"
10,52,"S̤umma|q̣eela|lil-laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|ẓooq̣oo|ʻaẓaabal|khuld!|Hal|tujzawna|ʹillaa|bimaa|kuñtum|taksiboon."
10,53,"Wa-yastambiʹoonaka|ʹaḥaq̣q̣un|hoo?|Q̣ul|ʹEe|wa-Rabbeee|ʹinnahoo|laḥaq̣q̣!|Wa-maaa|ʹañtum|bimuʻjizeen!"
10,54,"Wa-law|ʹanna|likulli|nafsiñ|z̤̣alamat|maa-|fil|ʹarḍi|laftadat|bih:|wa-ʹasarrun|nadaamata|lammaa|raʹawul|ʻaẓaab:|wa-q̣uḍiya|baynahum̃|bilq̣isṭi|wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
10,55,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|walaakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon?"
10,56,"Huwa|yuḥyee|wa-yumeetu|wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
10,57,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|q̣ad|jaaaʹatkum|mawʻiz̤̣atum|mir|Rabbikum|wa-shifaaaʹul|limaa|fiṣ|ṣudoori|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatul|lil-Muʹmineen."
10,58,"Q̣ul|bi-Faḍlil|laahi|wa-bi-Raḥmatihee|fabiẓaalika|fal-yafraḥoo:|huwa|khayrum|mimmaa|yajmaʻoon."
10,59,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|lakum|mir|rizq̣iñ|fajaʻaltum|minhu|ḥaraamañw|waḥalaalaa.|Q̣ul|ʹaaallaahu|ʹaẓina|lakum|ʹam|ʻalal|laahi|taftaroon?"
10,60,"Wa-maa|z̤̣annul|laẓeena|yaftaroona|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓiba|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah?|ʹInnal|laaha|la-Ẓoo|faḍlin|ʻalan|naasi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yashkuroon."
10,61,"Wa-maa|takoonu|fee|shaʹniñw|wamaa|tatloo|minhu|miñ|Q̣urʹaaniñw|Walaa|taʻmaloona|min|ʻamalin|ʹillaa|kunnaa|ʻalaykum|Shuhoodan|ʹiẓ|tufeeḍoona|feeh.|Wa-maa|yaʻzubu|ʻar|Rabbika|mim|mis̤q̣aali|ẓarratiñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|fis|samaaaʹi|wa-laaa|ʹaṣg̣ara|miñ|ẓaalika|wa-laaa|ʹakbara|ʹillaa|fee|kitaabim|Mubeen."
10,62,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|ʹAwliyaaaʹal|laahi|laa-|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
10,63,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-kaanoo|yattaq̣oon:"
10,64,"Lahumul|Bushraa|fil|Ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wafil|ʹAakhirah:|laa-|tabdeela|li-Kalimaatil|laah.|Ẓaalika|huwal|Fawzul|ʻAz̤̣eem."
10,65,"Wa-laa|yaḥzuñka|q̣awluhum.|ʹInnal|ʻizzata|lillaahi|jameeʻaa;|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
10,66,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|lillaahi|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wa-mañ|fil|arḍ.|Wa-maa|yattabiʻul|laẓeena|yadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|shurakaaaʹ?|ʹIñy|yattabiʻoona|ʹillaz̤̣|z̤̣anna|wa-ʹin|hum|ʹillaa|yakhruṣoon."
10,67,"Huwal|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|layla|litaskunoo|feehi|wannahaara|mubṣiraa.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yasmaʻoon."
10,68,"Q̣aalut|takhaẓal|laahu|waladaa;|Subḥaanah!|Huwal|G̣aniyy!|Lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ!|ʹIn|ʻiñdakum|miñ|sulṭaanim|bihaaẓaa!|ʹAtaq̣ooloona|ʻal|allaahi|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon?"
10,69,"Q̣ul|innal|laẓeena|yaftaroona|ʻal|allaahil|kaẓiba|laa-|yufliḥoon."
10,70,"Mataaʻuñ|fid|dunyaa|s̤umma|ʹilaynaa|marjiʻuhum|s̤umma|nuẓeeq̣uhumul|ʻAẓaabash|shadeeda|bimaa|kaanoo|yakfuroon:"
10,71,"Watlu|ʻalayhim|nabaʹa|Nooḥ.|ʹIẓ|q̣aala|liq̣awmihee|yaa-Q̣awmi|ʹiñ|kaana|kabura|ʻalaykum|maq̣aamee|wa-taẓkeeree|biʹAayaatil|laahi|faʻalal|laahi|tawakkaltu|faʹajmiʻooo|ʹamrakum|wa-shurakaaaʹakum|s̤umma|laa-|yakun|ʹamrukum|ʻalaykum|g̣ummatañ|s̤ummaq̣|ḍooo|ʹilayya|wa-laa|tuñz̤̣iroon."
10,72,"Faʹiñ|tawallaytum|famaa|saʹaltukum|min|ʹajr:|in|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalal|laahi|wa-ʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹakoona|minal|Muslimeen."
10,73,"Fakaẓẓaboohu|fanajjaynaahu|wa-mam|maʻahoo|fil|Fulki|wa-jaʻalnaahum|khalaaaʹifa|wa-ʹag̣raq̣nal|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa.|Fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|muñẓareen!"
10,74,"S̤umma|baʻas̤naa|mim|baʻdihee|Rusulan|ʹilaa|q̣awmihim|fajaaaʹoohum̃|bilbayyinaati|famaa|kaanoo|liyuʹminoo|bimaa|kaẓẓaboo|bihee|miñ|q̣abl.|Kaẓaalika|naṭbaʻu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobil|muʻtadeen."
10,75,"S̤umma|baʻas̤naa|mim|baʻdihim|Moosaa|wa-Haaroona|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹihee|biʹAayaatinaa|fastakbaroo|wa-kaanoo|q̣awmam|mujrimeen."
10,76,"Falammaa|jaaaʹahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|min|ʻiñdinaa|q̣aalooo|ʹinna|haaẓaa|lasiḥrum|mubeen!"
10,77,"Q̣aala|Moosaaa|ʹataq̣ooloona|lil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|lammaa|jaaaʹakum?|ʹA-siḥrun|haaẓaa?|Wa-laa|yufliḥus|saaḥiroon."
10,78,"Q̣aalooo|ʹajiʹtanaa|litalfitanaa|ʻammaa|wajadnaa|ʻalayhi|ʹaabaaaʹanaa|wa-takoona|lakumal|kibriyaaaʹu|fil|ʹarḍ?|Wa-maa|naḥnu|lakumaa|bi-Muʹmineen!"
10,79,"Wa-q̣aala|Firʻawnuʹ|toonee|bikulli|saaḥirin|ʻAleem."
10,80,"Falammaa|jaaaʹassa|ḥaratu|q̣aala|lahum|Moosaaa|ʹalq̣oo|maaa|ʹañtum|mulq̣oon!"
10,81,"Falammaaa|ʹalq̣aw|q̣aala|Moosaa|maa-|jiʹtum̃|bihis|siḥr:|ʹinnal|laaha|sayubṭiluh:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuṣliḥu|ʻamalal|mufsideen."
10,82,"Wa-yuḥiq̣q̣ul|laahul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|bi-Kalimaatihee|wa-law|karihal|mujrimoon!"
10,83,"Famaaa|ʹaamana|li-Moosaaa|ʹillaa|ẓurriyyatum|miñ|q̣awmihee|ʻalaa|khawfim|miñ|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹihim|ʹañy|yaftinahum;|wa-ʹinna|Firʻawna|laʻaaliñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹinnahoo|laminal|musrifeen."
10,84,"Wa-q̣aala|Moosaa|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ʹaamañtum|billaahi|faʻalayhi|tawakkalooo|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muslimeen."
10,85,"Faq̣aaloo|ʻalal|laahi|tawakkalnaa.|Rabbanaa|laa-|tajʻalnaa|fitnatal|lilq̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen;"
10,86,"Wa-najjinaa|bi-Raḥmatika|minal|q̣awmil|kaafireen."
10,87,"Wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosaa|wa-ʹakheehi|ʹañ|tabaw|waʹaali-Q̣awmikumaa|bi-Miṣra|buyootañw|wajʻaloo|buyootakum|Q̣iblatañw|Waʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaah:|wa-bashshiril|Muʹmineen!"
10,88,"Wa-q̣aala|Moosaa|Rabbanaaa|ʹinnaka|ʹaatayta|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹahoo|zeenatañw|waʹamwaalañ|fil|Ḥayaatid|dunyaa|Rabbanaa|liyuḍilloo|ʻañ|Sabeelik.|Rabbanaṭ|mis|ʻalaaa|ʹamwaalihim|washdud|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|falaa|yuʹminoo|ḥattaa|yarawul|ʻaẓaabal|ʹaleem."
10,89,"Q̣aala|q̣ad|ʹujeebad|Daʻwatukumaa|fastaq̣eemaa|wa-laa|tattabiʻaaanni|sabeelal|laẓeena|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
10,90,"Wa-jaawaznaa|bi-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelal|baḥra|faʹatbaʻahum|Firʻawnu|wa-junooduhoo|bag̣yañw|waʻadwaa.|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹadrakahul|g̣araq̣u|q̣aala|ʹaamañtu|ʹanna-Hoo|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillal|laẓeee|ʹaamanat|bihee|Banooo|ʹIsraaaʹeela|wa-ʹana|minal|Muslimeen."
10,91,"ʹAaalʹaana|wa-q̣ad|ʻaṣayta|q̣ablu|wa-kuñta|minal|mufsideen!"
10,92,"Falyawma|nunajjeeka|bibadanika|litakoona|liman|khalfaka|ʹAayah;|wa-ʹinna|kas̤eeram|minan|naasi|ʻan|ʹAayaatinaa|lag̣aafiloon!"
10,93,"Wa-laq̣ad|bawwaʹnaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|Mubawwaʹa|ṣidq̣iñw|warazaq̣naahum|minaṭ|ṭayyibaat:|famakh|talafoo|ḥattaa|jaaaʹahumul|ʻilm.|ʹInna|Rabbaka|yaq̣ḍee|baynahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|feemaa|kaanoo|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
10,94,"Faʹiñ|kuñta|fee|shakkim|mimmaaa|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilayka|fasʹalil|laẓeena|yaq̣raʹoonal|kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablik:|laq̣ad|jaaaʹakal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbika|falaa|takoonanna|minal|mumtareen."
10,95,"Wa-laa|takoonanna|minal|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatil|laahi|fatakoona|minal|khaasireen."
10,96,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ḥaq̣q̣at|ʻalayhim|Kalimatu|Rabbika|laa-|yuʹminoon."
10,97,"Wa-law|jaaaʹathum|kullu|ʹAayatin|ḥattaa|yarawul|ʻaẓaabal|ʹaleem."
10,98,"Falawlaa|kaanat|q̣aryatun|ʹaamanat|fanafaʻahaaa|ʹEemaanuhaaa|ʹillaa|Q̣awma|YOONUS?|Lammaaa|ʹaamanoo|kashafnaa|ʻanhum|ʻAẓaabal|khizyi|fil|Ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-mattaʻnaahum|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
10,99,"Wa-law|shaaaʹa|Rabbuka|laʹaamana|mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|kulluhum|jameeʻaa!|ʹA-faʹañta|tukrihun|naasa|ḥattaa|yakoonoo|Muʹmineen!"
10,100,"Wa-maa|kaana|linafsin|ʹañ|tuʹmina|ʹillaa|biʹIẓnil|laah:|wa-yajʻalur|rijsa|ʻalal|laẓeena|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon."
10,101,"Q̣uliñ|z̤̣uroo|maa-ẓaa|fissamaawaati|wal|ʹarḍ;|wa-maa|tug̣nil|ʹAayaatu|wan-Nuẓuru|ʻañ|q̣awmil|laa|yuʹminoon."
10,102,"Fahal|yañtaz̤̣iroona|ʹillaa|mis̤la|ʹayyaamil|laẓeena|khalaw|miñ|q̣ablihim?|Q̣ul|fañtaz̤̣irooo|ʹinnee|maʻakum|minal|muñtaz̤̣ireen."
10,103,"S̤umma|nunajjee|rusulanaa|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo:|Kaẓaalika|Ḥaq̣q̣an|ʻalaynaa|nuñjil|Muʹmineen!"
10,104,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|fee|shakkim|miñ|deenee|falaaa|ʹaʻbudul|laẓeena|taʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-laakin|ʹaʻbudul|laahal|laẓee|yatawaffaakum:|waʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹakoona|minal|Muʹmineen."
10,105,"Wa-ʹan|ʹaq̣im|wajhaka|lid-Deeni|ḥaneefaa,|wa-laa|takoonanna|minal|Mushrikeen."
10,106,"Wa-laa|tadʻu|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yañfaʻuka|wa-laa|yaḍurruk:|faʹiñ|faʻalta|faʹinnaka|ʹiẓam|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
10,107,"Wa-ʹiñy|yamsaskal|laahu|biḍurriñ|falaa|kaashifa|lahooo|ʹillaa|Hoo:wa-|ʹiñy|yuridka|bikhayriñ|falaa|raaadda|lifaḍlih:|yuṣeebu|bihee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadih.|Wa-Huwal|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
10,108,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|q̣ad|jaaaʹakumul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbikum!|famanih|tadaa|faʹinnamaa|yahtadee|linafsih;|wa-mañ|ḍalla|faʹinnamaa|yaḍillu|ʻalayhaa:|wa-maaa|ʹana|ʻalaykum̃|biwakeel."
10,109,"Wattabiʻ|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayka|waṣbir|ḥattaa|yaḥkumal|laahu|wa-Huwa|Khayrul|ḥaakimeen."
11,1,"ʹAlif-laaam-Raa.|Kitaabun|ʹuḥkimat|ʹAayaatuhoo|s̤umma|fuṣṣilat|mil|ladun|Ḥakeemin|Khabeer."
11,2,"ʹAllaa|taʻbudooo|ʹillal|laah.|ʹInnanee|lakum|minhu|basheer!|naẓeeruñwwa"
11,3,"Wa-ʹanis|tag̣firoo|Rabbakum|s̤umma|toobooo|ʹilayhi|yumattiʻkum|mataaʻan|ḥasanan|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammañw|wayuʹti|kulla|ẓee|faḍliñ|faḍlah!|Wa-ʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|ʻAẓaaba|Yawmiñ|Kabeer."
11,4,"ʹIlal|laahi|marjiʻukum,|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
11,5,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahum|yas̤noona|ṣudoorahum|liyastakhfoo|minh!|ʹAlaa|ḥeena|yastag̣shoona|s̤iyaabahum|yaʻlamu|maa-|yusirroona|wa-maa|yuʻlinoon:|ʹinnahoo|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
11,6,"Wa-maa|miñ|daaabbatiñ|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹillaa|ʻalal|laahi|rizq̣uhaa|wa-yaʻlamu|mustaq̣arrahaa|wa-mustawdaʻahaa:|Kulluñ|fee|Kitaabim|Mubeen."
11,7,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|fee|Sittati|ʹayyaamiñw|Wakaana|ʻArshuhoo|ʻalal|Maaaʹi|liyabluwakum|ʹayyukum|ʹaḥsanu|ʻamalaa.|Wa-laʹiñ|q̣ulta|ʹinnakum|mabʻoos̤oona|mim|baʻdil|mawti|layaq̣oolannal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|siḥrum|mubeen!"
11,8,"Wa-laʹin|ʹakhkharnaa|ʻanhumul|ʻaẓaaba|ʹilaaa|ʹummatim|maʻdoodatil|layaq̣oolunna|maa-|yaḥbisuh?|ʹAlaa|yawma|yaʹteehim|laysa|maṣroofan|ʻanhum|waḥaaq̣a|bihim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon!"
11,9,"Wa-laʹin|ʹaẓaq̣nal|ʹiñsaana|minnaa|Raḥmatañ|s̤umma|nazaʻnaahaa|minhu,|ʹinnahoo|layaʹoosuñ|kafoor."
11,10,"Wa-laʹin|ʹaẓaq̣naahu|naʻmaaaʹa|baʻda|ḍarraaaʹa|massathu|layaq̣oolanna|ẓahabas|sayyiʹaatu|ʻannee:|ʹinnahoo|lafariḥuñ|fakhoor."
11,11,"Illal|laẓeena|ṣabaroo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaat:|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|mag̣firatuñw|waʹajruñ|Kabeer."
11,12,"Falaʻallaka|taarikum|baʻḍa|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayka|wa-ḍaaaʹiq̣um|bihee|ṣadruka|ʹañy|yaq̣ooloo|laaa-law|ʹuñzila|ʻalayhi|kañzun|ʹaw|jaaaʹa|maʻahoo|malak?|ʹInnamaaa|ʹañta|naẓeer!|Wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñw|Wakeel!"
11,13,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloonaf|taraah.|Q̣ul|faʹtoo|biʻashri|Suwarim|mis̤lihee|muftarayaatiñw|wadʻoo|manis|taṭaʻtum|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
11,14,"Faʹillam|yastajeeboo|lakum|faʻlamooo|annamaaa|ʹuñzila|biʻilmil|laahi|wa-ʹal|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo!|Fahal|ʹañtum|Muslimoon?"
11,15,"Mañ|kaana|yureedul|Ḥayaatad|Dunyaa|wa-zeenatahaa|nuwaffi|ʹilayhim|ʹaʻmaalahum|feehaa|wa-hum|feehaa|laa-|yubkhasoon."
11,16,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|laysa|lahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʹillan|Naar:|Waḥabiṭa|maa-|ṣanaʻoo|feehaa|wa-baaṭilum|maa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon!"
11,17,"ʹAfamañ|kaa-na|ʻalaa|Bayyinatim|mir|Rabbihee|wa-yatloohu|Shaahidum|minhu|wa-miñ|q̣ablihee|Kitaabu|Moosaaa|ʹimaamañw|Waraḥmah?|ʹUlaaaʹika|yuʹminoona|bih.|Wa-mañy|yakfur|bihee|minal|ʹAḥzaabi|fan-naaru|mawʻiduh.|Falaa|taku|fee|miryatim|minh:|ʹinnahul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbika|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yuʹminoon!"
11,18,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓibaa?|ʹUlaaaʹika|yuʻraḍoona|ʻalaa|Rabbihim|wa-yaq̣oolul|ʹashhaa|Duhaaaʹulaaaʹil|laẓeena|kaẓaboo|ʻalaa|Rabbihim!|ʹAlaa|laʻnatul|laahi|ʻalaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen:"
11,19,"ʹAllaẓeena|yaṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-yabg̣oonahaa|ʻiwajaa:|wa-hum̃|bil|ʹAakhiratihum|kaafiroon!"
11,20,"ʹUlaaaʹika|lam|yakoonoo|muʻjizeena|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|kaana|lahum|miñ|doonil|laahi|min|ʹawliyaaaʹ!|Yuḍaaʻafu|lahumul|ʻaẓaab!|Maa-|kaanoo|yastaṭeeʻoonas|samʻa|wa-maa|kaanoo|yubṣiroon."
11,21,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon!"
11,22,"Laa-|jarama|ʹannahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|humul|ʹakhsaroon!"
11,23,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-ʹakhbatooo|ʹilaa|Rabbihim|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannah,|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon!"
11,24,"Mas̤alul|fareeq̣ayni|kal-ʹaʻmaa|wal-ʹaṣammi|walbaṣeeri|wassameeʻ.|Hal|yastawiyaani|mas̤alaa?|ʹAfalaa|taẓakkaroon?"
11,25,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Nooḥan|ʹilaa|Q̣awmih:|ʹinnee|lakum|naẓeerum|mubeen:"
11,26,"ʹAl|laa|taʻbudooo|ʹillal|laah:|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|ʻAẓaaba|Yawmin|ʹAleem."
11,27,"Faq̣aalal|Malaʹul|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|q̣awmihee|maa-|naraaka|ʹillaa|basharam|mis̤lanaa|wa-maa|naraakat|tabaʻaka|ʹillal|laẓeena|hum|ʹaraaẓilunaa|baadiyar|raʹy:|wa-maa|naraa|lakum|ʻalaynaa|miñ|faḍlim|bal|naz̤̣unnukum|kaaẓibeen!"
11,28,"Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹiñ|kuñtu|ʻalaa|Bayyinatim|mir|Rabbee|wa-ʹaataanee|Raḥmatam|min|ʻIñdihee|faʻummiyat|ʻalaykum?|ʹAnulzimukumoohaa|wa-ʹañtum|lahaa|kaarihoon?"
11,29,"Wa-yaaq̣awmi|laaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|maalaa:|ʹin|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalal|laahi|wa-maaa|ʹana|biṭaaridil|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo:|ʹinnahum|mulaaq̣oo|Rabbihim|wa-laakinneee|ʹaraakum|q̣awmañ|tajhaloon!"
11,30,"Wa-yaaq̣awmi|mañy|yañṣurunee|minal|laahi|ʹiñ|ṭarattuhum?|ʹAfalaa|taẓakkaroon!"
11,31,"Wa-laaa|ʹaq̣oolu|lakum|ʻiñdee|khazaaaʹinul|laahi|wa-laaa|ʹaʻlamul|g̣ayba|wa-laaa|ʹaq̣oolu|ʹinnee|malakuñw|walaaa|ʹaq̣oolu|lillaẓeena|tazdareee|ʹaʻyunukum|lañy|yuʹtiyahumul|laahu|khayraa:|ʹAllaahu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|feee|ʹañfusihim:|ʹinneee|ʹiẓal|laminaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
11,32,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Nooḥu|q̣ad|jaadaltanaa|faʹaks̤arta|jidaalanaa|faʹtinaa|bimaa|taʻidunaaa|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een?"
11,33,"Q̣aala|ʹinnamaa|yaʹteekum̃|bihil|laahu|ʹiñ|shaaʹa|wa-maaa|ʹañtum̃|bimuʻjizeen!"
11,34,"Wa-laa|yañfaʻukum|nuṣḥeee|ʹin|ʹarattu|ʹan|ʹañṣaḥa|lakum|ʹiñ|kaanal|laahu|yureedu|ʹañy|yug̣wiyakum:|Huwa|Rabbukum!|wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon!"
11,35,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloonaf|taraah?|Q̣ul|ʹinif|taraytuhoo|faʻalayya|ʹijraamee|wa-ʹana|bareeeʹum|mimmaa|tujrimoon!"
11,36,"Wa-ʹooḥiya|ʹilaa|Nooḥin|ʹannahu|lañy|yuʹmina|miñ|q̣awmika|ʹillaa|mañ|q̣ad|ʹaamana|falaa|tabtaʹis|bimaa|kaanoo|yafʻaloon."
11,37,"Waṣnaʻil|Fulka|biʹaʻyuninaa|wa-Waḥyinaa|wa-laa|tukhaaṭibnee|fil|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo:|ʹinnahum|mug̣raq̣oon."
11,38,"Wa-yaṣnaʻul|Fulk:|wa-kullamaa|marra|ʻalayhi|malaʹum|miñ|q̣awmihee|sakhiroo|minh.|Q̣aala|ʹiñ|taskharoo|minnaa|faʹinnaa|naskharu|miñkum|kamaa|taskharoon!"
11,39,"Fasawfa|taʻlamoona|mañy|yaʹteehi|ʻAẓaabuñy|yukhzeehi|wa-yaḥillu|ʻalayhi|ʻaẓaabum|muq̣eem:"
11,40,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹAmrunaa|wa-faarat|tannooru|q̣ulnaḥ|mil|feehaa|miñ|kulliñ|zawjaynis̤|nayni|wa-ʹahlaka|ʹillaa|mañ|sabaq̣a|ʻalayhil|Q̣awlu|wa-man|ʹaaman.|Wa-maaa|ʹaamana|maʻahooo|ʹillaa|q̣aleel."
11,41,"Wa-q̣aalar|kaboo|feeha|bismil|laahi|majraihaa|wa-mursaahaa!|ʹInna|Rabbee|la-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem!"
11,42,"Wa-hiya|tajree|bihim|fee|mawjiñ|kaljibaal.|Wa-naadaa|Nooḥunib|nahoo|wa-kaana|fee|maʻziliñy|yaa-bunay|yarkam|maʻanaa|wa-laa|takum|maʻal|Kaafireen!"
11,43,"Q̣aala|saʹaaweee|ʹilaa|jabaliñy|yaʻṣimunee|minal|maaaʹ.|Q̣aala|laa-|ʻaaṣimal|yawma|min|ʹAmril|laahi|ʹillaa|mar|raḥim!|Waḥaala|baynahumal|mawju|fakaana|minal|mug̣raq̣een."
11,44,"Wa-q̣eela|yaaaʹarḍub|laʻee|maaaʹaki|wa-yaasamaaaʹu|ʹaq̣liʻee|wa-g̣eeḍal|maaaʹu|wa-q̣uḍiyal|ʹamru|wastawat|ʻalal|joodiyyi|wa-q̣eela|buʻdal|lilq̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
11,45,"Wa-naadaa|Nooḥur|Rabbahoo|faq̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnab|Nee|min|ʹahlee|wa-ʹinna|waʻdakal|ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-ʹAñta|ʹaḥkamul|Ḥaakimeen!"
11,46,"Q̣aala|yaa-Nooḥu|ʹinnahoo|laysa|min|ʹahlik:|ʹinnahoo|ʻamalun|g̣ayru|ṣaaliḥ.|Falaa|tasʹalni|maa-|laysa|laka|bihee|ʻilm!|ʹInneee|ʹaʻiz̤̣uka|ʹañ|takoona|minal|jaahileen!"
11,47,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinneee|ʹaʻooẓu|bika|ʹan|ʹasʹalaka|maa-|laysa|lee|bihee|ʻilm.|Wa-ʹillaa|tag̣fir|lee|wa-tarḥamnee|ʹakum|minal|khaasireen!"
11,48,"Q̣eela|yaa-Nooḥuh|biṭ|bi-Salaamim|minnaa|wa-Barakaatin|ʻalayka|wa-ʻalaaa|ʹUmamim|mimmam|maʻak:|wa-ʹumamuñ|sanumattiʻuhum|s̤umma|yamassuhum|minnaa|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
11,49,"Tilka|min|ʹambaaaʹil|g̣aybi|nooḥeehaaa|ʹilayk:|maa-|kuñta|taʻlamuhaaa|ʹañta|wa-laa|q̣awmuka|miñ|q̣abli|haaẓaa.|Faṣbir|ʹinnal|ʻAaq̣ibata|lil-Muttaq̣een."
11,50,"Wa-ʹilaa|ʻAadin|ʹakhaahum|Hoodaa.|Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|ʹIn|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|muftaroon!"
11,51,"Yaa-q̣awmi|laaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|ʹajraa.|ʹIn|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalal|laẓee|faṭaranee:|ʹafalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
11,52,"Wa-yaaq̣awmis|tag̣firoo|Rabbakum|s̤umma|toobooo|ʹilayhi|yursilis|samaaaʹa|ʻalaykum|midraarañw|wayazidkum|q̣uwwatan|ʹilaa|q̣uwwatikum|wa-laa|tatawallaw|mujrimeen!"
11,53,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Hoodu|maa-|jiʹtanaa|bi-Bayyinatiñw|wamaa|naḥnu|bitaarikeee|ʹaalihatinaa|ʻañ|q̣awlika|wa-maa|naḥnu|laka|bi-Muʹmineen!"
11,54,"ʹIn|naq̣oolu|ʹillaʻ|taraaka|baʻḍu|ʹaalihatinaa|bisoooʹ.|Q̣aala|ʹinneee|ʹushhidul|laaha|washhadooo|ʹannee|bareeeʹum|mimmaa|tushrikoon."
11,55,"Miñ|doonihee|fakeedoonee|jameeʻañ|s̤umma|laa-|tuñz̤̣iroon."
11,56,"ʹInnee|tawakkaltu|ʻalal|laahi|Rabbee|Wa-Rabbikum!|Maa-|miñ|daaabbatin|ʹillaa|Huwa|ʹaakhiẓum|binaasiyatihaa.|ʹInna|Rabbee|ʻalaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
11,57,"Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faq̣ad|ʹablag̣tukum|maaa|ʹursiltu|biheee|ʹilaykum.|Wa-yastakhlifu|Rabbee|q̣awman|g̣ayrakum,|wa-laa|taḍurroonahoo|shayʹaa.|ʹInna|Rabbee|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹin|Ḥafeez̤̣."
11,58,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹa|ʹamrunaa|naj-jaynaa|Hoodañw|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|bi-Raḥmatim|minnaa:|wa-najjaynaahum|min|ʻaẓaabin|g̣aleez̤̣."
11,59,"Wa-tilka|ʻAaduñ|jaḥadoo|biʹAayaati|Rabbihim|wa-ʻaṣaw|Rusulahoo|wattabaʻooo|ʹamra|kulli|jabbaarin|ʻaneed."
11,60,"Wa-ʹutbiʻoo|fee|haaẓihid|dunyaa|laʻnatañw|wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|ʻAadañ|kafaroo|Rabbahum!|ʹAlaa|buʻdal|liʻAadiñ|Q̣awmi|Hood!"
11,61,"Wa-ʹilaa|S̤amooda|ʹakhaahum|Ṣaaliḥaa.|Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|min|lakum|ʹilahin|g̣ayruh.|Huwa|ʹañshaʹakum|minal|ʹarḍi|wastaʻmarakum|feehaa|fastag̣firoohu|s̤umma|toobooo|ʹilayh:|ʹinna|Rabbee|Q̣areebum|Mujeeb."
11,62,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Ṣaaliḥu|q̣ad|kuñta|feenaa|marjuwwañ|q̣abla|haaẓaaa|ʹatanhaanaaa|ʹan|naʻbuda|maa-|yaʻbudu|ʹaabaaaʹunaa|wa-ʹinnanaa|lafee|shakkim|mimmaa|tadʻoonaaa|ʹilayhi|mureeb."
11,63,"Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹiñ|kuñtu|ʻalaa|Bayyinatim|mir|Rabbee|wa-ʹaataanee|minhu|Raḥmatañ|famañy|yañṣurunee|minal|laahi|ʹin|ʻaṣaytuh?|Famaa|tazeedunanee|g̣ayra|takhseeer?"
11,64,"Wa-yaaq̣awmi|haaẓihee|naaq̣atul|laahi|lakum|ʹaayatañ|faẓaroohaa|taʹkul|feee|ʹarḍil|laahi|wa-laa|tamassoohaa|bisoooʹiñ|fayaʹkhuẓakum|ʻAẓaabuñ|q̣areeb!"
11,65,"Faʻaq̣aroohaa|faq̣aala|tamattaʻoo|fee|daarikum|s̤alaas̤ata|ʹay-yaam:|ẓaalika|waʻdun|g̣ayru|makẓoob!"
11,66,"Falammaa|jaaaʹa|ʹAmrunaa|najjaynaa|Ṣaaliḥañw|wal-laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|bi-Raḥmatim|minnaa|wa-min|khizyi|Yawmiʹiẓ.|ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwal|Q̣awiyyul|ʻAzeez."
11,67,"Wa-ʹakhaẓal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamuṣ|Ṣayḥatu|faʹaṣbaḥoo|fee|diyaarihim|jaas̤imeen."
11,68,"Kaʹal|lam|yag̣naw|feehaa.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|S̤amooda|kafaroo|Rabbahum!|ʹAlaa|buʻdal|li-S̤amood."
11,69,"Wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹat|Rusulunaaa|ʹIbraaheema|bilbushraa|q̣aaloo|Salaamaa!|Q̣aala|Salaamuñ|famaa|labis̤a|ʹañ|jaaaʻa|ḥaneeẓ.|biʻijlin"
11,70,"Falammaa|raʹaaa|ʹaydiyahum|laa-|taṣilu|ʹilayhi|nakirahum|wa-ʹawjasa|minhum|kheefah.|Q̣aaloo|laa-|takhaf|ʹinnaaa|ʹursilnaaa|ʹilaa|Q̣awmi|Looṭ."
11,71,"Wamraʹatuhoo|q̣aaaʹimatuñ|faḍaḥikat|fabashsharnaahaa|biʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-miñw|waraaaʹi|ʹIs-ḥaaq̣a|Yaʻq̣oob."
11,72,"Q̣aalat|yaa-waylataaa|ʹaʹalidu|wa-ʹana|ʻajoozuñw|Wahaaẓaa|baʻlee|shaykhaa?|ʹInna|haaẓaa|lashayʹun|ʻajeeb!"
11,73,"Q̣aalooo|ʹataʻjabeena|min|ʹAmril|laahi|Raḥmatul|laahi|wa-Barakaatuhoo|ʻalaykum|ʹAhlal|Bayt!|ʹInnahoo|Ḥameedum|Majeed!"
11,74,"Falammaa|ẓahaba|ʻan|ʹIbraaheemar|rawʻu|wa-jaaaʹat|hul-bushraa|yujaadilunaa|fee|Q̣awmi|Looṭ."
11,75,"ʹInna|ʹIbraaheema|laḥaleemun|ʹawwaahum|muneeb."
11,76,"YaaaʹIbraaheemu|ʹaʻriḍ|ʻan|haaẓaa.|ʹInnahoo|q̣ad|jaaaʹa|ʹamru|Rabbik:|wa-ʹinnahum|ʹaateehim|ʻaẓaabun|g̣ayru|mardood!"
11,77,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹat|Rusulunaa|Looṭañ|seeeʹa|bihim|wa-ḍaaq̣a|bihim|ẓarʻañw|waq̣aala|haaẓaa|yawmun|ʻaṣeeb."
11,78,"Wa-jaaaʹahoo|q̣awmuhoo|yuhraʻoona|ʹilayh.|Wa-miñ|q̣ablu|kaanoo|yaʻmaloonas|sayyiʹaat.|Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|haaaʹulaaaʹi|banaatee|hunna|ʹaṭharu|lakum|fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-laa|tukhzooni|fee|ḍayfee!|ʹAlaysa|miñkum|rajulur|rasheed?"
11,79,"Q̣aaloo|laq̣ad|ʻalimta|maa-|lanaa|fee|banaatika|min|ḥaq̣q̣:|wa-ʹinnaka|lataʻlamu|maa-|nureed!"
11,80,"Q̣aala|law|ʹanna|lee|bikum|q̣uwwatan|ʹaw|aaweee|ʹilaa|rukniñ|shadeed."
11,81,"Q̣aaloo|Yaa-Looṭu|ʹinnaa|Rusulu|Rabbika|lañy|yaṣilooo|ʹilayk:|faʹasri|biʹahlika|biq̣iṭʻim|minal|layli|wa-laa|yaltafit|miñkum|ʹaḥadun|ʹillam|raʹatak:|ʹinnahoo|muṣeebuhaa|maaa|ʹaṣaabahum.|ʹInna|mawʻidahumuṣ|ṣubḥ.|ʹAlaysaṣ|ṣubḥu|biq̣areeb?"
11,82,"Falammaa|jaaaʹa|ʹamrunaa|jaʻalnaa|ʻaaliyahaa|saafilahaa|wa-ʹamṭarnaa|ʻalayhaa|ḥijaaratam|miñ|sijjeelim|mañḍood,―"
11,83,"Musawwamatan|ʻiñda|Rabbik:|wa-maa|hiya|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|bibaʻeed!"
11,84,"Wa-ʹilaa|Madyana|ʹakhaahum|Shuʻaybaa:|q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|Wa-laa|tañq̣uṣul|mikyaala|walmeezaana|ʹinneee|ʹaraakum̃|bikhayriñw|waʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|ʻaẓaaba|Yawmim|Muḥeeṭ."
11,85,"Wayaaq̣awmi|ʹawful|mikyaala|walmeezaana|bilq̣isṭi|wa-laa|tabkhasun|naasa|ʹashyaaaʹahum|wa-laa|taʻs̤aw|fil|ʹarḍi|mufsideen."
11,86,"Baq̣eeyatul|laahi|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen!|Wa-maaa|ʹana|ʻalaykum̃|bi-Ḥafeez̤̣!"
11,87,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Shuʻaybu|ʹaṣalaatuka|taʹmuruka|ʹan|natruka|maa-|yaʻbudu|ʹaabaaaʹunaaa|ʹaw|ʹan|nafʻala|feee|ʹamwaalinaa|maa-|nashaaaʹ?|ʹInnaka|laʹañtal|ḥaleemur|Rasheed!"
11,88,"Q̣aala|yaaq̣awmi|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹiñ|kuñtu|ʻalaa|Bayyinatim|mir|Rabbee|wa-razaq̣anee|minhu|rizq̣an|ḥasanaa?|Wa-maaa|ʹureedu|ʹan|ʹukhaalifakum|ʹilaa|maaa|ʹanhaakum|ʻanh.|ʹIn|ʹureedu|ʹillal|ʹiṣlaaḥa|mas|taṭaʻt;|wa-maa|tawfeeq̣eee|ʹillaa|billaah.|ʻAlayhi|tawakkaltu|wa-ʹilayhi|ʹuneeb."
11,89,"Wa-yaaq̣awmi|laa-|yajrimannakum|shiq̣aaq̣eee|ʹañy|yuṣeebakum|mis̤lu|maaa|ʹaṣaaba|q̣awma|Nooḥin|ʹaw|q̣awma|Hoodin|ʹaw|q̣awma|Ṣaaliḥ:|wa-maa|q̣awmu|Looṭim|miñkum̃|bibaʻeed!"
11,90,"Wastag̣firoo|Rabbakum|s̤ummaa|toobooo|ʹilayh:|ʹinna|Rabbee|Raḥeemuñw|wadood."
11,91,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Shuʻaybu|maa-|nafq̣ahu|kas̤eeram|mimmaa|taq̣oolu|wa-ʹinnaa|lanaraaka|feenaa|ḍaʻeefaa!|Wa-lawlaa|rahṭuka|larajamnaak!|Wa-maaa|ʹañta|ʻalaynaa|biʻazeez!"
11,92,"Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹarahṭeee|ʹaʻazzu|ʻalaykum|minal|laah?|Wattakhaẓtumoohu|waraaaʹakum|z̤̣ihriyyaa.|ʹInna|Rabbee|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Muḥeeṭ!"
11,93,"Wa-yaaq̣awmiʻ|maloo|ʻalaa|makaanatikum|ʹinnee|ʻaamil:|sawfa|taʻlamoona|mañy|yaʹteehi|ʻaẓaabuñy|yukhzeehi|wa-man|huwa|kaaẓib!|Wartaq̣ibooo|ʹinnee|maʻakum|raq̣eeb."
11,94,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹa|ʹamrunaa|najjaynaa|Shuʻaybañw|wal-laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|bi-Raḥmatim|minnaa|wa-ʹakhaẓatil|laẓeena|z̤̣alamuṣ|Ṣayhatu|faʹaṣbaḥoo|fee|diyaarihim|jaas̤imeen,―"
11,95,"Kaʹal|lam|yag̣naw|feehaa!|ʹAlaa|buʻdal|li-Madyana|kamaa|baʻidat|S̤amood!"
11,96,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Moosaa|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-sulṭaanim|mubeen."
11,97,"ʹIlaa|firʻawna|wa-malaʹihee|fattabaʻooo|ʹamra|Firʻawna,|wa-maaa|ʹamru|Firʻawna|bi-Rasheed."
11,98,"Yaq̣dumu|q̣awmahoo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|faʹawradahumun|Naar:|wa-biʹsal|wirdul|mawrood!"
11,99,"Wa-ʹutbiʻoo|fee|haaẓihee|laʻnatañw|wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah:|biʹsar|rifdul|marfood!"
11,100,"Ẓaalika|min|ʹambaaaʹil|q̣uraa|naq̣uṣṣuhoo|ʻalayka|minhaa|q̣aaaʹimuñw|waḥaṣeed."
11,101,"Wa-maa|z̤̣alamnaahum|wa-laakiñ|z̤̣alamooo|ʹañfusahum|famaaa|ʹag̣nat|ʻanhum|ʹaalihatuhumul|latee|yadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|miñ|shayʹil|lammaa|jaaaʹa|ʹamru|Rabbik:|wa-maa|zaadoohum|g̣ayra|tatbeeb!"
11,102,"Wa-Kaẓaalika|ʹakhẓu|Rabbika|ʹiẓaaa|ʹakhaẓal|q̣uraa|wa-hiya|z̤̣aalimah:|ʹinna|ʹakhẓahooo|ʹaleemuñ|shadeed."
11,103,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|liman|khaafa|ʻaẓaabal|ʹAakhirah:|ẓaalika|Yawmum|majmooʻul|lahun|naasu|waẓaalika|Yawmum|Mashhood."
11,104,"Wa-maa|nuʹakhkhiruhooo|ʹillaa|liʹajalim|maʻdood."
11,105,"Yawma|yaʹti|laa-|takallamu|nafsun|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnih:|faminhum|shaq̣iyyuñw|wasaʻeed."
11,106,"Faʹammal|laẓeena|shaq̣oo|fafin|naari|lahum|feehaa|zafeeruñw|washaheeq̣."
11,107,"Khaalideena|feehaa|maa-|daamatis|samaawaatu|wal-ʹarḍu|ʹillaa|maa-|shaaaʹa|Rabbuk:|ʹinna|Rabbaka|faʻ-ʻaalul|limaa|yureed."
11,108,"Wa-ʹammal|laẓeena|suʻidoo|fafil|Jannati|khaalideena|feehaa|maa-|daamatis|samaawaatu|wal-ʹarḍu|ʹillaa|maa-|shaaaʹa|Rabbuk:|ʻaṭaaaʹan|g̣ayra|majẓooẓ."
11,109,"Falaa|taku|fee|miryatim|mimmaa|yaʻbudu|haaaʹulaaaʹ.|Maa-|yaʻbudoona|ʹillaa|kamaa|yaʻbudu|ʹaabaaaʹuhum|miñ|q̣abl:|wa-ʹinnaa|lamuwaffoohum|naṣeebahum|g̣ayra|mañq̣ooṣ."
11,110,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|fakhtulifa|feeh:|wa-lawlaa|kalimatuñ|sabaq̣at|mir|Rabbika|laq̣uḍiya|baynahum:|wa-ʹinnahum|lafee|shakkim|minhu|mureeb."
11,111,"Wa-ʹinna|kullal|lammaa|layuwaffiyannahum|Rabbuka|ʹaʻmaalahum:|ʹinnahoo|bimaa|yaʻmaloona|Khabeer."
11,112,"Fastaq̣im|kamaaa|ʹumirta|wa-mañ|taaba|maʻaka|wa-laa|taṭg̣aw:|ʹinnahoo|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
11,113,"Wa-laa|tarkanooo|ʹilal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|fatamassakumun|Naaru,―|wa-maa|lakum|miñ|doonil|laahi|min|ʹawliyaaaʹa|s̤umma|laa-|tuñṣaroon."
11,114,"Wa-ʹaq̣imiṣ|Ṣalaata|ṭarafayin|nahaari|wa-zulafam|minal|layl:|ʹinnal|ḥasanaati|yuẓhibnas|sayyiʹaat:|ẓaalika|ẓikraa|liẓ-ẓaakireen:"
11,115,"Waṣbir|faʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḍeeʻu|ʹajral|Muḥsineen."
11,116,"Falawlaa|kaana|minal|q̣urooni|miñ|q̣ablikum|ʹUloo|baq̣iyyatiñy|yanhawna|ʻanil|fasaadi|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|mimman|ʹañjaynaa|minhum?|Wattabaʻal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|maaa|ʹutrifoo|feehi|wa-kaanoo|mujrimeen."
11,117,"Wa-maa|kaana|Rabbuka|liyuhlikal|q̣uraa|biz̤̣ulmiñw|waʹahluhaa|muṣliḥoon."
11,118,"Wa-law|shaaaʹa|Rabbuka|lajaʻal|annaasa|ʹUmmatañw|waa-ḥidatañw|walaa|yazaaloona|mukhtalifeen."
11,119,"ʹIllaa|mar|raḥima|Rabbuk:|wa-liẓaalika|khalaq̣ahum:|wa-tammat|Kalimatu|Rabbika|laʹamlaʹanna|Jahannama|minal|jinnati|wannaasi|ʹajmaʻeen."
11,120,"Wa-kullan|naq̣uṣṣu|ʻalayka|min|ʹambaaaʹir|rusuli|maa-|nus̤abbitu|bihee|fuʹaadak:|wa-jaaaʹaka|fee|haaẓihil|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-mawʻiz̤̣atuñw|waẓikraa|lil-Muʹmineen."
11,121,"Waq̣ul|lillaẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoo|naʻmaloo|ʻalaa|makaanatikum:|ʹinnaa|ʻaamiloon;"
11,122,"Wañtaz̤̣iroo!|ʹinnaa|muñ-taz̤̣iroon."
11,123,"Wa-lillaahi|g̣aybus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-ʹilayhi|yurjaʻul|ʹamru|kulluhoo|faʻbudhu|wa-tawakkal|ʻalayh:|wa-maa|Rabbuka|big̣aafilin|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon."
12,1,"Alif-Laaam-Raa.|Tilka|ʹAayaatul|kitaabil|Mubeen."
12,2,"ʹInnaaa|ʹañzalnaahu|Q̣urʹaanan|ʻArabiyyal|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
12,3,"Naḥnu|naq̣uṣṣu|ʻalayka|ʹaḥsanal|q̣aṣaṣi|bimaaa|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaan:|wa-ʹiñ|kuñta|miñ|q̣ablihee|laminal|g̣aafileen."
12,4,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|Yoosufu|liʹabeehi|yaaaʹabati|ʹinnee|raʹaytu|ʹaḥada|ʻashara|kawkabañw|washshamsa|walq̣amara|raʹaytuhum|lee|saajideen."
12,5,"Q̣aala|yaa-bunayya|laa-|taq̣ṣuṣ|ruʹyaaka|ʻalaaa|ʹikhwatika|fayakeedoo|laka|kaydaa!|ʹInnash|shayṭaana|lil-ʹiñsaani|ʻaduwwum|mubeen!"
12,6,"Wa-kaẓaalika|yajtabeeka|Rabbuka|wa-yuʻallimuka|miñ|taʹweelil|ʹaḥaadees̤i|wa-yutimmu|niʻmatahoo|ʻalayka|wa-ʻalaaa|ʹaali|Yaʻq̣ooba|kamaaa|ʹatammahaa|ʻalaaa|ʹabawayka|miñ|q̣ablu|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹisḥaaq̣!|ʹInna|Rabbaka|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
12,7,"Laq̣ad|kaana|fee|yoosufa|wa-ʹikhwatihee|ʹAayaatul|lissaaaʹileen."
12,8,"ʹIẓ|q̣aaloo|la-Yoosufu|wa-ʹakhoohu|ʹaḥabbu|ʹilaaa|ʹabeenaa|minnaa|wa-naḥnu|ʻuṣbah!|ʹInna|ʹabaanaa|lafee|ḍalaalim|mubeen!"
12,9,"ʹUq̣tuloo|Yoosufa|ʹawiṭra|ḥoohu|ʹarḍañy|yakhlu|lakum|wajhu|ʹabeekum|wa-takoonoo|mim|baʻdihee|q̣awmañ|ṣaaliḥeen!"
12,10,"Q̣aala|q̣aaaʹilum|minhum|laa-|taq̣tuloo|Yoosufa|wa-ʹalq̣oohu|fee|g̣ayaabatil|jubbi|yaltaq̣iṭhu|baʻḍus|say-yaarati|ʹiñ|kuñtum|faa-ʻileen."
12,11,"Q̣aaloo|yaaaʹabaanaa|maa-|laka|laa-|taʹmannaa|ʻalaa|Yoosufa|wa-ʹinnaa|lahoo|lanaaṣiḥoon?"
12,12,"ʹArsilhu|maʻanaa|g̣adañy|yartaʻwa-|yalʻab|wa-ʹinnaa|lahoo|laḥaafiz̤̣oon."
12,13,"Q̣aala|ʹinnee|layaḥzununeee|ʹañ|taẓhaboo|bihee|wa-ʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yaʹkulahuẓ|ẓiʹbu|wa-ʹañtum|ʻanhu|g̣aafiloon."
12,14,"Q̣aaloo|laʹin|ʹakalahuẓ|ẓiʹbu|wa-naḥnu|ʻuṣbatun|ʹinnaaa|ʹiẓal|lakhaasiroon!"
12,15,"Falammaa|ẓahaboo|bihee|wa-ʹajmaʻooo|ʹañy|yajʻaloohu|fee|g̣ayaabatil|jubb:|wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayhi|latunabbiʹannahum̃|biʹamrihim|haaẓaa|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon."
12,16,"Wa-jaaaʹooo|ʹabaahum|ʻishaaaʹañy|yabkoon."
12,17,"Q̣aaloo|yaaaʹabaanaaa|ʹinnaa|ẓahabnaa|nastabiq̣u|wa-taraknaa|Yoosufa|ʻiñda|mataaʻinaa|faʹakalahuẓ|ẓiʹb.|Wa-maaa|ʹañta|bimuʹminil|lanaa|wa-law|kunnaa|ṣaadiq̣een."
12,18,"Wa-jaaaʹoo|ʻalaa|q̣ameeṣihee|bidamiñ|kaẓib.|Q̣aala|bal|sawwalat|lakum|ʹañfusukum|ʹamraa.|Faṣabruñ|jameel:|wallaahul|Mustaʻaanu|ʻalaa|maa-|taṣifoon."
12,19,"Wa-jaaaʹat|sayyaaratuñ|faʹarsaloo|waaridahum|faʹadlaa|dalwah.|Q̣aala|yaa-bushraa|haaẓaa|g̣ulaam!|Wa-ʹasarroohu|biḍaaʻah!|Wallaahu|ʻaleemum|bimaa|yaʻmaloon!"
12,20,"Wa-sharawhu|bis̤amanim|bakhsiñ|daraahima|maʻdoodah:|wa-kaanoo|feehi|minaz|zaahideen!"
12,21,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓish|taraahu|mim|Miṣra|limraʹatiheee|ʹakrimee|mas̤waahu|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yañfaʻanaaa|ʹaw|nattakhiẓahoo|waladaa.|Wa-kaẓaalika|mak-kannaa|li-Yoosufa|fil|ʹarḍi,|wa-linuʻallimahoo|miñ|taʹweelil|ʹaḥaadees̤.|Wallaahu|g̣aalibun|ʻalaaa|ʹamrihee|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa|yaʻlamoon."
12,22,"Wa-lammaa|balag̣a|ʹashuddahooo|ʹaataynaahu|ḥukmañw|waʻilmaa:|wa-kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
12,23,"Wa-raawadat-hul|latee|huwa|fee|baytihaa|ʻan|nafsihee|wa-g̣allaq̣atil|ʹabwaaba|wa-q̣aalat|hayta|lak!|Q̣aala|maʻaaẓal|laahi|ʹinnahoo|rabbeee|ʹaḥsana|mas̤waay!|Innahoo|laa-|yufliḥuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon!"
12,24,"Wa-laq̣ad|hammat|bihee|wa-hamma|bihaa|laaa-law|ʹar|raʹaa|burhaana|Rabbih:|Kaẓaalika|linaṣrifa|ʻanhus|soooʹa|wal-faḥshaaaʹ:|ʹinnahoo|min|ʻibaadinal|Mukhlaṣeen."
12,25,"Wastabaq̣al|baaba|wa-q̣addat|q̣ameeṣahoo|miñ|duburiñw|waʹalfayaa|sayyidahaa|ladal|baab.|Q̣aalat|maa-|jazaaaʹu|man|ʹaraada|biʹahlika|soooʹan|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yusjana|ʹaw|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem?"
12,26,"Q̣aala|hiya|raawadatnee|ʻan|nafsee|wa-shahida|shaahidum|min|ʹahlihaa:|ʹiñ|kaana|q̣ameeṣuhoo|q̣udda|miñ|q̣ubuliñ|faṣadaq̣at|wa-huwa|minal|kaaẓibeen!"
12,27,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|q̣ameeṣuhoo|q̣udda|miñ|duburiñ|fakaẓabat|wa-huwa|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een!"
12,28,"Falammaa|raʹaa|q̣ameeṣahoo|q̣udda|miñ|duburiñ|q̣aala|ʹinnahoo|miñ|kaydikunna!|ʹInna|kaydakunna|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
12,29,"Yoosufu|ʹaʻriḍ|ʻan|haaẓaa|wastag̣firee|liẓambiki|ʹinnaki|kuñti|minal|khaaṭiʹeen!"
12,30,"Wa-q̣aala|niswatuñ|fil|Madeenatim|raʹatul|ʻAzeezi|turaawidu|fataahaa|ʻan|nafsih:|q̣ad|shag̣afahaa|ḥubbaa:|ʹinnaa|lanaraahaa|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
12,31,"Falammaa|samiʻat|bimakrihinna|ʹarsalat|ʹilayhinna|wa-ʹaʻtadat|lahunna|muttakaʹañw|waʹaatat|kulla|waaḥidatim|min-hunna|sikkeenañw|waq̣aalatikh|ruj|ʻalayhinn.|Falammaa|raʹaynahooo|ʹakbarnahoo|wa-q̣aṭṭaʻna|ʹaydiyahunna|wa-q̣ulna|ḥaasha|lillaahi|maa-|haaẓaa|basharaa!|ʹIn|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|malakuñ|kareem!"
12,32,"Q̣aalat|faẓaalikunnal|laẓee|lumtunnanee|feeh!|Wa-laq̣ad|raawattuhoo|ʻan|nafsihee|fastaʻṣam!|Wa-laʹil|lam|yafʻal|maaa|ʹaamuruhoo|layusjananna|wa-layakoonam|minaṣ|ṣaag̣ireen!"
12,33,"Q̣aala|Rabbis|sijnu|ʹaḥabbu|ʹilayya|mimmaa|yadʻoonaneee|ʹilayh:|wa-ʹillaa|taṣrif|ʻannee|kaydahunna|ʹaṣbu|ʹilayhinna|wa-ʹakum|minal|jaahileen."
12,34,"Fastajaaba|lahoo|Rabbuhoo|faṣarafa|ʻanhu|kaydahunn:|ʹinnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
12,35,"S̤umma|badaa|lahum|mim|baʻdi|maa-|raʹawul|ʹAayaati|layasjununnahoo|ḥattaa|ḥeen."
12,36,"Wa-dakhala|maʻa|hussijna|fatayaan.|Q̣aala|ʹaḥaduhumaaa|ʹinneee|ʹaraaneee|ʹaʻṣiru|khamraa.|Wa-q̣aalal|ʹaakharu|ʹinneee|ʹaraaneee|ʹaḥmilu|fawq̣a|raʹsee|khubzañ|taʹkuluṭ|ṭayru|minh.|Nabbiʹnaa|bitaʹweelih:|ʹinnaa|naraaka|minal|Muḥsineen."
12,37,"Q̣aala|laa-|yaʹteekumaa|ṭaʻaamuñ|turzaq̣aaniheee|ʹillaa|nabbaʹtukumaa|bitaʹweelihee|q̣abla|ʹañy|yaʹtiyakumaa:|ẓaalikumaa|mimmaa|ʻallamanee|Rabbee.|ʹInnee|taraktu|millata|q̣awmil|laa|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wa-hum̃|bil-ʹAakhirati|hum|kaafiroon."
12,38,"Wattabaʻtu|Millata|ʹaabaaaʹeee|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣oob;|maa-|kaana|lanaaa|ʹan|nushrika|billaahi|miñ|shayʹ:|ẓaalika|miñ|faḍlil|laahi|ʻalaynaa|wa-ʻalan|naasi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yashkuroon."
12,39,"Yaa-ṣaaḥibayis|sijni|ʹaʹarbaabum|mutafarriq̣oona|khayrun|ʹamil|laahul|Waaḥidul|Q̣ahhaar?"
12,40,"Maa-|taʻbudoona|miñ|dooniheee|ʹillaaa|ʹasmaaaʹañ|sammaytumoohaaa|ʹañtum|wa-ʹaabaaaʹukum|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|bihaa|miñ|sulṭaan:|ʹinil|Ḥukmu|ʹillaa|lillaah:|ʹamara|ʹallaa|taʻbudooo|ʹillaaa|ʹiyyaah:|ẓaalikad|Deenul|Q̣ayyimu|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
12,41,"Yaa-ṣaaḥibayis|sijni|ʹammaaa|ʹaḥadukumaa|fayasq̣ee|rabbahoo|khamraa:|wa-ʹammal|ʹaakharu|fayuṣlabu|fataʹkuluṭ|ṭayru|mir|raʹsih.|Q̣uḍiyal|ʹamrul|laẓee|feehi|tastaftiyaan."
12,42,"Wa-q̣aala|lillaẓee|z̤̣anna|ʹannahoo|naajim|minhumaẓ|kurnee|ʻiñda|rabbik.|Faʹañsaahush|Shayṭaanu|ẓikra|rabbihee|falabis̤a|fis|sijni|biḍʻa|sineen."
12,43,"Wa-q̣aalal|maliku|ʹinneee|ʹaraa|sabʻa|baq̣araatiñ|simaaniñy|yaʹkuluhunna|sabʻun|ʻijaafuñw|Wasabʻa|sumbulaatin|khuḍriñw|waʹukhara|yaabisaat.|Yaaaʹayyuhal|malaʹu|ʹaftoonee|fee|ruʹyaaya|ʹiñ|kuñtum|lirruʹyaa|taʻburoon."
12,44,"Q̣aalooo|ʹaḍg̣aas̤u|ʹaḥlaam:|Wa-maa|naḥnu|bitaʹweelil|ʹaḥlaami|biʻaalimeen."
12,45,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓee|najaa|minhumaa|waddakara|baʻda|ʹummatin|ʹana|ʹunabbiʹukum̃|bitaʹweelihee|faʹarsiloon."
12,46,"Yoosufu|ʹayyuhaṣ|Ṣiddeeq̣u|ʹaftinaa|fee|sabʻi|baq̣araatiñ|simaaniñy|yaʹkuluhunna|sabʻun|ʻijaafuñw|Wasabʻi|sumbulaatin|khuḍriñw|waʹukhara|yaabisaatil|laʻalleee|ʹarjiʻu|ʹilan|naasi|laʻallahum|yaʻlamoon."
12,47,"Q̣aala|tazraʻoona|sabʻa|sineena|daʹabaa:|famaa|ḥaṣattum|faẓaroohu|fee|sumbuliheee|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|mimmaa|taʹkuloon."
12,48,"S̤umma|yaʹtee|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|sabʻuñ|shidaaduñy|yaʹkulna|maa-|q̣addamtum|lahunna|ʹillaa|q̣aleelam|mimmaa|tuḥṣinoon."
12,49,"S̤umma|yaʹtee|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|ʻaamuñ|feehi|yug̣aas̤un|naasu|wa-feehi|yaʻṣiroon."
12,50,"Wa-q̣aalal|malikuʹ|toonee|bih.|Falammaa|jaaaʹahur|rasoolu|q̣aalar|jiʻ|ʹilaa|rabbika|fasʹalhu|maa-|baalun|niswatil|laatee|q̣aṭṭaʻna|ʹaydiyahunn?|ʹInna|Rabbee|bikaydihinna|ʻAleem."
12,51,"Q̣aala|maa-|khaṭbukunna|ʹiẓ|raawattunna|Yoosufa|ʻan|nafsih?|Q̣ulna|Ḥaasha|lillaahi|maa-|ʻalimnaa|ʻalayhi|miñ|soooʹ!|Q̣aalatim|raʹatul|ʻAzeezil|ʹaana|ḥaṣḥaṣal|ḥaq̣q̣:|ʹana|raawattuhoo|ʻan|nafsihee|wa-ʹinnahoo|laminaṣ|Ṣaadiq̣een."
12,52,"Ẓaalika|liyaʻlama|ʹannee|lam|ʹakhunhu|bilg̣aybi|wa-ʹannal|laaha|laa-|yahdee|kaydal|khaaaʹineen."
12,53,"Wa-maaa|ʹubarriʻu|nafsee:|ʹinnan|nafsa|laʹammaaratum|bissoooʹi|ʹillaa|maa-|raḥima|Rabbee:|ʹinna|Rabbee|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
12,54,"Wa-q̣aalal|malikuʹ|toonee|biheee|ʹastakhliṣhu|linafsee.|Falammaa|kallamahoo|q̣aala|ʹinnakal|yawma|ladaynaa|makeenun|ʹameen!"
12,55,"Q̣aalaj|ʻalnee|ʻalaa|khazaaaʹinil|ʹarḍ:|ʹinnee|ḥafeez̤̣un|ʻaleem."
12,56,"Wa-kaẓaalika|makkannaa|li-Yoosufa|fil|ʹarḍi|yatabawwaʹu|minhaa|ḥays̤u|yashaaaʹ.|Nuṣeebu|bi-Raḥmatinaa|man|nashaaaʹu|wa-laa|nuḍeeʻu|ʹajral|Muḥsineen."
12,57,"Wa-laʹajrul|ʹAakhirati|khayrul|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-kaanoo|yattaq̣oon."
12,58,"Wa-jaaaʹa|ʹikhwatu|Yoosufa|fadakhaloo|ʻalayhi|faʻarafahum|wa-hum|lahoo|muñkiroon."
12,59,"Wa-lammaa|jahhazahum̃|bijahaazihim|q̣aalaʹ|toonee|biʹakhil|lakum|min|ʹabeekum:|ʹalaa|tarawna|ʹanneee|ʹoofil|kayla|wa-ʹana|khayrul|muñzileen?"
12,60,"Faʹil|lam|taʹtoonee|bihee|falaa|kayla|lakum|ʻiñdee|wa-laa|taq̣raboon."
12,61,"Q̣aaloo|sanuraawidu|ʻanhu|ʹabaahu|wa-ʹinnaa|lafaaʻiloon."
12,62,"Wa-q̣aala|lifityaanihij|ʻaloo|biḍaaʻatahum|fee|riḥaalihim|laʻallahum|yaʻrifoonahaaa|ʹiẓañ|q̣alabooo|ʹilaaa|ʹahlihim|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
12,63,"Falammaa|rajaʻooo|ʹilaaa|ʹabeehim|q̣aaloo|yaaaʹabaanaa|muniʻa|minnal|kaylu|faʹarsil|maʻanaaa|ʹakhaanaa|naktal|wa-ʹinnaa|lahoo|laḥaafiz̤̣oon."
12,64,"Q̣aala|hal|ʹaamanukum|ʻalayhi|ʹillaa|kamaaa|ʹamiñtukum|ʻalaaa|ʹakheehi|miñ|q̣abl?|Fal-laahu|khayrun|ḥaafiz̤̣aa,|wa-Huwa|ʹArḥamur|raaḥimeen!"
12,65,"Wa-lammaa|fataḥoo|mataaʻahum|wajadoo|biḍaaʻatahum|ruddat|ʹilayhim.|Q̣aaloo|yaaaʹabaanaa|maa-|nabg̣ee?|Haaẓihee|biḍaaʻatunaa|ruddat|ʹilaynaa:|wa-nameeru|ʹahlanaa|wa-naḥfaz̤̣u|ʹakhaanaa|wa-nazdaadu|kayla|baʻeer.|Ẓaalika|kayluñy|yaseer."
12,66,"Q̣aala|lan|ʹursilahoo|maʻakum|ḥattaa|tuʹtooni|maws̤iq̣am|minal|laahi|lataʹtunnanee|biheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yuḥaaṭa|bikum.|Falammaaa|ʹaatawhu|maws̤iq̣ahum|q̣aalal|laahu|ʻalaa|maa-|naq̣oolu|Wakeel!"
12,67,"Wa-q̣aala|yaa-baniyya|laa-|tadkhuloo|mim|baabiñw|waa-ḥidiñw|wadkhuloo|min|ʹabwaabim|mutafarriq̣ah.|Wa-maaa|ʹug̣nee|ʻañkum|minal|laahi|miñ|shayʹ:|ʹinil|ḥukmu|ʹillaa|lillaah:|ʻalayhi|tawakkalt:|wa-ʻalayhi|fal-yatawakkalil|Mutawakkiloon."
12,68,"Wa-lammaa|dakhaloo|min|ḥays̤u|ʹamarahum|ʹaboohum;|maa-|kaana|yug̣nee|ʻanhum|minal|laahi|miñ|shayʹin|ʹillaa|ḥaajatañ|fee|nafsi|Yaʻq̣ooba|q̣aḍaahaa.|Wa-ʹinnahoo|laẓoo|ʻilmil|limaa|ʻallamnaahu|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
12,69,"Wa-lammaa|dakhaloo|ʻalaa|Yoosufa|ʹaawaaa|ʹilayhi|ʹakhaahu|q̣aala|ʹinneee|ʹana|ʹakhooka|falaa|tabtaʹis|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
12,70,"Falammaa|jahhazahum̃|bijahaazihim|jaʻalas|siq̣aayata|fee|raḥli|ʹakheehi|s̤umma|ʹaẓẓana|Muʹaẓẓinun|ʹayyatuhal|ʻeeru|ʹinnakum|lasaariq̣oon!"
12,71,"Q̣aaloo|wa-ʹaq̣baloo|ʻalayhim|maaẓaa|tafq̣idoon?"
12,72,"Q̣aaloo|nafq̣idu|ṣuwaaʻal|maliki|wa-limañ|jaaaʹa|bihee|ḥimlu|baʻeeriñw|waʹana|bihee|zaʻeem."
12,73,"Q̣aaloo|tallaahi|laq̣ad|ʻalimtum|maa|jiʹnaa|linufsida|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|kunnaa|saariq̣een."
12,74,"Q̣aaloo|famaa|jazaaaʹuhooo|ʹiñ|kuñtum|kaaẓibeen?"
12,75,"Q̣aaloo|jazaaaʹuhoo|mañw|wujida|fee|raḥlihee|fahuwa|jazaaaʹuh.|Kaẓaalika|najziz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
12,76,"Fabadaʹa|biʹawʻiyatihim|q̣abla|wiʻaaaʹi|ʹakheehi|s̤ummas|takhrajahaa|miñw|wiʻaaaʹi|ʹakheeh.|Kaẓaalika|kidnaa|li-Yoosuf.|Maa-|kaana|liyaʹkhuẓa|ʹakhaahu|fee|deenil|maliki|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yashaaaʹal|laah.|Narfaʻu|darajaatim|man|nashaaaʹ:|wa-fawq̣a|kulli|ẓee|ʻilmin|ʻAleem."
12,77,"Q̣aalooo|ʹiñy|yasriq̣|faq̣ad|saraq̣a|ʹakhul|lahoo|miñ|q̣abl.|Faʹasarrahaa|Yoosufu|fee|nafsihee|wa-lam|yubdihaa|lahum.|Q̣aala|ʹañtum|sharrum|makaanaa;|wallaahu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|taṣifoon!"
12,78,"Q̣aaloo|yaaaʹayyuhal|ʻAzeezu|ʹinna|lahooo|ʹabañ|shaykhañ|kabeerañ|fakhuẓ|ʹaḥadanaa|makaanah;|ʹinnaa|naraaka|minal|Muḥsineen."
12,79,"Q̣aala|maʻaaẓal|laahi|ʹan|naʹkhuẓa|ʹillaa|mañw|wajadnaa|mataaʻanaa|ʻiñdahooo|ʹinnaaa|ʹiẓal|laz̤̣aalimoon."
12,80,"Falammas|tayʹasoo|minhu|khalaṣoo|najiyyaa.|Q̣aala|kabeeruhum|ʹalam|taʻlamooo|ʹanna|ʹabaakum|q̣ad|ʹakhaẓa|ʻalaykum|maws̤iq̣am|minal|laahi|wamiñ|q̣ablu|maa-|farraṭtum|fee|Yoosuf?|Falan|ʹabraḥal|ʹarḍa|ḥattaa|yaʹẓana|leee|ʹabeee|ʹaw|yaḥkumal|laahu|lee;|wa-huwa|khayrul|ḥaakimeen."
12,81,"ʹIrjiʻooo|ʹilaaa|ʹabeekum|faq̣ooloo|yaaaʹabaanaaa|ʹinnab|naka|saraq̣!|Wa-maa|shahidnaaa|ʹillaa|bimaa|ʻalimnaa|wa-maa|kunnaa|lilg̣aybi|ḥaafiz̤̣een!"
12,82,"Wasʹalil|q̣aryatal|latee|kunnaa|feehaa|walʻeeral|lateee|ʹaq̣balnaa|feehaa,|wa-ʹinnaa|laṣaadiq̣oon."
12,83,"Q̣aala|bal|sawwalat|lakum|ʹañfusukum|ʹamraa.|Faṣabruñ|jameel.|ʻAsal|laahu|ʹañy|yaʹ-tiyanee|bihim|jameeʻaa.|ʹInna-Hoo|Huwal|ʻAleemul|Ḥakeem."
12,84,"Wa-tawallaa|ʻanhum|wa-q̣aala|yaaaʹasafaa|ʻalaa|Yoosufa|wabyaḍḍat|ʻaynaahu|minal|ḥuzni|fahuwa|kaz̤̣eem."
12,85,"Q̣aaloo|tallaahi|taftaʹu|taẓkuru|Yoosufa|ḥattaa|takoona|ḥaraḍan|ʹaw|takoona|minal|haalikeen!"
12,86,"Q̣aala|ʹinnamaaa|ʹashkoo|bas̤s̤ee|waḥuzneee|ʹilal|laahi|wa-ʹaʻlamu|minal|laahi|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon."
12,87,"Yaa-baniyyaẓ|haboo|fataḥassasoo|miñy|Yoosufa|wa-ʹakheehi|wa-laa|tayʹasoo|mir|Rawḥil|laah:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yayʹasu|mir|Rawḥil|laahi|ʹillal|q̣awmul|Kaafiroon."
12,88,"Falammaa|dakhaloo|ʻalayhi|q̣aaloo|yaaaʹayyuhal|ʻAzeezu|massanaa|wa-ʹahlanaḍ|ḍurru|wa-jiʹnaa|bibiḍaaʻatim|muzjaatiñ|faʹawfi|lanal|kayla|wa-taṣaddaq̣|ʻalaynaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|yajzil|Mutaṣaddiq̣een."
12,89,"Q̣aala|hal|ʻalimtum|maa|faʻaltum̃|bi-Yoosufa|wa-ʹakheehi|ʹiẓ|ʹañtum|jaahiloon?"
12,90,"Q̣aalooo|ʹa-ʹinnaka|laʹañta|Yoosuf?|Q̣aala|ʹana|Yoosufu|wa-haaẓaaa|ʹakhee;|q̣ad|mannal|laahu|ʻalaynaa.|ʹInnahoo|mañy|yattaq̣i|wa-yaṣbir|faʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḍeeʻu|ʹajral|Muḥsineen."
12,91,"Q̣aaloo|tallaahi|laq̣ad|ʹaas̤arakal|laahu|ʻalaynaa|wa-ʹiñ|kunnaa|lakhaaṭiʹeen!"
12,92,"Q̣aala|laa-|tas̤reeba|ʻalaykumul|yawm.|Yag̣firul|laahu|lakum|wa-Huwa|ʹArḥamur|raaḥimeen!"
12,93,"ʹIẓhaboo|biq̣ameeṣee|haaẓaa|faʹalq̣oohu|ʻalaa|wajhi|ʹabee|yaʹti|baṣeeraa.|Waʹtoonee|biʹahlikum|ʹajmaʻeen."
12,94,"Wa-lammaa|faṣalatil|ʻeeru|q̣aala|ʹaboohum|ʹinnee|laʹajidu|reeḥa|Yoosufa|Laaa-law|ʹañ|tufannidoon."
12,95,"Q̣aaloo|tallaahi|ʹinnaka|lafee|ḍalaalikal|q̣adeem."
12,96,"Falammaaa|ʹañ|jaaa|ʹalbasheeru|ʹalq̣aahu|ʻalaa|wajhihee|fartadda|baṣeeraa.|Q̣aala|ʹalam|ʹaq̣ul|lakum.|ʹinneee|ʹaʻlamu|minal|laahi|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon?"
12,97,"Q̣aaloo|yaaaʹabaanas|tag̣fir|lanaa|ẓunoobanaaa|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|khaaṭiʹeen."
12,98,"Q̣aala|sawfa|ʹastag̣firu|lakum|Rabbee:|ʹinna-Hoo|Huwal|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
12,99,"Falammaa|dakhaloo|ʻalaa|Yoosufa|ʹaawaaa|ʹilayhi|ʹabawayhi|wa-q̣aalad|khuloo|Miṣra|ʹiñ|shaaa|ʹallaahu|ʹaamineen."
12,100,"Wa-rafaʻa|ʹabawayhi|ʻalal|ʻarshi|wa-kharroo|lahoo|sujjadaa.|Wa-q̣aala|yaaaʹabati|haaẓaa|taʹweelu|ruʹyaaya|miñ|q̣ablu|q̣ad|jaʻalahaa|Rabbee|ḥaq̣q̣aa!|Wa-q̣ad|ʹaḥsana|beee|ʹiẓ|ʹakhrajanee|minas|sijni|wa-jaaaʹa|bikum|minal|badwi|mim|baʻdi|ʹan|nazag̣ash|shayṭaanu|baynee|wa-bayna|ʹikhwatee.|ʹInna|Rabbee|Laṭeeful|limaa|yashaaaʹ.|ʹInna-Hoo|Huwal|ʻAleemul|Ḥakeem."
12,101,"Rabbi|q̣ad|ʹaataytanee|minal|mulki|wa-ʻallamtanee|miñ|taʹweelil|ʹaḥaadees̤,―|Faaṭiras|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ!|ʹAñta|Waliyyee|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah.|Tawaffanee|Muslimañw|waʹalḥiq̣nee|biṣ-Ṣaaliḥeen."
12,102,"Ẓaalika|min|ʹambaaaʹil|g̣aybi|nooḥeehi|ʹilayk:|wa-maa|kuñta|ladayhim|ʹiẓ|ʹajmaʻooo|ʹamrahum|wa-hum|yamkuroon."
12,103,"Wa-maaa|ʹaks̤arun|naasi|wa-law|ḥaraṣta|bi-Muʹmineen."
12,104,"Wa-maa|tasʹaluhum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajr:|ʹin|huwa|ʹillaa|Ẓikrul|lilʻaalameen."
12,105,"Wa-kaʹayyim|min|ʹAayatiñ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|yamurroona|ʻalayhaa|wa-hum|ʻanhaa|muʻriḍoon!"
12,106,"Wa-maa|yuʹminu|ʹaks̤aruhum̃|billaahi|ʹillaa|wa-hum|mushrikoon!"
12,107,"ʹA-faʹaminooo|ʹañ|taʹtiyahum|G̣aashiyatum|min|ʻaẓaabil|laahi|ʹaw|taʹtiyahumus|saaʻatu|wahum|bag̣tatañw|laa-|yashʻuroon?"
12,108,"Q̣ul|haaẓihee|sabeeleee|ʹadʻooo|ʹilal|laah:―|ʻalaa|Baṣeeratin|ʹana|wa-manit|tabaʻanee.|Wa-Subḥaanal|laahi|wa-maaa|ʹana|minal|mushrikeen!"
12,109,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|ʹillaa|rijaalan|nooḥeee|ʹilayhim|min|ʹahlil|q̣uraa.|ʹAfalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|Fayañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim?|Wa-la-Daarul|ʹAakhirati|khayrul|lillaẓeenat|taq̣aw.|ʹAfalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
12,110,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓas|tayʹasar|rusulu|waz̤̣annooo|ʹannahum|q̣ad|kuẓiboo|jaaaʹahum|naṣ-runaa|fanujjiya|man|nashaaaʹ.|Wa-laa|yuraddu|baʹsunaa|ʻanil|q̣awmil|mujrimeen."
12,111,"Laq̣ad|kaana|fee|q̣aṣaṣihim|ʻibratul|liʹulil|ʹalbaab.|Maa-|kaana|ḥadees̤añy|yuftaraa|wa-laakiñ|taṣdeeq̣al|laẓee|bayna|yadayhi|wa-tafṣeela|kulli|shayʹiñw|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatal|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
13,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Meeem-Raa.|Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Kitaab.|Wallaẓeee|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbikal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yuʹminoon."
13,2,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|rafaʻas|samaawaati|big̣ayri|ʻamadiñ|tarawnahaa|s̤ummas|tawaa|ʻalal|ʻArshi|wa-sakhkharash|shamsa|walq̣amar!|Kulluñy|yajree|liʹajalim|musammaa.|Yudabbirul|ʹamra|yufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|laʻallakum̃|biliq̣aaaʹi|Rabbikum|tooq̣inoon."
13,3,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|maddal|ʹarḍa|wa-jaʻala|feehaa|rawaasiya|wa-ʹanhaaraa:|wa-miñ|kullis̤|s̤amaraati|jaʻala|feehaa|zawjaynis̤|nayni|yug̣shil|laylan|nahaar.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
13,4,"Wa-fil|ʹarḍi|q̣iṭaʻum|mutajaawiraatuñw|wajannaatum|min|ʹaʻnaabiñw|Wazarʻuñw|Wanakheeluñ|ṣinwaanuñw|wag̣ayru|ṣinwaaniñy|yusq̣aa|bimaaaʹiñw|waaḥid.|Wa-nufaḍḍilu|baʻḍahaa|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñ|fil|ʹukul.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon!"
13,5,"Wa-ʹiñ|taʻjab|faʻajabuñ|q̣awluhum|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|kunnaa|turaaban|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lafee|khalq̣iñ|jadeed?|ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|kafaroo|bi-Rabbihim!|Wa-ʹulaaaʹikal|ʹag̣laalu|feee|ʹaʻnaaq̣ihim:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon!"
13,6,"Wa-yastaʻjiloonaka|Bis-sayyiʹati|q̣ablal|ḥasanati|wa-q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablihimul|Mas̤ulaat!|Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Ẓoo|Mag̣firatil|linnaasi|ʻalaa|z̤̣ulmihim,|wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
13,7,"Wa-yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|kafaroo|law-laaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalayhi|ʹAayatum|mir|Rabbih?|ʹInnamaaa|ʹañta|muñẓiruñw|walikulli|q̣awmin|haad."
13,8,"ʹAllaahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|taḥmilu|kullu|ʹuñs̤aa|wa-maa|tag̣eeḍul|ʹarḥaamu|wa-maa|tazdaad.|Wa-kullu|shayʹin|ʻiñdahoo|bimiq̣daar."
13,9,"ʻAalimul|G̣aybi|wash-Shahaadatil|Kabeerul|Mutaʻaal."
13,10,"Sawaaaʹum|miñkum|man|ʹasarral|q̣awla|wa-mañ|jahara|bihee|wa-man|huwa|mustakhfim|billayli|wa-saaribum|binnahaar."
13,11,"Lahoo|muʻaq̣q̣ibaatum|mim|bayni|yadayhi|wa-min|khalfihee|yaḥfaz̤̣oonahoo|min|ʹamril|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yug̣ayyiru|maa-|biq̣awmin|ḥattaa|yug̣ayyiroo|maa-|biʹañfusihim.|Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹaraadal|laahu|biq̣awmiñ|soooʹañ|falaa-|maradda|lahoo|wa-maa|lahum|miñ|doonihee|miñw|waal."
13,12,"Huwal|laẓee|yureekumul|barq̣a|khawfañw|waṭamaʻañw|wayuñshiʹus|saḥaabas̤|s̤iq̣aal!"
13,13,"Wa-yusabbiḥur|RAʻDU|bi-Ḥamdihee|walmalaaaʹikatu|min|kheefatih:|wa-yursiluṣ|ṣawaaʻiq̣a|fayuṣeebu|bihaa|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-hum|yujaadiloona|fil|laahi,|wa-Huwa|Shadeedul|miḥaal!"
13,14,"Lahoo|daʻwatul|Ḥaq̣q̣:|wallaẓeena|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|laa-|yastajeeboona|lahum̃|bishayʹin|ʹillaa|kabaasiṭi|kaffayhi|ʹilal|maaaʹi|liyablug̣a|faahu|wa-maa|huwa|bibaalig̣ih:|wa-maa|duʻaaaʹul|kaafireena|ʹillaa|fee|ḍalaal."
13,15,"Wa-lillaahi|yasjudu|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|ṭaw-ʻañw|wakarhañw|waz̤̣ilaaluhum̃|bilg̣uduwwi|wal-ʹaaṣaal."
13,16,"Q̣ul|mar|Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Q̣ulil|laah.|Q̣ul|ʹafattakhaẓtum|miñ|dooniheee|ʹawliyaaaʹa|laa-|yamlikoona|liʹañfusihim|nafʻañw|walaa|ḍarraa?|Q̣ul|hal|yastawil|ʹaʻmaa|wal-baṣeer.|ʹAm|hal|tastawiz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaatu|wannoor?|ʹAm|jaʻaloo|lillaahi|shurakaaaʹa|khalaq̣oo|kakhalq̣ihee|fatashaabahal|khalq̣u|ʻalayhim?|Q̣ulil|laahu|Khaaliq̣u|kulli|shayʹiñw|wa-Huwal|Waaḥidul|Q̣ahhaar."
13,17,"ʹAñzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|fasaalat|ʹawdiyatum|biq̣adarihaa|faḥtamalas|saylu|zabadar|raabiyaa.|Wa-mimmaa|yooq̣idoona|ʻalayhi|fin|naarib|tig̣aaaʹa|ḥilyatin|ʹaw|mataaʻiñ|zabadum|mis̤luh.|Kaẓalika|yaḍribul|laahul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wal-Baaṭil.|Faʹammaz|zabadu|fayaẓhabu|jufaaaʹaa.|Waʹammaa|maa-|yañfaʻun|naasa|fayamkus̤u|fil|ʹarḍ.|Kaẓaalika|yaḍribul|laahul|ʹams̤aal."
13,18,"Lillaẓeenas|tajaaboo|li-Rabbihimul|Ḥusnaa.|Wallaẓeena|lam|yastajeeboo|lahoo|law|ʹanna|lahum|maa|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻañw|wamis̤lahoo|maʻahoo|laftadaw|bih.|ʹUlaaaʹika|lahum|soooʹul|ḥisaab:|wa-maʹwaahum|jahannam.―|wabiʹsal|mihaad!"
13,19,"ʹAfamañy|yaʻlamu|ʹannamaaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbikal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|kaman|huwa|ʹaʻmaa?|ʹInnamaa|yataẓakkaru|ʹulul|ʹalbaab;―"
13,20,"ʹAllaẓeena|yoofoona|biʻAhdil|laahi|wa-laa|yañq̣uḍoonal|Mees̤aaq̣;"
13,21,"Wallaẓeena|yaṣiloona|maaa|ʹamaral|laahu|biheee|ʹañy|yooṣala|wa-yakhshawna|Rabbahum|wa-yakhaafoona|soooʹal|ḥisaab;"
13,22,"Wallaẓeena|ṣabarub|tig̣aaaʹa|Wajhi|Rabbihim|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹañfaq̣oo|mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|sirrañw|waʻalaaniyatañw|wayadraʹoona|bilḥasanatis|sayyiʹata|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻuq̣bad|Daar,―"
13,23,"Jannaatu|ʻAdniñy|yadkhuloonahaa|wa-mañ|ṣalaḥa|min|ʹaabaaaʹihim|wa-ʹazwaajihim|waẓurriyyaatihim|walmalaaaʹikatu|yadkhuloona|ʻalayhim|miñ|kulli|baab."
13,24,"Salaamun|ʻalaykum̃|bimaa|ṣabartum|faniʻma|ʻuq̣bad|Daar!"
13,25,"Wallaẓeena|yañq̣uḍoona|ʻAhdal|laahi|mim|baʻdi|Mees̤aaq̣ihee|wa-yaq̣ṭaʻoona|maaa|ʹamaral|laahu|biheee|ʹañy|yooṣala|wa-yufsidoona|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹulaaaʹika|lahumul|Laʻnatu|wa-lahum|soooʹud|Daar!"
13,26,"ʹAllaahu|yabsuṭur|Rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaq̣dir.|Wa-fariḥoo|bilḥayaatid|dunyaa.|Wa-mal|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʹillaa|mataaʻ."
13,27,"Wa-yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|kafaroo|laaa-law|ʹuñzila|ʻalayhi|ʹAayatum|mir|Rabbih?|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḍillu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yahdeee|ʹilayhi|man|ʹanaab."
13,28,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-taṭmaʹinnu|q̣uloobuhum̃|biẓikril|laah.|ʹAlaa|biẓikril|laahi|taṭmaʹinnul|q̣uloob."
13,29,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|ṭoobaa|lahum|waḥusnu|maʹaab."
13,30,"Kaẓaalika|ʹarsalnaaka|feee|ʹUmmatiñ|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablihaaa|ʹUmamul|litatluwa|ʻalayhimul|laẓeee|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|wa-hum|yakfuroona|bir-Raḥmaan!|Q̣ul|Huwa|Rabbee|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo!|ʻAlayhi|tawakkaltu|wa-ʹilayhi|mataab!"
13,31,"Wa-law|ʹanna|q̣urʹaanañ|suyyirat|bihil|jibaalu|ʹaw|q̣uṭṭiʻat|bihil|ʹarḍu|ʹaw|kullima|bihil|mawtaa,|bal|lillaahil|ʹAmru|jameeʻaa!|ʹAfalam|yayʹasil|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹal|law|yashaaa|ʹullaahu|lahadan|naasa|jameeʻaa?|Wa-laa|yazaalul|laẓeena|kafaroo|tuṣeebuhum̃|bimaa|ṣanaʻoo|Q̣aariʻatun|ʹaw|taḥullu|q̣areebam|miñ|daarihim|ḥattaa|yaʹtiya|waʻdul|laah.|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yukhliful|meeʻaad."
13,32,"Wa-laq̣adis|tuhziʹa|birusulim|miñ|q̣ablika|faʹamlaytu|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|s̤umma|ʹakhaẓtuhum:|fakayfa|kaana|ʻiq̣aab!"
13,33,"ʹAfaman|Huwa|q̣aaaʹimun|ʻalaa|kulli|nafsim|bimaa|Kasabat?|Wa-jaʻaloo|lil-laahi|shurakaaaʹ.|Q̣ul|sammoohum!|ʹAm|tunabbiʹoonahoo|bimaa|laa-|yaʻlamu|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹam|biz̤̣aahirim|minal|q̣awl?|Bal|zuyyina|lillazeena|kafaroo|makruhum|waṣuddoo|ʻanis|Sabeel.|Wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|min|haad."
13,34,"Lahum|ʻaẓaabuñ|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-laʻaẓaabul|ʹAakhirati|ʹashaq̣q̣:|wa-maa|lahum|minal|laahi|miñw|waaq̣."
13,35,"Mas̤alul|jannatil|latee|wuʻidal|Muttaq̣oon!|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaar:|ʹukuluhaa|daaaʹimuñw|waz̤̣illuhaa:|tilka|ʻUq̣bal|laẓeenat|taq̣aw:|Wa-ʻUq̣bal|kaafireenan|Naar."
13,36,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|yafraḥoona|bimaaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|wa-minal|ʹaḥzaabi|mañy|yuñkiru|baʻḍah.|Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹaʻbudal|laaha|wa-laaa|ʹushrika|bih.|ʹIlayhi|ʹadʻoo|wa-ʹilayhi|maʹaaab."
13,37,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ʹañzalnaahu|Ḥukman|ʻArabiyyaa.|Wa-laʹinit|tabaʻta|ʹahwaaaʹahum̃|baʻdamaa|jaaaʹaka|minal|ʻilmi|maa-|laka|minal|laahi|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|waaq̣."
13,38,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|rusulam|miñ|q̣ablika|wa-jaʻalnaa|lahum|ʹazwaajañw|waẓurriyyah:|wa-maa|kaana|lirasoolin|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|biʹAayatin|ʹillaa|biʹIẓnil|laah.|Likulli|ʹajaliñ|kitaab."
13,39,"Yamḥul|laahu|maa-|yashaaaʹu|wa-yus̤bitu|ʻiñdahooo|ʹummul|Kitaab."
13,40,"Wa-ʹim|maa|nuriyannaka|baʻḍal|laẓee|naʻiduhum|ʹaw|natawaffayannaka|faʹinnamaa|ʻalaykal|balaag̣u|wa-ʻalaynal|ḥisaab."
13,41,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannaa|naʹtil|ʹarḍa|nañq̣uṣuhaa|min|ʹaṭraafihaa?|Wallaahu|yaḥkumu|laa-|muʻaq̣q̣iba|li-Ḥukmih:|wa-Huwa|Sareeʻul|ḥisaab."
13,42,"Wa-q̣ad|makaral|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|falillaahil|makru|jameeʻaa.|Yaʻlamu|maa-|taksibu|kullu|nafs:|wa-sayaʻlamul|kuffaaru|liman|ʻUq̣bad|Daar."
13,43,"Wa-yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|kafaroo|lasta|mursalaa.|Q̣ul|kafaa|billaahi|shaheedam|baynee|wa-baynakum|wa-man|ʻiñdahoo|ʻilmul|Kitaab."
14,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Raa.|Kitaabun|ʹañzalnaahu|ʹilayka|litukhrijan|naasa|minaz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|Noori―|biʹiẓni|Rabbihim|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥameed!―"
14,2,"ʹAllaahil|laẓee|lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ!|Wa-waylul|lilkaafireena|min|ʻaẓaabiñ|shadeed!"
14,3,"ʹAllaẓeena|yastaḥibboonal|ḥayaatad|dunyaa|ʻalal|ʹAakhirati|wa-yaṣuddoona|ʻañ|sabeelil|laahi|wa-yabg̣oonahaa|ʻiwajaa:|ʹUlaaaʹika|fee|ḍalaalim|baʻeed."
14,4,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|mir|rasoolin|ʹillaa|bilisaani|q̣awmihee|liyubayyina|Lahum.|Fayuḍillul|laahu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
14,5,"wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Moosaa|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹan|ʹakhrij|q̣awmaka|minaz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|Noori,|waẓakkirhum̃|biʹAyyaamil|laah.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|likulli|ṣabbaariñ|shakoor."
14,6,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|liq̣awmihiẓ|kuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓ|ʹañjaakum|min|ʹAali|Firʻawna|yasoomoonakum|soooʹal|ʻaẓaabi|wa-yuẓabbiḥoona|ʹabnaaaʹakum|wa-yastaḥyoona|nisaaʹakum:|wa-fee|ẓaalikum|balaaaʹum|mir|Rabbikum|ʻaz̤̣eem."
14,7,"Wa-ʹiẓ|taʹaẓẓana|Rabbukum|laʹiñ|shakartum|laʹazeedannakum|wa-laʹiñ|kafartum|ʹinna|ʻaẓaabee|lashadeed."
14,8,"Wa-q̣aala|Moosaaa|ʹiñ|takfurooo|ʹañtum|wa-mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻañ|faʹinnal|laaha|la-G̣aniyyun|Ḥameed."
14,9,"ʹAlam|yaʹtikum|nabaʹul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablikum|Q̣awmi|Nooḥiñw|waʻAadiñw|wa-S̤amooda|wallaẓeena|mim|baʻdihim?|Laa-|yaʻlamuhum|ʹillallaah.|Jaaaʹat|hum|rusuluhum|bilbayyinaati|faraddooo|ʹaydiyahum|feee|ʹafwaahihim|wa-q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|kafarnaa|bimaaa|ʹursiltum̃|bihee|wa-ʹinnaa|lafee|shakkim|mimmaa|tadʻoonanaaa|ʹilayhi|mureeb."
14,10,"Q̣aalat|rusuluhum|ʹafil|laahi|shakkuñ|Faaṭiris|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Yadʻookum|liyag̣fira|lakum|miñ|ẓunoobikum|wa-yuʹakhkhirakum|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammaa!|Q̣aalooo|ʹin|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lunaa!|Tureedoona|ʹañ|taṣuddoonaa|ʻammaa|kaana|yaʻbudu|ʹaabaaaʹunaa|faʹtoonaa|bisulṭaanim|mubeen."
14,11,"Q̣aalat|lahum|rusuluhum|ʹin|naḥnu|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lukum|wa-laakinnal|laaha|yamunnu|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadih.|Wa-maa|kaana|lanaaa|ʹan|naʹtiyakum̃|bisulṭaanin|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnil|laah.|Wa-ʻalal|laahi|falyatawakkalil|Muʹminoon."
14,12,"Wa-maa|lanaaa|ʹallaa|natawakkala|ʻalal|laahi|wa-q̣ad|hadaanaa|Subulanaa.|Wa-lanaṣbiranna|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹaaẓaytumoonaa.|Wa-ʻalal|laahi|falyatawakkalil|Mutawakkiloon."
14,13,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lirusulihim|lanukhrijannakum|min|ʹarḍinaaa|ʹaw|lataʻoodunna|fee|millatinaa.|Faʹawḥaaa|ʹilayhim|Rabbuhum|lanuhlikannaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
14,14,"Wa-lanuskinan-nakumul|ʹarḍa|mim|baʻdihim.|Ẓaalika|liman|khaafa|Maq̣aamee|wa-khaafa|waʻeed."
14,15,"wastaftaḥoo|wa-khaaba|kullu|jabbaarin|ʻaneed;"
14,16,"Miñw|waraaaʹihee|Jahannamu|wa-yusq̣aa|mim|maaaʹiñ|ṣadeed."
14,17,"Yatajarraʻuhoo|wa-laa|yakaadu|yuseeg̣uhoo|wayaʹteehil|mawtu|miñ|kulli|makaaniñw|wamaa|huwa|bimayyit:|wa-miñw|waraaaʹihee|ʻaẓaabun|g̣aleez̤̣."
14,18,"Mas̤alul|laẓeena|kafaroo|bi-Rabbihim|ʹaʻmaaluhum|karamaadinish|taddat|bihir|reeḥu|fee|yawmin|ʻaaṣif:|laa-|yaq̣diroona|mimmaa|kasaboo|ʻalaa|shayʹ:|ẓaalika|huwaḍ|ḍalaalul|baʻeed."
14,19,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣?|ʹIñy|yashaʹ|yuẓhibkum|wa-yaʹti|bikhalq̣iñ|jadeed."
14,20,"Wa-maa|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|biʻazeez."
14,21,"Wa-barazoo|lillaahi|jameeʻañ|faq̣aalaḍ|ḍuʻafaaaʹu|lil-laẓeenas|takbarooo|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|lakum|tabaʻañ|fahal|ʹañtum|mug̣noona|ʻannaa|min|ʻAẓaabil|laahi|miñ|shayʹ?|Q̣aaloo|law|hadaanal|laahu|lahadaynaakum!|Sawaaaʹun|ʻalaynaaa|ʹajaziʻnaaa|ʹam|ṣabarnaa|maa-|lanaa|mim|maḥeeṣ."
14,22,"Wa-q̣aalash|shayṭaanu|lammaa|q̣uḍiyal|ʹamru|ʹinnal|laaha|waʻadakum|waʻdal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-waʻattukum|faʹakhlaftukum.|Wa-maa|kaana|liya|ʻalaykum|miñ|sulṭaanin|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|daʻawtukum|fastajabtum|lee:|falaa|taloomoonee|wa-loomooo|ʹañfusakum.|Maaa|ʹana|bimuṣrikhikum|wa-maaa|ʹañtum|bimuṣrikhiyy.|ʹInnee|kafartu|bimaaa|ʹashraktumooni|miñ|q̣abl.|ʹInnaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
14,23,"Wa-ʹudkhilal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa|biʹiẓni|Rabbihim.|Taḥiyyatuhum|feehaa|salaam!"
14,24,"ʹAlam|tara|kayfa|ḍarabal|laahu|mas̤alañ|Kalimatañ|Ṭayyibatañ|kashajaratiñ|ṭayyibatin|ʹaṣluhaa|s̤aabituñw|wafarʻuhaa|fis|samaaaʹ,―"
14,25,"Tuʹteee|ʹukulahaa|kulla|ḥeenim|biʹiẓni|Rabbihaa.|Wa-yaḍribul|laahul|ʹams̤aala|linnaasi|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
14,26,"Wa-mas̤alu|kalimatin|khabees̤atiñ|kashajaratin|khabees̤atinij|tus̤s̤at|miñ|fawq̣il|ʹarḍi|maa-|lahaa|miñ|q̣araar."
14,27,"Yus̤abbitul|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|bil-Q̣awlis̤|S̤aabiti|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-fil|ʹAakhirah;|wa-yuḍillul|laahuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|wayafʻalul|laahu|maa-|yashaaaʹ."
14,28,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|baddaloo|niʻmatal|laahi|kufrañw|waʹaḥalloo|q̣awmahum|Daaral|Bawaar.―"
14,29,"Jahannama|yaṣlawnahaa,|wa-biʹsal|q̣araar!"
14,30,"Wa-jaʻaloo|lillaahi|ʹañdaadal|liyuḍilloo|ʻañ|Sabeelih!|Q̣ul|tamattaʻoo|faʹinna|maṣeerakum|ʹilan|Naar!"
14,31,"Q̣ul|liʻibaadiyal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|yuq̣eemuṣ|ṣalaata|wa-yuñfiq̣oo|mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|sirrañw|waʻalaaniyatam|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|Yawmul|laa|bayʻuñ|feehi|wa-laa|khilaal."
14,32,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-ʹañzala|minas|samaaʹi|maaaʹañ|faʹakhraja|bihee|minas̤|s̤amaraati|rizq̣al|lakum:|wa-sakhkhara|lakumul|fulka|litajriya|fil|baḥri|biʹAmrih:|wa-sakhkhara|lakumul|ʹanhaar."
14,33,"Wa-sakhkhara|lakumush|shamsa|walq̣amara|daaaʹibayni;|wa-sakhkhara|lakumul|layla|wan-Nahaar."
14,34,"Waʹaataakum|miñ|kulli|maa-|saʹaltumooh.|Wa-ʹiñ|taʻuddoo|niʻmatal|laahi|laa-|tuḥṣoohaa.|ʹInnal|ʹiñsaana|laz̤̣aloomuñ|kaffaar."
14,35,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|Rabbij|ʻal|haaẓal|Balada|ʹaaminañw|wajnubnee|wa-baniyya|ʹan|naʻbudal|ʹaṣnaam."
14,36,"Rabbi|ʹinnahunna|ʹaḍlalna|kas̤eeram|minan|naas;|famañ|tabiʻanee|faʹinnahoo|minnee,|wa-man|ʻaṣaanee|faʹinnaka|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
14,37,"Rabbanaaa|ʹinneee|ʹaskañtu|miñ|ẓurriyyatee|biwaadin|g̣ayri|ẓee|zarʻin|ʻiñda|Baytikal|Muḥarrami|Rabbanaa|liyuq̣eemus|Ṣalaata|fajʻal|ʹafʹidatam|minan|naasi|tahweee|ʹilayhim|warzuq̣hum|minas̤|s̤amaraati|laʻallahum|yashkuroon."
14,38,"Rabbanaaa|ʹinnaka|taʻlamu|maa-|nukhfee|wa-maa|nuʻlin:|wa-maa|yakhfaa|ʻalal|laahi|miñ|shayʹiñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|fis|samaaaʹ."
14,39,"ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓee|wahaba|lee|ʻalal|kibari|ʹIsmaaʻeela|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣:|ʹInna|Rabbee|la-Sameeʻud|duʻaaaʹ!"
14,40,"Rabbij|ʻalnee|muq̣eemaṣ|Ṣalaati|wa-miñ|ẓurriyyatee,|Rabbanaa|wa-taq̣abbal|Duʻaaaʹ."
14,41,"Rabbanag̣|fir|lee|wa-liwaalidayya|wa-lil-Muʹmineena|Yawma|yaq̣oomul|Ḥisaab!"
14,42,"Wa-laa|taḥsabannal|laaha|g̣aafilan|ʻammaa|yaʻmaluz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon.|ʹInnamaa|yuʹakhkhiruhum|li-Yawmiñ|tashkhaṣu|feehil|ʹabṣaar,―"
14,43,"Muhṭiʻeena|muq̣niʻee|ruʹoosihim|laa-|yartaddu|ʹilayhim|ṭarfuhum,|wa-ʹafʹidatuhum|hawaaaʹ!"
14,44,"Wa-ʹañẓirin|naasa|Yawma|yaʹteehimul|ʻAẓaabu|fayaq̣oolul|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|Rabbanaaa|ʹakhkhirnaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹajaliñ|q̣areebin|nujib|Daʻwataka|wa-nattabiʻir|rusul!|ʹAwalam|takoonooo|ʹaq̣samtum|miñ|q̣ablu|maa-|lakum|miñ|zawaal?"
14,45,"Wa-sakañtum|fee|masaakinil|laẓeena|z̤̣alamooo|ʹañfusahum|wa-tabayyana|lakum|kayfa|faʻalnaa|bihim|wa-ḍarabnaa|lakumul|ʹAms̤aal!"
14,46,"Wa-q̣ad|makaroo|makrahum:|wa-ʻindal|laahi|makruhum:|wa-ʹiñ|kaana|makruhum|litazoola|minhul|jibaal!"
14,47,"Falaa|taḥsabannal|laaha|mukhlifa|waʻdihee|rusulah:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAzeezuñ|Ẓuñ|tiq̣aam."
14,48,"Yawma|tubaddalul|ʹArḍu|g̣ayral|ʹArḍi|was-Samaawaatu|wa-barazoo|lillaahil|Waaḥidil|Q̣ahhaar;"
14,49,"Wa-taral|Mujrimeena|yawmaʹiẓim|muq̣arraneena|fil|ʹaṣfaad;"
14,50,"Saraabeeluhum|miñ|q̣aṭiraaniñw|watag̣shaa|wujoohahumun|Naar:"
14,51,"Liyajziyal|laahu|kulla|nafsim|maa|kasabat;|ʹinnal|laaha|Sareeʻul|Ḥisaab."
14,52,"Haaẓaa|Balaag̣ul|linnaasi|wa-liyuñẓaroo|bihee|wa-liyaʻlamooo|ʹannamaa|Huwa|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥiduñw|Waliyaẓẓakkara|ʹulul|ʹalbaab."
15,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Raa.|Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Kitaabi|wa-Q̣urʹaanim|Mubeen."
15,2,"Rubamaa|yawaddul|laẓeena|kafaroo|law|kaanoo|Muslimeen."
15,3,"Ẓarhum|yaʹkuloo|wa-yatamattaʻoo|wa-yulhihimul|ʹamalu|fasawfa|yaʻlamoon."
15,4,"Wa-maaa|ʹahlaknaa|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹillaa|wa-lahaa|kitaabum|maʻloom."
15,5,"Maa-|tasbiq̣u|min|ʹummatin|ʹAjalahaa|wa-maa|yastaʹkhiroon."
15,6,"Wa-q̣aaloo|yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓee|nuzzila|ʻalayhiẓ|Ẓikru|ʹinnaka|lamajnoon."
15,7,"Law|maa-|taʹteenaa|bil-malaaaʹikati|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|Ṣaadiq̣een?"
15,8,"Maa-|nunazzilul|malaaaʹikata|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|illaa|wa-maa|kaanooo|ʹiẓam|muñz̤̣areen!"
15,9,"ʹInnaa|Naḥnu|nazzalnaẓ|Ẓikra|wa-ʹinnaa|lahoo|la-Ḥaafiz̤̣oon."
15,10,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|fee|shiyaʻil|ʹawwaleen:"
15,11,"Wa-maa|yaʹteehim|mir|rasoolin|ʹillaa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon."
15,12,"Kaẓaalika|naslukuhoo|fee|q̣uloobil|mujrimeen―"
15,13,"Laa-|yuʹminoona|bihee|wa-q̣ad|khalat|sunnatul|ʹawwaleen."
15,14,"Wa-law|fataḥnaa|ʻalayhim|baabam|minas|samaaaʹi|faz̤̣alloo|feehi|yaʻrujoon."
15,15,"Laq̣aalooo|ʹinnamaa|sukkirat|ʹabṣaarunaa|bal|naḥnu|q̣awmum|masḥooroon."
15,16,"Wa-laq̣ad|jaʻalnaa|fis|samaaaʹi|Buroojañw|Wazayyannaahaa|linnaaz̤̣ireen;"
15,17,"Wa-hafiz̤̣naahaa|miñ|kulli|Shayṭaanir|rajeem:"
15,18,"ʹIllaa|manis|taraq̣as|samʻa|faʹatbaʻahoo|shihaabum|mubeen."
15,19,"Wal-ʹarḍa|madadnaahaa|wa-ʹalq̣aynaa|feehaa|rawaasiya|wa-ʹambatnaa|feehaa|miñ|kulli|shayʹim|mawzoon."
15,20,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|lakum|feehaa|maʻaayisha|wa-mal|lastum|lahoo|biraaziq̣een."
15,21,"Wa-ʹim|miñ|shayʹin|ʹillaa|ʻiñdanaa|khazaaaʹinuh;|wa-maa|nunazziluhooo|ʹillaa|biq̣adarim|maʻloom."
15,22,"Wa-ʹarsalnar|riyaaḥa|lawaaq̣iḥa|faʹañzalnaa|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|faʹasq̣aynaakumooh:|wa-maaa|ʹañtum|lahoo|bikhaazineen."
15,23,"Wa-ʹinnaa|lanaḥnu|nuḥyee|wa-numeetu|wa-naḥnul|waaris̤oon."
15,24,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʻalimnal|mustaq̣dimeena|miñkum|wa-laq̣ad|ʻalimnal|mustaʹkhireen."
15,25,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|Huwa|yaḥshuruhum:|ʹinnahoo|Ḥakeemun|ʻAleem."
15,26,"Wa-laq̣ad|khalaq̣nal|ʹiñsaana|miñ|ṣalṣaalim|min|ḥamaʹim|masnoon:"
15,27,"Waljaaanna|khalaq̣naahu|miñ|q̣ablu|min|naaris|samoom."
15,28,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Rabbuka|lilmalaaaʹikati|ʹinnee|khaaliq̣um|basharam|miñ|ṣalṣaalim|min|ḥamaʹim|masnoon;"
15,29,"Faʹiẓaa|sawwaytuhoo|wa-nafakhtu|feehi|mir|Rooḥee|faq̣aʻoo|lahoo|saajideen."
15,30,"Fasajadal|malaaaʹikatu|kulluhum|ʹajmaʻoon."
15,31,"ʹIllaaa|ʹIblees:|ʹabaaa|ʹañy|yakoona|maʻas|Saajideen."
15,32,"Q̣aala|yaaaʹIbleesu|maa-|laka|ʹallaa|takoona|maʻas|Saajideen?"
15,33,"Q̣aala|lam|ʹakul|liʹasjuda|libasharin|khalaq̣tahoo|miñ|ṣalṣaalim|min|ḥamaʹim|masnoon."
15,34,"Q̣aala|fakhruj|minhaa|faʹinnaka|rajeem."
15,35,"Wa-ʹinna|ʻalaykal|laʻnata|ʹilaa|Yawmid|Deen."
15,36,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|faʹañz̤̣irneee|ʹilaa|Yawmi|yubʻas̤oon."
15,37,"Q̣aala|faʹinnaka|minal|muñz̤̣areen―"
15,38,"ʹIlaa|Yawmil|Waq̣til|Maʻloom."
15,39,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|bimaaa|ʹag̣waytanee|laʹuzayyinanna|lahum|fil|ʹarḍi|walaʹug̣wiyannahum|ʹajmaʻeen,―"
15,40,"ʹIllaa|ʻibaadaka|minhumul|Mukhlaṣeen."
15,41,"Q̣aala|haaẓaa|Ṣiraaṭun|ʻalayya|Mustaq̣eem."
15,42,"ʹInna|ʻibaadee|laysa|laka|ʻalayhim|sulṭaanun|ʹillaa|manit|tabaʻaka|minal|g̣aaween."
15,43,"Wa-ʹinna|Jahannama|lamawʻiduhum|ʹajmaʻeen!"
15,44,"Lahaa|sabʻatu|ʹAbwaab:|likulli|Baabim|minhum|juzʹum|maq̣soom."
15,45,"ʹInnal|Muttaq̣eena|fee|Jannaatiñw|Waʻuyoon."
15,46,"ʹUdkhuloohaa|bi-Salaamin|ʹAamineen."
15,47,"Wanazaʻnaa|maa-|fee|ṣudoorihim|min|g̣illin|ʹikhwaanan|ʻalaa|sururim|mutaq̣aabileen."
15,48,"Laa-|yamassuhum|feehaa|naṣabuñw|wamaa|hum|minhaa|bimukhrajeen."
15,49,"Nabbiʹ|ʻibaadeee|ʹanneee|ʹan|al-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem;"
15,50,"Wa-ʹanna|ʻAẓaabee|huwal|ʻAẓaabul|ʹaleem."
15,51,"Wa-nabbiʹhum|ʻañ|ḍayfi|ʹIbraaheem."
15,52,"ʹIẓ|dakhaloo|ʻalayhi|faq̣aaloo|Salaamaa!|Q̣aala|ʹinnaa|miñkum|wajiloon!"
15,53,"Q̣aaloo|laa-|tawjal|ʹinnaa|nubashshiruka|big̣ulaamin|ʻaleem."
15,54,"Q̣aala|ʹabashshartumoonee|ʻalaaa|ʹam|massaniyal|kibaru|fabima|tubashshiroon?"
15,55,"Q̣aaloo|bashsharnaaka|bilḥaq̣q̣i|falaa|takum|minal|q̣aaniṭeen!"
15,56,"Q̣aala|wa-mañy|yaq̣naṭu|mir|Raḥmati|Rabbiheee|ʹillaḍ|ḍaaalloon?"
15,57,"Q̣aala|famaa|khaṭbukum|ʹayyuhal|Mursaloon?"
15,58,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaaa|ʹursilnaaa|ʹilaa|q̣awmim|mujrimeen."
15,59,"ʹIllaa|ʹAala|Looṭ:|ʹinnaa|lamunajjoohum|ʹajmaʻeen,―"
15,60,"ʹIllam|raʹatahoo|q̣addarnaaa|ʹinnahaa|laminal|g̣aabireen."
15,61,"Falammaa|jaaaʹa|ʹAala|Looṭinil|mursaloon."
15,62,"Q̣aala|ʹinnakum|q̣awmum|muñkaroon."
15,63,"Q̣aaloo|bal|jiʹnaaka|bimaa|kaanoo|feehi|yamtaroon."
15,64,"Wa-ʹataynaaka|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹinnaa|laṣaadiq̣oon."
15,65,"Faʹasri|biʹahlika|biq̣iṭʻim|minal|layli|wattabiʻ|adbaarahum|wa-laa|yaltafit|miñkum|ʹaḥaduñw|wamḍoo|ḥays̤u|tuʹmaroon."
15,66,"Wa-q̣aḍaynaaa|ʹilayhi|ẓaalikal|ʹamra|ʹanna|daabira|haaaʹulaaaʹi|maq̣ṭooʻum|muṣbiḥeen."
15,67,"Wa-jaaaʹa|ʹahlul|Madeenati|yastabshiroon."
15,68,"Q̣aala|ʹinna|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ḍayfee|falaa|tafḍaḥoon:"
15,69,"Wattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-laa|tukhzoon."
15,70,"Q̣aalooo|ʹawalam|nanhaka|ʻanil|ʻaalameen?"
15,71,"Q̣aala|haaaʹulaaaʹi|banaateee|ʹiñ|kuñtum|faaʻileen."
15,72,"Laʻamruka|ʹinnahum|lafee|sakratihim|yaʻmahoon."
15,73,"Faʹakhaẓathumuṣ|Ṣayḥatu|mushriq̣een."
15,74,"Fajaʻalnaa|ʻaaliyahaa|saafilahaa|wa-ʹamṭarnaa|ʻalayhim|ḥijaaratam|miñ|sijjeel."
15,75,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|lilmutawassimeen."
15,76,"Wa-ʹinnahaa|labisabeelim|muq̣eem."
15,77,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|lil-Muʹmineen."
15,78,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|ʹAṣḥaabul|ʹAykati|laz̤̣aalimeen."
15,79,"Fañtaq̣amnaa|minhum.|Wa-ʹinnahumaa|labiʹimaamim|mubeen."
15,80,"Wa-laq̣ad|kaẓẓaba|ʻAṣḥaabul|ḤIJRIL|mursaleen:"
15,81,"Wa-ʹaataynaahum|ʹAayaatinaa|fakaanoo|ʻanhaa|muʻriḍeen."
15,82,"Wa-kaanoo|yanḥitoona|minal|jibaali|buyootan|ʹaamineen."
15,83,"Faʹakhaẓathumuṣ|Ṣayḥatu|muṣbiḥeen."
15,84,"Famaaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaksiboon!"
15,85,"Wa-maa|khalaq̣nas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaaa|ʹillaa|bilḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-ʹinnas|Saaʻata|laʹaatiyatuñ|faṣfaḥiṣ|ṣafḥal|jameel."
15,86,"ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwal|Khallaaq̣ul|ʻAleem."
15,87,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaaka|Sabʻam|minal|mas̤aanee|wal-Q̣urʹaanal|ʻAz̤̣eem."
15,88,"Laa-|tamuddanna|ʻaynayka|ʹilaa|maa-|mattaʻnaa|biheee|ʹazwaajam|minhum|wa-laa|taḥzan|ʻalayhim|wakhfiḍ|janaaḥaka|lil-Muʹmineen."
15,89,"Wa-q̣ul|ʹinneee|ʹanan|naẓeerul|mubeen,―"
15,90,"Kamaaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalal|muq̣tasimeen,―"
15,91,"ʹAllaẓeena|jaʻalul|Q̣urʹaana|ʻi-ḍeen."
15,92,"Fawa-Rabbika|lanasʹalannahum|ʹajmaʻeen."
15,93,"ʻAmmaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
15,94,"Faṣdaʻ|bimaa|tuʹmaru|wa-ʹaʻriḍ|ʻanil|mushrikeen."
15,95,"ʹInnaa|kafaynaakal|mustahziʹeen."
15,96,"ʹAllaẓeena|yajʻaloona|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhar:|fasawfa|yaʻlamoon."
15,97,"Wa-laq̣ad|naʻlamu|ʹannaka|yaḍeeq̣u|ṣadruka|bimaa|yaq̣ooloon."
15,98,"Fasabbiḥ|biḥamdi|Rabbika|wa-kum|minas|Saajideen."
15,99,"Waʻbud|Rabbaka|ḥattaa|yaʹtiyakal|yaq̣een."
16,1,"ʹAtaaa|ʹAmrul|laahi|falaa|tastaʻjilooh:|Subḥaanahoo|wa-taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon."
16,2,"Yunazzilul|malaaaʹikata|birrooḥi|min|ʹAmrihee|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadiheee|ʹan|ʹañẓirooo|ʹannahoo|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaaa|ʹana|fattaq̣oon."
16,3,"Khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bilḥaq̣q̣:|Taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
16,4,"Khalaq̣al|ʹiñsaana|min|nuṭfatiñ|faʹiẓaa|huwa|khaṣeemum|mubeen!"
16,5,"Wal-ʹanʻaama|khalaq̣ahaa|lakum|feehaa|difʹuñw|wamanaafiʻu|wa-minhaa|taʹkuloon."
16,6,"Wa-lakum|feehaa|jamaalun|ḥeena|tureeḥoona|waḥeena|tasraḥoon."
16,7,"Wa-taḥmilu|ʹas̤q̣aalakum|ʹilaa|baladil|lam|takoonoo|baalig̣eehi|ʹillaa|bishiq̣q̣il|ʹañfus:|ʹinna|Rabbakum|la-Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
16,8,"Walkhayla|wal-big̣aala|wal-ḥameera|litarkaboohaa|wa-zeenah;|wa-yakhluq̣u|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon."
16,9,"Wa-ʻalal|laahi|q̣aṣdus|Sabeeli|wa-minhaa|jaaaʹir:|wa-law|shaaaʹa|lahadaakum|ʹajmaʻeen."
16,10,"Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹal|lakum|minhu|sharaabuñw|waminhu|shajaruñ|feehi|tuseemoon."
16,11,"Yumbitu|lakum̃|bihiz|zarʻa|wazzaytoona|wannakheela|wal-ʹaʻnaaba|wa-miñ|kullis̤|s̤amaraat:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
16,12,"Wa-sakhkhara|lakumul|layla|wannahaara|washshamsa|walq̣amar;|wannujoomu|musakhkharaatum|biʹAmrih:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
16,13,"Wa-maa|ẓaraʹa|lakum|fil|ʹarḍi|mukhtalifan|ʹalwaanuh:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹaayatal|liq̣awmiñy|yaẓẓakkaroon."
16,14,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|sakhkharal|baḥra|litaʹkuloo|minhu|laḥmañ|ṭariyyañw|watastakhrijoo|minhu|ḥilyatañ|talbasoonahaa:|wa-taral|fulka|mawaakhira|feehi|wa-litabtag̣oo|miñ|faḍlihee|wa-laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
16,15,"Wa-ʹalq̣aa|fil|ʹarḍi|rawaasiya|ʹañ|tameeda|bikum|wa-ʹanhaarañw|wasubulal|laʻallakum|tahtadoon:"
16,16,"Wa-ʻalaamaat;|wa-binnajmi|hum|yahtadoon."
16,17,"ʹAfamañy|yakhluq̣u|kamal|laa|yakhluq̣?|ʹAfalaa|taẓakkaroon?"
16,18,"Wa-ʹiñ|taʻuddoo|niʻmatal|laahi|laa-|tuḥṣoohaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|la-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
16,19,"Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|tusirroona|wa-maa|tuʻlinoon."
16,20,"Wallaẓeena|yadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|laa-|yakhluq̣oona|shayʹañw|wahum|yukhlaq̣oon."
16,21,"ʹAmwaatun|g̣ayru|ʹaḥyaaaʹ:|wa-maa|yashʻuroona|ʹayyaana|yubʻas̤oon."
16,22,"ʹIlaahukum|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥid:|fallaẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|q̣uloobuhum|muñkiratuñw|wahum|mustakbiroon."
16,23,"Laa-|jarama|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|yusirroona|wa-maa|yuʻlinoon:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yuḥibbul|mustakbireen."
16,24,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|maaẓaaa|ʹañzala|Rabbukum|q̣aalooo|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleen?"
16,25,"Liyaḥmilooo|ʹawzaarahum|kaamilatañy|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|wa-min|ʹawzaaril|laẓeena|yuḍilloonahum̃|big̣ayri|ʻilm.|ʹAlaa|saaaʹa|maa-|yaziroon!"
16,26,"Q̣ad|makaral|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|faʹatal|laahu|bunyaanahum|minal|q̣awaaʻidi|fakharra|ʻalayhimus|saq̣fu|miñ|fawq̣ihim|wa-ʹataahumul|ʻaẓaabu|min|ḥays̤u|laa-|yashʻuroon."
16,27,"S̤umma|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|yukhzeehim|wa-yaq̣oolu|ʹayna|shurakaaaʹiyal|laẓeena|kuñtum|tushaaaq̣q̣oona|feehim?|Q̣aalal|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻilma|ʹinnal|khizyal|yawma|wassoooʹa|ʻalal|kaafireen,―"
16,28,"ʹAllaẓeena|tatawaffaahumul|malaaaʹikatu|z̤̣aalimeee|ʹañfusihim.|Faʹalq̣awus|salama|maa-|kunnaa|naʻmalu|miñ|soooʹ.|Balaaa|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|bimaa|kuntum|taʻmaloon."
16,29,"Fadkhulooo|ʹabwaaba|Jahannama|khaalideena|feeha.|Falabiʹsa|mas̤wal|mutakabbireen."
16,30,"Wa-q̣eela|lillaẓeenat|taq̣aw|maaẓaaa|ʹañzala|Rabbukum?|Q̣aaloo|khayraa.|Lillaẓeena|ʹaḥsanoo|fee|haaẓihid|dunyaa|ḥasanah.|Wa-la-Daarul|ʹAakhirati|khayr.|Wa-laniʻma|Daarul|Muttaq̣een,―"
16,31,"Jannaatu|ʻAdniñy|yadkhuloonahaa|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|lahum|feehaa|maa-|yashaaaʹoon:|kaẓaalika|yajzil|laahul|Muttaq̣een,―"
16,32,"ʹAllaẓeena|tatawaffaahumul|malaaaʹikatu|ṭayyibeena|yaq̣ooloona|Salaamun|ʻalaykumud|khulul|Jannata|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
16,33,"Hal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|taʹtiyahumul|malaaaʹikatu|ʹaw|yaʹtiya|ʹAmru|Rabbik?|Kaẓaalika|faʻalal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim.|Wa-maa|z̤̣alamahumul|laahu|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
16,34,"Faʹaṣaabahum|sayyiʹaatu|maa-|ʻamiloo|waḥaaq̣a|bihim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon."
16,35,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|ʹashrakoo|law|shaaaʹal|laahu|maa-|ʻabadnaa|miñ|doonihee|miñ|shayʹin|naḥnu|wa-laaa|ʹaabaaaʹunaa|wa-laa|ḥarramnaa|miñ|doonihee|miñ|shayyʹ.|Kaẓaalika|faʻalal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|Fahal|ʻalar|rusuli|ʹillal|Balaag̣ul|Mubeen?"
16,36,"Wa-laq̣ad|baʻas̤naa|fee|kulli|ʹummatir|rasoolan|ʹaniʻ|budul|laaha|wajtanibuṭ|Ṭaag̣oot;|faminhum|man|hadal|laahu|wa-minhum|man|ḥaq̣q̣at|ʻalayhiḍ|ḍalaalah.|Faseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mukaẓẓibeen."
16,37,"ʹIñ|taḥriṣ|ʻalaa|hudaahum|faʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yahdee|mañy|yuḍillu|wa-maa|lahum|min|naaṣireen."
16,38,"Wa-ʹaq̣samoo|billaahi|jahda|ʹaymaanihim|laa-|yabʻas̤ul|laahu|mañy|yamoot:|balaa|waʻdan|ʻalayhi|ḥaq̣q̣añw|walaakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
16,39,"Liyubayyina|lahumul|laẓee|yakhtalifoona|feehi|wa-liyaʻlamal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹannahum|kaanoo|kaaẓibeen."
16,40,"ʹInnamaa|q̣awlunaa|lishayʹin|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaradnaahu|ʹan|naq̣oola|lahoo|Kuñ|Fayakoon."
16,41,"Wallaẓeena|haajaroo|fil|laahi|mim|baʻdi|maa-|z̤̣ulimoo|lanubawwiʹannahum|fid|dunyaa|ḥasanah;|wa-laʹajrul|ʹAakhirati|ʹakbar.|Law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoon!"
16,42,"ʹAllaẓeena|ṣabaroo|wa-ʻalaa|Rabbihim|yatawakkaloon."
16,43,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|ʹillaa|rijaalan|nooḥeee|ʹilayhim,|fasʹalooo|ʹahlaẓ|Ẓikri|ʹiñ|kuñtum|laa-|taʻlamoon,―"
16,44,"Bil-Bayyinaati|waz-Zubur;|wa-ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykaẓ|Ẓikra|litubayyina|linnaasi|maa-|nuzzila|ʹilayhim|wa-laʻallahum|yatafakkaroon."
16,45,"ʹA-faʹaminal|laẓeena|makarus|sayyiʹaati|ʹañy|yakhsifal|laahu|bihimul|ʹarḍa|ʹaw|yaʹtiyahumul|ʻaẓaabu|min|ḥays̤u|laa-|yashʻuroon?"
16,46,"ʹAw|yaʹkhuẓahum|fee|taq̣allubihim|famaa|hum̃|bimuʻjizeen?―"
16,47,"ʹAw|yaʹkhuẓahum|ʻalaa|takhawwuf:|faʹinna|Rabbakum|la-Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
16,48,"ʹA-walam|yaraw|ʹilaa|maa-|khalaq̣al|laahu|miñ|shayʹiñy|yatafayyaʹu|z̤̣ilaaluhoo|ʻanil|yameeni|washshamaaaʹili|sujjadal|lillaahi|wa-hum|daakhiroon?"
16,49,"Wa-lillaahi|yasjudu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍi|miñ|daaabbatiñw|walmalaaaʹikatu|wa-hum|laa-|yastakbiroon,"
16,50,"Yakhaafoona|Rabbahum|miñ|fawq̣ihim|wayafʻaloona|maa-|yuʹmaroon."
16,51,"Waq̣aalal|laahu|laa-|tattakhiẓooo|ʹilaahaynis̤|nayn:|ʹinnamaa|Huwa|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥid:|faʹiyyaaya|farhaboon."
16,52,"Walahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-lahud|Deenu|waaṣibaa:|ʹafag̣ayral|laahi|tattaq̣oon?"
16,53,"Wa-maa|bikum|min|niʻmatiñ|faminal|laahi|s̤umma|ʹiẓaa|massakumuḍ|ḍurru|faʹilayhi|tajʹaroon;"
16,54,"S̤umma|ʹiẓaa|kashafaḍ|ḍurra|ʻañkum|ʹiẓaa|fareeq̣um|miñkum̃|bi-Rabbihim|yushrikoon."
16,55,"Liyakfuroo|bimaaa|ʹaataynaahum!|Fatamattaʻoo;|fasawfa|taʻlamoon!"
16,56,"Wa-yajʻaloona|limaa|laa-|yaʻlamoona|naṣeebam|mimmaa|razaq̣naahum!|Tallaahi|latusʹalunna|ʻammaa|kuñtum|taftaroon."
16,57,"Wa-yajʻaloona|lillaahil|banaati|Subḥaanahoo|wa-lahum|maa|yashtahoon!"
16,58,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|bushshira|ʹaḥaduhum̃|bil-ʹuñs̤aa|z̤̣alla|wajhuhoo|muswaddañw|wahuwa|kaz̤̣eem!"
16,59,"Yatawaaraa|minal|q̣awmi|miñ|soooʹi|maa-|bushshira|bih!|ʹA-yumsikuhoo|ʻalaa|hoonin|ʹam|yadussuhoo|fit|turaab?|ʹAlaa|saaaʹa|maa-|yaḥkumoon?"
16,60,"Lillaẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|mas̤alus|sawʹ:|wa-lillaahil|Mas̤alul|ʹAʻlaa:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
16,61,"Wa-law|yuʹaakhiẓul|laahun|naasa|biz̤̣ulmihim|maa|taraka|ʻalayhaa|miñ|daaabbatiñw|walaakiñy|yuʹakhkhiruhum|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammaa:|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹajaluhum|laa-|yastaʹkhiroona|saaʻatañw|walaa|yastaq̣dimoon."
16,62,"Wa-yajʻaloona|lillaahi|maa-|yakrahoona|wa-taṣifu|ʹalsinatuhumul|kaẓiba|ʹanna|lahumul|ḥusnaa:|laa-|jarama|ʹanna|lahumun|Naara|wa-ʹannahum|mufraṭoon!"
16,63,"Tallaahi|laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹumamim|miñ|q̣ablika|fazayyana|lahumush|Shayṭaanu|ʹaʻmaalahum|fahuwa|waliyyuhumul|yawma|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
16,64,"Wa-maaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|ʹillaa|litubayyina|lahumul|laẓikh|talafoo|feehi|wa-hudañw|waraḥmatal|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
16,65,"Wallaahu|ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|faʹaḥyaa|bihil|ʹarḍa|baʻda|mawtihaa:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|liq̣awmiñy|yasmaʻoon."
16,66,"Wa-ʹinna|lakum|fil|ʹanʻaami|laʻIbrah.|Nusq̣eekum|mimmaa|fee|buṭoonihee|mim|bayni|fars̤iñw|wadamil|labanan|khaaliṣañ|saaaʹig̣allish|shaaribeen."
16,67,"Wa-miñ|s̤amaraatin|nakheeli|wal-ʹaʻnaabi|tattakhiẓoona|minhu|sakarañw|warizq̣an|ḥasanaa:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
16,68,"Wa-ʹawḥaa|Rabbuka|ʹilan|NAḤLI|ʹanit|takhiẓee|minal|jibaali|buyootañw|waminash|shajari|wa-mimmaa|yaʻrishoon;"
16,69,"S̤umma|kulee|miñ|kullis̤|s̤amaraati|faslukee|subula|Rabbiki|ẓululaa.|Yakhruju|mim|buṭoonihaa|sharaabum|mukhtalifun|ʹalwaanuhoo|feehi|shifaaaʹul|linnaas:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
16,70,"Wallaahu|khalaq̣akum|s̤umma|yatawaffaakum|wa-miñkum|mañy|yuraddu|ʹilaaa|ʹarẓalil|ʻumuri|likay|laa-|yaʻlama|baʻda|ʻilmiñ|shayʹaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAleemuñ|Q̣adeer."
16,71,"Wallaahu|faḍḍala|baʻḍakum|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñ|fir|rizq̣:|famal|laẓeena|fuḍḍiloo|biraaaddee|rizq̣ihim|ʻalaa|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanuhum|fahum|feehi|sawaaaʹ.|ʹAfabiniʻmatil|laahi|yajḥadoon?"
16,72,"Wallaahu|jaʻala|lakum|min|ʹañfusikum|ʹazwaajañw|Wajaʻala|lakum|min|ʹazwaajikum|baneena|waḥafadatañw|warazaq̣akum|minaṭ|ṭayyibaat:|ʹafabilbaaṭili|yuʹminoona|wa-biniʻmatil|laahi|hum|yakfuroon?―"
16,73,"Wa-yaʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yamliku|lahum|rizq̣am|minas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|shayʹañw|walaa|yastaṭeeʻoon?"
16,74,"Falaa|taḍriboo|lillaahil|ʹams̤aal:|ʹinnal|laaha|yaʻlamu|waʹañtum|laa-|taʻlamoon."
16,75,"Ḍarabal|laahu|Mas̤alan|ʻabdam|mamlookal|laa|yaq̣diru|ʻalaa|shayʹiñw|wamar|razaq̣naahu|minnaa|rizq̣an|ḥasanañ|fahuwa|yuñfiq̣u|minhu|sirrañw|wajahraa:|hal|yastawoon?|ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaah.|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
16,76,"Wa-ḍarabal|laahu|Mas̤alar|rajulayni|ʹaḥaduhumaaa|ʹabkamu|laa-|yaq̣diru|ʻalaa|shayʹiñw|wa huwa|kallun|ʻalaa|mawlaahu|ʹaynamaa|yuwajjihhu|laa-|yaʹti|bikhayr:|hal|yastawee|huwa|wa-mañy|yaʹmuru|bilʻadli|wa-huwa|ʻalaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem?"
16,77,"Wa-lillaahi|g̣aybus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Wa-maaa|ʹamrus|Saaʻati|ʹillaa|kalamḥil|baṣari|ʹaw|huwa|ʹaq̣rab:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
16,78,"Wallaahu|ʹakhrajakum|mim|buṭooni|ʹummahaatikum|laa-|taʻlamoona|shayʹañw|wajaʻala|lakumus|samʻa|wal-ʹabṣaara|wal-ʹafʹidata|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
16,79,"ʹAlam|yaraw|ʹilaṭ|ṭayri|musakhkharaatiñ|fee|jawwis|samaaaʹ?|Maa-|yumsikuhunna|ʹillal|laah.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
16,80,"Wallaahu|jaʻala|lakum|mim|buyootikum|sakanañw|wajaʻala|lakum|miñ|juloodil|ʹanʻaami|buyootañ|tastakhiffoonahaa|yawma|z̤̣aʻnikum|wa-yawma|ʻiq̣aamatikum|wa-min|aṣwaafihaa|wa-ʹawbaarihaa|wa-ʹashʻaarihaaa|ʹas̤aas̤añw|Wamataaʻan|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
16,81,"Wallaahu|jaʻala|lakum|mimmaa|khalaq̣a|z̤̣ilaalañw|wajaʻala|lakum|minal|jibaali|ʹaknaanañw|Wajaʻala|lakum|saraabeela|taq̣eekumul|ḥarra|wa-saraabeela|taq̣eekum̃|baʹsakum.|Kaẓaalika|yutimmu|niʻmatahoo|ʻalaykum|laʻallakum|tuslimoon."
16,82,"Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinnamaa|ʻalaykal|Balaag̣ul|Mubeen."
16,83,"Yaʻrifoona|niʻmatal|laahi|s̤umma|yuñkiroonahaa|wa-ʹaksaruhumul|kaafiroon."
16,84,"Wa-yawma|nabʻas̤u|miñ|kulli|ʹummatiñ|Shaheedañ|s̤umma|laa-|yuʹẓanu|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-laa|hum|yustaʻtaboon."
16,85,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ra|ʹallaẓeena|z̤̣alamul|ʻAẓaaba|falaa|yukhaffafu|ʻanhum|wa-laa|hum|yuñz̤̣aroon."
16,86,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ra|ʹallaẓeena|ʹashrakoo|shurakaaaʹahum|q̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|haaaʹulaaaʹi|shurakaaaʹunal|laẓeena|kunnaa|nadʻoo|miñ|doonik.|Faʹalq̣aw|ʹilayhimul|q̣awla|ʹinnakum|lakaaẓiboon!"
16,87,"Wa-ʹalq̣aw|ʹilal|laahi|yawmaʹiẓinis|salama|wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
16,88,"ʹAllaẓeena|kafaroo|waṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|zidnaahum|ʻAẓaabañ|fawq̣al|ʻaẓaabi|bimaa|kaanoo|yufsidoon."
16,89,"Wa-yawma|nabʻas̤u|fee|kulli|ʹummatiñ|shaheedan|ʻalayhim|min|ʹañfusihim|wa-jiʹnaa|bika|shaheedan|ʻalaa|haaaʹulaaaʹ.|Wa-nazzalnaa|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|tibyaanal|likulli|shayʹiñw|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatañw|wa-Bushraa|lil-Muslimeen."
16,90,"ʹInnal|laaha|yaʹmuru|bil-ʻadli|wal-ʹiḥsaani|wa-ʹeetaaaʹi|ẓil|q̣urbaa|wa-yanhaa|ʻanil|faḥshaaaʹi|wal-muñkari|walbag̣yi:|yaʻi-Z̤̣ukum|laʻallakum|taẓakkaroon."
16,91,"Wa-ʹawfoo|biʻAhdil|laahi|ʹiẓaa|ʻaahattum|wa-laa|tañq̣uḍul|ʹaymaana|baʻda|tawkeedihaa|wa-q̣ad|jaʻaltumul|laaha|ʻalaykum|kafeelaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|tafʻaloon."
16,92,"Wa-laa|takoonoo|kallatee|naq̣aḍat|g̣azlahaa|mim|baʻdi|q̣uwwatin|ʹañkaas̤aa.|Tattakhiẓoona|ʹaymaanakum|dakhalam|baynakum|ʹañ|takoona|ʹummatun|hiya|ʹarbaa|min|ʹummah;|ʹinnamaa|yablookumul|laahu|bih;|wa-la-yubayyinanna|lakum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|maa-|kuñtum|feehi|takhtalifoon."
16,93,"Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|lajaʻalakum|ʹummatañw|waaḥidatañw|walaakiñy|yuḍillu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-latusʹalunna|ʻammaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
16,94,"Wa-laa|tattakhiẓooo|ʹaymaanakum|dakhalam|baynakum|fatazilla|q̣adamum|baʻda|s̤ubootihaa|wa-taẓooq̣us|soooʹa|bimaa|ṣadattum|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|walakum|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
16,95,"Wa-laa|tashtaroo|biʻAhdil|laahi|s̤amanañ|q̣aleelaa:|ʹinnamaa|ʻiñdal|laahi|huwa|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon."
16,96,"Maa-|ʻiñdakum|yañfadu|wa-maa|ʻiñdal|laahi|baaq̣.|Wa-lanajziyannal|laẓeena|ṣabarooo|ʹajrahum̃|biʹaḥsani|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
16,97,"Man|ʻamila|ṣaaliḥam|miñ|ẓakarin|ʹaw|ʹuñs̤aa|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|falanuḥyiyannahoo|Ḥayaatañ|Ṭayyibah,|wa-lanajzi-yannahum|ʹajrahum̃|biʹaḥsani|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
16,98,"Faʹiẓaa|q̣araʹtal|Q̣urʹaana|fastaʻiẓ|billaahi|minash|Shayṭaanir|Rajeem."
16,99,"ʹInnahoo|laysa|lahoo|sulṭaanun|ʻalal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻalaa|Rabbihim|yatawakkaloon."
16,100,"ʹInnamaa|sulṭaanuhoo|ʻalal|laẓeena|yatawallawnahoo|wallaẓeena|hum̃|bihee|mushrikoon."
16,101,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|baddalnaaa|ʹaayatam|makaana|ʹaayatiñw|wal-laahu|ʹAʻlamu|bimaa|yunazzilu|q̣aalooo|ʹinnamaaa|ʹañta|muftar:|bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
16,102,"Q̣ul|nazzalahoo|Rooḥul|Q̣udusi|mir|Rabbika|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|liyus̤abbital|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|Bushraa|wa-Hudañwwa|lil-Muslimeen."
16,103,"Wa-laq̣ad|naʻlamu|ʹannahum|yaq̣ooloona|ʹinnamaa|yuʻallimuhoo|bashar.|Lisaanul|laẓee|yulḥidoona|ʹilayhi|ʹaʻjamiyyuñw|Wahaaẓaa|lisaanun|ʻArabiyyum|mubeen."
16,104,"ʹInnal|lazeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|biʹaayaatil|lahi|laa-|yahdeehimul|laahu|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
16,105,"ʹInnamaa|yaftaril|kaẓibal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|biʹaayaatil|laahi|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|kaaẓiboon."
16,106,"Mañ|kafara|billaahi|mim|baʻdi|ʹeemaaniheee|ʹillaa|man|ʹukriha|wa-q̣albuhoo|muṭmaʹinnum|bil-ʹEemaani|wa-laakim|mañ|sharaḥa|bilkufri|ṣadrañ|faʻalayhim|g̣aḍabum|minal|laahi|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
16,107,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahumus|taḥabbul|ḥayaatad|dunyaa|ʻalal|ʹAakhirati|waʹannal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|Q̣awmal|kaafireen."
16,108,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ṭabaʻal|laahu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|wa-samʻihim|wa-ʹabṣaarihim|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|G̣aafiloon."
16,109,"Laa-|jarama|ʹannahum|fil|ʹaakhirati|humul|khaasiroon."
16,110,"S̤umma|ʹinna|Rabbaka|lillaẓeena|haajaroo|mim|baʻdi|maa-|futinoo|s̤umma|jaahadoo|waṣabarooo|ʹinna|Rabbaka|mim|baʻdihaa|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
16,111,"Yawma|taʹtee|kullu|nafsiñ|tujaadilu|ʻan|nafsihaa|wa-tuwaffaa|kullu|nafsim|maa|ʻamilat|Wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
16,112,"Wa-ḍarabal|laahu|Mas̤alañ|q̣aryatañ|kaanat|ʹaaminatam|muṭmaʹinnatañy|yaʹteehaa|rizq̣uhaa|rag̣adam|miñ|kulli|makaaniñ|fakafarat|biʹanʻumil|laahi|faʹaẓaaq̣ahal|laahu|libaasal|jooʻi|walkhawfi|bimaa|kaanoo|yaṣnaʻoon."
16,113,"Wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹahum|Rasoolum|minhum|fakaẓẓaboohu|faʹakhaẓahumul|ʻaẓaabu|wa-hum|z̤̣aalimoon."
16,114,"Fakuloo|mimmaa|razaq̣akumul|laahu|Ḥalaalañ|Ṭayyibaa;|washkuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ʹiyyaahu|taʻbudoon."
16,115,"ʹInnamaa|ḥarrama|ʻalaykumul|maytata|waddama|wa-laḥmal|khiñzeeri|wa-maaa|ʹuhilla|lig̣ayril|laahi|bih.|Famaniḍ|ṭurra|g̣ayra|baag̣iñw|walaa|ʻaadiñ|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
16,116,"wa-laa|taq̣ooloo|limaa|taṣifu|ʹalsinatukumul|kaẓiba|haaẓaa|ḥalaaluñw|wahaaẓaa|ḥaraamul|litaftaroo|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓib.|ʹInnal|laẓeena|yaftaroona|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓiba|laa-|yufliḥoon."
16,117,"Mataaʻuñ|q̣aleel;|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
16,118,"Wa-ʻalal|laẓeena|haadoo|ḥarramnaa|maa-|q̣aṣaṣnaa|ʻalayka|miñ|q̣abl:|wa-maa|z̤̣alamnaahum|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
16,119,"S̤umma|ʹinna|Rabbaka|lillaẓeena|ʻamilus|soooʹa|bijahaalatiñ|s̤umma|taaboo|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|wa-ʹaṣlaḥooo|ʹinna|Rabbaka|mim|baʻdihaa|la-G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
16,120,"ʹInna|ʹIbraaheema|kaana|ʹummatañ|q̣aanital|lillaahi|ḥaneefaa:|wa-lam|yaku|minal|mushrikeen:"
16,121,"Shaakiral|liʹanʻumih:|ʹijtabaahu|wa-hadaahu|ʹilaa|Ṣiraatim|Mustaq̣eem."
16,122,"Wa-ʹaataynaahu|fid|dunyaa|Ḥasanah:|wa-ʹinnahoo|fil|ʹAakhirati|laminaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
16,123,"S̤umma|awḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|ʹanit|tabiʻ|Millata|ʹIbraaheema|Ḥaneefaa,|wa-maa|kaana|minal|mushrikeen."
16,124,"Innamaa|juʻilas|Sabtu|ʻalal|laẓeenakh|talafoo|feeh:|wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|layaḥkumu|baynahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|feemaa|kaanoo|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
16,125,"ʹUdʻu|ʹilaa|sabeeli|Rabbika|bilḥikmati|walmawʻiz̤̣atil|ḥasanati|wa-jaadilhum̃|billatee|hiya|ʹaḥsan:|ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwa|ʹAʻlamu|bimañ|ḍalla|ʻañ|Sabeelihee|wa-Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bil-Muhtadeen."
16,126,"Wa-ʹin|ʻaaq̣abtum|faʻaaq̣iboo|bimis̤li|maa-|ʻooq̣ibtum̃|bih:|wa-laʹiñ|ṣabartum|lahuwa|khayrul|liṣ-Ṣaabireen."
16,127,"Waṣbir|wa-maa|ṣabruka|ʹillaa|billaahi|wa-laa|taḥzan|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|taku|fee|ḍayq̣im|mimmaa|yamkuroon."
16,128,"ʹInnal|laaha|maʻal|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|wal-laẓeena|hum|Muḥsinoon."
17,1,"Subḥaanal|laẓeee|ʹasraa|biʻAbdihee|laylam|minal|Masjidil|Ḥaraami|ʹilal|Masjidil|ʹAq̣ṣal|laẓee|baaraknaa|ḥaw-lahoo|linuriyahoo|min|ʹAayaatinaa:|ʹinnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|Baṣeer."
17,2,"Wa-ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|wa-jaʻalnaahu|Hudal|li-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʹallaa|tat-takhiẓoo|miñ|doonee|wakeelaa."
17,3,"Ẓurriyyata|man|ḥamalnaa|maʻa|Nooḥ!|ʹInnahoo|kaana|ʻabdañ|shakooraa."
17,4,"Wa-q̣aḍaynaaa|ʹilaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|fil|kitaabi|latufsidunna|fil|ʹarḍi|marratayni|wa-lataʻlunna|ʻuluwwañ|kabeeraa!"
17,5,"Faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|waʻdu|ʹulaahumaa|baʻas̤naa|ʻalaykum|ʻibaadal|lanaaa|ʹulee|baʹsiñ|shadeediñ|fajaasoo|khilaalad|diyaar;|wa-kaana|waʻdam|mafʻoolaa."
17,6,"S̤umma|radadnaa|lakumul|karrata|ʻalayhim|wa-ʹamdadnaakum̃|biʹamwaaliñw|wabaneena|wa-jaʻalnaakum|ʹaks̤ara|nafeeraa."
17,7,"ʹIn|ʹaḥsañtum|ʹaḥsañtum|liʹañfusikum;|wa-in|ʹasaʹtum|falahaa.|Faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|waʻdul|ʹaakhirati|liyasoooʹu|wujoohakum|wa-liyadkhulul|Masjida|kamaa|dakhaloohu|ʹawwala|marratiñw|waliyutabbiroo|maa-|ʻalaw|tatbeeraa."
17,8,"ʻAsaa|Rabbukum|ʹañy|yarḥamakum;|wa-ʹin|ʻuttum|ʻudnaa.|Wa-jaʻalnaa|Jahannama|lilkaafireena|ḥaṣeeraa."
17,9,"ʹInna|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaana|yahdee|lillatee|hiya|ʹaq̣wamu|wa-yubashshirul|Muʹmineenal|laẓeena|yaʻmaloonaṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|ʹanna|lahum|ʹajrañ|kabeeraa;"
17,10,"Waʹannal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|ʹaʻtadnaa|lahum|ʻAẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
17,11,"Wa-yadʻul|ʹiñsaanu|bishsharri|duʻaaʹahoo|bilkhayr;|wa-kaanal|ʹiñsaanu|ʻajoolaa."
17,12,"Wa-jaʻalnal|Layla|wan-Nahaara|ʹAayatayni|famaḥawnaaa|ʹAayatal|Layli|wa-jaʻalnaaa|ʹAayatan|Nahaari|mubṣiratal|litabtag̣oo|faḍlam|mir|rabbikum|wa-litaʻlamoo|ʻadadas|sineena|walḥisaab:|wa-kulla|shayʹiñ|faṣṣalnaahu|tafṣeelaa."
17,13,"Wa-kulla|ʹiñsaanin|ʹalzamnaahu|ṭaaaʹirahoo|fee|ʻunuq̣ih:|wa-nukhriju|lahoo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|kitaabañy|yalq̣aahu|mañshooraa."
17,14,"ʹIq̣raʹ|kitaabaka|kafaa|binafsikal|yawma|ʻalayka|ḥaseebaa."
17,15,"Manih|tadaa|faʹinnamaa|yahtadee|linafsih:|Wa-mañ|ḍalla|faʹinnamaa|yaḍillu|ʻalayhaa:|wa-laa|taziru|waaziratuñw|wizra|ʹukhraa:|wa-maa|kunnaa|muʻaẓẓibeena|ḥattaa|nabʻas̤a|rasoolaa."
17,16,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹaradnaaa|ʹan|nuhlika|q̣aryatan|ʹamarnaa|mutrafeehaa|fafasaq̣oo|feehaa|faḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhal|q̣awlu|fadammarnaahaa|tadmeeraa."
17,17,"Wa-kam|ʹahlaknaa|minal|q̣urooni|mim|baʻdi|Nooḥ?|Wa-kafaa|bi-Rabbika|biẓunoobi|ʻibaadihee|Khabeeram|Baṣeeraa."
17,18,"Mañ|kaana|yureedul|ʻaajilata|ʻajjalnaa|lahoo|feehaa|maa-|nashaaaʹu|liman|nureedu|s̤umma|jaʻalnaa|lahoo|Jahannam:|yaṣlaahaa|maẓmoomam|madḥooraa."
17,19,"Wa-man|ʹaraadal|ʹAakhirata|wa-saʻaa|lahaa|saʻyahaa|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|faʹulaaaʹika|kaana|saʻyuhum|mashkooraa."
17,20,"kullan|numiddu|haaaʹulaaaʹi|wa-haaaʹulaaaʹi|min|ʻaṭaaaʹi|rabbik:|Wa-maa|kaana|ʻaṭaaaʹu|Rabbika|maḥz̤̣ooraa."
17,21,"ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|faḍḍalnaa|baʻḍahum|ʻalaa|baʻḍ:|wa-lalʹAakhiratu|ʹakbaru|darajaatiñw|waʹakbaru|tafḍeelaa."
17,22,"Laa-|tajʻal|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhara|fataq̣ʻuda|maẓmoomam|makhẓoolaa."
17,23,"Wa-q̣aḍaa|Rabbuka|ʹallaa|taʻbudooo|ʹillaaa|ʹiyyaahu|wa-bilwaalidayni|ʹiḥsaanaa.|ʹImmaa|yablug̣anna|ʻiñdakal|kibara|ʹaḥaduhumaaa|aw|kilaahumaa|falaa|taq̣ul|lahumaaa|ʹuffiñw|Walaa|tanharhumaa|wa-q̣ul|lahumaa|q̣awlañ|kareemaa."
17,24,"Wakhfiḍ|lahumaa|janaaḥaẓ|ẓulli|minar|raḥmati|wa-q̣ur|Rabbir|ḥamhumaa|kamaa|rabbayaani|ṣag̣eeraa."
17,25,"Rabbukum|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|fee|nufoosikum:|ʹiñ|takoonoo|ṣaaliḥeena|faʹinnahoo|kaana|lil-ʹawwabeena|G̣afooraa."
17,26,"Wa-ʹaati|ẓal|q̣urbaa|ḥaq̣q̣ahoo|walmiskeena|wabnas|sabeeli|wa-laa|tubaẓẓir|tabẓeeraa."
17,27,"ʹInnal|mubaẓẓireena|kaanooo|ʹikhwaanash|shayaaṭeen;|wa-kaanash|Shayṭaanu|li-Rabbihee|kafooraa."
17,28,"Wa-ʹimmaa|tuʻriḍanna|ʻanhum|ubtig̣aaaʹa|Raḥmatim|mir|Rabbika|tarjoohaa|faq̣ullahum|raa.|q̣awlam|maysoo"
17,29,"Wa-laa|tajʻal|yadaka|mag̣loolatan|ʹilaa|ʻunuq̣ika|wa-laa|tabsuṭhaa|kullal|basṭi|fataq̣ʻuda|maloomam|maḥsooraa."
17,30,"ʹInna|Rabbaka|yabsuṭur|rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaq̣dir.|ʹInnahoo|kaana|biʻibaadihee|Khabeeram|Baṣeeraa."
17,31,"Wa-laa|taq̣tulooo|ʹawlaadakum|khashyata|ʹimlaaq̣:|Naḥnu|narzuq̣uhum|wa-ʹiyyaakum|ʹInna|q̣atlahum|kaana|khiṭʹañ|kabeeraa."
17,32,"Wa-laa|taq̣rabuz|zinaaa|ʹinnahoo|kaana|faaḥishah:|wa-saaaʹa|sabeelaa."
17,33,"Wa-laa|taq̣tulun|nafsal|latee|ḥarramal|laahu|ʹillaa|bilḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-mañ|q̣utila|maz̤̣loomañ|faq̣ad|jaʻalnaa|liwaliyyihee|sulṭaanañ|falaa|yusrif|fil|q̣atl;|ʹinnahoo|kaana|mañṣooraa."
17,34,"Wa-laa|taq̣raboo|maalal|yateemi|ʹillaa|billatee|hiya|ʹaḥsanu|ḥattaa|yablug̣a|ʹashuddah;|wa-ʹawfoo|bilʻahd:|ʹinnal|ʻahda|kaana|masʹoolaa."
17,35,"Wa-ʹawful|kayla|ʹiẓaa|kiltum|wazinoo|bilq̣isṭaasil|mustaq̣eem:|ẓaalika|khayruñw|waʹaḥsanu|taʹweelaa."
17,36,"Wa-laa|taq̣fu|maa-|laysa|laka|bihee|ʻilm;|ʹinnas|samʻa|walbaṣara|walfuʹaada|kullu|ʹulaaaʹika|kaana|ʻanhu|masʹoolaa."
17,37,"Wa-laa|tamshi|fil|ʹarḍi|maraḥaa:|ʹinnaka|lañ|takhriq̣al|ʹarḍa|wa-lañ|tablug̣al|jibaala|ṭoolaa."
17,38,"Kullu|ẓaalika|kaana|sayyiʹuhoo|ʻiñda|Rabbika|makroohaa."
17,39,"Ẓaalika|mimmaaa|ʹawḥaaa|ʹilayka|Rabbuka|minal|ḥikmah.|wa-laa|tajʻal|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhara|fatulq̣aa|fee|Jahannama|maloomam|madḥooraa."
17,40,"ʹA-faʹaṣfaakum|Rabbukum̃|bilbaneena|wattakhaẓa|minal|malaaaʹikati|ʹinaas̤aa?|ʹInnakum|lataq̣ooloona|q̣awlan|ʻaz̤̣eemaa!"
17,41,"Wa-laq̣ad|ṣarrafnaa|fee|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaani|liyaẓẓakkaroo:|wa-maa|yazeeduhum|ʹillaa|nufooraa!"
17,42,"Q̣ul|law|kaana|maʻahooo|ʹaalihatuñ|kamaa|yaq̣ooloona|ʹiẓal|labtag̣aw|ʹilaa|Ẓil|ʻArshi|sabeelaa!"
17,43,"Subḥaanahoo|wa-Taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yaq̣ooloona|ʻUluwwañ|Kabeeraa!"
17,44,"Tusabbiḥu|lahus|samaawaatus|sabʻu|wal-ʹarḍu|wa-mañ|feehinn:|wa-ʹim|miñ|shayʹin|ʹillaa|yusabbiḥu|bi-Ḥamdihee|wa-laakil|laa|tafq̣ahoona|tasbeeḥahum:|ʹInnahoo|kaana|Ḥaleeman|G̣afooraa!"
17,45,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣araʹtal|Q̣urʹaana|jaʻalnaa|baynaka|wa-baynal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|ḥijaabam|mastooraa;"
17,46,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|ʹakinnatan|ʹañy|yafq̣ahoohu|wa-feee|ʹaaẓaanihim|waq̣raa:|wa-ʹiẓaa|ẓakarta|Rabbaka|fil|Q̣urʹaani|Waḥdahoo|wallaw|ʻalaaa|ʹadbaarihim|nufooraa."
17,47,"Naḥnu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|yastamiʻoona|biheee|ʹiẓ|yastamiʻoona|ʹilayka|wa-ʹiẓ|hum|najwaaa|ʹiẓ|yaq̣ooluz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|ʹiñ|tattabiʻoona|ʹillaa|rajulam|mas-ḥooraa."
17,48,"ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|ḍaraboo|lakal|ʹams̤aala|faḍalloo|falaa|yastaṭeeʻoona|sabeelaa."
17,49,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|kunnaa|ʻiz̤̣aamañw|Warufaatan|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lamabʻoos̤oona|khalq̣añ|jadeedaa?"
17,50,"Q̣ul|koonoo|ḥijaaratan|ʹaw|ḥadeedaa,"
17,51,"ʹAw|khalq̣am|mimmaa|yakburu|fee|ṣudoorikum!|Fasayaq̣ooloona|mañy|yuʻeedunaa?|Q̣ulil|laẓee|faṭarakum|ʹawwala|marrah!|Fasayung̣iḍoona|ʹilayka|ruʹoosahum|wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|hu?|Q̣ul|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yakoona|q̣areebaa!"
17,52,"Yawma|yadʻookum|fatastajeeboona|bi-Ḥamdihee|wa-taunnoona|ʹil|labis̤tum|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa!"
17,53,"Wa-q̣ul|liʻibaadee|yaq̣oolul|latee|hiya|ʹaḥsan:|ʹinnash|shayṭaana|yañzag̣u|baynahum:|ʹinnash|Shayṭaana|kaana|lil-ʹiñsaani|ʻaduwwam|mubeenaa."
17,54,"Rabbukum|ʹaʻlamu|bikum:|ʹiñy|yashaʹ|yarḥamkum|ʹaw|ʹiñy|yashaʹ|yuʻaẓẓibkum:|wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʻalayhim|wakeelaa."
17,55,"Wa-Rabbuka|ʹaʻlamu|bimañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-laq̣ad|faḍḍalnaa|baʻḍan|nabiyyeena|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñw|waʹaataynaa|Daawooda|Zabooraa."
17,56,"Q̣ulid|ʻul|laẓeena|zaʻamtum|miñ|doonihee|falaa|yamlikoona|kashfaḍ|ḍurri|ʻañkum|wa-laa|taḥweelaa."
17,57,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|yadʻoona|yabtag̣oona|ʹilaa|Rabbihimul|Waseelata|ʹayyuhum|ʹaq̣rabu|wa-yarjoona|Raḥmatahoo|wa-yakhafoona|ʻAẓaabah:|ʹinna|ʻAẓaaba|Rabbika|kaana|maḥẓooraa."
17,58,"Wa-ʹim|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹillaa|Naḥnu|muhlikoohaa|q̣abla|yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|ʹaw|muʻaẓẓiboohaa|ʻaẓaabañ|shadeedaa:|kaana|ẓaalika|fil|Kitaabi|masṭooraa."
17,59,"Wa-maa|manaʻanaaa|ʹañ|nursila|bil-ʹaayaati|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|kaẓẓaba|bihal|ʹawwaloon:|wa-ʹaataynaa|S̤amoodan|Naaq̣ata|mubṣiratañ|faalamoo|bihaa:|wa-maa|nursilu|bil-ʹAayaati|ʹillaa|takhweefaa."
17,60,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ulnaa|laka|ʹinna|Rabbaka|ʹaḥaaṭa|binnaas:|wa-maa|jaʻalnar|ruʹyal|lateee|ʹaraynaaka|ʹillaa|fitnatal|linnaasi|wash-Shajaratal|Malʻoonata|fil|Q̣urʹaan:|wa-nukhaw-wifuhum|famaa|yazeeduhum|ʹillaa|ṭug̣yaanañ|kabeeraa."
17,61,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ulnaa|lil-malaaaʹikatis|judoo|liʹAadama|fasajadooo|ʹillaaa|ʹIblees:|q̣aala|ʹaʹasjudu|liman|khalaq̣ta|ṭeenaa?"
17,62,"Q̣aala|ʹaraʹaytaka|haaẓal|laẓee|karramta|ʻalayy!|Laʹin|ʹakhkhartani|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|laʹaḥtanikanna|ẓurriyyatahooo|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa!"
17,63,"Q̣aalaẓ|hab|famañ|tabiʻaka|minhum|faʹinna|Jahannama|jazaaaʹukum|jazaaaʹam|mawfooraa."
17,64,"Wastafziz|manis|taṭaʻta|minhum̃|biṣawtika|wa-ʹajlib|ʻalayhim̃|bikhaylika|wa-rajilika|wa-shaarik-hum|fil|ʹamwaali|wal-ʹawlaadi|wa-ʻidhum.|Wa-maa|yaʻiduhumush|Shayṭaanu|ʹillaa|g̣urooraa."
17,65,"ʹInna|ʻibaadi|laysa|laka|ʻalayhim|sulṭaan:|wa-kafaa|bi-Rabbika|Wakeelaa."
17,66,"Rabbukumul|laẓee|yuzjee|lakumul|Fulka|fil|baḥri|litabtag̣oo|miñ|faḍlih|ʹInnahoo|kaana|bikum|Raḥeemaa."
17,67,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|massakumuḍ|ḍurru|fil|baḥri|ḍalla|mañ|tadʻoona|ʹillaaa|ʹiyyaah!|Falammaa|najjaakum|ʹilal|barri|ʹaʻraḍtum.|Wa-kaanal|ʹiñsaanu|kafooraa!"
17,68,"ʹA-faʹamiñtum|ʹañy|yakhsifa|bikum|jaanibal|barri|ʹaw|yursila|ʻalaykum|ḥaasibañ|s̤umma|laa-|tajidoo|lakum|wakeelaa?"
17,69,"ʹAm|ʹamiñtum|ʹañy|yuʻeedakum|feehi|taaratan|ʹukhraa|fayursila|ʻalaykum|q̣aaṣifam|minar|reeḥi|fayug̣riq̣akum̃|bimaa|kafartum|s̤umma|laa-|tajidoo|lakum|ʻalaynaa|bihee|tabeeʻaa?"
17,70,"Wa-laq̣ad|karramnaa|Baneee|ʹAadama|waḥamalnaahum|fil|barri|walbaḥri|wa-razaq̣naahum|minaṭ|ṭayyibaati|wa-faḍḍalnaahum|ʻalaa|kas̤eerim|mimman|khalaq̣naa|tafḍeelaa."
17,71,"Yawma|nadʻoo|kulla|ʹunaasim|biʹImaamihim:|faman|ʹootiya|kitaabahoo|biyameenihee|faʹulaaaʹika|yaq̣raʹoona|kitaabahum|wa-laa|yuz̤̣lamoona|fateelaa."
17,72,"Wa-mañ|kaana|fee|haaẓiheee|ʹaʻmaa|fahuwa|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʹaʻmaa|wa-ʹaḍallu|Sabeelaa."
17,73,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaadoo|layaftinoonaka|ʻanil|laẓeee|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|litaftariya|ʻalaynaa|g̣ayrah:|wa-ʹiẓallat|takhaẓooka|khaleelaa!"
17,74,"Wa-lawlaaa|ʹañ|s̤abbatnaaka|laq̣ad|kitta|tarkanu|ʹilayhim|shayʹañ|q̣aleelaa."
17,75,"ʹIẓal|laʹaẓaq̣naaka|ḍiʻfal|ḥayaati|waḍiʻfal|mamaati|s̤umma|laa-|tajidu|laka|ʻalaynaa|naṣeeraa!"
17,76,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaadoo|layastafizzoonaka|minal|ʹarḍi|liyukhrijooka|minhaa|wa-ʹiẓal|laa|yalbas̤oona|khilaafaka|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa."
17,77,"Sunnata|mañ|q̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|q̣ablaka|mir|rusulinaa|wa-laa|tajidu|li-Sunnatinaa|taḥweelaa."
17,78,"ʹAq̣imiṣ|Ṣalaata|lidulookish|shamsi|ʹilaa|g̣asaq̣il|layli|wa-q̣urʹaanal|Fajr:|ʹinna|q̣urʹaanal|Fajri|kaana|mashhoodaa."
17,79,"Wa-minal|layli|fatahajjad|bihee|naafilatal|lak:|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yabʻas̤aka|Rabbuka|Maq̣aamam|Maḥmoodaa!"
17,80,"Wa-q̣ur|Rabbi|ʹadkhilnee|Mudkhala|Ṣidq̣iñw|Waʹakhrijnee|Mukhraja|Ṣidq̣iñw|wajʻal|lee|mil|laduñka|sulṭaanan|naseeraa."
17,81,"Wa-q̣ul|jaaaʹal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-zahaq̣al|Baaṭil:|ʹinnal|Baaṭila|kaana|zahooq̣aa."
17,82,"Wa-nunazzilu|minal|Q̣urʹaani|maa-|huwa|Shifaaaʹuñw|Wa-Raḥmatullil|Muʹmineena|walaa|yazeeduz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|ʹillaa|khasaaraa."
17,83,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹanʻamnaa|ʻalal|ʹiñsaani|ʹaʻraḍa|wa-naʹaa|bijaanibih;|wa-ʹiẓaa|massahush|sharru|kaana|yaʹoosaa!"
17,84,"Q̣ul|kulluñy|yaʻmalu|ʻalaa|Shaakilatih:|fa-Rabbukum|ʹaʻlamu|biman|huwa|ʹahdaa|Sabeelaa."
17,85,"Wa-yasʹaloonaka|ʻanir|Rooḥ|Q̣ulir|Rooḥu|min|ʹAmri|Rabbee|wa-maaa|ʹooteetum|minal|ʻilmi|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa."
17,86,"Wa-laʹiñ|shiʹnaa|lanaẓhabanna|billaẓeee|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|s̤umma|laa-|tajidu|laka|bihee|ʻalaynaa|wakeelaa,―"
17,87,"ʹIllaa|Raḥmatam|mir|Rabbika|ʹinna|Faḍlahoo|kaana|ʻalayka|kabeeraa."
17,88,"Q̣ul|laʹinij|tamaʻatil|ʹIñsu|wal-Jinnu|ʻalaaa|ʹañy|yaʹtoo|bimis̤li|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaani|laa-|yaʹtoona|bimis̤lihee|wa-law|kaana|baʻḍuhum|libaʻḍiñ|z̤̣aheeraa."
17,89,"Wa-laq̣ad|ṣarrafnaa|linnaasi|fee|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaani|miñ|kulli|mas̤al:|faʹabaaa|ʹaks̤arun|naasi|ʹillaa|kufooraa!"
17,90,"Wa-q̣aaloo|lan|nuʹmina|laka|ḥattaa|tafjura|lanaa|minal|ʹarḍi|yambooʻaa;"
17,91,"ʹAw|takoona|laka|jannatum|min|nakheeliñw|waʻinabiñ|fatufajjiral|ʹanhaara|khilaalahaa|tafjeeraa;"
17,92,"ʹAw|tusq̣iṭas|samaaaʹa|kamaa|zaʻamta|ʻalaynaa|kisafan|ʹaw|taʹtiya|billaahi|wal-malaaaʹikati|q̣abeelaa;"
17,93,"ʹAw|yakoona|laka|baytum|miñ|zukhrufin|ʹaw|tarq̣aa|fis|samaaaʹ.|Wa-lan|nuʹmina|liruq̣iyyika|ḥattaa|tunazzila|ʻalaynaa|kitaaban|naq̣raʹuh.|Q̣ul|Subḥaana|Rabbee|hal|kuñtu|ʹillaa|basharar|Rasoolaa?"
17,94,"Wa-maa|manaʻan|naasa|ʹañy|yuʹminooo|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹahumul|Hudaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aalooo|ʹabaʻas̤al|laahu|basharar|Rasoolaa?"
17,95,"Q̣ul|law|kaana|fil|ʹarḍi|malaaaʹikatuñy|yamshoona|muṭmaʹinneena|lanazzalnaa|ʻalayhim|minas|samaaaʹi|malakar|rasoolaa."
17,96,"Q̣ul|kafaa|billaahi|shaheedam|baynee|wa-baynakum:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|biʻibaadihee|khabeeram|Baṣeeraa."
17,97,"Wa-mañy|yahdil|laahu|fahuwal|muhtad;|wa-mañy|yuḍlil|falañ|tajida|lahum|ʹawliyaaaʹa|miñ|doonih.|Wa-naḥshuruhum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʻalaa|wujoohihim|ʻumyañw|Wabukmañw|waṣummaa:|maʹwaahum|Jahannam:|kullamaa|khabat|zidnaahum|Saʻeeraa."
17,98,"Ẓaalika|jazaaaʹuhum̃|biʹannahum|kafaroo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-q̣aalooo|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|kunnaa|ʻi-Z̤̣aamañw|Warufaatan|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lamabʻoos̤oona|khalq̣añ|jadeedaa?"
17,99,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannal|laahal|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|Q̣aadirun|ʻalaaa|ʹañy|yakhluq̣a|mis̤lahum|wa-jaʻala|lahum|ʹajalal|laa|rayba|feeh.|Faʹabaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|ʹillaa|kufooraa."
17,100,"Q̣ul|law|ʹañtum|tamlikoona|khazaaaʹina|Raḥmati|Rabbeee|ʹiẓal|laʹamsaktum|khashyatal|ʹiñfaaq̣:|wa-kaanal|ʹiñsaanu|q̣atooraa."
17,101,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosaa|tisʻa|ʹAayaatim|Bayyinaatiñ|fasʹal|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹahum|faq̣aala|lahoo|Firʻawnu|ʹinnee|laʹaz̤̣unnuka|yaa-Moosaa|mas-ḥooraa."
17,102,"Q̣aala|laq̣ad|ʻalimta|maaa|ʹañzala|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹillaa|Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|baṣaaaʹir:|wa-ʹinnee|laʹaz̤̣unnuka|yaa-Firʻawnu|mas̤booraa!"
17,103,"Faʹaraada|ʹañy|yastafizzahum|minal|ʹarḍi|faʹag̣raq̣naahu|wa-mam|maʻahoo|jameeʻaa."
17,104,"Wa-q̣ulnaa|mim|baʻdihee|li-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelas|kunul|ʹarḍa|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|Waʻdul|ʹaakhirati|jiʹnaa|bikum|lafeefaa."
17,105,"Wa-bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|ʹañzalnaahu|wa-bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|nazal:|wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʹillaa|Mubashshirañw|Wa-Naẓeeraa."
17,106,"Wa-Q̣urʹaanañ|faraq̣naahu|litaq̣raʹahoo|ʻalan|naasi|ʻalaa|muks̤iñw|wanazzalnaahu|tañzeelaa."
17,107,"Q̣ul|ʹaaminoo|biheee|ʹaw|laa-|tuʹminoo:|ʹinnal|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻilma|miñ|q̣abliheee|ʹiẓaa|yutlaa|ʻalayhim|yakhirroona|lil-ʹaẓq̣aani|sujjadaa,"
17,108,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|Subḥaana|Rabbinaaa|ʹiñ|kaana|waʻdu|Rabbinaa|lamafʻoolaa!"
17,109,"Wa-yakhirroona|lil-ʹaẓq̣aani|yabkoona|wa-yazeeduhum|khushooʻaa."
17,110,"Q̣ulid|ʻul|laaha|ʹawid|ʻur|Raḥmaan:|ʹayyam|maa|tadʻoo|falahul|ʹAsmaaaʹul|Ḥusnaa.|Wa-laa|tajhar|bi-Ṣalaatika|wa-laa|tukhaafit|bihaa|wabtag̣i|bayna|ẓaalika|Sabeelaa."
17,111,"Wa-q̣ulil|Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓee|lam|yattakhiẓ|waladañw|walam|yakul|lahoo|shareekuñ|fil|mulki|wa-lam|yakul|lahoo|waliyyum|minaẓ|ẓulli|wa-kabbirhu|takbeeraa."
18,1,"ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓeee|ʹañzala|ʻalaa|ʻAbdihil|Kitaaba|wa-lam|yajʻal|lahoo|ʻiwajaa―"
18,2,"Q̣ayyimal|liyuñẓira|Baʹsañ|shadeedam|mil|ladunhu|wa-yubashshiral|Muʹmineenal|laẓeena|yaʻmaloonaṣ|ṣaalihaati|ʹanna|lahum|ʹAjran|ḥasanaa,"
18,3,"Maakis̤eena|feehi|ʹabadaa:"
18,4,"Wa-yuñẓiral|laẓeena|q̣aalut|takhaẓal|laahu|waladaa:"
18,5,"Maa-|lahum̃|bihee|min|ʻilmiñw|walaa|liʹaabaaaʹihim.|Kaburat|kalimatañ|takhruju|min|ʹafwaahihim.|ʹIñy|yaq̣ooloona|ʹillaa|kaẓibaa."
18,6,"Falaʻallaka|baakhiʻun|nafsaka|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihim|ʹil|lam|yuʹminoo|bihaaẓal|Ḥadees̤i|ʹasafaa."
18,7,"ʹInnaa|jaʻalnaa|maa-|ʻalal|ʹarḍi|zeenatal|lahaa|linabluwahum|ʹayyuhum|ʹaḥsanu|ʻamalaa."
18,8,"Wa-ʹinnaa|lajaaʻiloona|maa-|ʻalayhaa|ṣaʻeedañ|juruzaa."
18,9,"ʹAm|ḥasibta|ʹanna|ʹAṣḥaabal|Kahfi|war-Raq̣eemi|kaanoo|min|ʹAayaatinaa|ʻajabaa?"
18,10,"ʹIẓ|ʹawal|fityatu|ʹilal|Kahfi|faq̣aaloo|Rabbanaaa|ʹaatinaa|mil|laduñka|Raḥmatañw|Wahayyiʹ|lanaa|min|ʹamrinaa|rashadaa!"
18,11,"Faḍarabnaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaaẓaanihim|fil|Kahfi|sineena|ʻadadaa:"
18,12,"S̤umma|baʻas̤naahum|linaʻlama|ʹayyul|ḥizbayni|ʹaḥṣaa|limaa|labis̤ooo|ʹamadaa!"
18,13,"Naḥnu|naq̣uṣṣu|ʻalayka|nabaʹahum̃|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣:|ʹinnahum|fityatun|ʹaamanoo|bi-Rabbihim|wa-zidnaahum|hudaa:"
18,14,"Wa-rabaṭnaa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|ʹiẓ|q̣aamoo|faq̣aaloo|Rabbunaa|Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|lan|nadʻuwa|miñ|dooniheee|ʹilaahal|laq̣ad|q̣ulnaaa|ʹiẓañ|shaṭaṭaa!"
18,15,"Haaaʹulaaaʹi|q̣awmunat|takhaẓoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹaalihah:|Lawlaa-|yaʹtoona|ʻalayhim̃|bisulṭaanim|bayyin?|Faman|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓibaa?"
18,16,"Wa-ʹiẓiʻtazal|tumoohum|wa-maa|yaʻbudoona|ʹillal|laaha|faʹwooo|ʹilal|Kahfi|yañshur|lakum|Rabbukum|mir|raḥmatihee|wa-yuhayyiʹ|lakum|min|ʹamrikum|mirfaq̣aa."
18,17,"Wa-tarash|shamsa|ʹiẓaa|ṭalaʻat|tazaawaru|ʻañ-|Kahfihim|ẓaatal|yameeni|wa-ʹiẓaa|g̣arabat|taq̣riḍuhum|ẓaatash|shimaali|wa-hum|fee|fajwatim|minh.|Ẓaalika|min|ʹAayaatil|laah:|mañy|yahdil|laahu|fahuwal|muhtad;|wa-mañy|yuḍlil|falañ|tajida|lahoo|waliyyam|murshidaa."
18,18,"Wa-taḥsabuhum|ʹayq̣aaz̤̣añw|Wahum|ruq̣ood:|wa-nuq̣allibuhum|ẓaatal|yameeni|waẓaatash|shimaal:|wa-kalbuhum̃|baasiṭuñ|ẓiraaʻayhi|bilwaṣeed:|lawiṭ|ṭalaʻta|ʻalayhim|lawallayta|minhum|firaarañw|wala-Muliʹta|minhum|ruʻbaa."
18,19,"Wa-kaẓaalika|baʻas̤naahum|liyatasaaaʹaloo|baynahum.|Q̣aala|q̣aaaʹilum|minhum|kam|labis̤tum?|Q̣aaloo|labis̤naa|yawman|ʹaw|baʻḍa|yawm.|Q̣aaloo|Rabbukum|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|labis̤tum....|Fabʻas̤ooo|ʹaḥadakum̃|biwariq̣ikum|haaẓiheee|ʹilal|madeenati|falyañz̤̣ur|ʹayyuhaaa|ʹazkaa|ṭaʻaamañ|falyaʹtikum̃|birizq̣im|minhu|walyatalaṭṭaf|wa-laa|yushʻiranna|bikum|ʹaḥadaa."
18,20,"ʹInnahum|ʹiñy|yaz̤̣haroo|ʻalaykum|yarjumookum|ʹaw|yuʻeedookum|fee|millatihim|wa-lañ|tufliḥooo|ʹiẓan|ʹabadaa."
18,21,"Wa-kaẓalika|ʹaʻs̤arnaa|ʻalayhim|liyaʻlamooo|ʹanna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|waʹannas|Saaʻata|laa-|rayba|feehaa.|ʹIẓ|yatanaazaʻoona|baynahum|ʹamrahum|faq̣aalub|noo|ʻalayhim̃|bunyaanaa:|Rabbuhum|ʹaʻlamu|bihim:|q̣aalal|laẓeena|g̣alaboo|ʻalaaa|ʹamrihim|lanattakhiẓanna|ʻalayhim|masjidaa."
18,22,"Sayaq̣ooloona|s̤alaas̤atur|raabiʻuhum|kalbuhum:|wa-yaq̣ooloona|khamsatuñ|saadisuhum|kalbuhum|rajmam|bilg̣ayb;|wa-yaq̣ooloona|sabʻatuñw|was̤aaminuhum|kalbuhum.|Q̣ur|Rabbeee|ʹaʻlamu|biʻiddatihim|maa|yaʻlamuhum|ʹillaa|q̣aleel.|Falaa|tumaari|feehim|ʹillaa|miraaaʹañ|z̤̣aahiraa,|wa-laa|tastafti|feehim|minhum|ʹaḥadaa."
18,23,"Wa-laa|taq̣oolanna|lishayʹin|ʹinnee|faaʻiluñ|ẓaalika|g̣adaa,"
18,24,"ʹIllaaa|ʹañy|yashaaaʹal|laah!|Waẓkur|Rabbaka|ʹiẓaa|naseeta|wa-q̣ul|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yahdiyani|Rabbee|liʹaq̣raba|min|haaẓaa|rashadaa."
18,25,"Wa-labis̤oo|fee|Kahfihim|s̤alaas̤a|miʹatiñ|sineena|wazdaadoo|tisʻaa."
18,26,"Q̣ulil|laahu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|labis̤oo:|lahoo|g̣aybus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|ʹabṣir|bihee|waʹasmiʻ!|Maa-|lahum|miñ|doonihee|miñw|waliyy;|wa-laa|yushriku|fee|Ḥukmiheee|ʹaḥadaa."
18,27,"Watlu|maaa|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayka|miñ|Kitaabi|Rabbik:|laa-|mubaddila|li-Kalimaatih:|wa-lañ|tajida|miñ|doonihee|multaḥadaa."
18,28,"Waṣbir|nafsaka|maʻal|laẓeena|yadʻoona|Rabbahum̃|bilg̣adaati|walʻashiyyi|yureedoona|Wajhahoo|wa-laa|taʻdu|ʻaynaaka|ʻanhum:|tureedu|zeenatal|Ḥayaatid|dunyaa;|wa-laa|tuṭiʻ|man|ʹag̣falnaa|q̣albahoo|ʻañ|ẓikrinaa|wattabaʻa|hawaahu|wa-kaana|ʹamruhoo|furuṭaa."
18,29,"Wa-q̣ulil|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbikum:|famañ|shaaaʹa|falyuʹmiñw|wamañ|shaaaʹa|falyakfur:|ʹinnaaa|ʹaʻtadnaa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|Naaran|ʹaḥaaṭa|bihim|suraadiq̣uhaa:|wa-ʹiñy|yastag̣ees̤oo|yug̣aas̤oo|bimaaaʹiñ|kalmuhli|yashwil|wujooh.|Biʹsash|sharaab!|wa-saaaʹat|murtafaq̣aa!"
18,30,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|ʹinnaa|laa-|nuḍeeʻu|ʹajra|man|ʹaḥsana|ʻamalaa."
18,31,"ʹUlaaaʹika|lahum|Jannaatu|ʻAdniñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihimul|ʹanhaaru|yuḥallawna|feehaa|min|ʹasaawira|miñ|ẓahabiñw|wayalbasoona|s̤iyaaban|khuḍram|miñ|suñdusiñw|waʹistabraq̣im|muttakiʹeena|feehaa|ʻalal|ʹaraaaʹik.|Niʻmas̤|s̤awaab!|Waḥasunat|murtafaq̣aa!"
18,32,"Waḍrib|lahum|mas̤alar|rajulayni|jaʻalnaa|liʹaḥadihimaa|jannatayni|min|ʹaʻnaabiñw|Waḥafafnaahumaa|binakhliñw|wajaʻalnaa|baynahumaa|zarʻaa."
18,33,"Kiltal|jannatayni|ʹaatat|ʹukulahaa|wa-lam|taz̤̣lim|minhu|shayʹañw|wafajjarnaa|khi-laalahumaa|naharaa,"
18,34,"Wa-kaana|lahoo|s̤amar:|faq̣aala|liṣaaḥibihee|wa-huwa|yuḥaawiruhooo|ʹana|ʹaks̤aru|miñka|maalañw|waʹaʻazzu|nafaraa."
18,35,"Wa-dakhala|jannatahoo|wa-huwa|z̤̣aalimul|linafsih:|q̣aala|maaa|ʹaz̤̣unnu|ʹañ|tabeeda|haaẓiheee|ʹabadaa."
18,36,"Wa-maaa|ʹaz̤̣unnus|saaʻata|q̣aaaʹimatañw|walaʹir|rudittu|ʹilaa|Rabbee|laʹajidanna|khayram|minhaa|muñq̣alabaa."
18,37,"Q̣aala|lahoo|ṣaaḥibuhoo|wa-huwa|yuḥaawiruhooo|ʹakafarta|billaẓee|khalaq̣aka|miñ|turaabiñ|s̤umma|min|nuṭfatiñ|s̤umma|sawwaaka|rajulaa?"
18,38,"Laakinna|Huwal|laahu|Rabbee|wa-laaa|ʹushriku|bi-Rabbeee|ʹaḥadaa."
18,39,"Wa-lawlaaa|ʹiẓ|dakhalta|jannataka|q̣ulta|maa-|shaaaʹal|laahu|Laa-|q̣uwwata|ʹillaa|billaah!|ʹIñ|tarani|ʹana|ʹaq̣alla|miñka|maalañw|wawaladaa."
18,40,"Faʻasaa|Rabbeee|ʹañy|yuʹtiyani|khayram|miñ|jannatika|wa-yursila|ʻalayhaa|ḥusbaanam|minas|samaaaʹi|fatuṣbiḥa|ṣaʻeedañ|zalaq̣aa!―"
18,41,"ʹAw|yuṣbiḥa|maaaʹuhaa|g̣awrañ|falañ|tastaṭeeʻa|lahoo|ṭalabaa."
18,42,"Wa-ʹuḥeeṭa|bis̤amarihee|faʹaṣbaḥa|yuq̣allibu|kaffayhi|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹañfaq̣a|feehaa|wa-hiya|khaawiyatun|ʻalaa|ʻurooshihaa|wa-yaq̣oolu|yaalaytanee|lam|ʹushrik|bi-Rabbeee|ʹaḥadaa!"
18,43,"Wa-lam|takul|lahoo|fiʹatuñy|yañṣuroonahoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-maa|kaana|muñtaṣiraa."
18,44,"Hunaalikal|walaayatu|lillaahil|Ḥaq̣q̣.|Huwa|Khayrun|s̤awaabañw|wa-Khayruñ|ʻuq̣baa."
18,45,"Waḍrib|lahum|mas̤alal|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|kamaaaʹin|ʹañzalnaahu|minas|samaaaʹi|fakhtalaṭa|bihee|nabaatul|ʹarḍi|faʹaṣbaḥa|hasheemañ|taẓroohur|riyaaḥ:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹim|Muq̣tadiraa."
18,46,"ʹAlmaalu|walbanoona|zeenatul|ḥayaatid|dunyaa:|wal-baaq̣iyaatuṣ|ṣaaliḥaatu|khayrun|ʻiñda|Rabbika|s̤awaabañw|wakhayrun|ʹamalaa."
18,47,"Wa-yawma|nusayyirul|jibaala|wa-taral|ʹarḍa|baarizatañw|waḥasharnaahum|falam|nug̣aadir|minhum|ʹaḥadaa."
18,48,"Wa-ʻuriḍoo|ʻalaa|Rabbika|ṣaffaa.|Laq̣ad|jiʹtumoonaa|kamaa|khalaq̣naakum|ʹawwala|marratim|bal|zaʻamtum|ʹallan|najʻala|lakum|mawʻidaa:"
18,49,"Wa-wuḍiʻal|Kitaabu|fataral|mujrimeena|mushfiq̣eena|mimmaa|feehi|wa-yaq̣ooloona|yaa-waylatanaa|maa|lihaaẓal|kitaabi|laa-|yug̣aadiru|ṣag̣eeratañw|walaa|kabeeratan|ʹillaaa|ʹaḥṣaahaa!|Wawajadoo|maa-|ʻamiloo|ḥaaḍiraa:|walaa|yaz̤̣limu|Rabbuka|ʹaḥadaa."
18,50,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ulnaa|lil-malaaaʹikatis|judoo|liʹAadama|fasajadooo|ʹillaaa|ʹIblees.|Kaana|minal|Jinni|fafasaq̣a|ʻan|ʹAmri|Rabbih.|ʹAfatattakhiẓoonahoo|waẓurriyyatahooo|ʹawliyaaaʹa|miñ|doonee|wa-hum|lakum|ʻaduww!|Biʹsa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|badalaa!"
18,51,"Maaa|ʹash-hattuhum|khalq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-laa|khalq̣a|ʹañfusihim:|wa-maa|kuñtu|muttakhiẓal|muḍilleena|ʻaḍudaa!"
18,52,"Wa-Yawma|yaq̣oolu|naadoo|shurakaaaʹi|yal-laẓeena|zaʻamtum|fadaʻawhum|falam|yastajeeboo|lahum|wa-jaʻalnaa|baynahum|maw-biq̣aa."
18,53,"Wa-ra|ʹal-mujrimoonan|Naara|faz̤̣annooo|ʹannahum|muwaaq̣iʻoohaa|wa-lam|yajidoo|ʻanhaa|maṣrifaa."
18,54,"Wa-laq̣ad|ṣarrafnaa|fee|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaani|linnaasi|miñ|kulli|mas̤al:|wa-kaanal|ʹIñsaanu|ʹaks̤ara|shayʹiñ|jadalaa."
18,55,"Wa-maa|manaʻan|naasa|ʹañy|yuʹminooo|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹahumul|Hudaa|wa-yastag̣firoo|Rabbahum|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|taʹtiyahum|sunnatul|ʹawwaleena|ʹaw|yaʹtiyahumul|ʻAẓaabu|q̣ubulaa?"
18,56,"Wa-maa|nursilul|mursaleena|ʹillaa|mubashshireena|wa-muñẓireen:|wa-yujaadilul|laẓeena|kafaroo|bilbaaṭili|liyudḥiḍoo|bihil|Ḥaq̣q̣:|wattakhaẓooo|ʹAayaatee|wa-maaa|ʹuñẓiroo|huzuwaa!"
18,57,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmañ|ẓukkira|biʹAayaati|Rabbihee|faʹaʻraḍa|ʻanhaa|Wanasiya|maa-|q̣addamat|yadaah?|ʹInnaa|jaʻalnaa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|ʹakinnatan|ʹañy|yafq̣ahoohu|wa-feee|ʹaaẓaanihim|waq̣raa.|Wa-ʹiñ|tadʻuhum|ʹilal|Hudaa|falañy|yahtadooo|ʹiẓan|ʹabadaa."
18,58,"Wa-Rabbukal|G̣afooru|Ẓur|Raḥmah.|Law|yuʹaakhiẓuhum̃|bimaa|kasaboo|laʻajjala|lahumul|ʻaẓaab:|bal|lahum|mawʻidul|lañy|yajidoo|miñ|doonihee|mawʹilaa."
18,59,"Wa-tilkal|q̣uraaa|ʹahlaknaahum|lammaa|z̤̣alamoo|wa-jaʻalnaa|limahlikihim|mawʻidaa."
18,60,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|lifataahu|laaa|ʹabraḥu|ḥattaaa|ʹablug̣a|majmaʻal|baḥrayni|ʹaw|ʹamḍiya|ḥuq̣ubaa."
18,61,"Falammaa|balag̣aa|majmaʻa|baynihimaa|nasiyaa|ḥootahumaa|fattakhaẓa|sabeelahoo|fil|baḥri|sarabaa."
18,62,"Falammaa|jaawazaa|q̣aala|lifataahu|ʹaatinaa|g̣adaaaʹanaa|laq̣ad|laq̣eenaa|miñ|safarinaa|haaẓaa|naṣabaa."
18,63,"Q̣aala|ʹaraʹayta|ʹiẓ|ʹawaynaaa|ʹilaṣ|ṣakhrati|faʹinnee|naseetul|ḥoot?|wa-maaa|ʹañsaaneehu|ʹillash|Shayṭaanu|ʹan|ʹaẓkurah:|wattakhaẓa|sabeelahoo|fil|baḥri|ʻajabaa!"
18,64,"Q̣aala|ẓaalika|maa-|kunnaa|nabg̣i|fartaddaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihimaa|q̣aṣaṣaa."
18,65,"Fawajadaa|ʻAbdam|min|ʻibaadinaaa|ʹaataynaahu|Raḥmatam|min|ʻiñdinaa|wa-ʻallamnaahu|mil|ladunna|ʻIlmaa."
18,66,"Q̣aala|lahoo|Moosaa|hal|ʹattabiʻuka|ʻalaaa|ʹañ|tuʻallimani|mimmaa|ʻullimta|rushdaa?"
18,67,"Q̣aala|ʹinnaka|lañ|tastaṭeeʻa|maʻiya|ṣabraa!"
18,68,"Wa-kayfa|taṣbiru|ʻalaa|maa-|lam|tuḥiṭ|bihee|khubraa?"
18,69,"Q̣aala|satajiduneee|ʹiñ|shaaa|ʹallaahu|ṣaabirañw|walaaa|ʹaʻṣee|laka|ʹamraa."
18,70,"Q̣aala|faʹinit|tabaʻtanee|falaa|tasʻalnee|ʻañ|shayʹin|ḥattaaa|ʹuḥdis̤a|laka|minhu|ẓikraa."
18,71,"Fañṭalaq̣aa:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|rakibaa|fis|safeenati|kharaq̣ahaa.|Q̣aala|ʹakharaq̣tahaa|litug̣riq̣a|ʹahlahaa?|Laq̣ad|jiʹta|shayʹan|ʹimraa!"
18,72,"Q̣aala|ʹalam|ʹaq̣ul|ʹinnaka|lañ|tasṭateeʻa|maʻiya|ṣabraa?"
18,73,"Q̣aala|laa-|tuʹaakhiẓnee|bimaa|naseetu|wa-laa|turhiq̣nee|min|ʹamree|ʻusraa."
18,74,"Fañṭalaq̣aa:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|laq̣iyaa|g̣ulaamañ|faq̣atalahoo|q̣aala|ʹaq̣atalta|nafsañ|zakiyyatam|big̣ayri|nafs?|Laq̣ad|jiʹta|shayʹan|nukraa!"
18,75,"Q̣aala|ʹalam|ʹaq̣ul|laka|ʹinnaka|lañ|tastaṭeeʻa|maʻiya|ṣabraa?"
18,76,"Q̣aala|ʹiñ|saʹaltuka|ʻañ|shayʹim|baʻdahaa|falaa|tuṣaaḥibnee:|q̣ad|balag̣ta|mil|ladunnee|ʻuẓraa."
18,77,"Fañṭalaq̣aa:|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹatayaaa|ʹahla|q̣aryatinis|taṭʻamaaa|ʹahlahaa|faʹabaw|ʹañy|yuḍayyifoohumaa|fawajadaa|feehaa|jidaarañy|yureedu|ʹañy|yañq̣aḍḍa|faʹaq̣aamah.|Q̣aala|law|shiʹta|lattakhaẓta|ʻalayhi|ʹajraa."
18,78,"Q̣aala|haaẓaa|firaaq̣u|baynee|wa-baynik:|saʹunabbiʹuka|bitaʹweeli|maa-|lam|tastaṭiʻ|ʻalayhi|ṣabraa."
18,79,"ʹAmmas|safeenatu|fakaanat|limasaakeena|yaʻmaloona|fil|baḥri|faʹarattu|ʹan|ʹaʻeebahaa|wa-kaana|wa-raaaʹahum|malikuñy|yaʹkhuẓu|kulla|safeenatin|g̣aṣbaa."
18,80,"Wa-ʹammal|g̣ulaamu|fakaana|ʹabawaahu|Muʹminayni|fakhasheenaaa|ʹañy|yurhiq̣ahumaa|ṭug̣yaanañw|wakufraa."
18,81,"Faʹaradnaaa|ʹañy|yubdilahumaa|Rabbuhumaa|khayram|minhu|zakaatañw|waʹaq̣raba|ruḥmaa."
18,82,"Wa-ʹammal|jidaaru|fakaana|lig̣ulaamayni|yateemayni|fil|Madeenati|wa-kaana|taḥtahoo|kañzul|lahumaa|wa-kaana|ʹaboohumaa|ṣaaliḥaa:|faʹaraada|Rabbuka|ʹañy|yablug̣aaa|ʹashuddahumaa|wa-yastakhrijaa|kañzahumaa|raḥmatam|mir|Rabbik.|Wa-maa|faʻaltuhoo|ʻan|ʹamree.|Ẓaalika|taʹweelu|maa-|lam|tasṭiʻ|ʻalayhi|ṣabraa."
18,83,"Wa-yasʹaloonaka|ʻañ|Ẓil|Q̣arnayn.|Q̣ul|saʹatloo|ʻalaykum|minhu|ẓikraa."
18,84,"ʹInnaa|makkannaa|lahoo|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹaataynaahu|miñ|kulli|shayʹiñ|sababaa."
18,85,"Faʹatbaʻa|sababaa."
18,86,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|balag̣a|mag̣ribash|shamsi|wajadahaa|tag̣rubu|fee|ʻaynin|ḥamiʹatiñw|wawajada|ʻiñdahaa|Q̣awmaa.|Q̣ulnaa|yaa-Ẓal|Q̣arnayni|ʹimmaaa|ʹañ|tuʻaẓẓiba|wa-ʹimmaaa|ʹañ|tattakhiẓa|feehim|ḥusnaa."
18,87,"Q̣aala|ʹammaa|mañ|z̤̣alama|fasawfa|nuʻaẓẓibuhoo|s̤umma|yuraddu|ʹilaa|Rabbihee|fayuʻaẓẓibuhoo|ʻaẓaaban|nukraa."
18,88,"Wa-ʹammaa|man|ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|falahoo|jazaaaʹanil|ḥusnaa,|wa-sanaq̣oolu|lahoo|min|ʹamrinaa|yusraa."
18,89,"S̤umma|ʹatbaʻa|sababaa."
18,90,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|balag̣a|maṭliʻash|shamsi|wajadahaa|taṭluʻu|ʻalaa|q̣awmil|lam|najʻal|lahum|miñ|doonihaa|sitraa."
18,91,"Kaẓaalika|wa-q̣ad|ʹaḥaṭnaa|bimaa|ladayhi|khubraa."
18,92,"S̤umma|ʹatbaʻa|sababaa,"
18,93,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|balag̣a|baynas|saddayni|wajada|miñ|doonihimaa|q̣awmal|laa|yakaadoona|yafq̣ahoona|q̣awlaa."
18,94,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Ẓal|Q̣arnayni|ʹinna|Yaʹjooja|wa-Maʹjooja|mufsidoona|fil|ʹarḍi|fahal|najʻalu|laka|kharjan|ʻalaaa|ʹañ|tajʻala|baynanaa|wa-baynahum|saddaa?"
18,95,"Q̣aala|maa-|makkannee|feehi|Rabbee|khayruñ|faʹaʻeenoonee|biq̣uwwatin|ʹajʻal|baynakum|wa-baynahum|radmaa:"
18,96,"ʹAatoonee|zubaral|ḥadeed.|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|saawaa|baynaṣ|ṣadafayni|q̣aalañ|fukhoo:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaʻalahoo|naarañ|q̣aala|ʹaatooneee|ʹufrig̣|ʻalayhi|q̣iṭraa."
18,97,"Famas|ṭaaʻooo|ʹañy|yaz̤̣haroohu|wa-mas|taṭaaʻoo|lahoo|naq̣baa."
18,98,"Q̣aala|haaẓaa|raḥmatum|mir|Rabbee:|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|waʻdu|Rabbee|jaʻalahoo|dakkaaaʹ;|wa-kaana|waʻdu|Rabbee|ḥaq̣q̣aa."
18,99,"Wa-taraknaa|baʻḍahum|Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yamooju|fee|baʻḍiñw|wanufikha|fiṣ|Ṣoori|fajamaʻnaahum|jamʻaa."
18,100,"Wa-ʻaraḍnaa|Jahannama|Yawmaʹiẓil|lilkaafireena|ʻarḍaa,―"
18,101,"ʹAllaẓeena|kaanat|ʹaʻyunuhum|fee|g̣iṭaaaʹin|ʻañ|ẓikree|wakaanoo|laa-|yastaṭeeʻoona|samʻaa."
18,102,"ʹAfaḥasibal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹañy|yattakhiẓoo|ʻibaadee|miñ|dooneee|ʹawliyaaaʹ?|ʹInnaaa|ʹaʻtadnaa|Jahannama|lil-kaafireena|nuzulaa."
18,103,"Q̣ul|hal|nunabbiʹukum̃|bilʹakhsareena|ʹaʻmaalaa?"
18,104,"ʹAllaẓeena|ḍalla|saʻyuhum|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-hum|yaḥsaboona|ʹannahm|yuḥsinoona|ṣunʻaa?"
18,105,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|kafaroo|biʹAayaati|Rabbihim|wa-Liq̣aaaʹihee|faḥabiṭat|ʹaʻmaaluhum|falaa|nuq̣eemu|lahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|waznaa."
18,106,"Ẓaalika|jazaaaʹuhum|Jahannamu|bimaa|kafaroo|wattakhaẓooo|ʹAayaatee|wa-Rusulee|huzuwaa."
18,107,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|kaanat|lahum|Jannaatul|Firdawsi|nuzulaa,"
18,108,"Khaalideena|feehaa|laa-|yabg̣oona|ʻanhaa|ḥiwalaa."
18,109,"Q̣ul|law|kaanal|baḥru|midaadal|li-Kalimaati|Rabbee|lanafidal|baḥru|q̣abla|ʹañ|tañfada|Kalimaatu|Rabbee|wa-law|jiʹnaa|bimis̤lihee|madadaa."
18,110,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|basharum|mis̤lukum|yooḥaaa|ʹilayya|ʹannamaaa|ʹIlaahukum|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥid:|famañ|kaana|yarjoo|Liq̣aaaʹa|Rabbihee|falyaʻmal|ʻamalañ|ṣaalihañw|walaa|yushrik|biʻibaadati|Rabbiheee|ʹaḥadaa."
19,1,"Kaaaf-Haa-Yaa-ʻAyyyñ-Ṣaaad."
19,2,"Ẓikru|Raḥmati|Rabbika|ʻabdahoo|Zakariyyaa."
19,3,"ʹIẓ|naadaa|Rabbahoo|nidaaaʹan|khafiyyaa."
19,4,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnee|wahanal|ʻaz̤̣mu|minnee|washtaʻalar|raʹsu|shaybañw|walam|ʹakum|biduʻaaaʹika|Rabbi|shaq̣iyyaa!"
19,5,"Wa-ʹinnee|khiftul|mawaaliya|miñw|waraaaʹee|wa-kaanat|imraʹatee|ʻaaq̣irañ|fahab|lee|mil|laduñka|waliyyaa,―"
19,6,"Yaris̤unee|wa-yaris̤u|min|ʹaali|Yaʻq̣ooba|wajʻalhu|Rabbi|raḍiyyaa!"
19,7,"Yaa-Zakariyyaaa|ʹinnaa|nubashshiruka|big̣ulaamin|ismuhoo|Yaḥyaa|lam|najʻal|lahoo|miñ|q̣ablu|samiyyaa."
19,8,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹannaa|yakoonu|lee|g̣ulaamuñw|wakaanatim|raʹatee|ʻaaq̣irañw|Waq̣ad|balag̣tu|minal|kibari|ʻitiyyaa?"
19,9,"Q̣aala|kaẓaalik:|q̣aala|Rabbuka|huwa|ʻalayya|hayyinuñw|waq̣ad|khalaq̣tuka|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-lam|taku|shayʹaa!"
19,10,"Q̣aala|Rabbij|ʻal|leee|ʹAayah.|Q̣aala|ʹAayatuka|ʹallaa|tukalliman|naasa|s̤alaas̤a|layaaliñ|sawiyyaa."
19,11,"Fakharaja|ʻalaa|q̣awmihee|minal|miḥraabi|faʹawḥaaa|ʹilayhim|ʹañ|sabbiḥoo|bukratañw|waʻashiyyaa."
19,12,"Yaa-Yaḥyaa|khuẓil|Kitaaba|biq̣uwwah:|wa-ʹaataynaahul|Ḥukma|ṣabiyyaa."
19,13,"Waḥanaanam|mil|ladunnaa|wazakaah:|wa-kaana|taq̣iyyaa,"
19,14,"Wa-barram|biwaalidayhi|wa-lam|yakuñ|jabbaaran|ʻaṣiyyaa."
19,15,"Wa-Salaamun|ʻalayhi|yawma|wulida|wa-yawma|yamootu|wa-yawma|yubʻas̤u|ḥayyaa!"
19,16,"Waẓkur|fil|Kitaabi|Maryam.|ʹIẓiñ|tabaẓat|min|ʹahlihaa|makaanañ|sharq̣iyyaa."
19,17,"Fattakhaẓat|miñ|doonihim|ḥijaabaa.|Faʹarsalnaaa|ʹilayhaa|rooḥanaa|fatamas̤s̤ala|lahaa|basharañ|sawiyyaa."
19,18,"Q̣aalat|ʹinneee|ʹaʻooẓu|bir-Raḥmaani|miñka|ʹiñ|kuñta|taq̣iyyaa."
19,19,"Q̣aala|ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|rasoolu|Rabbiki|liʹahaba|laki|g̣ulaamañ|zakiyyaa."
19,20,"Q̣aalat|ʹannaa|yakoonu|lee|g̣ulaamuñw|walam|yamsasnee|basharuñw|walam|ʹaku|bag̣iyyaa?"
19,21,"Q̣aala|kaẓaalik:|q̣aala|Rabbuki|huwa|ʻalayya|hay-yin:|wa-linajʻalahooo|ʹAayatal|linnaasi|wa-Raḥmatam|minnaa:|wa-kaana|ʹamram|maq̣ḍiyyaa."
19,22,"Faḥamalathu|fañtabaẓat|bihee|makaanañ|q̣aṣiyyaa."
19,23,"Faʹajaaaʹahal|makhaaḍu|ʹilaa|jiẓʻin|nakhlah;|q̣aalat|yaa-laytanee|mittu|q̣abla|haaẓaa|wa-kuñtu|nasyam|mañsiyyaa!"
19,24,"Fanaadaahaa|miñ|taḥtihaaa|ʹallaa|taḥzanee|q̣ad|jaʻala|Rabbuki|taḥtaki|sariyyaa;"
19,25,"Wa-huzzeee|ʹilayki|bijiẓʻin|nakhlati|tusaaq̣iṭ|ʻalayki|ruṭabañ|janiyyaa."
19,26,"Fakulee|washrabee|wa-q̣arree|ʻaynaa.|Faʹimmaa|tarayinna|minal|bashari|ʹaḥadañ|faq̣ooleee|ʹinnee|naẓartu|lir-Raḥmaani|ṣawmañ|falan|ʹukallimal|yawma|ʹiñsiyyaa."
19,27,"Faʹatat|bihee|q̣awmaahaa|taḥmiluh.|Q̣aaloo|yaa-Maryamu|laq̣ad|jiʹti|shayʹañ|fariyyaa."
19,28,"Yaaaʹukhta|Haaroona|maa-|kaana|ʹabookim|raʹa|sawʹiñw|wamaa|kaanat|ʹummuki|bag̣iyyaa!"
19,29,"Faʹashaarat|ʹilayh.|Q̣aaloo|kayfa|nukallimu|mañ|kaana|fil|mahdi|ṣabiyyaa?"
19,30,"Q̣aala|ʹinnee|ʻAbdul|laah:|ʹaataaniyal|Kitaaba|wa-jaʻalanee|Nabiyyaa;"
19,31,"Wa-jaʻalanee|mubaarakan|ʹayna|maa|kuñtu,|wa-ʹawṣaanee|biṣ-Ṣalaati|waz-Zakaati|maa-|dumtu|ḥayyaa:"
19,32,"Wa-barram|biwaalidatee|wa-lam|yajʻalnee|jabbaarañ|shaq̣iyyaa;"
19,33,"Was-Salaamu|ʻalayya|yawma|wulittu|wa-yawma|ʹamootu|wa-yawma|ʹubʻas̤u|ḥayyaa!"
19,34,"Ẓaalika|ʻEesab|nu|Maryam:|q̣awlal|ḥaq̣q̣il|laẓee|feehi|yamtaroon."
19,35,"Maa-|kaana|lillaahi|ʹañy|yattakhiẓa|miñw|waladiñ|Subḥaanah!|ʹIẓaa|q̣aḍaaa|ʹamrañ|faʹinnamaa|yaq̣oolu|lahoo|Kuñ|Fayakoon.˺"
19,36,"Wa-ʹinnal|laaha|Rabbee|wa-Rabbukum|faʻbudooh:|haaẓaa|Ṣiraaṭum|Mustaq̣eem."
19,37,"Fakhtalafal|ʹaḥzaabu|mim|baynihim:|fawaylul|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|mim|Mashhadi|yawmin|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
19,38,"ʹAsmiʻ|bihim|wa-ʹabṣir|Yawma|yaʹtoonanaa|laakiniz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoonal|yawma|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen!"
19,39,"Waʹañẓirhum|Yawmal|Ḥasrati|ʹiẓ|q̣uḍiyal|ʹamr.|Wa-hum|fee|g̣aflatiñw|wahum|laa-|yuʹminoon!"
19,40,"ʹInnaa|Naḥnu|naris̤ul|ʹarḍa|wa-man|ʻalayhaa|wa-ʹilaynaa|yurjaʻoon."
19,41,"Waẓkur|fil|Kitaabi|ʹIbraaheem:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|Ṣiddeeq̣an|Nabiyyaa."
19,42,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|liʹabeehi|yaaaʹabati|lima|taʻbudu|maa|laa-|yasmaʻu|wa-laa|yubṣiru|wa-laa|yug̣nee|ʻañka|shayʹaa?"
19,43,"Yaaaʹabati|ʹinnee|q̣ad|jaaaʹanee|minal|ʻilmi|maa-|lam|yaʹtika|fattabiʻneee|ʹahdika|Ṣiraaṭañ|sawiyyaa."
19,44,"Yaaaʹabati|laa-|taʻbudish|Shayṭaan:|ʹinnash|Shayṭaana|kaana|lir-Raḥmaani|ʻaṣiyyaa."
19,45,"Yaaaʹabati|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yamassaka|ʻAẓaabum|minar|Raḥmaani|fatakoona|lish-Shayṭaani|waliyyaa."
19,46,"Q̣aala|ʹaraag̣ibun|ʹañta|ʻan|ʹaalihatee|yaaaʹIbraaheem?|Laʹil|lam|tañtahi|laʹarjumannaka|wahjurnee|maliyyaa!"
19,47,"Q̣aala|Salaamun|ʻalayk:|saʹastag̣firu|laka|Rabbee:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|bee|Ḥafiyyaa."
19,48,"Wa-ʹaʻtazilukum|wa-maa|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-ʹadʻoo|Rabbee|ʻasaaa|ʹallaaa|ʹakoona|biduʻaaaʹi|Rabbee|shaq̣iyyaa."
19,49,"Falammaʻ|tazalahum|wa-maa|yaʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|wahabnaa|lahooo|ʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣oob:|wa-kullañ|jaʻalnaa|nabiyyaa."
19,50,"Wa-wahabnaa|lahum|mir|Raḥmatinaa|wa-jaʻalnaa|lahum|lisaana|ṣidq̣in|ʻaliyyaa."
19,51,"Waẓkur|fil|Kitaabi|Moosaaa|ʹinnahoo|kaana|mukhlaṣañw|wakaana|Rasoolan|Nabiyyaa."
19,52,"Wa-naadaynaahu|miñ|jaanibiṭ|Ṭooril|ʹaymani|wa-q̣arrabnaahu|najiyyaa."
19,53,"Wa-wahabnaa|lahoo|mir|Raḥmatinaaa|ʹakhaahu|Haaroona|Nabiyyaa."
19,54,"Waẓkur|fil|Kitaabi|ʹIsmaaʻeel;|ʹinnahoo|kaana|ṣaadiq̣al|waʻdi|wa-kaana|Rasoolan|Nabiyyaa."
19,55,"Wa-kaana|yaʹmuru|ʹahlahoo|biṣ-Ṣalaati|waz-Zakaah;|wa-kaana|ʻiñda|Rabbihee|marḍiyyaa."
19,56,"Waẓkur|fil|Kitaabi|ʹIdrees:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|ṣiddeeq̣an|Nabiyyaa:"
19,57,"Wa-rafaʻnaahu|makaanan|ʻaliyyaa."
19,58,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ʹanʻamal|laahu|ʻalayhim|minan|nabiyyeena|miñ|ẓurriyyati|ʹAadama,|wa-mimman|ḥamalnaa|maʻa|Nooḥ,|wa-miñ|ẓurriyyati|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsraaaʹeela|wa-mimman|hadaynaa|wajtabaynaa.|ʹIẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatur|Raḥmaani|kharroo|sujjadañw|wabukiyyaa."
19,59,"Fakhalafa|mim|baʻdihim|khalfun|ʹaḍaaʻuṣ|Ṣalaata|wattabaʻush|shahawaati|fasawfa|yalq̣awna|g̣ayyaa."
19,60,"ʹIllaa|mañ|taaba|wa-ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|faʹulaaaʹika|yadkhuloonal|Jannata|wa-laa|yuz̤̣lamoona|shayʹaa,"
19,61,"Jannaati|ʻAdninil|latee|waʻadar|Raḥmaanu|ʻibaadahoo|bil-G̣ayb:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|waʻduhoo|maʹtiyyaa."
19,62,"Laa-|yasmaʻoona|feehaa|lag̣wan|ʹillaa|Salaamaa:|wa-lahum|rizq̣uhum|feehaa|bukratañw|waʻashiyyaa."
19,63,"Tilkal|Jannatul|latee|nooris̤u|min|ʻibaadinaa|mañ|kaana|taq̣iyyaa."
19,64,"Wa-maa|natanazzalu|ʹillaa|biʹamri|Rabbik:|lahoo|maa-|bayna|ʹaydeenaa|wa-maa|khalfanaa|wa-maa|bayna|ẓaalika:|wa-maa|kaana|Rabbuka|nasiyyaa,"
19,65,"Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa|faʻbudhu|waṣṭabir|liʻibaadatih:|hal|taʻlamu|lahoo|samiyyaa?"
19,66,"Wa-yaq̣oolul|ʹiñsaanu|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|maa|mittu|lasawfa|ʹukhraju|ḥayyaa?"
19,67,"ʹAwalaa|yaẓkurul|ʹiñsaanu|ʹannaa|khalaq̣naahu|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-lam|yaku|shayʹaa?"
19,68,"Fawa-Rabbika|lanaḥshurannahum|washshayaaṭeena|s̤umma|lanuḥḍirannahum|ḥawla|Jahannama|jis̤iyyaa;"
19,69,"S̤umma|lanañziʻanna|miñ|kulli|sheeʻatin|ʹayyuhum|ʹashaddu|ʻalar|Raḥmaani|ʻitiyyaa."
19,70,"S̤umma|lanaḥnu|ʹaʻlamu|billaẓeena|hum|ʹawlaa|bihaa|ṣiliyyaa."
19,71,"Wa-ʹim|miñkum|ʹillaa|waariduhaa:|kaana|ʻalaa|Rabbika|Ḥatmam|maq̣ḍiyyaa."
19,72,"S̤umma|nunajjil|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|wanaẓaruz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|feehaa|jis̤iyyaa."
19,73,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|bayyinaatiñ|q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹayyul|fareeq̣ayni|khayrum|Maq̣aamañw|Waʹaḥsanu|Nadiyyaa?"
19,74,"Wa-kam|ʹahlaknaa|q̣ablahum|miñ|q̣arnin|hum|ʹaḥsanu|ʹas̤aas̤añw|Wariʹyaa?"
19,75,"Q̣ul|mañ|kaana|fiḍ|ḍalaalati|falyamdud|lahur|Raḥmaanu|maddaa:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|raʹaw|maa-|yooʻadoona|ʹimmal|ʻaẓaaba|wa-ʹimmas|Saaʻah.|Fasayaʻlamoona|man|huwa|sharrum|makaanañw|waʹaḍʻafu|juñdaa!"
19,76,"Wa-yazeedul|laahul|laẓeenah|tadaw|Hudaa;|wal-Baaq̣iyaatuṣ|Ṣaaliḥaatu|khayrun|ʻiñda|Rabbika|s̤awaabañw|wakhayrum|maraddaa."
19,77,"ʹAfaraʹaytal|laẓee|kafara|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-q̣aala|laʹootayanna|maalañw|wawaladaa?"
19,78,"ʹAṭ-ṭalaʻal|G̣ayba|ʹamit|takhaẓa|ʻiñdar|Raḥmaani|ʻahdaa?"
19,79,"Kallaa!|Sanaktubu|maa-|yaq̣oolu|wa-namuddu|lahoo|minal|ʻaẓaabi|maddaa."
19,80,"Wanaris̤uhoo|maa-|yaq̣oolu|wa-yaʹteenaa|fardaa."
19,81,"Wattakhaẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹaalihatal|liyakoonoo|lahum|ʻizzaa!"
19,82,"Kallaa!|sayakfuroona|biʻibaadatihim|wa-yakoonoona|ʻalayhim|ḍiddaa."
19,83,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannaaa|ʹarsalnash|shayaaṭeena|ʻalal|kaafireena|taʹuzzuhum|ʹazzaa?"
19,84,"Falaa|taʻjal|ʻalayhim:|ʹinnamaa|naʻuddu|lahum|ʻaddaa."
19,85,"Yawma|naḥshurul|Muttaq̣eena|ʹilar|Raḥmaani|wafdaa,"
19,86,"Wa-nasooq̣ul|mujrimeena|ʹilaa|Jahannama|wirdaa."
19,87,"Laa-|yamlikoonash|shafaaʻata|ʹillaa|manit|takhaẓa|ʻiñdar|Raḥmaani|ʻahdaa."
19,88,"wa-q̣aalut|takhaẓar|Raḥmaanu|waladaa!"
19,89,"Laq̣ad|jiʹtum|shayʹan|ʹiddaa!"
19,90,"Takaadus|samaawaatu|yatafaṭṭarna|minhu|wa-tañshaq̣|q̣ul-ʹarḍu|wa-takhirrul|jibaalu|haddaa,"
19,91,"ʹAñ|daʻaw|lir-Raḥmaani|waladaa."
19,92,"Wa-maa|yambag̣ee|lir-Raḥmaani|ʹañy|yattakhiẓa|waladaa."
19,93,"ʹIñ|kullu|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|ʹillaaa|ʹaatir|Raḥmaani|ʻabdaa."
19,94,"Laq̣ad|ʹaḥṣaahum|wa-ʻaddahum|ʻaddaa."
19,95,"Wa-kulluhum|ʹaateehi|yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|fardaa."
19,96,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|sayajʻalu|lahumur|Raḥmaanu|wuddaa."
19,97,"Faʹinnamaa|yassarnaahu|bilisaanika|litubashshira|bihil|Muttaq̣eena|wa-tuñẓira|bihee|q̣awmal|luddaa."
19,98,"Wa-kam|ʹahlaknaa|q̣ablahum|miñ|q̣arn?|Hal|tuḥissu|minhum|min|ʹaḥadin|ʹaw|tasmaʻu|lahum|rikzaa?"
20,1,"Ṭaa-Haa."
20,2,"Maaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaykal|Q̣ur-ʹaana|litashq̣aa,"
20,3,"ʹIllaa|taẓkiratal|limañy|yakhshaa,"
20,4,"Tañzeelam|mimman|khalaq̣al|ʹarḍa|was-samaawaatil|ʻulaa."
20,5,"ʹAr-Raḥmaanu|ʻalal|ʻArshis|tawaa."
20,6,"Lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa|wa-maa|taḥtas̤|s̤araa."
20,7,"Wa-ʹiñ|tajhar|bilq̣awli|faʹinnahoo|yaʻlamus|sirra|wa-ʹakhfaa."
20,8,"ʹAllaahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo!|Lahul|ʹAsmaaaʹul|Ḥusnaa."
20,9,"Wa-hal|ʹataaka|ḥadees̤u|Moosaa?"
20,10,"ʹIẓ|raʹaa|naarañ|faq̣aala|liʹahlihim|kus̤ooo|ʹinneee|ʹaanastu|naaral|laʻalleee|ʹaateekum|minhaa|biq̣abasin|ʹaw|ʹajidu|ʻalan|naari|hudaa."
20,11,"Falammaaa|ʹataahaa|noodiya|yaa-Moosaa!"
20,12,"ʹInneee|ʹAna|Rabbuka|fakhlaʻ|naʻlayk:|ʹInnaka|bilwaadil|muq̣addasi|Ṭuwaa."
20,13,"Wa-|ʹanakhtartuka|fastamiʻ|limaa|yooḥaa."
20,14,"ʹInnaneee|ʹAnal|laahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaaa|ʹAna|faʻbudnee|wa-ʹaq̣imiṣ|Ṣalaata|liẓikree."
20,15,"ʹInnas|Saaʻata|ʹaatiyatun|ʹakaadu|ʹukhfeehaa|litujzaa|kullu|nafsim|bimaa|tasʻaa."
20,16,"Falaa|yaṣuddannaka|ʻanhaa|mal|laa|yuʹminu|bihaa|wattabaʻa|hawaahu|fatardaa!"
20,17,"Wa-maa|tilka|biyameenika|yaa-Moosaa?"
20,18,"Q̣aala|hiya|ʻaṣaaya|ʹatawakkaʹu|ʻalayhaa|wa-ʹahushshu|bihaa|ʻalaa|g̣anamee|wa-liya|feehaa|maʹaaribu|ʹukhraa."
20,19,"Q̣aala|ʹalq̣ihaa|yaa-Moosaa!"
20,20,"Faʹalq̣aahaa|faʹiẓaa|hiya|ḥayyatuñ|tasʻaa."
20,21,"Q̣aala|khuẓhaa|wa-laa|takhaf,|sanuʻeeduhaa|seeratahal|ʹoolaa."
20,22,"Waḍmum|yadaka|ʹilaa|janaaḥika|takhruj|bayḍaaaʹa|min|g̣ayri|soooʹin|ʹAayatan|ʹukhraa,"
20,23,"Linuriyaka|min|ʹAayaatinal|kubraa."
20,24,"ʹIẓhab|ʹilaa|firʻawna|ʹinnahoo|ṭag̣aa."
20,25,"Q̣aala|Rabbish|raḥ|lee|ṣadree;"
20,26,"Wa-yassir|leee|ʹamree;"
20,27,"Waḥlul|ʻuq̣datam|milli|saanee,"
20,28,"Yafq̣ahoo|q̣awlee:"
20,29,"Wajʻal|lee|Wazeeram|min|ʹahlee,"
20,30,"Haaroona|ʹakhee;"
20,31,"ʹUshdud|biheee|ʹazree,"
20,32,"Wa-ʹashrik-hu|feee|ʹamree:"
20,33,"Kay|nusabbiḥaka|kas̤eeraa."
20,34,"Wa-naẓkuraka|kas̤eeraa:"
20,35,"ʹInnaka|kuñta|binaa|baṣeeraa."
20,36,"Q̣aala|q̣ad|ʹooteeta|suʹlaka|yaa-Moosaa!"
20,37,"Wa-laq̣ad|manannaa|ʻalayka|marratan|ʹukhraa,"
20,38,"ʹIẓ|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹummika|maa-|yooḥaa,"
20,39,"ʹAni|q̣ẓifeehi|fit|taabooti|faq̣ẓifeehi|fil|yammi|fal-yulq̣ihil|yammu|bis-saaḥili|yaʹkhuẓhu|ʻaduwwul|lee|wa-ʻaduwwul|lah:|wa-ʹalq̣aytu|ʻalayka|maḥabbatam|minnee:|wa-lituṣnaʻa|ʻalaa|ʻaynee."
20,40,"ʹIẓ|tamsheee|ʹukhtuka|fataq̣oolu|hal|ʹadullukum|ʻalaa|mañy|yakfuluh?|Farajaʻnaaka|ʹilaaa|ʹummika|kay|taq̣arra|ʻaynuhaa|wa-laa|taḥzan.|Wa-q̣atalta|nafsañ|fanajjaynaaka|minal|g̣ammi|wa-fatannaaka|futoonaa.|Falabis̤ta|sineena|feee|ʹahli|Madyan:|S̤umma|jiʹta|ʻalaa-|q̣adariñy|Yaa-Moosaa!"
20,41,"Waṣṭanaʻtuka|linafsee."
20,42,"ʹIẓhab|ʹañta|wa-ʹakhooka|biʹAayaatee|wa-laa|taniyaa|fee|ẓikree."
20,43,"ʹIẓhabaaa|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|ʹinnahoo|ṭag̣aa;"
20,44,"Faq̣oolaa|lahoo|q̣awlal|layyinal|laʻallahoo|yataẓakkaru|ʹaw|yakhshaa."
20,45,"Q̣aalaa|Rabbanaaa|ʹinnanaa|nakhaafu|ʹañy|yafruṭa|ʻalaynaaa|ʹaw|ʹañy|yaṭg̣aa."
20,46,"Q̣aala|laa-|takhaafaaa|ʹinnanee|maʻakumaaa|ʹasmaʻu|wa-ʹaraa."
20,47,"Faʹtiyaahu|faq̣oolaaa|ʹinnaa|Rasoolaa|Rabbika|faʹarsil|maʻanaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel:|wa-laa|tuʻaẓẓibhum:|q̣ad|jiʹnaaka|biʹAayatim|mir|Rabbik!|Was-Salaamu|ʻalaa|manit|tabaʻal|Hudaa!"
20,48,"ʹInnaa|q̣ad|ʹooḥiya|ʹilaynaaa|ʹannal|ʻAẓaaba|ʻalaa|mañ|kaẓ-ẓaba|wa-tawallaa."
20,49,"Q̣aala|famar|Rabbukumaa|yaa-Moosaa?"
20,50,"Q̣aala|Rabbunal|laẓeee|ʹaʻṭaa|kulla|shayʹin|khalq̣ahoo|s̤umma|hadaa."
20,51,"Q̣aala|famaa|baalul|q̣uroonil|ʹoolaa?"
20,52,"Q̣aala|ʻilmuhaa|ʻiñda|Rabbee|fee|Kitaab:|laa-|yaḍillu|Rabbee|wa-laa|yañsaa,"
20,53,"ʹAllaẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹarḍa|mahdañw|wa-salaka|lakum|feehaa|subulañw|waʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹaa.|Faʹakhrajnaa|biheee|ʹazwaajam|min|nabaatiñ|shattaa."
20,54,"Kuloo|warʻaw|ʹanʻaamakum:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liʹulin|nuhaa."
20,55,"Minhaa|khalaq̣naakum|wa-feehaa|nuʻeedukum|wa-minhaa|nukhrijukum|taaratan|ʹukhraa."
20,56,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaraynaahu|ʹAayaatinaa|kullahaa|fakaẓẓaba|wa-ʹabaa."
20,57,"Q̣aala|ʹajiʹtanaa|litukhrijanaa|min|ʹarḍinaa|bisiḥrika|yaa-Moosaa?"
20,58,"Falanaʹtiyannaka|bisiḥrim|mis̤lihee|fajʻal|baynana|wa-baynaka|mawʻidal|laa|nukhlifuhoo|naḥnu|wa-laaa|ʹañta|makaanañ|suwaa."
20,59,"Q̣aala|mawʻidukum|yawmuz|zeenati|wa-ʹañy|yuḥsharan|naasu|ḍuḥaa."
20,60,"Fatawallaa|firʻawnu|fajamaʻa|kaydahoo|s̤umma|ʹataa."
20,61,"Q̣aala|lahum|Moosaa|waylakum|laa-|taftaroo|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓibañ|fayusḥitakum̃|biʻaẓaab:|wa-q̣ad|khaaba|manif|taraa!"
20,62,"Fatanaazaʻooo|ʹamrahum̃|baynahum|wa-ʹasarrun|najwaa."
20,63,"Q̣aalooo|ʹin|haaẓaani|lasaaḥiraani|yureedaani|ʹañy|yukhrijaakum|min|ʹarḍikum̃|bisiḥrihimaa|wa-yaẓhabaa|biṭareeq̣atikumul|mus̤laa."
20,64,"Faʹajmiʻoo|kaydakum|s̤ummaʹ|too|ṣaffaa:|wa-q̣ad|ʹaflaḥal|yawma|manis|taʻlaa."
20,65,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹimmaaa|ʹañ|tulq̣iya|wa-ʹimmaaa|ʹan|nakoona|ʹawwala|man|ʹalq̣aa?"
20,66,"Q̣aala|bal|ʹalq̣oo!|Faʹiẓaa|ḥibaaluhum|wa-ʻiṣiyyuhum|yukhayyalu|ʹilayhi|miñ|siḥrihim|ʹannahaa|tasʻaa!"
20,67,"Faʹawjasa|fee|nafsihee|kheefatam|Moosaa."
20,68,"Q̣ulnaa|laa-|takhaf|ʹinnaka|ʹantal|ʹaʻlaa:"
20,69,"Waʹalq̣i|maa-|fee|yameenika|talq̣af|maa-|ṣanaʻoo.|ʹInnamaa|ṣanaʻoo|kaydu|saaḥir:|wa-laa|yufliḥus|saaḥiru|ḥays̤u|ʹataa."
20,70,"Faʹulq̣iyas|saharatu|sujjadañ|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|bi-Rabbi|Haaroona|wa-Moosaa."
20,71,"Q̣aala|ʹaamañtum|lahoo|q̣abla|ʹan|ʹaaẓana|lakum?|ʹInnahoo|lakabeerukumul|laẓee|ʻallamakumus|siḥr!|Falaʹuq̣aṭṭiʻanna|ʹaydiyakum|wa-ʹarjulakum|min|khilaafiñw|walaʹuṣallibannakum|fee|juẓooʻin|nakhl:|wa-lataʻlamunna|ʹayyunaaa|ʹashaddu|ʻaẓaabañw|Waʹabq̣aa!"
20,72,"Q̣aaloo|lan|nuʹs̤iraka|ʻalaa|maa-|jaaaʹanaa|minal|Bayyinaati|wallaẓee|faṭaranaa|faq̣ḍi|maaa|ʹañta|q̣aaḍ.|ʹInnamaa|taq̣ḍee|haaẓihil|ḥayaatad|dunyaa."
20,73,"ʹInnaaa|ʹaamannaa|bi-Rabbinaa|liyag̣fira|lanaa|khaṭaayaanaa|wa-maaa|ʹakrahtanaa|ʻalayhi|minas|siḥr:|wallaahu|Khayruñw|WaʹAbq̣aa."
20,74,"ʹInnahoo|mañy|yaʹti|Rabbahoo|mujrimañ|faʹinna|lahoo|Jahannam:|laa-|yamootu|feehaa|wa-laa|yaḥyaa."
20,75,"Wa-mañy|yaʹtihee|Muʹminañ|q̣ad|ʻamilaṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|faʹulaaaʹika|lahumud|darajaatul|ʻulaa,"
20,76,"Jannaatu|ʻAdniñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa:|waẓaalika|jazaaaʹu|mañ|tazakkaa."
20,77,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosaaa|ʹan|ʹasri|biʻibaadee|faḍrib|lahum|ṭareeq̣añ|fil|baḥri|yabasal|laa|takhaafu|darakañw|walaa|takhshaa."
20,78,"Faʹatbaʻahum|Firʻawnu|bijunoodihee|fag̣ashiyahum|minal|yammi|maa-|g̣ashiyahum."
20,79,"Wa-ʹaḍalla|Firʻawnu|q̣awmahoo|wa-maa|hadaa."
20,80,"Yaa-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|q̣ad|ʹañjaynaakum|min|ʻaduwwikum|wa-waaʻadnaakum|jaanibaṭ|Ṭooril|ʹaymana|wa-nazzalnaa|ʻalaykumul|Manna|was-Salwaa:"
20,81,"Kuloo|miñ|ṭayyibaati|maa-|razaq̣naakum|wa-laa|taṭg̣aw|feehi|fayaḥilla|ʻalaykum|g̣aḍabee:|wa-mañy|yaḥlil|ʻalayhi|g̣aḍabee|faq̣ad|hawaa!"
20,82,"Wa-ʹinnee|la-G̣affaarul|limañ|taaba|wa-ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|s̤ummah|tadaa"
20,83,"Wa-maaa|ʹaʻjalaka|ʻañ|q̣awmika|Yaa-Moosaa?"
20,84,"Q̣aala|hum|ʹulaaaʹi|ʻalaaa|ʹas̤aree|wa-ʻajiltu|ʹilayka|Rabbi|litarḍaa."
20,85,"Q̣aala|faʹinnaa|q̣ad|fatannaa|q̣awmaka|mim|baʻdika|waʹaḍallahumus|Saamiriyy."
20,86,"farajaʻa|Moosaaa|ʹilaa|q̣awmihee|g̣aḍbaana|ʹasifaa.|Q̣aala|Yaa-q̣awmi|ʹalam|yaʻidkum|Rabbukum|waʻdan|ḥasanaa?|ʹAfaṭaala|ʻalaykumul|ʻahdu|ʹam|ʹarattum|ʹañy|yaḥilla|ʻalaykum|g̣aḍabum|mir|Rabbikum|faʹakhlaftum|mawʻidee?"
20,87,"Q̣aaloo|maaa|ʹakhlafnaa|mawʻidaka|bimalkinaa|wa-laakinnaa|ḥummilnaaa|ʹawzaaram|miñ|zeenatil|q̣awmi|faq̣aẓafnaahaa|fakaẓaalika|ʹalq̣as|Saamiriyy."
20,88,"Faʹakhraja|lahum|ʻijlañ|jasadal|lahoo|khuwaaruñ|faq̣aaloo|haaẓaaa|ʹilaahukum|wa-ʹilaahu|Moosaa,|fanasee!"
20,89,"ʹAfalaa|yarawna|ʹallaa|yarjiʻu|ʹilayhim|q̣awlaa:|walaa|yamliku|lahum|ḍarrañw|walaa|nafʻaa."
20,90,"Wa-laq̣ad|q̣aala|lahum|Haaroonu|miñ|q̣ablu|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹinnamaa|futiñtum|bih:|wa-ʹinna|Rabbakumur|Raḥmaanu|fattabiʻoonee|wa-ʹaṭeeʻooo|ʹamree."
20,91,"Q̣aaloo|lan|nabraḥa|ʻalayhi|ʻaakifeena|ḥattaa|yarjiʻa|ʹilaynaa|Moosaa."
20,92,"Q̣aala|yaa-Haaroonu|maa|manaʻaka|ʹiẓ|raʹaytahum|ḍalloo."
20,93,"ʹAllaa|tattabiʻan?|ʹAfaʻaṣayta|ʹamree?"
20,94,"Q̣aala|yabnaʹumma|laa-|taʹkhuẓ|biliḥyatee|wa-laa|biraʹsee!|ʹInnee|khasheetu|ʹañ|taq̣oola|farraq̣ta|bayna|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|wa-lam|tarq̣ub|q̣awlee!"
20,95,"Q̣aala|famaa|khaṭbuka|Yaa-Saamiriyy?"
20,96,"Q̣aala|baṣurtu|bimaa|lam|yabṣuroo|bihee|faq̣abaḍtu|q̣abḍatam|min|ʹas̤arir|Rasooli|fanabaẓtuhaa|wa-kaẓaalika|sawwalat|lee|nafsee."
20,97,"Q̣aala|faẓhab|faʹinna|laka|fil|ḥayaati|ʹañ|taq̣oola|Laa-|Misaas˺:|wa-ʹinna|laka|mawʻidal|lañ|tukhlafah:|wañz̤̣ur|ʹilaaa|ʹilaahikal|laẓee|z̤̣alta|ʻalayhi|ʻaakifaa:|lanuḥarriq̣annahoo|s̤umma|lanañsifannahoo|fil|yammi|nasfaa!"
20,98,"ʹInnamaaa|ʹIlaahukumul|laahul|laẓee|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo:|wasiʻa|kulla|shayʹin|ʻilmaa."
20,99,"Kaẓaalika|naq̣uṣṣu|ʻalayka|min|ʹambaaaʹi|maa-|q̣ad|sabaq̣:|wa-q̣ad|ʹaataynaaka|mil|ladunnaa|Ẓikraa."
20,100,"Man|ʹaʻraḍa|ʻanhu|faʹinnahoo|yaḥmilu|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|wizraa;"
20,101,"Khaalideena|feeh:|wa-saaaʹa|lahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ḥimlaa,"
20,102,"Yawma|yuñfakhu|fiṣ|Ṣoori|wa-naḥshurul|mujrimeena|Yawmaʹiẓiñ|zurq̣aa."
20,103,"Yatakhaafatoona|baynahum|ʹil|labis̤tum|ʹillaa|ʻashraa;"
20,104,"Naḥnu|ʹAʻlamu|bimaa|yaq̣ooloona|ʹiẓ|yaq̣oolu|ʹams̤aluhum|Ṭareeq̣atan|ʹil|labis̤tum|ʹillaa|yawmaa!"
20,105,"Wa-yasʹaloonaka|ʻanil|jibaali|faq̣ul|yañsifuhaa|Rabbee|nasfaa:"
20,106,"Fayaẓaruhaa|q̣aaʻañ|ṣafṣafaa;"
20,107,"Laa-|taraa|feehaa|ʻiwajañw|Walaaa|ʹamtaa."
20,108,"Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yattabiʻoonad|Daaʻiya|laa-|ʻiwaja|lah:|wa-khashaʻatil|ʹaṣwaatu|lir-Raḥmaani|falaa|tasmaʻu|ʹillaa|hamsaa."
20,109,"Yawmaʹiẓil|laa|tañfaʻush|Shafaaʻatu|ʹillaa|man|ʹaẓina|lahur|Raḥmaanu|wa-raḍiya|lahoo|q̣awlaa."
20,110,"Yaʻlamu|maa-|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-maa|khalfahum|wa-laa|yuḥeeṭoona|bihee|ʻilmaa."
20,111,"Wa-ʻanatil|wujoohu|lil-Ḥayyil|Q̣ayyoom:|wa-q̣ad|khaaba|man|ḥamala|z̤̣ulmaa."
20,112,"Wa-mañy|yaʻmal|minaṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|falaa|yakhaafu|z̤̣ulmañw|walaa|haḍmaa."
20,113,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ʹañzalnaahu|Q̣ur-ʹaanan|ʻArabiyyañw|waṣarrafnaa|fee-hi|minal|waʻeedi|laʻallahum|yattaq̣oona|ʹaw|yuḥdis̤u|lahum|ẓikraa."
20,114,"Fataʻaalal|laahul|Malikul|Ḥaq̣q̣!|Wa-laa|taʻjal|bil-q̣urʹaani|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yuq̣ḍaaa|ʹilayka|waḥyuh:|wa-q̣ur|Rabbi|zidnee|ʻilmaa."
20,115,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʻahidnaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹAadama|miñ|q̣ablu|fanasiya|wa-lam|najid|lahoo|ʻazmaa."
20,116,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣ulnaa|lilmalaaaʹikatis|judoo|liʹAadama|fasajadooo|ʹillaaa|ʹIbleesa|ʹabaa."
20,117,"Faq̣ulnaa|YaaaʹAadamu|ʹinna|haaẓaa|ʻaduwwul|laka|wa-lizawjika|falaa|yukhrijannakumaa|minal|Jannati|fatashq̣aa."
20,118,"ʹInna|laka|ʹallaa|tajooʻa|feehaa|wa-laa|taʻraa,"
20,119,"Wa-ʹannaka|laa-|taz̤̣maʹu|feehaa|wa-laa|taḍḥaa."
20,120,"Fawaswasa|ʹilayhish|Shayṭaanu|q̣aala|YaaaʹAadamu|hal|ʹadulluka|ʻalaa|Shajaratil|khuldi|wa-mulkil|laa|yablaa."
20,121,"Faʹakalaa|minhaa|fabadat|lahumaa|saw-ʹaatuhumaa|waṭafiq̣aa|yakhṣifaani|ʻalayhimaa|miñw|waraq̣il|Jannah:|wa-ʻaṣaaa|ʹAadamu|Rabbahoo|fag̣awaa."
20,122,"S̤ummaj|tabaahu|Rabbuhoo|fataaba|ʻalayhi|wa-hadaa."
20,123,"Q̣aalah|biṭaa|minhaa|jameeʻam|baʻḍukum|libaʻḍin|ʻaduww:|faʹimmaa|yaʹtiyannakum|minnee|Hudañ|famanit|tabaʻa|Hudaaya|falaa|yaḍillu|wa-laa|yashq̣aa."
20,124,"Wa-man|ʹaʻraḍa|ʻañ|Ẓikree|faʹinna|lahoo|maʻeeshatañ|ḍañkañw|wanaḥshuruhoo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʹaʻmaa."
20,125,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|lima|ḥashartaneee|ʹaʻmaa-|wa-q̣ad|kuñtu|baṣeeraa?"
20,126,"Q̣aala|kaẓaalika|ʹatatka|ʹAayaatunaa|fanaseetahaa:|wa-kaẓaalikal|yawma|tuñsaa."
20,127,"Wa-kaẓaalika|najzee|man|ʹasrafa|wa-lam|yuʹmim|biʹAayaati|Rabbih:|wa-laʻaẓaabul|ʹAakhirati|ʹashaddu|wa-ʹabq̣aa."
20,128,"ʹAfalam|yahdi|lahum|kam|ʹahlaknaa|q̣ablahum|minal|q̣urooni|yamshoona|fee|masaakinihim?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liʹulin|nuhaa."
20,129,"Wa-lawlaa|Kalimatuñ|sabaq̣at|mir|Rabbika|lakaana|lizaamañw|waʹajalum|musammaa."
20,130,"Faṣbir|ʻalaa|maa-|yaq̣ooloona|wa-sabbiḥ|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbika|q̣abla|ṭulooʻish|shamsi|wa-q̣abla|g̣uroobihaa;|wa-min|ʹaanaaaʹil|layli|fasabbiḥ|wa-ʹaṭraafan|nahaari|laʻallaka|tarḍaa."
20,131,"Wa-laa|tamuddanna|ʹaynayka|ʹilaa|maa-|mattaʻnaa|biheee|ʹazwaajam|minhum|zahratal|ḥayaatid|dunyaa,|linaftinahum|feeh:|wa-rizq̣u|Rabbika|khayruñw|waʹabq̣aa."
20,132,"Waʹmur|ʹahlaka|biṣ-Ṣalaati|waṣṭabir|ʻalayhaa.|Laa-|nasʹaluka|rizq̣aa:|Naḥnu|narzuq̣uk.|Wal-ʻAaq̣ibatu|lit-Taq̣waa."
20,133,"Wa-q̣aaloo|Law-laa|yaʹteenaa|biʹAayatim|mir|Rabbih?|ʹA-walam|taʹtihim̃|Bayyinatu|maa-|fiṣ|Ṣuḥufil|ʹoolaa?"
20,134,"Wa-law|ʹannaaa|ʹahlaknaahum̃|biʻaẓaabim|miñ|q̣ablihee|laq̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|Law-laaa|ʹarsalta|ʹilaynaa|Rasoolañ|fanattabiʻa|ʹAayaatika|Miñ|q̣abli|ʹan|naẓilla|wa-nakhzaa."
20,135,"Q̣ul|kullum|mutarabbiṣuñ|fatarabbaṣoo:|fasataʻlamoona|man|ʹAṣḥaabuṣ|Ṣiraaṭis|sawiyyi|wa-manih|tadaa."
21,1,"ʹIq̣taraba|linnaasi|Ḥisaabuhum|wa-hum|fee|g̣aflatim|muʻriḍoon."
21,2,"Maa-|yaʹteehim|miñ|Ẓikrim|mir|Rabbihim|muḥdas̤in|ʹillas|tamaʻoohu|wa-hum|yalʻaboon,"
21,3,"Laahiyatañ|q̣uloobuhum.|Wa-ʹasarrun|najwal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|hal|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lukum?|ʹAfataʹtoonas|siḥra|wa-ʹañtum|tubṣiroon?"
21,4,"Q̣aala|Rabbee|yaʻlamul|Q̣awla|fis|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
21,5,"Bal|q̣aalooo|ʹaḍg̣aas̤u|ʹaḥlaamim|bal|iftaraahu|bal|huwa|shaaʻir!|fal-yaʹtinaa|biʹAayatiñ|kamaaa|ʹursilal|ʹawwaloon!"
21,6,"Maaa|ʹaamanat|q̣ablahum|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹahlaknaahaa:|ʹa-fahum|yuʹminoon?"
21,7,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|q̣ablaka|ʹillaa|rijaalan|nooḥeee|ʹilayhim|fasʹalooo|ʹAhlaẓ|Ẓikri|ʹiñ|kuñtum|laa-|taʻlamoon."
21,8,"Wa-maa|jaʻalnaahum|jasadal|laa|yaʹkuloonaṭ|ṭaʻaama|wa-maa|kaanoo|khaalideen."
21,9,"S̤umma|ṣadaq̣naahumul|waʻda|faʹañjaynaahum|wa-man|nashaaaʹu|wa-ʹahlaknal|musrifeen."
21,10,"Laq̣ad|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykum|Kitaabañ|feehi|Ẓikrukum:|ʹafalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
21,11,"Wa-kam|q̣aṣamnaa|miñ|q̣aryatiñ|kaanat|z̤̣aalimatañw|wa-ʹañshaʹnaa|baʻdahaa|q̣awman|ʹaakhareen?"
21,12,"Falammaaa|ʹaḥassoo|baʹsanaaa|ʹiẓaa|hum|minhaa|yarkuḍoon."
21,13,"Laa-|tarkuḍoo|warjiʻooo|ʹilaa|maaa|ʹutriftum|feehi|wa-masaakinikum|laʻallakum|tusʹaloon."
21,14,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-waylanaaa|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|z̤̣aalimeen!"
21,15,"Famaa|zaalat|tilka|daʻwaahum|ḥattaa|jaʻalnaahum|ḥaṣeedan|khaamideen."
21,16,"Wa-maa|khalaq̣nas|samaaaʹa|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaa|laaʻibeen!"
21,17,"Law|ʹaradnaaa|ʹan|nattakhiẓa|lahwal|lat-takhaẓnaahu|mil|ladunnaaa|ʹiñ|kunnaa|faaʻileen!"
21,18,"Bal|naq̣ẓifu|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|ʻalal|baaṭili|fayadmag̣uhoo|faʹiẓaa|huwa|zaahiq̣!|Wa-lakumul|waylu|mimmaa|taṣifoon."
21,19,"Wa-lahoo|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-man|ʻiñdahoo|laa-|yastakbiroona|ʻan|ʻibaadatihee|wa-laa|yastaḥsiroon."
21,20,"Yusabbiḥoonal|layla|wannahaara|laa-|yafturoon."
21,21,"ʹAmit|takhaẓooo|ʹaalihatam|minal|ʹarḍi|hum|yuñshiroon?"
21,22,"Law|kaana|feehimaaa|ʹaalihatun|ʹillal|laahu|lafasadataa!|Fa-Subḥaanal|laahi|Rabbil|ʻArshi|ʻammaa|yaṣifoon!"
21,23,"Laa-|yusʹalu|ʻammaa|yafʻalu|wa-hum|yusʹaloon."
21,24,"ʹAmit|takhaẓoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹaalihah?|Q̣ul|haatoo|burhaanakum:|haaẓaa|Ẓikru|mam|maʻiya|wa-Ẓikru|mañ|q̣ablee|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻlamoonal|Ḥaq̣q̣a|fahum|muʻriḍoon."
21,25,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|mir|rasoolin|ʹillaa|nooḥeee|ʹilayhi|ʹannahoo|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaaa|ʹAna|faʻbudoon."
21,26,"Wa-q̣aalut|takhaẓar|Raḥmaanu|waladañ|Subḥaanah!|Bal|ʻibaadum|mukramoon."
21,27,"Laa-|yasbiq̣oonahoo|bil-q̣awli|wa-hum̃|biʹamrihee|yaʻmaloon."
21,28,"Yaʻlamu|maa-|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-maa|khalfahum|wa-laa|yashfaʻoona|ʹillaa|limanir|taḍaa|wa-hum|min|khashyatihee|mushfiq̣oon."
21,29,"Wa-mañy|yaq̣ul|minhum|ʹinneee|ʹilaahum|miñ|doonihee|faẓaalika|najzeehi|Jahannam:|Kaẓaalika|najziz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
21,30,"ʹAwalam|yaral|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹannas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|kaanataa|ratq̣añ|fafataq̣naahumaa?|Wa-jaʻalnaa|minal|maaaʹi|kulla|shayʹin|ḥayy.|ʹAfalaa|yuʹminoon?"
21,31,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|fil|ʹarḍi|rawaasiya|ʹañ|tameeda|bihim|wa-jaʻalnaa|feehaa|fijaajañ|subulal|laʻallahum|yahtadoon."
21,32,"Wa-jaʻalnas|samaaaʹa|saq̣fam|maḥfooz̤̣aa:|wa-hum|ʻan|ʹAayaatihaa|muʻriḍoon!"
21,33,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣al|Layla|wan-Nahaara|washshamsa|wal-q̣amar:|kulluñ|fee|falakiñy|yasbaḥoon."
21,34,"Wa-maa|jaʻalnaa|libasharim|miñ|q̣ablikal|khuld:|ʹafa|ʹimmitta|fahumul|khaalidoon?"
21,35,"Kullu|nafsiñ|ẓaaaʹiq̣atul|mawt:|wa-nablookum̃|bishsharri|walkhayri|fitnah.|Wa-ʹilaynaa|turjaʻoon."
21,36,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|raʹaakal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹiñy|yattakhiẓoonaka|ʹillaa|huzuwaa.|ʹAhaaẓal|laẓee|yaẓkuru|ʹaalihatakum?|Wa-hum̃|biẓikrir|Raḥmaani|hum|kaafiroon!"
21,37,"Khuliq̣al|ʹiñsaanu|min|ʻajal:|saʹureekum|ʹAayaatee|falaa|tastaʻjiloon!"
21,38,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|waʻdu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
21,39,"Law|yaʻlamul|laẓeena|kafaroo|ḥeena|laa-|yakuffoona|ʻañw|wujoohihimun|Naara|wa-laa|ʻañ|z̤̣uhoorihim|wa-laa|hum|yuñṣaroon!"
21,40,"Bal|taʹteehim̃|bag̣tatañ|fatabhatuhum|falaa|yastaṭeeʻoona|raddahaa|wa-laa|hum|yuñz̤̣aroon."
21,41,"Wa-laq̣adis|tuhziʹa|birusulim|miñ|q̣ablika|faḥaaq̣a|billaẓeena|sakhiroo|minhum|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon."
21,42,"Q̣ul|mañy|yaklaʹukum̃|billayli|wannahaari|minar|Raḥmaan?|Bal|hum|ʻañ|ẓikri|Rabbihim|muʻriḍoon."
21,43,"ʹAm|lahum|ʹaalihatuñ|tamnaʻuhum|miñ|dooninaa?|Laa-|yastaṭeeʻoona|naṣra|ʹañfusihim|wa-laa|hum|minnaa|yuṣ-ḥaboon."
21,44,"Bal|mattaʻnaa|haaaʹulaaaʹi|wa-ʹaabaaaʹahum|ḥattaa|ṭaala|ʻalayhimul|ʻumur;|ʹafalaa|yarawna|ʹannaa|naʹtil|ʹarḍa|nañq̣uṣuhaa|min|ʹaṭraafihaa?|ʹAfahumul|g̣aaliboon?"
21,45,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹuñẓirukum̃|bilwaḥyi|wa-laa|yasmaʻuṣ|ṣummud|duʻaaaʹa|ʹiẓaa|maa-|yuñẓaroon."
21,46,"Wa-laʹim|massathum|nafḥatum|min|ʻAẓaabi|Rabbika|layaq̣oolunna|yaawaylanaaa|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|z̤̣aalimeen!"
21,47,"Wa-naḍaʻul|mawaazeenal|q̣isṭa|li-Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|falaa|tuz̤̣lamu|nafsuñ|shayʹaa.|Wa-ʹiñ|kaana|mis̤q̣aala|ḥabbatim|min|khardalin|ʹataynaa|bihaa:|wa-kafaa|binaa|ḥaasibeen."
21,48,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosaa|wa-Haaroonal|Furq̣aana|wa-Ḍiyaaaʹañw|wa-Ẓikral|lil-Muttaq̣een,"
21,49,"ʹAllaẓeena|yakhshawna|Rabbahum̃|bilg̣aybi|wa-hum|minas|Saaʻati|mushfiq̣oon."
21,50,"Wa-haaẓaa|Ẓikrum|Mubaarakun|ʹañzalnaah:|ʹa-faʹañtum|lahoo|muñkiroon."
21,51,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaaa|ʹIbraaheema|rushdahoo|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-kunnaa|bihee|ʻaalimeen."
21,52,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|liʹabeehi|waq̣awmihee|maa-|haaẓihit|tamaas̤eelul|lateee|ʹañtum|lahaa|ʻaakifoon."
21,53,"Q̣aaloo|wajadnaaa|ʹaabaaaʹanaa|lahaa|ʻaabideen."
21,54,"Q̣aala|laq̣ad|kuñtum|ʹañtum|wa-ʹaabaaaʹukum|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
21,55,"Q̣aalooo|ʹajiʹtanaa|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|ʹam|ʹañta|minal|laaʻibeen."
21,56,"Q̣aala|bar|Rabbukum|Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍil|laẓee|faṭarahunn:|Wa-ʹana|ʻalaa|ẓaalikum|minash|shaahideen."
21,57,"Wa-tallaahi|laʹakeedanna|ʹaṣnaamakum|baʻda|ʹañ|tuwalloo|mudbireen."
21,58,"Fajaʻalahum|jaẓaaẓan|ʹillaa|kabeeral|lahum|laʻallahum|ʹilayhi|yarjiʻoon."
21,59,"Q̣aaloo|mañ|faʻala|haaẓaa|biʹaalihatinaaa|ʹinnahoo|laminaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
21,60,"Q̣aaloo|samiʻnaa|fatañy|yaẓkuruhum|yuq̣aalu|lahooo|ʹIbraaheem."
21,61,"Q̣aaloo|faʹtoo|bihee|ʻalaaa|ʹaʻyunin|naasi|laʻallahum|yashhadoon."
21,62,"Q̣aalooo|ʹaʹañta|faʻalta|haaẓaa|biʹaalihatinaa|yaaaʹIbraaheem?"
21,63,"Q̣aala|bal|faʻalahoo|kabeeruhum|haaẓaa|fasʹaloohum|ʹiñ|kaanoo|yañṭiq̣oon!"
21,64,"Farajaʻooo|ʹilaaa|ʹañfusihim|faq̣aalooo|ʹinnakum|ʹañtumuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
21,65,"S̤umma|nukisoo|ʻalaa|ruʹoosihim:|laq̣ad|ʻalimta|maa-|haaaʹulaaaʹi|yañṭiq̣oon!"
21,66,"Q̣aala|ʹafataʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yañfaʻukum|shayʹañw|walaa|yaḍurrukum?"
21,67,"ʹUffil|lakum|wa-limaa|taʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laah!|ʹAfalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
21,68,"Q̣aaloo|ḥarriq̣oohu|wañṣurooo|ʹaalihatakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|faaʻileen!"
21,69,"Q̣ulnaa|yaa-Naaru|koonee|bardañw|wasalaaman|ʻalaaa|ʹIbraaheem!"
21,70,"Wa-ʹaraadoo|bihee|kaydañ|fajaʻalnaahumul|ʹakhsareen!"
21,71,"Wa-najjaynaahu|wa-Looṭan|ʹilal|ʹarḍil|latee|baaraknaa|feehaa|lil-ʻaalameem."
21,72,"Wa-wahabnaa|lahooo|ʹIsḥaaq̣:|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|naafilah:|wa-kullañ|jaʻalnaa|Ṣaaliḥeen."
21,73,"Wa-jaʻalnaahum|ʹAʹimmatañy|yahdoona|biʹAmrinaa|wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayhim|fiʻlal|khayraati|wa-ʹiq̣aamaṣ|Ṣalaati|wa-ʹeetaaaʹaz|Zakaah;|wa-kaanoo|lanaa|ʻaabideen."
21,74,"Wa-Looṭan|ʹaataynaahu|Ḥukmañw|WaʻIlmañw|Wanajjaynaahu|minal|q̣aryatil|latee|kaanat|taʻmalul|khabaaaʹis̤.|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣awma|Sawʹiñ|faasiq̣een."
21,75,"Wa-ʹadkhalnaahu|fee|Raḥmatinaa:|ʹinnahoo|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
21,76,"Wa-Nooḥan|ʹiz|naadaa|miñ|q̣ablu|fastajabnaa|lahoo|fanajjaynaahu|wa-ʹahlahoo|minal|karbil|ʻaz̤̣eem."
21,77,"Wa-naṣarnaahu|minal|q̣awmil|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣awma|Sawʹiñ|faʹag̣raq̣naahum|ʹajmaʻeen."
21,78,"Wa-Daawooda|wa-Sulaymaana|ʹiẓ|yaḥkumaani|fil|ḥars̤i|ʹiẓ|nafashat|feehi|g̣anamul|q̣awm:|wa-kunnaa|liḥukmihim|Shaahideen."
21,79,"Fafahhamnaahaa|Sulaymaan:|wa-kullan|ʹaataynaa|Ḥukmañw|waʻIlmaa;|wa-sakh-kharnaa|maʻa|Daawoodal|jibaala|yusabbiḥna|waṭṭayr:|wa-kunnaa|faaʻileen."
21,80,"Wa-ʻallamnaahu|ṣanʻata|laboosil|lakum|lituḥṣinakum|mim|baʹsikum:|fahal|ʹañtum|shaakiroon?"
21,81,"Wa-li-Sulaymaanar|reeḥa|ʻaaṣifatañ|tajree|biʹamriheee|ʹilal|ʹarḍil|latee|baaraknaa|feehaa:|wa- kunnaa|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻaalimeen."
21,82,"Wa-minash|shayaaṭeeni|mañy|yag̣ooṣoona|lahoo|wa-yaʻmaloona|ʻamalañ|doona|ẓaalik;|wa-kunnaa|lahum|Ḥaafiz̤̣een."
21,83,"Wa-ʹAyyooba|ʹiẓ|naadaa|Rabbahooo|ʹannee|massaniyaḍ|ḍurru|wa-ʹAñta|ʹArḥamur|raaḥimeen."
21,84,"Fastajabnaa|lahoo|fakashafnaa|maa-|bihee|miñ|ḍurriñw|waʹaataynaahu|ʹahlahoo|wa-mis̤lahum|maʻahum|Raḥmatam|min|ʻIñdinaa|waẓikraa|lilʻaabideen."
21,85,"Wa-ʹIsmaaʻeela|wa-ʹIdreesa|wa-Ẓal|kifl:|kullum|minaṣ|Ṣaabireen;"
21,86,"Wa-ʹadkhalnaahum|fee|Raḥmatinaa:|ʹinnahum|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
21,87,"Wa-Ẓan|Nooni|ʹiẓ|ẓahaba|mug̣aaḍibañ|fa-Z̤̣anna|ʹal|lan|naq̣dira|ʻalayhi|fanaadaa|fiz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|ʹal|˹Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaaa|ʹAñta|Subḥaanaka|ʹinnee|kuñtu|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen˺!"
21,88,"Fastajabnaa|lahoo|wa-najjaynaahu|minal|g̣amm:|wa-kaẓaalika|nuñjil|Muʹmineen."
21,89,"Wa-Zakariyyaaa|ʹiẓ|naadaa|Rabbahoo|Rabbi|laa-|taẓarnee|fardañw|waʹAñta|Khayrul|waaris̤een."
21,90,"Fastajabnaa|lahoo|wa-wahabnaa|lahoo|Yaḥyaa|wa-ʹaṣlaḥnaa|lahoo|zawjah.|ʹInnahum|kaanoo|yusaariʻoona|fil|khayraati|wa-yadʻoonanaa|rag̣abañw|warahabaa:|wa-kaanoo|lanaa|khaashiʻeen."
21,91,"Wallateee|ʹaḥṣanat|farjahaa|fanafakhnaa|feehaa|mir|Rooḥinaa|wa-jaʻalnaahaa|wabnahaaa|ʹAayatal|lilʻaalameen."
21,92,"ʹInna|haaẓiheee|ʹummatukum|ʹUmmatañw|Waaḥidatañw|WaʹAna|Rabbukum|faʻbudoon."
21,93,"Wa-taq̣aṭṭaʻooo|ʹamrahum̃|baynahum:|kullun|ʹilaynaa|raajiʻoon."
21,94,"Famañy|yaʻmal|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|falaa|kufraana|lisaʻyih:|wa-ʹInnaa|lahoo|katiboon."
21,95,"Waḥaraamun|ʻalaa|q̣aryatin|ʹahlaknaahaaa|ʹannahum|laa-|yarjiʻoon."
21,96,"Hattaaa|ʹiẓaa|futiḥat|Yaʹjooju|wa-Maʹjooju|wa-hum|miñ|kulli|ḥadabiñy|yañsiloon."
21,97,"Waq̣tarabal|Waʻdul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|faʹiẓaa|hiya|shaakhiṣatun|ʹabṣaarul|laẓeena|kafaroo:|yaawaylanaa|q̣ad|kunnaa|fee|g̣aflatim|min|haaẓaa|bal|kunnaa|z̤̣aalimeen!"
21,98,"ʹInnakum|wa-maa|taʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|ḥaṣabu|Jahannam!|ʹañtum|lahaa|waaridoon!"
21,99,"Law|kaana|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹaalihatam|maa|waradoohaa!|wa-kulluñ|feehaa|khaalidoon."
21,100,"Lahum|feehaa|zafeeruñw|wahum|feehaa|laa-|yasmaʻoon."
21,101,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|sabaq̣at|lahum|minnal|Ḥusnaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʻanhaa|mubʻadoon."
21,102,"Laa-|yasmaʻoona|ḥaseesahaa:|wa-hum|fee|mash|tahat|ʹañfusuhum|khaalidoon."
21,103,"Laa-|yaḥzunuhumul|Fazaʻul|ʹAkbaru|wa-tatalaq̣-q̣aahumul|malaaaʹikah:|haaẓaa|Yawmukumul|laẓee|kuñtum|tooʻadoon."
21,104,"Yawma|naṭwis|samaaaʹa|kaṭayyis|sijilli|lilkutub:|kamaa|badaʹnaaa|ʹawwala|khalq̣in|nuʻeeduh:|waʻdan|ʻalaynaa:|ʹInnaa|kunnaa|faaʻileen."
21,105,"Wa-laq̣ad|katabna|fiz|Zaboori|mim|baʻdiẓ|Ẓikri|ʹannal|ʹarḍa|yaris̤uhaa|ʻIbaadiyaṣ|Ṣaaliḥoon."
21,106,"ʹInna|fee|haaẓaa|la-Balaag̣al|liq̣awmin|ʻAabideen."
21,107,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʹillaa|Raḥmatal|lilʻaalameen."
21,108,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaa|yooḥaaa|ʹilayya|ʹannamaaa|ʹIlaahukum|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥid:|fahal|ʹañtum|Muslimoon?"
21,109,"Faʹiñ|tawallaw|faq̣ul|ʹaaẓañtukum|ʻalaa|sawaaaʹ;|wa-ʹin|ʹadreee|ʹaq̣areebun|ʹam̃|baʻeedum|maa|tooʻadoon."
21,110,"ʹInnahoo|yaʻlamul|jahra|minal|q̣awli|wa-yaʻlamu|maa-|taktumoon."
21,111,"Wa-ʹin|ʹadree|laʻallahoo|fitnatul|lakum|wa-mataaʻun|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
21,112,"Q̣aala|Rabbiḥ|kum̃|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣!|Wa-Rabbunar|Raḥmaanul|Mustaʻaanu|ʻalaa|maa-|taṣifoon!"
22,1,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasut|taq̣oo|Rabbakum!|ʹInna|zalzalatas|Saaʻati|shayʹun|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
22,2,"Yawma|tarawnahaa|taẓhalu|kullu|murḍiʻatin|ʻammaaa|ʹarḍaʻat|wa-taḍaʻu|kullu|ẓaati|ḥamlin|ḥamlahaa|wa-taran|naasa|sukaaraa|wa-maa|hum̃|bisukaaraa|wa-laakinna|ʻaẓaabal|laahi|shadeed."
22,3,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yujaadilu|fil|laahi|big̣ayri|ʻilmiñw|Wayattabiʻu|kulla|shayṭaanim|mareed!"
22,4,"Kutiba|ʻalayhi|ʹannahoo|mañ|tawallaahu|faʹannahoo|yuḍilluhoo|wa-yahdeehi|ʹilaa|ʻAẓaabis|Saʻeer."
22,5,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|fee|raybim|minal|Baʻs̤i|faʹinnaa|khalaq̣naakum|miñ|turaabiñ|s̤umma|min|nuṭfatiñ|s̤umma|min|ʻalaq̣atiñ|s̤umma|mim|muḍg̣atim|mukhallaq̣atiñw|wag̣ayri|mukhallaq̣atil|linubayyina|lakum.|Wa-nuq̣irru|fil|ʹarḥaami|maa-|nashaaaʹu|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammañ|s̤umma|nukhrijukum|ṭiflañ|s̤umma|litablug̣ooo|ʹashuddakum;|wa-miñkum|mañy|yutawaffaa|wa-miñkum|mañy|yuraddu|ʹilaaa|ʹarẓalil|ʻumuri|likaylaa|yaʻlama|mim|baʻdi|ʻilmiñ|shayʹaa.|Wa-taral|ʹarḍa|haamidatañ|faʹiẓaaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalayhal|maaaʹah|tazzat|wa-rabat|wa-ʹambatat|miñ|kulli|zawjim|baheej."
22,6,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|Huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-ʹannahoo|yuḥyil|mawtaa|wa-ʹannahoo|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
22,7,"Wa-ʹannas|Saaʻata|ʹaatiyatul|laa|rayba|feeha|wa-ʹannal|laaha|yabʻas̤u|mañ|fil|q̣uboor."
22,8,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yujaadilu|fil|laahi|big̣ayri|ʻilmiñw|walaa|Hudañw|Walaa|Kittabim|Muneer,"
22,9,"S̤aaniya|ʻiṭfihee|liyuḍilla|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah:|lahoo|fid|dunyaa|khizyuñw|wanuẓeeq̣uhoo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʻAẓaabal|Ḥareeq̣."
22,10,"Ẓaalika|bimaa|q̣addamat|yadaaka|wa-ʹannal|laaha|laysa|biz̤̣allaamil|lilʻabeed."
22,11,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yaʻbudul|laaha|ʻalaa|ḥarf:|faʹin|ʹaṣaabahoo|khayruniṭ|maʹanna|bih;|wa-ʹin|ʹaṣaabathu|fitnatuniñ|q̣alaba|ʻalaa|wajhih;|khasirad|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah;|ẓaalika|huwal|khusraanul|Mubeen."
22,12,"Yadʻoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yaḍurruhoo|wamaa|laa-|yañfaʻuh:|ẓaalika|huwaḍ|ḍalaalul|baʻeed!"
22,13,"Yadʻoo|lamañ|ḍarruhooo|ʹaq̣rabu|min|nafʻih:|labiʹsal|mawlaa|wa-labiʹsal|ʻasheer!"
22,14,"ʹInnal|laaha|yudkhilul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaar:|ʹinnal|laaha|yafʻalu|maa-|yureed."
22,15,"Mañ|kaana|yaz̤̣unnu|ʹal|lañy|yañṣurahul|laahu|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirati|fal-yamdud|bisababin|ʹilas|samaaaʹi|s̤ummal|yaq̣ṭaʻ|falyañz̤̣ur|hal|yuẓhibanna|kayduhoo|maa-|yag̣eez̤̣!"
22,16,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ʹañzalnaahu|ʹAayaatim|Bayyinaatiñw|Waʹannal|laaha|yahdee|mañy|yureed!"
22,17,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wallaẓeena|haadoo|waṣ-Ṣaabiʹeena|wan-Naṣaaraa|wal-Majoosa|wallaẓeena|ʹashrakooo|ʹinnal|laaha|yafṣilu|baynahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Shaheed."
22,18,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|yasjudu|lahoo|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wa-mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|washshamsu|walq̣amaru|wan-nujoomu|wal-jibaalu|washshajaru|wad-dawaaabbu|wa-kas̤eerum|minan|naas?|Wa-kas̤eerun|ḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhil|ʻAẓaab.|Wa-mañy|yuhinil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|mim|mukrim:|ʹinnal|laaha|yafʻalu|maa-|yashaaaʹ."
22,19,"Haaẓaani|khaṣmaanikh|taṣamoo|fee|Rabbihim:|fal-laẓeena|kafaroo|q̣uṭṭiʻat|lahum|s̤iyaabum|min|Naar:|yuṣabbu|miñ|fawq̣i|ruʹoosihimul|ḥameem."
22,20,"Yuṣharu|bihee|maa-|fee|buṭoonihim|waljulood."
22,21,"Wa-lahum|maq̣aamiʻu|min|ḥadeed."
22,22,"Kullamaaa|ʹaraadooo|ʹañy|yakhrujoo|minhaa|min|g̣ammin|ʹuʻeedoo|feehaa|wa-ẓooq̣oo|ʻaẓaabal|Ḥareeq̣!"
22,23,"ʹInnal|laaha|yudkhilul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|yuḥallawna|feehaa|min|ʹasaawira|miñ|ẓahabiñw|waluʹluʹaa:|wa-libaasuhum|feehaa|ḥareer."
22,24,"Wa-hudooo|ʹilaṭ|Ṭayyibi|minal|Q̣awli|wa-hudooo|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭil|Ḥameed."
22,25,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-yaṣuddoona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|wal-Masjidil|Ḥaraamil|laẓee|jaʻalnaahu|linnaasi|sawaaaʹanil|ʻaakifu|feehi|walbaad.|Wa-mañy|yurid|feehi|biʹilḥaadim|biz̤̣ulmin|nuẓiq̣hu|min|ʻAẓaabin|ʹaleem."
22,26,"Wa-ʹiẓ|bawwaʹnaa|liʹIbraaheema|Makaanal|Bayti|ʹal|laa|tushrik|bee|shayʹañw|waṭahhir|Baytiya|liṭ-Ṭaaaʹifeena|wal-Q̣aaaʹimeena|war-Rukkaʻis|Sujood."
22,27,"Wa-ʹaẓẓin|fin|naasi|bil-Ḥajji|yaʹtooka|rijaalañw|wa-ʻalaa|kulli|ḍaamiriñy|yaʹteena|miñ|kulli|fajjin|ʻameeq̣;"
22,28,"Liyashhadoo|manaafiʻa|lahum|wa-yaẓkurus|mal|laahi|feee|ʹAyyaamim|Maʻloomaatin|ʻalaa|maa-|razaq̣ahum|mim|baheematil|ʹanʻaam:|fakuloo|minhaa|wa-ʹaṭʻimul|baaaʹisal|faq̣eer."
22,29,"S̤ummal|yaq̣ḍoo|tafas̤ahum|wal-yoofoo|nuẓoorahum|wal-yaṭṭawwafoo|bil-Baytil|ʻAteeq̣."
22,30,"Ẓaalika|wa-mañy|yuʻaz̤̣z̤̣im|Ḥurumaatil|laahi|fahuwa|khayrul|lahoo|ʻiñda|Rabbih.|Wa-ʹuḥillat|lakumul|ʹanʻaamu|ʹillaa|maa-|yutlaa|ʻalaykum|fajtanibur|rijsa|minal|ʹaws̤aani|wajtaniboo|q̣awlaz|zoor"
22,31,"Ḥunafaaaʹa|lillaahi|g̣ayra|mushrikeena|bih:|wa-mañy|yushrik|billaahi|fakaʹannamaa|kharra|minas|samaaaʹi|fatakhṭafuhut|ṭayru|ʹaw|tahwee|bihir|reeḥu|fee|makaaniñ|saḥeeq̣."
22,32,"Ẓaalik:|wa-mañy|yuʻaz̤̣z̤̣im|shaʻaaaʹiral|laahi|faʹinnahaa|miñ|taq̣wal|q̣uloob."
22,33,"lakum|feehaa|manaafiʻu|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammañ|s̤umma|maḥilluhaaa|ʹilal|Baytil|ʻAteeq̣."
22,34,"Wa-likulli|ʹummatiñ|jaʻalnaa|mañsakal|liyaẓkurus|mal|laahi|ʻalaa|maa-|razaq̣ahum|mim|baheematil|ʹanʻaam.|FaʹIlaahukum|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥiduñ|falahooo|ʹaslimoo:|wa-bashshiril|Mukhbiteen,"
22,35,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹiẓaa|ẓukiral|laahu|wajilat|q̣uloobuhum|waṣ-Ṣaabireena|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹaṣaabahum|walmuq̣eemiṣ|Ṣalaati|wa-mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|yuñfiq̣oon."
22,36,"Walbudna|jaʻalnaahaa|lakum|miñ|Shaʻaaaʹiril|laahi|lakum|feehaa|khayr:|faẓkurus|mal|laahi|ʻalayhaa|ṣawaaaff:|faʹiẓaa|wajabat|junoobuhaa|fakuloo|minhaa|wa-ʹaṭʻimul|q̣aaniʻa|walmuʻtarr:|kaẓaalika|sakhkharnaahaa|lakum|laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
22,37,"Lañy|yanaalal|laaha|luḥoomuhaa|wa-laa|dimaaaʹuhaa|wa-laakiñy|yanaaluhut|Taq̣waa|miñkum;|kaẓaalika|sakhkharahaa|lakum|litukabbirul|laaha|ʻalaa|maa-|hadaakum:|wa-bashshiril|Muḥsineen."
22,38,"ʹInnal|laaha|yudaafiʻu|ʻanil|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbu|kulla|khawwaaniñ|kafoor."
22,39,"ʹUẓina|lillaẓeena|yuq̣aataloona|biʹannahum|z̤̣ulimoo;|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|naṣrihim|la-Q̣adeer;"
22,40,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹukhrijoo|miñ|diyaarihim̃|big̣ayri|ḥaq̣q̣in|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yaq̣ooloo|Rabbunallaah.|Wa-law|laa-|dafʻul|laahin|naasa|baʻḍahum̃|bibaʻḍil|lahuddimat|ṣawaamiʹu|wa-biyaʻuñw|waṣalawaatuñw|wamasaajidu|yuẓkaru|feehas|mul|laahi|kas̤eeraa.|Wa-layañṣurannal|laahu|mañy|yañṣuruh;|ʹinnal|laaha|la-Q̣awiyyun|ʻAzeez."
22,41,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹim|makkannaahum|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatawuz|Zakaata|wa-ʹamaroo|bilmaʻroofi|wa-nahaw|ʻanil|muñkar:|wa-lillaahi|ʻaaq̣ibatul|ʹumoor."
22,42,"Wa-ʹiñy|yukaẓẓibooka|faq̣ad|kaẓẓabat|q̣ablahum|Q̣awmu|Nooḥiñw|waʻAaduñw|wa-S̤amood;"
22,43,"Wa-Q̣awmu|ʹIbraaheema|wa-Q̣awmu|Looṭ;"
22,44,"Wa-ʹAṣḥaabu|madyan;|wa-kuẓẓiba|Moosaa|faʹamlaytu|lilkaafireena|s̤umma|ʹakhaẓtuhum:|fakayfa|kaana|nakeer!"
22,45,"Fakaʹayyim|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹahlaknaahaa|wa-hiya|z̤̣aalimatuñ|fahiya|khaawiyatun|ʻalaa|ʻurooshihaa|wa-biʹrim|muʻaṭṭalatiñw|waq̣aṣrim|masheed?"
22,46,"ʹAfalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fatakoona|lahum|q̣uloobuñy|yaʻq̣iloona|bihaaa|ʹaw|ʹaaẓaanuñy|yasmaʻoona|bihaa?|Faʹinnahaa|laa-|taʻmal|ʹabṣaaru|wa-laakiñ|taʻmal|q̣uloobul|latee|fiṣ|ṣudoor."
22,47,"Wa-yastaʻjiloonaka|bilʻAẓaabi|wa-lañy|yukhlifal|laahu|waʻdaḥ|Wa-ʹinna|yawman|ʻiñda|Rabbika|kaʹalfi|sanatim|mimmaa|taʻuddoon."
22,48,"Wa-kaʹayyim|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹamlaytu|lahaa|wa-hiya|z̤̣aalimatuñ|s̤umma|ʹakhaẓtuhaa.|Wa-ʹilayyal|maṣeer."
22,49,"Q̣ul|Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|lakum|naẓeerum|mubeen."
22,50,"Fallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|lahum|mag̣hfiratuñw|warizq̣uñ|kareem."
22,51,"Wallaẓeena|saʻaw|feee|ʹAayaatinaa|muʻaajizeena|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jaḥeem."
22,52,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|mir|rasooliñw|walaa|nabiyyin|ʹillaaa|ʹiẓaa|tamannaaa|ʹalq̣ash|Shayṭaanu|feee|ʹumniyyatih:|fayañsakhul|laahu|maa-|yulq̣ish|Shayṭaanu|s̤umma|yuḥkimul|laahu|ʹAayaatih:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem:"
22,53,"Liyajʻala|maa-|yulq̣ish|Shayṭaanu|fitnatal|lillaz̤̣eena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍuñw|walq̣aasiyati|q̣uloobuhum:|wa-ʹinnaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|lafee|shiq̣aaq̣im|baʻeed:"
22,54,"Wa-liyaʻlamal|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻllma|ʹannahul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbika|fayuʹminoo|bihee|fatukhbita|lahoo|q̣uloobuhum:|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|la-Haadil|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
22,55,"Wa-laa|yazaalul|laẓeena|kafaroo|fee|miryatim|minhu|ḥattaa|taʹtiyahumus|Saaʻatu|bag̣tatan|ʹaw|yaʹtiyahum|ʹaẓaabu|Yawmin|ʻAq̣eem."
22,56,"ʹAl-Mulku|Yawmaʹiẓil|lillaah:|yaḥkumu|baynahum:|fallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|fee|Jannaatin|Naʻeem."
22,57,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|faʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻAẓaabum|muheen."
22,58,"Wallaẓeena|haajaroo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|s̤umma|q̣utilooo|ʹaw|maatoo|layarzuq̣annahumul|laahu|Rizq̣an|ḥasanaa:|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|la-Huwa|Khayrur|raaziq̣een."
22,59,"Layudkhilannahum|mud-khalañy|yarḍawnah:|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|laʻAleemun|Ḥaleem."
22,60,"Ẓaalika.|Wa-man|ʻaaq̣aba|bimis̤li|maa-|ʻooq̣iba|bihee|s̤umma|bug̣iya|ʻalayhi|layañṣurannahul|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|laʻAfuwwun|G̣afoor."
22,61,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|yoolijul|layla|fin|nahaari|wa-yoolijun|nahaara|fil|layli|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Sameeʻum|Baṣeer."
22,62,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|Huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-ʹanna|maa-|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|huwal|Baaṭilu|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Huwal|ʻAliyyul|Kabeer."
22,63,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|fatuṣbiḥul|ʹarḍu|mukhḍarrah?|ʹInnal|laaha|Laṭeefun|Khabeer."
22,64,"Lahoo|Maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|la-Huwal|G̣aniyyul|Ḥameed."
22,65,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|sakhkhara|lakum|maa|fil|ʹarḍi|wal-fulka|tajree|fil|baḥri|biʹamrih?|Wa-yumsikus|samaaaʹa|ʹañ|taq̣aʻa|ʻalal|ʹarḍi|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnih:|ʹinnal|laaha|binnaasi|la-Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
22,66,"Wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹaḥyaakum|s̤umma|yumeetukum|s̤umma|yuḥyeekum:|ʹinnal|ʹiñsaana|lakafoor!"
22,67,"Likulli|ʹummatiñ|jaʻalnaa|mañsakan|hum|naasikoohu|falaa|yunaaziʻunnaka|fil|ʹamri|wadʻu|ʹilaa|Rabbik;|ʹinnaka|laʻalaa|Hudam|Mustaq̣eem."
22,68,"Wa-ʹiñ|jaadalooka|faq̣ulil|laahu|ʹAʻlamu|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
22,69,"ʹAllaahu|yaḥkumu|baynakum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|feema|kuñtum|feehi|takhtalifoon."
22,70,"ʹAlam|taʻlam|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍ?|ʹInna|ẓaalika|fee|Kitaab:|ʹinna|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseer."
22,71,"Wa-yaʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa-|lam|yunazzil|bihee|sulṭaanañw|wamaa|laysa|lahum̃|bihee|ʻilm:|wa-maa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|min|naṣeer."
22,72,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|Bayyinaatiñ|taʻrifu|fee|wujoohil|laẓeena|kafarul|muñkar!|Yakaadoona|yasṭoona|bil-laẓeena|yatloona|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatinaa.|Q̣ul|ʹa-faʹunabbiʹukum̃|bisharrim|miñ|ẓaalikum?|ʹAn-Naar!|Waʻadahal|laahul|laẓeena|kafaroo!|Wa-biʹsal|maṣeer."
22,73,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ḍuriba|mas̤aluñ|fastamiʻoo|lah!|ʹInnal|laẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|lañy|yakhluq̣oo|ẓubaabañw|walawij|tamaʻoo|lah!|Wa-ʹiñy|yaslubhumuẓ|ẓubaabu|shayʹal|laa|yastañq̣iẓoohu|minh.|Ḍaʻufaṭ|ṭaalibu|wal-maṭloob!"
22,74,"Maa-|q̣adarul|laaha|ḥaq̣q̣a|q̣adrih:|ʹinnal|laaha|la-Q̣awiyyun|ʻAzeez!"
22,75,"ʹAllaahu|yasṭafee|minal|malaaaʹikati|Rusulañw|Waminan|naas:|ʹinnal|laaha|Sameeʻum|Baṣeer."
22,76,"Yaʻlamu|maa-|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-maa|khalfahum:|wa-ʹilal|laahi|turjaʻul|ʹumoor."
22,77,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanur|kaʻoo|wasjudoo|waʻbudoo|Rabbakum|wafʻalul|khayra|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
22,78,"Wa-jaahidoo|fil|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣a|jihaadih.|Huwaj|tabaakum|wa-maa|jaʻala|ʻalaykum|fid|deeni|min|ḥaraj;|Millata|ʹabeekum|ʹIbraaheem.|Huwa|sammaakumul|Muslimeen.|Miñ|q̣ablu|wa-fee|haaẓaa|liyakoonar|Rasoolu|shaheedan|ʻalaykum|wa-takoonoo|shuhadaaaʹa|ʻalan|naas!|Faʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaata|waʻtaṣimoo|billaah!|Huwa|Mawlaakum|faniʻmal|Mawlaa|wa-niʻman|Naṣeer."
23,1,"Q̣ad|ʹaflaḥal|muʹminoon,"
23,2,"ʹAllaẓeena|hum|fee|Ṣalaatihim|khaashiʻoon;"
23,3,"Wallaẓeena|hum|ʻanil|lag̣wi|muʻriḍoon;"
23,4,"Wallaẓeena|hum|liz-Zakaati|faaʻiloon;"
23,5,"Wallaẓeena|hum|lifuroojihim|ḥaafiz̤̣oon,"
23,6,"ʹIllaa|ʻalaaa|ʹazwaajihim|ʹaw|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanuhum|faʹinnahum|g̣ayru|maloomeen."
23,7,"Famanib|tag̣aa|waraaaʹa|ẓaalika|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|ʻaadoon;"
23,8,"Wallaẓeena|hum|liʹamaanaatihim|wa-ʻahdihim|raaʻoon;"
23,9,"wallaẓeena|hum|ʻalaa|Ṣalawaatihim|yuḥaafiz̤̣oon."
23,10,"ʹUlaaaʹika|humul|waaris̤oon,"
23,11,"ʹAllaẓeena|yaris̤oonal|Firdaws:|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
23,12,"Wa-laq̣ad|khalaq̣nal|ʹiñsaana|miñ|sulaalatim|miñ|ṭeen;"
23,13,"S̤umma|jaʻalnaahu|nuṭfatañ|fee|q̣araarim|makeen;"
23,14,"S̤umma|khalaq̣nan|nuṭfata|ʻalaq̣atañ|fakhalaq̣nal|ʻalaq̣ata|muḍg̣atañ|fakhalaq̣nal|muḍg̣ata|ʻiz̤̣aamañ|fakasawnal|ʻiz̤̣aama|laḥmaa;|s̤umma|ʹañshaʹnaahu|khalq̣an|ʹaakhar.|Fatabaarakal|laahu|ʹAḥsanul|khaaliq̣een!"
23,15,"S̤umma|ʹinnakum|baʻda|ẓaalika|lamayyitoon."
23,16,"S̤umma|ʹinnakum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|tubʻas̤oon."
23,17,"Wa-laq̣ad|khalaq̣naa|fawq̣akum|sabʻa|ṭaraaaʹiq̣a|wa-maa|kunnaa|ʻanil|khalq̣i|g̣aafileen."
23,18,"Wa-ʹañzalnaa|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹam|biq̣adariñ|faʹaskannaahu|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹInnaa|ʻalaa|ẓahaabim|bihee|la-Q̣aadiroon."
23,19,"Faʹañshaʹnaa|lakum̃|bihee|jannaatim|min|nakheeliñw|waʹaʻnaab.|Lakum|feehaa|fawaakihu|kas̤eeratuñw|waminhaa|taʹkuloon,"
23,20,"Wa-shajaratañ|takhruju|miñ|Ṭoori|Saynaaaʹa|tambutu|bidduhni|waṣibg̣illil|ʹaa-kileen."
23,21,"Wa-ʹinna|lakum|fil|ʹanʻaami|laʻibrah:|nusq̣eekum|mimmaa|fee|buṭoonihaa|wa-lakum|feehaa|manaafiʻu|kas̤eeratuñw|waminhaa|taʹkuloon;"
23,22,"Wa-ʻalayhaa|wa-ʻalal|fulki|tuḥmaloon."
23,23,"Wa-laq̣ad.|ʹarsalnaa|Nooḥan|ʹilaa|q̣awmihee|faq̣aala|yaa|q̣awmiʻbudul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|ʹAfalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
23,24,"Faq̣aalal|malaʹul|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|q̣awmihee|maa-|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lukum|yureedu|ʹañy|yatafaḍḍala|ʻalaykum:|wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|laʹañzala|malaaaʹikah:|maa-|samiʻnaa|bihaaẓaa|feee|ʹaabaaaʹinal|ʹawwaleen."
23,25,"ʹIn|huwa|ʹillaa|rajulum|bihee|jinnatuñ|fatarabbaṣoo|bihee|ḥattaa|ḥeen."
23,26,"Q̣aala|Rabbiñ|ṣurnee|bimaa|kaẓẓaboon!"
23,27,"Faʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayhi|ʹaniṣ|naʻil|Fulka|biʹaʻyuninaa|wa-waḥyinaa|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹAmrunaa|wa-faarat|tannooru|fasluk|feehaa|miñ|kulliñ|zawjaynis̤|nayni|wa-ʹahlaka|ʹillaa|mañ|sabaq̣a|ʻalayhil|Q̣awlu|minhum:|wa-laa|tukhaaṭibnee|fil|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo;|ʹinnahum|mug̣raq̣oon."
23,28,"Faʹiẓas|tawayta|ʹañta|wa-mam|maʻaka|ʻalal|Fulki|faq̣ulil|Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓee|najjaanaa|minal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
23,29,"Wa-q̣ur|Rabbi|ʹañzilnee|muñzalam|mubaarakañw|waʹAñta|Khayrul|Muñzileen."
23,30,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatiñw|waʹiñ|kunnaa|lamubtaleen."
23,31,"S̤umma|ʹañshaʹnaa|mim|baʻdihim|q̣arnan|ʹaakhareen."
23,32,"Faʹarsalnaa|feehim|rasoolam|minhum|ʹaniʻ|budul|laaha|maa-|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayruh.|ʹAfalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
23,33,"Wa-q̣aalal|malaʹu|miñ|q̣awmihil|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|bi-Liq̣aaaʹil|ʹAakhirati|wa-ʹatrafnaahum|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|maa-|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lukum|yaʹkulu|mimmaa|taʹkuloona|minhu|wa-yashrabu|mimmaa|tashraboon."
23,34,"Wa-laʹin|ʹaṭaʻtum̃|basharam|mis̤lakum|ʹinnakum|ʹiẓal|lakhaasiroon."
23,35,"ʹA-yaʻidukum|ʹannakum|ʹiẓaa|mittum|wa-kuñtum|turaabañw|waʻiz̤̣aaman|ʹannakum|mukhrajoon?"
23,36,"Hayhaata|hayhaata|limaa|tooʻadoon!"
23,37,"ʹIn|hiya|ʹillaa|ḥayaatunad|dunyaa|namootu|wa-naḥyaa|wa-maa|naḥnoo|bimabʻoos̤een!"
23,38,"ʹIn|huwa|ʹillaa|rajulunif|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓibañw|wamaa|naḥnu|lahoo|bimuʹmineen!"
23,39,"Q̣aala|Rabbiñ|ṣurnee|bimaa|kaẓẓaboon."
23,40,"Q̣aala|ʻammaa|q̣aleelil|layuṣbiḥunna|naadimeen!"
23,41,"Faʹakhaẓathumuṣ|Ṣayḥatu|bilḥaq̣q̣i|fajaʻalnaahum|g̣us̤aaaʹaa!|Fabuʻdal|lilq̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
23,42,"S̤umma|ʹañshaʹnaa|mim|baʻdihim|q̣uroonan|ʹaakhareen."
23,43,"Maa-|tasbiq̣u|min|ʹummatin|ʹajalahaa|wa-maa|yastaʹkhiroon."
23,44,"S̤umma|ʹarsalnaa|rusulanaa|tatraa.|Kulla|maa|jaaaʹa|ʹummatar|rasooluhaa|kaẓẓaboohu|faʹatbaʻnaa|baʻḍahum|baʻḍañw|wajaʹalnaahum|ʹaḥaadees̤:|fabuʻdal|liq̣awmil|laa|yuʹminoon!"
23,45,"S̤umma|ʹarsalnaa|Moosaa|wa-ʹakhaahu|Haaroona|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-sulṭaanim|mubeen."
23,46,"ʹIlaa|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹihee|fastakbaroo|wa-kaanoo|q̣awman|ʻaaleen."
23,47,"Faq̣aalooo|ʹanuʹminu|libasharayni|mis̤linaa|wa-q̣awmuhumaa|lanaa|ʻaabidoon?"
23,48,"Fakaẓẓaboohumaa|fakaanoo|minal|muhlakeen."
23,49,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|laʻallahum|yahtadoon."
23,50,"Wa-jaʻalnab|na|Maryama|wa-ʹummahooo|ʹAayatañw|Waʹaawaynaahumaaa|ʹilaa|rabwatiñ|ẓaati|q̣araariñw|wamaʻeen."
23,51,"Yaaaʹayyuhar|rusulu|kuloo|minaṭ|ṭayyibaati|waʻmaloo|ṣaaliḥaa:|ʹinnee|bimaa|taʻmaloona|ʻAleem."
23,52,"Wa-ʹinna|haaẓiheee|ʹummatukum|ʹummatañw|Waaḥidatañw|WaʹAna|Rabbukum|fattaq̣oon."
23,53,"Fataq̣aṭṭaʻooo|ʹamrahum̃|baynahum|zuburaa:|kullu|ḥizbim|bimaa|ladayhim|fariḥoon."
23,54,"Faẓarhum|fee|g̣amratihim|ḥattaa|ḥeen."
23,55,"ʹA-yaḥsaboona|ʹannamaa|numidduhum̃|bihee|mim|maaliñw|wabaneen,"
23,56,"Nusaariʻu|lahum|fil|khayraat?|Bal|laa|yashʻuroon."
23,57,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|hum|min|khashyati|Rabbihim|mushfiq̣oon;"
23,58,"Wallaẓeena|hum̃|biʹAayaati|Rabbihim|yuʹminoon;"
23,59,"Wallaẓeena|hum̃|bi-Rabbihim|laa-|yushrikoon;"
23,60,"Wallaẓeena|yuʹtoona|maaa|ʹaataw|Waq̣uloobuhum|wajilatun|ʹannahum|ʹilaa|Rabbihim|raajiʻoon;"
23,61,"ʹUlaaaʹika|yusaariʻoona|fil|khayraati|wa-hum|lahaa|saabiq̣oon."
23,62,"Wa-laa|nukallifu|nafsan|ʹillaa|wusʻahaa|wa-ladaynaa|Kitaabuñy|yañṭiq̣u|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
23,63,"Bal|q̣uloobuhum|fee|g̣amratim|min|haaẓaa|wa-lahum|ʹaʻmaalum|miñ|dooni|ẓaalika|hum|lahaa|ʻaamiloon,"
23,64,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹakhaẓnaa|mutrafeehim̃|bilʻAẓaabi|ʹiẓaa|hum|yajʹaroon!"
23,65,"Laaa|tajʹarul|yawm:|ʹinnakum|minnaa|laa-|tuñṣaroon."
23,66,"Q̣ad|kaanat|ʹAayaatee|tutlaa|ʻalaykum|fakuñtum|ʻalaaa|ʹaʻq̣aabikum|tañkiṣoon."
23,67,"Mustakbireena|bihee|saamirañ|tahjuroon."
23,68,"ʹAfalam|yaddabbarul|Q̣awla|ʹam|jaaaʹahum|maa|lam|yaʹti|ʹaabaaaʹahumul|ʹawwaleen?"
23,69,"ʹAm|lam|yaʻrifoo|Rasoolahum|fahum|lahoo|muñkiroon?"
23,70,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloona|bihee|jinnah?|Bal|jaaaʹahum̃|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹaks̤aruhum|lil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|kaarihoon."
23,71,"Wa-lawit|tabaʻal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|ʹahwaaaʹahum|lafasadatis|samaawaatu|wal-ʹarḍu|wa-mañ|feehinn!|Bal|ʹataynaahum̃|biẓikrihim|fahum|ʻañ|ẓikrihim|muʻriḍoon."
23,72,"ʹAm|tasʹaluhum|kharjañ|fakharaaju|Rabbika|khayr:|wa-Huwa|Khayrur|raaziq̣een."
23,73,"Wa-ʹinnaka|latadʻoohum|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
23,74,"Waʹinnal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|ʻaniṣ|Ṣiraaṭi|lanaakiboon."
23,75,"Wa-law|raḥimnaahum|wakashafnaa|maa-|bihim|miñ|ḍurril|lalajjoo|fee|ṭug̣yaanihim|yaʻmahoon."
23,76,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹakhaẓnaahum̃|bilʻAẓaabi|famas|takaanoo|li-Rabbihim|wa-maa|yataḍarraʻoon,"
23,77,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|fataḥnaa|ʻalayhim|baabañ|ẓaa|ʻaẓaabiñ|shadeedin|ʹiẓaa|hum|feehi|mublisoon!"
23,78,"Wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañshaʹa|lakumus|samʻa|wal-ʹabṣaara|wal-ʹafʹidah:|q̣aleelam|maa|tashkuroon!"
23,79,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|ẓaraʹakum|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹilayhi|tuḥsharoon."
23,80,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|yuḥyee|wa-yumeetu|wa-lahukh|tilaaful|layli|wannahaar:|ʹafalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
23,81,"Bal|q̣aaloo|mis̤la|maa-|q̣aalal|ʹAwwaloon."
23,82,"Q̣aalooo|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|mitnaa|wa-kunnaa|turaabañw|waʻiz̤̣aaman|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lamabʻoos̤oon?"
23,83,"Laq̣ad|wuʻidnaa|naḥnu|wa-ʹaabaaaʹunaa|haaẓaa|miñ|q̣ablu|ʹin|haaẓa|illaaa|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleen!"
23,84,"Q̣ul|limanil|ʹarḍu|wa-mañ|feehaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon?"
23,85,"Sayaq̣ooloona|lillaah!|Q̣ul|ʹafalaa|taẓakkaroon?"
23,86,"Q̣ul|mar|Rabbus|samaawaatis|sabʻi|wa-Rabbul|ʻArshil|ʻAz̤̣eem?"
23,87,"Sayaq̣ooloona|lillaah.|Q̣ul|ʹafalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
23,88,"Q̣ul|mam|biyadihee|Malakootu|kulli|shayʹiñw|wa-Huwa|yujeeru|wa-laa|yujaaru|ʻalayhi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon?"
23,89,"Sayaq̣ooloona|lillaah.|Q̣ul|faʹannaa|tus-ḥaroon?"
23,90,"Bal|ʹataynaahum̃|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon!"
23,91,"Mat|takhaẓal|laahu|miñw|waladiñw|wamaa|kaana|maʻahoo|min|ʹilaahin|ʹiẓal|laẓahaba|kullu|ʹilaahim|bimaa|khalaq̣a|wa-laʻalaa|baʻḍuhum|ʻalaa|baʻḍ!|Subḥaanal|laahi|ʻammaa|yaṣifoon!"
23,92,"ʻAalimil|g̣aybi|washshahaadati|fataʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
23,93,"Q̣ur|Rabbi|ʹimmaa|turiyannee|maa-|yooʻadoon,"
23,94,"Rabbi|falaa|tajʻalnee|fil|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
23,95,"Wa-ʹinnaa|ʻalaaa|ʹan|nuriyaka|maa-|naʻiduhum|la-Q̣aadiroon."
23,96,"ʹIdfaʻ|billatee|hiya|ʹaḥsanus|sayyiʹah:|Naḥnu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|yaṣifoon."
23,97,"Wa-q̣ur|Rabbi|ʹaʻooẓu|bika|min|hamazaatish|shayaaṭeen."
23,98,"Wa-ʹaʻooẓu|bika|Rabbi|ʹañy|yaḥḍuroon."
23,99,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹaḥadahumul|mawtu|q̣aala|Rabbir|jiʻoon,"
23,100,"Laʻalleee|ʹaʻmalu|ṣaaliḥañ|feemaa|taraktu|kallaa!|ʹInnahaa|kalimatun|huwa|q̣aaaʹiluhaa.|Wa-miñw|waraaaʹihim|Barzakhun|ʹilaa|Yawmi|yubʻas̤oon."
23,101,"Faʹiẓaa|nufikha|fiṣ|Ṣoori|falaaa|ʹañsaaba|baynahum|Yawmaʹiẓiñw|Walaa|yatasaaaʹaloon!"
23,102,"Famañ|s̤aq̣ulat|mawaazeenuhoo|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon:"
23,103,"Wa-man|khaffat|mawaazeenuhoo|faʹulaaaʹikal|laẓeena|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|fee|Jahannama|khaalidoon."
23,104,"Talfaḥu|wujoohahumun|Naaru|wa-hum|feehaa|kaaliḥoon."
23,105,"ʹAlam|takun|ʹAayaatee|tutlaa|ʻalaykum|fakuñtum̃|bihaa|tukaẓẓiboon?"
23,106,"Q̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|g̣alabat|ʻalaynaa|shiq̣watunaa|wa-kunnaa|q̣awmañ|ḍaaalleen!"
23,107,"Rabbanaaa|ʹakhrijnaa|minhaa|faʹin|ʻudnaa|faʹinnaa|z̤̣aalimoon!"
23,108,"Q̣aalakh|saʹoo|feehaa|wa-laa|tukallimoon!"
23,109,"ʹInnahoo|kaana|fareeq̣um|min|ʻibaadee|yaq̣ooloona|˹Rabbanaaa|ʹaamannaa|fag̣fir|lanaa|warḥamnaa|wa-ʹAñta|Khayrur|raaḥimeen˺!"
23,110,"Fattakhaẓtumoohum|sikhriyyan|ḥattaaa|ʹañsawkum|Ẓikree|wa-kuñtum|minhum|taḍḥakoon!"
23,111,"ʹInnee|jazaytuhumul|yawma|bimaa|ṣabarooo|ʹannahum|humul|Faaaʹizoon."
23,112,"Q̣aala|kam|labis̤tum|fil|ʹarḍi|ʻadada|sineen?"
23,113,"Q̣aaloo|labis̤naa|yawman|ʹaw|baʻḍa|yawmiñ|fasʹalil|ʻaaaddeen."
23,114,"Q̣aala|ʹil|labis̤tum|ʹillaa|q̣aleelal|law|ʹannakum|kuñtum|taʻlamoon!"
23,115,"ʹAfaḥasibtum|ʹannamaa|khalaq̣naakum|ʻabas̤añw|Waʹannakum|ʹilaynaa|laa-|turjaʻoon?"
23,116,"Fataʻaalal|laahul|Malikul|Ḥaq̣q̣:|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo:|Rabbul|ʻArshil|Kareem!"
23,117,"Wa-mañy|yadʻu|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhara|laa-|burhaana|lahoo|bihee|faʹinnamaa|ḥisaabuhoo|ʻiñda|Rabbih!|ʹInnahoo|laa-|yufliḥul|Kaafiroon!"
23,118,"Wa-q̣ur|Rabbig̣|fir|warḥam|wa-ʹAñta|Khayrur|raaḥimeen!"
24,1,"Sooratun|ʹañzalnaahaa|wa-faraḍnaahaa|wa-ʹañzalnaa|feehaaa|ʹAayaatim|Bayyinaatil|laʻallakum|taẓakkaroon."
24,2,"ʹAzzaaniyatu|wazzaanee|fajlidoo|kulla|waaḥidim|minhumaa|miʹata|jaldah;|wa-laa|taʹkhuẓkum̃|bihimaa|raʹfatuñ|fee|Deenil|laahi|ʹiñ|kuñtum|tuʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir:|wal-yashhad|ʻaẓaabahumaa|ṭaaaʹifatum|minal|Muʹmineen."
24,3,"ʹAzzaanee|laa-|yañkiḥu|ʹillaa|zaaniyatan|ʹaw|mushrikah:|wazzaaniyatu|laa-|yañkiḥuhaaa|ʹillaa|zaanin|ʹaw|mushrik:|waḥurrima|ẓaalika|ʻalal|Muʹmineen."
24,4,"Wallaẓeena|yarmoonal|muḥṣanaati|s̤umma|lam|yaʹtoo|biʹarbaʻati|shuhadaaaʹa|fajlidoohum|s̤amaaneena|jaldatañw|walaa|taq̣baloo|lahum|shahaadatan|ʹabadaa:|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|faasiq̣oon;"
24,5,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|taaboo|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalika|wa-ʹaṣlaḥoo;|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
24,6,"Wallaẓeena|yarmoona|ʹazwaajahum|wa-lam|yakul|lahum|shuhadaaaʹu|ʹillaaa|ʹañfusuhum|fashahaadatu|ʹaḥadihim|ʹarbaʻu|shahaadaatim|billaahi|ʹinnahoo|laminaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een;"
24,7,"Wal-khaamisatu|ʹanna|laʻnatal|laahi|ʻalayhi|ʹiñ|kaana|minal|kaaẓibeen."
24,8,"Wa-yadraʹu|ʻanhal|ʻaẓaaba|ʹañ|tashhada|ʹarbaʻa|shahaadaatim|billaahi|ʹinnahoo|laminal|kaaẓibeen;"
24,9,"Wal-khaamisata|ʹanna|g̣aḍabal|laahi|ʻalayhaaa|ʹiñ|kaana|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een."
24,10,"Wa-lawlaa|faḍlul|laahi|ʻalaykum|wa-raḥmatuhoo|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Tawwaabun|Hakeem."
24,11,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|jaaaʹoo|bilʹifki|ʻuṣbatum|miñkum:|laa-|taḥsaboohu|sharral|lakum:|bal|huwa|khayrul|lakum:|likullim|riʹim|minhum|mak|tasaba|minal|ʹis̤m,|wallaẓee|tawallaa|kibrahoo|minhum|lahoo|ʻAẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
24,12,"Law-laaa|ʹiẓ|samiʻtumoohu|z̤̣annal|Muʹminoona|wal-Muʹminaatu|biʹañfusihim|khayrañw|waq̣aaloo|haaẓaaa|ʹifkum|mubeen?"
24,13,"Law-laa|jaaaʹoo|ʻalayhi|biʹarbaʻati|shuhadaaaʹ?|Faʹiẓ|lam|yaʹtoo|bishshuhadaaaʹi|faʹulaaaʹika|ʻiñdal|laahi|humul|kaaẓiboon!"
24,14,"Wa-lawlaa|faḍlul|laahi|ʻalaykum|wa-raḥmatuhoo|fiddunyaa|wal|ʹAakhirati|lamassakum|fee|maaa|ʹafaḍtum|feehi|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaz̤̣eem."
24,15,"ʹIẓ|talaq̣q̣awnahoo|biʹalsinatikum|wa-taq̣ooloona|biʹafwaahikum|maa|laysa|lakum̃|bihee|ʻilmuñw|Wataḥsaboonahoo|hayyinañw|wahuwa|ʻiñdal|laahi|ʻaz̤̣eem."
24,16,"Wa-lawlaaa|ʹiẓ|samiʻtumoohu|q̣ultum|maa|yakoonu|lanaaa|ʹan|natakallama|bihaaẓaa:|Subḥaanaka|haaẓaa|buhtaanun|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
24,17,"Yaʻiz̤̣ukumul|laahu|ʹañ|taʻoodoo|limis̤liheee|ʹabadan|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
24,18,"Wa-yubayyinul|laahu|lakumul|ʹAayaat:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
24,19,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yuḥibboona|ʹañ|tasheeʻal|faaḥishatu|fil|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleemuñ|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah:|wallaahu|yaʻlamu|waʹañtum|laa-|taʻlamoon."
24,20,"Wa-lawlaa|faḍlul|laahi|ʻalaykum|wa-raḥmatuhoo|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
24,21,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tattabiʻoo|khuṭuwaatish|Shayṭaan:|wa-mañy|yattabiʻ|khuṭuwaatish|Shayṭaani|faʹinnahoo|yaʹmuru|bilfaḥshaaaʹi|walmuñkar:|wa-lawlaa|faḍlul|laahi|ʻalaykum|Waraḥmatuhoo|maa-|zakaa|miñkum|min|ʹaḥadin|ʹabadañw|wa-laakinnal|laaha|yuzakkee|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wallaahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
24,22,"Wa-laa|yaʹtali|ʹulul|faḍli|miñkum|wassaʻati|ʹañy|yuʹtooo|ʹulil|q̣urbaa|walmasaakeena|wal-Muhaajireena|fee|Sabeelil|laah:|walyaʻfoo|walyaṣfaḥoo.|ʹAlaa|tuḥibboona|ʹañy|yag̣firal|laahu|lakum?|Wal-laahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
24,23,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yarmoonal|muḥṣanaatil|g̣aafilaatil|Muʹminaati|luʻinoo|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirah:|wa-lahum|ʻAẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem,"
24,24,"Yawma|tashhadu|ʻalayhim|ʹalsinatuhum|wa-ʹaydeehim|wa-ʹarjuluhum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
24,25,"Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yuwaffeehimul|laahu|deenahumul|ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-yaʻlamoona|ʹannal|laaha|Huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣ul|Mubeen."
24,26,"ʹAl-khabees̤aatu|lil-khabees̤eena|wal-khabees̤oona|lil-khabees̤aat;|waṭ-ṭayyibaatu|liṭ-ṭayyibeena|waṭ-ṭayyiboona|liṭ-ṭayyibaat:|ʹulaaaʹika|mubarraʹoona|mimmaa|yaq̣ooloon:|lahum|mag̣firatuñw|wa-rizq̣uñ|kareem."
24,27,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tadkhuloo|buyootan|g̣ayra|buyootikum|ḥattaa|tastaʹnisoo|wa-tusallimoo|ʻalaaa|ʹahlihaa:|ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|laʻallakum|taẓakkaroon."
24,28,"Faʹil|lam|tajidoo|feehaaa|ʹaḥadañ|falaa|tadkhuloohaa|ḥattaa|yuʹẓana|lakum:|wa-ʹiñ|q̣eela|lakumur|jiʻoo|farjiʻoo|huwa|ʹazkaa|lakum:|wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|ʻAleem."
24,29,"Laysa|ʻalaykum|junaaḥun|ʹañ|tadkhuloo|buyootan|g̣ayra|maskoonatiñ|feeha|mataaʻul|lakum:|wallaahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|tubdoona|wa-maa|taktumoon."
24,30,"Q̣ul|lil-Muʹmineena|yag̣uḍḍoo|min|ʹabṣaarihim|wa-yaḥfaz̤̣oo|furoojahum:|ẓaalika|ʹazkaa|lahum:|ʹinnal|laaha|khabeerum|bimaa|yaṣnaʻoon."
24,31,"Wa-q̣ul|lil-Muʹminaati|yag̣ḍuḍna|min|ʹabṣaarihinna|wa-yaḥfaz̤̣na|furoojahunna|wa-laa|yubdeena|zeenatahunna|ʹillaa|maa-|z̤̣ahara|minhaa|wal-yaḍribna|bikhumurihinna|ʻalaa|juyoobihinn;|wa-laa|yubdeena|zeenatahunna|ʹillaa|libuʻoolatihinna|ʹaw|ʹaabaaaʹihinna|ʹaw|ʹaabaaaʹi|buʻoolatihinna|ʹaw|ʹabnaaaʹihinna|ʹaw|ʹabnaaaʹi|buʻoolatihinna|ʹaw|ʹikhwaanihinna|ʹaw|baneee|ʹikhwaanihinna|ʹaw|baneee|ʹakhawaatihinna|ʹaw|nisaaaʹihinna|ʹaw|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanuhunna|ʹawit|taabiʻeena|g̣ayri|ʹulil|ʹirbati|minar|rijaali|ʹawiṭ|ṭiflil|laẓeena!|lam|yaz̤̣haroo|ʻalaa|ʻawraatin|nisaaaʹ;|wa-laa|yaḍribna|biʹarjulihinna|liyuʻlama|maa-|yukhfeena|miñ|zeenatihinn.|Wa-toobooo|ʹilal|laahi|jameeʻan|ʹayyuhal|Muʹminoona|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
24,32,"Wa-añkiḥul|ʹayaamaa|miñkum|waṣ-ṣaaliḥeena|min|ʻibaadikum|wa-ʹimaaaʹikum:|ʹiñy|yakoonoo|fuq̣araaaʹa|yug̣nihimul|laahu|miñ|faḍlih:|wal-laahu|Waasiʻun|ʻAleem."
24,33,"Wal-yastaʻfifil|laẓeena|laa-|yajidoona|nikaaḥan|ḥattaa|yug̣niyahumul|laahu|miñ|faḍliḥ.|Wallaẓeena|yabtag̣oonal|Kitaaba|mimmaa|malakat|ʹaymaanukum|fakaatiboohum|ʹin|ʻalimtum|feehim|khayrañw|waʹaatoohum|mim|maalil|laahil|laẓeee|ʹaataakum.|Wa-laa|tukrihoo|fatayaatikum|ʻalal|big̣aaaʹi|ʹin|ʹaradna|taḥaṣṣunal|litabtag̣oo|ʻaraḍal|ḥayaatid|dunyaa.|Wa-mañy|yukrihhunna|faʹinnal|laaha|mim|baʻdi|ʹikraahihinna|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
24,34,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykum|ʹaayaatim|mubayyinaatiñw|wamas̤alam|minal|laẓeena|khalaw|miñ|q̣ablikum|wa-mawʻiz̤̣atal|lil-Muttaq̣een."
24,35,"ʹAllaahu|Noorus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|Mas̤alu|Noorihee|ka-Mishkaatiñ|feehaa|Miṣbaaḥ:|ʹAl-Miṣbaaḥu|fee|Zujaajah:|ʹazzujaajatu|kaʹannahaa|kawkabuñ|durriyyuñy|yooq̣adu|miñ|Shajaratim|mubaarakatiñ|Zaytoonatil|laa|Sharq̣iyyatiñw|Walaa|G̣arbiyyatiñy|yakaadu|Zaytuhaa|yuḍeeeʹu|wa-law|lam|tamsashu|naar:|Noorun|ʻalaa|Noor!|Yahdil|laahu|li-Noorihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-yaḍribul|laahul|ʹams̤aala|linnaas:|wallaahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
24,36,"Fee|buyootin|ʹaẓinal|laahu|ʹañ|turfaʻa|wa-yuẓkara|feehas|muhoo|yusabbiḥu|lahoo|feehaa|bilg̣uduwwi|wal-ʹaaṣaal."
24,37,"Rijaalul|laa|tulheehim|tijaaratuñw|walaa|bayʻun|ʻañ|ẓikril|laahi|wa-ʹiq̣aamiṣ|Ṣalaati|wa-ʹeetaaaʹiz|Zakaati|yakhaafoona|Yawmañ|tataq̣allabu|feehil|q̣uloobu|wal-ʹabṣaar,"
24,38,"Liyajziyahumul|laahu|ʹaḥsana|maa-|ʻamiloo|wa-yazeedahum|miñ|faḍlih;|wal-laahu|yarzuq̣u|mañy|yashaaaʹu|big̣ayri|hisaab."
24,39,"Wallaẓeena|kafarooo|ʹaʻmaaluhum|kasaraabim|biq̣eeʻatiñy|yaḥsabuhuz̤̣|z̤̣amʹaanu|maaaʹaa;|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹahoo|lam|yajidhu|shayʹañw|wawajadal|laaha|ʻiñdahoo|fawaffaahu|ḥisaabah:|wallaahu|Sareeʻul|ḥisaab."
24,40,"ʹAw|kaz̤̣ulumaatiñ|fee|baḥril|lujjiyyiñy|yag̣shaahu|mawjum|miñ|fawq̣ihee|mawjum|miñ|fawq̣ihee|saḥaab:|z̤̣ulumaatum|baʻḍuhaa|fawq̣a|baʻḍ:|ʹiẓaaa|ʹakhraja|yadahoo|lam|yakad|yaraahaa!|wa-mal|lam|yajʻalil|laahu|lahoo|noorañ|famaa|lahoo|min|noor!"
24,41,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|yusabbiḥu|lahoo|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|waṭ-ṭayru|ṣaaaffaat?|Kulluñ|q̣ad|ʻalima|ṣalaatahoo|wa-tasbeeḥah.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum|bimaa|yafʻaloon."
24,42,"Wa-lillaahi|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ!|wa-ʹilal|laahil|maṣeer."
24,43,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|yuzjee|saḥaabañ|s̤umma|yuʹallifu|baynahoo|s̤umma|yajʻaluhoo|rukaamañ|fataral|wadq̣a|yakhruju|min|khilaalih.|Wa-yunazzilu|minas|samaaaʹi|miñ|jibaaliñ|feehaa|mim|baradiñ|fayuṣeebu|bihee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaṣrifuhoo|ʻam|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Yakaadu|sanaa|barq̣ihee|yaẓhabu|bil-ʹabṣaar."
24,44,"Yuq̣allibul|laahul|layla|wannahaar:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʻibratal|liʹulil|ʹabṣaar!"
24,45,"Wallaahu|khalaq̣a|kulla|daaabbatim|mim|maaaʹ:|faminhum|mañy|yamshee|ʻalaa|baṭnih;|wa-minhum|mañy|yamshee|ʻalaa|rijlayn;|wa-minhum|mañy|yamshee|ʻalaaa|ʹarbaʻ.|Yakhluq̣ul|laahu|maa-|yashaaaʹ;|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
24,46,"Laq̣ad|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹAayaatim|mubayyinaat:|wallaahu|yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
24,47,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|wa-bir-Rasooli|wa-ʹaṭaʻnaa|s̤umma|yatawallaa|fareeq̣um|minhum|mim|baʻdi|ẓaalik:|wa-maaa|ʹulaaaʹika|bil-Muʹmineen."
24,48,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|duʻooo|ʹilal|laahi|wa-Rasoolihee|liyaḥkuma|baynahum|ʹiẓaa|fareeq̣um|minhum|muʻriḍoon."
24,49,"Wa-ʹiñy|yakul|lahumul|ḥaq̣q̣u|yaʹtooo|ʹilayhi|muẓʻineen."
24,50,"ʹAfee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍun|ʹamir|taabooo|ʹam|yakhaafoona|ʹañy|yaḥeefal|laahu|ʻalayhim|wa-Rasooluh?|Bal|ʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
24,51,"ʹInnamaa|kaana|q̣awlal|Muʹmineena|ʹiẓaa|duʻooo|ʹilal|laahi|wa-Rasoolihee|liyaḥkuma|baynahum|añy|yaq̣ooloo|˹Samiʻnaa|wa-ʹaṭaʻnaa:˺|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
24,52,"Wa-mañy|yuṭiʻil|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wa-yakhshal|laaha|wa-yattaq̣hi|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|Faaaʹizoon."
24,53,"Wa-ʹaq̣samoo|billaahi|jahda|ʹaymaanihim|laʹin|ʹamartahum|layakhrujunn.|Q̣ul|laa-|tuq̣simoo;|ṭaaʻatum|maʻroofah;|ʹinnal|laaha|khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
24,54,"Q̣ul|ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻur|Rasool:|faʹiñ|tawallaw|faʹinnamaa|ʻalayhi|maa-|ḥummila|wa-ʻalaykum|maa|ḥummiltum.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuṭeeʻoohu|tahtadoo.|Wa-maa|ʻalar|Rasooli|ʹillal|Balaag̣ul|mubeen."
24,55,"Waʻadal|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|miñkum|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|layastakhlifannahum|fil|ʹarḍi|kamastakh|lafal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim:|wa-la-yumak-kinanna|lahum|deenahumul|laẓir|taḍaa|lahum|wa-la-yubaddi-lannahum|mim|baʻdi|khawfihim|ʹamnaa:|yaʻbudoonanee|laa-|yushrikoona|bee|shayʹaa.|Wa-mañ|kafara|baʻda|ẓaalika|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|fasiq̣oon."
24,56,"Wa-ʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaata|wa-ʹaṭeeʻur|Rasoola|laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
24,57,"Laa-|taḥsabannal|laẓeena|kafaroo|muʻjizeena|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-maʹwaahumun|Naar:|wa-labiʹsal|maṣeer!"
24,58,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|liyastaʹẓiñkumul|laẓeena|malakat|ʹaymaanukum|wallaẓeena|lam|yablug̣ul|ḥuluma|miñkum|s̤alaas̤a|marraat:|miñ|q̣abli|Ṣalaatil|fajri|waḥeena|taḍaʻoona|s̤iyaabakum|minaz̤̣|z̤̣aheerati|wa-mim|baʻdi|Ṣalaatil|ʻIshaaaʹ;|s̤alaas̤u|ʻawraatil|lakum:|Laysa|ʻalaykum|wa-laa|ʻalayhim|junaaḥum|baʻdahunn:|ṭawwaafoona|ʻalaykum|baʻḍukum|ʻalaa|baʻḍ:|kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakumul|ʹAayaat:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
24,59,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|balag̣al|ʹaṭfaalu|miñkumul|ḥu-lu-ma|fal-yastaʹẓinoo|kamas|taʹẓanal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim;|kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakum|ʹAayaatih:|wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
24,60,"Walq̣awaaʻidu|minan|nisaaaʹil|laatee|laa-|yarjoona|nikaahañ|falaysa|ʻalayhinna|junaaḥun|ʹañy|yaḍaʻna|s̤iyaabahunna|g̣ayra|mutabarrijaatim|bizeenah:|wa-ʹañy|yastaʻfifna|khayrul|lahunn:|wallaahu|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
24,61,"Laysa|ʻalal|ʹaʻmaa|ḥarajuñw|walaa|ʻalal|ʹaʻraji|ḥarajuñw|walaa|ʻalal|mareeḍi|ḥarajuñw|walaa|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusikum|ʹañ|taʹkuloo|mim|buyootikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʹaabaaaʹikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʹummahaatikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʹikhwaanikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʹakhawaatikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʹaʻmaamikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʻammaatikum|ʹaw|buyooti|ʹakhwaalikum|ʹaw|buyooti|khaalaatikum|ʹaw|maa-|malaktum|mafaatiḥahooo|ʹaw|ṣadeeq̣ikum:|laysa|ʻalaykum|junaaḥun|ʹañ|taʹkuloo|jameeʻan|ʹaw|ʹashtaataa.|Faʹiẓaa|dakhaltum̃|buyootañ|fasallimoo|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusikum|taḥiyyatam|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|mubaarakatañ|ṭayyibah.|Kaẓaalika|yubayyinul|laahu|lakumul|ʹAayati|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
24,62,"ʹInnamal|Muʹminoonal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-ʹiẓaa|kaanoo|maʻahoo|ʻalaaa|ʹamriñ|jaamiʻil|lam|yaẓhaboo|ḥattaa|yastaʹẓinooh:|ʹinnal|laẓeena|yastaʹẓinoonaka|ʹulaaaʹikal|laẓeena|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wa-Rasoolih;|faʹiẓas|taʹẓanooka|libaʻḍi|shaʹnihim|faʹẓal|limañ|shiʹta|minhum|wastag̣fir|lahumul|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
24,63,"Laa-|tajʻaloo|duʻaaaʹar|Rasooli|baynakum|kaduʻaaaʹi|baʻḍikum̃|baʻḍaa:|q̣ad|yaʻlamul|laahul|laẓeena|yatasallaloona|miñkum|liwaaẓaa:|fal-yaḥẓaril|laẓeena|yukhalifoona|ʻan|ʹamriheee|ʹañ|tuṣeebahum|fitnatun|ʹaw|yuṣeebahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
24,64,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Q̣ad|yaʻlamu|maaa|ʹañtum|ʻalayh:|wa-yawma|yurjaʻoona|ʹilayhi|fayunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|ʻamiloo:|wallaahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
25,1,"Tabaarakal|laẓee|nazzalal|Furq̣aana|ʻalaa|ʻAbdihee|liyakoona|lilʻaalameena|naẓeeraa;"
25,2,"ʹAllaẓee|lahoo|mulkus|samaawaati|walʹarḍi|wa-lam|yattakhiẓ|waladañw|walam|yakul|lahoo|shareekuñ|fil|mulki|wa-khalaq̣a|kulla|shayʹiñ|faq̣addarahoo|taq̣deeraa."
25,3,"Wattakhaẓoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹaalihatal|laa|yakhluq̣oona|shayʹañw|wahum|yukhlaq̣oona|wa-laa|yamlikoona|liʹañfusihim|ḍarrañw|walaa|nafʻañw|walaa|yamlikoona|Mawtañw|Walaa|Ḥayaatañw|Walaa|Nu-Shooraa."
25,4,"Wa-q̣aalal|laaẓeena|kafarooo|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹifkunif|taraahu|wa-ʹaʻaanahoo|ʻalayhi|q̣awmun|ʹaakharoona|faq̣ad|jaaaʹoo|z̤̣ulmañw|wazooraa."
25,5,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleenak|tatabahaa|fahiya|tumlaa|ʻalayhi|bukratañw|waʹaṣeelaa."
25,6,"Q̣ul|ʹañzalahul|laẓee|yaʻlamus|Sirra|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
25,7,"Wa-q̣aaloo|maa-li|haaẓar|Rasooli|yaʹkuluṭ|ṭaʻaama|wa-yamshee|fil|ʹaswaaq̣?|Law-Laaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilayhi|malakuñ|fayakoona|maʻahoo|naẓeeraa?"
25,8,"ʹAw|yulq̣aaa|ʹilayhi|kañzun|ʹaw|takoonu|lahoo|jannatuñy|yaʹkulu|minhaa?|Wa-q̣aalaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|ʹiñ|tattabiʻoona|ʹillaa|rajulam|mas-ḥooraa."
25,9,"ʹUñz̤̣ur|kayfa|ḍaraboo|lakal|ʹams̤aala|faḍalloo|falaa|yastaṭeeʻoona|sabeelaa!"
25,10,"Tabaarakal|laẓeee|ʹiñ|shaaaʹa|jaʻala|laka|khayram|miñ|ẓaalika|Jannaatin|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|wa-yajʻal|laka|Q̣uṣooraa."
25,11,"Bal|kaẓẓaboo|bis-Saaʻati|wa-ʹaʻtadnaa|limañ|kaẓẓaba|bis-Saaʻati|Saʻeeraa:"
25,12,"ʹIẓaa|raʹathum|mim|makaanim|baʻeediñ|samiʻoo|lahaa|tag̣ayyuz̤̣añw|wazafeeraa."
25,13,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹulq̣oo|minhaa|makaanañ|ḍayyiq̣am|muq̣arraneena|daʻaw|hunaalika|s̤ubooraa!"
25,14,"Laa-|tadʻul|yawma|s̤uboorañw|waaḥidañw|wadʻoo|s̤uboorañ|kas̤eeraa!"
25,15,"Q̣ul|ʹaẓaalika|khayrun|ʹam|jannatul|khuldil|latee|wuʻidal|Muttaq̣oon?|Kaanat|lahum|jazaaaʹañw|wamaseeraa."
25,16,"Lahum|feehaa|maa-|yashaaaʹoona|khaalideen:|kaana|ʻalaa|Rabbika|waʻdam|masʹoolaa."
25,17,"Wa-Yawma|yaḥshuruhum|wa-maa|yaʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|fayaq̣oolu|ʹAʹañtum|ʹaḍlaltum|ʻibaadee|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹam|hum|ḍallus|Sabeel?˺"
25,18,"Q̣aaloo|˹Subḥaanaka|maa-|kaana|yambag̣ee|lanaaa|ʹan|nattakhiẓa|miñ|doonika|min|ʹawliyaaaʹa|wa-laakim|mattaʻtahum|wa-ʹaabaaaʹahum|ḥattaa|nasuẓ|Ẓikr:|wa-kaanoo|q̣awmam|booraa."
25,19,"Faq̣ad|kaẓẓabookum̃|bimaa|taq̣ooloona|famaa|tastaṭeeʻoona|ṣarfañw|walaa|naṣraa.|Wa-mañy|yaz̤̣lim|miñkum|nuẓiq̣hu|ʻAẓaabañ|kabeeraa."
25,20,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|q̣ablaka|minal|mursaleena|ʹillaaa|ʹinnahum|layaʹkuloonaṭ|ṭaʻaama|wa-yamshoona|fil|ʹaswaaq̣:|wa-jaʻalnaa|baʻḍakum|libaʻḍiñ|fitnah:|ʹataṣbiroon?|Wa-kaana|Rabbuka|Baṣeeraa."
25,21,"Waq̣aalal|laẓeena|laa-|yarjoona|Liq̣aaaʹanaa|Law-laaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalaynal|malaaaʹikatu|ʹaw|naraa|Rabbanaa?|Laq̣adis|takbaroo|feee|ʹañfusihim|wa-ʻataw|ʻutuwwañ|kabeeraa!"
25,22,"Yawma|yarawnal|malaaaʹikata|laa-|bushraa|Yawmaʹiẓil|lil-mujrimeena|wa-yaq̣ooloona|ḥijram|maḥjooraa!"
25,23,"Wa-q̣adimnaaa|ʹilaa|maa-|ʻamiloo|min|ʻamaliñ|fajaʻalnaahu|habaaaʹam|mañs̤ooraa."
25,24,"ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannati|Yawmaʹiẓin|khayrum|mustaq̣arrañw|waʹaḥsanu|maq̣eelaa."
25,25,"Wa-Yawma|tashaq̣q̣aq̣us|samaaaʹu|bilg̣amaami|wa-nuzzilal|malaaaʹikatu|tañzeelaa,"
25,26,"ʹAlmulku|Yawmaʹiẓinil|ḥaq̣q̣u|lir-Raḥmaan:|wa-kaana|Yawman|ʻalal|kaafireena|ʻaseeraa."
25,27,"Wa-Yawma|yaʻaḍḍuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimu|ʻalaa|yadayhi|yaq̣oolu|yaa-laytanit|takhaẓtu|maʻar|Rasooli|sabeelaa!"
25,28,"Yaa-waylataa|laytanee|lam|ʹattakhiẓ|fulaanan|khaleelaa!"
25,29,"Laq̣ad|ʹaḍallanee|ʻaniẓ|Ẓikri|baʻda|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹanee!|Wa-kaanash|Shayṭaanu|lil-ʹiñsaani|khaẓoolaa!"
25,30,"Wa-q̣aalar|Rasoolu|yaa-Rabbi|ʹinna|q̣awmit|takhaẓoo|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaana|mahjooraa."
25,31,"Wa-kaẓaalika|jaʻalnaa|likulli|nabiyyin|ʻaduwwam|minal|mujrimeen:|wa-kafaa|bi-Rabbika|Haadiyañw|Wa-Naṣeeraa."
25,32,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|law-laa|nuzzila|ʻalayhil|Q̣urʹaanu|jumlatañw|Waaḥidah?|Kaẓaalika|linus̤abbita|bihee|fuʹaadaka|wa-rattalnaahu|tarteelaa."
25,33,"Wa-laa|yaʹtoonaka|bimas̤alin|ʹillaa|jiʹnaaka|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹaḥsana|tafseeraa."
25,34,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuḥsharoona|ʻalaa|wujoohihim|ʹilaa|Jahannama|ʹulaaaʹika|sharrum|makanañw|waʹaḍallu|Sabeelaa."
25,35,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|wa-jaʻalnaa|maʻahooo|ʹakhaahu|Haaroona|Wazeeraa;"
25,36,"Faq̣ulnaẓ|habaaa|ʹilal|q̣awmil|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa:|fadammarnaahum|tadmeeraa."
25,37,"Wa-q̣awma|Nooḥil|lammaa|kaẓẓabur|rusula|ʹag̣raq̣naahum|wa-jaʻalnaahum|linnaasi|ʹAayah;|wa-ʹaʻtadnaa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|ʻAẓaaban|ʹaleemaa;"
25,38,"Wa-ʻAadañw|Wa-S̤amooda|wa-ʹAṣḥaabar|Rassi|wa-q̣uroonam|bayna|ẓaalika|kas̤eeraa."
25,39,"Wa-kullañ|ḍarabnaa|lahul|ʹams̤aala|wa-kullañ|tabbarnaa|tatbeeraa."
25,40,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹataw|ʻalal|q̣aryatil|lateee|ʹumṭirat|maṭaras|sawʹ:|ʹafalam|yakoonoo|yarawnahaa?|Bal|kaanoo|laa-|yarjoona|Nushooraa."
25,41,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|raʹawka|ʹiñy|yattakhiẓoonaka|illaa|huzuwaa:˹|ʹahaaẓal|laẓee|baʻas̤al|laahu|rasoolaa?"
25,42,"ʹIñ|kaada|layuḍillunaa|ʻan|ʹaalihatinaa|Law-laaa|ʹañ|ṣabarnaa|ʻalayhaa!˺|Wa-sawfa|yaʻlamoona|ḥeena|yarawnal|ʻAẓaaba|man|ʹaḍallu|Sabeelaa!"
25,43,"ʹAraʹayta|manit|takhaẓa|ʹilaahahoo|hawaah?|ʹA-faʹañta|takoonu|ʻalayhi|wakeelaa?"
25,44,"ʹAm|taḥsabu|ʹanna|ʹaks̤arahum|yasmaʻoona|ʹaw|yaʻq̣iloon?|ʹIn|hum|ʹillaa|kal-ʹanʻaami|bal|hum|ʹaḍallu|Sabeelaa."
25,45,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilaa|Rabbika|kayfa|maddaz̤̣-|Z̤̣ill!|Wa-law|shaaaʹa|lajaʻalahoo|saakinaa!|S̤umma|jaʻalnash|shamsa|ʻalayhi|daleelaa;"
25,46,"S̤umma|q̣abaḍnaahu|ʹilaynaa|q̣abḍañy|yaseeraa."
25,47,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|Layla|libaasañw|wan-Nawma|subaatañw|wajaʻalan|Nahaara|Nushooraa."
25,48,"Wa-Huwal|laẓeee|ʹarsalar|Riyaaḥa|bushram|bayna|yaday|Raḥmatih,|wa-ʹañzalnaa|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|ṭahooraa,"
25,49,"Linuḥyiya|bihee|baldatam|maytañw|wanusq̣iyahoo|mimmaa|khalaq̣naaa|ʹanʻaamañw|Waʹanaasiyya|kas̤eeraa."
25,50,"Wa-laq̣ad|ṣarrafnaahu|baynahum|liyaẓẓakkaroo,|faʹabaaa|ʹaks̤arun|naasi|ʹillaa|kufooraa."
25,51,"Wa-law|shiʹnaa|labaʻas̤naa|fee|kulli|q̣aryatin|naẓeeraa."
25,52,"Falaa|tuṭiʻil|kaafireena|wa-jaahidhum̃|bihee|jihaadañ|kabeeraa."
25,53,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|marajal|baḥrayni|haaẓaa|ʻaẓbuñ|furaatuñw|wahaaẓaa|milḥun|ʹujaaj;|wa-jaʻala|baynahumaa|Barzakhañw|Waḥijram|maḥjooraa."
25,54,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣a|minal|maaaʹi|basharañ|fajaʻalahoo|nasabañw|waṣihraa:|wa-kaana|Rabbuka|Q̣adeeraa."
25,55,"Wa-yaʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|maa|laa-|yañfaʻuhum|wa-laa|yaḍurruhum:|wa-kaanal|kaafiru|ʻalaa|Rabbihee|z̤̣aheeraa!"
25,56,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʹillaa|mubashshirañw|wanaẓeeraa."
25,57,"Q̣ul|maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajrin|ʹillaa|mañ|shaaaʹa|ʹañy|yattakhiẓa|ʹilaa|Rabbihee|Sabeelaa."
25,58,"Wa-tawakkal|ʻalal|Ḥayyil|laẓee|laa-|yamootu|wa-sabbiḥ|bi-Ḥamdih;|wa-kafaa|bihee|biẓunoobi|ʻibaadihee|khabeeraa;"
25,59,"ʹAllaẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaa|fee|sittati|ʹayyaamiñ|s̤umma|stawaa|ʻalal|ʻArsh,|ʹAr-Raḥmaanu|fasʹal|bihee|khabeeraa."
25,60,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahumus|judoo|lir-Raḥmaani|q̣aaloo|wa-mar|Raḥmaan?|ʹAnasjudu|limaa|taʹmurunaa|wa-zaadahum|nufooraa."
25,61,"Tabaarakal|laẓee|jaʻala|fis|samaaaʹi|Buroojañw|Wajaʻala|feehaa|siraajañw|waq̣amaram|muneeraa!"
25,62,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|jaʻalal|layla|wannahaara|khilfatal|liman|ʹaraada|ʹañy|yaẓẓakkara|aw|ʹaraada|shukooraa."
25,63,"Wa-ʻibaadur|Raḥmaanil|laẓeena|yamshoona|ʻalal|ʹarḍi|hawnañw|waʹiẓaa|khaaṭabahumul|jaahiloona|q̣aaloo|˹Salaamaa!˺"
25,64,"Wallaẓeena|yabeetoona|li-Rabbihim|sujjadañw|waq̣iyaamaa;"
25,65,"Wallaẓeena|yaq̣ooloona|Rabbanaṣ|rif|ʻannaa|ʻAẓaaba|Jahannama|ʹinna|ʻAẓaabahaa|kaana|g̣araamaa,"
25,66,"ʹInnahaa|saaaʹat|mustaq̣arrañw|wamuq̣aamaa."
25,67,"Wallaẓeena|ʹiẓaaa|ʹañfaq̣oo|lam|yusrifoo|wa-lam|yaq̣turoo|wa-kaana|bayna|ẓaalika|q̣awaamaa."
25,68,"Wallaẓeena|laa-|yadʻoona|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhara|wa-laa|yaq̣tuloonan|nafsal|latee|ḥarramal|laahu|ʹillaa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laa|yaznoon;|wa-mañy|yafʻal|ẓaalika|yalq̣a|ʹas̤aamaa,"
25,69,"Yuḍaaʻaf|lahul|ʻAẓaabu|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|wa-yakhlud|feehee|muhaanaa,"
25,70,"ʹIllaa|mañ|taaba|wa-ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ʻamalañ|ṣaaliḥañ|faʹulaaaʹika|yubaddilul|laahu|sayyiʹaatihim|ḥasanaat:|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
25,71,"Wa-mañ|taaba|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|faʹinnahoo|yatoobu|ʹilal|laahi|mataabaa."
25,72,"Wallaẓeena|laa-|yashhadoonaz|zoora|wa-ʹiẓaa|marroo|billag̣wi|marroo|kiraamaa."
25,73,"Wallaẓeena|ʹiẓaa|ẓukkiroo|biʹAayaati|Rabbihim|lam|yakhirroo|ʻalayhaa|ṣummañw|waʻumyaanaa."
25,74,"Wallaẓeena|yaq̣ooloona|Rabbanaa|hab|lanaa|min|ʹazwaajinaa|wa-ẓurriyaatinaa|q̣urrata|ʹaʻyuniñw|waj-ʻalnaa|lil-Muttaq̣eena|ʹImaamaa."
25,75,"ʹUlaaaʹika|yujzawnal|g̣urfata|bimaa|ṣabaroo|wa-yulaq̣q̣awna|feehaa|taḥiyyatañw|wasalaamaa,"
25,76,"Khaalideena|feehaa;|ḥasunat|mustaq̣arrañw|wamuq̣aamaa!"
25,77,"Q̣ul|maa-|yaʻbaʹu|bikum|Rabbee|Law-laa|duʻaaaʹukum:|faq̣ad|kaẓẓabtum|fasawfa|yakoonu|lizaamaa!"
26,1,"Ṭaa-Seeen-Meeem."
26,2,"Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Kitaabil|mubeen."
26,3,"Laʻallaka|baakhiʻun|nafsaka|ʹallaa|yakoonoo|Muʹmineen."
26,4,"ʹIn|nashaʹ|nunazzil|ʻalayhim|minas|samaaaʹi|ʹAayatañ|faz̤̣allat|ʹaʻnaaq̣uhum|lahaa|khaaḍiʻeen."
26,5,"Wa-maa|yaʹteehim|miñ|Ẓikrim|minar|Raḥmaani|muḥdas̤in|ʹillaa|kaanoo|ʻanhu|muʻriḍeen."
26,6,"Faq̣ad|kaẓẓaboo|fasayaʹteehim|ʹambaaaʹu|maa-|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon!"
26,7,"ʹA-walam|yaraw|ʹilal|ʹarḍi|kam|ʹambatnaa|feehaa|miñ|kulli|zawjiñ|kareem?"
26,8,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,9,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,10,"Wa-ʹiẓ|naadaa|Rabbuka|Moosaaa|ʹaniʹ|til|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen,"
26,11,"Q̣awma|Firʻawn:|ʹalaa|yattaq̣oon?"
26,12,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yukaẓẓiboon:"
26,13,"Wa-yaḍeeq̣u|ṣadree|wa-laa|yañṭaliq̣u|lisaanee|faʹarsil|ʹilaa|Haaroon."
26,14,"Wa-lahum|ʻalayya|ẓambuñ|faʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yaq̣tuloon."
26,15,"Q̣aala|kallaa!|faẓhabaa|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹinnaa|maʻakum|mustamiʻoon."
26,16,"Faʹtiyaa|Firʻawna|faq̣oolaaa|ʹinnaa|Rasoolu|Rabbil|ʻaalameen,"
26,17,"ʹAn|ʹarsil|maʻanaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel."
26,18,"Q̣aala|ʹalam|nurabbika|feenaa|waleedañw|walabis̤ta|feenaa|min|ʻumurika|sineen?"
26,19,"Wa-faʻalta|faʻlatakal|latee|faʻalta|wa-ʹañta|minal|kaafireen!"
26,20,"Q̣aala|faʻaltuhaaa|ʹiẓañw|Waʹana|minaḍ|ḍaaalleen."
26,21,"Fafarartu|miñkum|lam-maa|khiftukum|fawahaba|lee|Rabbee|ḥukmañw|wajaʻalanee|minal|mursaleen."
26,22,"Wa-tilka|niʻmatuñ|tamunnuhaa|ʻalayya|ʹan|ʻabbatta|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel!"
26,23,"Q̣aala|Firʻawnu|wa-maa|Rabbul|ʻaalameen?"
26,24,"Q̣aala|Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa,|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Mooq̣ineen."
26,25,"Q̣aala|liman|ḥawlahooo|ʹalaa|tastamiʻoon?"
26,26,"Q̣aala|Rabbukum|wa-Rabbu|ʹaabaaaʹikumul|ʹawwaleen!"
26,27,"Q̣aala|ʹinna|rasoolakumul|laẓeee|ʹursila|ʹilaykum|lamajnoon!"
26,28,"Q̣aala|Rabbul|mashriq̣i|wal-mag̣ribi|wa-maa|baynahumaa!|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻq̣iloon!"
26,29,"Q̣aala|laʹinit|takhaẓta|ʹilaahan|g̣ayree|laʹajʻalannaka|minal|masjooneen!"
26,30,"Q̣aala|ʹawalaw|jiʹtuka|bishayʹim|mubeen?"
26,31,"Q̣aala|faʹti|biheee|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een!"
26,32,"Faʹalq̣aa|ʻaṣaahu|faʹiẓaa|hiya|s̤uʻbaanum|mubeen!"
26,33,"Wa-nazaʻa|yadahoo|faʹiẓaa|hiya|bayḍaaaʹu|linnaaz̤̣ireen!"
26,34,"Q̣aala|lilmalaʹi|ḥawlahooo|ʹinna|haazaa|lasaaḥirun|ʻaleem:"
26,35,"Yureedu|ʹañy|yukhrijakum|min|ʹarḍikum̃|bisiḥrihee|famaaẓaa|taʹmuroon?"
26,36,"Q̣aalooo|ʹarjih|wa-ʹakhaahu|wabʻas̤|fil|Madaaaʹini|ḥaashireen―"
26,37,"Yaʹtooka|bikulli|saḥ-ḥaarin|ʻaleem."
26,38,"Fajumiʻas|saḥaratu|limeeq̣aati|Yawmim|maʻloom,"
26,39,"Wa-q̣eela|linnaasi|hal|ʹañtum|mujtamiʻoon,"
26,40,"Laʻallanaa|nattabiʻus|saḥarata|ʹiñ|kaanoo|humul|g̣aalibeen?"
26,41,"Falammaa|jaaaʹas|saḥaratu|q̣aaloo|li-Firʻawna|ʹaʹinna|lanaa|laʹajran|ʹiñ|kunnaa|naḥnul|g̣aalibeen?"
26,42,"Q̣aala|naʻam|wa-ʹinnakum|ʹiẓal|laminal|muq̣arrabeen."
26,43,"Q̣aala|lahum|Moosaaa|ʹalq̣oo|maaa|ʹañtum|mulq̣oon!"
26,44,"Faʹalq̣aw|ḥibaalahum|wa-ʻiṣiyyahum|wa-q̣aaloo|biʻizzati|Firʻawna|ʹinnaa|lanaḥnul|g̣aaliboon!"
26,45,"Faʹalq̣aa|Moosaa|ʻaṣaahu|faʹiẓaa|hiya|talq̣afu|maa-|yaʹfikoon!"
26,46,"Faʹulq̣iyas|saḥaratu|saajideen."
26,47,"Q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|bi-Rabbil|ʻaalameen."
26,48,"Rabbi|Moosaa|wa-Haaroon."
26,49,"Q̣aala|ʹaamañtum|lahoo|q̣abla|ʹan|ʹaaẓana|lakum?|ʹInnahoo|lakabeerukumul|laẓee|ʻallamakumus|siḥr!|Falasawfa|taʻlamoon!|Laʹuq̣aṭṭiʻanna|ʹaydiyakum|wa-ʹarjulakum|min|khilaafiñw|walaʹuṣallibannakum|ʹajmaʻeen!"
26,50,"Q̣aaloo|laa-|ḍayra|ʹinnaaa|ʹilaa|Rabbinaa|muñq̣aliboon!"
26,51,"ʹInnaa|naṭmaʻu|ʹañy|yag̣fira|lanaa|Rabbunaa|khaṭaayaanaaa|ʹañ|kunnaaa|ʹawwalal|Muʹmineen!"
26,52,"Wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosaaa|ʹan|ʹasri|biʻibaadeee|ʹinnakum|muttabaʻoon."
26,53,"Faʹarsala|Firʻawnu|fil|Madaaaʹini|ḥaashireen."
26,54,"ʹInna|haaaʹulaaaʹi|lashirẓimatuñ|q̣aleeloon,"
26,55,"Wa-ʹinnahum|lanaa|lag̣aaaʹiz̤̣oon;"
26,56,"Wa-ʹinnaa|lajameeʻun|ḥaaẓiroon."
26,57,"Faʹakhrajnaahum|miñ|jannaatiñw|waʻuyoon,"
26,58,"Wa-kunooziñw|Wamaq̣aamiñ|kareem;"
26,59,"Kaẓaalik:|wa-ʹawras̤naahaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel."
26,60,"Faʹatbaʻoohum|mushriq̣een."
26,61,"Faalammaa|taraaaʹal|jamʻaani|q̣aala|ʹAṣḥaabu|Moosaaa|ʹinnaa|lamudrakoon."
26,62,"Q̣aala|kallaa!|ʹInna|maʻiya|Rabbee|sayahdeen!"
26,63,"Faʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosaaa|ʹaniḍ|rib|biʻaṣaakal|baḥr.|Fañfalaq̣a|fakaana|kullu|firq̣iñ|kaṭṭawdil|ʻaz̤̣eem."
26,64,"Wa-ʹazlafnaa|s̤ammal|ʹaakhareen."
26,65,"Wa-ʹañjaynaa|Moosaa|wa-mam|maʻahooo|ʹajmaʻeen;"
26,66,"S̤umma|ʹag̣raq̣nal|ʹaakhareen."
26,67,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,68,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,69,"Watlu|ʻalayhim|nabaʹa|ʹIbraaheem."
26,70,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|liʹabeehi|wa-q̣awmihee|maa-|taʻbudoon?"
26,71,"Q̣aaloo|naʻbudu|ʹaṣnaamañ|fanaz̤̣allu|lahaa|ʻaakifeen."
26,72,"Q̣aala|hal|yasmaʻoonakum|ʹiẓ|tadʻoon."
26,73,"ʹAw|yañfaʻoonakum|ʹaw|yaḍurroon?"
26,74,"Q̣aaloo|bal|wajadnaaa|ʹaabaaaʹanaa|kaẓaalika|yafʻaloon."
26,75,"Q̣aala|ʹafaraʹaytum|maa|kuñtum|taʻbudoon,"
26,76,"ʹAñtum|wa-ʹaabaaaʹukumul|ʹaq̣damoon,"
26,77,"Faʹinnahum|ʻaduwwul|leee|ʹillaa|Rabbal|ʻaalameen;"
26,78,"ʹAllaẓee|khalaq̣anee|fa-Huwa|yahdeen;"
26,79,"Wallaẓee|Huwa|yuṭʻimunee|wa-yasq̣een,"
26,80,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|mariḍtu|fa-Huwa|yashfeen:"
26,81,"wallaẓee|yumeetunee|s̤umma|yuḥyeen;"
26,82,"Wallaẓeee|ʹaṭmaʻu|añy|yag̣fira|lee|khaṭeeeʹatee|Yawmad|Deen..."
26,83,"Rabbi|hab|lee|ḥukmañw|waʹalḥiq̣nee|biṣ-Ṣaaliḥeen;"
26,84,"Wajʻal|lee|lisaana|ṣidq̣iñ|fil|ʹaakhireen;"
26,85,"Wajʻalnee|miñw|waras̤ati|Jannatin|Naʻeem."
26,86,"Wag̣fir|liʹabeee|ʹinnahoo|kaana|minaḍ|ḍaaalleen;"
26,87,"Wa-laa|tukhzinee|Yawma|yubʻas̤oon;"
26,88,"Yawma|laa-|yañfaʻu|maaluñw|walaa|banoon,"
26,89,"Illaa|man|ʹatal|laaha|biq̣albiñ|saleem."
26,90,"Wa-ʹuzlifatil|Jannatu|lil-Muttaq̣een,"
26,91,"Wa-burrizatil|Jaḥeemu|lilg̣aaween;"
26,92,"Wa-q̣eela|lahum|ʹayna|maa-|kuñtum|taʻbudoon."
26,93,"Miñ|doonil|laah?|Hal|yañṣuroonakum|ʹaw|yañtaṣiroon?"
26,94,"Fakubkiboo|feehaa|hum|walg̣aawoon,"
26,95,"Wa-junoodu|ʹIbleesa|ʹajmaʻoon."
26,96,"Q̣aaloo|wa-hum|feehaa|yakhtaṣimoon;"
26,97,"Tallaahi|ʹiñ|kunnaa|lafee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
26,98,"ʹIẓ|nusawweekum̃|bi-Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
26,99,"Wa-maaa|ʹaḍallanaaa|ʹillal|mujrimoon."
26,100,"Famaa|lanaa|miñ|shaafiʻeen,"
26,101,"Wa-laa|ṣadeeq̣in|ḥameem."
26,102,"Falaw|ʹanna|lanaa|karratañ|fanakoona|minal|Muʹmineen!"
26,103,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,104,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,105,"Kaẓẓabat|q̣awmu|Nooḥinil|mursaleen."
26,106,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|lahum|ʹakhoohum|Nooḥun|ʹalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
26,107,"ʹInnee|lakum|rasoolun|ʹameen:"
26,108,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,109,"Wa-maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajr;|ʹin|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
26,110,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,111,"Q̣aalooo|ʹanuʹminu|laka|wattabaʻakal|ʹarẓaloon?"
26,112,"Q̣aala|wa-maa|ʻilmee|Bimaa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon?"
26,113,"ʹIn|ḥisaabuhum|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|Rabbee|law|tashʻuroon."
26,114,"Wa-maaa|ʹana|biṭaaridil|Muʹmineen."
26,115,"In|ʹana|ʹillaa|mubeen.|naẓeerum"
26,116,"Q̣aaloo|laʹil|lam|tañtahi|yaa-Nooḥu|latakoonanna|minal|marjoomeen."
26,117,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinna|q̣awmee|kaẓẓaboon."
26,118,"Faftaḥ|baynee|wa-baynahum|fat-hañw|wanajjinee|wa-mam|maʻiya|minal|Muʹmineen."
26,119,"Faʹañjaynaahu|wa-mam|maʻahoo|fil|fulkil|mashḥoon."
26,120,"S̤umma|ʹag̣raq̣naa|baʻdul|baaq̣een."
26,121,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah;|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,122,"Wa-ʹInna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,123,"Kaẓẓabat|ʻAadunil|mursaleen,"
26,124,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|lahum|ʹakhoohum|Hoodun|ʹalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
26,125,"ʹInnee|lakum|rasoolun|ʹameen."
26,126,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,127,"Wa-maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajr;|ʹin|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
26,128,"ʹAtabnoona|bikulli|reeʻin|ʹaayatañ|taʻbas̤oon?"
26,129,"Wa-tattakhiẓoona|maṣaaniʻa|laʻallakum|takhludoon?"
26,130,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|baṭashtum̃|baṭashtum|jabbaareen?"
26,131,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,132,"Wattaq̣ul|laẓeee|ʹamaddakum̃|bimaa|taʻlamoon."
26,133,"ʹAmaddakum̃|biʹanʻaamiñw|wabaneen,"
26,134,"Wa-jannaatiñw|Waʻuyoon."
26,135,"ʹInneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|ʻAẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻaz̤̣eem."
26,136,"Q̣aaloo|sawaaaʹun|ʻalaynaaa|ʹa-waʻaz̤̣ta|ʹam|lam|takum|minal|waaʻiz̤̣een!"
26,137,"ʹIn|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|khuluq̣ul|ʹawwaleen,"
26,138,"Wa-maa|naḥnu|bimuʻaẓẓabeen!"
26,139,"Fakaẓẓaboohu|faʹahlaknaahum.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,140,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,141,"Kaẓẓabat|s̤amoodul|mursaleen."
26,142,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|lahum|ʹakhoohum|Ṣaaliḥun|ʹalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
26,143,"ʹInnee|lakum|rasoolun|ʹameen."
26,144,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,145,"Wa-maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajr:|ʹin|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
26,146,"ʹAtutrakoona|Fee|maa-|haahunaaa|ʹaamineen,"
26,147,"Fee|jannaatiñw|waʻuyoon,"
26,148,"Wa-zurooʻiñw|Wanakhliñ|ṭal-ʻuhaa|haḍeem?"
26,149,"Wa-tanḥitoona|minal|jibaali|buyootañ|faariheen?"
26,150,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon;"
26,151,"Wa-laa|tuṭeeʻooo|ʹamral|musrifeen,"
26,152,"ʹAllaẓeena|yufsidoona|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|yuṣliḥoon."
26,153,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnamaaa|ʹañta|minal|musaḥḥareen!"
26,154,"Maaa|ʹañta|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lunaa:|faʹti|biʹAayatin|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|Ṣaadiq̣een!"
26,155,"Q̣aala|haẓihee|naaq̣atul|lahaa|shirbuñw|walakum|shirbu|yawmim|maʻloom."
26,156,"Walaa|tamassoohaa|bisoooʹiñ|fayaʹkhuẓakum|ʻAẓaabu|yawmin|ʻaz̤̣eem."
26,157,"Faʻaq̣aroohaa|faʹaṣbaḥoo|naadimeen."
26,158,"Faʹakhaẓahumul|ʻAẓaab.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,159,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʹAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,160,"Kaẓẓabat|q̣awmu|Looṭinil|mursaleen."
