26,163,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,164,"Wa-maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajr:|ʹIn|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
