26,172,"S̤umma|dammarnal|ʹaakhareen."
26,173,"Wa-ʹamṭarnaa|ʻalayhim|maṭaraa:|fasaaaʹa|maṭarul|muñẓareen!"
26,174,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,175,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,176,"Kaẓẓaba|ʹAṣḥaabul|ʹAykatil|mursaleen."
26,177,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|lahum|Shuʻaybun|ʹalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
26,178,"ʹInnee|lakum|rasoolun|ʹameen."
26,179,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
26,180,"Wa-maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajr:|ʹin|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalaa|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
26,181,"ʹAwful|kayla|wa-laa|takoonoo|minal|mukhsireen."
26,182,"Wazinoo|bilq̣isṭaasil|mustaq̣eem."
26,183,"Wa-laa|tabkhasun|naasa|ʹashyaaaʹahum|wa-laa|taʻs̤aw|fil|ʹarḍi|mufsideen."
26,184,"Wattaq̣ul|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|waljibillatal|ʹawwaleen."
26,185,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnamaaa|ʹañta|minal|musaḥḥareen!"
26,186,"Wa-maaa|ʹañta|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lunaa|wa-ʹin|naz̤̣unnuka|laminal|kaaẓibeen!"
26,187,"Faʹasq̣iṭ|ʻalaynaa|kisafam|minas|samaaaʹi|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een!"
26,188,"Q̣aala|Rabbeee|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
26,189,"Fakaẓẓaboohu|faʹakhaẓahum|ʻaẓaabu|Yawmiz̤̣|z̤̣ullah:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|ʻaẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻAz̤̣eem."
26,190,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayah:|wa-maa|kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|Muʹmineen."
26,191,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
26,192,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|la-Tañzeelu|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
26,193,"Nazala|bihir|Rooḥul|ʹAmeen."
26,194,"ʻAlaa|q̣albika|litakoona|minal|muñẓireen."
26,195,"Bilisaanin|ʻArabiyyim|mubeen."
26,196,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|lafee|Zuburil|ʹawwaleen."
26,197,"ʹAwalam|yakul|lahum|ʹAayatan|ʹañy|yaʻlamahoo|ʻulamaaaʹu|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel?"
26,198,"Wa-law|nazzalnaahu|ʻalaa|baʻḍil|ʹaʻjameen,"
26,199,"Faq̣araʹahoo|ʻalayhim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|muʹmineen."
26,200,"Kaẓaalika|salaknaahu|fee|q̣uloobil|mujrimeen."
26,201,"Laa-|yuʹminoona|bihee|ḥattaa|yarawul|ʻaẓabal|ʹaleem;"
26,202,"Fayaʹtiyahum̃|bag̣tatañw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon."
26,203,"Fayaq̣ooloo|hal|naḥnu|muñz̤̣aroon."
26,204,"ʹAfabiʻaẓaabinaa|yastaʻjiloon?"
26,205,"ʹAfaraʹayta|ʹim|mattaʻnaahum|sineen."
26,206,"S̤umma|jaaaʹahum|maa|kaanoo|yooʻadoon!"
26,207,"Maaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yumattaʻoon!"
26,208,"Wa-maaa|ʹahlaknaa|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʹillaa|lahaa|muñẓiroon."
26,209,"Ẓikraa|wa-maa|kunnaa|z̤̣aalimeen."
26,210,"Wa-maa|tanazzalat|bihish|shayaaṭeen;"
26,211,"Wa-maa|yambag̣ee|lahum|wa-maa|yastaṭeeʻoon."
26,212,"ʹInnahum|ʻanis|samʻi|lamaʻzooloon."
26,213,"Falaa|tadʻu|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhara|fatakoona|minal|muʻaẓẓabeen."
26,214,"Wa-ʹañẓir|ʻasheeratakal|ʹaq̣rabeen,"
26,215,"Wakhfiḍ|janaaḥaka|limanit|tabaʻaka|minal|Muʹmineen."
26,216,"Faʹin|ʻaṣawka|faq̣ul|ʹinnee|bareeeʹum|mimmaa|taʻmaloon!"
26,217,"Wa-tawakkal|ʻalal|ʻAzeezir|Raḥeem."
26,218,"ʹAllaẓee|yaraaka|ḥeena|taq̣oom,"
26,219,"Wa-taq̣allubaka|fis|saajideen."
26,220,"ʹInnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
26,221,"Hal|ʹunabbiʹukum|ʻalaa|mañ|tanazzalush|shayaaṭeen?"
26,222,"Tanazzalu|ʻalaa|kulli|ʹaffaakin|ʹas̤eem,"
26,223,"Yulq̣oonas|samʻa|wa-ʹaks̤aruhum|kaaẓiboon."
26,224,"Washshuʻaraaaʹu|yattabiʻuhumul|g̣aawoon:"
26,225,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannahum|fee|kulli|waadiñy|yaheemoon."
26,226,"Wa-ʹannahum|yaq̣ooloona|maa|laa-|yafʻaloon?"
26,227,"ʹIllal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|waẓakarul|laaha|kas̤eerañw|wañtaṣaroo|mim|baʻdi|maa-|z̤̣ulimoo.|Wa-sayaʻlamul|laz̤̣eena|z̤̣alamooo|ʹayya|muñq̣alabiñy|yañq̣aliboon!"
27,1,"Ṭaa-Seeen.|Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Q̣ur-ʹaani|wa-kitaabim|mubeen;"
27,2,"Hudañw|Wa-Bushraa|lil-Muʹmineen,"
27,3,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuq̣eemoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-yuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wa-hum̃|bil-ʹAakhirati|hum|yooq̣inoon."
27,4,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|Zayyannaa|lahum|ʹaʻmaalahum|fahum|yaʻmahoon."
27,5,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|lahum|soooʹul|ʻaẓaabi|wa-hum|fil|ʹAakhirati|humul|ʹakhsaroon."
27,6,"Wa-ʹinnaka|latulaq̣q̣al|Q̣ur-ʹaana|mil|ladun|Ḥakeemin|ʻAleem."
27,7,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|liʹahliheee|ʹinneee|ʹaanastu|naaraa;|saʹaateekum|minhaa|bikhabarin|ʹaw|ʹaateekum̃|bishihaabiñ|q̣abasil|laʻallakum|taṣṭaloon."
27,8,"Falammaa|jaaaʹahaa|noodiya|ʹam|boorika|mañ|fin|Naari|wa-man|ḥawlahaa:|wa-Subḥaanal|laahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
27,9,"Yaa-Moosaaa|ʹinnahooo|ʹAnal|laahul|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem!"
27,10,"Wa-ʹalq̣i|ʻaṣaak!|falammaa|raʹaahaa|tahtazzu|kaʹannahaa|jaaannuñw|wallaa|mudbirañw|walam|yuʻaq̣q̣ib|yaa-Moosaa|laa-|takhaf:|ʹinnee|laa-|yakhaafu|ladayyal|mursaloon,"
27,11,"ʹIllaa|mañ|z̤̣alama|s̤umma|baddala|ḥusnam|baʻda|soooʹiñ|faʹinnee|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
27,12,"Wa-ʹadkhil|yadaka|fee|jaybika|takhruj|bayḍaaaʹa|min|g̣ayri|soooʹ:|fee|tisʻi|ʹAayaatin|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|wa-q̣awmih:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣awmañ|faasiq̣een."
27,13,"Falammaa|jaaaʹathum|ʹAayaatunaa|mubṣiratañ|q̣aaloo|haaẓaa|siḥrum|mubeen!"
27,14,"Wa-jaḥadoo|bihaa|wastayq̣anathaaa|ʹañfusuhum|z̤̣ulmañw|waʻuluwwaa;|fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mufsideen!"
27,15,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Daawooda|wa-Sulaymaana|ʻilmaa:|Wa-q̣aalal|Ḥamdu|lil-laahil|laẓee|faḍḍalnaa|ʻalaa|kas̤eerim|min|ʻibaadihil|Muʹmineen!"
27,16,"Wa-waris̤a|Sulaymaanu|Daawooda|wa-q̣aala|yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʻullimnaa|Mañṭiq̣aṭ|Ṭayri|wa-ʹooteenaa|miñ|kulli|shayʹ:|ʹinna|haaẓaa|lahuwal|Faḍlul|mubeen."
27,17,"Wa-ḥushira|li-Sulaymaana|junooduhoo|minal|jinni|wal-ʹiñsi|waṭṭayri|fahum|yoozaʹoon;"
27,18,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹataw|ʻalaa|Waadin|namli|q̣aalat|namlatuñy|yaaaʹayyuhan|namlud|khuloo|masaakinakum,|laa-|yaḥṭimannakum|Sulaymaanu|wa-junooduhoo|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon."
27,19,"Fatabassama|ḍaaḥikam|miñ|q̣awlihaa|wa-q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹawziʻneee|ʹan|ʹashkura|niʻmatakal|lateee|ʹanʻamta|ʻalayya|wa-ʻalaa|waalidayya|wa-ʹan|ʹaʻmala|ṣaaliḥañ|tarḍaahu|wa-ʹadkhilnee|bi-Raḥmatika|fee|ʻibaadikaṣ|ṣaaliḥeen."
