27,25,"ʹAllaa|yasjudoo|lillaahil|laẓee|yukhrijul|khabʹa|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wayaʻlamu|maa-|tukhfoona|wa-maa|tuʻlinoon."
27,26,"ʹAllaahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwa|Rabbul|ʻArshil|ʻAz̤̣eem!"
