27,30,"ʹInnahoo|miñ|Sulaymaana|wa-ʹinnahoo|˹Bismil|laahir|Raḥmaanir|Raḥeem:˺"
27,31,"ʹAllaa|taʻloo|ʻalayya|waʹ-toonee|Muslimeen."
27,32,"Q̣aalat|yaaaʹayyuhal|malaʹu|aftoonee|feee|ʹamree:|maa-|kuñtu|q̣aaṭiʻatan|ʹamran|ḥattaa|tashhadoon."
27,33,"Q̣aaloo|naḥnu|ʹuloo|q̣uwwatiñw|waʹuloo|baʹsiñ|shadeed:|wal-ʹamru|ʹilayki|fañz̤̣uree|maaẓaa|taʹmureen."
27,34,"Q̣aalat|ʹinnal|mulooka|ʹiẓaa|dakhaloo|q̣aryatan|ʹafsadoohaa|wa-jaʻalooo|ʹaʻizzata|ʹahlihaaa|ʹaẓillah:|wa-kaẓaalika|yafʻaloon."
27,35,"Wa-ʹinnee|mursilatun|ʹilayhim|bihadiyyatiñ|fanaaz̤̣iratum|bima|yarjiʻul|mursaloon."
27,36,"Falammaa|jaaaʹa|Sulaymaana|q̣aala|ʹatumiddoonani|bimaal?|Famaaa|ʹaataaniyal|laahu|khayrum|mimmaaa|ʹaataakum!|Bal|ʹañtum̃|bihadiyyatikum|tafraḥoon!"
27,37,"ʹIrjiʻ|ʹilayhim|falanaʹtiyannahum̃|bijunoodil|laa|q̣ibala|lahum̃|bihaa|wa-lanukhrijannahum|minhaaa|ʹaẓillatañw|Wahum|ṣaag̣iroon."
27,38,"Q̣aala|yaaaʹayyuhal|malaʹu|ʹayyukum|yaʹteenee|biʻarshihaa|q̣abla|ʹañy|yaʹtoonee|muslimeen?"
27,39,"Q̣aala|ʻIfreetum|minal|jinni|ʹana|ʹaateeka|bihee|q̣abla|ʹañ|taq̣ooma|mim|maq̣aamik:|wa-ʹinnee|ʻalayhi|laq̣awiyyun|ʹameen."
27,40,"Q̣aalal|laẓee|ʻiñdahoo|ʻilmum|minal|Kitaabi|ʹana|ʹaateeka|bihee|q̣abla|ʹañy|yartadda|ʹilayka|ṭarfuk!|Falammaa|raʹaahu|mustaq̣irran|ʻiñdahoo|q̣aala|haaẓaa|miñ|faḍli|Rabbee|liyabluwaneee|ʹaʹashkuru|ʹam|ʹakfur!|Wa-mañ|shakara|faʹinnamaa|yashkuru|linafsih;|wa-mañ|kafara|faʹinna|Rabbee|G̣aniyyuñ|Kareem!..."
27,41,"Q̣aala|nakkiroo|lahaa|ʻarshahaa|nañz̤̣ur|ʹatahtadeee|ʹam|takoonu|minal|laẓeena|laa-|yahtadoon."
27,42,"Falammaa|jaaaʹat|q̣eela|ʹahaakaẓaa|ʻarshuk?|Q̣aalat|kaʹannahoo|hoo;|wa-ʹooteenal|ʻilma|miñ|q̣ablihaa|wa-kunnaa|Muslimeen."
27,43,"Waṣaddahaa|maa-|kaanat|taʻbudu|miñ|doonil|laah:|ʹinnahaa|kaanat|miñ|q̣awmiñ|kaafireen."
27,44,"Q̣eela|lahad|khuliṣ|ṣarḥ:|falammaaنَ|raʹathu|ḥasibathu|lujjatañw|wakashafat|ʻañ|saaq̣ayhaa.|Q̣aala|ʹinnahoo|ṣarḥum|mumarradum|miñ|q̣awaareer.|Q̣aalat|Rabbi|ʹinnee|z̤̣alamtu|nafsee|wa-ʹaslamtu|maʻa|Sulaymaana|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
27,45,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaaa|ʹilaa|S̤amooda|ʹakhaahum|Ṣaaliḥan|ʹaniʻ|budul|laaha|faʹiẓaa|hum|fareeq̣aani|yakhtaṣimoon."
27,46,"Q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|lima|tastaʻjiloona|bissayyiʹati|q̣ablal|ḥasanah?|Law-laa|tas-tag̣firoonal|laaha|laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
27,47,"Q̣aaluṭ|ṭayyarnaa|bika|wa-bimam|maʻak.|Q̣aala|ṭaaaʹirukum|ʻiñdal|laahi|bal|ʹañtum|q̣awmuñ|tuftanoon."
27,48,"Wa-kaana|fil|madeenati|tisʻatu|rahṭiñy|yufsidoona|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|yuṣliḥoon."
27,49,"Q̣aaloo|taq̣aasamoo|billaahi|lanubayyitannahoo|wa-ʹahlahoo|s̤umma|lanaq̣oolanna|liwaliyyihee|maa-|shahidnaa|mahlika|ʹahlihee|wa-ʹinnaa|laṣaadiq̣oon."
27,50,"Wa-makaroo|makrañw|wamakarnaa|makrañw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon."
27,51,"Fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatu|makrihim|ʹannaa|dammarnaahum|wa-q̣awmahum|ʹajmaʻeen."
27,52,"Fatilka|buyootuhum|khaawiyatam|bimaa|z̤̣alamoo.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon."
27,53,"Wa-ʹañjaynal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-kaanoo|yattaq̣oon."
27,54,"Wa-Looṭan|ʹiẓ|q̣aala|liq̣awmiheee|ʹataʹtoonal|faa-ḥishata|wa-ʹañtum|tubṣiroon?"
27,55,"ʹAʹinnakum|lataʹtoonar|rijaala|shahwatam|miñ|doonin|nisaaaʹ?|Bal|ʹañtum|q̣awmuñ|tajhaloon!"
27,56,"Famaa|kaana|jawaaba|q̣awmiheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aalooo|ʹakhrijooo|ʹaala|Looṭim|miñ|q̣aryatikum:|ʹinnahum|ʹunaasuñy|yataṭahharoon!"
27,57,"Faʹañjaynaahu|wa-ʹahlahooo|ʹillam|raʹatah:|q̣addarnaahaa|minal|g̣aabireen."
27,58,"Wa-ʹamṭarnaa|ʻalayhim|maṭaraa:|fasaaaʹa|maṭarul|muñẓareen!"
27,59,"Q̣ulil|Ḥamdu|lillaahi|wa-Salaamun|ʻalaa|ʻibaadihil|laẓeenaṣ|ṭafaa.|ʹAaallaahu|khayrun|ʻammaa|yushrikoon?"
27,60,"ʹAmman|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-ʹañzala|lakum|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹaa?|Faʹambatnaa|bihee|ḥadaaaʹiq̣a|ẓaata|bahjah:|maa-|kaana|lakum|ʹañ|tumbitoo|shajarahaa.|ʹA-ʹilaahum|maʻal|laah?|Bal|hum|q̣awmuñy|yaʻdiloon."
27,61,"ʹAmmañ|jaʻalal|ʹarḍa|q̣araarañw|wajaʻala|khilaalahaaa|ʹanhaarañw|Wajaʻala|lahaa|rawaasiya|wa-jaʻala|baynal|baḥrayni|ḥaajizaa?|ʹA-ʹilaahum|ma|ʻallaah?|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
27,62,"ʹAmmañy|yujeebul|muḍ-ṭarra|ʹiẓaa|daʻaahu|wa-yakshifus|soooʹa|wa-yajʻalukum|khulafaaa|ʹalʹarḍ?|ʹA-ʹilaahum|maʻal|laah?|Q̣aleelam|maa|taẓakkaroon!"
27,63,"ʹAmmañy|yahdeekum|fee|z̤̣ulumaatil|barri|wal-baḥri|wa-mañy|yursilur|riyaaḥa|bushram|bayna|yaday|Raḥmatih?|ʹAʹilaahum|maʻal|laah?|Taʻaalal|laahu|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
27,64,"ʹAmmañy|yabdaʹul|khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduhoo|wa-mañy|yarzuq̣ukum|minas|samaaaʹi|wal|ʹarḍ?|ʹA-ʹilaahum|maʻallaah?|Q̣ul|haatoo|burhaanakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
27,65,"Q̣ul|laa|yaʻlamu|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍil|g̣ayba|ʹillal|laah:|wa-maa|yashʻuroona|ʹayyaana|yubʻas̤oon."
27,66,"Balid|daaraka|ʻilmuhum|fil|ʹAakhirah:|bal|hum|fee|shakkim|minhaa;|bal|hum|minhaa|ʻamoon!"
27,67,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|kunnaa|turaabañw|waʹaabaaaʹunaaa|ʹaʹinnaa|lamukhrajoon?"
27,68,"Laq̣ad|wuʻidnaa|haaẓaa|naḥnu|wa-ʹaabaaaʹunaa|miñ|q̣ablu|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleen."
27,69,"Q̣ul|seeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mujrimeen."
27,70,"Wa-laa|taḥzan|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|takuñ|fee|ḍayq̣im|mimmaa|yamkuroon."
27,71,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|waʻdu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
27,72,"Q̣ul|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yakoona|radifa|lakum|baʻḍul|laẓee|tastaʻjiloon!"
27,73,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Ẓoo|faḍlin|ʻalan|naasi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yashkuroon."
27,74,"Wa-ʹinna|Rabbaka|layaʻlamu|maa-|tukinnu|ṣudooruhum|wa-maa|yuʻlinoon."
27,75,"Wa-maa|min|g̣aaaʹibatiñ|fis|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍi|ʹillaa|fee|kitaabim|mubeen."
27,76,"ʹInna|haaẓal|Q̣ur-ʹaana|yaq̣uṣṣu|ʻalaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʹaks̤aral|laẓee|hum|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
27,77,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|la-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatul|lil-Muʹmineen."
27,78,"ʹInna|Rabbaka|yaq̣ḍee|baynahum̃|bi-Ḥukmih:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|ʻAleem."
27,79,"Fatawakkal|ʻalal|laah:|ʹinnaka|ʻalal|Ḥaq̣q̣il|mubeen."
27,80,"ʹInnaka|laa-|tusmiʻul|mawtaa|wa-laa|tusmiʻuṣ|ṣummad|duʻaaaʹa|ʹiẓaa|wallaw|mudbireen."
27,81,"Wa-maaa|ʹañta|bihaadil|ʻumyi|ʻañ|ḍalaalatihim:|ʹiñ|tusmiʻu|ʹillaa|mañy|yuʹminu|biʹAayaatinaa|fahum|Muslimoon."
27,82,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|waq̣aʻal|Q̣awlu|ʻalayhim|ʹakhrajnaa|lahum|Daaabbatam|minal|ʹarḍi|tukal-limuhum|ʹannan|naasa|kaanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|laa-|yooq̣inoon."
27,83,"Wa-Yawma|naḥshuru|miñ|kulli|ʹummatiñ|fawjam|mimmañy|yukaẓẓibu|biʹAayaatinaa|fahum|yoozaʻoon,"
27,84,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹoo|q̣aala|ʹakaẓẓabtum̃|biʹAayaatee|wa-lam|tuḥeeṭoo|bihaa|ʻilman|ʹammaaẓaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon?"
27,85,"Wa-waq̣aʻal|Q̣awlu|ʻalayhim̃|bimaa|z̤̣alamoo|fahum|laa-|yañṭiq̣oon."
27,86,"ʹAlam|yaraw|ʹannaa|jaʻalnal|Layla|liyaskunoo|feehi|wan-Nahaara|mubṣiraa?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon!"
27,87,"Wa-Yawma|yuñfakhu|fiṣ|Ṣoori|fafaziʻa|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wa-mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹillaa|mañ|shaaaʹal|laah:|wa-kullun|ʹatawhu|daakhireen."
27,88,"Wa-taral|jibaala|taḥsabuhaa|jaamidatañw|wahiya|tamurru|marras|saḥaab:|ṣunʻal|laahil|laẓeee|ʹatq̣ana|kulla|shayʹ:|innahoo|khabeerum|bimaa|tafʻaloon."
27,89,"Mañ|jaaaʹa|bil-ḥasanati|falahoo|khayrum|minhaa;|wa-hum|miñ|fazaʻiñy|Yawmaʹiẓin|ʹaaminoon."
27,90,"Wa-mañ|jaaaʹa|bissayyiʹati|fakubbat|wujoohuhum|fin|Naar:|hal|tujzawna|ʹillaa|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon?"
27,91,"ʹInnamaaa|ʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹaʻbuda|Rabba|haaẓihil|Baldatill|aẓee|ḥarramahaa|wa-lahoo|kullu|shayʹiñw|waʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹakoona|minal|Muslimeen,"
27,92,"Wa-ʹan|ʹatluwal|Q̣ur-ʹaan:|famanih|tadaa|faʹinnamaa|yahtadee|linafsih:|wa-mañ|ḍalla|faq̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|minal|muñẓireen."
27,93,"Wa-q̣ulil|Ḥamdu|lillaahi|sayureekum|ʹAayaatihee|fataʻrifoonahaa;|wa-maa|Rabbuka|big̣aafilin|ʻamaa|taʻmaloon."
28,1,"Ṭaa-seeen-Meeem."
28,2,"Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Kitaabil|mubeen."
28,3,"Natloo|ʻalayka|min|nabaʹi|Moosaa|wa-Firʻawna|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
28,4,"ʹInna|firʻawna|ʻalaa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-jaʻala|ʹahlahaa|shiyaʻañy|yastaḍʻifu|ṭaaaʹifatam|minhum|yuẓabbiḥu|ʹabnaaaʹahum|wa-yastaḥyee|nisaaaʹahum:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|minal|mufsideen."
28,5,"Wa-nureedu|ʹan|namunna|ʻalal|laẓeenas|tuḍʻifoo|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-najʻalahum|ʹaʹimmatañw|Wanajʻalahumul|waaris̤een,"
28,6,"Wa-numakkina|lahum|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-nuriya|Firʻawna|wa-Haamaana|wa-junoodahumaa|minhum|maa|kaanoo|yaḥẓaroon."
28,7,"Wa-ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹummi|Moosaaa|ʹan|ʹarḍiʻeeh:|faʹiẓaa|khifti|ʻalayhi|faʹalq̣eehi|fil|yammi|wa-laa|takhaafee|walaa|taḥzanee:|ʹinnaa|raaaddoohu|ʹilayki|wa-jaaʻiloohu|milnal|mursaleen."
28,8,"Faltaq̣aṭahooo|ʹaalu|Firʻawna|liyakoona|lahum|ʻaduwwañw|Waḥazanaa:|ʹInna|Firʻawna|wa-Haamaana|wa-junooda-humaa|kaanoo|khaaṭiʹeen."
28,9,"Wa-q̣aalatim|raʹatu|Firʻawna|q̣urratu|ʻaynil|lee|wa-lak:|laa-|taq̣tuloohu|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yañfaʻanaaa|ʹaw|nattakhiẓahoo|waladañw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon!"
28,10,"Wa-ʹaṣbaḥa|fuʹaadu|ʹummi|Moosaa|faarig̣aa:|ʹiñ|kaadat|latubdee|bihee|law|laaa|ʹarrabaṭnaa|ʻalaa|q̣albihaa|litakoona|minal|Muʹmineen."
28,11,"Wa-q̣aalat|liʹukhtihee|q̣uṣṣeeh.|Fabaṣurat|bihee|ʻañ|junubiñw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon."
28,12,"wa-ḥarramnaa|ʻalayhil|maraaḍiʻa|miñ|q̣ablu|faq̣aalat|hal|ʹadullukum|ʻalaaa|ʹahli|baytiñy|yakfuloonahoo|lakum|wa-hum|lahoo|naaṣiḥoon?..."
28,13,"Faradadnaahu|ʹilaaa|ʹummihee|kay|taq̣arra|ʻaynuhaa|wa-laa|taḥzana|wa-litaʻlama|ʹanna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|walaakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
28,14,"Wa-lammaa|balag̣a|ʹashuddahoo|wastawaaa|ʹaataynaahu|ḥukmañw|waʻilmaa:|wa-kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
28,15,"Wa-dakhalal|Madeenata|ʻalaa|ḥeeni|g̣aflatim|min|ʹahlihaa|fawajada|feeha|rajulayni|yaq̣tatilaani|haaẓaa|miñ|sheeʻatihee|wa-haaẓaa|min|ʻaduwwih.|Fastag̣aas̤ahul|laẓee|miñ|sheeʻatihee|ʻalal|laẓee|min|ʻaduwwihee|fawakazahoo|Moosaa|faq̣aḍaa|ʻalayh.|Q̣aala|haaẓaa|min|ʻamalish|shayṭaan:|ʹinnahoo|ʻaduwwum|muḍillum|mubeen!"
28,16,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnee|z̤̣alamtu|nafsee|fag̣fir|lee|fag̣afara|lah:|innahoo|Huwal|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
28,17,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|bimaaa|ʹanʻamta|ʻalayya|falan|ʹakoona|z̤̣aheeral|lilmujrimeen."
28,18,"Faʹaṣbaḥa|fil|Madeenati|khaaaʹifañy|yataraq̣q̣abu|faʹiẓal|laẓis|tañṣarahoo|bil-ʹamsi|yastaṣrikhuh.|Q̣aala|lahoo|Moosaaa|ʹinnaka|lag̣awiyyum|mubeen!"
28,19,"Falammaaa|ʹan|ʹaraada|ʹañy|yabṭisha|billaẓee|huwa|ʻaduwwul|lahumaa|q̣aala|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹatureedu|ʹañ|taq̣tulanee|kamaa|q̣atalta|nafsam|bil-ʹams?|ʹIñ|tureedu|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|takoona|jabbaarañ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|tureedu|ʹañ|takoona|minal|Muṣliḥeen!"
28,20,"Wa-jaaaʹa|rajulum|min|ʹaq̣ṣal|Madeenati|yasʻaa.|Q̣aala|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹinnal|malaʹa|yaʹ-tamiroona|bika|liyaq̣tulooka|fakhruj|ʹinnee|laka|minan|naaṣiḥeen."
28,21,"Fakharaja|minhaa|khaaaʹifañy|yataraq̣q̣ab:|Q̣aala|Rabbi|najjinee|minal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
28,22,"Wa-lammaa|tawajjaha|tilq̣aaaʹa|Madyana|q̣aala|ʻasaa|Rabbeee|ʹañy|yahdiyanee|sawaaaʹas|sabeel."
28,23,"Wa-lammaa|warada|maaaʹa|Madyana|wajada|ʻalayhi|ʹummatam|minan|naasi|yasq̣oona|wa-wajada|miñ|doonihimum|raʹatayni|taẓoodaan.|Q̣aala|maa-|khaṭbukumaa?|Q̣aalataa|laa-|nasq̣ee|ḥattaa|yuṣdirar|riʻaaaʹu|wa-ʹaboonaa|shaykhuñ|kabeer."
28,24,"Fasaq̣aa|lahumaa|s̤umma|tawallaaa|ʹilaz̤̣|z̤̣illi|faq̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnee|limaaa|añzalta|ʹilayya|min|khayriñ|faq̣eer!.."
28,25,"Fajaaaʹathu|ʹiḥdaahumaa|tamshee|ʻalas|tiḥyaaaʹ,|Q̣aalat|ʹinna|ʹabee|yadʻooka|liyajziyaka|ʹajra|maa-|saq̣ayta|lanaa.|Falammaa|jaaaʹahoo|wa-q̣aṣṣa|ʻalayhil|q̣aṣaṣa|q̣aala|laa-|takhaf:|najawta|minal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
28,26,"Q̣aalat|ʹiḥdaahumaa|yaaaʹabatis|taʹjirh;|ʹinna|khayra|manis|taʹjartal|q̣awiyyul|ʹameen."
28,27,"Q̣aala|ʹinneee|ʹureedu|ʹan|ʹuñkiḥaka|ʹiḥdab|natayya|haatayni|ʻalaaa|ʹañ|taʹjuranee|s̤amaaniya|ḥijaj;|faʹin|ʹatmamta|ʻashrañ|famin|ʻiñdik.|Wa-maaa|ʹureedu|ʹan|ʹashuq̣q̣a|ʻalayk:|satajiduneee|ʹiñ|shaaaʹal|laahu|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
28,28,"Q̣aala|ẓaalika|baynee|wa-baynak:|ʹayyamal|ʹajalayni|q̣aḍaytu|falaa|ʻudwaana|ʻalayy.|Wallaahu|ʻalaa|maa-|naq̣oolu|Wakeel."
28,29,"Falammaa|q̣aḍaa|Moosal|ʹajala|wa-saara|biʹahliheee|ʹaanasa|miñ|jaanibiṭ|Ṭoori|naaraa.|Q̣aala|liʹahlihim|kus̤ooo|ʹinneee|ʹaanastu|naaral|laʻalleee|ʹaateekum|minhaa|bikhabarin|ʹaw|jaẓwatim|minan|naari|laʻallakum|taṣṭaloon."
28,30,"Falammaaa|ʹataahaa|noodiya|miñ|shaaṭiʹil|waadil|ʹaymani|fil|buq̣ʻatil|mubaarakati|minash|shajarati|ʹañy|yaa-Moosaaa|ʹinneee|ʹAnal|laahu|Rabbul|ʻAalameen."
28,31,"Wa-ʹan|ʹalq̣i|ʻaṣaak!|Falammaa|raʹaahaa|tahtazzu|kaʹannahaa|jaaannuñw|wallaa|mudbirañw|walam|yuʻaq̣q̣ib:|Yaa-Moosaaa|ʹaq̣bil|wa-laa|takhaf:|ʹinnaka|minal|ʹaamineen."
28,32,"ʹUsluk|yadaka|fee|jaybika|takhruj|bayḍaaaʹa|min|g̣ayri|soooʹ:|waḍmum|ʹilayka|janaaḥaka|minar|rahbi|fazaanika|burhaanaani|mir|Rabbika|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹih:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣awmañ|faasiq̣een."
28,33,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnee|q̣ataltu|minhum|nafsañ|faʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yaq̣tuloon."
28,34,"Wa-ʹakhee|Haaroonu|huwa|ʹafṣaḥu|minnee|lisaanañ|faʹarsilhu|maʻiya|rid-ʹañy|yuṣaddiq̣unee;|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yukaẓẓiboon."
28,35,"Q̣aala|sanashuddu|ʻaḍudaka|biʹakheeka|wa-najʻalu|lakumaa|sulṭaanañ|falaa|yaṣiloona|ʹilaykumaa:|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹañtumaa|wa-manit|tabaʻakumal|g̣aaliboon."
28,36,"Falammaa|jaaaʹahum|Moosaa|biʹAayaatinaa|bayyinaatiñ|q̣aaloo|maa-|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|siḥrum|muftarañw|wamaa|samiʻnaa|bihaaẓaa|feee|ʹaabaaaʹinal|ʹawwaleen!"
28,37,"Wa-q̣aala|Moosaa|Rabbeee|ʹaʻlamu|bimañ|jaaaʹa|bil-Hudaa|min|ʻiñdihee|wa-mañ|takoonu|lahoo|ʻAaq̣ibatud|daar:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yufliḥuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
28,38,"Wa-q̣aala|Firʻawnu|yaaaʹayyuhal|malaʹu|maa-|ʻalimtu|lakum|min|ʹilaahin|g̣ayree:|faʹawq̣id|lee|yaa-Haamaanu|ʻalaṭ|ṭeeni|fajʻal|lee|ṣarḥal|laʻalleee|ʹaṭṭaliʻu|ʹilaaa|ʹilaahi|Moosaa|wa-ʹinnee|laʹaz̤̣unnuhoo|minal|kaaẓibeen!"
28,39,"Wastakbara|huwa|wa-junooduhoo|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣i|waz̤̣annooo|ʹannahum|ʹilaynaa|laa-|yurjaʻoon!"
28,40,"Faʹakhaẓnaahu|wa-junoo-dahoo|fanabaẓnaahum|fil|yamm:|fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen!"
28,41,"Wa-jaʻalnaahum|ʹaʹimmatañy|yadʻoona|ʹilan|Naar;|Wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|laa-|yuñṣaroon."
28,42,"Wa-ʹatbaʻnaahum|fee|haaẓihid|dunyaa|Laʻnah;|wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|hum|minal|maq̣booḥeen."
28,43,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|mim|baʻdi|maaa|ʹahlaknal|q̣uroonal|ʹoolaa|Baṣaaaʹira|linnaasi|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatal|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
28,44,"Wa-maa|kuñta|bijaanibil|G̣arbiyyi|ʹiẓ|q̣aḍaynaaa|ʹilaa|Moosal|ʹAmra|wa-maa|kuñta|minash|shaahideen."
28,45,"Wa-laakinnaaa|ʹañshaʹnaa|q̣uroonañ|fataṭaawala|ʻalayhimul|ʻumur;|wa-maa|kuñta|s̤aawiyañ|feee|ʹahli|Madyana|tatloo|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatinaa|wa-laakinnaa|kunnaa|mursileen."
28,46,"Wa-maa|kuñta|bijaanibiṭ|Ṭoori|ʹiẓ|naadaynaa|wa-laakir|Raḥmatam|mir|Rabbika|lituñẓira|q̣awmam|maaa|ʹataahum|min|naẓeerim|miñ|q̣ablika|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
28,47,"Wa-lawlaaa|ʹañ|tuṣeebahum|muṣeebatum|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeehim|fayaq̣ooloo|Rabbanaa|Law-laaa|ʹarsalta|ʹilaynaa|rasoolañ|fanattabiʻa|ʹAayaatika|wa-nakoona|minal|Muʹmineen!"
28,48,"Falammaa|jaaaʹahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|min|ʻiñdinaa|q̣aaloo|law-laaa|ʹootiya|mis̤la|maaa|ʹootiya|Moosaa?|ʹAwalam|yakfuroo|bimaaa|ʹootiya|Moosaa|miñ|q̣abl?|Q̣aaloo|siḥraani|taz̤̣aaharaa!|Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|bikulliñ|kaafiroon!"
28,49,"Q̣ul|faʹtoo|bi-Kitaabim|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|huwa|ʹahdaa|minhumaaa|ʹattabiʻhu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
28,50,"Faʹil|lam|yastajeeboo|laka|faʻlam|ʹannamaa|yattabiʻoona|ʹahwaaaʹahum:|wa-man|ʹaḍallu|mimmanit|tabaʻa|hawaahu|big̣ayri|hudam|minal|laah?|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
28,51,"Wa-laq̣ad|waṣṣalnaa|lahumul|Q̣awla|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
28,52,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablihee|hum̃|bihee|yuʹminoon;"
28,53,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|yutlaa|ʻalayhim|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|biheee|ʹinnahul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbinaaa|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|miñ|q̣ablihee|Muslimeen."
28,54,"ʹUlaaaʹika|yuʹtawna|ʹajrahum|marratayni|bimaa|ṣabaroo|wa-yadraʹoona|bil-ḥasanatis|sayyiʹata|wa-mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|yuñfiq̣oon."
28,55,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|samiʻul|lag̣wa|ʹaʻraḍoo|ʻanhu|wa-q̣aaloo|lanaaa|ʹaʻmaalunaa|wa-lakum|ʹaʻmaalukum;|Salaamun|ʻalaykum:|laa-|nabtag̣il|jaahileen."
28,56,"ʹInnaka|laa-|tahdee|man|ʹaḥbabta|wa-laakinnal|laaha|yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bil-muhtadeen."
28,57,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹin|nattabiʻil|hudaa|maʻaka|nutakhaṭṭaf|min|ʹarḍinaa.|ʹAwalam|numakkil|lahum|Ḥaraman|ʹaaminañy|yujbaaa|ʹilayhi|s̤amaraatu|kulli|shayʹir|rizq̣am|mil|ladunnaa|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
28,58,"Wa-kam|ʹahlaknaa|miñ|q̣aryatim|baṭirat|maʻeeshatahaa!|Fatilka|masaakinuhum|lam|tuskam|mim|baʻdihim|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa!|Wa-kunnaa|Naḥnul|waaris̤een!"
28,59,"Wa-maa|kaana|Rabbuka|muhlikal|q̣uraa|ḥattaa|yabʻas̤a|feee|ʹummihaa|rasoolañy|yatloo|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatinaa;|wa-maa|kunnaa|muhlikil|q̣uraaa|ʹillaa|wa-ʹahluhaa|z̤̣aalimoon."
28,60,"Wa-maaa|ʹooteetum|miñ|shayʹiñ|famataaʻul|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-zeenatuhaa;|wa-maa|ʻiñdal|laahi|khayruñw|waʹabq̣aa:|ʹafalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
28,61,"ʹAfamañw|waʻadnaahu|waʻdan|ḥasanañ|fahuwa|laaq̣eehi|kamam|mattaʻnaahu|mataaʻal|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|s̤umma|huwa|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|minal|muḥḍareen?"
28,62,"Wa-Yawma|yunaadeehim|fayaq̣oolu|ʹayna|shurakaaaʹiyal|laẓeena|kuñtum|tazʻumoon?"
28,63,"Q̣aalal|laẓeena|ḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhimul|q̣awlu|Rabbanaa|haaaʹulaaaʹil|laẓeena|ʹag̣waynaa:|ʹag̣waynaahum|kamaa|g̣awaynaa:|tabarraʹnaaa|ʹilayka|maa-|kaanooo|ʹiyyaanaa|yaʻbudoon."
28,64,"Wa-q̣eelad|ʻoo|shurakaaaʹakum|fadaʻawhum|falam|yastajeeboo|lahum|wa-raʹawul|ʻaẓaaba|law|ʹannahum|kaanoo|yahtadoon!"
28,65,"Wa-Yawma|yunaadeehim|fayaq̣oolu|maa-ẓaaa|ʹajabtumul|mursaleen?"
28,66,"Faʻamiyat|ʻalayhimul|ʹambaaaʹu|Yawmaʹiẓiñ|fahum|laa-|yatasaaaʹaloon!"
28,67,"Faʹammaa|mañ|taaba|wa-ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|faʻasaaa|ʹañy|yakoona|minal|Mufliḥeen."
28,68,"Wa-Rabbuka|yakhluq̣u|maa-|yashaaaʹu|wayakhtaar:|maa-|kaana|lahumul|khiyarah:|Subḥaanal|laahi|wa-taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
28,69,"Wa-Rabbuka|yaʻlamu|maa-|tukinnu|ṣudooruhum|wa-maa|yuʻlinoon."
28,70,"Wa-Huwal|laahu|laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo.|Lahul|Ḥamdu|fil|ʹoolaa|wal-ʹaakhirah:|wa-lahul|Ḥukmu|wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
28,71,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹiñ|jaʻalal|laahu|ʻalaykumul|Layla|sarmadan|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|man|ʹilaahun|g̣ayrul|laahi|yaʹ-teekum̃|biḍiyaaaʹ?|ʹAfalaa|tasmaʻoon?"
28,72,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹiñ|jaʻalal|laahu|ʻalaykumun|Nahaara|sarmadan|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|man|ʹilaahun|g̣ayrul|laahi|yaʹteekum̃|bi-Layliñ|taskunoona|feeh?|ʹAfalaa|tubṣiroon?"
28,73,"Wa-mir|Raḥmatihee|jaʻala|lakumul|Layla|wan-Nahaara|litaskunoo|feehi|wa-litabtag̣oo|miñ|Faḍlihee|wa-laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
28,74,"Wa-Yawma|yunaadeehim|fayaq̣oolu|ʹayna|shurakaaaʹiyal|laẓeena|kuñtum|tazʻumoon?"
28,75,"Wa-nazaʻnaa|miñ|kulli|ʹummatiñ|shaheedañ|faq̣ulnaa|haatoo|burhaanakum|faʻalimooo|ʹannal|Ḥaq̣q̣a|lillaahi|wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
28,76,"ʹInna|Q̣aaroona|kaana|miñ|q̣awmi|Moosaa|fabag̣aa|ʻalayhim:|wa-ʹaataynaahu|minal|kunoozi|maaa|ʹinna|mafaatiḥahoo|latanoooʹu|bilʻuṣbati|ʹulil|q̣uwwah.|ʹIẓ|q̣aala|lahoo|q̣awmuhoo|laa-|tafraḥ|ʹinnal|laah|laa-|yuḥibbul|fariḥeen."
28,77,"Wabtag̣i|feemaaa|ʹaataakal|laahud|Daaral|ʹAakhirata|wa-laa|tañsa|naṣeebaka|minad|dunyaa|wa-ʹaḥsin|kamaaa|ʹaḥsanal|laahu|ʹilayka|wa-laa|tabg̣il|fasaada|fil|ʹarḍ:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbul|mufsideen."
28,78,"Q̣aala|ʹinnamaaa|ʹooteetuhoo|ʻalaa|ʻilmin|ʻiñdee.|ʹAwalam|yaʻlam|ʹannal|laaha|q̣ad|ʹahlaka|miñ|q̣ablihee|minal|q̣urooni|man|huwa|ʹashaddu|minhu|q̣uwwatañw|waʹaks̤aru|jamʻaa?|Wa-laa|yusʹalu|ʻañ|ẓunoobihimul|mujrimoon."
28,79,"Fakharaja|ʻalaa|q̣awmihee|fee|zeenatih.|Q̣aalal|laẓeena|yureedoonal|Ḥayaatad|Dunyaa|yaalayta|lanaa|miṣla|maaa|ʹootiya|Q̣aaroonu|ʹinnahoo|ḥaz̤̣z̤̣in|laẓoo|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
28,80,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻilma|waylakum|s̤awaabul|laahi|khayrul|liman|ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥaa:|wa-laa|yulaq̣q̣aahaaa|ʹillaṣ|Ṣaabiroon."
28,81,"Fakhasafnaa|bihee|wa-bidaarihil|ʹarḍ;|famaa|kaana|lahoo|miñ|fiʹatiñy|yañṣuroonahoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-maa|kaana|minal|muñtaṣireen."
28,82,"Wa-ʹaṣbaḥal|laẓeena|tamannaw|makaanahoo|bil-ʹamsi|yaq̣ooloona|waykaʹannal|laaha|yabsuṭur|rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadihee|wa-yaq̣dir!|Law-laaa|ʹam|mannal|laahu|ʻalaynaa|lakhasafa|binaa!|Waykaʹannahoo|laa-|yufliḥul|kaafiroon!"
28,83,"Tilkad|Daarul|ʹAakhiratu|najʻaluhaa|lillaẓeena|laa-|yureedoona|ʻuluwwañ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|fasaadaa:|wal-ʻaaq̣ibatu|lil-Muttaq̣een."
28,84,"Mañ|jaaaʹa|bilḥasanati|falahoo|khayrum|minhaa;|wa-mañ|jaaaʹa|bissayyiʹati|falaa|yujzal|laẓeena|ʻamilus|sayyiʹaati|ʹillaa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
28,85,"ʹInnal|laẓee|faraḍa|ʻalaykal|Q̣ur-ʹaana|laraaadduka|ʹilaa|Maʻaad.|Q̣ur|Rabbeee|ʹaʻlamu|mañ|jaaaʹa|bil-hudaa|wa-man|huwa|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
28,86,"Wa-maa|kuñta|tarjooo|ʹañy|yulq̣aaa|ʹilaykal|Kitaabu|ʹillaa|Raḥmatam|mir|Rabbika|falaa|takoonanna|z̤̣aheeral|lil-kaafireen."
28,87,"Wa-laa|yaṣuddunnaka|ʻan|ʹAayaatil|laahi|baʻda|ʹiẓ|ʹuñzilat|ʹilayk:|wadʻu|ʹilaa|Rabbika|wa-laa|takoonanna|minal|mushrikeen."
28,88,"Wa-laa|tadʻu|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhar.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo.|Kullu|shayʹin|haalikun|ʹillaa|Wajhah.|Lahul|Ḥukmu|wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
29,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Meeem."
29,2,"ʹAḥasiban|naasu|ʹañy|yutrakooo|ʹañy|yaq̣oolooo|ʹaamannaa|Wahum|laa-|yuftanoon?"
29,3,"Wa-laq̣ad|fatannal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|falayaʻlamannal|laahul|laẓeena|ṣadaq̣oo|wa-la-yaʻlamannal|kaaẓibeen."
29,4,"ʹAm|ḥasibal|laẓeena|yaʻmaloonas|sayyiʹaati|ʹañy|yasbiq̣oonaa?|Saaaʹa|maa-|yaḥkumoon!"
29,5,"Mañ|Kaana|yarjoo|liq̣aaa|ʹallaahi|faʹinna|ʹAjalal|laahi|laʹaat;|wa-Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
29,6,"Wa-mañ|jaahada|faʹinnamaa|yujaahidu|linafsih;|ʹinnal|laaha|la-G̣aniyyun|ʻanil|ʻaalameen."
29,7,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|lanukaffiranna|ʻanhum|sayyiʹaatihim|wa-lanajziyannahum|ʹaḥsanal|laẓee|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
29,8,"Wa-waṣṣaynal|ʹiñsaana|biwaalidayhi|ḥusnaa:|wa-ʹiñ|jaahadaaka|litushrika|bee|maa-|laysa|laka|bihee|ʻilmuñ|falaa|tuṭiʻhumaa.|ʹIlayya|marjiʻukum|faʹunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
29,9,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|lanudkhilannahum|fiṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
29,10,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yaq̣oolu|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|faʹiẓaaa|ʹooẓiya|fil|laahi|jaʻala|fitnatan|naasi|kaʻAẓaabil|laah!|Wa-laʹiñ|jaaaʹa|naṣrum|mir|Rabbika|layaq̣oolunna|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|maʻakum!|ʹA-walaysal|laahu|biʹaʻlama|bimaa|fee|ṣudooril|ʻaalameen?"
29,11,"Wa-la-yaʻlamannal|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-la-yaʻlamannal|Munaafiq̣een."
29,12,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanut|tabiʻoo|sabeelanaa|walnaḥmil|khaṭaayaakum.|Wa-maa|hum̃|biḥaamileena|min|khaṭaayaahum|miñ|shayʹ;|ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon!"
29,13,"Wa-la-yaḥmilunna|ʹas̤q̣aalahum|wa-ʹas̤q̣aalam|maʻa|ʹas̤q̣aalihim,|wa-la-yusʹalunna|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʻammaa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
29,14,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Nooḥan|ʹilaa|q̣awmihee|falabis̤a|feehim|ʹalfa|sanatin|ʹillaa|khamseena|ʻaamaa;|faʹakhaẓahumuṭ|Ṭoofaanu|wa-hum|z̤̣aalimoon."
29,15,"Faʹañjaynaahu|wa-ʹAṣḥaabas|Safeenati|wa-jaʻalnaahaaa|ʹAayatal|lilʻAalameen!"
29,16,"Wa-ʹIbraaheema|ʹiẓ|q̣aala|liq̣awmihiʻ|budul|laaha|wattaq̣ooh.|Ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon!"
29,17,"ʹInnamaa|taʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹaws̤aanañwwa|takhluq̣oona|ʹifkaa.|ʹInnal|laẓeena|taʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|laa-|yamlikoona|lakum|rizq̣añ|fabtag̣oo|ʻiñdal|laahir|rizq̣a|waʻbudoohu|washkuroo|lah.|ʹIlayhi|turjaʻoon."
29,18,"Wa-ʹiñ|tukaẓẓiboo|faq̣ad|kaẓẓaba|ʹumamum|miñ|q̣ablikum.|Wa-maa|ʻalar|rasooli|ʹillal|balaag̣ul|mubeen."
29,19,"ʹA-walam|yaraw|kayfa|yubdiʹul|laahul|khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduh?|ʹInna|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseer."
29,20,"Q̣ul|seeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|badaʹal|khalq̣a|s̤ummal|laahu|yuñshiʹun|nashʹatal|ʹAakhirah:|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
29,21,"Yuʻaẓẓibu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yarḥamu|mañy|yashaaaʹ,|wa-ʹilayhi|tuq̣laboon."
29,22,"Wa-maaa|ʹañtum̃|bimuʻjizeena|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|fis|samaaaʹi|wa-maa|lakum|miñ|doonil|laahi|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|naṣeer."
29,23,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|biʹAayaatil|laahi|wa-Liq̣aaaʹiheee|ʹulaaaʹika|yaʹisoo|mir|raḥmatee|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem."
29,24,"Famaa|kaana|jawaaba|q̣awmiheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aaluq̣|tuloohu|ʹaw|ḥarriq̣oohu|faʹañjaahul|laahu|minan|Naar.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
29,25,"Wa-q̣aala|ʹinnamat|takhaẓtum|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹaws̤aanam|mawaddata|baynikum|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa;|s̤umma|yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|yakfuru|baʻḍukum̃|bibaʻḍiñw|wayalʻanu|baʻḍukum̃|baʻḍaa;|wa-maʹwaakumun|Naaru|wa-maa|lakum|min|naaṣireen."
29,26,"Faʹaamana|lahoo|Looṭ.|Wa-q̣aala|ʹinnee|muhaajirun|ʹilaa|Rabbee;|ʹinnahoo|Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
29,27,"Wa-wahabnaa|lahooo|ʹIs-ḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|wa-jaʻalnaa|fee|ẓurriyyatihin|Nubuwwata|wal-Kitaaba|wa-ʹaataynaahu|ʹajrahoo|fid|dunyaa;|wa-ʹinnahoo|fil|ʹAakhirati|laminaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen:"
29,28,"Wa-Looṭan|ʹiẓ|q̣aala|liq̣awmiheee|ʹinnakum|lataʹtoonal|faaḥishata|maa-|sabaq̣akum̃|bihaa|min|ʹaḥadim|minal|ʻAalameen."
29,29,"ʹAʹinnakum|lataʹtoonar|rijaala|wa-taq̣ṭaʻoonas|sabeel?|Wa-taʹtoona|fee|naadeekumul|muñkar?|Famaa|kaana|jawaaba|q̣awmiheee|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aaluʹ|tinaa|biʻAẓaabil|laahi|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een."
29,30,"Q̣aala|Rabbiñ|ṣurnee|ʻalal|q̣awmil|mufsideen!"
29,31,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹat|Rusulunaaa|ʹIbraaheema|bil-bushraa|q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|muhlikooo|ʹahli|haaẓihil|q̣aryah:|ʹinna|ʹahlahaa|kaanoo|z̤̣aalimeen."
29,32,"Q̣aala|ʹinna|feeha|Looṭaa.|Q̣aaloo|naḥnu|ʹaʻlamu|bimañ|feehaa.|Lanunajjiyannahoo|wa-ʹahlahooo|ʹillam|raʹatahoo|kaanat|minal|g̣aabireen!"
29,33,"Wa-lammaaa|ʹañ|jaaaʹat|Rusulunaa|Looṭañ|seeeʹa|bihim|wa-ḍaaq̣a|bihim|ẓarʻañw|waq̣aaloo|laa-|takhaf|wa-laa|taḥzan:|ʹinnaa|munajjooka|wa-ʹahlaka|ʹillam|raʹataka|kaanat|minal|g̣aabireen."
29,34,"ʹInnaa|muñziloona|ʻalaaa|ʹahli|Haaẓihil|q̣aryati|Rijzam|minas|samaaaʹi|bimaa|kaanoo|yafsuq̣oon."
29,35,"Wa-laq̣at|taraknaa|min-haaa|ʹAayatam|bayyinatal|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
29,36,"Wa-ʹilaa|Madyana|ʹakhaahum|shuʻaybañ|faq̣aala|yaa-q̣awmiʻ|budul|laaha|warjul|Yawmal|ʹAakhira|wa-laa|taʻs̤aw|fil|ʹarḍi|mufsideen."
29,37,"Fakaẓẓaboohu|faʹakhaẓathumur|rajfatu|faʹaṣbaḥoo|fee|daarihim|jaas̤imeen."
29,38,"Wa-ʻAadañw|Wa-S̤amooda|waq̣at|tabayyana|lakum|mim|masaakinihim.|Wa-zayyana|lahumush|Shayṭaanu|ʹaʻmaalahum|faṣaddahum|ʻanis|Sabeeli|wa-kaanoo|Mustabṣireen."
29,39,"Wa-Q̣aaroona|wa-Firʻawna|wa-Haamaan:|wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹahum|Moosaa|bil-Bayyinaati|fastakbaroo|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|kaanoo|saabiq̣een."
29,40,"Fakullan|ʹakhaẓnaa|biẓambih:|faminhum|man|ʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhi|ḥaaṣibaa;|wa-minhum|man|ʹakhaẓathuṣ|Ṣayḥah;|wa-minhum|man|khasafnaa|bihil|ʹarḍ:|wa-minhum|man|ʹag̣raq̣naa:|wa-maa|kaanal|laahu|liyaz̤̣limahum|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
29,41,"Mas̤alul|laẓeenat|takhaẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹawliyaaaʹa|kamas̤alil|ʻAñkaboot:|ʹittakhaẓat|baytaa!|Wa-ʹinna|ʹawhanal|buyooti|labaytul|ʻAñkaboot.|Law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoon."
29,42,"ʹInnal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|miñ|shayʹ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
29,43,"Wa-tilkal|ʹAms̤aalu|naḍribuhaa|linnaasi|wa-maa|yaʻq̣iluhaaa|ʹillal|ʻAalimoon."
29,44,"Khalaq̣al|laahus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bilḥaq̣q̣.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|lil-Muʹmineen."
29,45,"ʹUtlu|maaa|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayka|minal|Kitaabi|wa-ʹaq̣imiṣ|Ṣalaah:|ʹinnaṣ|Ṣalaata|tanhaa|ʻanil|faḥshaaaʹi|wal-muñkar;|wa-la-Ẓikrul|laahi|ʹAkbar.|Wal-laahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|taṣnaʻoon."
29,46,"Wa-laa|tujaadilooo|ʹAhlal|Kitaabi|ʹillaa|billatee|hiya|ʹaḥsanu|ʹillal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|minhum|wa-q̣oolooo|ʹaamannaa|billaẓeee|ʹuñzila|ʹilaynaa|wa-ʹuñzila|ʹilaykum|wa-ʹIlaahunaa|wa-ʹIlaahukum|Waaḥiduñwwa|naḥnu|lahoo|Muslimoon."
29,47,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykal|Kitaab.|Fallaẓeena|ʹaataynaahumul|Kitaaba|yuʹminoona|bihee|wa-min|haaaʹulaaaʹi|mañy|yuʹminu|bih:|wa-maa|yajḥadu|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹillal|kaafiroon."
29,48,"Wa-maa|kuñta|tatloo|miñ|q̣ablihee|miñ|kitaabiñw|walaa|takhuṭṭuhoo|biyameenika|ʹiẓal|lartaabal|mubṭiloon."
29,49,"Bal|huwa|ʹAayaatum|bayyinaatuñ|fee|ṣudooril|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻilm:|wa-maa|yajḥadu|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹillaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
29,50,"Wa-q̣aaloo|Law-laaa|ʹuñzila|ʻalayhi|ʹAayaatum|mir|Rabbih?|Q̣ul|ʹinnamal|ʹAayaatu|ʻiñdal|laah:|wa-ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|naẓeerum|mubeen."
29,51,"ʹA-walam|yakfihim|ʹannaaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|yutlaa|ʻalayhim?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|la-Raḥmatañw|wa-Ẓikraa|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
29,52,"Q̣ul|kafaa|billaahi|baynee|wa-baynakum|Shaheedaa:|yaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|bil-baaṭili|wa-kafaroo|billaahi|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
29,53,"Wa-yastaʻjiloonaka|bilʻAẓaab:|Wa-lawlaaa|ʹajalum|musammal|lajaaaʹahumul|ʻAẓaab:|walayaʹtiyannahum̃|bag̣tatañw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon!"
29,54,"Yastaʻjiloonaka|bilʻAẓaab:|wa-ʹinna|Jahannama|lamuḥeeṭatum|bil-kaafireen!"
29,55,"Yawma|yag̣shaahumul|ʻaẓaabu|miñ|fawq̣ihim|wa-miñ|taḥti|ʹarjulihim|wa-yaq̣oolu|ẓooq̣oo|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
29,56,"Yaa-ʻibaadiyal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹinna|ʹarḍee|waasiʻatuñ|faʹiyyaaya|faʻbudoon!"
29,57,"Kullu|nafsiñ|ẓaaaʹiq̣atul|Mawt:|s̤umma|ʹilaynaa|turjaʻoon."
29,58,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|Ṣaaliḥaati|lanubawwiʹannahum|minal|Jannati|g̣urafañ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa;―|niʻma|ʹajrul|ʻaamileen!"
29,59,"ʹAllaẓeena|ṣabaroo|wa-ʻalaa|Rabbihim|yatawakkaloon."
29,60,"Wa-kaʹayyim|miñ|daaabbatil|laa|taḥmilu|rizq̣ahaa?|ʹAllaahu|yarzuq̣uhaa|wa-ʹiyyaakum|wa-Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
29,61,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|man|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-sakhkharash|shamsa|wal-q̣amara|layaq̣oolunnal|laahu|faʹannaa|yuʹfakoon?"
29,62,"ʹAllaahu|yabsuṭur|rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadihee|wa-yaq̣diru|lah:|ʹinnal|laaha|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
29,63,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|man|nazzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|faʹaḥyaa|bihil|ʹarḍa|mim|baʻdi|mawtihaa|layaq̣oolunnal|laah!|Q̣ulil|Ḥamdu|lillaah!|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon."
29,64,"Wa-maa|haaẓihil|ḥayaatud|dunyaaa|ʹillaa|lahwuñw|walaʻib?|Wa-ʹinnad|Daaral|ʹAakhirata|lahiyal|Ḥayawaan.|Law|kaanu|yaʻlamoon."
29,65,"Faʹiẓaa|rakiboo|fil|fulki|daʻawul|laaha|mukhliṣeena|lahud|deen:|falammaa|najjaahum|ʹilal|barri|ʹiẓaa|hum|yushrikoon!"
29,66,"Liyakfuroo|bimaaa|ʹaataynaahum,|wa-li-yatamattaʻoo!|fasawfa|yaʻlamoon."
29,67,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannaa|jaʻalnaa|Ḥaraman|ʹaaminañw|Wayutakhaṭṭafun|naasu|min|ḥaw-lihim?|ʹAfabilbaaṭili|yuʹminoona|wa-biniʻmatil|laahi|yakfuroon?"
29,68,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimma|nif-taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|ʹaw|kaẓẓaba|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|lammaa|jaaaʹah?|ʹAlaysa|fee|Jahannama|mas̤wal|lil-kaafireen?"
29,69,"Wallaẓeena|jaahadoo|feenaa|lanahdiyannahum|Subulanaa;|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|lamaʻal|Muḥsineen."
30,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Meeem."
30,2,"G̣ulibatir|Room."
30,3,"Feee|ʹadnal|ʹarḍi|wa-hum|mim|baʻdi|g̣alabihim|sayag̣liboon."
30,4,"Fee|biḍʻi|sineen.|Lillaahil|ʹAmru|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-mim|baʻd:|Wa-yawmaʹiẓiñy|yafraḥul|Muʹminoon."
30,5,"Binaṣril|laah.|Yañṣuru|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
30,6,"Waʻdal|laah.|Laaʹ|yukhliful|laahu|waʻdahu|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
30,7,"Yaʻlamoona|z̤̣aahiram|minal|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-hum|ʻanil|ʹAakirati|hum|g̣aafiloon."
30,8,"ʹAwalam|yatafakkaroo|feee|ʹañfusihim?|Maa-|khalaq̣al|laahus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaaa|ʹillaa|bil-ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹajalim|musammaa:|wa-ʹinna|kas̤eeram|minan|naasi|biliq̣aaaʹi|Rabbihim|lakaafiroon!"
30,9,"ʹAwalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fayañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim?|Kaanooo|ʹashadda|minhum|q̣uwwatañw|waʹas̤aarul|ʹarḍa|wa-ʻamaroohaaa|ʹaks̤ara|mimmaa|ʻamaroohaa|wa-jaaaʹathum|rusuluhum̃|bil-Bayyinaat:|famaa|kaanal|laahu|liyaz̤̣limahum|wa-laakiñ|kaanooo|ʹañfusahum|yaz̤̣limoon."
30,10,"S̤umma|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatal|laẓeena|ʹasaaaʹus|soooʹaaa|ʹañ|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatil|laahi|wa-kaanoo|bihaa|yastahziʹoon."
30,11,"ʹAllaahu|yabdaʹul|khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduhoo|s̤umma|ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
30,12,"Wa-Yawma|taq̣oomus|Saaʻatu|yublisul|mujrimoon."
30,13,"Wa-lam|yakul|lahum|miñ|Shurakaaaʹihim|shufaʻaaaʹu|wa-kaanoo|bi-Shurakaaaʹihim|kaafireen."
30,14,"Wa-Yawma|taq̣oomus|Saaʻatu|Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yatafarraq̣oon."
30,15,"Faʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|fahum|fee|Rawḍatiñy|yuḥbaroon."
30,16,"Wa-ʹammal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-liq̣aaaʹil|ʹAakhirati|faʹulaaaʹika|fil|ʻaẓaabi|muḥḍaroon."
30,17,"Fa-Subḥaanal|laahi|ḥeena|tumsoona|waḥeena|tuṣbiḥoon."
30,18,"Wa-lahul|Ḥamdu|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-ʻashiyyañw|waḥeena|tuz̤̣hiroon."
30,19,"Yukhrijul|ḥayya|minal|mayyiti|wa-yukhrijul|mayyita|minal|ḥayyi|wa-yuḥyil|ʹarḍa|baʻda|mawtihaa:|wa-kaẓaalika|tukhrajoon."
30,20,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatiheee|ʹan|khalaq̣akum|miñ|turaabiñ|s̤umma|ʹiẓaaa|ʹañtum̃|basharuñ|tañtashiroon!"
30,21,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatiheee|ʹan|khalaq̣a|lakum|min|ʹañfusikum|ʹazwaajal|litaskunooo|ʹilayhaa|wa-jaʻala|baynakum|mawaddatañw|waraḥmah:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
30,22,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatihee|khalq̣us|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wakhtilaafu|ʹalsinatikum|wa-ʹalwaanikum:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|lilʻaalimeen."
30,23,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatihee|manaamukum̃|bil-layli|wannahaari|wabtig̣aaaʹukum|miñ|faḍlih:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yasmaʻoon."
30,24,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatihee|yureekumul|barq̣a|khawfañw|waṭamaʻañw|wayunazzilu|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|fayuḥyee|bihil|ʹarḍa|baʻda|mawtihaa:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
30,25,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatiheee|ʹañ|taq̣oomas|samaaaʹu|wal-ʹarḍu|biʹAmrih:|s̤umma|ʹiẓaa|daʻaakum|daʻwatam|minal|ʹarḍi|ʹiẓaaa|ʹañtum|takhrujoon."
30,26,"Wa-lahoo|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|kullul|lahoo|q̣aanitoon."
30,27,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|yabdaʹul|khalq̣a|s̤umma|yuʻeeduhoo|wa-huwa|ʹahwanu|ʻalayh.|wa-lahul|Mas̤alul|ʹAʻlaa|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
30,28,"Ḍaraba|lakum|mas̤alam|min|ʹañfusikum:|hal|lakum|mim|maa|malakat|ʹaymaanukum|miñ|shurakaaaʹa|fee|maa-|razaq̣naakum|faʹañtum|feehi|sawaaaʹuñ|takhaafoonahum|kakheefatikum|ʹañfusakum?|Kaẓaalika|nufaṣṣilul|ʹAayaati|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
30,29,"Balit|tabaʻal|laẓeena|z̤̣alamooo|ʹahwaaaʹahum̃|big̣ayri|ʻilm.|famañy|yahdee|man|ʹaḍallal|laah?|Wa-maa|lahum|min|naaṣireen."
30,30,"Faʹaq̣im|wajhaka|lid-Deeni|ḥaneefaa:|Fiṭratal|laahil|latee|faṭaran|naasa|ʻalayhaa:|laa-|tabdeela|likhalq̣il|laah:|ẓaalikad|Deenul|Q̣ayyimu|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
30,31,"Muneebeena|ʹilayhi|wattaq̣oohu|wa-ʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-laa|takoonoo|minal|mushrikeen;"
30,32,"Minal|laẓeena|farraq̣oo|Deenahum|wa-kaanoo|Shiyaʻaa:|kullu|ḥizbim|bimaa|ladayhim|fariḥoon!"
30,33,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|massan|naasa|ḍurruñ|daʻaw|Rabbahum|muneebeena|ʹilayhi|s̤umma|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaẓaaq̣ahum|minhu|Raḥmatan|ʹiẓaa|fareeq̣um|minhum̃|bi-Rabbihim|yushrikoon,―"
30,34,"Liyakfuroo|bimaaa|ʹaataynaahum!|Fatamattaʻoo:|fasawfa|taʻlamoon."
30,35,"ʹAm|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalayhim|Sulṭaanañ|fahuwa|yatakallamu|bimaa|kaanoo|bihee|yushrikoon?"
30,36,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹaẓaq̣nan|naasa|Raḥmatañ|fariḥoo|bihaa:|wa-ʹiñ|tuṣibhum|sayyiʹatum|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeehim|ʹiẓaa|hum|yaq̣naṭoon!"
30,37,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannal|laaha|yabsuṭur|rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaq̣dir?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon."
30,38,"Faʹaati|ẓal|q̣urbaa|ḥaq̣q̣ahoo|walmiskeena|wabnas|sabeel.|Ẓaalika|khayrul|lil-laẓeena|yureedoona|Wajhal|laahi|wa-ʹulaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
30,39,"Wa-maaa|ʹaataytum|mir|Ribal|liyarbuwa|feee|ʹamwaalin|naasi|falaa|yarboo|ʻiñdal|laah;|wa-maaa|ʹaataytum|miñ|Zakaatiñ|tureedoona|Wajhal|laahi|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|muḍʻifoon."
30,40,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|s̤umma|razaq̣akum|s̤umma|yumeetukum|s̤umma|yuḥyeekum.|Hal|miñ|Shurakaaaʹikum|mañy|yafʻalu|miñ|ẓaalikum|miñ|shayʹ?|Sub-ḥaanahoo|wa-taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
30,41,"Z̤̣aharal|fasaadu|fil|barri|wal-baḥri|bimaa|kasabat|ʹaydin|naasi|liyuẓeeq̣ahum|baʻḍal|laẓee|ʻamiloo|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
30,42,"Q̣ul|seeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣abl.|Kaana|ʹaks̤aruhum|mushrikeen."
30,43,"Faʹaq̣im|wajhaka|lid-Deenil|Q̣ayyimi|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|yawmul|laa|maradda|lahoo|minal|laahi|Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yaṣṣaddaʻoon."
30,44,"Mañ|kafara|faʻalayhi|kufruh:|wa-man|ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|faliʹañfusihim|yamhadoon:"
30,45,"Liyajziyal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|miñ|faḍlih.|ʹInnahoo|laa-|yuḥibbul|kaafireen."
30,46,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatiheee|ʹañy|yursilar|riyaaḥa|mubashshiraatiñw|wa-li-yuẓeeq̣akum|mir|Raḥmatihee|wa-litajriyal|fulku|biʹAmrihee|wa-litabtag̣oo|miñ|Faḍlihee|wa-laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
30,47,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|rusulan|ʹilaa|q̣awmihim|fajaaaʹoohum̃|bil-bayyinaati|fañtaq̣amnaa|minal|laẓeena|ʹajramoo:|wa-kaana|ḥaq̣q̣an|ʻalaynaa|naṣrul|Muʹmineen."
30,48,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|yursilur|riyaaḥa|fatus̤eeru|saḥaabañ|fayabsuṭuhoo|fis|samaaaʹi|kayfa|yashaaaʹu|wa-yajʻaluhoo|kisafañ|fataral|wadq̣a|yakhruju|min|khilaalih:|faʹiẓaaa|ʹaṣaaba|bihee|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadiheee|ʹiẓaa|hum|yastabshiroon!―"
30,49,"Wa-iñ|kaanoo|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yunazzala|ʻalayhim|miñ|q̣ablihee|lamubliseen!"
30,50,"Fañz̤̣ur|ʹilaaa|ʹaas̤aari|Raḥmatil|laahi|kayfa|yuḥyil|ʹarḍa|baʻda|mawtihaa!|ʹinna|Ẓaalika|la-Muḥyil|mawtaa:|wa-Huwaa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
30,51,"Wa-laʹin|arsalnaa|reeḥañ|faraʹawhu|muṣfarral|laz̤̣alloo|mim|baʻdihee|yakfuroon!"
30,52,"Faʹinnaka|laa-|tusmiʻul|mawtaa|wa-laa|tusmiʻuṣ|ṣummad|duʻaaaʹa|ʹiẓaa|wallaw|mudbireen."
30,53,"Wa-maaa|ʹañta|bihaadil|ʻumyi|ʻañ|ḍalaalatihim:|ʹiñ|tusmiʻu|illaa|mañy|yuʹminu|biʹAayaatinaa|fahum|Muslimoon."
30,54,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|miñ|ḍaʻfiñ|summa|jaʻala|mim|baʻdi|ḍaʻfiñ|q̣uwwatañ|s̤umma|jaʻala|mim|baʻdi|q̣uwwatiñ|ḍaʻfañw|washaybah:|yakhluq̣u|maa-|yashaaaʹu|wa-Huwal|ʻAleemul|Q̣adeer."
30,55,"Wa-Yawma|taq̣oomus|Saaʻatu|yuq̣simul|mujrimoona|maa-|labis̤oo|g̣ayra|saaʻah:|kaẓaalika|kaanoo|yuʹfakoon!"
30,56,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻilma|wal-ʹeemaana|laq̣ad|labis̤tum|fee|Kitaabil|laahi|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Baʻs̤:|fahaaẓaa|Yawmul|Baʻs̤i|wa-laakinnakum|kuñtum|laa-|taʻlamoon!"
30,57,"Fa-Yawmaʹiẓil|laa|yañfaʻul|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|maʻẓiratuhum|wa-laa|hum|yustaʻtaboon."
30,58,"Wa-laq̣ad|ḍarabnaa|linnaasi|fee|haaẓal|Q̣URʹAANI|miñ|kulli|mas̤al:|wa-laʹiñ|jiʹtahum̃|biʹAayatil|layaq̣oolannal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹin|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|mubṭiloon."
30,59,"Kaẓaalika|yaṭbaʻul|laahu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobil|laẓeena|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
30,60,"Faṣbir|ʹinna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|walaa|yastakhiffannakal|laẓeena|laa-|yooq̣inoon."
31,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Meeem."
31,2,"Tilka|ʹAayaatul|Kitaabil|Ḥakeem,―"
31,3,"Hudañw|Wa-Raḥmatal|lil-Muḥsineen,"
31,4,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuq̣eemoonaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-yuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wa-hum̃|bil-ʹAakhirati|hum|yooq̣inoon."
31,5,"ʹUlaaaʹika|ʻalaa|Hudam|mir|Rabbihim|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
31,6,"Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yashtaree|lahwal|ḥadees̤i|liyuḍilla|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|big̣ayri|ʻilmiñw|Wayattakhiẓahaa|huzuwaa:|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻAẓaabum|muheen."
31,7,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhi|ʹAayaatunaa|wallaa|mustakbirañ|kaʹal|lam|yasmaʻhaa|kaʹanna|feee|ʹuẓunayhi|waq̣raa:|fabashshirhu|biʻAẓaabin|ʹaleem."
31,8,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|lahum|Jannaatun|Naʻeem.―"
31,9,"Khaalideena|feehaa.|Waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣aa:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
31,10,"Khalaq̣as|samaawaati|big̣ayri|ʻamadiñ|tarawnahaa|wa-ʹalq̣aa|fil|ʹarḍi|rawaasiya|ʹañ|tameeda|bikum|wa-bas̤s̤a|feehaa|miñ|kulli|daaabbah.|Wa-ʹañzalnaa|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|faʹambatnaa|feehaa|miñ|kulli|zawjiñ|kareem."
31,11,"Haaẓaa|khalq̣ul|laahi|faʹaroonee|maa-ẓaa|khalaq̣al|laẓeena|miñ|doonih:|baliz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
31,12,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Luq̣maanal|Ḥikmata|ʹanish|kur|lillaah.|Wa-mañy|yashkur|faʹinnamaa|yashkuru|linafsih:|wa-mañ|kafara|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣aniyyun|Ḥameed."
31,13,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Luq̣maanu|libnihee|wa-huwa|yaʻiz̤̣uhoo|yaabunayya|laa-|tushrik|billaah.|ʹInnash|shirka|laz̤̣ulmun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
31,14,"Wa-waṣṣaynal|ʹiñsaana|biwaalidayh:|ḥamalathu|ʹummuhoo|wahnan|ʻalaa|wahniñw|wafiṣaaluhoo|fee|ʻaamayni|ʹanish|kur|lee|waliwaalidayka|ʹilayyal|Maṣeer."
31,15,"Wa-ʹiñ|jaahadaaka|ʻalaaa|ʹañ|tushrika|bee|maa-|laysa|laka|bihee|ʻilmuñ|falaa|tuṭiʻhumaa|waṣaaḥibhumaa|fid|dunyaa|maʻroofañw|wattabiʻ|sabeela|man|ʹanaaba|ʹilayy:|s̤umma|ʹilayya|marjiʻukum|faʹunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
31,16,"Yaabunayya|ʹinnahaaa|ʹiñ|taku|mis̤q̣aala|ḥabbatim|min|khardaliñ|fatakuñ|fee|ṣakhratin|ʹaw|fis|samaawaati|ʹaw|fil|ʹarḍi|yaʹti|bihal|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|Laṭeefun|Khabeer."
31,17,"Yaa|bunyya|ʹaq̣imiṣ-Ṣalaata|waʹmur|bilmaʻroofi|wanha|ʻanil|muñkari|waṣbir|ʻalaa|maaa|ʹaṣaabak:|ʹinna|ẓaalika|min|ʻazmil|ʹumoor."
31,18,"Wa-laa|tuṣaʻʻir|khaddaka|linnaasi|wa-laa|tamshi|fil|ʹarḍi|maraḥaa;|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yuḥibbu|kulla|mukhtaaliñ|fakhoor."
31,19,"Waq̣ṣid|fee|mashyika|wag̣ḍuḍ|miñ|ṣawtik;|ʹinna|ʹañkaral|ʹaṣwaati|laṣawtul|ḥameer."
31,20,"ʹAlam|taraw|ʹannal|laaha|sakhkhara|lakum|maa|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹasbag̣a|ʻalaykum|niʻamahoo|z̤̣aahiratañw|wa baaṭinah?|Wa-minan|naasi|mañy|yujaadilu|fil|laahi|big̣ayri|ʻilmiñw|walaa|hudañw|walaa|kitaabim|muneer."
31,21,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahumut|tabiʻoo|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|q̣aaloo|bal|nattabiʻu|maa-|wajadnaa|ʻalayhi|ʹaabaaaʹanaa.|ʹAwalaw|kaanash|Shayṭaanu|yadʻoohum|ʹilaa|ʻaẓaabis|Saʻeer?"
31,22,"Wa-mañy|yuslim|wajhahooo|ʹilal|laahi|wa-huwa|Muḥsinuñ|faq̣adis|tamsaka|bilʻurwatil|wus̤q̣aa:|wa-ʹilal|laahi|ʻAaq̣ibatul|ʹumoor."
31,23,"Wa-mañ|kafara|falaa|yaḥzuñka|kufruh:|ʹilaynaa|Marjiʻuhum|fanunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|ʻamiloo:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
31,24,"Numattiʻuhum|q̣aleelañ|s̤umma|naḍṭarruhum|ʹilaa|ʻaẓaabin|g̣aleez̤̣."
31,25,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|man|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|layaq̣oolunnal|laah.|Q̣ulil|Ḥamdu|lillaah!|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
31,26,"Lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|ʹinnal|laaha|Huwal|G̣aniyyul|Ḥameed."
31,27,"Walaw|ʹannamaa-|fil|ʹarḍi|miñ|shajaratin|ʹaq̣laamuñw|wal-baḥru|yamudduhoo|mim|baʻdihee|sabʻatu|ʹabḥurim|maa|nafidat|Kalimaatul|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|Ḥakeem."
31,28,"Maa-|khalq̣ukum|wa-laa|baʻs̤ukum|ʹillaa|kanafsiñw|waaḥidah:|ʹinnal|laaha|Sameeʻum|Baṣeer."
31,29,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|yoolijul|layla|fin|nahaari|wa-yoolijun|nahaara|fil|layli|wa-sakhkharash|shamsa|wal-q̣amar:|kulluñy|yajreee|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammañw|waʹannal|laaha|bimaa|taʻmaloona|khabeer?"
31,30,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|Huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|waʹanna|maa-|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihil|Baaṭilu|wa-ʹannal|laaha|Huwal|ʻAliyyul|Kabeer."
31,31,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|fulka|tajree|fil|baḥri|biniʻmatil|laahi|liyuriyakum|min|ʹAayaatih?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|likulli|ṣabbaariñ|shakoor."
31,32,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|g̣ashiyahum|mawjuñ|kaz̤̣z̤̣ulali|daʻawul|laaha|Mukhliṣeena|lahud|deen.|Falammaa|najjaahum|ʹilal|barri|faminhum|muq̣taṣid.|Wa-maa|yajḥadu|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹillaa|kullu|khattariñ|kafoor!"
31,33,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasut|taq̣oo|Rabbakum|wakhshaw|yawmal|laa|yajzee|waalidun|ʻañw|waladihee|wa-laa|mawloodun|huwa|jaazin|ʻañw|waalidihee|shayʹaa.|ʹInna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñ|falaa|tag̣urrannakumul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa:|wa-laa|yag̣urrannakum̃|billaahil|G̣aroor."
31,34,"ʹInnal|laaha|ʻiñdahoo|ʻilmus|Saaʻah.|Wa-yunazzilul|g̣ays̤a|wayaʻlamu|maa-|fil|ʹarḥaam.|Wa-maa|tadree|nafsum|maaẓaa|taksibu|g̣adaa:|wamaa|tadree|nafsum|biʹayyi|ʹarḍiñ|tamoot.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAleemun|khabeer."
32,1,"ʹAlif-Laaam-Meeem."
32,2,"Tañzeelul|Kitaabi|laa-|rayba|feehi|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
32,3,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloonaf|taraah?|Bal|huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbika|lituñẓira|q̣awmam|maaa|ʹataahum|min|naẓeerim|miñ|q̣ablika|laʻallahum|yahtadoon."
32,4,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaa|fee|sittati|ʹAyyaamiñ|s̤ummas|tawaa|ʻalal|ʻArsh:|maa-|lakum|miñ|doonihee|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa-|shafeeʻ:|ʹafalaa|tataẓakkaroon?"
32,5,"Yudabbirul|ʹamra|minas|samaaaʹi|ʹilal|ʹarḍi|s̤umma|yaʻruju|ʹilayhi|fee|yawmiñ|kaana|miq̣daaruhooo|ʹalfa|sanatim|mimmaa|taʻuddoon."
32,6,"Ẓaalika|ʻAalimul|g̣aybi|washshahaadatil|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem;―"
32,7,"ʹAllaẓeee|ʹaḥsana|kulla|shayʹin|khalaq̣ahoo|wa-badaʹa|khalq̣al|ʹiñsaani|miñ|ṭeen;"
32,8,"S̤umma|jaʻala|naslahoo|miñ|sulaalatim|mim|maaaʹim|maheen:"
32,9,"S̤umma|sawwaahu|wa-nafakha|feehi|mir|Rooḥihee|wa-jaʻala|lakumus|samʻa|wal-ʹabṣaara|wal-ʹafʹidah:|q̣aleelam|maa|tashkuroon!"
32,10,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹa-ʹiẓaa|ḍalalnaa|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lafee|khalq̣iñ|jadeed?|Bal|hum̃|bi-Liq̣aaaʹi|Rabbihim|kaafiroon!"
32,11,"Q̣ul|yatawaffaakum|Malakul|Mawtil|laẓee|wukkila|bikum|s̤umma|ʹilaa|Rabbikum|turjaʻoon."
32,12,"Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓil|mujrimoona|naakisoo|ruʹoosihim|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|Rabbanaaa|ʹabṣarnaa|wa-samiʻnaa|farjiʻnaa|naʻmal|ṣaaliḥan|ʹinnaa|mooq̣inoon."
32,13,"Wa-law|shiʹnaa|laʹaataynaa|kulla|nafsin|hudaahaa|wa-laakin|ḥaq̣q̣al|Q̣awlu|minnee|laʹamlaʹanna|Jahannama|minal|jinnati|wannaasi|ʹajmaʻeen."
32,14,"faẓooq̣oo|bimaa|naseetum|Liq̣aaaʹa|Yawmikum|haaẓaa.|ʹInnaa|naseenaakum|waẓooq̣oo|ʻAẓaabal|khuldi|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon!"
32,15,"ʹInnamaa|yuʹminu|biʹAayaatinal|laẓeena|ʹiẓaa|ẓukkiroo|bihaa|kharroo|sabbaḥoo|sujjadañwwa|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbihim|Wahum|laa-|yastakbiroon."
32,16,"Tatajaafaa|junoobuhum|ʻanil|maḍaajiʻi|yadʻoona|Rabbahum|khawfañw|waṭamaʻaa:|wa-mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|yuñfiq̣oon."
32,17,"Falaa|taʻlamu|nafsum|maaa|ʹukhfiya|lahum|miñ|q̣urrati|ʹaʻyun:|jazaaaʹam|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
32,18,"ʹAfamañ|kaana|muʹminañ|kamañ|kaana|faasiq̣aa?|Laa-|yastawoon."
32,19,"ʹAmmal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|falahum|Jannaatul|maʹwaa,|nuzulam|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
32,20,"Wa-ʹammal|laẓeena|fasaq̣oo|famaʹwaahumun|Naar:|kullamaaa|ʹaraadooo|ʹañy|yakhrujoo|minhaaa|ʹuʻeedoo|feehaa|wa-q̣eela|lahum|ẓooq̣oo|ʻAẓaaban|Naaril|laẓee|kuñtum̃|bihee|tukaẓẓiboon."
32,21,"Wa-lanuẓeeq̣an-nahum|minal|ʻAẓaabil|ʹadnaa|doonal|ʻAẓaabil|ʹakbari|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
32,22,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmañ|ẓukkira|biʹAayaati|Rabbihee|s̤umma|ʹaʻraḍa|ʻanhaa?|ʹInnaa|minal|mujrimeena|muñtaq̣imoon."
32,23,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|falaa|takuñ|fee|miryatim|mil|liq̣aaaʹihee|wa-jaʻalnaahu|hudal|li-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel."
32,24,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|minḥum|ʹAʹimmatañy|yahdoona|biʹAmrinaa|lammaa|ṣabaroo;|wa-kaanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|yooq̣inoon."
32,25,"ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwa|yafṣilu|baynahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|feemaa|kaanoo|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
32,26,"ʹAwalam|yahdi|lahum|kam|ʹahlaknaa|miñ|q̣ablihim|minal|q̣urooni|yamshoona|fee|masaakinihim?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaat:|ʹafalaa|yasmaʻoon?"
32,27,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannaa|nasooq̣ul|maaaʹa|ʹilal|ʹarḍil|juruzi|fanukhriju|bihee|zarʻañ|taʹkulu|minhu|ʹanʻaamuhum|wa-ʹañfusuhum?|ʹAfalaa|yubṣiroon?"
32,28,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|Fatḥu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
32,29,"Q̣ul|Yawmal|Fatḥi|laa-|yañfaʻul|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹeemaanuhum|wa-laa|hum|yuñz̤̣aroon."
32,30,"Faʹaʻriḍ|ʻanhum|wañtaz̤̣ir|ʹinnahum|muñtaz̤̣iroon."
33,1,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhan|Nabiyyut|taq̣il|laaha|wa-laa|tuṭiʻil|kaafireena|wal-Munaafiq̣een:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa."
33,2,"Wattabiʻ|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbik:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|bimaa|taʻmaloona|khabeeraa."
33,3,"Wa-tawakkal|ʻalal|laah:|wa-kafaa|billaahi|Wakeelaa."
33,4,"Maa-|jaʻalal|laahu|lirajulim|miñ|q̣albayni|fee|jawfih:|wa-maa|jaʻala|ʹazwaajakumul|laaaʹee|tuz̤̣aahiroona|minhunna|ʹummahaatikum:|wa-maa|jaʻala|ʹadʻiyaaaʹakum|ʹabnaaaʹakum.|Ẓaalikum|q̣awlukum̃|biʹafwaahikum.|Wallaahu|yaq̣oolul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-Huwa|yahdis|Sabeel."
33,5,"ʹUdʻoohum|liʹaabaaaʹihim|huwa|ʹaq̣saṭu|ʻiñdal|laah.|Faʹil|lam|taʻlamooo|ʹaabaaaʹahum|faʹikhwaanukum|fid|deeni|wa-mawaaleekum.|Wa-laysa|ʻalaykum|junaaḥuñ|feemaaa|ʹakhṭaʹtum̃|bihee|wa-laakim|maa|taʻammadat|q̣uloobukum:|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
33,6,"ʹAn-Nabiyyu|ʹawlaa|bil-Muʹmineena|min|ʹañfusihim|wa-ʹazwaajuhooo|ʹummahaatuhum.|Wa-ʹulul|ʹarḥaami|baʻḍuhum|ʹawlaa|bibaʻḍiñ|fee|Kitaabil|laahi|minal|Muʹmineena|wal-Muhaajireena|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|tafʻalooo|ʹilaaa|ʹawliyaaaʹikum|maʻroofaa:|kaana|ẓaalika|fil|Kitaabi|masṭooraa."
33,7,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹakhaẓnaa|minan|Nabiyyeena|Mees̤aaq̣ahum|wa-miñka|wa-min|Nooḥiñw|WaʹIbraaheema|wa-Moosaa|wa-ʻEesab|ni|Maryam:|wa-ʹakhaẓnaa|minhum|Mees̤aaq̣an|g̣aleez̤̣aa:"
33,8,"Liyasʹalaṣ|Ṣaadiq̣eena|ʻañ|Ṣidq̣ihim:|wa-ʹaʻadda|lilkaafireena|ʻAẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
33,9,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanuẓ|kuroo|Niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹatkum|junooduñ|faʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhim|reeḥañw|wajunoodal|lam|tarawhaa:|wa-kaanal|laahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeeraa."
33,10,"ʹIẓ|jaaaʹookum|miñ|fawq̣ikum|wa-min|ʹasfala|miñkum|wa-ʹiẓ|zaag̣atil|ʹabṣaaru|wa-balag̣atil|q̣uloobul|ḥanaajira|wa-taz̤̣unnoona|billaahiz̤̣|z̤̣unoonaa!"
33,11,"Hunaalikab|tuliyal|Muʹminoona|wa-zulziloo|zilzaalañ|shadeedaa."
33,12,"Wa-ʹiẓ|yaq̣oolul|Munaafiq̣oona|wallaẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍum|maa|waʻadanal|laahu|wa-Rasooluhooo|ʹillaa|g̣urooraa!"
33,13,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aalaṭ|ṭaaaʹifatum|minhum|yaaaʹAhla|Yas̤riba|laa-|muq̣aama|lakum|farjiʻoo!|Wa-yastaʹẓinu|fareeq̣um|minhumun|Nabiyya|yaq̣ooloona|ʹinna|buyootanaa|ʻawrah.|Wa-maa|hiya|biʻawratin|ʹiñy|yureedoona|ʹillaa|firaaraa."
33,14,"Wa-law|dukhilat|ʻalayhim|min|ʹaq̣ṭaarihaa|s̤umma|suʹilul|fitnata|laʹaatawhaa|wa-maa|talabbas̤oo|bihaaa|ʹillaa|yaseeraa!"
33,15,"Wa-laq̣ad|kaanoo|ʻaahadul|laaha|miñ|q̣ablu|laa-|yuwal-loonal|ʹadbaar:|wa-kaana|ʻahdul|laahi|masʹoolaa."
33,16,"Q̣ul|lañy|yañfaʻakumul|firaaru|ʹiñ|farartum|minal|mawti|ʹawil|q̣atli|wa-ʹiẓal|laa|tumattaʻoona|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa!"
33,17,"Q̣ul|mañ|ẓal|laẓee|yaʻṣimukum|minal|laahi|ʹin|ʹaraada|bikum|Soooʹan|ʹaw|ʹaraada|bikum|Raḥmah?|Wa-laa|yajidoona|lahum|miñ|doonil|laahi|wa-liyyañw|walaa|naṣeeraa."
33,18,"Q̣ad|yaʻlamul|laahul|muʻawwiq̣eena|miñkum|walq̣aaaʹileena|liʹikhwaanihim|halumma|ʹilaynaa,|wa-laa|yaʹtoonal|baʹsa|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa,"
33,19,"ʹAshiḥḥatan|ʻalaykum.|Faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹal|khawfu|raʹaytahum|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹilayka|tadooru|ʹaʻyunuhum|kallaẓee|yug̣shaa|ʻalayhi|minal|mawt:|Faʹiẓaa|ẓahabal|khawfu|salaq̣ookum̃|biʹalsinatin|ḥidaadin|ʹashiḥḥatan|ʻalal|khayr.|ʹUlaaaʹika|lam|yuʹminoo|faʹaḥbaṭal|laahu|ʹaʻmaalahum:|wa-kaana|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseeraa."
33,20,"Yaḥsaboonal|ʹAḤZAABA|lam|yaẓhaboo;|wa-ʹiñy|yaʹtil|ʹAḥzaabu|yawaddoo|law|ʹannahum̃|baadoona|fil|ʹAʻraabi|yasʹaloona|ʻan|ʹambaaaʹikum;|wa-law|kaanoo|feekum|maa|q̣aatalooo|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa."
33,21,"Laq̣ad|kaana|lakum|fee|Rasoolil|laahi|ʹUswatun|Ḥasanatul|limañ|kaana|yarjul|laaha|wal-Yawmal|ʹAakhira|waẓakaral|laaha|kas̤eeraa."
33,22,"Wa-lammaa|ra|ʹal-Muʹminoonal|ʹAḥzaaba|q̣aaloo|haaẓaa|maa-|waʻadanal|laahu|wa-Rasooluhoo|waṣadaq̣al|laahu|wa-Rasooluh.|Wa-maa|zaadahum|ʹillaaa|ʹeemaanañw|Watasleemaa."
33,23,"Minal|Muʹmineena|rijaaluñ|ṣadaq̣oo|maa-|ʻaahadul|laaha|ʻalayh:|faminhum|mañ|q̣aḍaa|naḥbahoo|wa-minhum|mañy|yañtaz̤̣ir:|wa-maa|baddaloo|tabdeelaa:"
33,24,"Liyajziyal|laahuṣ|Ṣaadiq̣eena|bi-Ṣidq̣ihim|wa-yuʻaẓẓibal|Munaafiq̣eena|ʹiñ|shaaaʹa|ʹaw|yatooba|ʻalayhim:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
33,25,"Wa-raddal|laahul|laẓeena|kafaroo|big̣ayz̤̣ihim|lam|yanaaloo|khayraa;|wa-kafal|laahul|Muʹmineenal|q̣itaal.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|Q̣awiyyan|ʻAzeezaa."
33,26,"Wa-ʹañzalal|laẓeena|z̤̣aaharoohum|min|ʹahlil|Kitaabi|miñ|ṣayaaṣeehim|wa-q̣aẓafa|fee|q̣uloobihi|mur-ruʻba|fareeq̣añ|taq̣tuloona|wa-taʹsiroona|fareeq̣aa."
33,27,"Wa-ʹawras̤akum|ʹarḍahum|wa-diyaarahum|wa-ʹamwaalahum|wa-ʹarḍal|lam|taṭaʹoohaa.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayiñ|Q̣adeeraa."
33,28,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|q̣ul|liʹazwaajika|ʹiñ|kuñtunna|turidnal|ḥayaatad|dunyaa|wa-zeenatahaa|fataʻaalayna|ʹumattiʻkunna|wa-ʹusarriḥkunna|saraahañ|jameelaa."
33,29,"Wa-ʹiñ|kuñtunna|turidnal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wad-Daaral|ʹAakhirata|faʹinnal|laaha|ʹaʻadda|lil-Muḥsinaati|miñ-kunna|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
33,30,"Yaa-Nisaaaʹan|Nabiyyi|mañy|yaʹti|miñkunna|bifaaḥishatim|mubayyinatiñy|yuḍaaʻaf|lahal|ʻAẓaabu|ḍiʻfayn:|wa-kaana|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseeraa."
33,31,"Wa-mañy|yaq̣nut|miñkunna|lillaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-taʻmal|ṣaaliḥan|nuʹtihaaa|ʹajrahaa|marratayni|wa-ʹaʻtadnaa|lahaa|Rizq̣añ|kareemaa."
33,32,"Yaa-Nisaaaʹan|Nabiyyi|lastunna|kaʹaḥadim|minan|nisaaaʹi|ʹinit|taq̣aytunna|falaa|takhḍaʻna|bilq̣awli|fayaṭmaʻal|laẓee|fee|q̣albihee|maraḍuñw|waq̣ulna|q̣awlam|maʻroofaa."
33,33,"Wa-q̣arna|fee|buyootikunna|wa-laa|tabarrajna|tabarrujal|Jaahiliyyatil|ʹoolaa|wa-ʹaq̣imnaṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaateenaz|Zakaata|wa-ʹaṭiʻnal|laaha|wa-Rasoolah.|ʹInnamaa|yureedul|laahu|liyuẓhiba|ʻañkumur|rijsa|ʹAhlal|Bayti|wa-yuṭahhirakum|taṭheeraa."
33,34,"Waẓkurna|maa-|yutlaa|fee|buyootikunna|min|ʹAayaatil|laahi|wal-Ḥikmah:|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|Laṭeefan|khabeeraa."
33,35,"ʹInnal|Muslimeena|wal-Muslimaati|wal-muʹmineena|wal-muʹminaati|walq̣aaniteena|walq̣aanitaati|waṣṣaadiq̣eena|waṣṣaadiq̣aati|waṣṣaabireena|waṣṣaabiraati|walkhaashiʻeena|walkhaashiʻaati|walmutaṣaddiq̣eena|walmutaṣaddiq̣aati|waṣṣaaaʹimeena|waṣṣaaaʹimaati|walḥaafiz̤̣eena|furoojahum|walḥaafiz̤̣aati|waẓ-ẓaakireenal|laaha|kas̤eerañw|waẓ-ẓaakiraati|ʹaʻaddal|laahu|lahum|mag̣firatañw|waʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
33,36,"Wa-maa|kaana|li-Muʹminiñw|walaa|Muʹminatin|ʹiẓaa|q̣aḍal|laahu|wa-Rasooluhooo|ʹamran|ʹañy|yakoona|lahumul|khiyaratu|min|ʹamrihim:|wa-mañy|yaʻṣil|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|faq̣ad|ḍalla|ḍalaalam|mubeenaa."
33,37,"Wa-ʹiẓ|taq̣oolu|lillaẓeee|ʹanʻamal|laahu|ʻalayhi|wa-ʹanʻamta|ʻalayhi|ʹamsik|ʻalayka|zawjaka|wattaq̣il|laaha|wa-tukhfee|fee|nafsika|mal|laahu|mubdeehi|watakhshan|naas.|Wallaahu|ʹaḥaq̣q̣u|ʹañ|takhshaah.|Falammaa|q̣aḍaa|Zaydum|minhaa|wa-ṭarañ|zawwajnaakahaa|likay|laa-|yakoona|ʻalal|Muʹmineena|ḥarajuñ|feee|ʹazwaaji|ʹadʻiyaaaʹihim|ʹiẓaa|q̣aḍaw|minhunna|waṭaraa.|Wa-kaana|ʹamrul|laahi|mafʻoolaa."
33,38,"Maa-|kaana|ʻalan|Nabiyyi|min|ḥarajiñ|feemaa|faraḍal|laahu|lah.|Sunnatal|laahi|fil|laẓeena|khalaw|miñ|q̣abl.|Wa-kaana|ʹamrul|laahi|q̣adaram|maq̣dooraa."
33,39,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuballig̣oona|Risaalaatil|laahi|wa-yakhshaw-nahoo|wa-laa|yakhshawna|ʹaḥadan|ʹillal|laah.|Wa-kafaa|billaahi|Ḥaseebaa."
33,40,"Maa-|kaana|Muḥammadun|ʹabaaa|ʹaḥadim|mir|rijaalikum|wa-laakir|Rasoolal|laahi|wa-Khaataman|Nabiyyeen:|wa-kaanal|laahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleemaa."
33,41,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanuẓ|kurul|laaha|ẓikrañ|kas̤eeraa;"
33,42,"Wa-sabbiḥoohu|bukratañw|waʹaṣeelaa."
33,43,"Huwal|laẓee|yuṣallee|ʻalaykum|wa-malaaaʹikatuhoo|liyukhrijakum|minaz̤̣|Z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|Noor:|wa-kaana|bil-Muʹmineena|Raḥeemaa."
33,44,"Taḥiyyatuhum|Yawma|yalq̣awnahoo|Salaam;|wa-ʹaʻadda|lahum|ʹAjrañ|Kareemaa."
33,45,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|ʹinnaaa|ʹarsalnaaka|Shaahidañw|Wa-Mubashshirañw|Wa-Naẓeeraa,"
33,46,"Wa-Daaʻiyan|ʹilal|laahi|biʹiẓnihee|wa-Siraajam|Muneeraa."
33,47,"Wa-bashshiril|Muʹmineena|biʹanna|lahum|minal|laahi|Faḍlañ|kabeeraa."
33,48,"Wa-laa|tuṭiʻil|kaafireena|wal-Munaafiq̣eena|wa-daʻ|ʹaẓaahum|wa-tawakkal|ʻalal|laah.|Wa-kafaa|billaahi|Wakeelaa."
33,49,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|nakaḥtumul|Muʹminaati|s̤umma|ṭallaq̣tumoohunna|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañt|amassoohunna|famaa|lakum|ʻalayhinna|min|ʻIddatiñ|taʻtaddoonahaa|famattiʻoohunna|wa-sarriḥoo-hunna|saraaḥañ|jameelaa."
33,50,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|ʹinnaaa|ʹaḥlalnaa|laka|ʹazwaajakal|laateee|ʹaatayta|ʹujoorahunna|wa-maa|malakat|yameenuka|mimmaaa|ʹafaaaʹal|laahu|ʻalayka|wa-banaati|ʻammika|wa-banaati|ʻammaatika|wa-banaati|khaalika|wa-banaati|khaalaatikal|laatee|haajarna|maʻak:|wamraʹatam|Muʹminatan|ʹiñw|wahabat|nafsahaa|lin-Nabiyyi|ʹin|ʹaraadan|Nabiyyu|ʹañy|yastañkiḥahaa;―|khaaliṣatal|laka|miñ|doonil|Muʹmineen;|q̣ad|ʻalimnaa|maa-|faraḍnaa|ʻalayhim|feee|ʹazwaajihim|wa-maa|malakat|ʹaymaanuhum|likaylaa|yakoona|ʻalayka|ḥaraj.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
33,51,"Turjee|mañ|tashaaaʹu|minhunna|wa-tuʹweee|ʹilayka|mañ|tashaaaʹ:|wa-manib|tag̣ayta|mimman|ʻazalta|falaa|junaaḥa|ʻalayk.|Ẓaalika|ʹadnaaa|ʹañ|taq̣arra|ʹaʻyunuhunna|wa-laa|yaḥzanna|wa-yarḍayna|bimaaa|ʹaataytahunna|kulluhunn:|wal-laahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|fee|q̣uloobikum:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAleeman|Ḥaleemaa."
33,52,"Laa-|yaḥillu|lakan|nisaaaʹu|mim|baʻdu|wa-laaa|ʹañ|tabaddala|bihinna|min|ʹazwaajiñw|Walaw|ʹaʻjabaka|ḥusnuhunna|ʹillaa|maa-|malakat|yameenuk:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹir|Raq̣eebaa."
33,53,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tadkhuloo|buyootan|Nabiyyi|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yuʹẓana|lakum|ʹilaa|ṭaʻaamin|g̣ayra|naaz̤̣ireena|ʹinaahu|wa-laakin|ʹiẓaa|duʻeetum|fadkhuloo|faʹiẓaa|ṭaʻimtum|fañtashiroo|wa-laa|mustaʹniseena|liḥadees̤.|ʹInna|ẓaalikum|kaana|yuʹẓin|Nabiyya|fayastaḥyee|miñkum;|wallaahu|laa-|yastaḥyee|minal|ḥaq̣q̣.|Wa-ʹiẓaa|saʹaltumoohunna|mataaʻañ|fasʹaloohunna|miñw|waraaaʹi|ḥijaab:|ẓaalikum|ʹaṭharu|liq̣uloobikum|wa-q̣uloobihinn.|Wa-maa|kaana|lakum|ʹañ|tuʹẓoo|Rasoolal|laahi|wa-laaa|ʹañ|tañkiḥooo|ʹazwaajahoo|mim|baʻdiheee|ʹabadaa.|ʹInna|ẓaalikum|kaana|ʻiñdal|laahi|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
33,54,"ʹIñ|tubdoo|shayʹan|ʹaw|tukhfoohu|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻaleemaa."
33,55,"Laa-|junaaḥa|ʻalayhinna|feee|ʹaabaaaʹihinna|wa-laaa|ʹabnaaaʹihinna|wa-laaa|ʹikhwaanihinna|wa-laaa|ʹabnaaaʹi|ʹikhwaanihinna|wa-laaa|ʹabnaaaʹi|ʹakhawaatihinna|wa-laa|nisaaaʹihinna|walaa|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanuhunn.|Wattaq̣eenal|laah;|ʹinnal|laaha|kaana|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Shaheedaa."
33,56,"ʹInnal|laaha|wa-Malaaaʹikatahoo|yuṣalloona|ʻalan|Nabiyy:|Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|ṣalloo|ʻalayhi|wa-sallimoo|tasleemaa."
33,57,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yuʹẓoonal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|laʻanahumul|laahu|fid|dunyaa|wal-ʹAakhirati|wa-ʹaʻadda|lahum|ʻAẓaabam|muheenaa."
33,58,"Wallaẓeena|yuʹẓoonal|Muʹmineena|wal-Muʹminaati|big̣ayri|mak|tasaboo|faq̣adiḥ|tamaloo|buhtaanañw|waʹis̤mam|mubeenaa."
33,59,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|q̣ul|liʹazwaajika|wa-banaatika|wa-nisaaaʹil|Muʹmineena|yudneena|ʻalayhinna|miñ|jalaabeebihinn:|ẓaalika|ʹadnaaa|ʹañy|yuʻrafna|falaa|yuʹẓayn.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
33,60,"Laʹil|lam|yañtahil|Munaafiq̣oona|wallaẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍuñw|walmurjifoona|fil|Madeenati|lanug̣riyannaka|bihim|s̤umma|laa-|yujaawiroonaka|feehaaa|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa:"
33,61,"Malʻooneena|ʹaynamaa|s̤uq̣ifooo|ʹukhiẓoo|wa-q̣uttiloo|taq̣teelaa."
33,62,"Sunnatal|laahi|fil|laẓeena|khalaw|miñ|q̣abl:|wa-lañ|tajida|li-Sunnatil|laahi|tabdeelaa."
33,63,"Yasʹalukan|naasu|ʻanis|Saaʻah:|q̣ul|ʹinnamaa|ʻilmuhaa|ʻiñdal|laah:|wa-maa|yudreeka|laʻallas|Saaʻata|takoonu|q̣areebaa!"
33,64,"ʹInnal|laaha|laʻanal|Kaafireena|wa-ʹaʻadda|lahum|Saʻeeraa,―"
33,65,"Khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa:|laa-|yajidoona|waliyyañw|walaa|naṣeeraa."
33,66,"Yawma|tuq̣allabu|wujoohuhum|fin|Naari|yaq̣ooloona|yaa-laytanaaa|ʹaṭaʻnal|laaha|wa-ʹaṭaʻnar|Rasoolaa!"
33,67,"Wa-q̣aaloo|Rabbanaaa|ʹinnaaa|ʹaṭaʻnaa|saadatanaa|wa-kubaraaaʹanaa|faʹaḍalloonas|sabeelaa."
33,68,"Rabbanaaa|ʹaatihim|ḍiʻfayni|minal|ʻAẓaabi|walʻanhum|Laʻnañ|kabeeraa!"
33,69,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|aamanoo|laa-ʹ|takoonoo|kallaẓeena|ʹaaẓaw|Moosaa|fabarraʹahul|laahu|mimmaa|q̣aaloo:|wa-kaana|ʻiñdal|laahi|wajeehaa."
33,70,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|wa-q̣ooloo|q̣awlañ|sadeedaa:"
33,71,"Yuṣliḥ|lakum|ʹaʻmaalakum|wa-yag̣fir|lakum|ẓunoobakum:|wa-mañy|yuṭiʻil|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|faq̣ad|faaza|fawzan|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
33,72,"ʹInnaa|ʻaraḍnal|ʹAmaanata|ʻalas|Samaawaati|walʹArḍi|wal-Jibaali|faʻabayna|ʹañy|yaḥmilnahaa|wa-ʹashfaq̣na|minhaa|waḥamalahal|ʹIñsaan:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|z̤̣aloomañ|jahoolaa;―"
33,73,"Liyuʻaẓẓibal|laahul|Munafiq̣eena|wal-Munaafiq̣aati|wal-Mushrikeena|wal-Mushrikaati|wa-yatoobal|laahu|ʻalal|Muʹmineena|wal-Muʹminaat:|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
34,1,"ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓee|lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-lahul|Ḥamdu|fil|ʹAakhirah:|wa-Huwal|Ḥakeemul|Khabeer."
34,2,"Yaʻlamu|maa-|yaliju|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|yakhruju|minhaa|wa-maa|yañzilu|minas|samaaaʹi|wa-maa|yaʻruju|feeha:|wa-Huwar|Raḥeemul|G̣afoor."
34,3,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|laa-|taʹteenas|Saaʻah:|q̣ul|balaa|wa-Rabbee|lataʹtiyannakum|ʻAalimil|g̣ayb.|Laa-|yaʻzubu|ʻanhu|mis̤q̣aalu|ẓarratiñ|fis|samaawaati|wa-laa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laaa|ʹaṣg̣aru|miñ|ẓaalika|wa-laaa|ʹakbaru|ʹillaa|fee|kitaabim|mubeen:"
34,4,"Liyajziyal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaat:|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|Mag̣firatuñw|Wa-Rizq̣uñ|kareem."
34,5,"Wallaẓeena|saʻaw|feee|ʹAayaatinaa|muʻaajizeena|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻaẓaabum|mir|rijzin|ʹaleem."
34,6,"Wa-yaral|laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻilmal|laẓeee|ʹuñzila|ʹilayka|mir|Rabbika|huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣a|wa-yahdeee|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥameed."
34,7,"Wa-q̣aalal|lazeena|kafaroo|hal|nadullukum|ʻalaa|rajuliñy|yunabbiʹukum|ʹiẓaa|muzziq̣tum|kulla|mumazzaq̣in|ʹinnakum|lafee|khalq̣iñ|jadeed?"
34,8,"ʹAftaraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓiban|ʹam̃|bihee|jinnah?|Balil|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|filʻAẓaabi|waḍ|Ḍalaalil|baʻeed."
34,9,"ʹAfalam|yaraw|ʹilaa|maa-|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-maa|khalfahum|minas|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍ?|ʹIn|nashaʹ|nakhsif|bihimul|ʹarḍa|ʹaw|nusq̣iṭ|ʻalayhim|kisafam|minas|samaaaʹ.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayatal|likulli|ʻabdim|muneeb."
34,10,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Daawooda|minnaa|Faḍlaa:|yaa-Jibaalu|ʹawwibee|maʻahoo|waṭṭayr!|Wa-ʹalannaa|lahul|ḥadeed:―"
34,11,"ʹAniʻ|mal|saabig̣aatiñw|waq̣addir|fis|sardi|waʻmaloo|ṣaaliḥaa;|ʹinnee|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
34,12,"Wa-li-Sulaymaanar|reeḥa|g̣uduwwuhaa|shahruñw|warawaaḥuhaa|shahr.|Wa-ʹasalnaa|lahoo|ʻaynal|q̣iṭr;|wa-minal|jinni|mañy|yaʻmalu|bayna|yadayhi|biʹiẓni|Rabbih.|Wa-mañy|yazig̣|minhum|ʻan|ʹamrinaa|nuẓiq̣hu|min|ʻAẓaabis|saʻeer."
34,13,"Yaʻmaloona|lahoo|maa-|yashaaaʹu|mim|maḥaareeba|wa-tamaas̤eela|wa-jifaaniñ|kaljawaabi|wa-q̣udoorir|raasiyaat.|ʹIʻmalooo|ʹAala|Daawooda|shukraa!|Wa-q̣aleelum|min|ʻibaadiyash|shakoor!"
34,14,"Falammaa|q̣aḍaynaa|ʻalayhil|mawta|maa-|dallahum|ʻalaa|mawtiheee|ʹillaa|daaabbatul|ʹarḍi|taʹkulu|miñsaʹatah:|falammaa|kharra|tabayyanatil|Jinnu|ʹal|law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoonal|g̣ayba|maa-|labis̤oo|fil|ʻaẓaabil|muheen."
34,15,"Laq̣ad|kaana|li-Sabaʹiñ|fee|maskanihim|ʹAayah:|Jannataani|ʻañy|yameeniiñw|washimaal.|Kuloo|mir|Rizq̣i|Rabbikum|washkuroo|lah:|Baldatuñ|ṭayyibatuñw|wa-Rabbun|G̣afoor!"
34,16,"Faʹaʻraḍoo|faʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhim|saylal|ʻArimi|wa-baddalnaahum̃|bijannatayhim|jannatayni|ẓawaatay|ʹukulin|khamṭiñw|waʹas̤liñw|washayʹim|miñ|sidriñ|q̣aleel."
34,17,"Ẓaalika|jazaynaahum̃|bimaa|kafaroo:|wa-hal|nujaazeee|ʹillal|kafoor."
34,18,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|baynahum|wa-baynal|Q̣ural|latee|baaraknaa|feehaa|q̣urañ|z̤̣aahiratañw|waq̣addarnaa|feehas|sayr:|seeroo|feehaa|layaaliya|wa-ʹayyaaman|ʹaamineen."
34,19,"Faq̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|baaʻid|bayna|ʹasfaarinaa|waz̤̣alamooo|ʹañfusahum|fajaʻalnaahum|ʹaḥaadees̤a|wa-mazzaq̣-naahum|kulla|mumazzaq̣.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|likulli|Ṣabbaariñ|Shakoor."
34,20,"Wa-laq̣ad|ṣaddaq̣a|ʻalayhim|ʹIbleesu|z̤̣annahoo|fattabaʻoohu|ʹillaa|fareeq̣am|minal|Muʹmineen."
34,21,"Wa-maa|kaana|lahoo|ʻalayhim|miñ|sulṭaanin|ʹillaa|linaʻlama|mañy|yuʹminu|bil-ʹAakhirati|mimman|huwa|minhaa|fee|shakk:|wa-Rabbuka|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹin|Ḥafeez̤̣."
34,22,"Q̣ulid|ʻul|laẓeena|zaʻamtum|miñ|doonil|laah:|laa-|yamlikoona|mis̤q̣aala|ẓarratiñ|fis|samaawaati|wa-laa|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-maa|lahum|feehimaa|miñ|shirkiñw|wamaa|lahoo|minhum|miñ|z̤̣aheer."
34,23,"Wa-laa|tañfaʻush|shafaaʻatu|ʻiñdahooo|ʹillaa|liman|ʹaẓina|lah.|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|fuzziʻa|ʻañ|q̣uloobihim|q̣aaloo|maaẓaa|q̣aala|Rabbukum?|Q̣aalul|Ḥaq̣q̣;|wa-Huwal|ʻAliyyul|Kabeer."
34,24,"Q̣ul|mañy|yarzuq̣ukum|minas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Q̣ulil|laahu|wa-ʹinnaaa|ʹaw|ʹiyyaakum|laʻalaa|hudan|ʹaw|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen!"
34,25,"Q̣ul|laa|tusʹaloona|ʻammaaa|ajramnaa|wa-laa|nusʹalu|ʻammaa|taʻmaloon."
34,26,"Q̣ul|yajmaʻu|baynanaa|Rabbunaa|s̤umma|yaftaḥu|baynanaa|bilḥaq̣q̣:|wa-Huwal|Fattaaḥul|ʻAleem."
34,27,"Q̣ul|ʹarooniyal|laẓeena|ʹalḥaq̣tum̃|bihee|shurakaaaʹa|kallaa.|Bal|Huwal|laahul|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
34,28,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʹillaa|kaaaffatal|linnaasi|basheerañw|wanaẓeerañw|walaakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
34,29,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|waʻdu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
34,30,"Q̣ul|lakum|meeʻaadu|Yawmil|laa|tastaʹkhiroona|ʻanhu|saaʻatañw|walaa|tastaq̣dimoon."
34,31,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lan|nuʹmina|bihaaẓal|Q̣urʹaani|wa-laa|billaẓee|bayna|yadayh.|Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|mawq̣oofoona|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|yarjiʻu|baʻḍuhum|ʹilaa|baʻḍinil|q̣awl.|Yaq̣oolul|laẓeenas|tuḍʻifoo|lillaẓeenas|takbaroo|law-laaa|ʹañtum|lakunnaa|Muʹmineen!"
34,32,"Q̣aalal|laẓeenas|takbaroo|lillaẓeenas|tuḍʻifooo|ʹanaḥnu|ṣadadnaakum|ʻanil|Hudaa|baʻda|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹakum|bal|kuñtum|mujrimeen."
34,33,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeenas|tuḍʻifoo|lillaẓeenas|takbaroo|bal|makrul|layli|wannahaari|ʹiẓ|taʹmuroonanaaa|ʹan|nakfura|billaahi|wa-najʻala|lahooo|ʹañdaadaa!|Wa-ʹasarrun|nadaamata|lammaa|raʹawul|ʻAẓaab.|Wa-jaʻalnal|ʹag̣laala|feee|ʹaʻnaaq̣il|laẓeena|kafaroo:|hal|yujzawna|ʹillaa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
34,34,"Wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaa|fee|q̣aryatim|min|Naẓeerin|ʹillaa|q̣aala|mutrafoohaaa|ʹinnaa|bimaaa|ʹursiltum̃|bihee|kaafiroon."
34,35,"Wa-q̣aaloo|naḥnu|ʹaks̤aru|ʹawlaadañw|waʹamwaalañw|wamaa|naḥnu|bimuʻaẓẓabeen."
34,36,"Q̣ul|ʹinna|Rabbee|yabsuṭur|Rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaq̣diru|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
34,37,"Wa-maaa|ʹamwaalukum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaadukum|billatee|tuq̣arribukum|ʻiñdanaa|zulfaaa|ʹillaa|man|ʹaamana|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥaa.|Faʹulaaaʹika|lahum|Jazaaaʹuḍ|ḍiʻfi|bimaa|ʻamiloo|wa-hum|fil|g̣urufaati|ʹaaminoon!"
34,38,"Wallaẓeena|yasʻawna|feee|ʹAayaatinaa|muʻaajizeena|ʹulaaaʹika|fil|ʻAẓaabi|muḥḍaroon."
34,39,"Q̣ul|ʹinna|Rabbee|yabsuṭur|Rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadihee|wa-yaq̣diru|lah.|Wa-maaa|ʹañfaq̣tum|miñ|shayʹiñ|fa-Huwa|yukhlifuh:|wa-Huwa|Khayrur|Raaziq̣een."
34,40,"Wa-Yawma|yaḥshuruhum|jameeʻañ|s̤umma|yaq̣oolu|lilmalaaaʹikati|ʹa-haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹiyyaakum|kaanoo|yaʻbudoon?"
34,41,"Q̣aaloo|Subḥaanaka|ʹAñta|Waliyyunaa|miñ|doonihim.|Bal|kaanoo|yaʻbudoonal|Jinn:|ʹaks̤aruhum̃|bihim|Muʹminoon."
34,42,"Fal-Yawma|laa-|yamliku|baʻḍukum|libaʻḍin|nafʻañw|walaa|ḍarraa:|wa-naq̣oolu|lil-laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|ẓooq̣oo|ʻAẓaaban|Naaril|latee|kuñtum̃|bihaa|tukaẓẓiboon!"
34,43,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|Bayyinaatiñ|q̣aaloo|maa-|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|rajuluñy|yureedu|ʹañy|yaṣuddakum|ʻammaa|kaana|yaʻbudu|ʹaabaaaʹukum.|Wa-q̣aaloo|maa-|haaẓaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹifkum|muftaraa!|Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|lammaa|jaaaʹahum|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|siḥrum|mubeen!"
34,44,"Wa-maaa|ʹaataynaahum|miñ|Kutubiñy|yadrusoonahaa|wa-maaa|ʹarsalnaaa|ʹilayhim|q̣ablaka|min|Naẓeer."
34,45,"Wa-kaẓẓabal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|wa-maa|balag̣oo|miʻshaara|maaa|ʹaataynaahum|fakaẓẓaboo|rusulee:|fakayfa|kaana|nakeer!"
34,46,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹaʻiz̤̣ukum̃|biwaaḥidah:|ʹañ|taq̣oomoo|lillaahi|mas̤naa|wa-furaadaa|s̤umma|tatafakkaroo:|maa-|bi-Ṣaaḥibikum|miñ|Jinnah:|ʹin|huwa|ʹillaa|Naẓeerul|lakum̃|bayna|yaday|ʻAẓaabiñ|shadeed."
34,47,"Q̣ul|maa-|saʹaltukum|min|ʹajriñ|fahuwa|lakum:|ʹin|ʹajriya|ʹillaa|ʻalal|laah:|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Shaheed."
34,48,"Q̣ul|ʹinna|Rabbee|yaq̣ẓifu|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|ʻAllaamul|g̣uyoob."
34,49,"Q̣ul|jaaaʹal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-maa|yubdiʹul|Baaṭilu|wa-maa|yuʻeed."
34,50,"Q̣ul|ʹiñ|ḍalaltu|faʹinnamaaa|ʹaḍillu|ʻalaa|nafsee:|waʹinih|tadaytu|fabimaa|yooḥeee|ʹilayya|Rabbee:|ʹinnahoo|Sameeʻuñ|Q̣areeb."
34,51,"Wa-law|taraaa|ʹiẓ|faziʻoo|falaa|fawta|wa-ʹukhiẓoo|mim|makaaniñ|q̣areeb,"
34,52,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|bih;|wa-ʹannaa|lahumut|tanaawushu|mim|makaanim|baʻeed,―"
34,53,"Wa-q̣ad|kafaroo|bihee|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-yaq̣ẓifoona|bilg̣aybi|mim|makaanim|baʻeed?"
34,54,"Waḥeela|baynahum|wabayna|maa-|yashtahoona|kamaa|fuʻila|biʹashyaaʻihim|miñ|q̣abl:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|fee|shakkim|mureeb."
35,1,"ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaahi|Faaṭiris|Samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|jaaʻilil|malaaaʹikati|rusulan|ʹuleee|ʹajniḥatim|mas̤naa|wa-s̤ulaas̤a|wa-rubaaʻ:|yazeedu|fil|khalq̣i|maa-|yashaaaʹ:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
35,2,"Maa-|yaftaḥil|laahu|linnaasi|mir|Raḥmatiñ|falaa|mumsika|lahaa:|wa-maa|yumsik|falaa|mursila|lahoo|mim|baʻdih:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
35,3,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasuẓ|kuroo|niʻmatal|laahi|ʻalaykum!|Hal|min|Khaaliq̣in|g̣ayrul|laahi|yarzuq̣ukum|minas|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍ?|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo!|Faʹannaa|tuʹfakoon?"
35,4,"Wa-ʹiñy|yukaẓẓibooka|faq̣ad|kuẓẓibat|rusulum|miñ|q̣ablik:|wa-ʹilal|laahi|turjaʻul|ʹumoor."
35,5,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹinna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñ|falaa|tag̣urrannakumul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa:|wa-laa|yag̣urrannakum̃|billaahil|G̣aroor."
35,6,"ʹInnash|Shayṭaana|lakum|ʻaduwwuñ|fattakhiẓoohu|ʻaduwwaa.|ʹInnamaa|yadʻoo|ḥizbahoo|liyakoonoo|min|ʹAṣḥaabis|Saʻeer."
35,7,"ʹAllaẓeena|kafaroo|lahum|ʻAẓaabuñ|shadeed!|Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|lahum|mag̣firatuñw|waʹAjruñ|kabeer."
35,8,"ʹAfamañ|zuyyina|lahoo|soooʹu|ʻamalihee|faraʹaahu|ḥasanaa?|Faʹinnal|laaha|yuḍillu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yahdee|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Falaa|taẓhab|nafsuka|ʻalayhim|ḥasaraat.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAleemum|bimaa|yaṣnaʻoon!"
35,9,"Wallaahul|laẓeee|ʹarsalar|riyaaḥa|fatus̤eeru|saḥaabañ|fasuq̣naahu|ʹilaa|baladim|mayyitiñ|faʹaḥyaynaa|bihil|ʹarda|baʻda|mawtihaa.|Kaẓaalikan|Nushoor!"
35,10,"Mañ|kaana|yureedul|ʻizzata|falillahil|ʻizzatu|jameeʻaa.|ʹIlayhi|yaṣʻadul|Kalimuṭ|Ṭayyibu|walʻAmaluṣ|Ṣaaliḥu|yarfaʻuh.|Wallaẓeena|yamkuroonas|sayyiʹaati|lahum|ʻAẓaabuñ|shadeed;|wa-makru|ʹulaaaʹika|huwa|yaboor."
35,11,"Wallaahu|khalaq̣akum|miñ|turaabiñ|s̤umma|min|nuṭfatiñ|s̤umma|jaʻalakum|ʹazwaajaa.|Wa-maa|taḥmilu|min|ʹuñs̤aa.|wa-laa|taḍaʻu|ʹillaa|biʻilmih.|Wa-maa|yuʻammaru|mim|muʻammariñw|walaa|yuñq̣aṣu|min|ʻumuriheee|ʹillaa|fee|Kitaab.|ʹInna|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseer."
35,12,"Wa-maa|yastawil|baḥraani|haaẓaa|ʻaẓbuñ|furaatuñ|saaaʹig̣uñ|sharaabuhoo|wa-haaẓaa|milḥun|ʹujaaj.|Wa-miñ|kulliñ|taʹkuloona|laḥmañ|ṭariyyañw|watastakhrijoona|ḥilyatañ|talbasoonahaa;|wa-taral|fulka|feehi|mawaakhira|litabtag̣oo|miñ|Faḍlihee|wa-laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
35,13,"Yoolijul|layla|fin|nahaari|wa-yoolijun|nahaara|fil|layli|wa-sakhkharash|shamsa|wal-q̣amar:|Kulluñy|yajree|liʹajalim|musammaa.|Ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukum|lahul|Mulk.|Wallaẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|maa-|yamlikoona|miñ|q̣iṭmeer."
35,14,"ʹIñ|tadʻoohum|laa-|yasmaʻoo|duʻaaaʹakum.|Wa-law|samiʻoo|mas|tajaaboo|lakum.|Wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|yakfuroona|bishirkikum.|Wa-laa|yunabbiʹuka|mis̤lu|khabeer."
35,15,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹañtumul|fuq̣araaaʹu|ʹilal|laah:|wallaahu|Huwal|G̣aniyyul|Ḥameed."
35,16,"ʹIñy|yashaʹ|yuẓhibkum|wa-yaʹti|bi-Khalq̣iñ|Jadeed."
35,17,"Wa-maa|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|biʻazeez."
35,18,"Wa-laa|taziru|waaziratuñw|wizra|ʹukhraa.|Wa-ʹiñ|tadʻu|mus̤q̣alatun|ʹilaa|ḥimlihaa|laa-|yuḥmal|minhu|shayʹuñw|walaw|kaana|ẓaa|q̣urbaa.|ʹInnamaa|tuñẓirul|laẓeena|yakhshawna|Rabbahum̃|bilg̣aybi|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaah.|Wa-mañ|tazakkaa|faʹinnamaa|yatazakkaa|linafsih:|wa-ʹilal|laahil|maṣeer."
35,19,"Wa-maa|yastawil|ʹaʻmaa|wal-baṣeer;"
35,20,"Wa-laz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaatu|wa-lan|noor;"
35,21,"Wa-laz̤̣|z̤̣illu|wa-lal|ḥaroor:"
35,22,"Wa-maa|yastawil|ʹaḥyaaaʹu|wa-lal|ʹamwaat.|ʹInnal|laaha|yusmiʻu|mañy|yashaaaʹ;|wa-maaa|ʹañta|bimusmiʻim|mañ|fil|q̣uboor."
35,23,"ʹIn|ʹañta|ʹillaa|naẓeer."
35,24,"ʹInnaaa|ʹarsalnaaka|bil-ḥaq̣q̣i|basheerañw|wanaẓeeraa:|wa-ʹim|min|ʹummatin|ʹillaa|khalaa|feehaa|naẓeer."
35,25,"Wa-ʹiñy|yukaẓẓibooka|faq̣ad|kaẓẓabal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim:|jaaaʹathum|rusuluhum̃|bil-Bayyinaati|wa-biz-Zuburi|wa-bil-Kitaabil|Muneer."
35,26,"S̤umma|ʹakhaẓtul|laẓeena|kafaroo|fakayfa|kaana|nakeer."
35,27,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹaa?|Faʹakhrajnaa|bihee|s̤amaraatim|mukhtalifan|ʹalwaanuhaa.|Wa-minal|jibaali|judadum|beeḍuñw|waḥumrum|mukhtalifun|ʹalwaanuhaa|wa-g̣araabeebu|sood."
35,28,"Wa-minan|naasi|waddawaaabbi|wal-ʹanʻaami|mukhtalifun|ʹalwaanuhoo|kaẓaalik.|ʹInnamaa|yakhshal|laaha|min|ʻIbaadihil|ʻulamaaaʹ:|ʹinnal|laaha|ʻAzeezun|G̣afoor."
35,29,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yatloona|Kitaabal|laahi|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹañfaq̣oo|mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|sirrañw|waʻalaaniyatañy|yarjoona|Tijaaratal|lañ|taboor:"
35,30,"Liyuwaffiyahum|ʹujoorahum|wa-yazeedahum|miñ|Faḍlih:|ʹinnahoo|G̣afooruñ|Shakoor."
35,31,"Wallaẓeee|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|minal|Kitaabi|huwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayh:|ʹinnal|laaha|biʻIbaadihee|la-Khabeerum|Baṣeer."
35,32,"S̤umma|ʹawras̤nal|Kitaabal|laẓeenaṣ|ṭafaynaa|min|ʻibaadinaa:|faminhum|z̤̣aalimul|linafsih;|wa-minhum|muq̣taṣid;|wa-minhum|saabiq̣um|bilkhayraati|biʹiẓnil|laah;|ẓaalika|huwal|Faḍlul|Kabeer."
35,33,"Jannaatu|ʻAdniñy|yad-khuloonahaa|yuḥallawna|feehaa|min|ʹasaawira|miñ|ẓahabiñw|waluʹluʹaa;|wa-libaa-suhum|feehaa|ḥareer."
35,34,"Wa-q̣aalul|Ḥamdu|lillaahil|laẓeee|ʹaẓhaba|ʻannal|ḥazan:|ʹinna|Rabbanaa|la-G̣afooruñ|Shakoor:"
35,35,"ʹAllaẓeee|ʹaḥallanaa|Daaral|muq̣aamati|miñ|Faḍlih:|laa-|yamassunaa|feehaa|naṣabuñw|walaa|yamassunaa|feehaa|lug̣oob."
35,36,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|lahum|Naaru|Jahannam;|laa-|yuq̣ḍaa|ʻalayhim|fayamootoo|wa-laa|yukhaffafu|ʻanhum|min|ʻAẓaabihaa.|Kaẓaalika|najzee|kulla|kafoor!"
35,37,"Wa-hum|yaṣṭarikhoona|feehaa:|Rabbanaaa|ʹakhrijnaa|naʻmal|ṣaaliḥan|g̣ayral|laẓee|kunnaa|naʻmal!|ʹA-walamnu|ʻammirkum|maa|yataẓakkaru|feehi|mañ|taẓakkara|wa-jaaaʹakumun|naẓeer.|Faẓooq̣oo|famaa|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|min|naṣeer."
35,38,"ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAalimu|g̣aybis|samaawaati|wal-ʹard:|ʹInnahoo|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
35,39,"Huwal|laẓee|jaʻalakum|khalaaaʹifa|fil|ʹarḍ:|famañ|kafara|faʻalayhi|kufruh:|wa-laa|yazeedul|kaafireena|kufruhum|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|ʹillaa|maq̣taa:|wa-laa|yazeedul|kaafireena|kufruhum|ʹillaa|khasaaraa."
35,40,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|shurakaaaʹakumul|laẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laah?|ʹAroonee|maaẓaa|khalaq̣oo|minal|ʹarḍi|ʹam|lahum|shirkuñ|fis|samaawaat?|ʹAm|ʹaataynaahum|Kitaabañ|fahum|ʻalaa|Bayyinatim|minh?―|Bal|ʹiñy|yaʻiduz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoona|baʻḍuhum̃|baʻḍan|ʹillaa|g̣urooraa."
35,41,"ʹInnal|laaha|yumsikus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|ʹañ|tazoolaa:|wa-laʹiñ|zaalataaa|ʹin|ʹamsakahumaa|min|ʹaḥadim|mim|baʻdih:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|Ḥaleeman|G̣afooraa!"
35,42,"Wa-ʹaq̣samoo|billaahi|jahda|ʹaymaanihim|laʹiñ|jaaaʹahum|naẓeerul|layakoonunna|ʹahdaa|min|ʹiḥdal|ʹUmami|falammaa|jaaaʹahum|naẓeerum|maa|zaadahum|ʹillaa|nufooraa,―"
35,43,"ʹIstikbaarañ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-makras|Sayyiʹ.|Wa-laa|yaḥeeq̣ul|makrus|Sayyiʹu|ʹillaa|biʹahlih.|Fahal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillaa|sunnatal|ʹawwaleen?|Falañ|tajida|li-Sunnatil|laahi|tabdeelaa:|wa-lañ|tajida|li-Sunnatil|laahi|taḥweelaa."
35,44,"ʹAwalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fayañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|wa-kaanooo|ʹashadda|minhum|q̣uwwah?|Wa-maa|kaanal|laahu|liyuʻjizahoo|miñ|shayʹiñ|fis|samaawaati|wa-laa|fil|ʹarḍ:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|ʻAleemañ|Q̣adeeraa."
35,45,"Wa-law|yuʹaakhiẓul|laahun|naasa|bimaa|kasaboo|maa-|taraka|ʻalaa|z̤̣ahrihaa|miñ|daaabbatiñw|walaakiñy|yuʹakhkhiruhum|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammaa:|Faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹAjaluhum|faʹinnal|laaha|kaana|biʻibaadihee|Baṣeeraa."
36,1,"Yaa-Seeen."
36,2,"Wal-Q̣urʹaanil|Ḥakeem,―"
36,3,"ʹInnaka|laminal|mursaleen,"
36,4,"ʻAlaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
36,5,"Tañzeelal|ʻAzeezir|Raḥeem,"
36,6,"Lituñẓira|q̣awmam|maaa|ʹuñẓira|ʹaabaaaʹuhum|fahum|g̣aafiloon."
36,7,"Laq̣ad|ḥaq̣q̣al|Q̣awlu|ʻalaaa|ʹaks̤arihim|fahum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
36,8,"ʹInnaa|jaʻalnaa|feee|ʹaʻnaaq̣ihim|ʹag̣laalañ|fahiya|ʹilal|ʹaẓq̣aani|fahum|muq̣maḥoon."
36,9,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|mim|bayni|ʹaydeehim|saddañw|wamin|khalfihim|saddañ|faʹag̣shaynaahum|fahum|laa-|yubṣiroon."
36,10,"Wa-sawaaaʹun|ʻalayhim|ʹaʹañẓartahum|ʹam|lam|tuñẓirhum|laa-|yuʹminoon."
36,11,"ʹInnamaa|tuñẓiru|manit|taba|ʻaẓ-Ẓikra|wa-khashiyar|Raḥmaana|bilg̣ayb:|fabashshirhu|bi-Mag̣firatiñw|waʹAjriñ|Kareem."
36,12,"ʹInnaa|Naḥnu|nuḥyil|mawtaa|wanaktubu|maa-|q̣addamoo|wa-ʹaas̤aarahum:|wa-kulla|shayʹin|ʹaḥṣaynaahu|feee|ʹImaamim|mubeen."
36,13,"Waḍrib|lahum|mas̤alan|ʹAṣḥaabal|Q̣aryah.|ʹIẓ|jaaaʹahal|mursaloon."
36,14,"ʹIẓ|ʹarsalnaaa|ʹilayhimus̤|nayni|fakaẓẓaboohumaa|faʻazzaznaa|bis̤aalis̤iñ|faq̣aalooo|ʹinnaaa|ʹilaykum|mursaloon."
36,15,"Q̣aaloo|maaa|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|basharum|mis̤lunaa|wa-maaa|ʹañzalar|Raḥmaanu|miñ|shayʹin|ʹin|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|takẓiboon."
36,16,"Q̣aaloo|Rabbunaa|yaʻlamu|ʹinnaaa|ʹilaykum|lamursaloon:"
36,17,"Wa-maa|ʻalaynaaa|ʹillal|Balaag̣ul|mubeen."
36,18,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|taṭayyarnaa|bikum:|laʹil|lam|tañtahoo|lanarjumannakum|wa-la-yamassan-nakum|minnaa|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
36,19,"Q̣aaloo|ṭaaaʹirukum|maʻakum:|ʹaʹiñ|ẓukkirtum?|Bal|ʹañtum|q̣awmum|musrifoon!"
36,20,"Wa-jaaaʹa|min|ʹaq̣ṣal|Madeenati|rajuluñy|yasʻaa|q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmit|tabiʻul|mursaleen:"
36,21,"ʹIttabiʻoo|mal|laa|yasʹalukum|ʹajrañw|Wahum|muhtadoon."
36,22,"Wa-maa|liya|laaa|ʹaʻbudul|laẓee|faṭaranee|wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
36,23,"ʹA-ʹattakhiẓu|miñ|dooniheee|ʹaalihatan|ʹiñy|yuridnir|Raḥmaanu|biḍurril|laa|tug̣ni|ʻannee|shafaaʻatuhum|shayʹañw|walaa|yuñq̣iẓoon."
36,24,"ʹInneee|ʹiẓal|lafee|Ḍalaalim|mubeen."
36,25,"ʹInneee|ʹaamañtu|bi-Rabbikum|fasmaʻoon!"
36,26,"Q̣eelad|khulil|Jannah.|Q̣aala|yaa-layta|Q̣awmee|yaʻlamoon,"
36,27,"Bimaa|lee|g̣afara|Rabbee|wa-jaʻalanee|minal|mukrameen!"
36,28,"Wa-maaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaa|Q̣awmihee|mim|baʻdihee|miñ|juñdim|minas|samaaaʹi|wa-maa|kunnaa|muñzileen."
36,29,"ʹIñ|kaanat|ʹillaa|ṣayḥatañw|waaḥidatañ|faʹiẓaa|hum|khaamidoon."
36,30,"Yaa-ḥasratan|ʻalal|ʻibaad!|Maa-|yaʹteehim|mir|rasoolin|ʹillaa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon!"
36,31,"ʹAlam|yaraw|kam|ʹahlaknaa|q̣ablahum|minal|q̣urooni|ʹannahum|ilayhim|laa-ʹ|yarjiʻoon?"
36,32,"Waʹiñ|kullul|lammaa|jameeʻul|ladaynaa|muḥḍaroon."
36,33,"Wa-ʹAayatul|lahumul|ʹarḍul|maytah:|ʹaḥyaynaahaa|wa-ʹakhrajnaa|minhaa|ḥabbañ|faminhu|yaʹkuloon."
36,34,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|feehaa|jannaatim|min|nakheeliñw|waʹaʻnaabiñw|wafajjarnaa|feehaa|minal|ʻuyoon:"
36,35,"Liyaʹkuloo|miñ|s̤amarihee,|wa-maa|ʻamilathu|ʹaydeehim:|ʹafalaa|yashkuroon?"
36,36,"Subḥaanal|laẓee|khalaq̣al|ʹazwaaja|kullahaa|mimmaa|tumbitul|ʹarḍu|wa-min|ʹañfusihim|Wamimmaa|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
36,37,"Wa-ʹAayatul|lahumul|Laylu|naslakhu|minhun|Nahaara|faʹiẓaa|hum|muz̤̣limoon;"
36,38,"Wash-Shamsu|tajree|limustaq̣arril|lahaa:|ẓaalika|taq̣deerul|ʻAzeezil|ʻAleem."
36,39,"Wal-Q̣amara|q̣addarnaahu|manaazila|ḥattaa|ʻaada|kalʻurjoonil|q̣adeem."
36,40,"Lash|Shamsu|yambag̣ee|lahaaa|ʹañ|tudrikal|Q̣amara|wa-lal|Laylu|saabiq̣un|Nahaar:|wa-kulluñ|fee|falakiñy|yasbaḥoon."
36,41,"Wa-ʹAayatul|lahum|ʹannaa|ḥamalnaa|ẓurriyyatahum|fil|fulkil|mashḥoon;"
36,42,"Wa-khalaq̣naa|lahum|mim|mis̤lihee|maa-|yarkaboon."
36,43,"Wa-ʹin|nashaʹ|nug̣riq̣hum|falaa|ṣareekha|lahum|wa-laa|hum|yuñq̣aẓoon,"
36,44,"ʹIllaa|Raḥmatam|minnaa|wa-mataaʻan|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
36,45,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahumut|taq̣oo|Maa-|bayna|ʹaydeekum|wa-maa|khalfakum|laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
36,46,"Wa-maa|taʹteehim|min|ʹAayatim|min|ʹAayaati|Rabbihim|ʹillaa|kaanoo|ʻanhaa|muʻriḍeen."
36,47,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|ʹañfiq̣oo|mimmaa|razaq̣akumul|laahu|q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹanuṭʻimu|mal|law|yashaaaʹul|laahu|ʹaṭʻamah?―|ʹIn|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
36,48,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|waʻdu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
36,49,"Maa-|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillaa|Ṣayḥatañw|waaḥidatañ|taʹkhuẓuhum|wa-hum|yakhiṣṣimoon!"
36,50,"Falaa|yastaṭeeʻoona|taw-ṣiyatañw|walaaa|ʹilaaa|ʹahlihim|yarjiʻoon!"
36,51,"Wa-nufikha|fiṣ|Ṣoori|faʹiẓaa|hum|minal|ʹajdaas̤i|ʹilaa|Rabbihim|yañsiloon!"
36,52,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-waylanaa|mam|baʻas̤anaa|mim|marq̣adinaa|Haaẓaa|maa-|waʻadar|Raḥmaanu|waṣadaq̣al|mursaloon!"
36,53,"ʹIñ|kaanat|ʹillaa|Ṣayḥatañw|waaḥidatañ|faʹiẓaa|hum|jameeʻul|ladaynaa|muḥḍaroon!"
36,54,"Fal-Yawma|laa-|tuz̤̣lamu|nafsuñ|shayʹañwwa|laa-|tujzawna|ʹillaa|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
36,55,"ʹInna|ʹAṣḥaabal|Jannatil|Yawma|fee|shug̣uliñ|faakihoon;"
36,56,"Hum|wa-ʹazwaajuhum|fee|z̤̣ilaalin|ʻalal|ʹaraaaʹiki|muttakiʹoon;"
36,57,"Lahum|feehaa|faakihatuñw|walahum|maa|yaddaʻoon;"
36,58,"˹Salaam!˺―|Q̣awlam|mir|Rabbir|Raḥeem!"
36,59,"Wamtaazul|Yawma|ʹayyuhal|mujrimoon!"
36,60,"ʹAlam|ʹaʻhad|ʹilaykum|yaa|Baneee|ʹAadama|ʹallaa|taʻbudush|Shayṭaan;|ʹinnahoo|lakum|ʻaduwwum|mubeen?―"
36,61,"Wa-ʹaniʻ|budoonee.|Haaẓaa|Ṣiraaṭum|Mustaq̣eem."
36,62,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaḍalla|miñkum|jibillañ|kas̤eeraa.|ʹAfalam|takoonoo|taʻq̣iloon?"
36,63,"Haaẓihee|Jahannamul|latee|kuñtum|tooʻadoon!"
36,64,"ʹIṣlawhal|Yawma|bimaa|kuñtum|takfuroon."
36,65,"ʹAl-Yawma|nakhtimu|ʻalaaa|ʹafwaahihim|wa-tukallimunaaa|ʹaydeehim|wa-tashhadu|ʹarjuluhum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
36,66,"Wa-law|nashaaaʹu|laṭamasnaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaʻyunihim|fastabaq̣uṣ|Ṣiraaṭa|faʹannaa|yubṣiroon?"
36,67,"Wa-law|nashaaaʹu|lamasakhnaahum|ʻalaa|makaanatihim|famas|taṭaaʻoo|muḍiyyañwwa|laa-|yarjiʻoon."
36,68,"Wa-man|nuʻammirhu|nunakkishu|fil|khalq̣:|ʹafalaa|yaʻq̣iloon?"
36,69,"Wa-maa|ʻallamnaahush|Shiʻra|wa-maa|yambag̣ee|lah:|ʹin|huwa|ʹillaa|Ẓikruñwwa|Q̣ur-ʹaanum|Mubeen:"
36,70,"Liyuñẓira|mañ|kaana|ḥayyañw|wayaḥiq̣q̣al|q̣awlu|ʻalal|kaafireen."
36,71,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannaa|khalaq̣naa|lahum|mimmaa|ʻamilat|ʹaydeenaaa|ʹanʻaamañ|fahum|lahaa|maalikoon?―"
36,72,"Wa-ẓallalnaahaa|lahum|faminhaa|rakoobuhum|wa-minhaa|yaʹkuloon:"
36,73,"Wa-lahum|feehaa|manaafiʻu|wa-mashaarib.|ʹAfalaa|yashkuroon?"
36,74,"Wattakhaẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹaalihatal|laʻallahum|yuñṣaroon!"
36,75,"Laa-|yastaṭeeʻoona|naṣrahum|wa-hum|lahum|juñdum|muḥḍaroon."
36,76,"Falaa|yaḥzuñka|q̣awluhum.|ʹInnaa|naʻlamu|maa-|yusirroona|wa-maa|yuʻlinoon."
36,77,"ʹAwalam|yaral|ʹiñsaanu|ʹannaa|khalaq̣naahu|min|nuṭfatiñ|faʹiẓaa|huwa|khaṣeemum|mubeen!"
36,78,"Wa-ḍaraba|lanaa|mas̤alañw|wanasiya|khalq̣ah:|q̣aala|mañy|yuḥyil|ʻiz̤̣aama|wa-hiya|rameem?"
36,79,"Q̣ul|yuḥ-yeehal|laẓeee|ʹañshaʹahaaa|ʹawwala|marrah!|Wa-Huwa|bikulli|khalq̣in|ʻAleem!"
36,80,"ʹAllaẓee|jaʻala|lakum|minash|shajaril|ʹakhḍari|naarañ|faʹiẓaaa|ʹañtum|minhu|tooq̣idoon!"
36,81,"ʹA-walaysal|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal|ʹarḍa|bi-Q̣aadirin|ʻalaaa|ʹañyyakhluq̣a|mis̤lahum?―|Balaa!|wa-Huwal|Khallaaq̣ul|ʻAleem!"
36,82,"ʹInnamaaa|ʹAmruhooo|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaraada|shayʹan|ʹañy|yaq̣oola|lahoo|˹KUÑ˺|fayakoon!"
36,83,"Fa-Subḥaanal|laẓee|biyadihee|Malakootu|kulli|shayʹiñw|waʹilayhi|turjaʻoon"
37,1,"Waṣṣaaaffaati|ṣaffaa."
37,2,"Fazzaajiraati|zajraa."
37,3,"Fattaaliyaati|Ẓikraa."
37,4,"ʹInna|ʹIlaahakum|la-Waaḥid!―"
37,5,"Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa|wa-Rabbul|mashaariq̣!"
37,6,"ʹInnaa|zayyannas|samaaa|ʹad-dunyaa|bizeenatinil|kawaakib,―"
37,7,"Wa-ḥifz̤̣am|miñ|kulli|Shayṭaanim|maarid,"
37,8,"Laa-|yassammaʻoona|ʹilal|Malaʹil|ʹAʻlaa|wa-yuq̣ẓafoona|miñ|kulli|jaanib,"
37,9,"Duḥoorañw|Walahum|ʻaẓaabuñw|waaṣib,"
37,10,"ʹIllaa|man|khaṭifal|khaṭfata|faʹatbaʻahoo|shihaabuñ|s̤aaq̣ib."
37,11,"Fastaftihim|ʹahum|ʹashaddu|khalq̣an|ʹam|man|khalaq̣naa?|ʹInnaa|khalaq̣naahum|miñ|ṭeenil|laazib!"
37,12,"Bal|ʹajibta|wa-yaskharoon,"
37,13,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ẓukkiroo|laa-|yaẓkuroon,―"
37,14,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|raʹaw|ʹaayatañ|yastaskhiroon."
37,15,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillaa|siḥrum|mubeen!"
37,16,"ʹA-ʹiẓaa|mitnaa|wa-kunnaa|turabañw|waʻiz̤̣aaman|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lamabʻoos̤oon."
37,17,"ʹA-waʹaabaaaʹunal|ʹawwaloon?"
37,18,"Q̣ul|naʻam|wa-ʹañtum|daakhiroon."
37,19,"Faʹinnamaa|hiya|zajratuñw|waaḥidatuñ|faʹiẓaa|hum|yañz̤̣uroon!"
37,20,"Wa-q̣aaloo|yaa-waylanaa|haaẓaa|Yawmud|deen!"
37,21,"Haaẓaa|Yawmul|Faṣlil|laẓee|kuñtum̃|bihee|tukaẓẓiboon!"
37,22,"ʹUḥshurul|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|wa-ʹazwaajahum|wa-maa|kaanoo|yaʻbudoon."
37,23,"Miñ|doonil|laahi|fahdoohum|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭil|Jaḥeem!"
37,24,"Waq̣ifoohum|ʹinnahum|masʹooloon:"
37,25,"Maa-|lakum|laa-|tanaaṣaroon?"
37,26,"Bal|humul|yawma|mustaslimoon;"
37,27,"Wa-ʹaq̣bala|baʻḍuhum|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñy|yatasaaaʹaloon."
37,28,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnakum|kuñtum|taʹtoonanaa|ʻanil|yameen!"
37,29,"Q̣aaloo|bal|lam|takoonoo|Muʹmineen!"
37,30,"Wa-maa|kaana|lanaa|ʻalaykum|miñ|sulṭaan.|Bal|kuñtum|q̣awmañ|ṭaag̣een!"
37,31,"Faḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalaynaa|Q̣awlu|Rabbinaaa|ʹinnaa|laẓaaaʹiq̣oon."
37,32,"Faʹag̣waynaakum|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|g̣aaween."
37,33,"Faʹinnahum|Yawmaʹiẓiñ|fil|ʻAẓaabi|mushtarikoon."
37,34,"ʹInnaa|kaẓaalika|nafʻalu|bil-mujrimeen."
37,35,"ʹInnahum|kaanooo|ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|˹Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillal|laahu˺|yastakbiroon,"
37,36,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|ʹaʹinnaa|lataarikooo|ʹaalihatinaa|lishaaʻirim|majnoon?"
37,37,"Bal|jaaaʹa|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ṣaddaq̣al|mursaleen."
37,38,"ʹInnakum|laẓaaaʹiq̣ul|ʻAẓaabil|ʹAleem;"
37,39,"Wa-maa|tujzawna|ʹillaa|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon;"
37,40,"ʹIllaa|ʻibaadal|laahil|mukhlaṣeen."
37,41,"ʹUlaaaʹika|lahum|Rizq̣um|maʻloom,"
37,42,"Fawaakihu|wa-hum|mukramoon,"
37,43,"Fee|Jannaatin|Naʻeem,"
37,44,"ʻAlaa|sururim|mutaq̣aabileen:"
37,45,"Yuṭaafu|ʻalayhim̃|bikaʹsim|mim|maʻeen,"
37,46,"Bayḍaaaʹa|laẓẓatillish|shaaribeen,"
37,47,"Laa-|feehaa|g̣awluñw|walaa|hum|ʻanhaa|yuñzafoon."
37,48,"Wa-ʻiñdahum|q̣aaṣiraatuṭ|ṭarfi|ʻeen,"
37,49,"Kaʹannahunna|bayḍum|maknoon."
37,50,"Faʹaq̣bala|baʻḍuhum|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñy|yatasaaaʹaloon."
37,51,"Q̣aala|q̣aaaʹilum|minhum|ʹinnee|kaana|lee|q̣areen,"
37,52,"Yaq̣oolu|ʹa-ʹinnaka|laminal|muṣaddiq̣een?"
37,53,"ʹA-ʹiẓaa|mitnaa|wa-kunnaa|turaabañw|waʻiz̤̣aaman|ʹa-ʹinnaa|lamadeenoon?"
37,54,"Q̣aala|hal|ʹañtum|muṭṭaliʻoon?"
37,55,"Faṭṭalaʻa|faraʹaahu|fee|sawaaaʹil|Jaḥeem."
37,56,"Q̣aala|tallaahi|ʹiñ|kitta|laturdeen!"
37,57,"Wa-lawlaa|Niʻmatu|Rabbee|lakuñtu|minal|muḥḍareen!"
37,58,"ʹAfamaa|naḥnu|bimayyiteen,"
37,59,"ʹIllaa|mawtatanal|ʹoolaa|wa-maa|naḥnu|bimuʻaẓẓabeen?"
37,60,"ʹInna|haaẓaa|lahuwal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
37,61,"Limis̤li|haaẓaa|falyaʻmalil|ʻaamiloon."
37,62,"ʹAẓaalika|khayrun|nuzulan|ʹam|Shajaratuz|Zaq̣q̣oom?"
37,63,"ʹInnaa|jaʻalnaahaa|fitnatal|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeen."
37,64,"ʹInnahaa|shajaratuñ|takhruju|feee|ʹaṣlil|Jaḥeem:"
37,65,"Ṭalʻuhaa|kaʹannahoo|ruʹoosush|shayaaṭeen:"
37,66,"Faʹinnahum|laʹaakiloona|minhaa|famaaliʹoona|minhal|buṭoon."
37,67,"S̤umma|ʹinna|lahum|ʻalayhaa|lashawbam|min|ḥameem."
37,68,"S̤umma|ʹinna|marjiʻahum|laʹilal|Jaḥeem."
37,69,"ʹInnahum|ʹalfaw|ʹaabaaaʹahum|ḍaaalleen;"
37,70,"Fahum|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihim|yuhraʻoon!"
37,71,"Wa-laq̣ad|ḍalla|q̣ablahum|ʹaks̤arul|ʹawwaleen;―"
37,72,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|feehim|muñẓireen;―"
37,73,"Fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|muñẓareen,―"
37,74,"ʹIllaa|ʻibaadal|laahil|mukhlaṣeen."
37,75,"Wa-laq̣ad|naadaanaa|Nooḥuñ|falaniʻmal|Mujeeboon,"
37,76,"Wa-najjaynaahu|wa-ʹahlahoo|minal|Karbil|ʻAz̤̣eem,"
37,77,"Wa-jaʻalnaa|ẓurriyyatahoo|humul|baaq̣een."
37,78,"Wa-taraknaa|ʻalayhi|fil|ʹaakhireen:"
37,79,"Salaamun|ʻalaa|Nooḥiñ|fil|ʻaalameen!"
37,80,"ʹInnaa|kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
37,81,"ʹInnahoo|min|ʻibaadinal|Muʹmineen."
37,82,"S̤umma|ʹag̣raq̣nal|ʹaakhareen."
37,83,"Wa-ʹinna|miñ|Sheeʻatihee|laʹIbraaheem."
37,84,"ʹIẓ|jaaaʹa|Rabbahoo|biq̣albiñ|saleem."
37,85,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|liʹabeehi|wa-q̣awmihee|maaẓaa|taʻbudoon?"
37,86,"ʹAʹifkan|ʹaalihatañ|doonal|laahi|tureedoon?"
37,87,"Famaa|z̤̣annukum̃|bi-Rabbil|ʻAalameen?"
37,88,"Fanaz̤̣ara|naz̤̣ratañ|fin|Nujoom,"
37,89,"Faq̣aala|ʹinnee|saq̣eem!"
37,90,"Fatawallaw|ʻanhu|mudbireen."
37,91,"Faraag̣a|ʹilaaa|ʹaalihatihim|faq̣aala|ʹalaa|taʹkuloon?..."
37,92,"Maa-|lakum|laa-|tañṭiq̣oon?"
37,93,"Faraag̣a|ʻalayhim|ḍarbam|bilyameen."
37,94,"Faʹaq̣balooo|ʹilayhi|yaziffoon."
37,95,"Q̣aala|ʹataʻbudoona|maa-|tanḥitoon?"
37,96,"Wallaahu|khalaq̣akum|wa-maa|taʻmaloon!"
37,97,"Q̣aalub|noo|lahoo|bun-yaanañ|faʹalq̣oohu|fil|Jaḥeem!"
37,98,"Faʹaraadoo|bihee|kaydañ|fajaʻalnaahumul|ʹasfaleen!"
37,99,"Wa-q̣aala|ʹinnee|ẓaahibun|ʹilaa|Rabbee|sayahdeen!"
37,100,"Rabbi|hab|lee|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen!"
37,101,"Fabashsharnaahu|big̣ulaamin|ḥaleem."
37,102,"Falammaa|balag̣a|maʻahus|saʻya|q̣aala|yaa-bunayya|ʹinneee|ʹaraa|fil|manaami|ʹanneee|ʹaẓbaḥuka|fañz̤̣ur|maaẓaa|taraa!|Q̣aala|yaaaʹabatif|ʻal|maa-|tuʹmar:|satajiduneee|ʹiñ|shaaa|ʹallaahu|minaṣ|Ṣaabireen!"
37,103,"Falammaaa|ʹaslamaa|wa-tallahoo|liljabeen,"
37,104,"Wa-naadaynaahu|ʹañy|YaaaʹIbraaheem!"
37,105,"Q̣ad|ṣaddaq̣tar|ruʹyaa!|ʹInnaa|kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
37,106,"ʹInna|haaẓaa|lahuwal|balaaaʹul|mubeen."
37,107,"Wa-fadaynaahu|biẓibḥin|ʻaz̤̣eem:"
37,108,"Wa-taraknaa|ʻalayhi|fil|ʹaakhireen:"
37,109,"Salaamun|ʻalaaa|ʹIbraaheem!"
37,110,"Kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
37,111,"ʹInnahoo|min|ʻIbaadinal|Muʹmineen."
37,112,"Wa-bashsharnaahu|biʹIsḥaaq̣a|Nabiyyam|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
37,113,"Wa-baaraknaa|ʻalayhi|wa-ʻalaaa|ʹIsḥaaq̣:|wa-miñ|ẓurriyyatihimaa|muḥsinuñw|waz̤̣aalimul|linafsihee|mubeen."
37,114,"Wa-laq̣ad|manannaa|ʻalaa|Moosaa|wa-Haaroon."
37,115,"Wa-najjaynaahumaa|wa-q̣awmahumaa|minal|Karbil|ʻAz̤̣eem;"
37,116,"Wa-naṣarnaahum|fakaanoo|humul|g̣aalibeen."
37,117,"Wa-ʹaataynaahumal|kitaabal|mustabeen;"
37,118,"Wa-hadaynaahumaṣ|Ṣiraaṭal|Mustaq̣eem."
37,119,"Wa-taraknaa|ʻalayhimaa|fil|ʹaakhireen:"
37,120,"Salaamun|ʻalaa|Moosaa|wa-Haroon!"
37,121,"ʹInnaa|kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
37,122,"ʹInnahumaa|min|ʻibaadinal|Muʹmineen."
37,123,"Wa-ʹinna|ʹIlyaasa|laminal|mursaleen."
37,124,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|liq̣awmiheee|ʹalaa|tattaq̣oon?"
37,125,"ʹAtadʻoona|taẓaroona|Baʻlañwwa|ʹAḥsanal|Khaaliq̣een,―"
37,126,"ʹAllaaha|Rabbakum|wa-Rabba|ʹaabaaaʹikumul|ʹawwaleen?"
37,127,"Fakaẓẓaboohu|faʹinnahum|lamuḥḍaroon,―"
37,128,"ʹIllaa|ʻibaadal|laahil|mukhlaṣeen."
37,129,"Wa-taraknaa|ʻalayhi|fil|ʹaakhireen:"
37,130,"Salaamun|ʻalaaa|ʹIlyaaseen!"
37,131,"ʹInnaa|kaẓaalika|najzil|Muḥsineen."
37,132,"ʹInnahoo|min|ʻIbaadinal|Muʹmineen."
37,133,"Wa-ʹinna|Looṭal|laminal|mursaleen."
37,134,"ʹIẓ|najjaynaahu|wa-ʹahlahooo|ʹajmaʻeen,"
37,135,"ʹIllaa|ʻajoozañ|fil|g̣aabireen:"
37,136,"S̤umma|dammarnal|ʹaakhareen."
37,137,"Wa-ʹinnakum|latamurroona|ʻalayhim|muṣbiḥeen―"
37,138,"Wa-billayli|ʹafalaa|taʻq̣iloon?"
37,139,"Wa-ʹinna|Yoonusa|laminal|mursaleen."
37,140,"ʹIẓ|ʹabaq̣a|ʹilal|fulkil|mashḥoon."
37,141,"Fasaahama|fakaana|minal|mudḥaḍeen:"
37,142,"Faltaq̣amahul|Ḥootu|wa-huwa|muleem."
37,143,"Falawlaaa|ʹannahoo|kaana|minal|musabbiḥeen,"
37,144,"Lalabis̤a|fee|baṭniheee|ʹilaa|Yawmi|yubʻas̤oon."
37,145,"Fanabaẓnaahu|bilʻaraaaʹi|wa-huwa|saq̣eem."
37,146,"Wa-ʹambatnaa|ʻalayhi|shajaratam|miñy|yaq̣ṭeen."
37,147,"Wa-ʹarsalnaahu|ʹilaa|miʹati|ʹalfin|ʹaw|yazeedoon."
37,148,"Faʹaamanoo|famattaʻnaahum|ʹilaa|ḥeen."
37,149,"Fastaftihim|ʹa-li-Rabbikal|banaatu|wa-lahumul|banoon?―"
37,150,"ʹAm|khalaq̣nal|malaaaʹikata|ʹinaas̤añw|Wahum|shaahidoon?"
37,151,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahum|min|ʹifkihim|layaq̣ooloon:"
37,152,"Waladal|laahu|wa-ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon!"
37,153,"ʹAṣṭafal|banaati|ʻalal|baneen?"
37,154,"Maa-|lakum|Kayfa|taḥkumoon?"
37,155,"ʹAfalaa|taẓakkaroon?"
37,156,"ʹAm|lakum|sulṭaanum|mubeen?"
37,157,"Faʹtoo|bi-Kitaabikum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
37,158,"Wa-jaʻaloo|baynahoo|wa-baynal|Jinnati|nasabaa:|wa-laq̣ad|ʻalimatil|Jinnatu|ʹinnahum|lamuḥḍaroon!"
37,159,"Subḥaanal|laahi|ʻammaa|yaṣifoon!"
37,160,"ʹIllaa|ʻIbaadal|laahil|mukhlaṣeen."
37,161,"Faʹinnakum|wa-maa|taʻbudoon―"
37,162,"Maaa|ʹañtum|ʻalayhi|bifaatineen,"
37,163,"ʹIllaa|man|huwa|ṣaalil|Jaḥeem!"
37,164,"Wa-maa|minnaaa|ʹillaa|lahoo|maq̣aamum|maʻloom;"
37,165,"Wa-ʹinnaa|lanaḥnuṣ|ṣaaaffoon;"
37,166,"Wa-ʹinnaa|lanaḥnul|musabbiḥoon!"
37,167,"Wa-ʹiñ|kaanoo|layaq̣ooloon,"
37,168,"Law|ʹanna|ʻiñdanaa|Ẓikram|minal|ʹawwaleen,"
37,169,"Lakunnaa|ʻIbaadal|laahil|mukhlaṣeen!"
37,170,"Fakafaroo|bihee|fasawfa|yaʻlamoon!"
37,171,"Wa-laq̣ad|sabaq̣at|Kalimatunaa|liʻIbaadinal|mursaleen;"
37,172,"ʹInnahum|lahumul|mañṣooroon,"
37,173,"Wa-ʹinna|juñdanaa|lahumul|g̣aaliboon."
37,174,"Fatawalla|ʻanhum|ḥattaa|ḥeen,"
37,175,"Wa-ʹabṣirhum|fasawfa|yubṣiroon!"
37,176,"ʹAfabiʻaẓaabinaa|yastaʻjiloon?"
37,177,"Faʹiẓaa|nazala|bisaaḥatihim|fasaaaʹa|ṣabaaḥul|muñẓareen!"
37,178,"Wa-tawalla|ʻanhum|ḥattaa|ḥeen,"
37,179,"Wa-ʹabṣir|fasawfa|yubṣiroon!"
37,180,"Subḥaana|Rabbika|Rabbil|ʻIzzati|ʻammaa|yaṣifoon!"
37,181,"Wa-Salaamun|ʻalal|mursaleen!"
37,182,"Wal-Ḥamdu|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
38,1,"ṢAAAD|Wal-Q̣urʹaani|Ẓiẓ|Ẓikr."
38,2,"Balil|laẓeena|kafaroo|fee|ʻizzatiñw|Washiq̣aaq̣."
38,3,"Kam|ʹahlaknaa|miñ|q̣ablihim|miñ|q̣arniñ|fanaadaw|walaata|ḥeena|manaaṣ!"
38,4,"Wa-ʻajibooo|ʹañ|jaaaʹahum|Muñẓirun|minhum!|Wa-q̣aalal|Kaafiroonna|haaẓaa|saaḥiruñ|kaẓẓaab!"
38,5,"ʹAjaʻalal|ʹaalihata|ʹIlaahañw|Waaḥidaa?|ʹInna|haaẓaa|lashayʹun|ʻujaab!"
38,6,"Wañṭalaq̣al|malaʹu|minhum|ʻanim|shoo|waṣbiroo|ʻalaaa|ʹaalihatikum!|ʹInna|haaẓaa|lashayʹuñy|yuraad!"
38,7,"Maa-|samiʻnaa|bihaaẓaa|fil|millatil|ʹaakhirah:|ʹin|haaẓaaa|ʹillakh|tilaaq̣!"
38,8,"ʹA-ʹuñzila|ʻalayhiẓ|Ẓikru|mim|bayninaa?|Bal|hum|fee|shakkim|miñ|Ẓikree!|Bal|lammaa|yaẓooq̣oo|ʻAẓaab!"
38,9,"ʹAm|ʻiñdahum|khazaaaʹinu|Raḥmati|Rabbikal|ʻAzeezil|Wahhaab?"
38,10,"ʹAm|lahum|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa?|Falyartaq̣oo|fil|ʹasbaab!"
38,11,"Juñdum|maa|hunaalika|mahzoomum|minal|ʹaḥzaab."
38,12,"Kaẓẓabat|q̣ablahum|Q̣awmu|Nooḥiñw|WaʻAaduñw|Wa-Firʻawnu|Ẓul|ʹawtaad,"
38,13,"Wa-S̤amoodu|wa-Q̣awmu|Looṭiñw|waʹAṣḥaabul|ʹAykah;―|ʹulaaaʹikal|ʹAḥzaab."
38,14,"ʹIñ|kullun|ʹillaa|kaẓẓabar|rusula|faḥaq̣q̣a|ʻIq̣aab."
38,15,"Wa-maa|yañz̤̣uru|haaaʹulaaaʹi|ʹillaa|Ṣayḥatañw|waaḥidatam|maa|lahaa|miñ|fawaaq̣."
38,16,"Wa-q̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|ʻajjil|lanaa|q̣iṭṭanaa|q̣abla|Yawmil|Ḥisaab!"
38,17,"ʹIṣbir|ʻalaa|maa-|yaq̣ooloona|waẓkur|ʻAbdanaa|Daawooda|Ẓal|ʹayd:|ʹinnahooo|ʹawwaab."
38,18,"ʹInnaa|sakhkharnal|jibaala|maʻahoo|yusabbiḥna|bilʻashiyyi|wal-ʹishraaq̣,"
38,19,"Waṭṭayra|maḥshoorah:|kullul|lahooo|ʹawwaab."
38,20,"Wa-shadadnaa|mulkahoo|wa-ʹaataynaahul|ḥikmata|wa-faṣlal|khiṭaab."
38,21,"Wa-hal|ʹataaka|nabaʹul|khaṣm?|ʹIẓ|tasawwarul|miḥraab;"
38,22,"ʹIẓ|dakhaloo|ʻalaa|Daawooda|fafaziʻa|minhum|q̣aaloo|laa-|takhaf:|khaṣmaani|bag̣aa|baʻḍunaa|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñ|faḥkum̃|baynanaa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laa|tushṭiṭ|wahdinaaa|ʹilaa|sawaaaʹiṣ|ṣiraaṭ..."
38,23,"ʹInna|haaẓaaa|ʹakhee:|lahoo|tisʻuñw|watisʻoona|naʻjatañw|waliya|naʻjatuñw|waaḥidah:|faq̣aala|ʹakfilneehaa|wa-ʻazzanee|fil|khiṭaab."
38,24,"Q̣aala|laq̣ad|z̤̣alamaka|bisuʹaali|naʻjatika|ʹilaa|niʻaajih:|wa-ʹinna|kas̤eeram|minal|khulaṭaaaʹi|layabg̣ee|baʻḍuhum|ʻalaa|baʻḍin|ʹillal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-q̣aleelum|maa|hum!|Wa-z̤̣anna|Daawoodu|ʹannamaa|fatannaahu|fastag̣fara|Rabbahoo|wa-kharra|raakiʻañw|waʹanaab."
38,25,"Fag̣afarnaa|lahoo|ẓaalik:|wa-ʹinna|lahoo|ʻiñdanaa|lazulfaa|wa-ḥusna|maʹaab."
38,26,"Yaa-Daawoodu|ʹinnaa|jaʻalnaaka|Khaleefatañ|fil|ʹarḍi|faḥkum̃|baynan|naasi|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laa|tattabiʻil|hawaa|fayuḍillaka|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah:|ʹinnal|laẓeena|yaḍilloona|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|lahum|ʻaẓaabuñ|shadeedum|bimaa|nasoo|Yawmal|Ḥisaab."
38,27,"Wa-maa|khalaq̣nas|samaaaʹa|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaa|baaṭilaa!|Ẓaalika|z̤̣annul|laẓeena|kafaroo!|Fawaylul|lil-laẓeena|kafaroo|minan|Naar!"
38,28,"ʹAm|najʻalul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|kalmufsideena|fil|ʹarḍ?|ʹAm|najʻalul|muttaq̣eena|kalfujjaar?"
38,29,"Kitaabun|ʹañzalnaahu|ʹilayka|mubaarakul|liyaddabbarooo|ʹAayaatihee|wa-liyataẓakkara|ʹulul|ʹalbaab."
38,30,"Wa-wahabnaa|li-Daawooda|Sulaymaan:|niʻmal|ʻAbd!|ʹInnahooo|ʹawwaab!"
38,31,"ʹIẓ|ʻuriḍa|ʻalayhi|bilʻashiyyiṣ|ṣaafinaatul|jiyaad;"
38,32,"Faq̣aala|ʹinneee|ʹaḥbabtu|ḥubbal|khayri|ʻañ|ẓikri|Rabbee,―|ḥattaa|tawaarat|bilḥijaab:"
38,33,"Ruddoohaa|ʻalayy.|faṭafiq̣a|mas-ḥam|bissooq̣i|wal-ʹaʻnaaq̣."
38,34,"Wa-laq̣ad|fatannaa|Sulaymaana|wa-ʹalq̣aynaa|ʻalaa|kursiyyihee|jasadañ|s̤umma|ʹanaab:"
38,35,"Q̣aala|Rabbig̣|fir|lee|wa-hab|lee|Mulkal|laa|yambag̣ee|liʹaḥadim|mim|baʻdee:|ʹinnaka|ʹAñtal|Wahhaab."
38,36,"Fasakhkharnaa|lahur|Reeḥa|tajree|biʹamrihee|rukhaaaʹan|ḥays̤u|ʹaṣaab,―"
38,37,"Washshayaaṭeena|kulla|bannaaaʹiñw|wag̣awwaaṣ,―"
38,38,"Wa-ʹaakhareena|muq̣arraneena|fil|ʹaṣfaad."
38,39,"Haaẓaa|ʻAṭaaaʹunaa|famnun|ʹaw|ʹamsik|big̣ayri|ḥisaab."
38,40,"Wa-ʹinna|lahoo|ʻiñdanaa|lazulfaa|waḥusna|maʹaab."
38,41,"Waẓkur|ʻAbdanaaa|ʹAyyoob.|ʹIẓ|naadaa|Rabbahooo|ʹannee|massaniyash|shayṭaanu|binuṣbiñw|waʻaẓaab!"
38,42,"ʹUrkuḍ|birijlik:|haaẓaa|mug̣tasalum|baariduñw|washaraab."
38,43,"Wa-wahabnaa|lahooo|ʹahlahoo|wa-mis̤lahum|maʻahum|Raḥmatam|minnaa|wa-ẓikraa|liʹUlil|ʹalbaab."
38,44,"Wa-khuẓ|biyadika|ḍig̣s̤añ|faḍrib|bihee|wa-laa|taḥnas̤.|ʹInnaa|wa-jadnaahu|ṣaabiraa.|Niʻmal|ʻAbd!|ʹInnahooo|ʹawwaab!"
38,45,"Waẓkur|ʻIbaadanaaa|ʹIbraaheema|wa-ʹIsḥaaq̣a|wa-Yaʻq̣ooba|ʹUlil|ʹAydee|walʹAbṣaar."
38,46,"ʹInnaaa|ʹakhlaṣnaahum̃|bikhaaliṣatiñ|Ẓikrad|Daar."
38,47,"Wa-ʹinnahum|ʻiñdanaa|laminal|Muṣṭafaynal|ʹakhyaar."
38,48,"Waẓkur|ʹIsmaaʻeela|wal|yasaʻa|wa-Ẓal-Kifl:|wa-kullum|minal|ʹAkhyaar."
38,49,"Haaẓaa|Ẓikr:|wa-ʹinna|lil-Muttaq̣eena|laḥusna|maʹaab."
38,50,"Jannaati|ʻAdnim|mufattaḥatal|lahumul|ʹabwaab;"
38,51,"Muttakiʹeena|feehaa|yadʻoona|feehaa|bifaakihatiñ|kas̤eeratiñw|washaraab;"
38,52,"Wa-ʻiñdahum|q̣aaṣiratuṭ|ṭarfi|ʹatraab."
38,53,"Haaẓaa|maa-|tooʻadoona|li-Yawmil|Ḥisaab!"
38,54,"ʹInna|haaẓaa|la-Rizq̣unaa|maa-|lahoo|min|nafaad."
38,55,"Haaẓaa!|Wa-ʹinna|liṭṭaag̣eena|lasharra|maʹaab!―"
38,56,"Jahannama|Yaṣlawnahaa|fabiʹsal|mihaad!"
38,57,"Haaẓaa|falyaẓooq̣oohu|ḥameemuñw|wag̣assaaq̣!"
38,58,"Wa-ʹaakharu|miñ|shakliheee|ʹazwaaj!"
38,59,"Haaẓaa|fawjum|muq̣taḥimum|maʻakum!|Laa-|marḥabam|bihim!|ʹInnahum|ṣaalun|Naar!"
38,60,"Q̣aaloo|bal|ʹañtum!|Laa-|marḥabam|bikum!|ʹAñtum|q̣addamtumoohu|lanaa!|Fabiʹsal|q̣araar!"
38,61,"Q̣aaloo|Rabbanaa|mañ|q̣addama|lanaa|haaẓaa|fazidhu|ʻAẓaabañ|ḍiʻfañ|fin|Naar!"
38,62,"Waq̣aaloo|maa-|lanaa|laa-|naraa|rijaalañ|kunnaa|naʻudduhum|minal|ʹashraar?"
38,63,"ʹAttakhaẓnaahum|sikhriyyan|ʹam|zaag̣at|ʻanhumul|ʹabṣaar?"
38,64,"ʹInna|ẓaalika|laḥaq̣q̣uñ|takhaaṣumu|ʹAhlin|Naar!"
38,65,"Q̣ul|ʹInnamaaa|ʹana|Muñẓir:|wa-maa|min|ʹilaahin|ʹillal|laahul|Waaḥidul|Q̣ahhaar,―"
38,66,"Rabbus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumal|ʻAzeezul|G̣affaar."
38,67,"Q̣ul|huwa|Nabaʹun|ʻAz̤̣eem,"
38,68,"ʹAñtum|ʻanhu|muʻriḍoon!"
38,69,"Maa-|kaana|liya|min|ʻilmim|bil-malaʹil|ʹaʻlaaa|ʹiẓ|yakhtaṣimoon."
38,70,"ʹIñy|yooḥaaa|ʹilayya|ʹillaaa|ʹannamaaa|ʹana|Naẓeerum|mubeen."
38,71,"ʹIẓ|q̣aala|Rabbuka|lilmalaaaʹikati|ʹinnee|khaaliq̣um|basharam|miñ|ṭeen."
38,72,"Faʹiẓaa|sawwaytuhoo|wa-nafakhtu|feehi|mir|Rooḥee|faq̣aʻoo|lahoo|saajideen."
38,73,"Fasajadal|malaaaʹikatu|kulluhum|ʹajmaʻoon:"
38,74,"ʹIllaaa|ʹIblees;|ʹistakbara|wa-kaana|minal|kaafireen."
38,75,"Q̣aala|YaaaʹIbleesu|maa-|manaʻaka|ʹañ|tasjuda|limaa|khalaq̣tu|biyadayy?|ʹAs-takbarta|ʹam|kuñta|min|alʻaaleen?"
38,76,"Q̣aala|ʹana|khayrum|minh:|khalaq̣tanee|min|naariñw|wakhalaq̣tahoo|miñ|ṭeen."
38,77,"Q̣aala|fakhruj|minha|faʹinnaka|rajeem."
38,78,"Wa-ʹinna|ʻalayka|laʻnateee|ʹilaa|Yawmid|Deen."
38,79,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|faʹañz̤̣irneee|ʹilaa|Yawmi|yubʻas̤oon."
38,80,"Q̣aala|faʹinnaka|minal|muñz̤̣areen―"
38,81,"ʹIlaa|Yawmil|Waq̣til|Maʻloom."
38,82,"Q̣aala|fabiʻIzzatika|laʹug̣wiyannahum|ʹajmaʻeen.―"
38,83,"ʹIlaa|ʻIbaadaka|minhumul|mukhlaṣeen."
38,84,"Q̣aala|falhaq̣q̣u|walḥaq̣q̣a|ʹaq̣ool―"
38,85,"Laʹamlaʹanna|Jahannama|miñka|wa-mimmañ|tabiʻaka|minhum|ʹajmaʻeen."
38,86,"Q̣ul|maaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|min|ʹajriñw|Wamaaa|ʹana|minal|mutakallifeen."
38,87,"ʹIn|huwa|ʹillaa|Ẓikrul|lilʻaalameen."
38,88,"Wa-lataʻlamunna|nabaʹahoo|baʻda|ḥeen."
39,1,"Tañzeelul|Kitaabi|minal|laahil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥakeem."
39,2,"ʹInnaaa|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹilaykal|Kitaaba|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|faʻbudil|laaha|mukhliṣal|lahud|deen."
39,3,"ʹAlaa|lillaahid|deenul|khaaliṣ?|Wallaẓeenat|takhaẓoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹawliyaaaʹ.|Maa-|naʻbuduhum|ʹillaa|liyuq̣arriboonaaa|ʹilal|laahi|zulfaa.|ʹInnal|laaha|yaḥkumu|baynahum|fee|maa-|hum|feehi|yakhtalifoon.|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdee|man|huwa|kaaẓibuñ|kaffaar."
39,4,"Law|ʹaaraadal|laahu|ʹañy|yattakhiẓa|waladal|laṣṭafaa|mimmaa|yakhluq̣u|maa-|yashaaaʹu|Subḥaanah!|Huwal|laahul|Waaḥidul|Q̣ahhaar."
39,5,"Khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bilḥaq̣q̣:|yukawwirul|layla|ʻalan|nahaari|wa-yukawwirun|nahaara|ʻalal|layli|wa-sakhkharash|shamsa|walq̣amar:|kulluñy|yajree|liʹajalim|musammaa.|ʹAlaa|Huwal|ʻAzeezul|G̣affaar."
39,6,"Khalaq̣akum|min|nafsiñw|waaḥidatiñ|s̤umma|jaʻala|minhaa|zawjahaa|wa-ʹañzala|lakum|minal|ʹanʻaami|s̤amaaniyata|ʹazwaaj:|yakhluq̣ukum|fee|buṭooni|ʹummahaatikum|khalaq̣am|mim|baʻdi|khalq̣iñ|fee|ẓulumaatiñ|s̤alaas̤.|Ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukum|lahul|mulk.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo.|Faʹannaa|tuṣrafoon?"
39,7,"ʹIñ|takfuroo|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣aniyyun|ʻañkum:|wa-laa|yarḍaa|liʻibaadihil|kufr:|wa-ʹiñ|tashkuroo|yarḍahu|lakum.|Wa-laa|taziru|waaziratuñw|wizra|ʹukhraa.|S̤umma|ʹilaa|Rabbikum|Marjiʻukum|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon.|ʹInnahoo|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
39,8,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|massal|ʹiñsaana|ḍurruñ|daʻaa|Rabbahoo|muneeban|ʹilayhi|s̤umma|ʹiẓaa|khawwalahoo|niʻmatam|minhu|nasiya|maa-|kaana|yadʻooo|ʹilayhi|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-jaʻala|lillaahi|ʹañdaadal|liyuḍilla|ʻañ|Sabeelih.|Q̣ul|tamattaʻ|bikufrika|q̣aleelan|ʹinnaka|min|ʹAṣḥaabin|Naar!"
39,9,"ʹAmman|huwa|q̣aanitun|ʹaanaaaʹal|layli|saajidañw|waq̣aaaʹimañy|yaḥẓarul|ʹAakhirata|wa-yarjoo|Raḥmata|Rabbih?|Q̣ul|hal|yastawil|laẓeena|yaʻlamoona|wallaẓeena|la|yaʻlamoon?|ʹInnamaa|yataẓakkaru|ʹulul|ʹalbaab."
39,10,"Q̣ul|yaa-ʻibaadil|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣oo|Rabbakum.|Lillaẓeena|ʹaḥsanoo|fee|haaẓihid|dunyaa|ḥasanah.|Wa-ʹarḍul|laahi|waasiʻah!|ʹInnamaa|yuwaffaṣ|ṣaabiroona|ʹajrahum̃|big̣ayri|ḥisaab!"
39,11,"Q̣ul|ʹinneee|ʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹaʻbudal|laaha|mukhliṣal|lahud|deen;"
39,12,"Wa-ʹumirtu|liʹan|ʹakoona|ʹawwalal|Muslimeen."
39,13,"Q̣ul|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹin|ʻaṣaytu|Rabbee|ʻaẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻaz̤̣eem."
39,14,"Q̣ulil|laaha|ʹaʻbudu|mukhliṣal|lahoo|deenee:"
39,15,"Faʻbudoo|maa-|shiʹtum|miñ|doonih.|Q̣ul|ʹinnal|khaasireenal|laẓeena|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|wa-ʹahleehim|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah:|ʹalaa|ẓaalika|huwal|khusraanul|mubeen!"
39,16,"Lahum|miñ|fawq̣ihim|z̤̣ulalum|minañ|Naari|wa-miñ|taḥtihim|z̤̣ulal.|Ẓaalika|yukhawwiful|laahu|bihee|ʻIbaadah:|yaa-ʻIbaadi|fattaq̣oon."
39,17,"Wallaẓeenaj|tanabuṭ|Ṭaag̣oota|ʹañy|yaʻbudoohaa|wa-ʹanaabooo|ʹilal|laahi|lahumul|Bushraa:|fabashshir|ʻIbaad,―"
39,18,"ʹAllaẓeena|yastamiʻoonal|Q̣awla|fayattabiʻoona|ʹaḥsanah:|ʹulaaaʹikal|laẓeena|hadaahumul|laahu|wa-ʹulaaaʹika|hum|ʹulul|ʹalbaab."
39,19,"ʹAfaman|ḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhi|kalimatul|ʻAẓaab?|ʹA-faʹañta|tuñq̣iẓu|mañ|fin|Naar?"
39,20,"Laakinil|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|Rabbahum|lahum|g̣urafum|miñ|fawq̣ihaa|g̣urafum|mabniyyatuñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaar;|Waʻdal|laah:|laa-|yukhliful|laahul|meeʻaad."
39,21,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|ʹañzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹañ|fasalakahoo|yanaabeeʻa|fil|ʹarḍi|s̤umma|yukhriju|bihee|zarʻam|mukhtalifan|ʹalwaanuhoo|s̤umma|yaheeju|fataraahu|muṣfarrañ|s̤umma|yajʻaluhoo|ḥuṭaamaa.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|la-Ẓikraa|liʹulil|ʹalbaab."
39,22,"ʹAfamañ|sharaḥal|laahu|ṣadrahoo|lil-ʹIslaami|fahuwa|ʻalaa|Noorim|mir|Rabbih?|Fawaylul|lilq̣aasiyati|q̣uloobuhum|miñ|ẓikril|laah!|ʹulaaaʹika|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen!"
39,23,"ʹAllaahu|nazzala|ʹaḥsanal|Ḥadees̤i|Kitaabam|mutashaabiham|mas̤aaniya|taq̣shaʻirru|minhu|juloodul|laẓeena|yakhshawna|Rabbahum;|s̤umma|taleenu|julooduhum|wa-q̣uloobuhum|ʹilaa|Ẓikril|laah.|Ẓaalika|hudal|laahi|yahdee|bihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ;|wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|min|haad."
39,24,"ʹAfamañy|yattaq̣ee|biwajhihee|soooʹal|ʻaẓaabi|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah?|Wa-q̣eela|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|ẓooq̣oo|maa-|kuñtum|taksiboon!"
39,25,"Kaẓẓabal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|faʹataahumul|ʻAẓaabu|min|ḥays̤u|laa-|yashʻuroon."
39,26,"Faʹaẓaaq̣ahumul|laahul|khizya|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-laʻAẓaabul|ʹAakhirati|ʹakbar.|Law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoon!"
39,27,"Wa-laq̣ad|ḍarabnaa|linnaasi|fee|haaẓal|Q̣ur-ʹaani|miñ|kulli|Mas̤alil|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
39,28,"Q̣ur-ʹaanan|ʻArabiyyan|g̣ayra|ẓee|ʻiwajil|laʻallahum|yattaq̣oon."
39,29,"Ḍarabal|laahu|Mas̤alar|rajulañ|feehi|shurakaaaʹu|mutashaakisoona|wa-rajulañ|salamal|lirajul:|Hal|yastawiyaani|mas̤alaa?|ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaah!|Bal|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
39,30,"ʹInnaka|mayyituñw|waʹinnahum|mayyitoon."
39,31,"S̤umma|ʹinnakum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|ʻiñda|Rabbikum|takhtaṣimoon."
39,32,"Faman|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmañ|kaẓaba|ʻalal|laahi|wa-kaẓẓaba|biṣ-Ṣidq̣i|ʹiẓ|jaaaʹah?|ʹAlaysa|fee|Jahannama|mas̤wal|lilkaafireen?"
39,33,"Wallaẓee|jaaaʹa|biṣ-Ṣidq̣i|wa-ṣaddaq̣a|biheee|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|Muttaq̣oon."
39,34,"Lahum|maa|yashaaaʹoona|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|ẓaalika|jazaaaʹul|Muḥsineen,"
39,35,"Liyukaffiral|laahu|ʻanhum|ʹaswa|ʹallaẓee|ʻamiloo|wa-yajziyahum|ʹajrahum̃|biʹaḥsanil|laẓee|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
39,36,"ʹAlaysal|laahu|bi-Kaafin|ʻabdah?|Wa-yukhawwi-foonaka|billaẓeena|miñ|doonih!|Wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|min|haad."
39,37,"Wa-mañy|yahdil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|mim|muḍill.|ʹAlaysal|laahu|biʻAzeeziñ|Ẓiñ|tiq̣aam?"
39,38,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|man|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|layaq̣oolunnal|laah.|Q̣ul|ʹafaraʹaytum|maa|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹin|ʹaraadaniyal|laahu|biḍurrin|hal|hunna|kaashifaatu|ḍurriheee|ʹaw|ʹaraadanee|bi-Raḥmatin|hal|hunna|mumsikaatu|Raḥmatih?|Q̣ul|ḥasbiyal|laah!|ʻAlayhi|yatawakkalul|Mutawakkiloon."
39,39,"Q̣ul|yaa|q̣awmiʻmaloo|ʻalaa|makaanatikum|ʹinnee|ʻaamil:|fasawfa|taʻlamoon."
39,40,"Mañy|yaʹteehi|ʻaẓaabuñy|yukhzeehi|wa-yaḥillu|ʻalayhi|ʻaẓaabum|muq̣eem."
39,41,"ʹInnaaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalaykal|Kitaaba|linnaasi|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣.|famanih|tadaa|falinafsih:|wa-mañ|ḍalla|faʹinnamaa|yaḍillu|ʻalayhaa.|Wa-maaa|ʹañta|ʻalayhim̃|biwakeel."
39,42,"ʹAllaahu|yatawaffal|ʹañfusa|ḥeena|mawtihaa|wallatee|lam|tamut|fee|manaamihaa:|fayumsikul|latee|q̣aḍaa|ʻalayhal|mawta|wa-yursilul|ʹukhraaa|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammaa.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
39,43,"ʹAmit|takhaẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|shufaʻaaaʹ?|Q̣ul|ʹawalaw|kaanoo|laa-|yamlikoona|shayʹañw|walaa|yaʻq̣iloon?"
39,44,"Q̣ul|lillaahish|Shafaaʻatu|jameeʻaa:|lahoo|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|s̤umma|ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
39,45,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ẓukiral|laahu|Waḥdahush|maʹazzat|q̣uloobul|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirah;|wa-ʹiẓaa|ẓukiral|laẓeena|miñ|dooniheee|ʹiẓaa|hum|yastabshiroon!"
39,46,"Q̣ulil|laahumma|Faaṭiras|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|ʻAalimal|g̣aybi|washshahaadati|ʹAñta|taḥkumu|bayna|ʻibaadika|Fee|maa-|kaanoo|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
39,47,"Wa-law|ʹanna|lillaẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|maa-|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻañw|wamis̤lahoo|maʻahoo|laftadaw|bihee|miñ|soooʹil|ʻaẓaabi|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah:|wa-badaa|lahum|minal|laahi|maa-|lam|yakoonoo|yaḥtasiboon!"
39,48,"Wa-badaa|lahum|sayyiʹaatu|maa-|kasaboo|waḥaaq̣a|bihim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon!"
39,49,"Faʹiẓaa|massal|ʹiñsaana|ḍurruñ|daʻaanaa:|s̤umma|ʹiẓaa|khawwalnaahu|niʻmatam|minnaa|q̣aala|ʹinnamaaa|ʹooteetuhoo|ʻalaa|ʻilm!|Bal|hiya|fitnatuñw|walaakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon!"
39,50,"Q̣ad|q̣aalahal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|famaaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
39,51,"Faʹaṣaabahum|sayyiʹaatu|maa-|kasaboo.|Wallaẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|min|haaaʹulaaaʹi|sayuṣeebuhum|sayyiʹaatu|maa-|kasaboo|wa-maa|hum̃|bimuʻjizeen!"
39,52,"ʹAwalam|yaʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|yabsuṭur|rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaq̣dir?|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yuʹminoon!"
39,53,"Q̣ul|yaaʻIbaadiyal|laẓeena|ʹasrafoo|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim|laa-|taq̣naṭoo|mir|Raḥmatil|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|yag̣firuẓ|ẓunooba|jameeʻaa.|ʹInnahoo|Huwal|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
39,54,"Wa-ʹaneebooo|ʹilaa|Rabbikum|wa-ʹaslimoo|lahoo|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiyakumul|ʻAẓaabu|s̤umma|laa-|tuñṣaroon."
39,55,"Wattabiʻooo|ʹaḥsana|maaa|ʹuñzila|ʹilaykum|mir|Rabbikum|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiyakumul|ʻaẓaabu|bag̣tatañw|waʹañtum|laa-|tashʻuroon!―"
39,56,"ʹAñ|taq̣oola|nafsuñy|yaaḥasrataa|ʻalaa|maa-|farraṭtu|fee|jambil|laahi|wa-ʹiñ|kuñtu|laminas|saakhireen!"
39,57,"ʹAw|taq̣oola|law|ʹannal|laaha|hadaanee|lakuñtu|minal|Muttaq̣een!"
39,58,"ʹAw|taq̣oola|ḥeena|taral|ʻaẓaaba|law|ʹanna|lee|karratañ|faʹakoona|minal|Muḥsineen!"
39,59,"Balaa|q̣ad|jaaaʹatka|ʹAayaatee|fakaẓẓabta|bihaa|wastakbarta|wa-kuñta|minal|kaafireen."
39,60,"Wa-Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|taral|laẓeena|kaẓaboo|ʻalal|laahi|wujoohuhum|muswaddah:|ʹalaysa|fee|Jahannama|mas̤wal|lilmutakabbireen?"
39,61,"Wa-yunajjil|laahul|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|Bimafaazatihim|laa-|yamassuhumus|soooʹu|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
39,62,"ʹAllaahu|khaaliq̣u|kulli|shayʹ:|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñw|Wakeel."
39,63,"Lahoo|maq̣aaleedus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wallaẓeena|kafaroo|biʹAayaatil|laahi|ʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
39,64,"Q̣ul|ʹafag̣ayral|laahi|taʹmurooonneee|ʹaʻbudu|ʹayyuhal|jaahiloon?"
39,65,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayka|wa-ʹilal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablik:|laʹin|ʹashrakta|layaḥbaṭanna|ʻamaluka|wa-latakoonanna|minal|khaasireen."
39,66,"Balil|laaha|faʻbud|wa-kum|minash|shaakireen."
39,67,"Wa-maa|q̣adarul|laaha|ḥaq̣q̣a|q̣adrihee|wal-ʹarḍu|jameeʻañ|q̣abḍatuhoo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|wassamaawaatu|maṭwiyyaatum|biyameenih:|Subḥaanahoo|wa-Taʻaalaa|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
39,68,"Wa-nufikha|fiṣ|Ṣoori|faṣaʻiq̣a|mañ|fis|samaawaati|wa-mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹillaa|mañ|shaaaʹal|laah.|S̤umma|nufikha|feehi|ʹukhraa|faʹiẓaa|hum|q̣iyaamuñy|yañz̤̣uroon!"
39,69,"Wa-ʹashraq̣atil|ʹarḍu|binoori|Rabbihaa|wa-wuḍiʻal|Kitaabu|wa-jeeeʹa|bin-nabiyyeena|washshuhadaaaʹi|wa-q̣uḍiya|baynahum̃|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-hum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
39,70,"Wa-wuffiyat|kullu|nafsim|maa|ʻamilat|wa-Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|yafʻaloon."
39,71,"Wa-seeq̣al|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹilaa|Jahannama|zumaraa:|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹoohaa|futiḥat|ʹabwaabuhaa|wa-q̣aala|lahum|khazanatuhaaa|ʹalam|yaʹtikum|rusulum|miñkum|yatloona|ʻalaykum|ʹAayaati|Rabbikum|wa-yuñẓiroonakum|Liq̣aaaʹa|Yawmikum|haaẓaa?|Q̣aaloo|balaa|wa-laakin|ḥaq̣q̣at|Kalimatul|ʻAẓaabi|ʻalal|kaafireen!"
39,72,"Q̣eelad|khulooo|ʹabwaaba|Jahannama|khaalideena|feehaa:|fabiʹsa|mas̤wal|mutakabbireen!"
39,73,"Wa-seeq̣al|laẓeenat|taq̣aw|Rabbahum|ʹilal|Jannati|zumaraa:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹooha|wa-futiḥat|ʹabwaabuhaa|wa-q̣aala|lahum|khazanatuhaa|ʻʻSalaamun|ʻalaykum|ṭibtum|fadkhuloohaa|khaalideen.ʹʹ"
39,74,"Wa-q̣aalul|Ḥamdulillaahil|laẓee|ṣadaq̣anaa|Waʻdahoo|wa-ʹawras̤anal|ʹarḍa|natabaw|waʹu|minal|Jannati|ḥays̤u|Nashaaaʹ:|Faniʻma|ʹajrul|ʻaamileen!"
39,75,"Wa-taral|malaaaʹikata|ḥaaaffeena|Min|ḥawlil|ʻArshi|yusabbiḥoona|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbihim.|Wa-q̣uḍiya|baynahum̃|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-q̣eelal|Ḥamdu|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen!"
40,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem."
40,2,"Tañzeelul|Kitaabi|minal|laahil|ʻAzeezil|ʻAleem,―"
40,3,"G̣aafiriẓ|Ẓambi|wa-Q̣aabilit|Tawbi|Shadeedil|ʻIq̣aabi|Ẓiṭ|Ṭawl.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo:|ʹilayhil|Maṣeer."
40,4,"Maa-|yujaadilu|feee|ʹAayaatil|laahi|ʹillal|laẓeena|kafaroo|falaa|yag̣rurka|taq̣allubuhum|fil|bilaad!"
40,5,"Kaẓẓabat|q̣ablahum|Q̣awmu|Nooḥiñw|wal-ʹAḥzaabu|mim|baʻdihim;|wa-hammat|kullu|ʹummatim|birasoolihim|liyaʹkhuẓoohu|wa-jaadaloo|bilbaaṭili|liyudḥiḍoo|bihil|Ḥaq̣q̣a|faʹakhaẓtuhum!|Fakayfa|kaana|ʻIq̣aab!"
40,6,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ḥaq̣q̣at|Kalimatu|Rabbika|ʻalal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹannahum|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naar!"
40,7,"ʹAllaẓeena|yaḥmiloonal|ʻArsha|wa-man|ḥawlahoo|yusabbiḥoona|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbihim|wa-yuʹminoona|bihee|wa-yastag̣firoona|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo:|Rabbanaa|wasiʻta|kulla|shayʹir|Raḥmatañw|wa-ʻilmañ|fag̣fir|lillaẓeena|taaboo|wattabaʻoo|Sabeelaka|waq̣ihim|ʻAẓaabal|Jaḥeem!"
40,8,"Rabbanaa|wa-ʹadkhilhum|Jannaati|ʻAdninil|latee|waʻattahum|wa-mañ|ṣalaḥa|min|ʹaabaaaʹihim|wa-ʹazwaajihim|wa-ẓurriyyaatihim!|ʹInnaka|ʹAñtal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
40,9,"Waq̣ihimus|sayyiʹaat;|wa-mañ|taq̣is|sayyiʹaati|Yawmaʹiẓiñ|faq̣ad|raḥimtah:|wa-zaalika|huwal|Fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
40,10,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|yunaadawna|lamaq̣tul|laahi|ʹakbaru|mim|maq̣tikum|ʹañfusakum|ʹiẓ|tudʻawna|ʹilal|ʹeemaani|fatakfuroon."
40,11,"Q̣aaloo|Rabbanaaa|ʹamat|tanas̤natayni|wa-ʹaḥyaytanas̤|natayni|faʻtarafnaa|biẓunoobinaa|fahal|ʹilaa|khuroojim|miñ|sabeel?"
40,12,"Ẓaalikum̃|biʹannahooo|ʹiẓaa|duʻiyal|laahu|waḥdahoo|kafartum,|wa-ʹiñy|yushrak|bihee|tuʹminoo!|Fal-Ḥukmu|lillaahil|ʻAliyyil|Kabeer!"
40,13,"Huwal|laẓee|yureekum|ʹAayaatihee|wa-yunazzilu|lakum|minas|samaaaʹi|Rizq̣aa:|wa-maa|yataẓakkaru|ʹillaa|mañy|yuneeb."
40,14,"Fadʻul|laaha|mukhliṣeena|lahud|deena|wa-law|karihal|kaafiroon."
40,15,"Rafeeʻud|darajaati|Ẓul|ʻArsh:|yulq̣ir|rooḥa|min|ʹAmrihee|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹu|min|ʻibaadihee|liyuñẓira|Yawmat|Talaaq̣,―"
40,16,"Yawma|hum̃|baarizoon:|laa-|yakhfaa|ʻalal|laahi|minhum|shayʹ.|Limanil|Mulkul|Yawm?|Lillaahil|Waaḥidil|Q̣ahhaar!"
40,17,"ʹAl-Yawma|tujzaa|kullu|nafsim|bimaa|Kasabat|laa|z̤̣ulmal|Yawm.|ʹInnal|laaha|Sareeʻul|Ḥisaab."
40,18,"Wa-ʹañẓirhum|Yawmal|ʹAazifati|ʹiẓil|q̣uloobu|ladal|ḥanaajiri|kaaz̤̣imeen;|maa-|liz̤̣z̤̣aalimeena|min|ḥameemiñw|walaa|shafeeʻiñy|yuṭaaʻ."
40,19,"Yaʻlamu|khaaaʹinatal|ʹaʻyuni|wa-maa|tukhfiṣ|ṣudoor."
40,20,"Wallaahu|yaq̣ḍee|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣:|wallaẓeena|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihee|laa-|yaq̣ḍoona|bishayʹ|ʹInnal|laaha|Huwas|Sameeʻul|Baṣeer."
40,21,"ʹAwalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fayañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|kaanoo|miñ|q̣ablihim?|Kaanoo|hum|ʹashadda|minhum|q̣uwwatañw|waʹaas̤aarañ|fil|ʹarḍi|faʹakhaẓahumul|laahu|biẓunoobihim:|wa-maa|kaana|lahum|minal|laahi|miñw|waaq̣."
40,22,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|kaanat|taʹteehim|rusuluhum̃|bilbayyinaati|fakafaroo|faʹakhaẓahumul|laah:|ʹinnahoo|Q̣awiyyuñ|Shadeedul|ʻiq̣aab."
40,23,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Moosaa|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-Ṣultaanim|mubeen,"
40,24,"ʹIlaa|Firʻawna|wa-Haamaana|wa-Q̣aaroona|faq̣aaloo|saaḥiruñ|kaẓẓaab!"
40,25,"Falammaa|jaaʹahum̃|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|min|ʻiñdinaa|q̣aaluq̣|tulooo|ʹabnaaaʹal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻahoo|wastaḥyoo|nisaaaʹahum.|Wa-maa|kaydul|kaafireena|ʹillaa|fee|ḍalaal!..."
40,26,"Wa-q̣aala|Firʻawnu|ẓarooneee|ʹaq̣tul|Moosaa|walyadʻu|Rabbah!|ʹInneee|ʹakhaafu|ʹañy|yubaddila|deenakum|ʹaw|ʹañy|yuz̤̣hira|fil|ʹarḍil|fasaad!"
40,27,"Wa-q̣aala|Moosaaa|ʹinnee|ʻuẓtu|bi-Rabbee|wa-Rabbikum|miñ|kulli|mutakabbiril|laa|yuʹminu|bi-Yawmil|Ḥisaab."
40,28,"Wa-q̣aala|rajulum|Muʹminum|min|ʹAali|Firʻawna|yaktumu|ʹeemaanahooo|ʹataq̣tuloona|rajulan|ʹañy|yaq̣oola|Rabbiyal|laahu|wa-q̣ad|jaaaʹakum|bil-Bayyinaati|mir|Rabbikum?|Wa-ʹiñy|yaku|kaaẓibañ|faʻalayhi|kaẓibuh;|wa-ʹiñy|yaku|ṣaadiq̣añy|yuṣibkum̃|baʻḍul|laẓee|yaʻidukum:|ʹinnal|laaha|laa-|yahdee|man|huwa|musrifuñ|kaẓẓaab!"
40,29,"Yaa-Q̣awmi|lakumul|mulkul|yawma|z̤̣aahireena|fil|ʹarḍ:|famañy|yañṣurunaa|mim|baʹsil|laahi|ʹiñ|jaaaʹanaa?|Q̣aala|Firʻawnu|maaa|ʹureekum|ʹillaa|maaa|ʹaraa|wa-maaa|ʹahdeekum|ʹillaa|Sabeelar|Rashaad!"
40,30,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeee|ʹaamana|yaa-Q̣awmi|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|mis̤la|Yawmil|ʹAḥzaab;"
40,31,"Mis̤la|daʹbi|Q̣awmi|Nooḥiñw|WaʻAadiñw|Wa-Samooda|wallaẓeena|mim|baʻdihim:|wa-mal|laahu|yureedu|z̤̣ulmal|lilʻIbaad."
40,32,"Wa-yaa-Q̣awmi|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|Yawmat|Tanaad,―"
40,33,"Yawma|tuwalloona|mud-bireen:|maa-|lakum|minal|laahi|min|ʻaaṣim:|wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|min|haad."
40,34,"Wa-laq̣ad|jaaaʹakum|Yoosufu|miñ|q̣ablu|bil-Bayyinaati|famaa|ziltum|fee|shakkim|mimmaa|jaaaʹakum̃|bih:|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|halaka|q̣ultum|lañy|yab-ʻas̤al|laahu|mim|baʻdihee|rasoolaa.|Kaẓaalika|yuḍillul|laahu|man|huwa|musrifum|murtaab,―"
40,35,"ʹAllaẓeena|yujaadiloona|feee|ʹAayaatil|laahi|big̣ayri|sulṭaanin|ʹataahum.|Kabura|maq̣tan|ʻiñdal|laahi|wa-ʻiñdal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo.|Kaẓaalika|yaṭbaʻul|laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|q̣albi|mutakabbiriñ|jabbaar."
40,36,"Wa-q̣aala|Firʻawnu|yaa-Haamaanub|ni|lee|ṣarḥal|laʻalleee|ʹablug̣ul|ʹasbaab―"
40,37,"ʹAsbaabas|samaawaati|faʹaṭṭaliʻa|ʹilaaa|ʹilaahi|Moosaa|wa-ʹinnee|laʹaz̤̣unnuhoo|kaaẓibaa!|Wa-kaẓaalika|zuyyina|li-Firʻawna|soooʹu|ʻamalihee|waṣudda|ʻanis|Sabeel:|wa-maa|kaydu|Firʻawna|ʹillaa|fee|tabaab."
40,38,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeee|ʹaamana|yaa-Q̣awmit|tabiʻooni|ʹahdikum|Sabeelar|Rashaad."
40,39,"Yaa-Q̣awmi|ʹinnamaa|haaẓihil|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|mataaʻ;|wa-ʹinnal|ʹAakhirata|hiya|Daarul|Q̣araar."
40,40,"Man|ʻamila|sayyiʹatañ|falaa|yujzaaa|ʹillaa|mis̤lahaa:|wa-man|ʻamila|ṣaaliḥam|miñ|ẓakarin|ʹaw|ʹuñs̤aa|wa-huwa|Muʹminuñ|faʹulaaaʹika|yadkhuloonal|Jannata|yurzaq̣oona|feehaa|big̣ayri|ḥisaab."
40,41,"Wayaa-Q̣awmi|maa-|leee|ʹadʻookum|ʹilan|Najaati|wa-tadʻoonaneee|ʹilan|Naar!"
40,42,"Tadʻoonanee|liʹakfura|billaahi|wa-ʹushrika|bihee|maa-|laysa|lee|bihee|ʻilm:|wa-ʹana|ʹadʻookum|ʹilal|ʻAzeezil|G̣affaar."
40,43,"Laa-|jarama|ʹannamaa|tadʻoonaneee|ʹilayhi|laysa|lahoo|daʻwatuñ|fid|dunyaa|wa-laa|fil|ʹAakhirati|wa-ʹanna|maraddanaaa|ʹilal|laahi|wa-ʹannal|musrifeena|hum|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naar!"
40,44,"Fasataẓkuroona|maaa|ʹaq̣oolu|lakum.|Wa-ʹufawwiḍu|ʹamreee|ʹilal|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|Baṣeerum|bilʻibaad."
40,45,"Fawaq̣aahul|laahu|sayyiʹaati|maa-|makaroo|waḥaaq̣a|biʹAali|Firʻawna|soooʹul|ʻAẓaab."
40,46,"ʹAn-Naaru|yuʻraḍoona|ʻalayhaa|g̣uduwwañw|waʻashiyyaa:|wa-Yawma|taq̣oomus|Saaʻah:|ʹadkhilooo|ʹAala|Firʻawna|ʹashaddal|ʻaẓaab!"
40,47,"Wa-ʹiẓ|yataḥaaajjoona|fin|Naari|fayaq̣ooluḍ|ḍuʻafaaaʹu|lillaẓeenas|takbarooo|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|lakum|tabaʻañ|fahal|ʹañtum|mug̣noona|ʻannaa|naṣeebam|minan|Naar?"
40,48,"Q̣aalal|laẓeenas|takbarooo|ʹinnaa|kulluñ|feehaaa|ʹinnal|laaha|q̣ad|ḥakama|baynal|ʻibaad!"
40,49,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|fin|Naari|likhazanati|Jahannamad|ʻoo|Rabbakum|yukhaffif|ʻannaa|yawmam|minal|ʻaẓaab!"
40,50,"Q̣aalooo|ʹawalam|taku|taʹteekum|rusulukum̃|bil-Bayyinaat?|Q̣aaloo|balaa.|Q̣aaloo|fadʻoo!|Wa-maa|duʻaaaʹul|kaafireena|ʹillaa|fee|ḍalaal!"
40,51,"ʹInnaa|lanañṣuru|rusulanaa|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-Yawma|yaq̣oomul|ʹAshhaad,―"
40,52,"Yawma|laa-|yañfaʻuz̤̣z̤̣|aalimeena|maʻẓiratuhum|wa-lahumul|Laʻnatu|wa-lahum|Soooʹud|Daar."
40,53,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Hudaa|wa-ʹawras̤naa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelal|Kitaab―"
40,54,"Hudañw|Wa-Ẓikraa|liʹulil|ʹalbaab."
40,55,"Faṣbir|ʹinna|Waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|wastag̣fir|liẓambika|wa-sabbiḥ|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbika|bilʻashiyyi|wal-ʹibkaar."
40,56,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yujaadiloona|feee|ʹAayaatil|laahi|big̣ayri|sulṭaanin|ʹataahum|ʹiñ|fee|ṣudoorihim|ʹillaa|kibrum|maa|hum̃|bibaalig̣eeh:|fastaʻiẓ|billaah:|ʹinnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|Baṣeer."
40,57,"Lakhalq̣us|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|ʹakbaru|min|khalq̣in|naasi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
40,58,"Wa-maa|yastawil|ʹaʻmaa|walbaṣeer:|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-lal|museeeʹ.|Q̣aleelam|maa|tataẓakkaroon!"
40,59,"ʹInnas|Saaʻata|laʹaatiyatul|laa|rayba|feehaa|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yuʹminoon."
40,60,"Wa-q̣aala|Rabbukumud|ʻooneee|ʹastajib|lakum.|ʹInnal|laẓeena|yastakbiroona|ʻan|ʻibaadatee|sayadkhuloona|Jahannama|daakhireen!"
40,61,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|layla|litaskunoo|feehi|wannahaara|mubṣiraa.|ʹInnal|laaha|la-Ẓoo|Faḍlin|ʻalan|naasi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yashkuroon."
40,62,"Ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukum|khaaliq̣u|kulli|shayʹ.|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo:|Faʹannaa|tuʹfakoon!"
40,63,"Kaẓaalika|yuʹfakul|laẓeena|kaanoo|biʹAayaatil|laahi|yajḥadoon."
40,64,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹarḍa|q̣araarañw|wassamaaaʹa|binaaaʹañw|waṣawwarakum|faʹaḥsana|ṣuwarakum|wa-razaq̣akum|minaṭ|ṭayyibaat;―|ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbukum.|Fatabaarakal|laahu|Rabbul|ʻAalameen!"
40,65,"Huwal|Ḥayyu|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwa|fadʻoohu|mukhliṣeena|lahud|deen.|ʹAl-Ḥamdu|lillaahi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen!"
40,66,"Q̣ul|ʹinnee|nuheetu|ʹan|ʹaʻbudal|laẓeena|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|lammaa|jaaʹaniyal|Bayyinaatu|mir|Rabbee,|wa-ʹumirtu|ʹan|ʹuslima|li-Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
40,67,"Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|miñ|turaabiñ|s̤umma|min|nuṭfatiñ|s̤umma|min|ʻalaq̣atiñ|s̤umma|yukhrijukum|ṭiflañ|s̤umma|litablug̣ooo|ʹashuddakum|s̤umma|litakoonoo|shuyookhaa,―|Wa-miñkum|mañy|yutawaffaa|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-litablug̣ooo|ʹajalam|musammañw|walaʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
40,68,"Huwal|laẓee|yuḥyee|wa-yumeet;|faʹiẓaa|q̣aḍaaa|ʹamañ|faʹinnamaa|yaq̣oolu|lahoo|ʻʻKUÑʹʹ|fayakoon."
40,69,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|yujaadiloona|feee|ʹAayaatil|laah?|ʹAnnaa|yuṣrafoon?"
40,70,"ʹAllaẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|bil-Kitaabi|wa-bimaaa|ʹarsalnaa|bihee|rusulanaa|fasawfa|yaʻlamoon,"
40,71,"ʹIẓil|ʹag̣laalu|feee|ʹaʻnaaq̣ihim|wassalaasilu|yusḥaboon."
40,72,"Fil|ḥameemi,|s̤umma|fin|Naari|yusjaroon."
40,73,"S̤umma|q̣eela|lahum|ʹayna|maa-|kuñtum|tushrikoon"
40,74,"Miñ|doonil|laah?|Q̣aaloo|ḍalloo|ʻannaa|bal|lam|nakun|nadʻoo|miñ|q̣ablu|shayʹaa.|Kaẓaalika|yuḍillul|laahul|kaafireen."
40,75,"Ẓaalikum̃|bimaa|kuñtum|tafraḥoona|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-bimaa|kuñtum|tamraḥoon."
40,76,"ʹUdkhulooo|ʹabwaaba|Jahannama|khaalideena|feehaa:|fabiʹsa|mas̤wal|mutakabbireen!"
40,77,"Faṣbir|ʹinna|Waʹdal|laahi|Ḥaq̣q̣;|faʹimmaa|nuriyannaka|baʻḍal|laẓee|naʻiduhum|ʹaw|natawaffayannaka|faʹilaynaa|yurjaʹoon."
40,78,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|rusulam|miñ|q̣ablika|minhum|mañ|q̣aṣaṣnaa|ʻalayka|wa-minhum|mal|lam|naq̣ṣuṣ|ʻalayk.|Wa-maa|kaana|lirasoolin|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|biʹAayatin|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnil|laah:|faʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹamrul|laahi|q̣uḍiya|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-khasira|hunaalikal|mubṭiloon."
40,79,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹanʻaama|litarkaboo|minhaa|wa-minhaa|taʹkuloon;"
40,80,"Wa-lakum|feehaa|manaafiʻu|wa-litablug̣oo|ʻalayhaa|ḥaajatañ|fee|ṣudoorikum|wa-ʻalayhaa|wa-ʻalal|fulki|tuḥmaloon."
40,81,"Wa-yureekum|ʹAayaatihee|faʹayya|ʹAayaatil|laahi|tuñkiroon."
40,82,"ʹAfalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fayañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim?|Kaanooo|ʹaks̤ara|minhum|wa-ʹashadda|q̣uwwatañw|waʹaas̤aarañ|fil|ʹarḍi|famaaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
40,83,"Falammaa|jaaaʹathum|rusuluhum̃|bil-Bayyinaati|fariḥoo|bimaa|ʻiñdahum|minal|ʻilmi|wa-ḥaaq̣a|bihim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon."
40,84,"Falammaa|raʹaw|Baʹsanaa|q̣aalooo|ʹaamannaa|billaahi|Waḥdahoo|wa-kafarnaa|bimaa|kunnaa|bihee|mushrikeen."
40,85,"Falam|yaku|yañfaʻuhum|ʹeemaanuhum|lammaa|raʹaw|Baʹsanaa.|Sunnatal|laahil|latee|q̣ad|khalat|fee|ʻibaadih.|Wa-khasira|hunaalikal|kaafiroon!"
41,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem:"
41,2,"Tañzeelum|minar|Raḥmaanir|Raḥeem;―"
41,3,"Kitaabuñ|fuṣṣilat|ʹAayaatuhoo|Q̣ur-ʹaanan|ʻarabiyyal|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻlamoon;"
41,4,"Basheerañw|Wa-Naẓeeraa:|faʹaʻraḍa|ʹaks̤aruhum|fahum|laa-|yasmaʻoon."
41,5,"Wa-q̣aaloo|q̣uloobunaa|feee|ʹakinnatim|mimmaa|tadʻoonaaa|ʹilayhi|wa-feee|ʹaaẓaaninaae|waq̣ruñw|wamim|bayninaa|wa-baynika|ḥijaabuñ|faʻmal|ʹinnanaa|ʻaamiloon."
41,6,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|basharum|mis̤lukum|yooḥaaa|ʹilayya|ʹannamaaa|ʹIlaahukum|ʹIlaahuñw|Waaḥiduñ|fastaq̣eemooo|ʹilayhi|wastag̣firooh.|Wa-waylul|lil-Mushrikeen,―"
41,7,"ʹAllaẓeena|laa-|yuʹtoonaz|Zakaata|wa-hum̃|bil-ʹAakhirati|hum|kaafiroon."
41,8,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|lahum|ʹajrun|g̣ayru|mamnoon."
41,9,"Q̣ul|ʹaʹinnakum|latakfuroona|billaẓee|khalaq̣al|ʹarḍa|fee|Yawmayni|wa-tajʻaloona|lahooo|ʹañdaadaa?|Ẓaalika|Rabbul|ʻAalameen."
41,10,"Wa-jaʻala|feehaa|rawaasiya|miñ|fawq̣ihaa|wa-baaraka|feehaa|wa-q̣addara|feehaaa|ʹaq̣waatahaa|feee|arbaʻati|ʹAyyaam;|sawaaaʹal|lissaaaʹileen."
41,11,"S̤ummas|tawaaa|ʹilas|samaaaʹi|wa-hiya|dukhaanuñ|faq̣aala|lahaa|wa-lilʹarḍiʹ|tiyaa|ṭawʻan|ʹaw|karhaa.|Q̣aalataaa|ʹataynaa|ṭaaʹiʻeen."
41,12,"Faq̣aḍaahunna|sabʻa|samaawaatiñ|fee|Yawmayni|wa-ʹawḥaa|fee|kulli|samaaaʹin|ʹamrahaa.|Wa-zayyannassa|maaaʹad|dunyaa|bimaṣaabeeḥa|wa-ḥifz̤̣aa.|Ẓaalika|Taq̣deerul|ʻAzeezil|ʻAleem."
41,13,"Faʹin|ʹaʻraḍoo|faq̣ul|ʹañẓartukum|Ṣaaʻiq̣atam|mis̤la|Ṣaaʻiq̣ati|ʻAadiñw|Wa-S̤amood!"
41,14,"ʹIẓ|jaaaʹathumur|rusulu|mim|bayni|ʹaydeehim|wa-min|khalfihim|ʹallaa|taʻbudooo|ʹillal|laah.|Q̣aaloo|law|shaaaʹa|Rabbunaa|laʹañzala|malaaaʹikatañ|faʹinnaa|bimaaa|ʹursiltum̃|bihee|kaafiroon."
41,15,"Faʹammaa|ʻAaduñ|fastakbaroo|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-q̣aaloo|man|ʹashaddu|minnaa|q̣uwwah?|ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannal|laahal|laẓee|khalaq̣ahum|Huwa|ʹashaddu|minhum|q̣uwwah?|Wa-kaanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|yajḥadoon!"
41,16,"Faʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhim|Reeḥañ|ṣarṣarañ|feee|ʹAyyaamin|naḥisaatil|linuẓeeq̣ahum|ʻaẓaabal|khizyi|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa;|wa-laʻAẓaabul|ʹAakhirati|ʹakhzaa|Wahum|laa-|yuñṣaroon."
41,17,"Wa-ʹammaa|S̤amoodu|fahadaynaahum|fastaḥabbul|ʻamaa|ʻalal|Hudaa|faʹakhaẓathum|Ṣaaʻiq̣atul|ʻaẓaabil|hooni|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
41,18,"Wa-najjaynal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-kaanoo|yattaq̣oon."
41,19,"Wa-Yawma|yuḥsharu|ʹaʻdaaaʹul|laahi|ʹilan|Naari|fahum|yoozaʻoon."
41,20,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|maa-|jaaaʹoohaa|shahida|ʻalayhim|samʻuhum|wa-ʹabṣaaruhum|wa-julooduhum̃|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
41,21,"Wa-q̣aaloo|lijuloodihim|lima|shahittum|ʻalaynaa?|Q̣aalooo|ʹañṭaq̣anal|laahul|laẓeee|ʹañṭaq̣a|kulla|shayʹiñw|wa-Huwa|khalaq̣akum|ʹawwala|marratiñw|waʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
41,22,"Wa-maa|kuñtum|tastatiroona|ʹañy|yashhada|ʻalaykum|samʻukum|wa-laaa|ʹabṣaarukum|wa-laa|juloodukum|wa-laakiñ|z̤̣anañtum|ʹannal|laaha|laa-|yaʻlamu|kas̤eeram|mimmaa|taʻmaloon!"
41,23,"Wa-ẓaalikum|z̤̣annukumul|laẓee|z̤̣anañtum̃|bi-Rabbikum|ʹardaakum|faʹaṣbaḥtum|minal|khaasireen."
41,24,"Faʹiñy|yaṣbiroo|fan-naaru|mas̤wal|lahum!|Wa-ʹiñy|yastaʻtiboo|famaa|hum|minal|muʻtabeen."
41,25,"Wa-q̣ayyaḍnaa|lahum|q̣uranaaaʹa|fazayyanoo|lahum|maa|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-maa|khalfahum|wa-ḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhimul|q̣awlu|feee|ʹumamiñ|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablihim|minal|Jinni|wal-ʹIñs;|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|khaasireen."
41,26,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|laa-|tasmaʻoo|lihaaẓal|Q̣urʹaani|walg̣aw|feehi|laʻallakum|tag̣liboon!"
41,27,"Falanuẓeeq̣annal|laẓeena|kafaroo|ʻaẓaabañ|shadeedañw|walanajziyannahum|ʹaswaʹal|laẓee|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
41,28,"Ẓaalika|jazaaaʹu|ʹaʻdaaaʹil|laahin|Naar:|lahum|feehaa|Daarul|Khuld:|jazaaaʹam|bimaa|kaanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|yajḥadoon."
41,29,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|Rabbanaaa|ʹarinal|laẓeena|ʹaḍal-laanaa|minal|jinni|wal-ʹiñsi|najʻalhumaa|taḥta|ʹaq̣daaminaa|liyakoonaa|minal|ʹasfaleen."
41,30,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|q̣aaloo|Rabbunal|laahu|s̤ummas|taq̣aamoo|tatanazzalu|ʻalayhimul|malaaaʹikatu|ʹallaa|takhaafoo|wa-laa|taḥzanoo|wa-ʹabshiroo|bil-Jannatil|latee|kuñtum|tooʻadoon!"
41,31,"Naḥnu|ʹawliyaaaʹukum|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-fil|ʹAakhirah:|wa-lakum|feehaa|maa-|tashtaheee|ʹañfusukum|wa-lakum|feehaa|maa-|taddaʻoon!"
41,32,"Nuzulam|min|G̣afoorir|Raḥeem."
41,33,"Wa-man|ʹaḥsanu|q̣awlam|mimmañ|daʻaaa|ʹilal|laahi|wa-ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañw|waq̣aala|ʹinnanee|minal|Muslimeen?"
41,34,"Wa-laa|tastawil|ḥasanatu|wa-las|sayyiʹah.|ʹIdfaʻ|billatee|hiya|ʹaḥsanu|faʹiẓal|laẓee|baynaka|wa-baynahoo|ʻadaawatuñ|kaʹannahoo|wa-liyyun|ḥameem!"
41,35,"Wa-maa|yulaq̣q̣aahaaa|ʹillal|laẓeena|wa-maa|ṣabaroo|yulaq̣q̣aahaaa|ʹillaa|ẓoo|ḥaz̤̣z̤̣in|ʻaz̤̣eem."
41,36,"Wa-ʹimmaa|yañzag̣annaka|minash|Shayṭaani|nazg̣uñ|fastaʻiẓ|billaah.|ʹInnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem."
41,37,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatihil|laylu|wannahaaru|washshamsu|walq̣amar.|Laa-|tasjudoo|lishshamsi|wa-laa|lilq̣amari|wasjudoo|lillaahil|laẓee|khalaq̣ahunna|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ʹiyyaahu|taʻbudoon."
41,38,"Faʹinis|takbaroo|fallaẓeena|ʻiñda|Rabbika|yusabbiḥoona|lahoo|billayli|wannahaari|wahum|laa-|yasʹamoon."
41,39,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatiheee|ʹannaka|taral|ʹarḍa|khaashiʻatañ|faʹiẓaaa|ʹañzalnaa|ʻalayhal|maaaʹah|tazzat|wa-rabat.|ʹInnal|laẓeee|ʹaḥyaahaa|la-Muḥyil|mawtaa.|ʹInnahoo|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
41,40,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yulḥidoona|feee|ʹAayaatinaa|laa-|yakhfawna|ʻalaynaa.|ʹAfamañy|yulq̣aa|fin|naari|khayrun|ʹam|mañy|yaʹteee|ʹaaminañy|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah?|ʹIʻmaloo|maa-|shiʹtum|ʹinnahoo|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
41,41,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|biẓ-Ẓikri|lammaa|jaaaʹahum.|Wa-ʹinnahoo|la-Kitaabun|ʻAzeez."
41,42,"Laa-|yaʹteehil|baaṭilu|mim|bayni|yadayhi|wa-laa|min|khalfih:|Tañzeelum|min|Ḥakeemin|Ḥameed."
41,43,"Maa-|yuq̣aalu|laka|ʹillaa|maa-|q̣ad|q̣eela|lir-rusuli|miñ|q̣ablik:|ʹinna|Rabbaka|la-Ẓoo|mag̣firatiñw|wa-Ẓoo|ʻIq̣aabin|ʹaleem."
41,44,"Wa-law|jaʻalnaahu|Q̣ur-ʹaanan|ʹAʻjamiyyal|laq̣aaloo|law-laa|fuṣṣilat|ʹAayaatuh?|ʹAʻ-jamiyyuñw|WaʻArabiyy?|Q̣ul|huwa|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|hudañw|washifaaaʹ:|wallaẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|feee|ʹaaẓaanihim|waq̣ruñw|wahuwa|ʻalayhim|ʻamaa.|ʹUlaaaʹika|yunaadawna|mim|makaanim|baʻeed!"
41,45,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Moosal|Kitaaba|fakhtulifa|feeh.|Wa-lawlaa|Kalimatuñ|sabaq̣at|mir|Rabbika|laq̣uḍiya|baynahum:|wa-ʹinnahum|lafee|shakkim|minhu|mureeb."
41,46,"Man|ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|falinafsihee|wa-man|ʹasaaaʹa|faʻalayhaa:|wa-maa|Rabbuka|biz̤̣allamil|lil-ʻabeed."
41,47,"ʹIlayhi|yuraddu|ʻilmus|Saaʻah:|wa-maa|takhruju|miñ|s̤amaraatim|min|ʹakmaamihaa|wa-maa|taḥmilu|min|ʹuñs̤aa|wa-laa|taḍaʻu|ʹillaa|biʻilmih.|Wa-Yawma|yunaadeehim|ʹayna|shurakaaaʹee|q̣aalooo|ʹaaẓannaaka|maa-|minnaa|miñ|shaheed!"
41,48,"Wa-ḍalla|ʻanhum|maa|kaanoo|yadʻoona|miñ|q̣ablu|waz̤̣annoo|maa-|lahum|mim|maḥeeṣ."
41,49,"Laa-|yasʹamul|ʹiñsaanu|miñ|duʻaaaʹil|khayri|wa-ʹim|massa|hushsharru|fayaʹoosuñ|q̣anooṭ."
41,50,"Wa-laʹin|ʹaẓaq̣naahu|Raḥmatam|minnaa|mim|baʻdi|ḍar-raaaʹa|massathu|layaq̣oolanna|haaẓaa|lee|wa-maaa|ʹaz̤̣unnus|Saaʻata|q̣aaaʹimatañw|walaʹir|rujiʻtu|ʹilaa|Rabbeee|ʹinna|lee|ʻiñdahoo|lalḥusnaa!|Falanunabbiʹannal|laẓeena|kafaroo|bimaa|ʻamiloo,|wa-lanuẓeeq̣an-nahum|min|ʻAẓaabin|g̣aleez̤̣."
41,51,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʹanʻamnaa|ʻalal|ʹiñsaani|ʹaʻraḍa|wa-naʹaa|bijaanibih;|wa-ʹiẓaa|massahush|sharru|faẓoo|duʻaaaʹin|ʻareeḍ!"
41,52,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹiñ|kaana|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|s̤umma|kafartum̃|bihee|man|ʹaḍallu|mimman|huwa|fee|shiq̣aaq̣im|baʻeed?"
41,53,"Sanureehim|ʹAayaatinaa|fil|ʹaafaaq̣i|wa-feee|ʹañfusihim|ḥattaa|yatabayyana|lahum|ʹannahul|Ḥaq̣q̣.|ʹA-walam|yakfi|bi-Rabbika|ʹannahoo|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|shaheed?"
41,54,"ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahum|fee|miryatim|mil|Liq̣aaaʹi|Rabbihim?|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahoo|bikulli|shayʹim|Muḥeeṭ."
42,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem;"
42,2,"ʻAyyyn-Seeen-Q̣aaaf."
42,3,"Kaẓaalika|yooḥeee|ʹilayka|wa-ʹilal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablikal|laahul|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
42,4,"Lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAliyyul|ʻAz̤̣eem."
42,5,"Takaadus|samaawaatu|yatafaṭṭarna|miñ|fawq̣ihinna|walmalaaaʹikatu|yusabbiḥoona|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbihim|wa-yastag̣firoona|limañ|fil|ʹarḍ:|ʹalaaa|ʹinnal|laaha|Huwal|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
42,6,"Wallaẓeenat|takhaẓoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹawliyaaaʹal|laahu|ḥafeez̤̣un|ʻalayhim|wa-maaa|ʹañta|ʻalayhim̃|biwakeel."
42,7,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|Q̣ur-ʹaanan|ʻArabiyyal|lituñẓira|ʹUmmal|Q̣uraa|wa-man|ḥawlahaa|wa-tuñẓira|Yawmal|Jamʻi|laa-|rayba|feeh:|fareeq̣uñ|fil|Jannati|wa-fareeq̣uñ|fis|Saʻeer."
42,8,"Wa-law|shaaaʹal|laahu|lajaʻalahum|ʹUmmatañw|Waaḥidatañw|walaakiñy|yudkhilu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|fee|Raḥmatih;|waz̤̣z̤̣aalimoona|maa-|lahum|miñw|waliyyiñw|walaa|naṣeer."
42,9,"ʹAmit|takhaẓoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹawliyaaaʹ?|Fallaahu|Huwal|Waliyyu|wa-Huwa|yuḥyil|mawtaa,|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
42,10,"Wa-makh|talaftum|feehi|miñ|shayʹiñ|faḥukmuhooo|ʹilal|laah:|ẓaalikumul|laahu|Rabbee|ʻalayhi|tawakkaltu|wa-ʹilayhi|ʹuneeb."
42,11,"Faaṭirus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ!|Jaʻala|lakum|min|ʹañfusikum|ʹazwaajañw|Waminal|ʹanʻaami|ʹazwaajaa:|yaẓraʹukum|feeh:|Laysa|kamis̤lihee|shayʹ;|wa-Huwas|sameeʻul|Baṣeer."
42,12,"Lahoo|maq̣aaleedus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ;|Yabsuṭur|Rizq̣a|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yaq̣dir:|ʹinnahoo|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
42,13,"Sharaʻa|lakum|minad|Deeni|maa-|waṣṣaa|bihee|Nooḥañw|wallaẓeee|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|wa-maa|waṣṣaynaa|biheee|ʹIbraaheema|wa-Moosaa|wa-ʻEesaaa|ʹan|ʹaq̣eemud|Deena|wa-laa|tatafarraq̣oo|feeh:|kabura|ʻalal|mushrikeena|maa-|tadʻoohum|ʹilayh.|ʹAllaahu|yajtabeee|ʹilayhi|mañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yahdeee|ʹilayhi|mañy|yuneeb."
42,14,"Wa-maa|tafarraq̣ooo|ʹillaa|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹahumul|ʻilmu|bag̣yam|baynahum.|Wa-lawlaa|Kalimatuñ|sabaq̣at|mir|Rabbika|ʹilaaa|ʹajalim|musammal|liq̣uḍiya|baynahum:|wa-ʹinnal|laẓeena|ʹooris̤ul|Kitaaba|mim|baʻdihim|lafee|shakkim|minhu|mureeb."
42,15,"Faliẓaalika|fadʻu|wastaq̣im|kamaaa|ʹumirt.|Wa-laa|tattabiʻ|ʹahwaaaʹahum;|wa-q̣ul|ʹaamañtu|bimaaa|ʹañzala|laahu|miñ|Kitaab;|wa-ʹumirtu|liʹaʻdila|baynakum.|ʹAllaahu|Rabbunaa|wa-Rabbukum.|Lanaaa|ʹaʻmaalunaa|wa-lakum|ʹaʻmaalukum.|Laa-|ḥujjata|baynanaa|wa-baynakum.|ʹAllaahu|yajmaʻu|baynanaa,|wa-ʹilayhil|maṣeer."
42,16,"Wallaẓeena|yuḥaaajjoona|fil|laahi|mim|baʻdi|mas|tujeeba|lahoo|ḥujjatuhum|daaḥiḍatun|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|wa-ʻalayhim|g̣aḍabuñw|walahum|ʻAẓaabuñ|shadeed."
42,17,"ʹAllaahul|laẓeee|ʹañzalal|Kitaaba|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wal-Meezaan.|Wa-maa|yudreeka|laʻallas|Saaʻata|q̣areeb?"
42,18,"Yastaʻjilu|bihal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bihaa:|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|mushfiq̣oona|minhaa|wa-yaʻlamoona|ʹannahal|Ḥaq̣q̣.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnal|laẓeena|yumaaroona|fis|Saaʻati|lafee|ḍalaalim|baʻeed."
42,19,"ʹAllaahu|Laṭeefum|biʻibaadihee|yarzuq̣u|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-Huwal|Q̣awiyyul|ʻAzeez."
42,20,"Mañ|kaana|yureedu|ḥars̤al|ʹAakhirati|nazid|lahoo|fee|ḥars̤ih;|wa-mañ|kaana|yureedu|ḥars̤ad|dunyaa|nuʹtihee|minhaa|wa-maa|lahoo|fil|ʹAakhirati|min|naṣeeb."
42,21,"ʹAm|lahum|shurakaaaʹu|sharaʻoo|lahum|minad|Deeni|maa-|lam|yaʹẓam|bihil|laah?|Wa-lawlaa|Kalimatul|Faṣli|laq̣uḍiya|baynahum.|Wa-ʹinnaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|lahum|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem."
42,22,"Taraz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|mushfiq̣eena|mimmaa|kasaboo|wa-huwa|waaq̣iʻum|bihim.|Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|fee|rawḍaatil|Jannaat:|lahum|maa|yashaaaʹoona|ʻiñda|Rabbihim.|Ẓaalika|huwal|Faḍlul|Kabeer."
42,23,"Ẓaalikal|laẓee|yubashshirul|laahu|ʻIbaadahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaat.|Q̣ul|laaa|ʹasʹalukum|ʻalayhi|ʹajran|ʹillal|mawaddata|fil|q̣urbaa.|Wa-mañy|yaq̣tarif|ḥasanatan|nazid|lahoo|feehaa|ḥusnaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afooruñ|Shakoor."
42,24,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloonaf|taraa|ʻalal|laahi|kaẓibaa?|Faʹiñy|yasha|ʹillaahu|yakhtim|ʻalaa|q̣albik.|Wa-yamḥul|laahul|Baaṭila|wa-yuḥiq̣q̣ul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|bi-Kalimaatih.|ʹInnahoo|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
42,25,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|yaq̣balut|Tawbata|ʻan|ʻIbaadihee|wa-yaʻfoo|ʻanis|sayyiʹaati|wayaʻlamu|maa-|tafʻaloon."
42,26,"Wa-yastajeebul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-yazeeduhum|miñ|faḍlih:|wal-kaafiroona|lahum|ʻAẓaabuñ|shadeed."
42,27,"Wa-law|basaṭal|laahur|Rizq̣a|liʻIbaadihee|labag̣aw|fil|ʹarḍi|walaakiñy|yunazzilu|biq̣adarim|maa|yashaaaʹ.|ʹInnahoo|biʻIbaadihee|Khabeerum|Baṣeer."
42,28,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|yunazzilul|g̣ays̤a|mim|baʻdi|maa-|q̣anaṭoo|wa-yañshuru|Raḥmatah.|Wa-Huwal|Waliyyul|Ḥameed."
42,29,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatihee|khalq̣us|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|bas̤s̤a|feehimaa|miñ|daaabbah:|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|jamʻihim|ʹiẓaa|yashaaaʹu|Q̣adeer."
42,30,"Wa-maaa|ʹaṣaabakum|mim|muṣeebatiñ|fabimaa|kasabat|ʹaydeekum|wa-yaʻfoo|ʻañ|kas̤eer."
42,31,"Wa-maaa|ʹañtum̃|bimuʻjizeena|fil|ʹarḍi|lakum|wa-maa|miñ|doonil|laahi|miñw|waliyyiñw|naṣeer.|wa-laa"
42,32,"Wa-min|ʹAayaatihil|jawaari|fil|baḥri|kal-ʹaʻlaam."
42,33,"ʹIñy|yashaʹ|yuskinir|reeḥa|fayaz̤̣lalna|rawaakida|ʻalaa|z̤̣ahrih.|ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|likulli|ṣabbariñ|shakoor."
42,34,"ʹAw|yoobiq̣hunna|bimaa|kasaboo|wa-yaʻfu|ʻañ|kas̤eer."
42,35,"Wa-yaʻlamal|laẓeena|yujaadiloona|feee|Aayaatinaa,|maa-ʹ|lahum|mim|maḥeeṣ."
42,36,"Famaaa|ʹooteetum|miñ|shayʹiñ|famataaʻul|ḥayaatid|dunyaa:|wa-maa|ʻiñdal|laahi|khayruñw|waʹabq̣aa|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻalaa|Rabbihim|yatawakkaloon;"
42,37,"Wallaẓeena|yajtaniboona|kabaaaʹiral|ʹis̤mi|wal-fawaaḥisha|waʹiẓaa|maa-|g̣aḍiboo|hum|yag̣firoon;"
42,38,"Wallaẓeenas|tajaaboo|li-Rabbihim|wa-ʹaq̣aamuṣ|Ṣalaah;|wa-ʹamruhum|SHOORAA|baynahum;|wa-mimmaa|razaq̣naahum|yuñfiq̣oon;"
42,39,"Wallaẓeena|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaṣaabahumul|bag̣yu|hum|yañtaṣiroon."
42,40,"Wa-jazaaaʹu|sayyiʹatiñ|sayyiʹatum|mis̤luhaa:|faman|ʻafaa|wa-ʹaṣlaḥa|faʹajruhoo|ʻalal|laah:|ʹinnahoo|laa-|yuḥibbuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
42,41,"Wa-lamaniñ|taṣara|baʻda|z̤̣ulmihee|faʹulaaaʹika|maa-|ʻalayhim|miñ|sabeel."
42,42,"ʹInnamas|sabeelu|ʻalal|laẓeena|yaz̤̣limoonan|naasa|wa-yabg̣oona|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣:|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem."
42,43,"Wa-lamañ|ṣabara|wa-g̣afara|ʹinna|ẓaalika|lamin|ʻazmil|ʹumoor."
42,44,"Wa-mañy|yuḍli|lillaahu|famaa|lahoo|miñw|waliyyim|mim|baʻdih.|Wa-taraz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|lammaa|raʹawul|ʻaẓaaba|yaq̣ooloona|hal|ʹilaa|maraddim|miñ|sabeel?"
42,45,"Wa-taraahum|yaʻraḍoona|ʻalayhaa|khaashiʻeena|minaẓ|ẓulli|yañz̤̣uroona|miñ|ṭarfin|khafiyy.|Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹinnal|khaasireenal|laẓeena|khasirooo|ʹañfusahum|wa-ʹahleehim|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|fee|ʻAẓaabim|muq̣eem!"
42,46,"Wa-maa|kaana|lahum|min|ʹawliyaaaʹa|yañṣuroonahum|miñ|doonil|laah.|Wa-mañy|yuḍlilil|laahu|famaa|lahoo|miñ|sabeel."
42,47,"ʹIstajeeboo|li-Rabbikum|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|Yawmul|laa|maradda|lahoo|min|allaah.|maa-|lakum|mim|maljaʹiñy|Yawmaʹiẓiñw|Wa-Maa|lakum|min|nakeer."
42,48,"Faʹin|ʹaʻraḍoo|famaaa|ʹarsalnaaka|ʻalayhim|ḥafeez̤̣aa.|ʹIn|ʻalayka|ʹillal|balaag̣.|Wa-ʹinnaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaẓaq̣nal|ʹiñsaana|minnaa|Raḥmatañ|fariḥa|bihaa:|wa-ʹiñ|tuṣibhum|sayyiʹatum|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeehim|faʹinnal|ʹiñsaana|kafoor!"
42,49,"Lillaahi|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Yakhluq̣u|maa-|yashaaaʹ.|Yahabu|limañy|yashaaaʹu|ʹinaas̤añw|wa-yahabu|limañy|yashaaaʹuẓ|ẓukoor,"
42,50,"ʹAw|yuzawwijuhum|ẓukraanañw|waʹinaas̤aa;|wa-yajʻalu|mañy|yashaaaʹu|ʻaq̣eemaa:|ʹinnahoo|ʻAleemuñ|Q̣adeer."
42,51,"Wa-maa|kaana|libasharin|ʹañy|yukallimahul|laahu|ʹillaa|Waḥyan|ʹaw|miñw|waraaaʹi|ḥijaabin|ʹaw|yursila|rasoolañ|fayooḥiya|biʹiẓnihee|maa-|yashaaaʹ:|ʹinnahoo|ʻAliyyun|Ḥakeem."
42,52,"Wa-kaẓaalika|ʹawḥaynaaa|ʹilayka|Rooḥam|min|ʹamrinaa:|maa-|kuñta|tadree|mal|kitaabu|wa-lal|ʹeemaanu|wa-laakiñ|jaʻalnaahu|Nooran|nahdee|bihee|man|nashaaaʹu|min|ʻIbaadinaa:|wa-ʹinnaka|latahdeee|ʹilaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem,―"
42,53,"Ṣiraaṭil|laahil|laẓee|lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ;|ʹAlaaa|ʹilal|laahi|taṣeerul|ʹumoor."
43,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem."
43,2,"Wal-Kitaabil|Mubeen,―"
43,3,"ʹInnaa|jaʻalnaahu|Q̣urʹaanan|ʻArabiyyal|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
43,4,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|feee|ʹUmmil|Kitaabi|ladaynaa|laʻaliyyun|Ḥakeem."
43,5,"ʹA-fanaḍribu|ʻañkumuẓ|Ẓikra|ṣafḥan|ʹañ|kuñtum|q̣awmam|musrifeen?"
43,6,"Wa-kam|ʹarsalnaa|min|nabiyyiñ|fil|ʹawwaleen?"
43,7,"Wa-maa|yaʹteehim|min|nabiyyin|ʹillaa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon."
43,8,"Faʹahlaknaaa|ʹashadda|minhum̃|baṭshañw|wamaḍaa|Mas̤alul|ʹawwaleen."
43,9,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|man|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|layaq̣oolunna|khalaq̣ahunnal|ʻAzeezul|ʻAleem;―"
43,10,"ʹAllaẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹarḍa|mahdañw|wajaʻala|lakum|feehaa|subulal|laʻallakum|tahtadoon;"
43,11,"Wallaẓee|nazzala|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹam|biq̣adar;―|faʹañsharnaa|bihee|baldatam|maytaa;|kaẓaalika|tukhrajoon;―"
43,12,"Wallaẓee|khalaq̣al|ʹazwaaja|kullahaa|wa-jaʻala|lakum|minal|fulki|wal-ʹanʻaami|maa-|tarkaboon."
43,13,"Litastawoo|ʻalaa|z̤̣uhoorihee|s̤umma|taẓkuroo|niʻmata|Rabbikum|ʹiẓas|tawaytum|ʻalayhi|wa-taq̣ooloo|ʻʻSubḥaanal|laẓee|sakhkhara|lanaa|haaẓaa|wa-maa|kunnaa|lahoo|muq̣rineen."
43,14,"Wa-ʹinnaaa|ʹilaa|Rabbinaa|lamuñq̣aliboon!ʹʹ"
43,15,"Wa-jaʻaloo|lahoo|min|ʻibaadihee|juzʹaa!|ʹInnal|ʹiñsaana|lakafoorum|mubeen!"
43,16,"ʹAmit|takhaẓa|mimmaa|yakhluq̣u|banaatiñw|waʹaṣfaakum|bilbaneen?"
43,17,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|bushshira|ʹaḥaduhum̃|bimaa|ḍaraba|lir-Raḥmaani|mas̤alañ|z̤̣alla|wajhuhoo|muswaddañw|wahuwa|kaz̤̣eem!"
43,18,"ʹA-wamañy|yunashshaʹu|fil|ḥilyati|wa-huwa|fil|khiṣaami|g̣ayru|mubeen?"
43,19,"Wa-jaʻalul|malaaaʹikatal|laẓeena|hum|ʻibaadur|Raḥmaani|ʹinaas̤aa.|ʹA-shahidoo|khalq̣ahum?|Satuktabu|shahaadatuhum|wa-yusʹaloon!"
43,20,"Wa-q̣aaloo|law|shaaaʹar|Raḥmaanu|Maa-|ʻabadnaahum!|maa-|lahum̃|biẓaalika|min|ʻilm!|ʹIn|hum|ʹillaa|yakhruṣoon!"
43,21,"ʹAm|ʹaataynaahum|Kitaabam|miñ|q̣ablihee|fahum̃|bihee|mustamsikoon?"
43,22,"Bal|q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|wajadnaaa|ʹaabaaaʹanaa|ʻalaaa|ʹummatiñw|Waʹinnaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihim|muhtadoon."
43,23,"Wa-kaẓaalika|maaa|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|fee|q̣aryatim|min|Naẓeerin|ʹillaa|q̣aala|mutrafoohaaa|ʹinnaa|wajadnaaa|ʹaabaaaʹanaa|ʻalaaa|ʹummatiñw|waʹinnaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihim|muq̣tadoon."
43,24,"Q̣aala|ʹa-wa law|jiʹtukum̃|biʹahdaa|mimmaa|wajattum|ʻalayhi|ʹaabaaaʹakum?|Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|bimaaa|ʹursiltum̃|bihee|kaafiroon."
43,25,"Fañtaq̣amnaa|minhum|fañz̤̣ur|kayfa|kaana|ʻaaq̣ibatul|mukaẓẓibeen!"
43,26,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|ʹIbraaheemu|liʹabeehi|wa-q̣awmiheee|ʹinnanee|baraaaʹum|mimmaa|taʻbudoon:"
43,27,"ʹIllal|laẓee|faṭaranee|faʹinnahoo|sayahdeen."
43,28,"Wa-jaʻalahaa|Kalimatam|baaq̣iyatañ|fee|ʻaq̣ibihee|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
43,29,"Bal|mattaʻtu|haaaʹulaaaʹi|wa-ʹaabaaaʹahum|ḥattaa|jaaaʹahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|wa-Rasoolum|mubeen."
43,30,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹahumul|Ḥaq̣q̣u|q̣aaloo|haaẓaa|siḥruñw|waʹinnaa|bihee|kaafiroon."
43,31,"Waq̣aaloo|Law-laa|nuzzila|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaanu|ʻalaa|rajulim|minal|q̣aryatayni|ʻaz̤̣eem?"
43,32,"ʹAhum|yaq̣simoona|Raḥmata|Rabbik?|Naḥnu|q̣asamnaa|baynahum|maʻeeshatahum|fil|ḥayaatid|dunyaa|wa-rafaʻnaa|baʻḍahum|fawq̣a|baʻḍiñ|darajaatil|liyattakhiẓa|baʻḍuhum̃|baʻḍañ|sukhriyyaa.|Wa-Raḥmatu|Rabbika|khayrum|mimmaa|yajmaʻoon."
43,33,"Wa-lawlaaa|ʹañy|yakoonan|naasu|ʹummatañw|waaḥidatal|lajaʻalnaa|limañy|yakfuru|bir-Raḥmaani|libuyootihim|suq̣ufam|miñ|fiḍḍatiñw|wamaʻaarija|ʻalayhaa|yaz̤̣haroon,"
43,34,"Wa-li-buyootihim|ʹabwaabañw|Wasururan|ʻalayhaa|yattakiʹoon,"
43,35,"Wa-ZUKHRUFAA.|Wa-ʹiñ|kullu|ẓaalika|lammaa|mataaʻul|ḥayaatid|dunyaa:|wal-ʹAakhiratu|ʻiñda|Rabbika|lil-Muttaq̣een."
43,36,"Wa-mañy|yaʻshu|ʻañ|ẓikrir|Raḥmaani|nuq̣ayyiḍ|lahoo|shayṭaanañ|fahuwa|lahoo|q̣areen."
43,37,"Wa-ʹinnahum|layaṣuddoonahum|ʻanis|sabeeli|wa-yaḥsaboona|ʹannahum|muhtadoon!"
43,38,"Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹanaa|q̣aala|yaa-layta|baynee|wa-baynaka|buʻdal|Mashriq̣ayni|fabiʹsal|q̣areen!"
43,39,"Wa-lañy|yañfaʻakumul|yawma|ʹiz̤̣|z̤̣alamtum|ʹannakum|fil|ʻaẓaabi|mushtarikoon!"
43,40,"ʹA-faʹañta|tusmiʻuṣ|ṣumma|ʹaw|tahdil|ʻumya|wa-mañ|kaana|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen?"
43,41,"Faʹimmaa|naẓhabanna|bika|faʹinnaa|minhum|muñtaq̣imoon,"
43,42,"ʹAw|nuriyannakal|laẓee|waʻadnaahum|faʹinnaa|ʻalayhim|muq̣tadiroon."
43,43,"Fastamsik|billaẓeee|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayk:|ʹinnaka|ʻalaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
43,44,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|la-Ẓikrul|laka|wa-liq̣awmik;|wa-sawfa|tusʹaloon."
43,45,"Wasʹal|man|ʹarsalnaa|miñ|q̣ablika|mir|rusulinaaa|ʹajaʻalnaa|miñ|doonir|Raḥmaani|ʹaalihatañy|yuʻbadoon?"
43,46,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Moosaa|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|wa-malaʹihee|faq̣aala|ʹinnee|Rasoolu|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
43,47,"Falammaa|jaaaʹahum̃|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹiẓaa|hum|minhaa|yaḍḥakoon."
43,48,"Wa-maa|nureehim|min|ʹaayatin|ʹillaa|hiya|ʹakbaru|min|ʹukhtihaa,|wa-ʹakhaẓnaahum̃|bilʻaẓaabi|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
43,49,"Wa-q̣aaloo|yaaaʹayyuhas|saaḥirud|ʹu|lanaa|Rabbaka|bimaa|ʻahida|ʻiñdak;|ʹinnanaa|lamuhtadoon."
43,50,"Falammaa|kashafnaa|ʻanhumul|ʻaẓaaba|ʹiẓaa|hum|yañkus̤oon."
43,51,"Wa-naadaa|Firʻawnu|fee|q̣awmihee|q̣aala|yaa-q̣awmi|ʹalaysa|lee|mulku|Miṣra|wa-haaẓihil|ʹanhaaru|tajree|miñ|taḥtee?|ʹAfalaa|tubṣiroon?"
43,52,"ʹAm|ʹana|khayrum|min|haaẓal|laẓee|huwa|maheenuñw|walaa|yakaadu|yubeen?"
43,53,"Falawlaaa|ʹulq̣iya|ʻalayhi|ʹaswiratum|miñ|ẓahabin|ʹaw|jaaaʹa|maʻahul|malaaaʹikatu|muq̣tarineen?"
43,54,"Fastakhaffa|q̣awmahoo|faʹaṭaaʻooh:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣awmañ|faasiq̣een."
43,55,"Falammaaa|ʹaasafoonañ|taq̣amnaa|minhum|faʹag̣raq̣naahum|ʹajmaʻeen."
43,56,"Fajaʻalnaahum|Salafañw|Wa-Mas̤alal|lil-ʹaakhireen."
43,57,"Wa-lammaa|ḍuribab|nu|Maryama|mas̤alan|ʹiẓaa|q̣awmuka|minhu|yaṣiddoon!"
43,58,"Wa-q̣aalooo|ʹa-ʹaalihatunaa|khayrun|ʹam|hoo?|Maa-|ḍaraboohu|laka|ʹillaa|jadalaa:|bal|hum|q̣awmun|khaṣimoon."
43,59,"ʹIn|huwa|ʹillaa|ʻabdun|ʹanʻamnaa|ʻalayhi|wa-jaʻalnaahu|mas̤alal|li-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeel."
43,60,"Wa-law|nashaaaʹu|lajaʻalnaa|miñkum|malaaaʹikatañ|fil|ʹarḍi|yakhlufoon."
43,61,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|laʻilmul|lis-Saaʻati|falaa|tamtarunna|bihaa|wattabiʻoon:|haaẓaa|Ṣiraṭum|Mustaq̣eem."
43,62,"Wa-laa|yaṣuddannakumush|Shayṭaan:|ʹinnahoo|lakum|ʻaduwwum|mubeen."
43,63,"Wa-lammaa|jaaaʹa|ʻEesaa|bil-Bayyinaati|q̣aala|q̣ad|jiʹtukum̃|bil-Ḥikmati|wa-liʹubayyina|lakum|baʻḍal|laẓee|takhtalifoona|feeh:|fattaq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon."
43,64,"ʹInnal|laaha|Huwa|Rabbee|wa-Rabbukum|faʻbudooh:|haaẓaa|Ṣiraaṭum|Mustaq̣eem."
43,65,"Fakhtalafal|ʹaḥzaabu|mim|baynihim:|fawaylul|lil-laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|min|ʻaẓaabi|Yawmin|ʹAleem!"
43,66,"Hal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillas|Saaʻata|ʹañ|taʹtiyahum̃|bag̣tatañw|wahum|laa-|yashʻuroon?"
43,67,"ʹAlʹakhillaaaʹu|Yawmaʹizim|baʻḍuhum|libaʻḍin|ʻaduwwun|ʹillal|Muttaq̣een."
43,68,"Yaa-ʻibaadi|laa-|khawfun|ʻalaykumul|Yawma|wa-laaa|ʹañtum|taḥzanoon,―"
43,69,"ʹAllaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|biʹAayaatinaa|wa-kaanoo|Muslimeen."
43,70,"ʹUdkhulul|Jannata|ʹañtum|wa-ʹazwaajukum|tuḥbaroon."
43,71,"Yuṭaafu|ʻalayhim̃|biṣiḥaafim|miñ|ẓahabiñw|waʹakwaab:|wafeehaa|maa-|tashtaheehil|ʹañfusu|wa-talaẓẓul|ʹaʻyun:|wa-ʹañtum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
43,72,"Wa-tilkal|Jannatul|lateee|ʹooris̤tumoohaa|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
43,73,"Lakum|feeha|faakihatuñ|kas̤eeratum|minhaa|taʹkuloon."
43,74,"ʹInnal|mujrimeena|fee|ʻaẓaabi|Jahannama|khaalidoon."
43,75,"Laa-|yufattaru|ʻanhum|wa-hum|feehi|mublisoon."
43,76,"Wa-maa|z̤̣alamnaahum|wa-laakiñ|kaanoo|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
43,77,"Wa-naadaw|yaa-Maaliku|liyaq̣ḍi|ʻalaynaa|Rabbuk!|Q̣aala|ʹinnakum|maakis̤oon."
43,78,"Laq̣ad|jiʹnaakum̃|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arakum|lil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|kaarihoon."
43,79,"ʹAm|ʹabramooo|ʹamrañ|faʹinnaa|mubrimoon."
43,80,"ʹAm|yaḥsaboona|ʹannaa|laa-|nasmaʻu|sirrahum|wa-najwaahum?|Balaa|wa-Rusulunaa|ladayhim|yaktuboon."
43,81,"Q̣ul|ʹiñ|kaana|lir-Raḥmaani|waladuñ|faʹana|ʹawwalul|ʻaabideen."
43,82,"Subḥaana|Rabbis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|Rabbil|ʻArshi|ʻammaa|yaṣifoon!"
43,83,"Faẓarhum|yakhooḍoo|wa-yalʻaboo|ḥattaa|yulaaq̣oo|Yawmahumul|laẓee|yooʻadoon."
43,84,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|fis|samaaaʹi|ʹIlaahuñw|Wafil|ʹarḍi|ʹIlaah;|wa-Huwal|Ḥakeemul|ʻAleem."
43,85,"Wa-tabaarakal|laẓee|lahoo|mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa:|wa-ʻiñdahoo|ʻilmus|Saaʻah:|wa-ʹilayhi|turjaʻoon."
43,86,"Wa-laa|yamlikul|laẓeena|yadʻoona|miñ|doonihish|Shafaaʻata|ʹillaa|mañ|shahida|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon."
43,87,"Wa-laʹiñ|saʹaltahum|man|khalaq̣ahum|layaq̣oolun|nallaahu|faʹannaa|yuʹfakoon?"
43,88,"Wa-q̣eelihee|yaa-Rabbi|ʹinna|haaaʹulaaaʹi|q̣awmul|laa|yuʹminoon!"
43,89,"Faṣfaḥ|ʻanhum|wa-q̣ul|salaam!|Fasawfa|yaʻlamoon!"
44,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem."
44,2,"Wal-Kitaabil|Mubeen."
44,3,"ʹInnaaa|ʹañzalnaahu|fee|laylatim|mubaarakatin|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|muñẓireen."
44,4,"Feehaa|yufraq̣u|kullu|ʹamrin|ḥakeem,"
44,5,"ʹAmram|min|ʻiñdinaa.|ʹInnaa|kunnaa|mursileen―"
44,6,"Raḥmatam|mir|Rabbik:|ʹinnahoo|Huwas|Sameeʻul|ʻAleem;"
44,7,"Rabbis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wa-maa|baynahumaa,|Iñ|kuntum|mooq̣ineen."
44,8,"Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Huwa|yuḥyee|wa-yumeet:―|Rabbukum|wa-Rabbu|ʹaabaaaʹikumul|ʹawwaleen."
44,9,"Bal|hum|fee|shakkiñy|yalʻaboon."
44,10,"Fartaq̣ib|Yawma|taʹtis|samaaaʹu|bi-DUKHAANIM|mubeen,"
44,11,"Yag̣shan|naas:|haaẓaa|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem."
44,12,"Rabbanak|shif|ʻannal|ʻaẓaaba|ʹinnaa|Muʹminoon!"
44,13,"ʹAnnaa|lahumuẓ|Ẓikraa|wa-q̣ad|jaaaʹahum|Rasoolum|mubeen,―"
44,14,"S̤umma|tawallaw|ʻanhu|wa-q̣aaloo|muʻallamum|majnoon."
44,15,"ʹInnaa|kaashiful|ʻaẓaabi|q̣aleelan|ʹinnakum|ʻaaaʹidoon."
44,16,"Yawma|nabṭishul|baṭshatal|kubraa:|ʹinnaa|muñtaq̣imoon!"
44,17,"Wa-laq̣ad|fatannaa|q̣ablahum|q̣awma|Firʻawna|wa-jaaaʹahum|Rasooluñ|Kareem,"
44,18,"ʹAn|ʹaddooo|ʹilayya|ʻibaadal|laah:|ʹinnee|lakum|Rasoolun|ʹameen;"
44,19,"Wa-ʹal|laa|taʻloo|ʻalal|laah:|ʹinneee|ʹaateekum̃|bisulṭaanim|mubeen."
44,20,"Wa-ʹinnee|ʻuẓtu|bi-Rabbee|wa-Rabbikum|ʹañ|tarjumoon."
44,21,"Wa-ʹil|lam|tuʹminoo|lee|faʻtaziloon."
44,22,"Fadaʻaa|Rabbahooo|ʹanna|haaaʹulaaaʹi|q̣awmum|mujrimoon."
44,23,"Faʹasri|biʹibaadee|laylan|ʹinnakum|muttabaʻoon."
44,24,"Watrukil|baḥra|rahwaa:|ʹinnahum|juñdum|mug̣raq̣oon."
44,25,"Kam|tarakoo|miñ|jannaatiñw|waʻuyoon,"
44,26,"Wa-zurooʻiñw|Wamaq̣aamiñ|kareem,"
44,27,"Wa-naʻmatiñ|kaanoo|feehaa|faakiheen!"
44,28,"Kaẓaalik!|wa-ʹawras̤naahaa|q̣awman|ʹaakhareen!"
44,29,"Famaa|bakat|ʻalayhimus|samaaaʹu|wal-ʹarḍu|wa-maa|kaanoo|muñz̤̣areen."
44,30,"Wa-laq̣ad|najjaynaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|minal|ʻaẓaabil|muheen."
44,31,"Miñ|Firʻawn:|ʹinnahoo|kaana|ʻaaliyam|minal|musrifeen."
44,32,"Wa-laq̣adikh|tarnaahum|ʻalaa|ʻilmin|ʻalal|ʻaalameen,"
44,33,"Waʹaataynaahum|minal|ʹAayaati|maa-|feehi|balaaaʹum|mubeen."
44,34,"ʹInna|haaaʹulaaaʹi|layaq̣ooloon,"
44,35,"ʹIn|hiya|ʹillaa|mawtatunal|ʹoolaa|wa-maa|naḥnu|bimuñshareen."
44,36,"Faʹtoo|biʹaabaaaʹinaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
44,37,"ʹAhum|khayrun|ʹam|q̣awmu|Tubbaʻiñw|wallaẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim?|ʹAhlaknaahum|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|mujrimeen."
44,38,"Wa-maa|khalaq̣nas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaa|laaʻibeen."
44,39,"Maa-|khalaq̣naahumaaa|ʹillaa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
44,40,"ʹInna|Yawmal|faṣli|meeq̣aatuhum|ʹajmaʻeen.―"
44,41,"Yawma|laa-|yug̣nee|mawlan|ʻam|mawlañ|shayʹañw|walaa|hum|yuñṣaroon,"
44,42,"ʹIllaa|mar|raḥimal|laah:|ʹinnahoo|Huwal|ʻAzeezur|Raḥeem."
44,43,"ʹInna|shajarataz|Zaq̣q̣oom,"
44,44,"Ṭaʻaamul|ʹas̤eem,―"
44,45,"Kalmuhli|yag̣lee|fil|buṭoon,"
44,46,"Kag̣alyil|ḥameem."
44,47,"Khuẓoohu|faʻtiloohu|ʹilaa|sawaaaʹil|Jaḥeem!"
44,48,"S̤umma|ṣubboo|fawq̣a|raʹsihee|min|ʻAẓaabil|Ḥameem."
44,49,"Ẓuq̣!|ʹinnaka|ʹañtal|ʻazeezul|kareem!"
44,50,"ʹInna|haaẓaa|maa-|kuñtum̃|bihee|tamtaroon!"
44,51,"ʹInnal|Muttaq̣eena|fee|maq̣aamin|ʹameen,"
44,52,"Fee|Jannaatiñw|Waʻuyoon;"
44,53,"Yalbasoona|Miñ|suñdusiñw|waʹistabraq̣im|mutaq̣aabileen;"
44,54,"Kaẓaalik;|wa-zawwajnaahum̃|biḥoorin|ʻeen."
44,55,"Yadʻoona|feeha|bikulli|faakihatin|ʹaamineen;"
44,56,"Laa-|yaẓooq̣oona|feehal|Mawta|ʹillal|mawtatal|ʹoolaa;|wa-waq̣aahum|ʻaẓaabal|Jaḥeem,―"
44,57,"Faḍlam|mir|Rabbik!|Ẓaalika|huwal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
44,58,"Faʹinnamaa|yassarnaahu|bilisaanika|laʻallahum|yataẓakkaroon."
44,59,"Fartaq̣ib|ʹinnahum|murtaq̣iboon."
45,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem."
45,2,"Tañzeelul|Kitaabi|minal|laahil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥakeem."
45,3,"ʹInna|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|laʹAayaatil|lil-Muʹmineen."
45,4,"Wa-fee|khalq̣ikum|wa-maa|yabus̤s̤u|miñ|daaabbatin|ʹAayaatul|liq̣awmiñy|yooq̣inoon."
45,5,"Wakhtilaafil|Layli|wan-Nahaari|wa-maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|minas|samaaaʹi|mir|Rizq̣iñ|faʹaḥyaa|bihil|ʹarḍa|baʻda|mawtihaa|wa-taṣreefir|riyaaḥi|ʹAayaatul|liq̣awmiñy|yaʻq̣iloon."
45,6,"Tilka|ʹAayaatul|laahi|natloohaa|ʻalayka|bil-ḥaq̣q̣:|fabiʹayyi|ḥadees̤im|baʻdal|laahi|wa-ʹAayaatihee|yuʹminoon?"
45,7,"Waylul|likulli|ʹaffaakin|ʹas̤eem:"
45,8,"yasmaʻu|ʹAayaatil|laahi|tutlaa|ʻalayhi|s̤umma|yuṣirru|mustakbirañ|kaʹal|lam|yasmaʻhaa:|fabashshirhu|biʻAẓaabin|ʹaleem!"
45,9,"Wa-ʹiẓaaa|ʻalima|min|ʹAayaatinaa|shayʹanit|takhaẓahaa|huzuwaa:|ʹulaaaʹika|lahum|ʻAẓaabum|muheen."
45,10,"Miñw|Waraaaʹihim|Jahannam:|wa-laa|yug̣nee|ʻanhum|maa|kasaboo|shayʹañw|walaa|mat|takhaẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹawliyaaaʹ:|wa-lahum|ʻAẓaabun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
45,11,"Haaẓaa|Hudaa:|wal-laẓeena|kafaroo|biʹAayaati|Rabbihim|lahum|ʻAẓaabum|mir|rijzin|ʹaleem."
45,12,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|sakhkhara|lakumul|baḥra|litajriyal|fulku|feehi|biʹamrihee|wa-litabtag̣oo|miñ|Faḍlihee|wa-laʻallakum|tashkuroon."
45,13,"Wa-sakhkhara|lakum|maa|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻam|minh:|ʹinna|fee|ẓaalika|laʹAayaatil|liq̣awmiñy|yatafakkaroon."
45,14,"Q̣ul|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|yag̣firoo|lillaẓeena|laa-|yarjoona|ʹAyyaamal|laahi|liyajziya|Q̣awmam|bimaa|kaanoo|yaksiboon."
45,15,"Man|ʻamila|ṣaaliḥañ|falinafsih;|wa-man|ʹasaaaʹa|faʻalayhaa.|S̤umma|ʹilaa|Rabbikum|turjaʻoon."
45,16,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹaataynaa|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeelal|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥukma|wan-Nubuwwa|wa-razaq̣naahum|minaṭ|Ṭayyibaati|wa-faḍḍalnaahum|ʻalal|ʻaalameen."
45,17,"Wa-ʹaataynaahum̃|Bayyinaatim|minal|ʹamr:|famakh|talafooo|ʹillaa|mim|baʻdi|maa-|jaaaʹahumul|ʻilmu|bag̣yam|baynahum.|ʹInna|Rabbaka|yaq̣ḍee|baynahum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamati|feemaa|kaanoo|feehi|yakhtalifoon."
45,18,"S̤umma|jaʻalnaaka|ʻalaa|Shareeʻatim|minal|ʹamri|fattabiʻhaa|wa-laa|tattabiʻ|ʹahwaaa|ʹallaẓeena|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
45,19,"ʹInnahum|lañy|yug̣noo|ʹañka|minal|laahi|shayʹaa:|wa-ʹinnaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|baʻḍuhum|ʹawliyaaaʹu|baʻḍ:|wallaahu|Wa-liyyul|Muttaq̣een."
45,20,"Haaẓaa|Baṣaaaʹiru|linnaasi|wa-Hudañw|wa-Raḥmatul|liq̣awmiñy|yooq̣inoon."
45,21,"ʹAm|ḥasibal|laẓeenaj|taraḥus|sayyiʹaati|ʹan|najʻalahum|kallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|sawaaaʹam|maḥyaahum|wa-mamaatuhum?|Saaaʹa|maa-|yaḥkumoon."
45,22,"Wa-khalaq̣al|laahus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-litujzaa|kullu|nafsim|bimaa|kasabat|wa-hum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
45,23,"ʹAfaraʹayta|manit|takhaẓa|ʹilaahahoo|hawaahu|wa-ʹaḍal-lahul|laahu|ʻalaa|ʻilmiñw|Wakhatama|ʻalaa|samʻihee|wa-q̣albihee|wa-jaʻala|ʻalaa|baṣarihee|g̣ishaawah.|Famañy|yahdeehi|mim|baʻdil|laah?|ʹAfalaa|taẓakkaroon?"
45,24,"Wa-q̣aaloo|maa-|hiya|ʹillaa|ḥayaatunad|dunyaa|namootu|wa-naḥyaa|wa-maa|yuhlikunaaa|ʹillad|Dahr.|Wa-maa|lahum̃|biẓaalika|min|ʻilm:|ʹin|hum|ʹillaa|yaz̤̣unnoon."
45,25,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|Bayyinaatim|maa|kaana|ḥujjatuhum|ʹillaaa|ʹañ|q̣aaluʹ|too|biʹaabaaaʹinaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
45,26,"Q̣ulil|laahu|yaḥyeekum|s̤umma|yumeetukum|s̤umma|yajmaʻukum|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|laa-|rayba|feehi|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤aran|naasi|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
45,27,"Wa-lillaahi|Mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Wa-Yawma|taq̣oomus|Saaʻatu|Yawmaʹiẓiñy|yakhsarul|mubṭiloon!"
45,28,"Wa-taraa|kulla|ʹummatiñ|JAAS̤IYAH:|Kullu|ʹummatiñ|tudʻaaa|ʹilaa|Kitaabihaa;|ʹal-Yawma|tujzawna|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon!"
45,29,"Haaẓaa|Kitaabunaa|yañṭiq̣u|ʻalaykum̃|bilḥaq̣q̣;|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|nastañsikhu|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
45,30,"Faʹammal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|fayudkhiluhum|Rabbuhum|fee|Raḥmatih.|Ẓaalika|huwal|Fawzul|mubeen."
45,31,"Wa-ʹammal|laẓeena|kafaroo:|ʹafalam|takun|ʹAayaatee|tutlaa|ʻalaykum|fastakbartum|wa-kuñtum|q̣awmam|mujrimeen?"
45,32,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|ʹinna|waʻdallaahi|ḥaq̣q̣uñw|was|Saaʻatu|laa-|rayba|feehaa|q̣ultum|maa|nadree|mas|Saaʻatu|ʹin|naz̤̣unnu|ʹillaa|z̤̣annañw|wamaa|naḥnu|bimustayq̣ineen."
45,33,"Wa-badaa|lahum|sayyiʹaatu|maa-|ʻamiloo|wa-ḥaaq̣a|bihim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon!"
45,34,"Wa-q̣eelal|Yawma|nañsaakum|kamaa|naseetum|Liq̣aaaʹa|Yawmikum|haaẓaa|wa-maʹwaakumun|Naaru|wa-maa|lakum|min|naaṣireen!"
45,35,"Ẓaalikum̃|biʹannakumut|takhaẓtum|ʹAayaatil|laahi|huzuwañw|wag̣arratkumul|ḥayaatud|dunyaa:|fal-Yawma|laa-|yukhrajoona|minhaa|wa-laa|hum|yustaʻtaboon."
45,36,"Falillaahil|Ḥamdu|Rabbis|samaawaati|wa-Rabbil|ʹarḍi|Rabbil|ʻAalameen!"
45,37,"Wa-lahul|Kibriyaaaʹu|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem!"
46,1,"Ḥaa-Meeem."
46,2,"Tañzeelul|Kitaabi|minal|laahil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥakeem."
46,3,"Maa-|khalaq̣nas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaaa|ʹillaa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹajalim|musammaa:|wallaẓeena|kafaroo|ʻammaaa|ʹuñẓiroo|muʻriḍoon."
46,4,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|maa|tadʻoona|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹaroonee|maaẓaa|khalaq̣oo|minal|ʹarḍi|ʹam|lahum|shirkuñ|fis|samaawaat?|ʹEetoonee|bi-Kitaabim|miñ|q̣abli|haaẓaaa|ʹaw|ʹas̤aaratim|min|ʻilmin|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
46,5,"Wa-man|ʹaḍallu|mimmañy|yadʻoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|mal|laa|yastajeebu|lahooo|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|wa-hum|ʻañ|duʻaaaʹihim|g̣aafiloon?"
46,6,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|ḥushiran|naasu|kaanoo|lahum|ʹaʻdaaaʹañw|Wakaanoo|biʻibaadatihim|kaafireen!"
46,7,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatunaa|Bayyinaatiñ|q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|lammaa|jaaaʹahum|haaẓaa|siḥrum|mubeen!"
46,8,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloonaf|taraah?|Q̣ul|ʹinif|taraytuhoo|falaa|tamlikoona|lee|minal|laahi|shayʹaa.|Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|tufeeḍoona|feeh!|Kafaa|bihee|Shaheedam|baynee|wa-baynakum!|Wa-Huwal|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
46,9,"Q̣ul|maa-|kuñtu|bidʻam|minar|rusuli|wa-maaa|ʹadree|maa-|yufʻalu|bee|wa-laa|bikum.|ʹIn|ʹattabiʻu|ʹillaa|maa-|yooḥaaa|ʹilayya|wa-maaa|ʹana|ʹillaa|Naẓeerum|mubeen."
46,10,"Q̣ul|ʹaraaytum|ʹiñ|kaana|min|ʻiñdil|laahi|wa-kafartum̃|bihee|wa-shahida|shaahidum|mim|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʻalaa|mis̤lihee|faʹaamana|wastakbartum?|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
46,11,"Wa-q̣aalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|law|kaana|khayram|maa|sabaq̣oonaaa|ʹilayh!|Wa-ʹiẓ|lam|yahtadoo|bihee|fasayaq̣ooloona|haaẓaaa|ʹifkuñ|q̣adeem!"
46,12,"Wa-miñ|q̣ablihee|Kitaabu|Moosaaa|ʹimaamañw|Waraḥmah:|wa-haaẓaa|Kitaabum|muṣaddiq̣ul|lisaanan|ʻArabiyyal|liyuñẓiral|laẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|wa-Bushraa|lil-Muḥsineen."
46,13,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|q̣aaloo|Rabbunal|laahu|s̤ummas|taq̣aamoo|falaa|khawfun|ʻalayhim|wa-laa|hum|yaḥzanoon."
46,14,"ʹUlaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannati|khaalideena|feehaa:|jazaaaʹam|bimaa|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
46,15,"Wa-waṣṣaynal|ʹiñsaana|biwaalidayhi|ʹiḥsaanaa:|ḥamalathu|ʹummuhoo|kurhañw|wawaḍaʻathu|kurhaa.|Wa-ḥamluhoo|wa-fiṣaaluhoo|s̤alaas̤oona|shahraa.|Ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|balag̣a|ʹashuddahoo|wa-balag̣a|ʹarbaʻeena|sanatañ|q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹawziʻneee|ʹan|ʹashkura|niʻmatakal|lateee|ʹanʻamta|ʻalayya|wa-ʻalaa|waalidayya|wa-ʹan|ʹaʻmala|ṣaaliḥañ|tarḍaahu|wa-ʹaṣliḥ|lee|fee|ẓurriyyatee.|ʹInnee|tubtu|ʹilayka|wa-ʹinnee|minal|Muslimeen."
46,16,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|nataq̣abbalu|ʻanhum|ʹaḥsana|maa-|ʻamiloo|wa-natajaawazu|ʻañ|sayyiʹaatihim|feee|ʹaṣḥaabil|Jannah:|waʻdaṣ|ṣidq̣il|laẓee|kaanoo|yooʻadoon."
46,17,"Wallaẓee|q̣aala|liwaalidayhi|ʹuffil|lakumaaa|ʹataʻidaanineee|ʹan|ʹukhraja|wa-q̣ad|khalatil|q̣uroonu|miñ|q̣ablee?|Wa-humaa|yastag̣ees̤aanil|laaha|waylaka|ʹaamin!|ʹInna|waʻdal|laahi|ḥaq̣q̣.|Fayaq̣oolu|maa-|haaẓaaa|ʹillaaa|ʹasaaṭeerul|ʹawwaleen!"
46,18,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ḥaq̣q̣a|ʻalayhimul|Q̣awlu|feee|ʹumamiñ|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablihim|minal|jinni|wal-ʹiñs:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|khaasireen."
46,19,"Wa-likulliñ|darajaatum|mimmaa|ʻamiloo,|wa-liyuwaf-fiyahum|ʹaʻmaalahum|Wahum|laa-|yuz̤̣lamoon."
46,20,"Wa-Yawma|yuʻraḍul|laẓeena|kafaroo|ʻalan|Naar.|ʹAẓhabtum|ṭayyibaatikum|fee|ḥayaatikumud|dunyaa|wastamtaʻtum̃|bihaa:|fal-Yawma|tujzawna|ʻaẓaabal|hooni|bimaa|kuñtum|tastakbiroona|fil|ʹarḍi|big̣ayril|ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-bimaa|kuñtum|tafsuq̣oon."
46,21,"Waẓkur|ʹAkhaa|ʻAad:|ʹIẓ|ʹañẓara|q̣awmahoo|bil-ʹAḤQ̣AAFI|wa-q̣ad|khalatin|nuẓuru|mim|bayni|yadayhi|wa-min|khalfiheee|ʹallaa|taʻbudooo|ʹillal|laah:|ʹinneee|ʹakhaafu|ʻalaykum|ʻaẓaaba|Yawmin|ʻaz̤̣eem."
46,22,"Q̣aalooo|ʹajiʹtanaa|litaʹfikanaa|ʻan|ʹaalihatinaa?|Faʹtinaa|bimaa|taʻidunaaa|ʹiñ|kuñta|minaṣ|ṣaadiq̣een!"
46,23,"Q̣aala|ʹinnamal|ʻilmu|ʻiñdal|laah:|wa-ʹuballig̣ukum|maaa|ʹursiltu|bihee|wa-laakinneee|ʹaraakum|q̣awmañ|tajhaloon!"
46,24,"falammaa|raʹawhu|ʻaariḍam|mustaq̣bila|ʹawdiyatihim|q̣aaloo|haaẓaa|ʻaariḍum|mumṭirunaa!|Bal|huwa|mas|taʻjaltum̃|bih!|reeḥuñ|feehaa|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem!"
46,25,"Tudammiru|kulla|shayʹim|biʹamri|Rabbihaa|faʹaṣbaḥoo|laa-|yuraaa|ʹillaa|masaakinuhum!|Kaẓaalika|najzil|q̣awmal|mujrimeen!"
46,26,"Wa-laq̣ad|makkannaahum|feemaaa|ʹim|makkannaakum|feehi|wa-jaʻalnaa|lahum|samʻañw|waʹabṣaarañw|waʹafʹidah:|famaaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻanhum|samʻuhum|wa-laaa|ʹabṣaaruhum|wa-laaa|ʹafʹidatuhum|miñ|shayʹin|ʹiẓ|kaanoo|yajḥadoona|biʹAayaatil|laahi|wa-ḥaaq̣a|bihim|maa|kaanoo|bihee|yastahziʹoon!"
46,27,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹahlaknaa|maa-|ḥawlakum|minal|q̣uraa|wa-ṣarrafnal|ʹAayaati|laʻallahum|yarjiʻoon."
46,28,"Falawlaa|naṣarahumul|laẓeenat|takhaẓoo|miñ|doonil|laahi|q̣urbaanan|ʹaalihah?|Bal|ḍalloo|ʻanhum:|wa-ẓaalika|ʹifkuhum|wa-maa|kaanoo|yaftaroon."
46,29,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ṣarafnaaa|ʹilayka|nafaram|minal|Jinni|yastamiʻoonal|Q̣urʹaan.|Falammaa|ḥaḍaroohu|q̣aalooo|ʹañṣitoo!|Falammaa|q̣uḍiya|wallaw|ʹilaa|q̣awmihim|muñẓireen."
46,30,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-q̣awmanaaa|ʹinnaa|samiʻnaa|Kitaaban|ʹuñzila|mim|baʻdi|Moosaa|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayhi|yahdeee|ʹilal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ʹilaa|Ṭareeq̣im|Mustaq̣eem."
46,31,"Yaa-q̣awmanaaa|ʹajeeboo|Daaʻiyal|laahi|wa-ʹaaminoo|bihee|yag̣fir|lakum|miñ|ẓunoobikum|wa-yujirkum|min|ʻAẓaabin|ʹaleem."
46,32,"Wa-mal|laa|yujib|Daaʻiyal|laahi|falaysa|bimuʻjiziñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laysa|lahoo|miñ|dooniheee|ʹawliyaaaʹ:|ʹulaaaʹika|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
46,33,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹannal|laahal|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-lam|yaʻya|bikhalq̣ihinna|biq̣aadirin|ʻalaaa|ʹañy|yuḥyiyal|mawtaa?|Balaaa|ʹinnahoo|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
46,34,"Wa-Yawma|yuʻraḍul|laẓeena|kafaroo|ʻalan|Naar;|ʹalaysa|haaẓaa|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣?|Q̣aaloo|balaa|wa-Rabbinaa!|Q̣aala|faẓooq̣ul|ʻaẓaaba|bimaa|kuñtum|takfuroon!"
46,35,"Faṣbir|kamaa|ṣabara|ʹulul|ʻazmi|minar|rusuli|wa-laa|tastaʻjil|lahum.|Kaʹannahum|Yawma|yarawna|maa-|yooʻadoona|lam|yalbas̤ooo|ʹillaa|saaʻatam|min|nahaar.|Balaag̣uñ|fahal|yuhlaku|ʹillal|q̣awmul|faasiq̣oon."
47,1,"ʹAllaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-ṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|ʹaḍalla|ʹaʻmaalahum."
47,2,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|wa-ʹaamanoo|bimaa|nuzzila|ʻalaa|MUḤAMMADIÑ-W|Wahuwal|Ḥaq̣q̣u|mir|Rabbihim|kaffara|ʻanhum|sayyiʹaatihim|wa-ʹaṣlaḥa|baalahum."
47,3,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laẓeena|kafarut|tabaʻul|baaṭila|wa-ʹannal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|tabaʻul|Ḥaq̣q̣a|mir|Rabbihim:|kaẓaalika|yaḍribul|laahu|linnaasi|ʹams̤aalahum."
47,4,"Faʹiẓaa|laq̣eetumul|laẓeena|kafaroo|faḍarbar|riq̣aab;|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaaa|ʹas̤khañtumoohum|fashuddul|was̤aaq̣a|faʹimmaa|mannam|baʻdu|wa-ʹimmaa|fidaaaʹan|ḥattaa|taḍaʻal|ḥarbu|ʹawzaarahaa.|Ẓaalika|wa-law|yashaaaʹul|laahu|lañtaṣara|minhum|wa-laakil|liyabluwa|baʻḍakum̃|bibaʻḍ.|Wallaẓeena|q̣utiloo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|falañy|yuḍilla|ʹaʻmaalahum."
47,5,"Sayahdeehim|wa-yuṣliḥu|baalahum,―"
47,6,"Wayudkhiluhumul|Jannata|ʻarrafahaa|lahum."
47,7,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiñ|tañṣurul|laaha|yañṣurkum|wa-yus̤abbit|ʹaq̣daamakum."
47,8,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|fataʻsal|lahum|wa-ʹaḍalla|ʹaʻmaalahum."
47,9,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|karihoo|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|faʹaḥbaṭa|ʹaʻmaalahum."
47,10,"ʹAfalam|yaseeroo|fil|ʹarḍi|fayañz̤̣uroo|kayfa|kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatul|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim?|Dammaral|laahu|ʻalayhim,|wa-lilkaafireena|ʹams̤aaluhaa."
47,11,"Ẓaalika|biʹannal|laaha|Mawlal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|waʹannal|kaafireena|laa-|mawlaa|lahum."
47,12,"ʹInnal|laaha|yudkhilul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaar;|wallaẓeena|kafaroo|yatamattaʻoona|wa-yaʹkuloona|kamaa|taʹkulul|ʹanʻaamu|wan-Naaru|mas̤wal|lahum."
47,13,"Wa-kaʹayyim|miñ|q̣aryatin|hiya|ʹashaddu|q̣uwwatam|miñ|q̣aryatikal|lateee|ʹakhrajatka:|ʹAhlaknaahum|falaa|naaṣira|lahum."
47,14,"ʹAfamañ|kaana|ʻalaa|Bayyinatim|mir|Rabbihee|kamañ|zuyyina|lahoo|soooʹu|ʻamalihee|wattabaʻooo|ʹahwaaaʹahum?"
47,15,"Mas̤alul|Jannatil|latee|wuʻidal|Muttaq̣oon:|feehaaa|ʹanhaarum|mim|maaaʹin|g̣ayri|ʹaasin;|wa-ʹanhaarum|mil|labanil|lam|yatag̣ayyar|ṭaʻmuh;|wa-ʹanhaarum|min|khamril|laẓẓatil|lishshaaribeen;|wa-ʹanhaarum|min|ʻasalim|muṣaffaa.|Wa-lahum|feehaa|miñ|kullis̤|s̤amaraati|wa-mag̣firatum|mir|Rabbihim:|Kaman|huwa|khaaliduñ|fin|Naari|wa-suq̣oo|maaaʹan|ḥameemañ|faq̣aṭṭaʹa|ʹamʻaaaʹahum?"
47,16,"Wa-minhum|mañy|yastamiʻu|ʹilayka|ḥattaaa|ʹiẓaa|kharajoo|min|ʻiñdika|q̣aaloo|lil-laẓeena|ʹootul|ʻIlma|maaẓaa|q̣aala|ʹaanifaa?|ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|ṭabaʻal|laahu|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|wattabaʻooo|ʹahwaaaʹahum."
47,17,"Wallaẓeenah|tadaw|zaadahum|hudañw|waʹataahum|taq̣waahum."
47,18,"Fahal|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹillas|Saaʻata|ʹañ|taʹtiyahum̃|bag̣tah?|Faq̣ad|jaaaʹa|ʹashraaṭuhaa.|Faʹannaa|lahum|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹathum|ẓikraahum?"
47,19,"Faʻlam|ʹannahoo|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillal|laahu|wastag̣fir|liẓambika|wa-lil-Muʹmineena|wal-Muʹminaat:|wallaahu|yaʻlamu|mutaq̣allabakum|wa-mas̤waakum."
47,20,"Wa-yaq̣oolul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|Law-laa|nuzzilat|Soorah?|Faʹiẓaaa|ʹuñzilat|Sooratum|Muḥkamatuñw|Waẓukira|feehal|q̣itaalu|raʹaytal|laẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍuñy|yañz̤̣uroona|ʹilayka|naz̤̣aral|mag̣shiyyi|ʻalayhi|minal|mawt.|Faʹawlaa|lahum!"
47,21,"Ṭaaʻatuñw|Waq̣awlum|maʻroof.|Faʹiẓaa|ʻazamal|ʹamr.|Falaw|ṣadaq̣ul|laaha|lakaana|khayral|lahum."
47,22,"Fahal|ʻasaytum|ʹiñ|tawallaytum|ʹañ|tufsidoo|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-tuq̣aṭṭiʻooo|ʹarḥaamakum?"
47,23,"ʹUlaaaʹikal|laẓeena|laʻanahumul|laahu|faʹaṣammahum|wa-ʹaʻmaaa|ʹabṣaarahum."
47,24,"ʹAfalaa|yatadabbaroonal|Q̣ur-ʹaana|ʹam|ʻalaa|q̣uloobin|ʹaq̣faaluhaa?"
47,25,"ʹInnal|laẓeenar|taddoo|ʻalaaa|ʹadbaarihim|mim|baʻdi|maa-|tabayyana|lahumul|Hudash|Shayṭaanu|sawwala|lahum,|wa-ʹamlaa|lahum."
47,26,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣aaloo|lillaẓeena|karihoo|maa-|nazzalal|laahu|sanuṭeeʻukum|fee|baʻḍil|ʹamr;|wallaahu|yaʻlamu|ʹisraarahum."
47,27,"Fakayfa|ʹizaa|tawaffathumul|malaaaʹikatu|yaḍriboona|wujoohahum|wa-ʹadbaa-rahum?"
47,28,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahumut|tabaʻoo|maaa|ʹaskhaṭal|laaha|wa-karihoo|riḍwaanahoo|faʹaḥbaṭa|ʹaʻmaalahum."
47,29,"ʹAm|ḥasibal|laẓeena|fee|q̣uloobihim|maraḍun|ʹal|lañy|yukhrijal|laahu|ʹaḍg̣aanahum?"
47,30,"Wa-law|nashaaaʹu|laʹaraynaakahum|falaʻaraftahum̃|biseemaahum:|wa-lataʻrifan-nahum|fee|laḥnil|q̣awl!|Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|ʹaʻmaalakum."
47,31,"Wa-lanabluwannakum|ḥattaa|naʻlamal|mujaahideena|miñkum|waṣṣaabireena|wa-nabluwa|ʹakhbaarakum."
47,32,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-ṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-shaaaq̣q̣ur|Rasoola|mim|baʻdi|maa-|tabayyana|lahumul|Hudaa|lañy|yaḍurrul|laaha|shayʹaa:|wa-sa-yuḥbiṭu|ʹaʻmaalahum."
47,33,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻur|Rasoola|wa-laa|tubṭilooo|ʹaʻmaalakum!"
47,34,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-ṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|s̤umma|maatoo|wa-hum|kuffaaruñ|falañy|yag̣firal|laahu|lahum."
47,35,"Falaa|tahinoo|wa-tadʻooo|ʹilas|salmi|wa-ʹañtumul|ʹaʻlawna|wallaahu|maʻakum|wa-lañy|yatirakum|ʹaʻmaalakum."
47,36,"ʹInnamal|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|laʻibuñw|walahw:|wa-ʹiñ|tuʹminoo|wa-tattaq̣oo|yuʹtikum|ʹujoorakum|wa-laa|yasʹalkum|ʹamwaalakum."
47,37,"ʹIñy|yasʹalkumoohaa|fayuḥfikum|tabkhaloo|wa-yukhrij|ʹaḍg̣aanakum."
47,38,"Haaaʹañtum|haaaʹulaaaʹi|tudʻawna|lituñfiq̣oo|fee|Sabeelil|laah:|famiñkum|mañy|yabkhal|Wa-mañy|yabkhal|faʹinnamaa|yabkhalu|ʻan|nafsih.|Wallaahul|G̣aniyyu|wa-ʹañtumul|Fuq̣araaaʹ.|Wa-ʹiñ|tatawallaw|yastabdil|q̣awman|g̣ayrakum|s̤umma|laa-|yakoonooo|ʹams̤aalakum!"
48,1,"ʹInnaa|fataḥnaa|laka|Fatḥam|Mubeenaa,"
48,2,"Liyag̣fira|lakal|laahu|maa-|taq̣addama|miñ|ẓambika|wa-maa|taʹakhkhara|wa-yutimma|niʻmatahoo|ʻalayka|wa-yahdiyaka|Ṣiraaṭam|Mustaq̣eemaa,"
48,3,"Wa-yañṣurakal|laahu|Naṣran|ʻAzeezaa."
48,4,"Huwal|laẓee|ʹañzalas|Sakeenata|fee|q̣uloobil|Muʹmineena|liyazdaadooo|ʹeemaanam|maʻa|ʹeemaanihim:|wa-lillaahi|Junoodus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ;|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAleeman|Ḥakeemaa,"
48,5,"Liyudkhilal|Muʹmineena|wal-Muʹminaati|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa|wa-yukaffira|ʻanhum|sayyiʹaatihim;―|wakaana|ẓaalika|ʻiñdal|laahi|fawzan|ʻaz̤̣eemaa,―"
48,6,"Wa-yuʻaẓẓibal|Munaafiq̣eena|wal-Munaafiq̣aati|wal-Mushrikeena|wal-Mushrikaatiz̤̣|z̤̣aaanneena|billaahi|z̤̣annas|sawʹ.|ʻAlayhim|daaaʹiratus|sawʹ:|wa-g̣aḍibal|laahu|ʻalayhim|wa-laʻanahum|wa-ʹaʻadda|lahum|Jahannam;|wa-saaaʹat|maṣeeraa."
48,7,"Wa-lillaahi|Junoodus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAzeezan|Ḥakeemaa."
48,8,"ʹInnaaa|ʹarsalnaaka|Shaahidañw|Wa-Mubashshirañw|Wa-Naẓeeraa:"
48,9,"Lituʹminoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-tuʹazziroohu|wa-tuwaq̣q̣irooh,|wa-tusabbiḥoohu|bukratañw|waʹaṣeelaa."
48,10,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yubaayiʻoonaka|ʹinnamaa|yubaayiʻoonal|laah:|Yadul|laahi|fawq̣a|ʹaydeehim:|faman|nakas̤a|faʹinnamaa|yañkus̤u|ʻalaa|nafsih;|wa-man|ʹawfaa|bimaa|ʻaahada|ʻalayhul|laaha|fasayuʹteehi|ʹajran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
48,11,"Sayaq̣oolu|lakal|mukhal-lafoona|minal|ʹAʻraabi|shag̣alatnaaa|ʹamwaalunaa|wa-ʹahloonaa|fastag̣fir|lanaa.|Yaq̣ooloona|biʹalsinatihim|maa|laysa|fee|q̣uloobihim.|Q̣ul|famañy|yamliku|lakum|minal|laahi|shayʹan|ʹin|ʹaraada|bikum|ḍarran|ʹaw|ʹaraada|bikum|nafʻaa?|Bal|kaanal|laahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|khabeeraa."
48,12,"Bal|z̤̣anañtum|ʹal|lañy|yañq̣alibar|Rasoolu|wal-Muʹminoona|ʹilaaa|ʹahleehim|ʹabadañw|wa-zuyyina|ẓaalika|fee|q̣uloobikum|wa-z̤̣anañtum|z̤̣annas|sawʹi|wa-kuñtum|q̣awmam|booraa."
48,13,"Wa-mal|lam|yuʹmim|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|faʹinnaaa|ʹaʻtadnaa|lilkaafireena|Saʻeeraa!"
48,14,"Wa-lillaahi|Mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|yag̣firu|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yuʻaẓẓibu|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wa-kaanal|laahu|G̣afoorar|Raḥeemaa."
48,15,"Sayaq̣oolul|mukhallafoona|ʹiẓañ|ṭalaq̣tum|ʹilaa|mag̣aanima|litaʹkhuẓoohaa|ẓaroonaa|nattabiʻkum:|yureedoona|ʹañy|yubaddiloo|Kalaamal|laah.|Q̣ul|lañ|tattabiʻoonaa|kaẓaalikum|q̣aalal|laahu|miñ|q̣abl:|fasayaq̣ooloona|bal|taḥsudoonanaa.|Bal|kaanoo|laa-|yafq̣ahoona|ʹillaa|q̣aleelaa."
48,16,"Q̣ul|lilmukhallafeena|minal|ʹAʻraabi|satudʻawna|ʹilaa|q̣awmin|ʹulee|baʹsiñ|shadeediñ|tuq̣aatiloonahum|ʹaw|yuslimoon.|Faʹiñ|tuṭeeʻoo|yuʹtikumul|laahu|ʹajran|ḥasanaa:|wa-ʹiñ|tatawallaw|kamaa|tawallaytum|miñ|q̣ablu|yuʻaẓẓibkum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
48,17,"Laysa|ʻalal|ʹaʻmaa|ḥarajuñw|walaa|ʻalal|ʹaʻraji|ḥarajuñw|walaa|ʻalal|mareeḍi|haraj.|Wa-mañy|yuṭiʻil|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|yudkhilhu|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaar;|wa-mañy|yatawalla|yuʻaẓẓibhu|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
48,18,"Laq̣ad|raḍiyal|laahu|ʻanil|Muʹmineena|ʹiẓ|yubaayiʻoonaka|taḥtash|Shajarati|faʻalima|maa-|q̣uloobihim|fee|faʹañzalas|Sakeenata|ʻalayhim|wa-ʹas̤aabahum|Fat-ḥañ|q̣areebaa;"
48,19,"Wa-mag̣aanima|kas̤eeratañy|yaʹkhuẓoonahaa:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻAzeezan|Ḥakeemaa."
48,20,"Waʻadakumul|laahu|mag̣aanima|kas̤eeratañ|taʹkhuẓoonahaa|faʻajjala|lakum|haaẓihee|wa-kaffa|ʹaydiyan|naasi|ʻañkum;|wa-litakoona|ʹAayatal|lil-Muʹmineena|wa-yahdiyakum|Ṣiraaṭam|Mustaq̣eemaa;"
48,21,"Wa-ʹukhraa|lam|taq̣diroo|ʻalayhaa|q̣ad|ʹaḥaaṭal|laahu|bihaa:|wa-kaanal|laahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeeraa."
48,22,"Wa-law|q̣aatalakumul|laẓeena|kafaroo|lawallawul|ʹadbaara|s̤umma|laa-|yajidoona|wa-liyyañwwa|laa-|naṣeeraa."
48,23,"Sunnatal|laahil|latee|q̣ad|khalat|miñ|q̣ablu|wa-lañ|tajida|li-Sunnatil|laahi|tabdeelaa."
48,24,"Wa-Huwal|laẓee|kaffa|ʹaydiyahum|ʻañkum|wa-ʹaydiyakum|ʻanhum|bibaṭni|Makkata|mim|baʻdi|ʹan|ʹaz̤̣farakum|ʻalayhim.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeeraa."
48,25,"Humul|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-ṣaddookum|ʻanil|Masjidil|Ḥaraami|walhadya|maʻkoofan|ʹañy|yablug̣a|maḥillah.|Wa-lawlaa|rijaalum|Muʹminoona|wa-nisaaaʹum|Muʹminaatul|lam|taʻlamoohum|ʹañ|taṭaʹoohum|fatuṣeebakum|minhum|maʻarratum|big̣ayri|ʻilm,|liyudkhilal|laahu|fee|Raḥmatihee|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Law|tazayyaloo|laʻaẓẓabnal|laẓeena|kafaroo|minhum|ʻaẓaaban|ʹaleemaa."
48,26,"ʹIẓ|jaʻalal|laẓeena|kafaroo|fee|q̣uloobihimul|ḥamiyyata|Ḥamiyyatal|Jaahiliyyati|faʹañzalal|laahu|Sakeenatahoo|ʻalaa|Rasoolihee|wa-ʻalal|Muʹmineena|wa-ʹalzamahum|kalimatat|taq̣waa|wa-kanooo|ʹaḥaq̣q̣a|bihaa|wa-ʹahlahaa.|Wa-kaanal|laahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleemaa."
48,27,"Laq̣ad|ṣadaq̣al|laahu|Rasoolahur|ruʹyaa|bilḥaq̣q̣:|latadkhulunnal|Masjidal|Ḥaraama|ʹiñ|shaaaʹal|laahu|ʹaamineena|muḥalliq̣eena|ruʹoosakum|wa-muq̣aṣṣireena|laa|takhaafoon.|Faʻalima|maa-|lam|taʻlamoo|fajaʻala|miñ|dooni|ẓaalika|fatḥañ|q̣areebaa."
48,28,"Huwal|laẓeee|ʹarsala|Rasoolahoo|bil-Hudaa|wa-Deenil|Ḥaq̣q̣i|liyuz̤̣hirahoo|ʻalad|deeni|kullih:|wa-kafaa|billaahi|Shaheedaa."
48,29,"Muḥammadur|Rasoolul|laah:|wallaẓeena|maʻahooo|ʹashiddaaaʹu|ʻalal|kuffaari|ruḥamaaaʹu|baynahum|taraahum|rukkaʻañ|sujjadañy|yabtag̣oona|faḍlam|minal|laahi|wa-Riḍwaanaa.|Seemaahum|fee|wujoohihim|min|ʹas̤aris|sujood.|Ẓaalika|mas̤aluhum|fit|Tawraati|wa-mas̤aluhum|fil|ʹIñjeel:|kazarʻin|ʹakhraja|shaṭʹahoo|faʹaazarahoo|fastag̣laz̤̣a|fastawaa|ʻalaa|sooq̣ihee|yuʻjibuz|zurraaʻa|liyag̣eez̤̣a|bihimul|kuffaar.|Waʻadal|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|minhum|Mag̣firatañw|WaʹAjran|ʻaz̤̣eemaa."
49,1,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tuq̣addimoo|bayna|yadayil|laahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wattaq̣ul|laah:|ʹInnal|laaha|Sameeʻun|ʻAleem."
49,2,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tarfaʻooo|ʹaṣwaatakum|fawq̣a|ṣawtin|Nabiyyi|wa-laa|tajharoo|lahoo|bilq̣awli|kajahri|baʻḍikum|libaʻḍin|ʹañ|taḥbaṭa|ʹaʻ-maalukum|wa-ʹañtum|laa-|tashʻuroon."
49,3,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yag̣uḍḍoona|ʹaṣwaatahum|ʻiñda|Rasoolil|laahi|ʹulaaaʹikal|laẓeenam|ta-ḥanal|laahu|q̣uloobahum|littaq̣waa:|lahum|Mag̣firatuñw|WaʹAjrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
49,4,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yunaadoonaka|miñw|waraaaʹil|ḤUJURAATI|ʹaks̤aruhum|laa-|yaʻq̣iloon."
49,5,"Wa-law|ʹannahum|ṣabaroo|ḥattaa|takhruja|ʹilayhim|lakaana|khayral|lahum:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
49,6,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiñ|jaaʹakum|faasiq̣um|binabaʹiñ|fatabayyanooo|ʹañ|tuṣeeboo|q̣awmam|bijahaalatiñ|fatuṣbiḥoo|ʻalaa|maa-|faʻaltum|naadimeen."
49,7,"Waʻlamooo|ʹanna|feekum|Rasoolal|laah:|law|yuṭeeʻukum|fee|kas̤eerim|minal|ʹamrila|ʻanittum|wa-laakinnal|laaha|ḥabbaba|ʹilaykumul|ʹEemaana|wa-zayyanahoo|fee|q̣uloobikum|wa-karraha|ʹilaykumul|kufra|walfusooq̣a|walʻiṣyaan:|ʹulaaaʹika|humur|raashidoon;―"
49,8,"Faḍlam|minal|laahi|wa-niʻmah;|wallaahu|ʹAleemun|Ḥakeem."
49,9,"Wa-ʹiñ|ṭaaaʹifataani|minal|Muʹminee|naq̣tataloo|faʹaṣliḥoo|baynahumaa:|faʹim|bag̣at|ʹiḥdaahumaa|ʻalal|ʹukhraa|faq̣aatilul|latee|tabg̣ee|ḥattaa|tafeeeʹa|ʹilaaa|ʹamril|laah:|faʹiñ|faaaʹat|faʹaṣliḥoo|baynahumaa|bilʻadli|wa-ʹaq̣siṭoo:|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muq̣siṭeen."
49,10,"ʹInnamal|Muʹminoona|ʹIkhwatuñ|faʹaṣliḥoo|bayna|ʹakhawaykum|wattaq̣ul|laaha|laʻallakum|turḥamoon."
49,11,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|la|yaskhar|q̣awmum|miñ|q̣awmin|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yakoonoo|khayram|minhum|wa-laa|nisaaaʹum|min|nisaaaʹin|ʻasaaa|ʹañy|yakunna|khayram|minhunn:|wa-laa|talmizooo|ʹañfusakum|wa-laa|tanaabazoo|bilʹalq̣aab:|biʹsal|ismul|fusooq̣u|baʻdal|ʹeemaan:|wa-mal|lam|yatub|faʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
49,12,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanuj|taniboo|kas̤eeram|minaz̤̣|z̤̣ann:|ʹinna|baʻḍaz̤̣|z̤̣anni|ʹis̤muñw|Walaa|tajassasoo|wa-laa|yag̣tab|baʻḍukum|baʻḍaa.|ʹA-yuḥibbu|ʻaḥadukum|ʹañy|yaʹkula|laḥma|ʹakheehi|maytañ|fakarihtumooh?|Wattaq̣ul|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|Tawwaabur|Raḥeem."
49,13,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|naasu|ʹinnaa|khalaq̣naakum|miñ|ẓakariñw|waʹuñs̤aa|wa-jaʻalnaakum|shuʻoobañw|waq̣abaaaʹila|litaʻaarafoo.|ʹInna|ʹakramakum|ʻiñdal|laahi|ʹatq̣aakum.|ʹInnal|laaha|ʻAleemun|Khabeer."
49,14,"Q̣aalatil|ʹAʻraabu|ʹaamannaa.|Q̣ul|lam|tuʹminoo|wa-laakiñ|q̣oolooo|ʹaslamnaa|wa-lammaa|yadkhulil|ʹeemaanu|fee|q̣uloobikum.|Wa-ʹiñ|tuṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|laa-|yalitkum|min|ʹaʻmaalikum|shayʹaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
49,15,"ʹInnamal|Muʹminoonal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|s̤umma|lam|yartaaboo|wa-jaahadoo|biʹamwaalihim|wa-ʹañfusihim|fee|Sabeelil|laah:|ʹulaaaʹika|humuṣ|Ṣaadiq̣oon."
49,16,"Q̣ul|ʹatuʻallimoonal|laaha|bideenikum?|Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|arḍ:|wallaahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
49,17,"Yamunnoona|ʻalayka|ʹan|ʹaslamoo.|Q̣ul|laa-|tamunnoo|ʻalayya|ʹIslaamakum.|Balil|laahu|yamunnu|ʻalaykum|ʹan|hadaakum|lil-ʹeemaani|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
49,18,"ʹInnal|laaha|yaʻlamu|g̣aybas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wallaahu|baṣeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
50,1,"Q̣AAAF:|Wal-Q̣urʹaanil|Majeed."
50,2,"Bal|ʻajibooo|ʹañ|jaaaʹahum|Muñẓirum|minhum|faq̣aalal|kaafiroona|haaẓaa|shayʹun|ʻajeeb!"
50,3,"ʹA-ʹiẓaa|mitnaa|wa-kunnaa|turaabaa?|Ẓaalika|Rajʻum|baʻeed!"
50,4,"Q̣ad|ʻalimnaa|maa-|tañq̣uṣul|ʹarḍu|minhum:|wa-ʻiñdanaa|Kitaabun|Hafeez̤̣."
50,5,"Bal|kaẓẓaboo|bil-Ḥaq̣q̣i|lammaa|jaaaʹahum|fahum|feee|ʹamrim|mareej."
50,6,"ʹAfalam|yañz̤̣urooo|ʹilas|samaaaʹi|fawq̣ahum|kayfa|banaynaahaa|wa-zayyannaahaa|wa-maa|lahaa|miñ|furooj?"
50,7,"Wal-ʹarḍa|madadnaahaa|wa-ʹalq̣aynaa|feehaa|rawaasiya|wa-ʹambatnaa|feehaa|miñ|kulli|zawjim|baheej,―"
50,8,"Tabṣiratañw|Waẓikraa|likulli|ʻabdim|muneeb."
50,9,"Wa-nazzalnaa|minas|samaaaʹi|maaaʹam|mubaarakañ|faʹambatnaa|bihee|jannatiñw|waḥabbal|ḥaṣeed;"
50,10,"Wannakhla|baasiq̣aatil|lahaa|ṭalʻun|naḍeed;―"
50,11,"Rizq̣al|lilʻibaadi|wa-ʹaḥyaynaa|bihee|baldatam|maytaa.|Kaẓaalikal|khurooj."
50,12,"Kaẓẓabat|q̣ablahum|Q̣awmu|Nooḥiñw|waʹAṣḥaabur|Rassi|wa-S̤amood,"
50,13,"Wa-ʻAaduñw|Wa-Firʻawnu|wa-ʹIkhwaanu|Looṭ"
50,14,"Wa-ʹAṣḥaabul|ʹaykati|wa-Q̣awmu|Tubbaʻ;|kulluñ|kaẓẓabar|rusula|faḥaq̣q̣a|Waʻeed."
50,15,"ʹAfaʻayeenaa|bilkhalq̣il|ʹawwal:|bal|hum|fee|labsim|min|khalq̣iñ|jadeed?"
50,16,"Wa-laq̣ad|khalaq̣nal|ʹiñsaana|Wanaʻlamu|maa-|tuwaswisu|bihee|nafsuh:|wa-Naḥnu|ʹaq̣rabu|ʹilayhi|min|ḥablil|wareed."
50,17,"ʹIẓ|yatalaq̣q̣al|mutalaq̣q̣iyaani|ʻanil|yameeni|wa-ʻanish|shimaali|q̣aʻeed."
50,18,"Maa-|yalfiz̤̣u|miñ|q̣awlin|ʹillaa|ladayhi|raq̣eebun|ʻateed."
50,19,"Wa-jaaaʹat|sakratul|mawṭi|bilḥaq̣q̣:|ẓaalika|maa-|kuñta|minhu|taḥeed!"
50,20,"Wa-nufikha|fiṣ|Ṣoor:|ẓaalika|Yawmul|Waʻeed."
50,21,"Wa-jaaaʹat|kullu|nafsim|maʻahaa|saaaʹiq̣uñw|washaheed."
50,22,"Laq̣ad|kuñta|fee|g̣aflatim|min|haaẓaa|fakashafnaa|ʻañka|g̣iṭaaaʹaka|fabaṣarukal|Yawma|ḥadeed!"
50,23,"Wa-q̣aala|Q̣areenuhoo|haaẓaa|maa-|ladayya|ʻateed!"
50,24,"ʹAlq̣iyaa|fee|Jahannama|kulla|kaffaarin|ʻaneed,"
50,25,"Mannaaʻil|lilkhayri|muʻtadim|mureeb;"
50,26,"ʹAllaẓee|jaʻala|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhara|faʹalq̣iyaahu|fil|ʻAẓaabish|shadeed."
50,27,"Q̣aala|Q̣areenuhoo|Rabbanaa|maaa|ʹaṭg̣aytuhoo|wa-laakiñ|kaana|fee|ḍalaalim|baʻeed."
50,28,"Q̣aala|laa-|takhtaṣimoo|ladayya|wa-q̣ad|q̣addamtu|ʹilaykum̃|bilwaʻeed."
50,29,"Maa-|yubaddalul|Q̣awlu|ladayya|wa-maaa|ʹana|biz̤̣al-laamil|lilʻAbeed."
50,30,"Yawma|naq̣oolu|li-Jahannama|halim|talaʹti|wa-taq̣oolu|hal|mim|mazeed?"
50,31,"Wa-ʹuzlifatil|Jannatu|lil-Muttaq̣eena|g̣ayra|baʻeed."
50,32,"Haaẓaa|maa-|tooʻadoona|likulli|ʹawwaabin|ḥafeez̤̣,―"
50,33,"Man|khashiyar|Raḥmaana|bilg̣aybi|wa-jaaaʹa|biq̣albim|muneeb:"
50,34,"ʹUdkhuloohaa|bi-Salaam;|ẓaalika|Yawmul|Khulood!"
50,35,"Lahum|maa|yashaaaʹoona|feehaa|wa-Ladaynaa|mazeed."
50,36,"Wa-kam|ʹahlaknaa|q̣ablahum|miñ|q̣arnin|hum|ʹashaddu|minhum|baṭshañ|fanaq̣q̣aboo|fil|bilaad?|Hal|mim|maḥeeṣ?"
50,37,"ʹInna|fee|ẓaalika|la-Ẓikraa|limañ|kaana|lahoo|q̣albun|ʹaw|ʹalq̣as|samʻa|wa-huwa|shaheed."
50,38,"Wa-laq̣ad|khalaq̣nas|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|wa-maa|baynahumaa|fee|Sittati|ʹAyyaam;|wa-maa|massanaa|mil|lug̣oob."
50,39,"Faṣbir|ʻalaa|maa-|yaq̣ooloona|wa-sabbiḥ|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbika|q̣abla|ṭulooʻish|shamsi|wa-q̣ablal|g̣uroob,―"
50,40,"Wa-minal|layli|fasabbiḥhu|wa-ʹadbaaras|sujood."
50,41,"Wastamiʻ|Yawma|yunaadil|Munaadi|mim|makaaniñ|q̣areeb,―"
50,42,"Yawma|yasmaʻoonaṣ|Ṣay-ḥata|bilḥaq̣q̣:|ẓaalika|Yawmul|Khurooj."
50,43,"ʹInnaa|Naḥnu|nuḥyee|wa-numeetu|wa-ʹilaynal|Maṣeer!"
50,44,"Yawma|tashaq̣q̣aq̣ul|ʹarḍu|ʻanhum|siraaʻaa:|ẓaalika|ḥashrun|ʻalaynaa|yaseer."
50,45,"Naḥnu|ʹaʻlamu|bimaa|yaq̣ooloona|wa-maaa|ʹañta|ʻalayhim̃|bijabbaar.|Faẓakkir|bil-Q̣urʹaani|mañy|yakhaafu|Waʻeed!"
51,1,"Waẓ-Ẓaariyaati|ẓarwaa."
51,2,"Falḥaamilaati|wiq̣raa."
51,3,"Faljaariyaati|yusraa."
51,4,"Falmuq̣assimaati|ʹAmraa."
51,5,"ʹInnamaa|tooʻadoona|laṣaadiq̣;"
51,6,"Wa-ʹinnad|Deena|lawaaq̣iʻ."
51,7,"Wassamaaaʹi|ẓaatil|Ḥubuk,"
51,8,"ʹInnakum|lafee|q̣awlim|mukhtalif."
51,9,"Yuʹfaku|ʻanhu|man|ʹufik."
51,10,"Q̣utilal|kharraaṣoon,―"
51,11,"ʹAllaẓeena|hum|fee|g̣amratiñ|saahoon:"
51,12,"Yasʹaloona|ʹayyaana|Yawmud|Deen?"
51,13,"Yawma|hum|ʻalan|Naari|yuftanoon!"
51,14,"Ẓooq̣oo|fitnatakum!|Haa-ẓal|laẓee|kuñtum̃|bihee|tas-taʻjiloon!"
51,15,"ʹInnal|Muttaq̣eena|fee|Jannaatiñw|Waʻuyoon,"
51,16,"ʹAakhiẓeena|maaa|ʹaataahum|Rabbuhum:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣abla|ẓaalika|Muḥsineen."
51,17,"Kaanoo|q̣aleelam|minal|layli|maa-|yahjaʻoon:"
51,18,"Wa-bilʹasḥaari|hum|yastag̣firoon:"
51,19,"Wa-feee|ʹamwaalihim|ḥaq̣q̣ul|lissaaaʹili|walmaḥroom."
51,20,"Wa-fil|ʹarḍi|ʹAayaatul|lil-Mooq̣ineen,"
51,21,"Wa-feee|ʹañfusikum|ʹafalaa|tubṣiroon?"
51,22,"Wa-fis|samaaaʹi|Rizq̣ukum|wa-maa|tooʻadoon."
51,23,"Fawa-Rabbis|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍi|ʹinnahoo|la-Ḥaq̣q̣um|mis̤la|maaa|ʹannakum|tañṭiq̣oon."
51,24,"Hal|ʹataaka|ḥadees̤u|ḍayfi|ʹibraaheemal|mukrameen?"
51,25,"ʹIẓ|dakhaloo|ʻalayhi|faq̣aaloo|Salaamaa!|Q̣aala|Salaam!|Q̣awmum|muñkaroon."
51,26,"Faraag̣a|ʹilaaa|ʹahlihee|fajaaaʹa|biʻijliñ|sameen,"
51,27,"Faq̣arrabahooo|ʹilayhim|Q̣aala|ʹalaa|taʹkuloon?"
51,28,"Faʹawjasa|minhum|kheefaḥ|Q̣aaloo|laa-|takhaf!|wa-bashsharoohu|big̣ulaamin|ʻaleem."
51,29,"Faʹaq̣balatim|raʹatuhoo|fee|ṣarratiñ|faṣakkat|wajhahaa|wa-q̣aalat|ʻajoozun|ʻaq̣eem!"
51,30,"Q̣aaloo|kaẓaaliki|q̣aala|Rabbuk:|ʹinnahoo|Huwal|Ḥakeemul|ʻAleem."
51,31,"Q̣aala|famaa|khaṭbukum|ʹayyuhal|Mursaloon?"
51,32,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaaa|ʹursilnaaa|ʹilaa|q̣awmim|mujrimeen;―"
51,33,"Linursila|ʻalayhim|ḥijaaratam|miñ|ṭeen."
51,34,"Musawwamatan|ʻiñda|Rabbika|lilmusrifeen."
51,35,"Faʹakhrajnaa|mañ|kaana|feehaa|minal|Muʹmineen."
51,36,"Famaa|wa-jadnaa|feeha|g̣ayra|baytim|minal|Muslimeen:"
51,37,"Wa-taraknaa|feehaaa|ʹAayatal|lillaẓeena|yakhaafoonal|ʻAẓaabal|ʹaleem."
51,38,"Wa-fee|Moosaaa|ʹiẓ|ʹarsalnaahu|ʹilaa|Firʻawna|bisulṭaanim|mubeen."
51,39,"Fatawallaa|biruknihee|wa-q̣aala|˹saaḥirun|ʹaw|majnoon!"
51,40,"Faʹakhaẓnaahu|wa-junoo-dahoo|fanabaẓnaahum|fil|yammi|wa-huwa|muleem."
51,41,"Wa-fee|ʻAadin|ʹiẓ|ʹarsalnaa|ʻalayhimur|Reeḥal|ʻaq̣eem:"
51,42,"Maa-|taẓaru|miñ|shayʹin|ʹatat|ʻalayhi|ʹillaa|jaʻalathu|karrameem."
51,43,"Wa-fee|S̤amooda|ʹiẓ|q̣eela|lahum|tamattaʻoo|ḥattaa|ḥeen!"
51,44,"Faʻataw|ʻan|ʹAmri|Rabbihim|faʹakhaẓathumuṣ|ṣaaʻiq̣atu|wa-hum|yañz̤̣uroon."
51,45,"famas|taṭaaʻoo|miñ|q̣iyaamiñw|wamaa|kaanoo|muñtaṣireen."
51,46,"Wa-Q̣awma|Nooḥim|miñ|q̣abl:|ʹinnahum|kaanoo|q̣awmañ|faasiq̣een."
51,47,"Was-Samaaaʹa|banaynaahaa|biʹaydiñw|waʹInnaa|lamoosiʻoon."
51,48,"Wal-ʹarḍa|farashnaahaa|faniʻmal|maahidoon!"
51,49,"Wa-miñ|kulli|shayʹin|khalaq̣naa|zawjayni|laʻallakum|taẓakkaroon."
51,50,"Fafirrooo|ʹilal|laah:|ʹinnee|lakum|minhu|Naẓeerum|mubeen!"
51,51,"Wa-laa|tajʻaloo|maʻal|laahi|ʹilaahan|ʹaakhar:|ʹinnee|lakum|minhu|Naẓeerum|mubeen!"
51,52,"Kaẓaalika|maaa|ʹatal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|mir|Rasoolin|ʹillaa|q̣aaloo|saaḥirun|ʹaw|majnoon!"
51,53,"ʹAtawaaṣaw|bih?|Bal|hum|q̣awmuñ|ṭaag̣oon!"
51,54,"Fatawalla|ʻanhum|famaaa|ʹañta|bimaloom."
51,55,"Wa-ẓakkir|faʹinnaẓ|Ẓikraa|tañfaʻul|Muʹmineen."
51,56,"Wa-maa|khalaq̣tul|Jinna|wal-ʹiñsa|ʹillaa|liyaʻbudoon."
51,57,"Maaa|ʹureedu|minhum|mir|Rizq̣iñw|Wamaaa|ʹureedu|ʹañy|yuṭʻimoon."
51,58,"ʹInnal|laaha|Huwar|Razzaaq̣u|Ẓul|Q̣uwwatil|Mateen."
51,59,"Faʹinna|lillaẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|ẓanoobam|mis̤la|ẓanoobi|ʹaṣḥaabihim|falaa|yastaʻjiloon!"
51,60,"Fawaylul|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|miñy|Yawmihimul|laẓee|yooʻadoon"
52,1,"Wat-Ṭoor;"
52,2,"Wa-Kitaabim|masṭoor"
52,3,"Fee|Raq̣q̣im|mañshoor;"
52,4,"Wal-Baytil|maʻmoor;"
52,5,"Was-Saq̣fil|marfooʻ;"
52,6,"Wal-Baḥril|masjoor;"
52,7,"ʹInna|ʻAẓaaba|Rabbika|lawaaq̣iʻ;―"
52,8,"Maa-|lahoo|miñ|daafiʻ;―"
52,9,"Yawma|tamoorus|samaaaʹu|mawraa,"
52,10,"Wa-taseerul|jibaalu|sayraa."
52,11,"Fawayluñy|Yawmaʹiẓil|lil-mukaẓẓibeen;―"
52,12,"ʹAllaẓeena|hum|fee|khawḍiñy|yalʻaboon."
52,13,"Yawma|yudaʻʻoona|ʹilaa|Naari|Jahannama|daʻ-ʻaa."
52,14,"Haaẓihin|Naarul|latee|kuñtum̃|bihaa|tukaẓẓiboon!"
52,15,"ʹAfasiḥrun|haaẓaaa|ʹam|ʹañtum|laa-|tubṣiroon?"
52,16,"ʹIṣlawhaa|faṣbirooo|ʹaw|laa-|taṣbiroo:|sawaaaʹun|ʻalaykum:|ʹinnamaa|tujzawna|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
52,17,"ʹInnal|Muttaq̣eena|Fee|Jannaatiñw|Wa-Naʻeem,―"
52,18,"Faakiheena|bimaaa|ʹaataahum|rabbuhum|wa-waq̣aahum|Rabbuhum|ʻAẓaabal|Jaḥeem."
52,19,"Kuloo|washraboo|haneeeʹam|bimaa|kuñtum|taʻmaloon."
52,20,"Muttakiʹeena|ʻalaa|sururim|maṣfoofah:|wa-zawwaj-naahum̃|biḥoorin|ʻeen."
52,21,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wattabaʻathum|ẓurriyyatuhum̃|biʹeemaanin|ʹalḥaq̣naa|bihim|ẓurriyyatahum|wa-maaa|ʹalatnaahum|min|ʻamalihim|miñ|shayʹ:|kullum|riʹim|bimaa|kasaba|raheen."
52,22,"Wa-ʹamdadnaahum̃|bifaakihatiñw|walaḥmim|mimmaa-|yashtahoon."
52,23,"Yatanaazaʻoona|feehaa|kaʹsal|laa|lag̣wuñ|feehaa|wa-laa|taʹs̤eem."
52,24,"Wa-yaṭoofu|ʻalayhim|g̣ilmaanul|lahum|kaʹannahum|Luʹluʹum|maknoon."
52,25,"Wa-ʹaq̣bala|baʻḍuhum|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñy|yatasaaaʹaloon."
52,26,"Q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|q̣ablu|feee|ʹahlinaa|mushfiq̣een."
52,27,"Famannal|laahu|ʻalaynaa|wa-waq̣aanaa|ʻAẓaabas|Samoom."
52,28,"ʹInnaa|kunnaa|miñ|q̣ablu|nadʻooh:|ʹinnahoo|Huwal|Barrur|Raḥeem!"
52,29,"Faẓakkir|famaaa|ʹañta|bi-Niʻmati|Rabbika|bikaahiniñw|walaa|majnoon."
52,30,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloona|Shaaʻirun|natarabbaṣu|bihee|raybal|manoon!"
52,31,"Q̣ul|tarabbaṣoo|faʹinnee|maʻakum|minal|mutarabbiṣeen!"
52,32,"ʹAm|taʹmuruhum|ʹaḥlaamuhum̃|bihaaẓaaa|ʹam|hum|q̣awmuñ|ṭaag̣oon?"
52,33,"ʹAm|yaq̣ooloona|taq̣awwalah?|Bal|laa|yuʹminoon!"
52,34,"Falyaʹtoo|biḥadees̤im|mis̤liheee|ʹiñ|kaanoo|Ṣaadiq̣een!"
52,35,"ʹAm|khuliq̣oo|min|g̣ayri|shayʹin|ʹam|humul|khaaliq̣oon?"
52,36,"ʹAm|khalaq̣us|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ?|Bal|laa|yooq̣inoon."
52,37,"ʹAm|ʻiñdahum|khazaaaʹinu|Rabbika|ʹam|humul|musayṭiroon?"
52,38,"ʹAm|lahum|sullamuñy|yastamiʻoona|feeh?|falyaʹti|mustamiʻuhum̃|bisulṭaanim|mubeen."
52,39,"ʹAm|lahul|banaatu|wa-lakumul|banoon?"
52,40,"ʹAm|tasʹaluhum|ʹajrañ|fahum|mim|mag̣ramim|mus̤q̣aloon?"
52,41,"ʹAm|ʻiñdahumul|G̣aybu|fahum|yaktuboon?"
52,42,"ʹAm|yureedoona|kaydaa?|Fallaẓeena|kafaroo|humul|makeedoon!"
52,43,"ʹAm|lahum|ʹilaahun|g̣ayrul|laah?|Subḥaanal|laahi|ʻammaa|yushrikoon!"
52,44,"Wa-ʹiñy|yaraw|kisfam|minas|samaaaʹi|saaq̣iṭañy|yaq̣ooloo|saḥaabum|markoom!"
52,45,"Faẓarhum|ḥattaa|yulaaq̣oo|Yawmahumul|laẓee|feehi|yuṣʻaq̣oon,―"
52,46,"Yawma|laa-|yug̣nee|ʻanhum|kayduhum|shayʹañw|walaa|hum|yuñṣaroon."
52,47,"Wa-ʹinna|lillaẓeena|z̤̣alamoo|ʻaẓaabañ|doona|ẓaalika|wa-laakinna|ʹaks̤arahum|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
52,48,"Waṣbir|liḥukmi|Rabbika|faʹinnaka|biʹaʻyuninaa|wa-sabbiḥ|bi-Ḥamdi|Rabbika|ḥeena|taq̣oom,"
52,49,"Wa-minal|layli|fasabbiḥhu|wa-ʹidbaaran|nujoom!"
53,1,"Wan-NAJMI|ʹiẓaa|hawaa,―"
53,2,"Maa-|ḍalla|Ṣaaḥibukum|wa-maa|g̣awaa,"
53,3,"Wa-maa|yañṭiq̣u|ʻanil|hawaa."
53,4,"ʹIn|huwa|ʹillaa|Waḥyuñy|yooḥaa:"
53,5,"ʻAllamahoo|Shadeedul|Q̣uwaa,―"
53,6,"Ẓoo|Mirratiñ|fastawaa,"
53,7,"Wa-huwa|bil-ʹufuq̣il|ʹaʻlaa:"
53,8,"S̤umma|danaa|fatadallaa,"
53,9,"Fakaana|Q̣aaba|q̣awsayni|ʹaw|ʹadnaa."
53,10,"Faʹawḥaaa|ʹilaa|ʻAbdihee|maaa|ʹawḥaa."
53,11,"Maa-|kaẓabal|fuʹaadu|maa-|raʹaa."
53,12,"ʹAfatumaaroonahoo|ʹalaa|maa-|yaraa?"
53,13,"Wa-laq̣ad|raʹaahu|nazlatan|ʹukhraa,"
53,14,"ʻIñda|Sidratil|muñtahaa:"
53,15,"ʻIñdahaa|Jannatul|Maʹwaa."
53,16,"ʹIẓ|yag̣shas|Sidrata|maa-|yag̣shaa!"
53,17,"Maa-|zaag̣al|baṣaru|wa-maa|ṭag̣aa!"
53,18,"Laq̣ad|raʹaa|min|ʹAayaati|Rabbihil|Kubraa!"
53,19,"ʹAfaraʹaytumul|Laata|wal-ʻUzzaa,"
53,20,"Wa-Manaatas̤|s̤aalis̤atal|ʹukhraa?"
53,21,"ʹA-lakumuẓ|ẓakaru|wa-lahul|ʹuñs̤aa?"
53,22,"Tilka|ʹiẓañ|q̣ismatuñ|ḍeezaa!"
53,23,"ʹIn|hiya|ʹillaaa|ʹasmaaaʹuñ|sammaytumoohaaa|ʹañtum|wa-ʹaabaaaʹukum|maaa|ʹañzalal|laahu|bihaa|miñ|sulṭaan.|ʹIñy|yattabiʻoona|ʹillaz̤̣|z̤̣anna|wa-maa|tahwal|ʹañfus!-|Walaq̣ad|jaaaʹahum|mir|Rabbihimul|Hudaa!"
53,24,"ʹAm|lil-ʹiñsaani|maa-|tamannaa?"
53,25,"Falillahil|ʹAakhiratu|wal-ʹoolaa."
53,26,"Wa-kam|mim|malakiñ|fis|samaawaati|laa-|tug̣nee|shafaaʻatuhum|shayʹan|ʹillaa|mim|baʻdi|ʹañy|yaʹẓanal|laahu|limañy|yashaaaʹu|wa-yarḍaa."
53,27,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|laa-|yuʹminoona|bil-ʹAakhirati|layusammoonal|malaaaʹikata|tasmiyatal|ʹuñs̤aa."
53,28,"Wa-maa|lahum̃|bihee|min|ʻilm.|ʹIñy|yattabiʻoona|ʹillaz̤̣|z̤̣ann:|wa-ʹinnaz̤̣|z̤̣anna|laa-|yug̣nee|minal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|shayʹaa."
