56,48,"ʹA-waʹaabaaaʹunal|ʹawwaloon?"
56,49,"Q̣ul|ʹinnal|ʹawwaleena|wal-ʹaakhireen,"
56,50,"Lamajmooʻoona|ʹilaa|meeq̣aati|Yawmim|maʻloom."
56,51,"S̤umma|ʹinnakum|ʹayyuhaḍ|ḍaaalloonal|mukaẓẓiboon!"
56,52,"Laʹaakiloona|miñ|Shajarim|miñ|Zaq̣q̣oom."
56,53,"Famaaliʹoona|minhal|buṭoon,―"
56,54,"Fashaariboona|ʻalayhi|minal|Ḥameem:"
56,55,"Fashaariboona|shurbal|heem."
56,56,"Haaẓaa|nuzuluhum|Yawmad|Deen!"
56,57,"Naḥnu|khalaq̣naakum|falawlaa|tuṣaddiq̣oon?"
56,58,"ʹAfaraʹaytum|maa|tumnoon?"
56,59,"ʹAʹañtum|takhluq̣oonahooo|ʹam|Naḥnul|Khaaliq̣oon?"
56,60,"Naḥnu|q̣addarnaa|baynakumul|Mawta|wa-maa|Naḥnu|bimasbooq̣een"
56,61,"ʻAlaaa|ʹan|nubaddila|ʹAms̤aalakum|wa-nuñshiʹakum|fee|maa|laa-|taʻlamoon."
56,62,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʻalimtumun|nashʹatal|ʹoolaa|falawlaa|taẓakkaroon?"
56,63,"ʹAfaraʹaytum|maa|taḥrus̤oon?"
56,64,"ʹAʹañtum|tazraʻoonahooo|ʹam|Naḥnuz|zaariʻoon?"
56,65,"Law|nashaaaʹu|lajaʻal-naahu|ḥuṭaamañ|faz̤̣altum|tafakkahoon:"
56,66,"ʹInnaa|lamug̣ramoon:"
56,67,"Bal|naḥnu|maḥroomoon."
56,68,"ʹAfaraʹaytumul|maaa|ʹallaẓee|tashraboon?"
56,69,"ʹAʹañtum|ʹañzaltumoohu|minal|muzni|ʹam|Naḥnul|muñziloon?"
56,70,"Law|nashaaaʹu|jaʻalnaahu|ʹujaajañ|falawlaa|tashkuroon?"
56,71,"ʹAfaraʹaytumun|naaral|latee|tooroon?"
56,72,"ʹAʹañtum|ʹañshaʹtum|shajaratahaaa|ʹam|Naḥnul|muñshiʹoon?"
56,73,"Naḥnu|jaʻalnaahaa|taẓkiratañw|wamataaʻal|lilmuq̣ween."
56,74,"Fasabbiḥ|bismi|Rabbikal|ʻAz̤̣eem!"
56,75,"Falaaa|ʹuq̣simu|bimawaaq̣iʻin|Nujoom,―"
56,76,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|laq̣asamul|law|taʻlamoona|ʻaz̤̣eem,―"
56,77,"ʹInnahoo|la-Q̣urʹaanuñ|Kareem,"
56,78,"Fee|Kitaabim|maknoon,―"
56,79,"Laa-|yamassuhooo|ʹillal|muṭahharoon:"
56,80,"Tañzeelum|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
56,81,"ʹAfabihaaẓal|Ḥadees̤i|ʹañtum|mudhinoon?"
56,82,"Wa-tajʻaloona|rizq̣akum|ʹannakum|tukaẓẓiboon?"
56,83,"Falawlaa|ʹiẓaa|balag̣atil|ḥulq̣oom,―"
56,84,"Wa-ʹañtum|ḥeenaʹiẓiñ|tañz̤̣uroon,―"
56,85,"Wa-Naḥnu|ʹaq̣rabu|ʹilayhi|miñkum|wa-laakil|laa|tubṣiroon,―"
56,86,"Falawlaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|g̣ayra|madeeneen,―"
56,87,"Tarjiʻoonahaaa|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een?"
56,88,"Faʹammaaa|ʹiñ|kaana|minal|Muq̣arrabeen,―"
56,89,"Fa-Rawḥuñw|Wa-Rayḥaanuñw|Wa-Jannatu|Naʻeem."
56,90,"Wa-ʹammaaa|ʹiñ|kaana|min|ʹAṣḥaabil|yameen.―"
56,91,"Fa-Salaamul|laka|min|Aṣḥaabil|yameen."
56,92,"Wa-ʹammaaa|ʹiñ|kaana|minal|Mukaẓẓibeenaḍ|ḍaaalleen,"
56,93,"Fanuzulum|min|ḥameem,―"
56,94,"Wa-taṣliyatu|Jaḥeem."
56,95,"ʹInna|haaẓaa|lahuwa|Ḥaq̣q̣ul|Yaq̣een."
56,96,"Fasabbiḥ|bismi|Rabbikal|ʻAz̤̣eem."
57,1,"Sabbaḥa|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
57,2,"Lahoo|Mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|yuḥyee|wa-yumeet;|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
57,3,"Huwal|ʹAwwalu|walʹAakhiru|waz̤̣-Z̤̣aahiru|wal-Baaṭin:|wa-Huwa|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
57,4,"Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal|ʹarḍa|fee|Sittati|ʹAyyaamiñ|s̤ummas|tawaa|ʻalal|ʻArsh.|Yaʻlamu|maa-|yaliju|filʹarḍi|wa-maa|yakhruju|minhaa|wa-maa|yañzilu|minas|samaaaʹi|wa-maa|yaʻruju|feehaa.|Wa-Huwa|maʻakum|ʹayna|maa-|kuñtum.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|baṣeer."
57,5,"Lahoo|Mulkus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-ʹilal|laahi|turjaʻul|ʹumoor."
57,6,"Yoolijul|Layla|fin|Nahaari|wa-yoolijun|Nahaara|fil|Layl;|wa-Huwa|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
57,7,"ʹAaminoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-ʹañfiq̣oo|mimmaa|jaʻalakum|mustakhlafeena|feeh.|Fallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|miñkum|wa-ʹañfaq̣oo|lahum|ʹAjruñ|kabeer."
57,8,"Wa-maa|lakum|laa-|tuʹminoona|billaahi|war-Rasoolu|yadʻookum|lituʹminoo|bi-Rabbikum|wa-q̣ad|ʹakhaẓa|Mees̤aaq̣akum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|Muʹmineen."
57,9,"Huwal|laẓee|yunazzilu|ʻalaa|ʻAbdiheee|ʹAayaatim|Bayyinaatil|liyukhrijakum|minaz̤̣|Z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|Noor.|Wa-ʹinnal|laaha|bikum|la-Raʻoofur|Raḥeem."
57,10,"Wa-maa|lakum|ʹallaa|tuñfiq̣oo|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|wa-lillaahi|meeraas̤us|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ.|Laa-|yastawee|miñkum|man|ʹañfaq̣a|miñ|q̣ablil|Fat-ḥi|wa-q̣aatal.|ʹUlaaaʹika|ʹaʻz̤̣amu|darajatam|minal|laẓeena|ʹañfaq̣oo|mim|baʻdu|wa-q̣aataloo.|Wa-kullañw|waʻad|allaahul|ḥusnaa.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Khabeer."
57,11,"Mañ|ẓal|laẓee|yuq̣riḍul|laaha|Q̣arḍan|Ḥasanañ|fayuḍaaʻifahoo|lahoo|wa-lahooo|ʹajruñ|kareem."
57,12,"Yawma|taral|Muʹmineena|wal-Muʹminaati|yasʻaa|Nooruhum̃|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-biʹaymaanihim|Bushraakumul|Yawma|Jannaatuñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feeha!|Ẓaalika|huwal|Fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem!"
57,13,"Yawma|yaq̣oolul|Munaafiq̣oona|wal-Munaafiq̣aatu|lil-laẓeena|ʹaamanuñ|z̤̣uroonaa|naq̣tabis|min|Noorikum!|Q̣eela|rjiʻoo|waraaaʹakum|faltamisoo|nooraa!|Faḍuriba|baynahum̃|bisooril|lahoo|baab.|Baaṭinuhoo|feehir|Raḥmatu|wa-z̤̣aahiruhoo|miñ|q̣ibalihil|ʻaẓaab!"
57,14,"Yunaadoonahum|ʹalam|nakum|maʻakum?|Q̣aaloo|balaa|walaakinnakum|fatañtum|ʹañfusakum|wa-tarabbaṣtum|wartabtum|wa-g̣arratkumul|ʹamaaniyyu|ḥattaa|jaaaʹa|ʹAmrul|laahi|wa-g̣arrakum̃|billaahil|G̣aroor."
57,15,"Fal-Yawma|laa-|yuʹkhaẓu|miñkum|fidyatuñw|walaa|minal|laẓeena|kafaroo.|Maʹwaakumun|Naar:|hiya|maw-laakum:|wa-biʹsal|Maṣeer!"
57,16,"ʹAlam|yaʹni|lil-laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹañ|takhshaʻa|q̣uloobuhum|liẓikril|laahi|wa-maa|nazala|minal|Ḥaq̣q̣i|wa-laa|yakoonoo|kallaẓeena|ʹootul|Kitaaba|miñ|q̣ablu|faṭaala|ʻalayhimul|ʹamadu|faq̣asat|q̣uloobuhum?|Wa-kas̤eerum|minhum|faasiq̣oon."
57,17,"ʹIʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|yuḥyil|ʹarḍa|baʻda|mawtihaa!|Q̣ad|bayyannaa|lakumul|ʹAayaati|laʻallakum|taʻq̣iloon."
57,18,"ʹInnal|Muṣṣaddiq̣eena|wal-Muṣṣaddiq̣aati|wa-ʹaq̣raḍul|laaha|Q̣arḍan|ḥasanañy|yuḍaaʻafu|lahum|wa-lahum|ʹajruñ|kareem."
57,19,"Wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|wa-rusulihee|ʹulaaaʹika|humuṣ|Ṣiddeeq̣oona|wash-Shuhadaaaʹu|ʻiñda|Rabbihim:|lahum|ʹAjruhum|wa-Nooruhum.|Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jaḥeem."
57,20,"ʹIʻlamooo|ʹannamal|ḥayaatud|dunyaa|laʻibuñw|walahwuñw|wazeenatuñw|watafaakhurum|baynakum|wa-takaas̤uruñ|fil|ʹamwaali|wal-ʹawlaad;|Kamas̤ali|g̣ays̤in|ʹaʻjabal|kuffaara|nabaatuhoo|s̤umma|yaheeju|fataraahu|muṣfarrañ|s̤umma|yakoonu|ḥuṭaamaa.|Wa-fil|ʹAakhirati|ʻAẓaabuñ|shadeeduñw|wa-Mag̣firatum|minal|laahi|wa-Riḍwaan.|Wa-mal|ḥayatud|dun-yaaa|ʹillaa|mataaʻul|g̣uroor?"
57,21,"Saabiq̣ooo|ʹilaa|Mag̣firatim|mir|Rabbikum|wa-Jannatin|ʻarḍuhaa|kaʻarḍis|samaaaʹi|wal-ʹarḍi|ʹuʻiddat|lillaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|billaahi|wa-rusulih:|ẓaalika|Faḍlul|laahi|yuʹteehi|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wal-laahu|Ẓul|Faḍlil|ʻAḍeem."
57,22,"Maaa|ʹaṣaaba|mim|muṣeebatiñ|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-laa|feee|ʹañfusikum|ʹillaa|fee|kitaabim|miñ|q̣abli|ʹan|nabraʹahaa:|ʹinna|ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseer:"
57,23,"Likaylaa|taʹsaw|ʻalaa|maa-|faatakum|wa-laa|tafraḥoo|bimaaa|ʹaataakum.|Wallaahu|laa-|yuḥibbu|kulla|mukhtaaliñ|fakhoor,―"
57,24,"ʹAllaẓeena|yabkhaloona|wa-yaʹmuroonan|naasa|bil-bukhl.|Wa-mañy|yatawalla|faʹinnal|laaha|Huwal|G̣aniyyul|Ḥameed."
57,25,"Laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|rusulanaa|bil-Bayyinaati|wa-ʹañzalnaa|maʻahumul|Kitaaba|wal-Meezaana|liyaq̣ooman|naasu|bilq̣isṭ;|wa-ʹañzalnal|ḤADEEDA|feehi|baʹsuñ|shadeeduñw|wamanaafiʻu|linnaasi|wa-liyaʻlamal|laahu|mañy|yañṣuruhoo|wa-rusulahoo|bil-G̣ayb:|ʹinnal|laaha|Q̣awiyyun|ʻAzeez."
57,26,"Wa-laq̣ad|ʹarsalnaa|Nooḥañw|WaʹIbraaheema|wa-jaʻalnaa|fee|ẓurriyatihiman|Nubuwwata|wal-kitaaba|faminhum|muhtad,|wa-kas̤eerum|minhum|faasiq̣oon."
57,27,"S̤umma|q̣affaynaa|ʻalaaa|ʹaas̤aarihim̃|birusulinaa|wa-q̣affaynaa|biʻEesab|ni|Maryama|wa-ʹaataynaahul|ʹIñjeel;|wa-jaʻalnaa|fee|q̣uloobil|laẓeenat|tabaʻoohu|Raʹfatañw|Wa-Raḥmah.|Wa-Rahbaaniyyatan|ibtadaʻoohaa|maa-|katabnaahaa|ʻalayhim|ʹillab|tig̣aaaʹa|Riḍwaanil|laahi|famaa|raʻawhaa|ḥaq̣q̣a|riʻaayatihaa.|Faʹaataynal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|minhum|ʹajrahum,|wa-kas̤eerum|minhum|faasiq̣oon."
57,28,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|wa-ʹaaminoo|bi-Rasoolihee|yuʹtikum|kiflayni|mir|Raḥmatihee|wa-yajʻal|lakum|Noorañ|tamshoona|bihee|wa-yag̣fir|lakum:|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem:"
57,29,"Liʹallaa|yaʻlama|ʹAhlul|Kitaabi|ʹallaa|yaq̣diroona|ʻalaa|shayʹim|miñ|Faḍlil|laahi|wa-ʹannal|Faḍla|biyadil|laahi|yuʹteehi|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|Ẓul|Faḍlil|ʻAz̤̣eem."
58,1,"Q̣ad|samiʻal|laahu|q̣awlal|latee|tujaadiluka|fee|zawjihaa|wa-tashtakeee|ʹilal|laah:|wallaahu|yasmaʻu|taḥaawurakumaa:|ʹinnal|laaha|Sameeʻum|Baṣeer."
58,2,"ʹAllaẓeena|yuz̤̣aahiroona|miñkum|min|nisaaaʹihim|maa|hunna|ʹummahaatihim:|ʹin|ʹummahaatuhum|ʹillal|laaaʹee|wa-ladnahum.|Wa-ʹinnahum|layaq̣ooloona|muñkaram|minal|q̣awli|wa-zooraa:|wa-ʹinnal|laaha|laʻAfuwwun|G̣afoor."
58,3,"Wallaẓeena|yuz̤̣aahiroona|min|nisaaaʹihim|s̤umma|yaʻoodoona|limaa|q̣aaloo|fataḥreeru|raq̣abatim|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yatamaaassaa:|ẓaalikum|tooʻaz̤̣oona|bih:|wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|khabeer."
58,4,"Famal|lam|yajid|faṣiyaamu|shahrayni|mutataabiʻayni|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yatamaaassaa.|Famal|lam|yastaṭiʻ|faʹiṭʻaamu|sitteena|miskeenaa.|Ẓaalika|lituʹminoo|billahi|wa-Rasoolih-Wa|tilka|Ḥudoodul|laah;|Wa-lilkaafireena|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem."
58,5,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yuḥaaaddoonal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|kubitoo|kamaa|kubital|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|wa-q̣ad|ʹañzalnaaa|ʹAayaatim|Bayyinaat.|Wa-lilkaafireena|ʻAẓaabum|muheen,―"
58,6,"Yawma|yabʻas̤uhumul|laahu|jameeʹañ|fayunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|ʻamiloo.|ʹAḥṣaahul|laahu|wa-nasooh:|wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Shaheed."
58,7,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹannal|laaha|yaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ?|Maa-|yakoonu|min|najwaa|s̤alaas̤atin|ʹillaa|Huwa|raabiʻuhum|wa-laa|khamsatin|ʹillaa|Huwa|saadisuhum|wa-laaa|ʹadnaa|miñ|ẓaalika|wa-laaa|ʹaks̤ara|ʹillaa|Huwa|maʻahum|ʹayna|maa|kaanoo:|s̤umma|yunabbiʹuhum̃|bimaa|ʻamiloo|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah.|ʹInnal|laaha|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
58,8,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|nuhoo|ʻanin|najwaa|s̤umma|yaʻoodoona|limaa|nuhoo|ʻanhu|wa-yatanaajawna|bil-ʹis̤mi|walʻudwaani|wa-maʻṣiyatir|Rasool.|Wa-ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹooka|ḥayyawka|bimaa|lam|yuḥayyika|bihil|laahu|wa-yaq̣ooloona|feee|ʹañfusihim|Law-laa|yuʻaẓẓibunal|laahu|bimaa|naq̣ool?|Ḥasbuhum|Jahannam:|yaṣlawnahaa,|fabiʹsal|maṣeer!"
58,9,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|tanaajaytum|falaa|tatanaajaw|bil-ʹis̤mi|wal-ʻudwaani|wa-maʻsiyatir|Rasooli|wa-tanaajaw|bil-birri|wattaq̣waa;|wattaq̣ul|laahal|laẓeee|ʹilayhi|tuḥsharoon."
58,10,"ʹInnaman|najwaa|minash|Shayṭaani|liyaḥzunal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-laysa|biḍaaarrihim|shayʹan|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnil|laah;|wa-ʻalal|laahi|falyatawakkalil|Muʹminoon."
58,11,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lakum|tafassaḥoo|fil|majaalisi|fafsahoo|yafsaḥil|laahu|lakum.|Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eelañ|shuzoo|fañshuzoo|yarfaʻil|laahul|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|miñkum|wallaẓeena|ʹootul|ʻIlma|darajaat.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|khabeer."
58,12,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|naajaytumur|Rasoola|faq̣addimoo|bayna|yaday|najwaakum|ṣadaq̣ah.|Ẓaalika|khayrul|lakum|wa-ʹaṭhar.|Faʹil|lam|tajidoo|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
58,13,"ʹAʹashfaq̣tum|ʹañ|tuq̣addimoo|bayna|yaday|najwaakum|ṣadaq̣aat?|Faʹiẓ|lam|tafʻaloo|wa-taabal|laahu|ʻalaykum|faʹaq̣eemuṣ|Ṣalaata|wa-ʹaatuz|Zakaata|wa-ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-Rasoolah.|Wallaahu|khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
58,14,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|lazeena|tawallaw|q̣awman|g̣aḍibal|laahu|ʻalayhim?|Maa-|hum|miñkum|wa-laa|minhum|wa-yaḥlifoona|ʻalal|kaẓibi|wa-hum|yaʻlamoon."
58,15,"ʹAʻaddal|laahu|lahum|ʻaẓaabañ|shadeedaa:|ʹinnahum|saaaʹa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
58,16,"ʹIttakhaẓooo|ʹaymaanahum|junnatañ|faṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laahi|falahum|ʻAẓaabum|muheen."
58,17,"Lañ|tug̣niya|ʻanhum|ʹamwaaluhum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaaduhum|minal|laahi|shayʹaa:|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naar;|hum|feehaa|khaalidoon."
58,18,"Yawma|yabʻas̤uhumul|laahu|jameeʻañ|fayaḥlifoona|lahoo|kamaa|yaḥlifoona|lakum|wa-yaḥsaboona|ʹannahum|ʻalaa|shayʹ.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinnahum|humul|kaaẓiboon!"
58,19,"ʹIstaḥwaẓa|ʻalayhimush|Shayṭaanu|faʹañsaahum|ẓikral|laah.|ʹUlaaaʹika|Ḥizbush|Shayṭaan.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|Ḥizbash|Shayṭaani|humul|khaasiroon!"
58,20,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yuḥaaaddoonal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahooo|ʹulaaaʹika|fil|ʹaẓalleen."
58,21,"Katabal|laahu|laʹag̣libanna|ʹana|wa-rusulee:|ʹinnal|laaha|Q̣awiyyun|ʻAzeez."
58,22,"Laa-|tajidu|q̣awmañy|yuʹminoona|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhiri|yuwaaaddoona|man|ḥaaaddal|laaha|wa-Rasoolahoo|wa-law|kaanooo|ʹaabaaaʹahum|ʹaw|ʹabnaaaʹahum|ʹaw|ʹikhwaanahum|ʹaw|ʻasheeratahum.|ʹUlaaaʹika|kataba|fee|q̣uloobihimul|ʹeemaana|wa-ʹayyadahum̃|birooḥim|minh.|Wa-yudkhiluhum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaa.|Raḍiyal|laahu|ʻanhum|wa-raḍoo|ʻanh.|ʹUlaaaʹika|Ḥizbul|laah.|ʹAlaaa|ʹinna|Ḥizbal|laahi|humul|Mufliḥoon."
59,1,"Sabbaḥa|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
59,2,"Huwal|laẓeee|ʹakhrajal|laẓeena|kafaroo|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|miñ|diyaarihim|liʹawwalil|ḤASHR.|Maa-|z̤̣anañtum|ʹañy|yakhrujoo|wa-z̤̣annooo|ʹannahum|Maa-niʻatuhum|ḥuṣoonuhum|minal|laahi|faʹataahumul|laahu|min|ḥays̤u|lam|yaḥtasiboo,|wa-q̣aẓafa|fee|q̣uloobihimur|ruʻba|yukhriboona|buyootahum̃|biʹaydeehim|wa-ʹaydil|Muʹmineen.|Faʻtabiroo|yaaaʹulil|ʹabṣaar!"
59,3,"Wa-lawlaaa|ʹañ|katabal|laahu|ʻalayhimul|jalaaaʹa|laʻaẓẓabahum|fid|dunyaa:|wa-lahum|fil|ʹAakhirati|ʻAẓaabun|Naar."
59,4,"Ẓaalika|biʹAnnahum|shaaaq̣q̣ul|laaha|wa-Rasoolah.|Wa-mañy|yushaaaq̣q̣il|laaha|faʹinnal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻIq̣aab."
59,5,"Maa-|q̣aṭaʻtum|mil|leenatin|aw|taraktumoohaa|q̣aaaʹimatan|ʻalaaa|ʹuṣoolihaa|fabiʹiẓnil|laahi|wa-liyukhziyal|faasiq̣een."
59,6,"Wa-maaa|ʹafaaaʹal|laahu|ʻalaa|Rasoolihee|minhum|famaaa|ʹawjaftum|ʻalayhi|min|khayliñw|walaa|rikaabiñw|walaakinnal|laaha|yusalliṭu|rusulahoo|ʻalaa|mañy|yashaaaʹ.|Wallaahu|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
59,7,"Maaa|ʹafaaaʹal|laahu|ʻalaa|Rasoolihee|min|ʹahlil|Q̣uraa|falillaahi|wa-lir-rasooli|wa-liẓil|q̣urbaa|wal-yataamaa|walmasaakeeni|wabnis|sabeeli|kay|laa-|yakoona|doolatam|baynal|ʹag̣niyaaaʹi|miñkum.|Wa-maaa|ʹaataakumur|Rasoolu|fakhuẓoohu|wa-maa|nahaakum|ʻanhu|fañtahoo.|Wattaq̣ul|laah;|ʹinnal|laaha|Shadeedul|ʻIq̣aab."
59,8,"Lilfuq̣araaaʹil|Muhaajireenal|laẓeena|ʹukhrijoo|miñ|diyaarihim|wa-ʹamwaalihim|yabtag̣oona|Faḍlam|minal|laahi|wa-Riḍwaanañw|wayañṣuroonal|laaha|wa-Rasoolah:|ʹulaaaʹika|humuṣ|Ṣaadiq̣oon;―"
59,9,"Wallaẓeena|tabawwaʹud|daara|wal-ʹeemaana|miñ|q̣ablihim|yuḥibboona|man|haajara|ʹilayhim|wa-laa|yajidoona|fee|ṣudoorihim|ḥaajatam|mimmaaa|ʹootoo|wa-yuʹs̤iroona|ʻalaaa|ʹañfusihim|wa-law|kaana|bihim|khaṣaaṣah.|Wa-mañy|yooq̣a|shuḥḥa|nafsihee|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
59,10,"Wallaẓeena|jaaaʹoo|mim|baʻdihim|yaq̣ooloona|Rabbanag̣|fir|lanaa|wa-liʹikhwaaninal|laẓeena|sabaq̣oonaa|bil-ʹEemaani|wa-laa|tajʻal|fee|q̣uloobinaa|g̣illallil|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|Rabbanaaa|ʹinnaka|Raʹoofur|Raḥeem."
59,11,"ʹAlam|tara|ʹilal|laẓeena|naafaq̣oo|yaq̣ooloona|liʹikhwaanihimul|laẓeena|kafaroo|min|ʹAhlil|Kitaabi|laʹin|ʹukhrijtum|lanakhrujanna|maʻakum|wa-laa|nuṭeeʻu|feekum|ʹaḥadan|ʹabadañw|waʹiñ|q̣ootiltum|lanañṣurannakum.|Wallaahu|yashhadu|ʹinnahum|lakaaẓiboon."
59,12,"Laʹin|ʹukhrijoo|laa-|yakhrujoona|maʻahum;|walaʹiñ|q̣ootiloo|laa-|yañṣuroonahum;|wa-laʹin|naṣaroohum|layuwallunnal|ʹadbaar;|s̤umma|laa-|yuñṣaroon."
59,13,"Laʹañtum|ʹashaddu|rahbatañ|fee|ṣudoorihim|minal|laah.|Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣awmul|laa|yafq̣ahoon."
59,14,"Laa-|yuq̣aatiloonakum|jameeʻan|ʹillaa|fee|q̣uram|muḥaṣṣanatin|ʹaw|miñw|waraaaʹi|judur.|Baʹsuhum̃|baynahum|shadeed:|taḥsabuhum|jameeʻañwwa|q̣uloobuhum|shattaa:|ẓaalika|biʹannahum|q̣awmul|laa|yaʻq̣iloon."
59,15,"Kamas̤alil|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|q̣areebañ|ẓaaq̣oo|wa-baala|ʹamrihim;|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem;―"
59,16,"Kamas̤alish|Shayṭaani|ʹiẓ|q̣aala|lil-ʹiñsaanik|fur:|falammaa|kafara|q̣aala|ʹinnee|bareeeʹum|miñka|ʹinneee|ʹakhaaful|laaha|Rabbal|ʻAalameen!"
59,17,"Fakaana|ʻaaq̣ibatahumaaa|ʹannahumaa|fin|Naari|khaalidayni|feehaa.|Wa-ẓaalika|jazaaaʹuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
59,18,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanut|taq̣ul|laaha|Waltañz̤̣ur|nafsum|maa|q̣addamat|lig̣ad.|Wattaq̣ul|laah:|ʹInnal|laaha|khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
59,19,"Wa-laa|takoonoo|kallaẓeena|nasul|laaha|faʹañsaahum|ʹañfusahum!|ʹUlaaaʹika|humul|faasiq̣oon!"
59,20,"Laa-|yastaweee|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|wa-ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannah:|ʹAṣḥaabul|Jannati|humul|Faaaʹizoon."
59,21,"Law|ʹañzalnaa|haaẓal|Q̣urʹaana|ʻalaa|jabalil|laraʹaytahoo|khaashiʻam|mutaṣaddiʻam|min|khashyatil|laah.|Wa-tilkal|ʹams̤aalu|naḍribuhaa|linnaasi|laʻallahum|vatafakkaroon."
59,22,"Huwal|laahul|laẓee|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo;―ʻ|ʻAalimul|g̣aybi|washshahaadah;|Huwar|Raḥmaanur|Raḥeem."
59,23,"Huwal|laahul|laẓee|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo,ʹAl|Malikul|Q̣uddoosus|Salaamul|Muʹminul|Muhayminul|ʻAzeezul|Jabbaarul|Mutakabbir:|Subḥaanal|laahi|ʻammaa|yushrikoon."
59,24,"Huwal|laahul|Khaaliq̣ul|Baariʹul|Muṣawwiru|lahul|ʹAsmaaa|ʹul-Ḥusnaa:|yusabbiḥu|lahoo|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
60,1,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tattakhiẓoo|ʻaduwwee|wa-ʻaduwwakum|ʹawliyaaaʹa|tulq̣oona|ʹilayhim̃|bilmawaddati|wa-q̣ad|kafaroo|bimaa|jaaaʹakum|minal|Ḥaq̣q̣i,|yukhrijoonar|Rasoola|wa-ʹiyyaakum|ʹañ|tuʹminoo|billaahi|Rabbikum!|ʹIñ|kuñtum|kharajtum|jihaadañ|fee|Sabeelee|wabtig̣aaaʹa|Marḍaatee|tusirroona|ʹilayhim|bilmawaddati|wa-ʹana|ʹaʻlamu|bimaaa|ʹakhfaytum|wa-maaa|ʹaʻlañtum.|Wa-mañy|yafʻalhu|miñkum|faq̣ad|ḍalla|Sawaaaʹas|Sabeel."
60,2,"ʹIñy|yas̤q̣afookum|yakoonoo|lakum|ʹaʻdaaaʹañw|Wayabsuṭooo|ʹilaykum|ʹaydiyahum|wa-ʹalsinatahum̃|bissoooʹi|wa-waddoo|law|takfuroon."
60,3,"Lañ|tañfaʻakum|ʹarḥaamukum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaadukum|Yawmal|Q̣iyaamah:|yafṣilu|baynakum:|wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
60,4,"Q̣ad|kaanat|lakum|ʹuswatun|ḥasanatuñ|feee|ʹIbraaheema|wallaẓeena|maʻahooo|ʹiẓ|q̣aaloo|liq̣awmihim|ʹinnaa|buraʹaaaʹu|miñkum|wa-mimmaa|taʻbudoona|miñ|doonil|laah:|kafarnaa|bikum|wa-badaa|baynanaa|wa-baynakumul|ʻadaawatu|wal-bag̣ḍaaaʹu|ʹabadan|ḥattaa|tuʹminoo|billaahi|Waḥdahooo|ʹillaa|q̣awla|ʹIbraaheema|liʹabeehi|laʹastag̣firanna|laka|wa-maaa|ʹamliku|laka|minal|laahi|miñ|shayʹ.|Rabbanaa|ʻalayka|tawakkalnaa|wa-ʹilayka|ʹanabnaa|wa-ʹilaykal|Maṣeer."
60,5,"Rabbanaa|laa-|tajʻalnaa|fitnatal|lillaẓeena|kafaroo|wag̣fir|lanaa|Rabbanaa!|ʹInnaka|ʹAñtal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
60,6,"Laq̣ad|kaana|lakum|feehim|ʹuswatun|ḥasanatul|limañ|kaana|yarjul|laaha|wal-Yawmal|ʹAakhir.|Wa-mañy|yatawalla|faʹinnal|laaha|Huwal|G̣aniyyul|Ḥameed."
60,7,"ʻAsal|laahu|ʹañy|yajʻala|baynakum|wa-baynal|laẓeena|ʻaadaytum|minhum|mawaddah.|Wallaahu|Q̣adeer;|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
60,8,"Laa-|yanhaakumul|laahu|ʻanil|laẓeena|lam|yuq̣aatilookum|fid|Deeni|wa-lam|yukhrijookum|miñ|diyaarikum|ʹañ|tabarroohum|wa-tuq̣siṭooo|ʹilayhim:|ʹinnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|Muq̣siṭeen."
60,9,"ʹInnamaa|yanhaakumul|laahu|ʻanil|laẓeena|q̣aatalookum|fid|Deeni|wa-ʹakhrajookum|miñ|diyaarikum|wa-z̤̣aaharoo|ʻalaaa|ʹikhraajikum|ʹañ|tawallawhum.|Wa-mañy|yatawallahum|faʹulaaaʹika|humuz̤̣|z̤̣aalimoon."
60,10,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹakumul|Muʹminaatu|Muhaajiraatiñ|famtaḥinoohunn:|ʹAllaahu|ʹaʻlamu|biʹeemaanihinn:|faʹin|ʻalimtumoohunna|Muʹminaatiñ|falaa|tarjiʻoohunna|ʹilal|Kuffaar.|Laa-|hunna|ḥillul|lahum|wa-laa|hum|yaḥilloona|lahunn.|Wa-ʹaatoohum|maaa|ʹañfaq̣oo.|Wa-laa|junaaḥa|ʻalaykum|ʹañ|tañkiḥoohunna|ʹiẓaaa|ʹaataytumoohunna|ʹujoorahunn.|Wa-laa|tumsikoo|biʻiṣamil|kawaafiri|wasʹaloo|maaa|ʹañfaq̣tum|walyasʹaloo|maaa|ʹañfaq̣oo.|Ẓaalikum|ḥukmul|laah.|Yaḥkumu|baynakum.|Wallaahu|ʻAleemun|Ḥakeem."
60,11,"Wa-ʹiñ|faatakum|shayʹum|min|ʹazwaajikum|ʹilal|kuffaari|faʻaaq̣abtum|faʹaatul|laẓeena|ẓahabat|ʹazwaajuhum|mis̤la|maaa|ʹañfaq̣oo.|Wattaq̣ul|laahal|laẓeee|ʹañtum̃|bihee|Muʹminoon."
60,12,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹakal|Muʹminaatu|yubaayiʻnaka|ʻalaaa|ʹal|laa|yushrikna|billaahi|shayʹañw|walaa|yasriq̣na|wa-laa|yazneena|wa-laa|yaq̣tulna|ʹawlaadahunna|wa-laa|yaʹteena|bibuhtaaniñy|yaftareenahoo|bayna|ʹaydeehinna|wa-ʹarjulihinna|wa-laa|yaʻṣeenaka|fee|maʻroofiñ|fabaayiʻhunna|wastag̣fir|lahunnal|laah:|ʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
60,13,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tatawallaw|q̣awman|g̣aḍibal|laahu|ʻalayhim|q̣ad|yaʹisoo|minal|ʹAakhirati|kamaa|yaʹisal|kuffaaru|min|ʹaṣḥaabil|q̣uboor."
61,1,"Sabbaḥa|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
61,2,"Yaaa-ʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|lima|taq̣ooloona|maa|laa-|tafʻaloon?"
61,3,"Kabura|maq̣tan|ʻiñdal|laahi|ʹañ|taq̣ooloo|maa|laa-|tafʻaloon."
61,4,"ʹInnal|laaha|yuḥibbul|laẓeena|yuq̣aatiloona|fee|Sabeelihee|ṢAFFAÑ|kaʹannahum̃|bunyaanum|marṣooṣ."
61,5,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|Moosaa|liq̣awmihee|yaa-q̣awmi|lima|tuʹẓoonanee|wa-q̣at|taʻlamoona|ʹannee|rasoolul|laahi|ʹilaykum?˺|Falammaa|zaag̣ooo|ʹazaag̣al|laahu|q̣uloobahum.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|faasiq̣een."
61,6,"Wa-ʹiẓ|q̣aala|ʻEesab|nu|Maryama|yaa-Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|ʹinnee|Rasoolul|laahi|ʹilaykum|muṣaddiq̣al|limaa|bayna|yadayya|minat|Tawraati|wa-Mubashshiram|bi-Rasooliñy|yaʹtee|mim|baʻdis|muhooo|ʹAhmad.˺|Falammaa|jaaaʹahum̃|bil-Bayyinaati|q̣aaloo|Haaẓaa|Siḥrum|mubeen."
61,7,"Wa-man|ʹaz̤̣lamu|mimmanif|taraa|ʻalal|laahil|kaẓiba|wa-huwa|yudʻaaa|ʹilal|ʹIslaam?|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
61,8,"Yureedoona|liyuṭfiʹoo|Nooral|laahi|biʹafwaahihim|wallaahu|mutimmu|Noorihee|wa-law|karihal|kaafiroon."
61,9,"Huwal|laẓeee|ʹarsala|Rasoolahoo|bil-Hudaa|wa-Deenil|Ḥaq̣q̣i|liyuz̤̣hirahoo|ʻalad|deeni|kullihee|wa-law|karihal|Mushrikoon."
61,10,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|hal|ʹadullukum|ʻalaa|tijaaratiñ|tuñjeekum|min|ʻAẓaabin|ʹaleem?"
61,11,"Tuʹminoona|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wa-tujaahidoona|fee|Sabeelil|laahi|biʹamwaalikum|wa-ʹañfusikum:|ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon!"
61,12,"Yag̣fir|lakum|ẓunoobakum|wa-yudkhilkum|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|wa-masaakina|ṭayyibatañ|fee|Jannaati|ʻAdn:|ẓaalikal|Fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
61,13,"Wa-ʹukhraa|tuḥibboonahaa,―|naṣrum|minal|laahi|wa-fatḥuñ|q̣areeb.|Wa-bashshiril|Muʹmineen."
61,14,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|koonooo|ʹañṣaaral|laahi|kamaa|q̣aala|ʻEesab|nu|Maryama|lil-Ḥawaariyyeena|man|ʹañṣaareee|ʹilal|laah?|Q̣aalal|Ḥawaariyyoona|naḥnu|ʹañṣaarul|laahi|faʹaamanaṭ|ṭaaaʹifatum|mim|Baneee|ʹIsraaaʹeela|wa-kafaraṭ|ṭaaaʹifah.|Faʹayyadnal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|ʻalaa|ʻaduwwihim|faʹaṣbaḥoo|z̤̣aahireen."
62,1,"Yusabbiḥu|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍil|Malikil|Q̣uddoosil|ʻAzeezil|Ḥakeem."
62,2,"Huwal|laẓee|baʻas̤a|fil|ʹUmmiyyeena|Rasoolam|min-hum|yatloo|ʻalayhim|ʹAayaatihee|wa-yuzakkeehim|wa-yuʻallimuhumul|Kitaaba|wal-Ḥikmah,―|wa-ʹiñ|kaanoo|miñ|q̣ablu|lafee|ḍalaalim|mubeen;―"
62,3,"Wa-ʹaakhareena|minhum|lammaa|yalḥaq̣oo|bihim:|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
62,4,"Ẓaalika|Faḍlul|laahi|yuʹteehi|mañy|yashaaaʹ:|wallaahu|Ẓul|Faḍlil|ʻaz̤̣eem."
62,5,"Mas̤alul|laẓeena|ḥum-milut|Tawraata|s̤umma|lam|yaḥmiloohaa|kamas̤alil|ḥimaari|yaḥ-milu|ʹasfaaraa.|Biʹsa|mas̤alul|q̣awmil|laẓeena|kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatil|laah.|Wallaahu|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmaz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen."
62,6,"Q̣ul|yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|haadooo|ʹiñ|zaʻamtum|ʹannakum|ʹawliyaaaʹu|lillaahi|miñ|doonin|naasi|fatamannawul|Mawta|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een!"
62,7,"Wa-laa|yatamannawnahooo|ʹabadam|bimaa|q̣addamat|ʹaydeehim!|Wallaahu|ʻAleemum|biz̤̣z̤̣aalimeen!"
62,8,"Q̣ul|ʹinnal|Mawtal|laẓee|tafirroona|minhu|faʹinnahoo|mulaaq̣eekum|summa|turaddoona|ʹilaa|ʻAalimil|g̣aybi|washshahaadati|fayunabbiʹukum̃|bimaa|kuntum|taʻmaloon!"
62,9,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|lazeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹiẓaa|noodiya|liṣ-Ṣalaati|miñy|Yawmil|JUMUʻATI|fasʻaw|ʹilaa|Ẓikril|laahi|wa-ẓarul|bayʻ:|ẓaalikum|khayrul|lakum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|taʻlamoon!"
62,10,"Faʹiẓaa|q̣uḍiyatiṣ|Ṣalaatu|fañtashiroo|fil|ʹarḍi|wabtag̣oo|miñ|Faḍlil|laahi|waẓkurul|laaha|kas̤eeral|laʻallakum|tufliḥoon."
62,11,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|raʹaw|tijaaratan|ʹaw|lahwaniñ|faḍḍooo|ʹilayhaa|wa-tarakooka|q̣aaaʹimaa:|Q̣ul|maa-|ʻiñdal|laahi|khayrum|minal|lahwi|wa-minat|tijaarah!|wallaahu|Khayrur|Raaziq̣een."
63,1,"ʹIẓaa|jaaaʹakal|MUNAAFIQ̣OONA|q̣aaloo|nashhadu|ʹinnaka|la-Rasoolul|laah.|Wallaahu|yaʻlamu|ʹinnaka|la-Rasooluh:|wallaahu|yashhadu|ʹinnal|Munaafiq̣eena|lakaaẓiboon."
63,2,"ʹIttakhaẓooo|ʹaymaanahum|junnatañ|faṣaddoo|ʻañ|Sabeelil|laah:|ʹinnahum|saaaʹa|maa-|kaanoo|yaʻmaloon."
63,3,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahum|ʹaamanoo|s̤umma|kafaroo|faṭubiʻa|ʻalaa|q̣uloobihim|fahum|laa-|yafq̣ahoon."
63,4,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|raʹaytahum|tuʻjibuka|ʹajsaamuhum;|wa-ʹiñy|yaq̣ooloo|tasmaʻ|liq̣awlihim:|Kaʹannahum|khushubum|musannadah.|Yaḥsaboona|kulla|ṣayḥatin|ʻalayhim.|Humul|ʻaduwwu|faḥẓarhum.|Q̣aatalahumul|laah!|ʹAnnaa|yuʹfakoon!"
63,5,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|q̣eela|lahum|taʻaalaw|yastag̣fir|lakum|Rasoolul|laahi|lawwaw|ruʹoosahum|wa-raʹaytahum|yaṣuddoona|wa-hum|mustakbiroon."
63,6,"Sawaaaʹun|ʻalayhim|ʹastag̣farta|lahum|ʹam|lam|tastag̣fir|lahum.|Lañy|yag̣firal|laahu|lahum.|ʹInnal|laaha|laa-|yahdil|q̣awmal|faasiq̣een."
63,7,"Humul|laẓeena|yaq̣ooloona|laa-|tuñfiq̣oo|ʻalaa|man|ʻiñda|Rasoolil|laahi|ḥattaa|yañfaḍḍoo.|Wa-lillaahi|khazaaaʹinus|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|walaakinnal|Munaafiq̣eena|laa-|yafq̣ahoon."
63,8,"Yaq̣ooloona|laʹir|rajaʻnaaa|ʹilal|Madeenati|layukhrijannal|ʹaʻazzu|minhal|ʹaẓall.|Wa-lillaahil|ʻizzatu|wa-li-Rasoolihee|wa-lil-Muʹmineena|walaakinnal|Munaafiq̣eena|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
63,9,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|laa-|tulhikum|ʹamwaalukum|wa-laaa|ʹawlaadukum|ʻañ-Ẓik|ril|laah.|Wa-mañy|yafʻal|ẓaalika|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|khaasiroon."
63,10,"Wa-ʹañfiq̣oo|mim|maa|razaq̣naakum|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiya|ʹaḥadakumul|Mawtu|fayaq̣oola|Rabbi|Law-laaa|ʹakhkhartaneee|ʹilaaa|ʹajaliñ|q̣areebiñ|faʹaṣṣaddaq̣a|wa-ʹakum|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
63,11,"Wa-lañy|yuʹakhkhiral|laahu|nafsan|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|ʹajaluhaa;|Wallaahu|khabeerum|bimaa|taʻmaloon."
64,1,"Yusabbiḥu|lillaahi|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wa-maa|fil|ʹarḍ.|Lahul|Mulku|wa-lahul|Ḥamd;|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer."
64,2,"Huwal|laẓee|khalaq̣akum|famiñkum|kaafiruñw|wamiñkum|Muʹmin.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|Baṣeer."
64,3,"Khalaq̣as|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍa|bilḥaq̣q̣i|wa-ṣawwarakum|faʹaḥsana|ṣuwarakum,|wa-ʹilayhil|Maṣeer."
64,4,"Yaʻlamu|maa-|fis|samaawaati|wal-ʹarḍi|wayaʻlamu|maa-|tusirroona|wa-maa|tuʻlinoon;|wallaahu|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
64,5,"ʹAlam|yaʹtikum|nabaʹul|laẓeena|kafaroo|miñ|q̣abl?|Faẓaaq̣oo|wa-baala|ʹamrihim|wa-lahum|ʻaẓaabun|ʹaleem."
64,6,"Ẓaalika|biʹannahoo|kaanat|taʹteehim|rusuluhum̃|bil-Bayyinaati|faq̣aalooo|ʹa-basharuñy|yahdoonanaa?|Fakafaroo|wa-tawallaw|wastag̣nal|laah:|wallaahu|G̣aniyyun|Ḥameed."
64,7,"Zaʻamal|laẓeena|kafarooo|ʹal|lañy|yubʻas̤oo.|Q̣ul|balaa|wa-Rabbee|latubʻas̤unna|s̤umma|latunabbaʹunna|bimaa|ʻamiltum.|Wa-ẓaalika|ʻalal|laahi|yaseer."
64,8,"Faʹaaminoo|billaahi|wa-Rasoolihee|wan-Nooril|laẓeee|ʹañzalnaa.|Wallaahu|bimaa|taʻmaloona|khabeer."
64,9,"Yawma|yajmaʻukum|li-Yawmil|Jamʻi|ẓaalika|Yawmut|TAG̣AABUN.|Wa-mañy|yuʹmim|billaahi|wa-yaʻmal|ṣaaliḥañy|yukaffir|ʻanhu|sayyiʹaatihee|wa-yudkhilhu|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa:|ẓaalikal|fawzul|ʻaz̤̣eem."
64,10,"Wallaẓeena|kafaroo|wa-kaẓẓaboo|biʹAayaatinaaa|ʹulaaaʹika|ʹAṣḥaabun|Naari|khaalideena|feehaa:|wa-biʹsal|Maṣeer."
64,11,"ʹaṣaaba|Maaa|mim|muṣeebatin|ʹillaa|biʹiẓnil|laah.|Wa-mañy|yuʹmim|billaahi|yahdi|q̣albah;|wallaahu|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻAleem."
64,12,"Wa-ʹaṭeeʻul|laaha|wa-ʹaṭeeʻur|Rasool:|faʹiñ|tawallaytum|faʹinnamaa|ʻalaa|Rasoolinal|Balaag̣ul|mubeen."
64,13,"ʹAllaahu|Laaa|ʹilaaha|ʹillaa|Hoo!|Wa-ʻalal|laahi|falyatawakkalil|Muʹminoon."
64,14,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanooo|ʹinna|min|ʹazwaajikum|wa-ʹawlaadikum|ʻaduwwal|lakum|faḥẓaroohum!|Wa-ʹiñ|taʻfoo|wa-taṣfaḥoo|wa-tag̣firoo|faʹinnal|laaha|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
64,15,"ʹInnamaaa|ʹamwaalukum|wa-ʹawlaadukum|fitnah:|wallaahu|ʻiñdahooo|ʹAjrun|ʻaz̤̣eem."
64,16,"Fattaq̣ul|laaha|mas|taṭaʻtum|wasmaʻoo|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoo|wa-ʹañfiq̣oo|khayralli|ʹañfusikum.|Wa-mañy|yooq̣a|shuḥḥa|nafsihee|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|Mufliḥoon."
64,17,"ʹIñ|tuq̣riḍul|laaha|Q̣arḍan|Ḥasanañy|yuḍaaʻifhu|lakum|wa-yag̣fir|lakum:|wallaahu|Shakoorun|Ḥaleem,―"
64,18,"ʻAalimul|g̣aybi|washshahaadatil|ʻAzeezul|Ḥakeem."
65,1,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|ʹiẓaa|ṭallaq̣tumun|nisaaaʹa|faṭalliq̣oohunna|liʻiddatihinna|wa-ʹaḥṣul|ʻiddah;|wattaq̣ul|laaha|Rabbakum:|laa-|tukhrijoohunna|mim|buyootihinna|wa-laa|yakhrujna|ʹillaaa|ʹañy|yaʹteena|bifaaḥishatim|mubayyinah.|Wa-tilka|ḥudoodul|laah:|wa-mañy|yataʻadda|ḥudoodal|laahi|faq̣ad|z̤̣alama|nafsah:|laa-|tadree|laʻallal|laaha|yuḥdis̤u|baʻda|ẓaalika|ʹamraa."
65,2,"Faʹiẓaa|balag̣na|ʹajalahunna|faʹamsikoohunna|bimaʻroofin|ʹaw|faariq̣oohunna|bimaʻroofiñw|waʹashhidoo|ẓaway|ʻadlim|miñkum|wa-ʹaq̣eemush|shahaadata|lillaah.|Ẓaalikum|yooʻaz̤̣u|bihee|mañ|kaana|yuʹminu|billaahi|wal-Yawmil|ʹAakhir.|Wa-mañy|yattaq̣il|laaha|yajʻal|lahoo|makhrajaa,"
65,3,"Wa-yarzuq̣hu|min|hays̤u|laa-|yaḥtasib.|Wa-mañy|yatawakkal|ʻalal|laahi|fa-Huwa|ḥasbuh.|ʹInnal|laaha|baalig̣u|ʹamrih:|q̣ad|jaʻalal|laahu|likulli|shayʹiñ|q̣adraa."
65,4,"Wallaaaʹee|yaʹisna|minal|maḥeeḍi|min|nisaaaʹikum|ʹinir|tabtum|faʻiddatuhunna|s̤alaas̤atu|ʹashhuriñw|wallaaaʹee|lam|yaḥiḍn:|wa-ʹulaatul|ʹaḥmaali|ʹajaluhunna|ʹañy|yaḍaʻna|ḥamlahunn:|wa-mañy|yattaq̣il|laaha|yajʻal|lahoo|min|ʹamrihee|yusraa."
65,5,"Ẓaalika|ʹAmrul|laahi|ʹañzalahooo|ʹilaykum:|wa-mañy|yattaq̣il|laaha|yukaffir|ʻanhu|sayyiʹaatihee|wa-yuʻz̤̣im|lahooo|ʹajraa."
65,6,"ʹAskinoohunna|min|ḥays̤u|sakañtum|miñw|wujdikum|wa-laa|tuḍaaarroohunna|lituḍayyiq̣oo|ʻalayhinn.|Wa-ʹiñ|kunna|ʹulaati|ḥamliñ|faʹañfiq̣oo|ʻalayhinna|ḥattaa|yaḍaʻna|ḥamlahunn.|Faʹin|ʹarḍaʻna|lakum|faʹaatoohunna|ʹujoorahunn:|waʹtamiroo|baynakum̃|bimaʻroof.|Wa-ʹiñ|taʻaasartum|fasaturḍiʻu|lahooo|ʹukhraa."
65,7,"Liyuñfiq̣|ẓoo|saʻatim|miñ|saʻatih,|wa-mañ|q̣udira|ʻalayhi|rizq̣uhoo|falyuñfiq̣|mimmaaa|ʹaataahul|laah.|Laa-|yukalliful|laahu|nafsan|ʹillaa|maaa|ʹaataahaa.|Sayajʻalul|laahu|baʻda|ʻusriñy|yusraa."
65,8,"Wa-kaʹayyim|miñ|q̣aryatin|ʻatat|ʻan|ʹAmri|Rabbihaa|wa-rusulihee|faḥaasabnaahaa|ḥisaabañ|shadeedañw|waʻaẓẓabnaahaa|ʻAẓaaban|nukraa."
65,9,"Faẓaaq̣at|wa-baala|ʹamrihaa|wa-kaana|ʻAaq̣ibatu|ʹamrihaa|khusraa."
65,10,"ʹAʻaddal|laahu|lahum|ʻAẓaabañ|shadeedañ|fattaq̣ul|laaha|yaaaʹulil|ʹalbaabil|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo!―|Q̣ad|ʹanzalal|laahu|ʹilaykum|Ẓikraa,―"
65,11,"Rasoolañy|yatloo|ʻalaykum|ʹAayaatil|laahi|mubayyinaatil|liyukhrijal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|wa-ʻamiluṣ|ṣaaliḥaati|minaz̤̣|z̤̣ulumaati|ʹilan|Noor.|Wa-mañy|yuʹmim|billaahi|wa-yaʻmal|ṣaliḥañy|yudkhilhu|Jannaatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|khaalideena|feehaaa|ʹabadaa:|q̣ad|ʹaḥsanal|laahu|lahoo|rizq̣aa."
65,12,"ʹAllaahul|laẓee|khalaq̣a|sabʻa|Samaawaatiñw|Waminal|ʹarḍi|mis̤lahunn.|Yatanazzalul|ʹAmru|baynahunna|litaʻlamooo|ʹannal|laaha|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer:|wa-ʹannal|laaha|q̣ad|ʹaḥaaṭa|bikulli|shayʹin|ʻilmaa."
66,1,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|lima|tuḥarrimu|maaa|ʹaḥallal|laahu|lak?|Tabtag̣i|marḍaata|ʹazwaajik.|wallaahu|G̣afoorur|Raḥeem."
66,2,"Q̣ad|faraḍal|laahu|lakum|taḥillata|ʹaymaanikum:|wallaahu|Mawlaakum,|wa-Huwal|ʻAleemul|Ḥakeem."
66,3,"Wa-ʹiẓ|ʹasarran|Nabiyyu|ʹilaa|baʻḍi|ʹazwaajihee|ḥadees̤aa,|falammaa|nabbaʹat|bihee|wa-ʹaz̤̣harahul|laahu|ʻalayhi|ʻarrafa|baʻḍahoo|wa-ʹaʻraḍa|ʻam|baʻḍ.|Falammaa|nabbaʹahaa|bihee|q̣aalat|man|ʹambaʹaka|haaẓaa?|Q̣aala|nabbaʹaniyal|ʻAleemul|Khabeer."
66,4,"ʹIñ|tatoobaaa|ʹilal|laahi|faq̣ad|ṣag̣at|q̣uloobukumaa;|wa-ʹiñ|taz̤̣aaharaa|ʻalayhi|faʹinnal|laaha|Huwa|Mawlaahu|wa-Jibreelu|wa-Ṣaaliḥul|Muʹmineen,|wal-malaaaʹikatu|baʻda|ẓaalika|z̤̣aheer."
66,5,"ʻAsaa|Rabbuhooo|ʹiñ|ṭallaq̣akunna|ʹañy|yubdilahooo|ʹazwaajan|khayram|miñkunna|Muslimaatim|Muʹminaatiñ|q̣aanitaatiñ|taaaʹibaatin|ʻaabidaatiñ|saaaʹiḥaatiñ|s̤ayyibaatiñw|waʹabkaaraa."
66,6,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|q̣ooo|ʹañfusakum|wa-ʹahleekum|Naarañw|Waq̣ooduhan|Naasu|wal-Ḥijaaratu|ʻalayhaa|malaaʹikatun|g̣ilaaz̤̣uñ|shidaadul|laa|yaʻṣoonal|laaha|maaa|ʹamarahum|Wayafʻaloona|maa-|yuʹmaroon."
66,7,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|kafaroo|laa-|taʻtaẓirul|Yawm!|ʹInnamaa|tujzawna|maa-|kuñtum|taʻmaloon!"
66,8,"Yaaaʹayyuhal|laẓeena|ʹaamanoo|toobooo|ʹilal|laahi|Tawbatan|Naṣooḥaa:|ʻasaa|Rabbukum|ʹañy|yukaffira|ʻañkum|sayyiʹaatikum|wa-yudkhilakum|Jannatiñ|tajree|miñ|taḥtihal|ʹanhaaru|Yawma|laa-|yukhzil|laahun|Nabiyya|wallaẓeena|ʹaamanoo|maʻah.|Nooruhum|yasʻaa|bayna|ʹaydeehim|wa-biʹaymaanihim|yaq̣ooloona|˹Rabbanaaa|ʹatmim|lanaa|Nooranaa|wag̣fir|lanaa:|ʹinnaka|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer.˺"
66,9,"Yaaaʹayyuhan|Nabiyyu|jaahidil|kuffaara|wal-Munaafiq̣eena|wag̣luz̤̣|ʻalayhim.|Wa-maʹwaahum|Jahannam,―|Wabiʹsal|maṣeer."
66,10,"Ḍarabal|laahu|mas̤alal|lillaẓeena|kafarum|raʹata|Nooḥiñw|wamraʹata|Looṭ.|Kaanataa|taḥta|ʻAbdayni|min|ʻibaadinaa|ṣaaliḥayni|fakhaanataahumaa|falam|yug̣niyaa|ʻanhumaa|minal|laahi|shayʹañw|waq̣eelad|khulan|Naara|maʻad|daakhileen!"
66,11,"Wa-ḍarabal|laahu|mas̤alal|lil-laẓeena|ʹaamanum|raʹata|Firʻawn.|ʹIẓ|q̣aalat|Rab-bib|ni|lee|ʻiñdaka|baytañ|fil|Jannati|wa-najjinee|miñ|Firʻawna|wa-ʻamalihee|wa-najjinee|minal|q̣awmiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeen;"
66,12,"Wa-Maryamab|nata|ʻImraanal|lateee|ʹaḥṣanat|farjahaa|fanafakhnaa|feehi|mir|rooḥinaa|wa-ṣaddaq̣at|bi-Kalimaati|Rabbihaa|wa-Kutubihee|wa-kaanat|minal|Q̣aaniteen."
67,1,"Tabaarakal|laẓee|bi-Yadihil|MULK;|wa-Huwa|ʻalaa|kulli|shayʹiñ|Q̣adeer:―"
67,2,"ʹAllaẓee|khalaq̣al|Mawta|wal-Ḥayaata|liyabluwakum|ʹayyukum|ʹaḥsanu|ʻamalaa;|wa-Huwal|ʻAzeezul|G̣afoor;―"
67,3,"ʹAllaẓee|khalaq̣a|sabʻa|samaawaatiñ|ṭibaaq̣aa:|maa-|taraa|fee|Khalq̣ir|Raḥmaani|miñ|tafaawut.|Farjiʻil|baṣara|hal|taraa|miñ|fuṭoor?"
67,4,"S̤ummar|jiʻil|baṣara|karratayni|yañq̣alib|ʹilaykal|baṣaru|khaasiʹañw|wahuwa|ḥaseer."
67,5,"Wa-laq̣ad|zayyannas|samaaaʹad|dunyaa|bimaṣaabeeḥa|wa-jaʻalnaahaa|rujoomal|lishshayaaṭeeni|wa-ʹaʻtadnaa|lahum|ʻaẓaabas|Saʻeer."
67,6,"Wa-lillaẓeena|kafaroo|bi-Rabbihim|ʻAẓaabu|Jahannam:|wa-biʻsal|maṣeer."
67,7,"ʹIẓaaa|ʹulq̣oo|feehaa|samiʻoo|lahaa|shaheeq̣añw|wahiya|tafoor,―"
67,8,"Takaadu|tamayyazu|minal|g̣ayz̤̣:|kullamaaa|ʹulq̣iya|feehaa|fawjuñ|saʹalahum|khazanatuhaaa|ʹalam|yaʹtikum|Naẓeer?"
67,9,"Q̣aaloo|balaa|q̣ad|jaaaʹanaa|Naẓeer;|fakaẓẓabnaa|waq̣ulnaa|maa-|nazzalal|laahu|miñ|shayʹ:|ʹin|ʹañtum|ʹillaa|fee|ḍalaaliñ|kabeer!"
67,10,"Wa-q̣aaloo|law|kunnaa|nasmaʻu|ʹaw|naʻq̣ilu|maa-|kunnaa|feee|ʹAṣḥaabis|Saʻeer!"
67,11,"Faʻtarafoo|biẓambihim:|fasuḥq̣al|liʹAṣḥaabis|Saʻeer!"
67,12,"ʹInnal|laẓeena|yakhshawna|Rabbahum̃|bilg̣aybi|lahum|Mag̣firatuñw|WaʹAjruñ|kabeer."
67,13,"Wa-ʹasirroo|q̣awlakum|ʹawij|haroo|bih;|ʹinnahoo|ʻAleemum|biẓaatiṣ|ṣudoor."
67,14,"ʹAlaa|yaʻlamu|man|khalaq̣?|Wa-Huwal|Laṭeeful|Khabeer."
67,15,"Huwal|laẓee|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹarḍa|ẓaloolañ|famshoo|fee|manaakibihaa|wa-kuloo|mir|rizq̣ih:|wa-ʹilayhin|Nushoor."
67,16,"ʹA-ʹamiñtum|mañ|fis|Samaaaʹi|ʹañy|yakhsifa|bikumul|ʹarḍa|faʹiẓaa|hiya|tamoor?"
67,17,"ʹAm|ʹamiñtum|mañ|fis|Samaaaʹi|ʹañy|yursila|ʻalaykum|ḥaaṣibaa?|Fasataʻlamoona|kayfa|naẓeer."
67,18,"Wa-laq̣ad|kaẓẓabal|laẓeena|miñ|q̣ablihim|fakayfa|kaana|nakeer?"
67,19,"ʹAwalam|yaraw|ʹilaṭ|ṭayri|fawq̣ahum|ṣaaaffaatiñw|Wayaq̣biḍn?|Maa-|yum-siku-hunna|ʹillar|Raḥmaan:|ʹinnahoo|bikulli|shayʹim|Baṣeer."
67,20,"ʹAmman|haaẓal|laẓee|huwa|juñdul|lakum|yañṣurukum|miñ|doonir|Raḥmaan?|ʹInil|kaafiroona|ʹillaa|fee|g̣uroor."
67,21,"ʹAmman|haaẓal|laẓee|yarzuq̣ukum|ʹin|ʹamsaka|Rizq̣ah?|Bal|lajjoo|fee|ʻutuwwiñw|Wanufoor."
67,22,"ʹAfamañy|yamshee|mukibban|ʻalaa|wajhiheee|ʹahdaaa|ʹammañy|yamshee|sawiyyan|ʻalaa|Ṣiraaṭim|Mustaq̣eem."
67,23,"Q̣ul|Huwal|laẓeee|ʹañshaʹakum|wa-jaʻala|lakumus|samʻa|wal-ʹabṣaara|wal-ʹafʹidah:|q̣aleelam|maa|tashkuroon."
67,24,"Q̣ul|Huwal|laẓee|ẓaraʹakum|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-ʹilayhi|tuḥsharoon."
67,25,"Wa-yaq̣ooloona|mataa|haaẓal|waʻdu|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaadiq̣een."
67,26,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamal|ʻilmu|ʻiñdal|laah:|wa-ʹinnamaaa|ʹana|Naẓeerum|mubeen."
67,27,"Falammaa|raʹawhu|zulfatañ|seeeʹat|wujoohul|laẓeena|kafaroo|wa-q̣eela|haaẓal|laẓee|kuñtum̃|bihee|taddaʻoon!"
67,28,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹin|ʹahlakaniyal|laahu|wa-mam|maʻiya|ʹaw|raḥimanaa|famañy|yujeerul|kaafireena|min|ʻAẓaabin|ʹaleem."
67,29,"Q̣ul|Huwar|Raḥmaanu|ʹaamannaa|bihee|wa-ʻalayhi|tawakkalnaa:|fasataʻlamoona|man|huwa|fee|ḍalaalim|mubeen."
67,30,"Q̣ul|ʹaraʹaytum|ʹin|ʹaṣbaḥa|maaaʹukum|g̣awrañ|famañy|yaʹteekum̃|bimaaaʹim|maʻeen?"
68,1,"NOOON.|WALQ̣ALAMI|wa-maa|yasṭuroon,―"
68,2,"Maaa|ʹañta|biniʻmati|Rabbika|bimajnoon."
68,3,"Wa-ʹinna|laka|laʹAjran|g̣ayra|mamnoon:"
68,4,"Wa-ʹinnaka|laʻalaa|khuluq̣in|ʻaz̤̣eem."
68,5,"Fasatubṣiru|wa-yubṣiroon,"
68,6,"Biʹayyikumul|maftoon."
68,7,"ʹInna|Rabbaka|Huwa|ʹaʻlamu|bimañ|ḍalla|ʻañ|Sabeelih:|wa-Huwa|ʹAʻlamu|bil-Muhtadeen."
68,8,"Falaa|tuṭiʻil|mukaẓẓibeen."
68,9,"Waddoo|law|tudhinu|fayudhinoon."
68,10,"Wa-laa|tuṭiʻ|kulla|ḥallaafim|maheen,"
68,11,"Hammaazim|mashshaaaʹim|binameem,"
68,12,"Mannaaʻil|lilkhayri|muʻtadin|ʹas̤eem,"
68,13,"ʻUtullim|baʻda|ẓaalika|zaneem,―"
68,14,"ʹAñ|kaana|ẓaa|maaliñwwa|baneen."
68,15,"ʹIẓaa|tutlaa|ʻalayhi|ʹAayaatunaa|q̣aala|ʹAsaaṭeerul|ʹAwwaleen!"
68,16,"Sanasimuhoo|ʻalal|khurṭoom!"
68,17,"ʹInnaa|balawnaahum|kamaa|balawnaaa|ʹAṣḥaabal|Jannah,|ʹiẓ|ʹaq̣samoo|layaṣrimunnahaa|muṣbiḥeen,"
68,18,"Wa-laa|yastas̤noon."
68,19,"Faṭaafa|ʻalayhaa|ṭaaaʹifum|mir|Rabbika|wa-hum|naaaʹimoon."
68,20,"Faʹaṣbaḥat|kaṣṣareem."
68,21,"Fatanaadaw|muṣbiḥeen,"
68,22,"ʹAnig̣|doo|ʻalaa|ḥars̤ikum|ʹiñ|kuñtum|ṣaarimeen."
68,23,"Fañṭalaq̣oo|wa-hum|yatakhaafatoon―"
68,24,"ʹAl|laa|yadkhulannahal|yawma|ʻalaykum|miskeen."
68,25,"Wa-g̣adaw|ʻalaa|ḥardiñ|q̣aadireen."
68,26,"Falammaa|raʹawhaa|q̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|laḍaaalloon:"
68,27,"Bal|naḥnu|maḥroomoon!"
68,28,"Q̣aala|ʹawsaṭuhum|ʹalam|ʹaq̣ul|lakum|law-laa|tusabbiḥoon?"
68,29,"Q̣aaloo|Subḥaana|Rabbinaaa|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|z̤̣aalimeen!"
68,30,"Faʹaq̣bala|baʻḍuhum|ʻalaa|baʻḍiñy|yatalaawamoon."
68,31,"Q̣aaloo|yaa-waylanaaa|ʹinnaa|kunnaa|ṭaag̣een!"
68,32,"ʻAsaa|Rabbunaaa|ʹañy|yubdilanaa|khayram|minhaaa|ʹinnaaa|ʹilaa|Rabbinaa|raag̣iboon!"
68,33,"Kaẓaalikal|ʻAẓaab;|wa-laʻAẓaabul|ʹAakhirati|ʹakbar.|Law|kaanoo|yaʻlamoon!"
68,34,"ʹInna|lil-Muttaq̣eena|ʻiñda|Rabbihim|Jannatin|Naʻeem."
68,35,"ʹAfanajʻalul|Muslimeena|kalmujrimeen?"
68,36,"Maa-|lakum?|kayfa|taḥkumoon?"
68,37,"ʹAm|lakum|Kitaabuñ|feehi|tadrusoon―"
68,38,"ʹInna|lakum|feehi|lamaa|takhayyaroon?"
68,39,"ʹAm|lakum|ʹAymaanun|ʻalaynaa|baalig̣atun|ʹilaa|Yawmil|Q̣iyaamati|ʹinna|lakum|lamaa|taḥkumoon?"
68,40,"Salhum|ʹayyuhum̃|biẓaalika|zaʻeem!"
68,41,"ʹAm|lahum|shurakaaaʹu|fal-yaʹtoo|bishurakaaaʹihim|ʹiñ|kaanoo|ṣaadiq̣een!"
68,42,"Yawma|yukshafu|ʻañ|saaq̣iñw|wayudʻawna|ʹilas|sujoodi|falaa|yastaṭeeʻoon,―"
68,43,"Khaashiʻatan|ʹabṣaaruhum|tarhaq̣uhum|ẓillah:|wa-q̣ad|kaanoo|yudʻawna|ʹilas|sujoodi|wa-hum|saalimoon."
68,44,"Faẓarnee|wa-mañy|yukaẓẓibu|bihaaẓal|Ḥadees̤:|sanastadrijuhum|min|ḥays̤u|laa-|yaʻlamoon."
68,45,"Wa-ʹumlee|lahum:|ʹinna|kaydee|mateen."
68,46,"ʹAm|tasʹaluhum|ʹajrañ|fahum|mim|mag̣ramim|mus̤q̣aloon?"
68,47,"ʹAm|ʻiñdahumul|G̣aybu|fahum|yaktuboon?"
68,48,"Faṣbir|li-Ḥukmi|Rabbika|wa-laa|takuñ|ka-Ṣaaḥibil|Ḥoot.|ʹIẓ|naadaa|wa-huwa|makz̤̣oom."
68,49,"Law-laaa|ʹañ|tadaarakahoo|Niʻmatum|mir|Rabbihee|lanubiẓa|bilʻaraaaʹi|wa-huwa|maẓmoom."
68,50,"Fajtabaahu|Rabbuhoo|fajaʻalahoo|minaṣ|Ṣaaliḥeen."
68,51,"Wa-ʹiñy|yakaadul|laẓeena|kafaroo|layuzliq̣oonaka|biʹabṣaarihim|lammaa|samiʻuẓ|Ẓikra|wa-yaq̣ooloona|ʹinnahoo|lamajnoon!"
68,52,"Wa-maa|huwa|ʹillaa|Ẓikrul|lilʻAalameen."
69,1,"ʹALḤAAAQ̣Q̣ATU!"
69,2,"Mal|Ḥaaaq̣q̣ah?"
69,3,"Wa-maaa|ʹadraaka|mal|Ḥaaaq̣q̣ah?"
69,4,"Kaẓẓabat|S̤amoodu|wa-ʻAadum|bil-Q̣aariʻah!"
69,5,"Faʹammaa|S̤amoodu|faʹuhlikoo|biṭ-Ṭaag̣iyah!"
69,6,"Wa-ʹammaa|ʻAaduñ|faʹuhlikoo|bi-Reeḥiñ|ṣarṣarin|ʻaatiyah;"
69,7,"Sakhkharahaa|ʻalayhim|sabʻa|layaaliñw|was̤amaaniyata|ʹayyaamin|ḥusoomañ|fataral|q̣awma|feehaa|ṣarʻaa|kaʹannahum|ʹaʻjaazu|nakhlin|khaawiyah!"
69,8,"Fahal|taraa|lahum|mim|baaq̣iyah?"
69,9,"Wa-jaaaʹa|Firʻawnu|wa-mañ|q̣ablahoo|wal-muʹtafikaatu|bil-khaaṭiʹah,"
69,10,"Faʻaṣaw|rasoola|Rabbihim|faʹakhaẓahum|ʹakhẓatar|raabiyah."
69,11,"ʹInnaa|lammaa|ṭag̣al|maaaʹu|ḥamalnaakum|fil|jaariyah."
69,12,"Linajʻalahaa|lakum|Taẓkiratañwwa|taʻiyahaaa|ʹuẓunuñw|waaʻiyah."
69,13,"Faʹiẓaa|nufikha|fiṣ|Ṣoori|nafkhatuñw|waaḥidah,"
69,14,"Wa-ḥumilatil|ʹarḍu|wal-jibaalu|fadukkataa|dakkatañw|waaḥidah,―"
69,15,"Fayawmaʹiẓiñw|Waq̣aʻatil|Waaq̣iʻah,"
69,16,"Wañshaq̣q̣atis|samaaaʹu|fahiya|Yawmaʹiẓiñw|waahiyah,"
69,17,"Wal-malaku|ʻalaaa|ʹarjaaaʹihaa,|wa-yaḥmilu|ʻArsha|Rabbika|fawq̣ahum|Yawmaʹiẓiñ|s̤amaaniyah."
69,18,"Yawmaʹiẓiñ|tuʻraḍoona|laa-|takhfaa|miñ-kum|khaafiyah."
69,19,"Faʹammaa|man|ʹootiya|Kitaabahoo|biyameenihee|fayaq̣oolu|haaaʹumuq̣|raʹoo|Kitaabiyah!"
69,20,"ʹInnee|z̤̣anañtu|ʹannee|mulaaq̣in|Ḥisaabiyah!"
69,21,"Fahuwa|fee|ʻeeshatir|raaḍiyah,"
69,22,"Fee|Jannatin|ʻaaliyah,"
69,23,"Q̣utoofuhaa|daaniyah."
69,24,"Kuloo|washraboo|haneeeʹam|bimaaa|ʹaslaftum|fil|ʹayyaamil|khaaliyah!"
69,25,"Wa-ʹammaa|man|ʹootiya|Kitaabahoo|bishimaalihee|fayaq̣oolu|yaalaytanee|lam|ʹoota|Kitaabiyah!"
69,26,"Wa-lam|ʹadri|maa-|ḥisaabiyah!"
69,27,"Yaa-laytahaa|kaanatil|q̣aaḍiyah!"
69,28,"Maaa|ʹag̣naa|ʻannee|maaliyah!"
69,29,"Halaka|ʻannee|sulṭaaniyah!"
69,30,"Khuẓoohu|fag̣ullooh,"
69,31,"S̤ummal|Jaḥeema|ṣallooh,"
69,32,"S̤umma|fee|silsilatiñ|ẓarʻuhaa|sabʻoona|ẓiraaʻañ|faslukooh!"
69,33,"ʹInnahoo|kaana|laa-|yuʹminu|billaahil|ʻAz̤̣eem,"
69,34,"Wa-laa|yaḥuḍḍu|ʻalaa|ṭaʻaamil|miskeen!"
69,35,"Falaysa|lahul|Yawma|haahunaa|ḥameem,"
69,36,"Wa-laa|ṭaʻaamun|ʹillaa|min|g̣isleen,"
69,37,"Laa-|yaʹkuluhooo|ʹillal|khaaṭiʹoon."
69,38,"Falaaa|ʹuq̣simu|bimaa|tubṣiroon"
69,39,"Wamaa|laa-|tubṣiroon,―"
69,40,"ʹInnahoo|laq̣awlu|Rasooliñ|Kareem;"
69,41,"Wa-maa|huwa|biq̣awli|shaaʻir:|q̣aleelam|maa|tuʹminoon!"
69,42,"Wa-laa|biq̣awli|kaahin:|q̣aleelam|maa|taẓakkaroon."
69,43,"Tañzeelum|mir|Rabbil|ʻAalameen."
69,44,"Wa-law|taq̣awwala|ʻalaynaa|baʻḍal|ʹaq̣aaweel,"
69,45,"Laʹakhaẓnaa|minhu|bilyameen,"
69,46,"S̤umma|laq̣aṭaʻnaa|minhul|wateen:"
69,47,"Famaa|miñkum|min|ʹaḥadin|ʻanhu|ḥaajizeen."
69,48,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|la-Taẓkiratul|lil-Muttaq̣een."
69,49,"Wa-ʹinnaa|lanaʻlamu|ʹanna|miñkum|mukaẓẓibeen."
69,50,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|laḥasratun|ʻalal|kaafireen."
69,51,"Wa-ʹinnahoo|la-Ḥaq̣q̣ul|yaq̣een."
69,52,"Fasabbiḥ|bismi|Rabbikal|ʻAz̤̣eem."
70,1,"Saʹala|saaʹilum|biʻAẓaabiñw|waaq̣iʻ―"
70,2,"Lil-kaafireena|laysa|lahoo|daafiʻ,―"
70,3,"Minal|laahi|Ẓil|MAʻAARIJ."
70,4,"Taʻrujul|malaaaʹikatu|war-Rooḥu|ʹilayhi|fee|Yawmiñ|kaana|miq̣daaruhoo|khamseena|ʹalfa|sanah:"
70,5,"Faṣbir|Ṣabrañ|jameelaa."
70,6,"ʹInnahum|yarawnahoo|baʻeedaa:"
70,7,"Wa-naraahu|q̣areebaa."
70,8,"Yawma|takoonus|samaaaʹu|kalmuhl,"
70,9,"Wa-takoonul|jibaalu|kalʻihn,"
70,10,"Wa-laa|yasʹalu|ḥameemun|ḥameemaa,"
70,11,"Yubaṣṣaroonahum,:|yawaddul|mujrimu|law|yaftadee|min|ʻAẓaabi|Yawmiʹiẓim|bibaneeh,"
70,12,"Wa-ṣaaḥibatihee|wa-ʹakheeh,"
70,13,"Wa-faṣeelatihil|latee|tuʹweeh,"
70,14,"Wa-mañ|fil|ʹarḍi|jameeʻañ|s̤umma|yuñjeeh:"
70,15,"Kallaa!|ʹinnahaa|laz̤̣aa!"
70,16,"Nazzaaʻatal|lishshawaa!"
70,17,"Tadʻoo|man|ʹadbara|wa-tawallaa,"
70,18,"Wa-jamaʻa|faʹawʻaa!"
70,19,"ʹInnal|ʹiñsaana|khuliq̣a|halooʻaa;―"
70,20,"ʹIẓaa|massahush|sharru|jazooʻaa;"
70,21,"Wa-ʹiẓaa|massahul|khayru|manooʻaa;―"
70,22,"ʹIllal|Muṣalleen;―"
70,23,"ʹAllaẓeena|hum|ʻalaa|Ṣalaatihim|daaaʹimoon;"
70,24,"Wallaẓeena|feee|ʹamwaalihim|ḥaq̣q̣um|maʻloom"
70,25,"Lissaaaʹili|walmaḥroom;"
70,26,"Wallaẓeena|yuṣaddiq̣oona|bi-Yawmid|Deen;"
70,27,"Wallaẓeena|hum|min|ʻazaabi|Rabbihim|mushfiq̣oon,―"
70,28,"ʹInna|ʻaẓaaba|Rabbihim|g̣ayru|maʹ-moon;―"
70,29,"Wallaẓeena|hum|lifuroojihim|ḥaafiz̤̣oon,"
70,30,"ʹIllaa|ʻalaaa|ʹazwaajihim|ʹaw|maa-|malakat|ʹaymaanuhum|faʹinnahum|g̣ayru|maloomeen,"
70,31,"Famanib|tag̣aa|waraaaʹa|ẓaalika|faʹulaaaʹika|humul|ʻaadoon;―"
70,32,"Wallaẓeena|hum|liʹamaanaatihim|wa-ʻahdihim|raaʻoon."
70,33,"Wallaẓeena|hum̃|bishahaadaatihim|q̣aaaʹimoon;"
70,34,"Wallaẓeena|hum|ʻalaa|Ṣalaatihim|yuḥaafiz̤̣oon;―"
70,35,"ʹUlaaaʹika|fee|Jannaatim|mukramoon."
70,36,"Famaa|lil-laẓeena|kafaroo|q̣ibalaka|muhṭiʻeen―"
70,37,"ʻAnil|yameeni|wa-ʻanish|shimaali|ʻizeen?"
70,38,"ʹAyaṭmaʻu|kullum|riʹim|minhum|ʹañy|yudkhala|Jannata|Naʻeem?"
70,39,"Kallaa!|ʹInnaa|khalaq̣naahum|mimmaa|yaʻlamoon!"
70,40,"Falaaa|ʹuq̣simu|bi-Rabbil|Mashaariq̣i|wal-Mag̣aaribi|ʹinnaa|la-Q̣aadiroon."
70,41,"ʻAlaaa|ʹan|nubaddila|khayram|minhum|wa-maa|Naḥnu|bimasbooq̣een."
70,42,"Faẓarhum|yakhooḍoo|wa-yalʻaboo|ḥattaa|yulaaq̣oo|Yawmahumul|laẓee|yooʻadoon!"
70,43,"Yawma|yakhrujoona|minal|ʹajdaas̤i|siraaʻañ|kaʹannahum|ʹilaa|nuṣubiñy|yoofiḍoon,―"
70,44,"Khaashiʻatan|ʹabṣaaruhum|tarhaq̣uhum|ẓillah!|Ẓaalikal|Yawmul|laẓee|kaanoo|yooʻadoon!"
71,1,"ʹInnaaa|ʹarsalnaa|Nooḥan|ʹilaa|Q̣awmiheee|ʹan|ʹañẓir|Q̣awmaka|miñ|q̣abli|ʹañy|yaʹtiyahum|ʻAẓaabun|ʹaleem,"
71,2,"Q̣aala|yaa-Q̣awmi|ʹinnee|lakum|Naẓeerum|mubeen:"
71,3,"ʹAniʻ|budul|laaha|wattaq̣oohu|wa-ʹaṭeeʻoon:"
71,4,"Yag̣fir|lakum|miñ|ẓunoobikum|wa-yuʹakhkhirukum|ʹilaaa|ʹAjalim|Musammaa:|ʹinna|ʹAjalal|laahi|ʹiẓaa|jaaaʹa|laa-|yuʹakhkhar,|Law|kuñtum|taʻlamoon."
71,5,"Q̣aala|Rabbi|ʹinnee|daʻawtu|Q̣awmee|laylañw|wanahaaraa:"
71,6,"Falam|yazidhum|duʻaaaʹeee|ʹillaa|firaaraa."
71,7,"Wa-ʹinnee|kullamaa|daʻawtuhum|litag̣fira|lahum|jaʻalooo|ʹaṣaabiʻahum|feee|ʹaaẓaanihim|wastag̣shaw|s̤iyaabahum|wa-ʹaṣarroo|wastakbarus|tikbaaraa,"
71,8,"S̤umma|ʹinnee|daʻawtuhum|jihaaraa;"
71,9,"S̤umma|ʹinneee|ʹaʻlañtu|lahum|wa-ʹasrartu|lahum|ʹisraaraa,"
71,10,"Faq̣ultus|tag̣firoo|Rabbakum;|ʹinnahoo|kaana|G̣affaaraa;"
71,11,"Yursilis|samaaaʹa|ʻalaykum|midraaraa;"
71,12,"Wa-yumdidkum̃|biʹamwaaliñw|wabaneena|wa-yajʻal|lakum|Jannaatiñw|Wa yajʻal|lakum|ʹanhaaraa."
71,13,"Maa-|lakum|laa-|tarjoona|lillaahi|wa-q̣aaraa,―"
71,14,"Wa-q̣ad|khalaq̣akum|ʹaṭwaaraa?"
71,15,"ʹAlam|taraw|kayfa|khalaq̣al|laahu|sabʻa|samaawaatiñ|ṭibaaq̣aa,"
71,16,"Wa-jaʻalal|q̣amara|feehinna|noorañw|wajaʻalash|shamsa|Siraajaa?"
71,17,"Wallaahu|ʹambatakum|minal|ʹarḍi|nabaataa,"
71,18,"S̤umma|yuʻeedukum|feehaa|wa-yukhrijukum|ʹikhraajaa?"
71,19,"Wallaahu|jaʻala|lakumul|ʹarḍa|bisaaṭaa,"
71,20,"Litaslukoo|minhaa|subulañ|fijaajaa."
71,21,"Q̣aala|Nooḥur|Rabbi|ʹinnahum|ʻaṣawnee|wattabaʻoo|mal|lam|yazidhu|maaluhoo|wa-waladuhooo|ʹillaa|khasaaraa."
71,22,"Wa-makaroo|Makrañ|kubbaaraa."
71,23,"Waq̣aaloo|laa-|taẓarunna|ʹaalihatakum|wa-laa|taẓarunna|Waddañw|Walaa|Suwaaʻaa,|wa-laa|Yag̣oos̤a|wa-Yaʻooq̣a|wa-Nasraa;―"
71,24,"Wa-q̣ad|ʹaḍalloo|kas̤eeraa;|wa-laa|tazidiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|ʹillaa|ḍalaalaa."
71,25,"Mimmaa|khaṭeeeʹaatihim|ʹug̣riq̣oo|faʹudkhiloo|Naaraa:|falam|yajidoo|lahum|miñ|doonil|laahi|ʹañṣaaraa."
71,26,"Wa-q̣aala|Nooḥur|Rabbi|laa-|taẓar|ʻalal|ʹarḍi|minal|kaafireena|dayyaaraa!"
71,27,"ʹInnaka|ʹiñ|taẓarhum|yuḍilloo|ʻibaadaka|wa-laa|yalidooo|ʹillaa|faajirañ|kaffaaraa."
71,28,"Rabbig̣|fir|lee|wa-li-waalidayya|wa-limañ|dakhala|baytiya|Muʹminañw|Walil-Muʹmineena|wal-Muʹminaat:|wa-laa|tazidiz̤̣|z̤̣aalimeena|ʹillaa|tabaaraa!"
72,1,"Q̣ul|ʹooḥiya|ʹilayya|ʹanna|hustamaʻa|nafarum|minal|Jinni|faq̣aalooo|ʹinnaa|samiʻnaa|Q̣urʹaanan|ʻajabaa,"
72,2,"Yahdeee|ʹilar|Rushdi|faʹaamannaa|bih:|wa-lan|nushrika|bi-Rabbinaaa|ʹaḥadaa."
72,3,"Wa-ʹannahoo|Taʻaalaa|Jaddu|Rabbinaa|mat|takhaẓa|ṣaaḥibatañw|walaa|waladaa."
72,4,"Wa-ʹannahoo|kaana|yaq̣oolu|safeehunaa|ʻal|allaahi|shaṭaṭaa;"
72,5,"Wa-ʹannaa|z̤̣anannaaa|ʹal|lañ|taq̣oolal|ʹiñsu|wal-jinnu|ʻal|allaahi|kaẓibaa."
72,6,"Wa-ʹannahoo|kaana|rijaalum|minal|ʹiñsi|yaʻooẓoona|birijaalim|minal|Jinni|fazaadoohum|rahaq̣aa."
72,7,"Wa-ʹannahum|z̤̣annoo|kamaa|z̤̣anañtum|ʹal|lañy|yabʻas̤al|laahu|ʹaḥadaa."
72,8,"Wa-ʹannaa|lamasnas|samaaaʹa|fawajadnaahaa|muliʹat|ḥarasañ|shadeedañw|washuhubaa."
72,9,"Wa-ʹannaa|kunnaa|naq̣ʻudu|minhaa|maq̣aaʻida|lissamʻ;|famañy|yastamiʻil|ʹaana|yajid|lahoo|shihaabar|raṣadaa."
72,10,"Waʹannaa|laa-|nadreee|ʹasharrun|ʹureeda|bimañ|fil|ʹarḍi|ʹam|ʹaraada|bihim|Rabbuhum|rashadaa."
72,11,"Wa-ʹannaa|minnaṣ|ṣaaliḥoona|wa-minnaa|doona|ẓaalik:|kunnaa|ṭaraaaʹiq̣a|q̣idadaa."
72,12,"Wa-ʹannaa|z̤̣anannaaa|ʹal|lan|nuʻjizal|laaha|fil|ʹarḍi|wa-lan|nuʻjizahoo|harabaa."
72,13,"Wa-ʹannaa|lammaa|samiʻnal|Hudaaa|ʹaamannaa|bih.|Famañy|yuʹmim|bi-Rabbihee|falaa|yakhaafu|bakhsañw|walaa|rahaq̣aa."
72,14,"Wa-ʹannaa|minnal|Muslimoona|wa-minnal|Q̣aasiṭoon.|Faman|ʹaslama|faʹulaaaʹika|taḥarraw|rashadaa."
72,15,"Wa-ʹammal|Q̣aasiṭoona|fakaanoo|li-Jahannama|ḥaṭabaa―"
72,16,"Wa-ʹalla-wis|taq̣aamoo|ʻalaṭ|Ṭareeq̣ati|laʹasq̣aynaahum|maaaʹan|g̣adaq̣aa."
72,17,"Linaftinahum|feeh.|Wa-mañy|yuʻriḍ|ʻañ|Ẓikri|Rabbihee|yaslukhu|ʻAẓaabañ|ṣaʻadaa."
72,18,"Wa-ʹannal|Masaajida|lil-laahi|falaa|tadʻoo|maʻal|laahi|ʹaḥadaa;"
72,19,"Wa-ʹannahoo|lammaa|q̣aama|ʻAbdul|laahi|yadʻoohu|kaadoo|yakoonoona|ʻalayhi|libadaa."
72,20,"Q̣ul|ʹinnamaaa|ʹadʻoo|Rabbee|wa-laaa|ʹushriku|biheee|ʹaḥadaa."
72,21,"Q̣ul|ʹinnee|laaa|ʹamliku|lakum|ḍarrañw|walaa|rashadaa."
72,22,"Q̣ul|ʹinnee|lañy|yujeeranee|minal|laahi|ʹaḥad,|wa-lan|ʹajida|miñ|doonihee|multaḥadaa,"
