76,10,"ʹInnaa|nakhaafu|mir|Rabbinaa|Yawman|ʻaboosañ|q̣amṭareeraa."
76,11,"Fawaq̣aahumul|laahu|sharra|ẓaalikal|Yawmi|wa-laq̣q̣aahum|naḍratañw|wasurooraa."
76,12,"Wa-jazaahum̃|bimaa|ṣabaroo|Jannatañw|Waḥareeraa."
76,13,"Muttakiʹeena|feehaa|ʻalal|ʹaraaaʹik,|laa-|yarawna|feehaa|shamsañw|walaa|zamhareeraa."
76,14,"Wa-daaniyatan|ʻalayhim|z̤̣ilaaluhaa|wa-ẓullilat|q̣uṭoofuhaa|taẓleelaa."
76,15,"Wa-yuṭaafu|ʻalayhim̃|biʹaaniyatim|miñ|fiḍḍatiñw|waʹakwaabiñ|kaanat|q̣awaareeraa,―"
